pravizya tu mahAraNyaM daNDakAraNyamAtmavAn . rAmo dadarza durdharSastApasAzramamaNDalam . kuzacIraparikSiptaM brAhmalakSmyA samAvRtam . yathA pradIptaM durdarza gagane sUryamaNDalam . zaraNyaM sarvabhUtAnAM susaMmRSTAjiraM sadA . mRgairbahubhirAkIrNaM pakSisaMdhaiH samAvRtam . pUjitaM copanRttaM ca nityamapsarasa gaNaiH . vizAlairagnizaraNaiH sragbhANDairajinaiH kuzaiH . samidbhistoyakalazaiH phalamUlaizca zobhitam . AraNyaizca mahAvRkSaiH puNyaiH svAduphalairvRtam . balihomArcitaM puNyaM brahmaghoSaninAditam . puSpaizcAnyaiH parikSiptaM padminyA ca sapAyA . phalamUlAzanairdAntaizcIrakRSNAjinAmbaraiH . sUryavaizvAnarAbhaizca purANairmunibhiryutam .7 . .
puNyaizca niyatAhAraiH zobhitaM paramarSibhiH . tadbrahmabhavanaprakhyaM brahmaghoSaninAditam . brahmavidbhirmahAbhAgaiAhmaNairupazobhitam . tad dRSTvA rAghavaH zrImAMstApasAzramamaNDalam . abhyagacchanmahAtejA vijyaM kRtvA mahad dhanuH .
divyajJAnopapannAste rAmaM dRSTvA maharSayaH . abhijagmustadA prItA vaidehIM ca yazasvinIm . te tu somamivodyantaM dRSTvA vai dharmacAriNam . lakSmaNaM caiva dRSTvA tu vaidehIM ca yazasvinIm . maGgalAni prayuJjAnAH pratyagRhNandRDhavratAH .
rUpasaMhananaM lakSmI saukumAryaM suveSatAm . dadRzurvismitAkArA rAmasya vanavAsinaH .
vaidehI lakSmaNaM rAmaM netrairanimiSairiva . AzcaryabhUtAndadRzuH sarve te vanavAsinaH .
atrainaM hi mahAbhAgAH sarvabhUtahite ratAH . atithiM parNazAlAyAM rAghavaM saMnyavezayan .
tato rAmasya satkRtya vidhinA pAvakopamAH . Ajahuste mahAbhAgAH salalaM dharmacAriNaH .
maGgalAni prayuJjAnA mudA paramayA yutAH . mUlaM puSpaM phalaM sarvamAzramaM ca mahAtmanaH . nivedayitvA dharmajJAste tu prAJjalayo ' bruvan . dharmapAlo janasyAsya zaraNyazca mahAyazAH . pUjanIyazca mAnyazca rAjA daNDadharo guruH . indrasyaiva caturbhAgaH prajA rakSati rAghavaH . rAjA tasmAd varAn bhogAn ramyAn bhuGkte namaskRtaH .
te vayaM bhavatA rakSyA bhavadviSayavAsinaH . nagarastho vanastho vA tvaM no rAjA janezvaraH .
nyastadaNDA vayaM rAjaJjitakrodhA jitendriyAH . rakSaNIyAstvayA zazvad garbhabhUtAstapodhanAH .
evamuktvA phalairmUlaiH puSpairanyaizca rAghavam . vanyaizca vividhAhAraiH salakSmaNamapUjayan .
tathAnye tApasAH siddhA rAmaM vaizvAnaropamAH . nyAvRtA yathAnyAyaM tarpayAmAsurIzvaram .
tamuktavantaM vaidehaM vizvAmitro mahAmuniH . uvAca vacanaM vIraM vasiSThasahito nRpam .
acintyAnyaprameyANi kulAni narapuGgava . ikSvAkUNAM videhAnAM naiSAM tulyo ' sti kazcana .
sadRzo dharmasambandhaH sadRzo rUpasampadA . rAmalakSmaNayo rAjan sItA cormilayA saha .
vaktavyaM ca narazreSTha zrUyatAM vacanaM mama . bhrAtA yavIyAn dharmajJa eSa rAjA kuzadhvajaH . asya dharmAtmano rAjan rUpeNApratimaM bhuvi . sutAdvayaM narazreSTha patnyarthaM varayAmahe . bharatasya kumArasya zatrughnasya ca dhImataH . varaye te sute rAjaMstayorarthe mahAtmanoH .
putrA dazarathasyeme rUpayauvanazAlinaH . lokapAlasamAH sarve devatulyaparAkramAH .7 . .
ubhayorapi rAjendra sambandhenAnubadhyatAm . ikSvAkukulamavyagraM bhavataH puNyakarmaNaH .
vizvAmitravacaH zrutvA vasiSThasya mate tadA . janakaH prAJjalirvAkyamuvAca munipuGgavau .
kulaM dhanyamidaM manye yeSAM tau munipuGgavau . sadRzaM kulasambandhaM yadAjJApayataH svayam .
evaM bhavatu bhadraM vaH kuzadhvajasute ime . patnyau bhajetAM sahitau zatrughnabharatAbubhau .
ekAhvA rAjaputrINAM catasRNAM mahAmune . pANIn gRhNantu catvAro rAjaputrA mahAbalAH .
uttare divase brahman phalgunIbhyAM manISiNaH . vaivAhikaM prazaMsanti bhago yatra prajApatiH .
evamuktvA vacaH saumyaM pratyutthAya kRtAJjaliH . ubhau munivarau rAjA janako vAkyamabravIt .
paro dharmaH kRto mahyaM ziSyo ' smi bhavatostathA . imAnyAsanamukhyAni AsyatAM munipuGgavau .
yathA dazarathasyeyaM tathAyodhyA purI mama . prabhutve nAsti saMdeho yathArha kartumarhatha .
tathA bruvati vaidehe janake raghunandanaH . rAjA dazaratho hRSTaH pratyuvAca mahIpatim .
yuvAmasaMkhyeyaguNau bhrAtarau mithilezvarau . RSayo rAjasaGghAzca bhavadbhayAmabhipUjitAH .
svasti prApnuhi bhadraM te gamiSyAmaH svamAlayam . zrAddhakarmANi vidhivadvidhAsya iti cAbravIt .
tamApRSTvA narapatiM rAjA dazarathastadA . munIndrau tau puraskRtya jagAmAzu mahAyazAH .
sa gatvA nilayaM rAjA zrAddhaM kRtvA vidhAnataH . prabhAte kAlyamutthAya cakre godAnamuttamam .
gavAM zatasahasraM ca brAhmaNebhyo narAdhipaH . ekaikazo dadau rAjA putrAnuddizya dharmataH .
suvarNazRGgyaH sampannAH savatsAH kAMsyadohanAH . gavAM zatasahasrANi catvAri puruSarSabhaH . vittamanyacca subahu dvijebhyo raghunandanaH . dadau godAnamuddizya putrANAM putravatsalaH .
sa sutaiH kRtagodAnairvRtaH sannRpatistadA . lokapAlairivAbhAti vRtaH saumyaH prajApatiH .
saptadhA tu kRte garbhe ditiH paramaduHkhitA . sahasrAkSaM durAdharSaM vAkyaM sAnunayAbravIt .
mamAparAdhAd garbho ' yaM saptadhA zakalIkRtaH . nAparAdho hi deveza tavAtra balasUdana .
priyaM tvatkRtamicchAmi mama garbhaviparyaye . marutAM sapta saptAnAM sthAnapAlA bhavantu te .
vAtaskandhA ime sapta carantu divi putraka . mArutA iti vikhyAtA divyarUpA mamAtmajAH .
brahmalokaM caratveka indralokaM tathAparaH . divyavAyuriti khyAtastRtIyo ' pi mahAyazAH .
catvArastu surazreSTha dizo vai tava zAsanAt . saMcariSyanti bhadraM te kAlena hi mamAtmajAH . tvatkRtenaiva nAmnA vai mArutA iti vizrutAH .
tasyAstad vacanaM zrutvA sahasrAkSaH puraMdaraH . uvAca prAJjalirvAkyamitIdaM balasUdanaH .
sarvametad yathoktaM te bhaviSyati na saMzayaH . vicariSyanti bhadraM te devarUpAstavAtmajAH .
evaM tau nizcayaM kRtvA mAtAputrau tapovane . jagmatustridivaM rAma kRtArthAviti naH zrutam .
eSa dezaH sa kAkutstha mahendrAdhyuSitaH purA . ditiM yatra tapaHsiddhAmevaM paricacAra saH .
ikSvAkostu naravyAghra putraH paramadhArmikaH . alambuSAyAmutpanno vizAla iti vizrutaH . tena cAsIdiha sthAne vizAleti purI kRtA .
vizAlasya suto rAma hemacandro mahAbalaH . sucandra iti vikhyAto hemacandrAdanantaraH .
sucandratanayo rAma dhUmrAzva iti vizrutaH . dhUmrAzvatanayazcApi sRJjayaH samapadyata .
sRJjayasya sutaH zrImAn sahadevaH pratApavAn . kuzAzvaH sahadevasya putraH paramadhArmikaH .
kuzAzvasya mahAtejAH somadattaH pratApavAn . somadattasya putrastu kAkutstha iti vizrutaH . tasya putro mahAtejAH sampratyeSa purImimAm . Avasat paramaprakhyaH sumati ma durjayaH .
ikSvAkostu prasAdena sarve vaizAlikA nRpAH . dIrghAyuSo mahAtmAno vAryavantaH sudhArmikAH .
ihAdya rajanImekAM sukhaM svapsyAmahe vayam . zvaH prabhAte narazreSTha janakaM draSTumarhasi .
sumatistu mahAtejA vizvAmitramupAgatam . zrutvA naravarazreSThaH pratyAgacchanmahAyazAH .
pUjAM ca paramAM kRtvA sopAdhyAyaH sabAndhavaH . prAJjaliH kuzalaM pRSTvA vizvAmitramathAbravIt .
dhanyo ' smyanugRhIto ' smi yasya me viSayaM mune . samprApto darzanaM caiva nAsti dhanyataro mama .
evamasmi tadA muktaH kathaMcit tena saMyuge . idAnImapi yad vRttaM tacchRNuSva yaduttaram .
rAkSasAbhyAmahaM dvAbhyAmanirviNNastathAkRtaH . sahito mRgarUpAbhyAM praviSTo daNDakAvane .
dIptajihvo mahAdaMSTrastIkSNazRGgo mahAbalaH . vyacaran daNDakAraNyaM mAMsabhakSo mahAmRgaH . agnihotreSu tIrtheSu caityavRkSeSu rAvaNa . atyantaghoro vyacaraMstApasAMstAn pradharSayan . nihatya daNDakAraNye tApamAn dharmacAriNaH . rudhirANi pibaMsteSAM tanmAsAni ca bhakSayan .
RSimAMsAzanaH krUrastrAsayan vanagocarAn . tadA rudhiramatto ' haM vacaraM daNDakAvanam .
tadAhaM daNDakAraNye vicaran dharmadUSakaH . AsAdayaM tadA rAmaM tApasaM dharmamAzritam . vaidehIM ca mahAbhAgAM lakSmaNaM ca mahAratham . tApasaM niyatAhAraM sarvabhUtahite ratam .
so ' haM vanagataM rAmaM paribhUya mahAbalam . tApaso ' yamiti jJAtvA pUrvavairamanusmaran . abhyadhAvaM susaMkruddhastIkSNazRGgo mRgAkRtiH . jighAMsurakRtaprajJastaM prahAramanusmaran .
tena tyaktAzrayo bANAH zitAH zatrunivarhaNAH . vikRSya sumahaccApaM suparNAnilatulyagAH . te bANA vajrasaMkAzAH sughorA raktabhojanAH . AjagmuH sahitAH sarve trayaH saMnataparvaNaH .
parAkramajJo rAmasya zaTho dRSTabhayaH purA . samutkrAntastato muktastAvubhau rAkSasau hatau .
zareNa mukto rAmasya kathaMcit prApya jIvitam . iha pravrAjito yuktastApaso ' haM samAhitaH .
vRkSe vRkSe hi pazyAmi cIrakRSNAjinAmbaram . gRhItadhanuSaM rAmaM pAzahastamivAntakam .
api rAmasahasrANi bhItaH pazyAmi rAvaNa . rAmabhUtamidaM sarvamaraNyaM pratibhAti me .
romameva hi pazyAmi rahite rAkSasezvara . dRSTvA svapnagataM rAmamuddhamAmIva cetanaH .
rakArAdIni nAmAni rAmatrastasya rAvaNa . ratnAni ca rathAzcaiva vitrAsaM janayanti me .
ahaM tasya prabhAvajJo na yuddhaM tena te kSamam . baliM vA namuciM vApi hanyAddhi raghunandanaH .
raNe rAmeNa yudhyasva kSamA vA kuru rAvaNa . na te rAmakathA kAryA yati mAM draSTumicchasi .
bahavaH sAdhavo loke yuktA dharmamanuSThitAH . pareSAmaparAdhena vinaSTAH saparicchadAH .
so ' haM parAparAdhema vinazeyaM nizAcara . kuru yat te kSamaM tattvamahaM tvAM nAnuyAmi vai .
rAmazca hi mahAtejA mahAsattvo mahAbalaH . api rAkSasalokasya bhavedantakaro ' pi hi .
yadi zUrpaNakhAhetorjanasthAnagataH kharaH . ativRtto hataH pUrvaM rAmeNakliSTakarmaNA . atra brUhi yathAtatvaM ko rAmasya vayatikramaH .
idaM vaco bandhuhitArthinA mayA yathocyamAnaM yadi nAbhipatsyase . sabAndhavastyakSyasi jIvitaM raNe hato ' dya rAmeNa zarairajihmagaiH .
sa tadA vAlinaM hatvA sugrIvamabhiSicya ca . vasan mAlyavataH pRSThe rAmo lakSmaNamabravIt .
ayaM sa kAlaH samprAptaH samayo ' dya jalAgamaH . sampazya tvaM nabho meghaiH saMvRtaM girisaMnibhaiH .
navamAsadhRtaM garbhe bhAskarasya gabhastibhiH . pItvA rasaM samudrANAM dyauH prasUte rasAyanam .
zakyamambaramAruhya meghasopAnapaMktibhiH . kuTajArjunamAlAbhiralaMkartuM divAkaraH .
saMdhyArAgotthitaistAnairanteSvapi ca pANDubhiH . snigdhairabhrapaTacchedairbaddhavraNamivAmbaram .
mandamArutani : zvAsaM saMdhyAcandanaraJjitam . ApANDujaladaM bhAti kAmAturamivAmbaram .
eSA dharmaparikliSTA navavAripariplutA . sIteva zokasaMtaptA mahI vASpaM vimuJcati .
meghodaravinirmuktAH karpUradalazItalAH . zakyamaJjalibhiH pAtuM vAtAH ketakagandhinaH .
eSa phullArjunaH zailaH ketakairabhivAsitaH . sugrIva iva zAntArirdhArAbhirabhiSicyate .
meghakRSNAjinadharA dhArAyajJopavItinaH . mArutApUritaguhAH prAdhItA iva parvatAH .
kazAbhiriva haimIbhirvidyudbhirabhitADitam . antastanitanirghoSaM savedanamivAmbaram .
nIlameghAzritA vidyut sphurantI pratibhAti me . sphurantI rAvaNasyAGke vaidehIva tapasvinI .
imAstA manmathavatAM hitAH pratihatA dizaH . anuliptA iva ghanairnaSTagrahanizAkarAH .
kvacid bASpAbhisaMruddhAn varSAgamasamutsukAn . kuTajAn pazya saumitre puSpitAn girisAnuSu . mama zokAbhibhUtasya kAmasaMdIpamAn sthitAn .
nidAghadoSaprasarAH prazAntAH . sthitA hi yAtrA vasudhAdhipAnAM pravAsino yAnti narAH svadezAn .
samprasthitA mAnasavAsalubdhAH priyAnvitAH samprati cakravAkAH . abhIkSNavarSodakavikSateSu yAnAni mArgeSu na sampatanti .
kvacit prakAzaM kvacidaprakAzaM nabhaH prakIrNAmbudharaM bibhAti . kvacikvacit parvatasaMniruddhaM rUpaM yathA zAntamahArNavasya .
navaM jalaM parvatadhAtutAmram . mayUrakekAbhiranuprayAtaM zailApagAH zIghrataraM vahanti .
rasAkulaM SaTpadasaMnikAzaM prabhujyate jambuphalaM prakAmam . anekavarNaM pavanAvadhUtaM bhUmau patatyAmaphalaM vipakvam .
vidyutpatAkAH sabalAkamAlAH zailendrakUTAkRtisaMnikAzAH . garjanti meghAH samudIrNanAdA mattA gajendrA iva saMyugasthAH .
varSodakApyAyitazAdvalAni pravRttanRttotsavabarhiNAni . vanAni nirvRSTabalAhakAni pazyAparAhveSvadhikaM vibhAnti .
samudvahantaH salilAtibhAraM balAkino vAridharA nadantaH . mahatsu zRGgeSu mahIdharANAM vizramya vizramya punaH prayAnti .
meghAbhikAmA parisampatantI sammoditA bhAti balAkapaMktiH . vAtAvadhUtA varapauNDarIkI lambeva mAlA rucirAmbarasya .
bAlendragopAntaracitritena vibhAti bhUmirnavazAdvalena . gAtrAnupRktena zukraprabheNa nArIva lAkSokSitakambalena .
nidrA zanaiH kezavamabhyupaiti dutaM nadI sAgaramabhyupaiti . hRSTA balAkA dhanamabhyupaiti kAntA sakAmA priyamabhyupaiti .
jAtA vanAntAH zikhisupranRttA jAtAH kadambAH sakadambazAkhAH . jAtA vRSA goSu samAnakAmA jAtA mahI sasyavanAbhirAmA .
vahanti varSanti nadanti bhAnti dhyAyanti nRtyanti samAzvasanti . nadyo ghanA mattagajA vanAntAH priyAvihInAH zikhinaH plavaGgamAH .
mAghrAya mattA vananijhareSu . prapAtazabdAkulitA gajendrAH sArdhaM mayUraiH samadA nadanti .
dhArAnipAtairabhihanyamAnAH kadambazAkhAsu vilambamAnAH . kSaNArjitaM zanairmadaM SaTcaraNAstyajanti . puSparasAvagADhaM
aGgAracUrNotkarasaMnikAzaiH phalaiH suparyAptarasaiH samRddhaiH . jambUdumANAM pravibhAnti zAkhA nipIyamAnA iva SaTpadaughaiH .
mudIrNagambhIramahAravANAm . vibhAnti rUpANi balAhakAnAM raNotsukAnAmiva vAraNAnAm .
mArgAnugaH zailavanAnusArI samprasthito megharavaM nizamya . yuddhAbhikAmaH pratinAdazaGkI matto gajendraH pratisaMnivRttaH .
kvacit pragItA iva SaTpadauthaiH kvacit prartRttA iva nIlakaNThaiH . vibhAntyanekAzrayiNo vanAntAH .
kadambasarjArjunakandalADhyA vanAntabhUmirmadhuvAripUrNA . rApAnabhUmipratimA vibhAti .
muktAsamAbhaM salilaM patad vai sunirmalaM patrapuTeSu lagnam . hRSTA vivarNacchadanA vihaMgAH surendradattaM tRSitAH pibanti .
SaTpAdatantrImadhurAbhidhAnaM plavaGgamodIritakaNThatAlam . vaneSu saMgItamiva pravRttam .
kvacit pranRttaiH kvacidunnadadbhiH kacicca vRkSAgraniSNakAyaiH . vaneSu saMgItamiva pravRttam .
svanairghanAnAM plavagAH prabuddhA vihAya nidrAM cirasaMniruddhAm . anekarUpAkRtivarNanAdA navAmbudhArAbhihatA nadanti .
staTAni zIrNAnyapavAhayitvA . dRtaM svabhartAramupopayanti .
nIleSu nIlA navavAripUrNA megheSu meghAH pratibhAnti saktAH . davAgnidagdheSu davAgnidagdhAH zaileSu zailA iva baddhamUlAH .
pramattasaMnAditabarhiNAni sazakragopAkulazAdvalAni . caranti nIpArjunavAsitAni gajAH suramyANi vanAntarANi .
navAmbudhArAhatakesarANi dhruvaM pariSvajya saroruhANi . kadambapuSpANi sakesarANi navAni hRSTA bhramarAH pibanti .
mattA gajendrA muditA gavendrA vaneSu vikrAntatarA mRgendrAH . ramyA nagendrA nibhRtA narendrAH prakIDitI vAridharaiH surendraH .
meghAH samudbhUtasamudra nAdA mahAjalaughairgaganAvalambAH . mahIM ca kRtsnAmapavAhayanti .
varSapravegA vipulAH patanti pravAnti vAtAH samudIrNavegAH . pranaSTakUlAH pravahanti zIghra nadyo jalaM vipratipannamArgAH .
narainarendrA iva parvatendrAH surendradattaiH pavanopanItaiH . ghanAmbukumbhairabhiSicyamAnA rUpaM zriyaM svAmiva darzayanti .
ghanopagUDhaM gaganaM na tArA na bhAskaro darzanamabhyupaiti . navairjalaughairdharaNI vitRptA tamoviliptA na dizaH prakAzAH .
mahAnti kUTAni mahIdharANAM dhArAvidhautAnyadhikaM vibhAnti . muktAkalApairiva lambamAnaiH .
zailopalapraskhalamAnavegAH zailottamAnAM vipulAH prapAtAH . guhAsu saMnAditabarhiNAsu hArA vikIryanta ivAvabhAnti .
zIghrapravegA vipulAH prapAtA nirdhAtazRGgopatalA girINAm . muktAkalApapratimAH patanto mahAguhotsaGgatalaidhriyante .
suratAmardavicchinnAH svargastrIhAramauktikAH . patanti cAtulA dikSu toyadhArAH samantataH .
vilIyamAnairvihagainimIladbhizca paGkajaiH . vikasantyA ca mAlatyA gato ' staM jJAyate raviH .
vRttA yAtrA narendrANAM senA pathyeva vartate . vairANi caiva mArgAzca salilena samIkRtAH .
mAsi prauSThapade brahma brAhmaNAnAM vivakSatAm . ayamadhyAyasamayaH sAmagAnAmupasthitaH .
vivRttakamAyatano nUnaM saMcitasaMcayaH . ASADhImabhyupagato bharataH kosalAdhipaH .
nUnamApUryamANAyAH sarayvA vardhate rayaH . mAM samIkSya samAyAntamayodhyAyA iva svanaH .
imAH sphItaguNA varSAH sugrIvaH sukhamaznute . vijitAriH sadArazca rAjye mahati ca sthitaH .
ahaM tu hRtadArazca rAjyAcca mahatazcyutaH . nadIkUlamiva klinnamavasIdAmi lakSmaNa .
zokazca mama vistIrNo varSAzca bhRzadurgamAH . rAvaNazca mahAJchatrurapAraH pratibhAti me .
ayAtrAM caiva dRSTvemAM mArgAzca bhRzadurgamAn . praNate caiva sugrIve na mayA kiMcidIritam .
api cApi parikliSTaM cirAd dAraiH samAgatam . AtmakAryagarIyastvAd vaktuM necchAmi vAnaram .
svayameva hi vizramya jJAtvA kAlamupAgatam . upakAraM ca sugrIvo vetsyate nAtra saMzayaH .
tasmAt kAlapratIkSo ' haM sthito ' smi zubhalakSaNa . sugrIvasya nadInAM ca prasAdamabhikAGkSayan .
upakAreNa vIro hi pratIkAreNa yujyate . akRtajJo ' pratikRto hanti sattvavatAM manaH .
athaivamuktaH praNidAya lakSmaNaH kRtAJjalistat pratipUjya bhASitam . uvAca rAmaM svabhirAmadarzanaM pradarzayan darzanamAtmanaH zubham .
yaduktametat tava sarvamIpsitaM narendra kartA nacirAddharIzvaraH . zaratpratIkSaH kSamatAmidaM bhavAn jalaprapAtaM ripunigrahe dhRtaH .
saMdizya rAmaM nRpatiH zvobhAvinyabhiSecane . purohitaM samAhUya vasiSThamidamabravIt .
gacchopavAsaM kAkutsthaM kArayAdya tapodhana . zreyase rAjyalAbhAya vadhvA saha yatavrata .
tatheti ca sa rAjAnamuktvA vedavidAM varaH . svayaM vasiSTho bhagavAn yayau rAmanivezanam . upavAsayituM vIraM mantravinmantrakovidam . brAjhai rathavaraM yuktamAsthAya sudhRtavrataH .
sa rAmabhavanaM prApya pANDurAbhradhanaprabham . tisraH kakSyA rathenaiva viveza munisattamaH .
tamAgatamRSi rAmastvaraniva sasambhramam . mAnayiSyan sa mAnAhaM nizcakrAma nivezanAt .
