tAvAsInau tato dRSTvA hanUmAnapi lakSmaNam . zAlazAkhAM samutpATya vinItamupavezayat .
sukhopaviSTaM rAmaM tu prasannamudadhiM yathA . sAlapuSpAvasaMkIrNe tasmin girivarottame . tataH prahRSTaH sugrIvaH zlakSNayA zubhayA girA . uvAca praNayAd rAmaM harSavyAkulitAkSaram .
ahaM vinikRto bhrAtrA carAmyeSa bhayAditaH . RSyamUkaM girivaraM hRtabhAryaH suduHkhitaH .
so ' haM trasto bhaye magno vane sambhrAntacetanaH . vAlinA nikRto bhrAtrA kRtavairazca rAghava .
vAlino me bhayArtasya sarvalokAbhayaMkara . mamApi tvamanAthasya prasAdaM kartumarhasi .
evamuktastu tejasvI dharmajJo dharmavatsalaH . pratyuvAca sa kAkutstha : sugrIvaM prahasanniva .
upakAraphalaM mitramapakAro ' rilakSaNam . adyaiva taM vadhiSyAmi tava bhAryApahAriNam .
ime hi me mahAbhAga patriNastigmatejasaH . kArtikeyavanodbhUtAH zarA hemavibhUSitAH . kaGkapatraparicchannA mahendrAzanisaMnibhAH . suparvANaH sutIkSNAgrAH saroSA bhujagA iva .
vAlisaMjJamamitraM te bhrAtaraM kRtakilviSam . zarairvinihataM pazya vikIrNamiva parvatam .
rAghavasya vacaH zrutvA sugrIvo vAhinIpatiH . praharSamatulaM lebhe sAdhusAdhviti cAbravIt .
rAma zokAbhibhUto ' haM zokArtAnAM bhavAn gatiH . vayasya iti kRtvA hi tvayyahaM paridevaye .
tvaM hi pANipradAnena vayasyo me ' gnisAkSikam . kRtaH prANairbahumataH satyena ca zapAmyaham .
vayasya iti kRtvA ca visrabdhaH pravadAmyaham . duHkhamantargataM tanme mano harati nityazaH .
etAvaduktvA vacanaM vASpadUSitalocanaH . vASpadUSitayA vAcA noccaiH zaknoti bhASitum .
vASpavegaM tu sahasA nadIvegamivAgatam . dhArayAmAsa dhairyeNa sugrIvo rAmasaMnidhau .
sa nigRhya tu taM bASpa prasRjya nayane zubhe . viniHzvasya ca tejasvI rAghavaM punarUcivAn .
purAhaM vAlinA rAma rAjyAt svAdavaropitaH . paruSANi ca saMzrAvya nirdhRto ' smi balIyasA .
hRtA bhAryA ca me tena prANebhyo ' pi garIyasI . suhRdazca madIyA ye saMyatA bandhuneSu te .
yatnavAMzca sa duSTAtmA madvinAzAya rAghava . bahuzastatprayuktAzca vAnarA nihatA mayA .
zaGkayA tvetayAhaM ca dRSTvA tvAmapi rAghava . nopasarpAmyahaM bhIto bhaye sarve hi bibhyati .
kevalaM hi sahAyA me hanumatpramukhAstvime . ato ' haM dhArayAmyadya prANAn kRcchagato ' pi san .
me zokAntaH ete hi kapayaH snigdhA mAM rakSanti samantataH . saha gacchanti gantavye nityaM tiSThanti cAsthite .
saMkSepastveSa me rAma kimuktvA vistaraM hi te . sa me jyeSTho ripuItA vAlI vizrutapauruSaH .
tadvinAze ' pi me dukhaM pramRSTaM syAdanantaram . sukhaM me jIvitaM caiva tadvinAzanibandhanam .
eSa rAma zokArtena niveditaH . duHkhitaH sukhito vApi sakhyurnityaM sakhA gatiH .
zrutvaitacca vaco rAmaH sugrIvamidamabravIt . kiMnimittamabhUd vairaM zrotumicchAmi tattvataH .
sukhaM hi kAraNaM zrutvA vairasya tava vAnara . AnantaryAd vidhAsyAmi sampradhArya balAbalam .
balavAn hi mamAmarSaH zrutvA tvAmavamAnitam . vardhate hRdayotkampI prAvRDvega ivAmbhasaH .
hRSTaH kathaya visrabdho yAvadAropyate dhanuH . sRSTazca hi mayA bANo nirastazca ripustava .
evamuktastu sugrIvaH kAkutsthena mahAtmanA . praharSamadulaM lebhe caturbhiH saha vAnaraiH .
