bhitvA tu tAM gadAM bANe rAghavo dharmavatsalaH . smayamAna idaM vAkyaM saMrabdhamidamabravIt .
etat te balasarvasvaM darzitaM rAkSasAdhama . zaktihInataro matto vRthA tvamupagarjasi .
eSA bANavinirbhinnA gadA bhUmitalaM gatA . abhidhAnapragalbhasya tava pratyayaghAtinI .
yat tvayoktaM vinaSTAnAmidamazrupramArjanam . rAkSasAnAM karomIti mithyA tadapi te vacaH .
nIcasya kSudrazIlasya mithyAvRttasya rakSasaH . prANAnapahariSyAmi garutmAnamRtaM yathA .
adya te bhinnakaNThasya phenabubudabhUSitam . vidAritasya madbANairmahI pAsyati zoNitam .
pAMsurUSitasarvAGgaH srastanyastabhujadvayaH . svapsyase gAM samAzliSya durlabhAM pramadAmiva .
pravRddhanidre zayite tvayi rAkSasapAMsane . bhaviSyanti zaraNyAnAM zaraNyA daNDakA ime .
janasthAne hatasthAne tava rAkSasa maccharaiH . nirbhayA vicariSyanti sarvato munayo vane .
adya viprasariSyanti rAkSasyo hatabAndhavAH . vASpArdravadanA dInA bhayAdanyabhayAvahAH .
adya zokarasajJAstA bhaviSyanti nirarthikAH . anurUpakulAH patnyo yAsAM tvaM patirIdRzaH .
nRzaMsazIla kSudrAtman nityaM brAhmaNakaNTaka . tvatkRte zaGkitairagnau munibhiH pAtyate haviH .
tamevabhisaMrabdhaM bruvANaM rAghavaM vane . kharo nirbhartsayAmAsa roSAt kharatarasvaraH .
dRDhaM khalvavalipto ' si bhayeSvapi ca nirbhayaH . vAcyAvAcyaM tato hi tvaM mRtyorvazyo na budhyase .
kAlapAzaparikSiptA bhavanti puruSA hi ye . kAryAkAryaM na jAnanti te nirastaSaDindriyAH .
evamuktvA tato rAmaM saMrudhya bhRkuTiM tataH . sa dadarza mahAsAlamavidUre nizAcaraH . raNe praharaNasyArthe sarvato hyavalokayan . sa tamutpATayAmAsa saMdaSTadazanacchadam .
taM samutkSipya bAhubhyAM vinarditvA mahAbalaH . rAmamuddizya cikSepa hatastvamiti cAbravIt .
tamApatantaM bANaughaizchitvA rAmaH pratApavAn . roSamAhArayat tIvra nihantuM samare kharam .
jAtasvedastato rAmo roSaraktAntalocanaH . nirbibheda sahasreNa bANAnAM samare kharam .
tasya bANAntarAd raktaM bahu susrAva phenilam . gireH prasravaNasyeva dhAraNAM ca parisravaH . vikalaH sa kRto bANaiH kharo rAmeNa saMyuge . matto rudhiragandhena tamevAbhyadravad drutam .
tamApatantaM saMkruddhaM kRtAstro rudhirAplutam . apAsarpad dvitripadaM kiMcitvarita vikramaH .
tataH pAvakasaMkAzaM vadhAya samare zaram . kharasya rAmo jagrAha brahmadaNDamivAparam .
sa tad dattaM maghavatA surarAjena dhImatA . saMdadhe ca sa dharmAtmA mumoca ca kharaM prati .
sa vimukto mahAbANo nirghAtasamani : svanaH . rAmeNa dhanurAyamya kharasyorasi cApatat .
sa papAta kharo bhUmau dahyamAnaH zarAgninA . rudreNeva vinirdagdhaH zvetAraNye yathAndhakaH .
sa vRtra iva vajreNa phenena namuciryathA . balo vendrAzanihato nipapAta hataH kharaH .
etasminnantare devAzcAraNaiH saha saMgatAH . dundubhIzcAbhinighnantaH puSpavarSaM samantataH . rAmasyopari saMhRSTA vavarSurvismitAstadA . adhikamuhUrtena rAmeNa nizitaiH zaraiH . caturdaza sahasrANi rakSasAM kAmarUpiNAm . kharadUSaNamukhyAnAM nihatAni mahAmRdhe .
aho bata mahatkarma rAmasya viditAtmanaH . aho vIryamaho dADhayaM viSNoriva hi dRzyate .
ityevamuktvA te sarve yayurdevA yathAgatam . tato rAjarSayaH sarve saMgatAH paramarSayaH . sabhAjya mudritA rAmaM sAgastyA idamabruvan .
etadarthaM mahAtejA mahendraH pAkazAsanaH . zarabhaGgAzramaM puNyamAjagAma puraMdaraH . etadarthaM mahAtejA mahendraH pAkazAsanaH .
eSAM vadhArthaM zatrUNAM rakSasAM pApakarmaNAm . tadidaM naH kRtaM kAryaM tvayA dazarathAtmaja . svadharma pracariSyanti daNDakeSu maharSayaH .
etasminnantare vIro lakSmaNaH saha sItayA . giridurgAd viniSkramya saMvivezAzrame sukhI .
tato rAmastu vijayI pUjyamAno maharSibhiH . pravivezAzramaM vIro lakSmaNenAbhipUjitaH .
taM dRSTvA zatruhantAraM maharSINAM sukhAvaham . babhUva hRSTA vaidehI bhartAhaM pariSasvaje . mudA paramayA yuktA dRSTvA rakSogaNAn hatAn . rAmaM caivAvyayaM dRSTvA tutoSa janakAtmajA .
tatastu taM rAkSasasaGghamardanaM sampUjyamAnaM muditairmamAtmabhiH . punaH pariSvajya mudAnvitAnanA babhUva dRSTvA janakAtmajA tadA . 41 . .
AkhyAtA gRdhrarAjena samutplutya plavaGgamAH . saMgatAH prItisaMyuktA vineduH siMhavikramAH .
sampAtervacanaM zrutvA harayo rAvaNakSayam . hRSTAH sAgaramAjagmuH sItAdarzanakAGkSiNaH .
abhigamya tu taM dezaM dadRzubhImavikramAH . kRtsnaM lokasya mahataH pratibimbamavasthitam .
dakSiNasya samudrasya samAsAdyottarAM dizam . saMnivezaM tatazcakrurharivIrA mahAbalAH .
prasuptamiva cAnyatra krIDantamiva cAnyataH . kvacit parvatamAtraizca jalarAzibhirAvRtam . saMkulaM dAnavendraizca pAtAlatalavAsibhiH . romaharSakaraM dRSTvA viSeduH kapikuJjarAH .
AkAzamiva duSpAraM sAgaraM prekSya vAnarAH . viSeduH sahitAH sarve kathaM kAryamiti bruvan .
viSaNNAM vAhinIM dRSTvA sAgarasya nirIkSaNAt . AzvAsayAmAsa harIn bhayArtAn harisattamaH .
na viSAde manaH kArya viSAdo doSavattaraH . viSAdo hanti puruSaM bAlaM kruddha ivoragaH .
yo viSAdaM prasahate vikrame samupasthite . tejasA tasya hInasya puruSArtho na siddhyati .
tasyAM rAtryAM vyatItAyAmaGgado vAnaraiH saha . harivRddhaiH samAgamya punarmantramamantrayat .
sA vAnarANAM dvajinI parivAryAGgadaM babhau . vAsavaM parivAryeva marutAM vAhinI sthitam .
ko ' nyastAM vAnarI senAM zaktaH stambhayituM bhavet . anyatra vAlitanyAdanyatra ca hanUmataH .
tatastAn harivRddhAMzca tacca sainyamariMdamaH . anumAnyAGgadaH zrImAn vAkyamarthavadabravIt .
ka idAnIM mahAtejA layiSyati sAgaram . ka kariSyati sugrIvaM satyasaMdhamarindamam .
ko vIro yojanazataM laGghayeta plavaGgamaH . imAMzca yUthapAn sarvAn mocayet ko mahAbhayAt .
kasya prasAdAd dArAMzca putrAMzcaiva gRhANi ca . ito nivRttAH pazyema siddhArthAH sukhino vayam .
kasya prasAdAd rAmaM ca lakSmaNaM ca mahAbalam . abhigacchema saMhRSTAH sugrIvaM ca vanaukasam . yadi kazcit samartho vaH sAgaraplavane hariH . sa dadAtviha naH zIghraM puNyAmabhayadakSiNAm . aGgadasya vacaH zrutvA na kazcit kiMcidabravIt . stimitevAbhavat sarvA sA tatra harivAhinI .
punarevAGgadaH prAha tAn harIn harisattamaH . sarve balavatAM zreSThA bhavanto dRDhavikramAH . vyapadezakule jAtAH pUjitAzcApyabhIkSNazaH .
nahi vo gamane saGgaH kadAcit kasyacidbhavet . bruvadhvaM yasya yA zaktiH plavane plavagarSabhAH .
tatastrizaGkorvacanaM zrutvA krodhasamanvitam . RSiputrazataM rAma rAjAnamidamabravIt . pratyAkhyAto ' si durmedho guruNA satyavAdinA . taM kathaM samatikramya zAkhAntaramupeyivAn .
ikSvAkUNAM hi sarveSAM purodhAH paramA gatiH . na cAtikramatuM zakyaM vacanaM satyavAdinaH .
azakyamiti sovAca vasiSTho bhagavAnRSiH . taM vayaM vai samAhartuM kratuM zaktAH kathaMcana .
bAlizastvaM narazreSTha gamyatAM svapuraM punaH . yAjane bhagavAzaktastrailokyasyApi pArthiva . avamAnaM kathaM kartuM tasya zakSyAmahe vayam .
teSAM tad vacanaM zrutvA krodhaparyAkulAkSaram . sa rAjA punarevaitAnidaM vacanamabravIt . pratyAkhyAto bhagavatA guruputraistathaiva hi . anyAM gatiM gamiSyAmi svasti vo ' stu tapodhanAH .
RSiputrAstu tacchrutvA vAkyaM ghorAbhisaMhitam . zepuH paramasaMkruddhAzcaNDAlatvaM gamiSyasi . ityuktvA me mahAtmAno vivizuH svaM svamAzramam .
atha rAtryAM vyatItAyAM rAjA caNDAlatAM gataH . nIlavastradharo nIlaH puruSo dhvastamUrdhajaH . cityamAlyAGgarAgazca AyasAbharaNo ' bhavat .
taM dRSTvA mantriNaH sarve tyajya caNDAlarUpiNam . prAdravan sahitA rAma paurA ye ' syAnugAminaH . eko hi rAjA kAkutstha jagAma paramAtmavAn .
dahyamAno divArAcaM vizvAmitraM tapodhanam . caNDAlarUpiNaM rAma muniH kAruNyamAgataH . kAruNyAt sa mahAtejA vAkyaM paramadhArmikaH . idaM jagAda bhadraM te rAjAnaM ghoradarzanam . kimAgamanakAryaM te rAjaputra mahAbala . ayodyAdhipate vIra zApAccaNDAlatAM gataH .
atha tadvAkyamAkarNya rAjA caNDAlatAM gataH . abravIt prAJjalirvAkyaM vAkyajJo vAkyakovidam .
pratyAkhyAto ' smi guruNA guruputraistathaiva ca . anavApyaiva taM kAmaM mayA prApto viparyayaH .
sazarIro divaM yAyAmiti me saumyadarzana . mayA ceSTaM kratuzataM tacca nAvApyate phalam .
anRtaM noktapUrvaM me na ca vakSye kadAcana . kRcchreSvapi gataH saumya kSatradharmeNa te zape .
yajJairbahuvidhairiSTaM prajA dharmeNa pAlitAH . guravazca mahAtmAnaH zIlavRttena toSitAH . dharme prayatamAnasya yajJaM cAhartumicchataH . paritoSaM na gacchanti guravo munipuGgava . daivameva paraM manye pauruSaM tu nirrathakam .
daivenAkramyate sarvaM daivaM hi paramA gatiH . tasya me paramArtasya prasAdamabhikAGkSataH . kartumarhasi bhadraM te daivopahatakarmaNaH .
nAnyAM gatiM gamiSyAmi nAnyaccharaNamasti me . daivaM puruSakAreNa nivartayitumarhasi .
mArIcasya tu tad vAkyaM kSamaM yuktaM ca rAvaNaH . ukto na pratijagrAha martukAma ivauSadham .
taM pathyahitavaktAraM mArIcaM rAkSasAdhina . abravIt paruSaM vAkyamayuktaM kAlacoditaH .
duSkulaitadayuktArthaM mArIca mayi kathyate . vAkyaM niSphalamatyarthaM bIjamuptamivokhare .
tvadvAkyairna tu mAM zakyaM bhettuM rAmasya saMyuge . mUrkhasya pApazIlasya mAnuSasya vizeSataH .
yastyaktvA suhado rAjyaM mAtaraM pitaraM tathA . strIvAkyaM prAkRtaM zrutvA vanamekapade gataH . avazyaM tu mayA tasya saMyuge kharaghAtinaH . prANaiH priyatarA sItA hartavyA tava saMnidhau .
evaM me nizcitA buddhirhadi mArIca vidyate . na vyAvartayituM zakyA senTrairapi surAsuraiH .
deSaM guNaM vA sampRSTastvamevaM vaktumarhasi . apAyaM vA upAyaM vA kAryasyAsya vinizcaye .
sampRSTena tu vaktavyaM sacivena vipazcitA . udyatAJjalinA rAjJA ya icched bhUtimAtmanaH .
vAkyamapratikUlaM tu mRdupUrvaM zubhaM hitam . upacAreNa vaktavyo yuktaM ca vasudhAdhipaH .
sAvamadaM tu yadvAkyamathavA hitamucyate . nAbhinandeta tad rAjA mAnArthI mAnavarjitam .
paJca rUpANi rAjAno dhArayantyamitaujasaH . agnerindrasya somasya yamasya varuNasya ca . auSNyaM tathA vikramaM ca saumyaM daNDaM prasannatAm . dhArayanti mahAtmAno rAjAnaH kSaNadAcara .
tasmAt sarvAsvavasthAsu mAnyAH pUjyAzca nityadA . tvaM tu dharmamavijJAya kevalaM mohamAzritaH . abhyAgataM tu daurAtmyAt paruSaM vadasIdRzam . guNadoSau na pRcchAmi kSemaM cAtmani rAkSasa .
mayoktamapi caitAvat tvAM pratyamitavikrama . asmiMstu sa bhavAn kRtye sAhAyyaM kartumarhasi .
zRNu tatkarma sAhAyye yatkAryaM vacanAnmama . sauvarNastvaM mRgo bhUtvA citro rajatabindubhiH . Azrame tasya rAmasya sItAyAH pramukhe cara . pralobhayitvA vaidehI yatheSTaM gantumarhasi .
tvAM hi mAyAmayaM dRSTvA kAJcanaM jAtavismayA . Anayainamiti kSipraM rAmaM vakSyati maithilI .
apakrAnte ca kAkutsthe dUraM gatvApyudAhara . hA sIte lakSmaNetyevaM rAmavAkyAnurUpakam .
tacchrutvA rAmapadavIM sItayA ca pracoditaH . anugacchati sambhrAntaM saumitrirapi sauhadAt .
apakrAnte ca kAkutsthe lakSmaNe ca yathAsukham . AhariSyAmi vaidehI sahasrAkSaH zacImiva .
evaM kRtvA tvidaM kAryaM yatheSTaM gaccha rAkSasa . rAjyasyArdhaM pradAsyAmi mArIca tava suvrata .
gaccha saumya zivaM mArga kAryasyAsya vivRddhaye . ahaM tvAnugamiSyAmi saratho daNDakAvanam .
prApya sItAmayuddhena vaJcayitvA tu rAghavam . laGkAM prati gamiSyAmi kRtakAryaH saha tvayA .
no cet karoSi mArIca hanmi tvAmahamadya vai . etad kAryamavazyaM me balAdapi kariSyasi . rAjJo vipratikUlastho na jAtu sukhamedhate .
AsAdya taM jIvitasaMzayaste mRtyubhruvo hyadya mayA virudhyataH . etad yathAvat parigaNya buddhyA yadatra pathyaM kuru tattathA tvam .
kasyacittvatha kAlasya yudhAjitkekayo nRpaH . svaguruM preSayAmAsa rAghavAya mahAtmane . gAy/amaGgirasaH putraM brahmarSimamitaprabham . daza cAzvasahasrANi prItidAnamanuttamam . kambalAni ca ratnAni citravastramathottamam . rAmAya pradadau rAjA zubhAnyAbharaNAni ca .
zrutvA tu rAghavo dhImAnmaharSi gAryamAgatam . mAtulasyAzvapatinaH prahitaM tanmahAdhanam . pratyudgamya ca kAkutsthaH krozamA sahAnujaH . gAyaM saMpUjayAmAsa yathA zakro bRhaspatim .
tathA saMpUjya tamRrSi taddhanaM pratigRhya ca . pRSTvA pratipadaM sarvaM kuzalaM mAtulasya ca . upaviSTaM mahAbhAgaM rAmaH praSTuM pracakrame . kimAha mAtulo vAkyaM yadartha bhagavAniha . prApto vAkyavidAM zreSThaH sAkSAdiva bRhaspatiH .
rAmasya bhASitaM zrutvA maharSiH kAryavistaram . . . . . vaktumadbhutasaMkAzaM rAghavAyopacakrame . mAtulaste mahAbAho vAkyamAha nararSabhaH . yudhAjitprItisaMyuktaM zrUyatAM yadi rocate .
ayaM gandharvaviSayaH phalamUlopazodhitaH . sindhorubhayataH pArzve dezaH paramazobhanaH . taM ca rakSanti gandharvAH sAyudhA yuddhakovidAH . zailUSasya sutA vIra tisraH koTyo mahAbalAH .
tAnvinirjitya kAkutstha gandharvanagaraM zubham . nivezaya mahAbAho sve pure susamAhite . anyasya na gatistatra dezaH paramazobhanaH . rocatAM te mahAbAho nAhaM tvAmahitaM vade .
tacchrutvA rAghavaH prIto maharSermAtulasya ca . uvAca bADhamityeva bharataM cAnvavaikSata .
so ' bravIdrAghavaH prItaH sAJjalipragraho dvijam . imau kumArau taM dezaM brahmarSe vicariSyataH . bharatasyAtmajau vIrau takSaH puSkala eva ca . mAtulena suguptau tu dharmeNa susamAhitau . bharataM cAgrataH kRtvA kumArau sabalAnugau . nihatya gandharvasutAndve pure vibhajiSyataH .
nivezya te puravare Atmajau saMnivezya ca . AgamiSyati me bhUyaH sakAzamatidhArmikaH .
brahmarSimevamuktvA tu bharataM sabalAnugam . AjJApayAmAsa tadA kumArau cAbhyaSecayat .
nakSatreNa ca saumyena puraskRtyAGgiraHsutam . bharataH saha sainyena kumArAbhyAM viniryayau .
sA senA zakrayukteva nagarAniryayAvatha . . rAghavAnugatA dUraM durAdharSA surairapi .
mAMsAzinazca ye sattvA rakSAMsi sumahAnti ca . anujagmurhi bharataM rudhirasya pipAsayA . bhUtagrAmAzca bahavo mAMsabhakSAH sudAruNAH . gandharvaputramAMsAni bhoktukAmAH sahasrazaH .
siMhavyAghravarAhANAM khecarANAM ca pakSiNAm . bahUni vai sahasrANi senAyA yayuragrataH .
adhyardhamAsamuSitA pathi senA nirAmayA . hRSTapuSTajanAkIrNA kekayaM samupAgamat .
nakSatreNa ca saumyena puraskRtyAGgiraHsutam . bharataH saha sainyena kumArAbhyAM viniryayau .
