siMhavyAghravarAhANAM khecarANAM ca pakSiNAm . bahUni vai sahasrANi senAyA yayuragrataH .
adhyardhamAsamuSitA pathi senA nirAmayA . hRSTapuSTajanAkIrNA kekayaM samupAgamat .
zrutvA hanumato vAkyaM prazritaM dharmasaMhitam . svAmisatkArasaMyuktamaGgado vAkyamabravIt .
sthairyamAtmamanaHzaucamAnRzaMsyamathArjavam . vikramazcaiva dhairyaM ca sugrIve nopapadyate .
bhrAtujyeSThasya yo bhAryAM jIvato mahiSIM priyAm . dharmeNa mAtaraM yastu svIkaroti jugupsitaH . kathaM sa dharmaM jAnIte yena bhrAtrA durAtmanA . yuddhAyAbhiniyuktena bilasya pihitaM mukham .
satyAt pANigRhItazca kRtakarmA mahAyazAH . vismRto rAghavo yena sa kasya sukRtaM smaret . lakSmaNasya bhayeneha nAdharmabhayabhIruNA . AdiSTA mArgituM sItA dharmastasmin kathaM bhavet .
tasmin pApe kRtaghne tu smRtibhinne calAtmani . AryaH ko vizvasejjAtu tatkulIno vizeSataH .
rAjye putraH pratiSThApya saguNo nirguNo ' pi vA . kathaM zatrukulInaM mAM sugrIvo jIvayiSyati . . . . .
bhinnamantro ' parAddhazca bhinnazaktiH kathaM hyaham . kiSkindhAM prApya jIveyamanAtha iva durbalaH .
upAMzudaNDena hi mAM bandhanenopapAdayet . zaThaH krUro nRzaMsazca sugrIvo rAjyakAraNAt .
bandhanAccAvasAdAnme zreyaH prAyopavezanam . anujAnantu mAM sarve gRhaM gacchantu vAnarAH .
ahaM vaH pratijAnAmi na gamiSyAmyahaM purIm . ihaiva prAyamAsiSye zreyo maraNameva me .
abhivAdanapUrvaM tu rAjA kuzalameva ca . abhivAdanapUrvaM tu rAghavau balazAlinau . vAcyastAto yavIyAn me sugrIvo vAnarezvaraH . ArogyapUrvaM kuzalaM vAcyA mAtA rumA ca me .
mAtaraM caiva me tAsamAzvAsayitumarhatha . prakRtyA priyaputrA sA sAnukrozA tapasvinI . vinaSTamiha mAM zrutvA vyaktaM hAsyati jIvitam . etAvaduktvA vacanaM vRddhAMstAnabhivAdya ca . viveza cAGgado bhUmau rudan darbheSu durmakhaH .
tasya saMvizatastatra rudanto vAnararSabhAH . nayanebhyaH pramumucuruSNaM vai vAri duHkhitAH . sugrIvaM caiva nindantaH prazaMsantazca vAlinam . parivAryAGgadaM sarve vyavasan prAyamAsitum .
tad vAkyaM vAliputrasya vijJAya plavagarSabhAH . upaspRzyodakaM sarve prAGmukhAH samupAvizan . dakSiNAgreSu darbheSu udaktIraM samAzritAH . mumUrSavo harizreSThA etat kSamamiti sma ha .
rAmasya vanavAsaM ca kSayaM dazarathasya ca . janasthAnavadhaM caiva vadhaM caiva jayAyuSaH . haraNaM caiva vaidehyA vAlinazca vadhaM tathA . rAmakopaM ca vadatAM harINAM bhayamAgatam .
sa saMvizadbhirbahubhirmahIdharo mahAdrikUTapratimaiH plavaGgamaiH . babhUva saMnAditanirjharAntaro bhRzaM nadadbhirjaladairivAmbaram .
tato nIlAmbudaprakhyaH prahasto nAma rAkSasaH . abravItprAJjalirvAkyaM zUraH senApatistadA .
devadAnavagandharvAH pizAcapatagoragAH . sarve dharSayituM zakyAH kiM punarmAnavau raNe .
sarve pramattA vizvastA vaJcitAH sma hanUmatA . nahi me jIvato gacchejjIvansa vanagocaraH .
sarvAM sAgaraparyantAM sazailavanakAnanAm . karomyavAnarAM bhUmimAjJApayatu mAM bhavAn .
rakSAM caiva vidhAsyAmi vAnarAdrajanIcara . nAgamiSyati te duHkhaM kiMcidAtmAparAdhajam .
abravIttamasaMkruddho durmukho nAma rAkSasaH . idaM na kSA gIyaM hi sarveSAM naH pradharSaNam . ayaM paribhavo bhUyaH purasyAntaHpurasya ca . zrImato rAkSasendrasya vAnarendrapradharSaNam .
asminmuhUrte gatvaiko nivartiSyAmi vAnarAn . praviSTAnsAgaraM bhImamambaraM vA rasAtalam .
tato ' bravItsusaMkruddho vajradaMSTro mahAbalaH . pragRhya parighaM ghoraM mAMsazoNitadUSitam .
kiM no hanUmatA kArya kRpaNena tapasvinA . rAme tiSThati durdharSe sugrIve ' pi salakSmaNe .
adya rAmaM sasugrIvaM parigheNa salakSmaNam . AgamiSyAmi hatvaiko vikSobya harivAhinIm .
idaM mamAparaM vAkyaM zRNu rAjanyadIcchasi . upAyakuzalo hyeva jayecchavUnatandritaH .
kAmarUpadharAH zUrAH subhImA bhImadarzanAH . rAkSasAnAM sahasrANi rAkSasAdhipa nizcitAH . kAkutsthamupasaMgamya vivRtaM mAnuSaM vapuH . sarve hyasaMbhramA bhUtvA bruvantu raghusattamam . preSitA bharatenaiva bhrAtrA tava yavIyasA . sa hi senAM samutthApya kSipramevopayAsyati .
tato vayamitastUrNaM zUlazaktigadAdharAH . cApabANAsihastAzca tvaritAstatra yAmahe . AkAze gaNazaH sthitvA hatvA tAM harivAhinIm . azmazastramahAvRSTyA prApayAma yamakSayam .
evaM cedupasaptAmanayaM rAmalakSmaNau . avazyamapanItena jahatAmeva jIvitam .
kaumbhakarNistato vIro nikumbho nAma vIryavAn . abravItparamavuddho rAvaNaM lokarAvaNam .
sarve bhavantasthiSThanta mahArAjena saMgatAH . ahameko haniSyAmi rAghavaM sahalakSmaNam . sugrIvaM sahanUmantaM sarvAMzcaivAtra vAnarAn .
tato vajrahanurnAma rAkSasaH parvatopamaH . kruddhaH parilihansRkkAM jihvayA vAkyamabravIt .
svairaM kurvantu kAryANi bhavanto vigatajvarAH . eko ' haM bhakSayiSyAmi tAM sarvAM harivAhinIm .
svasthAH krIDantu nizcintA pibantu madhu vAruNam . ahameko vadhiSyAmi sugrIvaM sahalakSmaNam . sAGgadaM ca hanUmantaM sarvAMzcaivAtra vAnarAn .
punarevAbravIt prIto rAghavaM raghunandanam . ayamAkhyAti te rAma sacivo mantrisattamaH . hanumAn yanimittaM tvaM nirjanaM vanamAgataH .
lakSmeNa saha bhrAtrA vasatazca vane tava . rakSasApahRtA bhAryA maithilI janakAtmajA . tvayA viyuktA rudatI lakSmaNena ca dhImatA . antaraM prepsunA tena hatvA gRdhaM jaTAyuSam . bhAryAvayogajaM duHkhaM prApitastena rakSasA .
bhAryAviyogajaM duHkhaM nacirAt tvaM vimokSyase . ahaM tAmAnayiSyAmi naSTAM vedazrutImiva .
rasAtale vA vartantI vartantI vA nabhastale . ahamAnIya dAsyAmi tava bhAryAmariMdama .
idaM tathyaM mama vacastvamavehi ca rAghava . na zakyA sA jarayitumapi sendraiH surAsuraiH . tava bhAryA mahAbAho bhakSyaM viSakRtaM yathA . tyaja zokaM mahAbAho tAM kAntAmAnayAmi te .
anumAnAt tu jAnAmi maithilI sA na saMzayaH . hriyamANA mayA dRSTA rakSasA raudrakarmaNA . krozantI rAmarAmeti lakSmaNeti ca visvaram . sphurantI rAvaNasyAGke pannagendravadhUryathA .
AtmanA paJcamaM mAM hi dRSTvA zailatale sthitam . uttarIyaM tayA tyaktaM zubhAnyAbharaNAni ca .
tAnyasmAbhirgRhItAni nihitAni ca rAghava . AnayiSyAmyahaM tAni pratyabhijJAtumarhasi .
tamabravIt tato rAmaH sugrIvaM priyavAdinam . Anayasva sakhe zIghraM kimarthaM pravilambase .
evamuktastu sugrIvaH zailasya gahanAM guhAm . praviveza tataH zIghraM rAghavapriyakAmyayA . uttarIyaM gRhItvA tu sa tAnyAbharaNAni ca . idaM pazyati rAmAya darzayAmAsa vAnaraH .
tato gRhItvA vAsastu zubhAnyAbharaNAni ca . abhavad vASpasaMruddho nIhAreNeva candramAH .
sItAsnehapravRttena sa tu vASpeNa dUSitaH . hA priyeti rudandhairyamutsRjya nyapatat kSitau .
hRdi kRtvA sa bahuzastamalaMkAramuttamam . nizazvAsa bhRzaM sarpo bilastha iva roSitaH .
avicchinnAzruvegastu saumitriM prekSya pArzvataH . paridevayituM dInaM rAmaH samupacakrame .
pazya lakSmaNa vaidehyA saMtyaktaM hriyamANayA . uttarIyamidaM bhUmau zarIrAd bhUSaNAni ca .
zAdvalinyAM dhruvaM bhUmyAM sItayA hriyamANayA . utsRSTaM bhUSaNamidaM tathA rUpaM hi dRzyate .
evamuktastu rAmeNa lakSmaNo vAkyamabravIt . nAhaM jAnAmi keyUre nAhaM jAnAmi kuNDale .
nUpure tvabhijAnAmi nityaM pAdAbhivandanAt . tatastu rAghavo vAkyaM sugrIvamidamabravIt . brUhi sugrIva kaM dezaM hriyantI lakSitA tvayA . rakSasA raudrarUpeNa mama prANapriyA hRtA .
kva vA vasati tad rakSo mahad vyasanadaM mama . yanimittamahaM sarvAn nAzayiSyAmi rAkSasAn .
haratA maithilI yena mAM ca roSayatA dhruvam . Atmano jIvitAntAya mRtyudvAramapAvRtam .
mama dayitatamA hRtA vanAd rajanicareNa vimathya yena sA . kathaya mama ripuM tamadya vai plavagapate yamasaMnidhiM nayAmi .
janakena samAdiSTA dUtAste klAntavAhanAH . trirAtramuSitA mArge te ' yodhyAM prAvizanpurIm .
te rAjavacanAd gatvA rAjavezma pravezitAH . dadRzurdevasaMkAzaM vRddhaM dazarathaM nRpam .
baddhAJjalipuTAH sarve dUtA vigatasAdhvasAH . rAjAnaM prazritaM vAkyamabruvan madhurAkSaram . maithilo janako rAjA sAgnihotrapuraskRtaH . muhurmuhurmadhurayA snehasaMraktayA girA . kuzalaM cAvyayaM caiva sopAdhyAyapurohitam . janakastvAM mahArAja pRcchate sapuraHsaram .
pRSTvA kuzalamavyagraM vaidehI mithilAdhipaH . kauzikAnumate vAkyaM bhavantamidamabravIt .
pUrvaM pratijJA viditA vIryazulkA mamAtmajA . rAjAnazca kRtAmarSA nirvIryA vimukhIkRtAH .
seyaM mama sutA rAjan vizvAmitrapuraskRtaiH . yadRcchayAgatai rAjan nirjitA tava putrakaiH . tacca ratnaM dhanurdivyaM madhye bhagnaM mahAtmanA . rAmeNa hi mahAbAho mahatyAM janasaMsadi .
asmai deyA mayA sItA vIryazulkA mahAtmane . pratijJAM tartumicchAmi tadanujJAtumarhasi .
sopAdhyAyo mahArAja purohitapuraskRtaH . zIghramAgaccha bhadraM te draSTumarhasi rAghavau .
pratijJAM mama rAjendra nirvartayitumarhasi . putrayorubhayoreva prItiM tvamupalapsyase .
evaM videhAdhipatirmadhuraM vAkyamabravIt . vizvAmitrAbhyanujJAtaH zatAnandamate sthitaH .
dUtavAkyaM tu tacchrutvA rAjA paramaharSitaH . vasiSThaM vAmadevaM ca mantriNazcaivamabravIt .
guptaH kuzikaputreNa kausalyAnandavardhanaH . lakSmaNena saha bhrAtrA videheSu vasatyasau .
dRSTavIryastu kAkutstho janakena mahAtmanA . sampradAnaM sutAyAstu rAghave kartumicchati .
yadi vo rocate vRttaM janakasya mahAtmanaH . purIM gacchAmahe zIghraM mA bhUt kAlasya paryayaH .
mantriNo bADhamityAhuH saha sarvairmaharSibhiH . suprItazcAbravId rAjA zvo yAtreti ca mantriNaH .
triNastu narendrasya rAtriM paramasatkRtAH . USuH pramuditAH sarve guNaiH sarvaiH samanvitAH .
evamAdharSitaH zUraH zUrpanakhyA kharastataH . uvAca rakSasAM madhye kharaH kharataraM vacaH .
tavApamAnaprabhavaH krodho ' yamatulo mama . na zakyate dhArayituM lavaNAmbha ivolbaNam .
na rAmaM gaNaye vIryAnmAnuSaM kSINajIvitam . AtmaduzcaritaiH prANAn hato yo ' dya vimokSyate .
vASpaH saMdhAryatAmeSa sambhramazca vimucyatAm . ahaM rAmaM saha bhrAtrA nayAmi yamasAdanam .
parazvadhahatasyAdya mandaprANasya bhUtale . rAmasya rudhiraM raktamuSNaM pAsyasi rAkSasi .
samprahRSTA vacaH zrutvA kharasya vadanAccyutam . prazazaMsa punarmoAd bhrAtaraM rakSasAM varam .
tayA paruSitaH pUrvaM punareva prazaMsitaH . abravId dUSaNaM nAma kharaH senApati tadA .
caturdaza sahasrANi mama cittAnuvartinAm . rakSasAM bhImavegAnAM samareSvanivartinAm . nIlajImUtavarNAnAM lokahiMsAvihAriNAm . sarvodyogamudIrNAnAM rakSasAM saumya kAraya .
upasthApaya me kSipraM rathaM saumya dhanUMSi ca . zarAMzca citrAn khaGgAMzca zaktIzca vividhAH zitAH .
agre niryAtumicchAmi paulastyAnAM mahAtmanAm . vadhArthaM durvinItasya rAmasya raNakovida .
iti tasya bruvANasya sUryavarNaM mahAratham . sadazvaiH zabalairyuktamAcacakSe ' tha dUSaNaH .
taM meruzikharAkAraM taptakAJcanabhUSaNam . hemaMcakramasambAdhaM vaidUryamayakUvaram . matsyaiH puSpairdumaiH zailaizcandrakAntaizca kAJcanaiH . mAGgalyaiH pakSisaGghazca tArAbhizca samAvRtam . dhvajanistrizasampanna kiGkiNIvarabhUSitam . sadazvayuktaM so ' marSAdAruroha kharastadA .
kharastu tanmahatsainyaM rathacarmAyudhadhvajam . niryAtetyabravIt prekSya dUSaNaH sarvarAkSasAn .
tatastad rAkSasaM sainyaM ghoracarmAyudhadhvajam . nirjagAma janasthAnAnmAhAnAdaM mahAjavam . mudvaraiH paTTizaiH zUlaiH sutIkSNaizca parazvadhaiH . khaGgaizcakraizca hastasthaibhrAjamAnaiH satomaraiH . zaktibhiH paridhaiorairatimAtraizca kArmukaiH . gadAsimusalairvajragRhItairbhImadarzanaiH . rAkSasAnAM sughorANAM sahasrANi caturdaza . niryAtAni janasthAnAt kharacittAnuvartinAm .
sAMstu nirdhAvato dRSTvA rAkSasAn bhImadarzanAn . kharasyAtha rathaH kiMcijjagAma tadanantaram .
tatastAJchabalAnazvAMstaptakAJcanabhUSitAn . kharasya matamAjJAya sArathiH paryacodayat .
saMcodito rathaH zIghraM kharasya ripughAtinaH . zabdenApUrayAmAsa dizaH sapradizastathA .
pravRddhamanyustu kharaH kharasvaro riporvadhArtha tvarito yathAntakaH . mahAbalo megha ivAzmavarSavAn .
tathA bruvati tAre tu tArAdhipativarcasi . atha mene hRtaM rAjyaM hanUmAnaGgadena tat .
buddhyA hyaSTAGgayA yuktaM caturbalasamanvitam . caturdazaguNaM mene hanUmAn vAlinaH sutam . ApUryamANaM zazvacca tejobalaparAkramaiH . zazinaM zuklapakSAdau vardhamAnamiva zriyA . bRhaspatisamaM buddhyA vikrame sadRzaM pituH . zuzrUSamANaM tArasya zukrasyeva puraMdaram .
bharturarthe parizrAntaM sarvazAstravizAradaH . abhisaMdhAtumArebhe hanUmAnaGgadaM tataH .
sa caturNAmupAyAnAM dvitIyamupavarNayan . bhedayAmAsa tAn sarvAn vAnarAn vAkyasampadA .
teSu sarveSu bhinneSu tato ' bhISayadaGgadam . bhISaNairvividhairvAkyaiH kopopAyasamanvataiH .
tvaM samarthataraH pitrA yuddhe tAreya vai dhruvam . dRDhaM dhArayituM zaktaH kapirAjyaM yathA pitA .
nityamasthiracittA hi kapayo haripuMgava . nAjJApyaM viSahiSyanti putradAraM vinA tvayA .
tvaM naite hyanuraJjeyuH pratyakSaM pravadAmi te . yathA ' yaM jAmbavAn nIlaH suhotrazca mahAkapiH . nAhaM te ime sarve sAmadAnAdibhirguNaiH . daNDena na tvayA zakyAH sugrIvAdapakarSitum .
vigRhyAsanamapyAhurdurbalena balIyasA . AtmarakSAkarastasmAnna vigRhNIta durbalaH .
yAM cemAM manyase dhAtrImetad balamiti zrutam . etallakSmaNabANAnAmISat kArya vidAraNam .
svalpaM hi kRtamindreNa kSipatA hyazaniM purA . lakSmaNo nizitairbANairbhindyAt patrakuTaM yathA .
lakSmaNasya ca nArAcA bahavaH santi tadvidhAH . vajrAzanisamasparzA girINAmapi dArakAH .
avasthAnaM yadaiva tvamAsiSyasi paraMtapa . tadaiva harayaH sarve tyakSyanti kRtanizcayAH .
smarantaH putradArANAM nityodvignA bubhukSitAH . kheditA duHkhazayyAbhistvAM kariSyanti pRSThataH .
sa tvaM hInaH suhRdbhizca hitakAmaizca bandhubhiH . tRNAdapi bhRzodvigraH spandamAnAd bhaviSyasi . atyugravegA nizitA ghorA lakSmaNasAyakAH . apAvRttaM jighAMsanto mahAvegA durAsadAH .
asmAbhistu gataM sArdhaM vinItavadupasthitam . AnupUrvyAttu sugrIvo rAjye tvAM sthApayiSyati .
dharmarAjaH pitRvyaste prItikAmo dRDhavrataH . zuciH satyapratijJazca sa tvAM jAtu na nAzayet .
priyakAmazca te mAtusdarthaM cAsya jIvitam . tasyApatyaM ca nAstyanyat tasmAdaGgada gamyatAm .
tatprayAtaM balaM ghoramazivaM zoNitodakam . abhyavarSanmahAgorastumulo gardavAruNaH .
nipetusturagAstasya rathayuktA mahAjavAH . same puSpacite deze rAjamArge yadRcchayA .
zyAmaM rudhiraparyantaM babhUva pariveSaNam . alAtacakrapratima pratigRhya divAkaram .
tato dhvajamupAgamya hemadaNDaM samucchritam . samAkramya mahAkAyastasthau gRdhraH sudAruNaH .
janasthAnasamIpe ca samAkramya kharasvanAH . visvarAn vividhAn nAdAn mAMsAdA mRgapakSiNaH . . . . vyAjahurabhidIptAyAM dizi vai bhairavasvanam . azivaM yAtudhAnAnAM zivA ghorA mahAsvanAH .
prabhinnagajasaMkAzAstoyazoNitadhAriNaH . AkAzaM tadanAkAzaM cakrubhImAmbuvAhakAH .
babhUva timiraM ghoramuddhataM romaharSaNam . dizo vA prAdizo vApi suvyaktaM na cakAzire .
kSatajAsavarNAbhA saMdhyA kAlaM binA babhau . kharaM cAbhimukhaM nedustadA ghorA mRgAH khagAH .
kaGkagomAyugRdhrAzca cukruzurbhayazaMsinaH . nityAzivakarA yuddhe zivA ghoranidarzanAH . nedurbalasyAbhimukhaM jvAlodgAribhirAnanaiH .
kabandhaH parighAbhAso dRzyate bhAskarAntike . jagrAha sUryaM svarbhAnuraparvaNi mahAgrahaH . pravAti mArutaH zIghraM niSprabhau ' bhUd divAkaraH .
upetuzca vinA rAtriM tArAH khadyotasaprabhAH . saMlInamInavihagA nalinyaH zuSkapaGkajAH .
tasmin kSaNe babhUvuzca vinA puSpaphalairdumAH . uddhRtazca vinA vAtaM reNurjaladharAruNaH .
cIcIkUcIti vAsyantyo babhUvustatra sArikAH . ulkAzcApi sanirghoSA nipeturporadarzanAH .
pracacAla mahI cApi sazailavanakAnanA . kharasya ca rathasthasya nardamAnasya dhImataH .
prAkampata bhujaH savyaH svarazcAsyAvasajjata . sAsrA sampadyate dRSTiH pazyamAnasya sarvataH . lalATe ca rujo jAtA na ca mohAnnyavartata . tAn samIkSya mahotpAtAnutthitAn romaharSaNAn . abravId rAkSasAn sarvAn prahasan sa kharastadA .
mahotpAtAnimAn sarvAnutthitAn ghoradarzanAn . na cintayAmyahaM vIryAd balavAn durbalAniva . tArA api zaraistIkSNaiH pAtayeyaM nabhastalAt . mRtyu maraNadharmeNa saMkruddho yojayAmyaham . rAghavaM taM balotsiktaM bhrAtaraM cApi lakSmaNam . ahatvA sAyakaistIkSNairnopAvartitumutsahe .
