yamAzritya narA rAjan vartayeyurthathAsukham . anAthAstapyamAnAzca dasyubhiH paripIDitAH . tameva pUjayeyuste prItyA svamiva bAndhavam . abhIrabhIkSNaM kauravya kartA sanmAnamarhati .
kiM tairye ' naDuho nohyAH kiM dhenvA vApyadugdhayA . vandhyayA bhAryayA ko ' rthaH ko ' rtho rAjJApyarakSatA .
yathA dArumayo hastI yathA carmamayo mRgaH . yathA hyanathaH SaNDho vA pArtha kSetraM yathoSaram . evaM vipro ' nadhIyAno rAjA yazca na rakSitA . megho na varSate yazca sarvathA te nirarthakAH .
nityaM yastu sato rakSedasatazca nivartayet . sa eva rAjA kartavyastena sarvamidaM dhRtam .
saMjaya uvAca duHzAsanabalaM hatvA sabyasAcI mahArathaH . sindhurAja parIpsan vai droNAnIkamupAdravat .
sa tu droNaM samAsAdya vyUhasya pramukhe sthitam . kRtAJjaliridaM vAkyaM kRSNasyAnumate ' bravIt .
arjuna uvAca zivena dhyAhi mAM brahman svasti caiva vadasva me . bhavataprasAdAdicchAmi praveSTuM durbhidAM camUm .
bhavAn pitRsamo mahyaM dharmarAjasamo ' pi ca . tathA kRSNasamazcaiva satyametad bravImi te .
azvatthAmA yathA tAta rakSaNIyastvayAnagha . tathAhamapi te rakSyaH sadaiva dvijasattama .
tava prasAdAdiccheyaM sindhurAjAnamAhave . nihantuM dvipadAM zreSTha pratijJAM rakSa me prabho .
saMjaya uvAca evamuktastadAcAryaH pratyuvAca smayanniva . mAmajitvA na bIbhatyo zakyo jetuM jayadrathaH .
etAvaduktvA taM droNaH zaravAtairavAkirat . sArathAzvadhvajaM tIkSNaiH prahasan vaisasArathim .
tato ' rjunaH zaravAtAn droNasyAvArya sAyakaiH . droNamabhyadravad bANairghorarUmairmahattaraiH .
vivyAdha caraNe droNamanumAnya vizAmyate . kSatradharme samAsthAya navabhiH sAyakaiH punaH .
tasyeSUniSubhizchattvA droNo vivyAdha tAvubhau . viSAgnijvalitaprakhyairiSubhiH kRSNapANDavau .
iyeSa pANDavastasya bANaizchettuM zarAsanam . tasya cintayatastvevaM phAlgunasya mahAtmanaH .
droNaH zarairasambhrAnto jyAM vicchedAzu vIryavAn . vivyAdha ca hayAnasya dhvajaM sArathimeva ca .
arjunaM ca zarairvIraH smayamAno ' bhyavAkirat . etasminnantare pArthaH sajyaM kRtvA mahad dhanuH .
vizeSayiSyannAcArye sarvAstraviduSAM varaH . mumoca SaTzatAn bANAn gRhItvaikamiva dutam .
punaH saptazatAnanyAn sahasraM cAnivartinaH . cikSepAyutazazcAnyAMste ' nan droNasya tAM camUm .
taiH samyagastairvalinA kRtinA citrayodhinA . manuSyavAjimAtaGgA viddhAH peturgatAsavaH .
visUtAzvadhvajAH petuH saMchinnAyudhajIvitAH . rathino sthamukhyebhyaH sahasA zarapIDitAH .
cUrNitAkSiptadagdhAnAM vajrAnilahutAzanaiH . tulyarUpA gajA : peturgiryagrAmbudavezmanAm .
petuzvasahasrANi prahatAnyarjuneSubhiH . haMsA himavataH pRSThe vAriviprahatA iva . .
sthAzvadvipapattayoghAH salilaughA ivAdbhutAH . yugAntAdityarazmayAbhaiH pANDavAstrazarairhatAH .
taM pANDavAdityazarAMzujAlaM kurupravIrAn yudhi niSTapantam . sa droNameghaH zaravRSTivegaiH prAcchAdayanmegha ivArkarazmIn .
athAtyarthaM visRSTena dviSatAmasubhojinA . Ajaghne vakSasi droNo nArAcena dhanaMjayam .
sa vihvalitasarvAGgaH kSitikampe yathAcalaH . dhairyamAlambya bIbhatsuyNaM vivyAdha patrabhiH .
droNastu paJcabhirbANairvAsudevamatADayat . arjunaM ca trisaptatyA dhvajaM cAsya tribhiH zaraiH .
vizeSayiSyaziSyaM ca droNo rAjan parAkramI . adRzyamarjunaM cakre nimeSAccharavRSTibhiH .
prasaktAn patato ' drAkSama bhAradvAjasya sAyakAn . maNDalIkRtamevAsya dhanuzcAdRzyatAdbhutam .
te ' bhyayuH samare rAjan vAsudevadhanaMjayau . droNasRSTAH subahavaH kaGkapatraparicchadAH .
tad dRSTvA tAdRzaM yuddhaM droNapANDavayostadA . vAsudevo mahAbuddhiH kAryavattAmacintayat .
tato ' bravId vAsudevo dhanaMjayamidaM vacaH . pArtha pArtha mahAbAho na na : kAlAtyayo bhavet .
droNamutsRjya gacchAmaH kRtyametanmahattaram . pArthazcApyabravIt kRSNaM yatheSTamiti kezavam .
tataH pradakSiNaM kRtvA droNaM prAyAnmahAbhujam . parivRttazca bIbhatsuragacchad visRjazarAn .
tato ' bravIt svayaM droNaH kvedaM pANDava gamyate . nanu nAma raNe zatrumajitvA na nivartase .
arjuna uvAca gurubhavAn na me zatruH ziSyaH putrasamo ' smi te . na cAsti sa pumAlloke yastvAM yudhi parAjayet .
saMjaya uvAca evaM bruvANo bIbhatsurjayadrathavadhotsukaH . tvarAyukto mahAbAhustvatsainyaM samupAdravat .
taM cakrarakSau pAJcAlyau yudhAmanyUttamaujasau . anvayAtAM mahAtmAnau vizantaM tAvakaM balam .
tato jayo mahArAja kRtavarmA ca sAtvataH . kAmbojazca zrutAyuzca dhanaJjayamavArayan .
teSAM daza sahasrANi rathAnAmanuyAyinAm . abhISAhAH zUrasenAH zibayo ' tha vasAtayaH .
mAvellakA lalityAzca kekayA madrakAstathA . nArAyaNAca gopAlAH kAmbojAnAM ca ye gaNAH .
karNena vijitAH pUrvaM saMgrAme zUrasammatAH . bhAradvAjaM puraskRtya hRSTAtmAno ' rjunaM prati .
putrazokAbhisaMtaptaM kruddhaM mRtyumivAntakam . tyajantaM tumule prANAn saMnaddhaM citrayodhinam .
gAhamAnamanIkAni mAtaGgamiva yUthapam . maheSvAsaM parAkrAntaM naravyAghramavArayan .
tataH pravavRte yuddhaM tumulaM lomaharSaNam . anyonyaM vai prArthayatAM yodhAnAmarjunasya ca .
jayadrathavadhaprepsumAyAntaM puruSarSabham . nyavArayanta sahitAH kriyA vyAdhimivotthitam .
trigatairabhavad yuddhaM kRtavairaiH kirITinaH . mahArathasamAjJAtairhatAnAM putranaptRbhiH .
te samAjJAya samprAptaM yajJiyaM turagottamam . viSayAntaM tato vIrA daMzitAH paryavArayan .
rathino baddhatUNIrAH sadazvaiH tUNIrA : sadazvaiH samalaMkRtaiH . parivArya hayaM rAjan grahItuM sampracakramuH .
tataH kirITI saMcintya teSAM tatra cikIrSitam . vArayAmAsa tAn vIrAn sAntvapUrvamariMdamaH .
tadanAdRtya te sarve zarairabhyahanastadA . tamorajobhyAM saMchannAMstAn kirITI nyavArayat .
tAnabravIt tato jiSNuH prahasanniva bhArata . nivartadhvamadharmajJAH zreyo jIvitameva ca .
sa hi vIraH prayAsyan vai dharmarAjena vAritaH . hatabAndhavA na te pArtha hantavyAH pArthivA iti .
sa tadA tad vacaH zrutvA dharmarAjasya dhImataH . tAn nivartadhvamityAha na nyavartanta cApi te .
tatastrigartarAjAnaM sUryavarmANamAhave . vicitya zarajAlena prajahAsa dhanaMjayaH .
tataste rathaghoSeNa sthanemisvanena ca . pUrayanto dizaH sarvA dhanaMjayamupAdravan .
sUryavarmA tataH pArthe zarANAM nataparvaNAm . zatAnyamuJcad rAjendra ladhvastramabhidarzayan .
tathaivAnye maheSvAsA ye ca tasyAnuyAyinaH . mumucuH zaravarSANi dhanaMjayavadhaiSiNaH .
sa tAn jyAmukhanirmuktairbahubhiH subahUzarAn . ciccheda pANDavo rAjaMste bhUmau nyapataMstadA .
ketuvarmA tu tejasvI tasyaivAvarajo yuvA . yuyudhe bhrAturAya pANDavena yazasvinA .
tamApatantaM samprekSya ketuvarmANamAhave . abhyannizitairvANairbIbhatsuH paravIrahA . .
ketuvarmaNyabhihate dhRtavarmA mahArathaH . rathenAzu samutpatya zarairjiSNumavAkirat .
tasya tAM zIghratAmIkSya tutoSAtIva vIryavAn . guDAkezo mahAtejA bAlasya dhRtavarmaNaH .
na saMdadhAnaM dadRze nAdadAnaM ca taM tadA . kirantameva sa zarAn dadRze pAkazAsaniH .
sa tu taM pUjayAmAsa dhRtavarmANamAhave . manasA tu muhUrtaM vai raNe samabhiharSayan .
taM pannagamiva kruddhaM kuruvIraH smayannivA prItipUrvaM mahAbAhuH prANairna vyaparopayat .
sa tathA rakSyamANo vai pArthenAmitatejasA . dhRtavarmA zaraM dIpta mumoca vijaye tadA .
sa tena vijayastUrNamAsId viddhaH kare bhRzam . mumoca gANDivaM mohAt tat papAtAtha bhUtale .
dhanuSaH patatastasya savyasAcikarAd vibho . babhUva sadRzaM rUpaM zakracApasya bhArata .
tasmin vipatite divaye mahAdhanuSi pArthivaH . jahAsa sasvanaM hAsa dhRtavarmA mahAhave .
tato roSArdito jiSNuH pramRtya rudhiraM karAt . dhanurAdatta tad divyaM zaravarvavarSa ca .
tato halahalAzabdo divaspRgabhavat tadA . nAnAvidhAnAM bhUtAnAM tatkarmANi prazaMsatAm .
tataH samprekSya saMkruddhaM kAlAntakayamopamam . jiSNuM traigartakA yodhAH parItAH paryavArayan . abhisRtya parIpsArthaM tataste dhRtavarmaNaH . parivavarguDAkezaM tatrAddhyad dhanaMjayaH .
tato yodhAn jaghAnAzu teSAM sa daza cASTa ca . mahendravajrapratimairAyasairbahubhiH zaraiH .
tAn samprabhagnAn samprekSya tvamANo dhanaMjayaH . zarairAzIviSAkArairjadhAna svanavaddhasan .
te bhagnamanasaH sarve traigartakamahArathAH . dizo ' bhidudruvU rAjan dhanaMjayazarArditAH .
tamUcuH puruSavyAghraM saMzaptakaniSUdanam . tavAsma kiMkarAH sarve sarve vai vazagAstava .
AjJApayasva naH pAthai prahvAn preSyAnavasthitAn . kariSyAmaH priyaM sarvaM tava kauravanandana .
etadAjJAya vacanaM sarvostAnabravIt tadA . jIvitaM rakSata nRpAH zAsanaM pratigRhyatAm .
yudhiSThira uvAca neha pazyAmi vibudhA rAdheyamamitaujasam . bhrAtarau ca mahAtmAnau yudhAmanyUttamaujasau . juhuvurye zarIrANi raNavahnau mahArathAH . rAjAno rAjaputrAzca ye madarthe hatA raNe .
kva te mahArathAH sarve zArdUlasamavikramAH . tairapyayaM jito lokaH kaccit puruSasattamaiH .
yadi lokAnimAn prAptAste ca sarve mahArathAH . sthitaM vitta hi mAM devA : sahitaM tairmahAtmabhiH .
kaccinna tairavApto ' yaM nRpairloko ' kSayaH zubhaH . na tairahaM vinA raMsye bhrAtRbhirjAtibhistathA .
mAturhi vacanaM zrutvA tadA salilakarmaNi . karNasya kriyatAM toyamiti tapyAmi tena vai .
idaM ca paritapyAmi punaH punarahaM surAH . yanmAtuH sadRzau pAdau tasyAhamamitAtmanaH . dRSTvaiva tau nAnugataH karNaM parabalArdanam . na hyasmAn karNasahitAn jayecchakro ' pi saMyuge .
tamahaM yatra tatrasthaM draSTumicchAmi sUryajam . avijJAto mayA yo ' sau ghAtitaH savyasAcinA .
bhImaM ca bhImavikrAntaM prANebhyo ' pi priyaM mama . arjunaM cendrasaMkAzaM yamau caiva yamopamau . draSTumicchAmi tAM cAhaM pAJcAlIM dharmacAriNIm . na ceha sthAtumicchAmi satyamevaM bravImi vaH .
kiM me bhrAtRvihInasya svargeNa surasattamAH . yatra te mama sa svargo nAyaM svargo mato mama .
devA UcuH yadi vai tatra te zraddhA gamyatAM putra mA ciram . priye hi tava vartAmo devarAjasya zAsanAt .
vaizampAyana ityuktvA taM tato devA devadUtamupAdizan . yudhiSThirasya suhRdo darzayeti paraMtapa . tataH kuntIsuto rAjA devadUtazca jagmatuH . sahitau rAjazArdUla yatra te puruSarSabhAH .
agrato devadUtazca yayau rAjA ca pRSThataH . panthAnamazubhaM durgaM sevitaM pApakarmabhiH .
tamasA saMvRtaM ghoraM kezazaivalazAdvalam . yuktaM pApakRtAM gandhairmIsazoNitakardamam . daMzotpAtakabhallUkamakSikAmazakAvRtam . itazcetazca kuNapaiH samantAt parivAritam .
asthikezasamAkIrNaM kRmikITasamAkulam . jvalanena pradIptena samantAt pariveSTitam .
ayomukhaizca kAkAdyairgudhaizca samabhidrutam . sUcImukhaistathA pretairvithyazailopamairvRtam .
medorudhirayuktaizca cchinnabAhUrupANibhiH . nikRttodarapAdaizca tatra tatra praveritaiH .
sa tatkuNapadurgandhamazivaM lomaharSaNam . jagAma rAjA dharmAtmA madhye bahu vicintayan .
dadarzoSNodakaiH pUrNA nadIM cApi sudurgamAm . asipatravanaM caiva nizitaM kSurasaMvRtam .
karambhavAlukAstaptA AyasIzca zilAH pRthak . lohakumbhIzca tailasya kvAthyamAnAH samantataH .
kUTazAlmalikaM cApi duHsparza tIkSNakaNTakam . dadarza cApi kaunteyo yAtanAH pApakarmiNAm .
sa taM durgandhamAlakSya devadUtamuvAca ha . kiyadadhvAnamasmAbhirgantavyamimamIdRzam .
kva ca te bhrAtaro mahyaM tanmamAkhyAtumarhasi . dezo ' yaM kazca devAnAmetadicchAmi veditum .
sa saMnivavRte zrutvA dharmarAjasya bhASitam . devadUto ' bravIccainametAvad gamanaM tava .
nivartitavyo hi mayA tathAsamyukto divaukasaiH . yadi zrAnto ' si rAjendra tvamathAgantumarhasi .
yudhiSThirastu nirviNNastena gandhena mUrcchitaH . nivartane dhRtamanAH paryAvartata bhArata .
sa saMnivRtto dharmAtmA duHkhazokasamAhataH . zuzrAva tatra vadatAM dInA vAcaH samantataH .
bho bho dharmaja rAjarSe puNyAbhijana pANDava . anugrahArthamasmAkaM tiSTha tAvanmuhUrtakam .
AyAti tvayi durdharSe vAti puNyaH samIraNaH . tava gandhAnugastAta yenAsmAn sukhamAgamat .
te vayaM pArtha dIrghasya kAlasya puruSarSabha . sukhamAsAdayiSyAmastvAM dRSTvA rAjasattama .
saMtiSThasva mahAbAho muhUrtamapi bhArata . tvayi tiSThati kauravya yAtanAsmAn na bAdhate .
evaM bahuvidhA vAcaH kRpaNA vedanAvatAm . tasmin deze sa zuzrAva samantAd vadatAM nRpa .
teSAM tu vacanaM zrutvA dayAvAn dInabhASiNAm . aho kRcchramiti prAha tasthau sa ca yudhiSThiraH .
sa tA giraH purastAd vai zrutapUrvA punaH punaH . glAnAnAM duHkhitAnAM ca nAbhyajAnata pANDavaH .
abudhyamAnastA vAco dharmaputro yudhiSThiraH . uvAca ke bhavanto vai kimarthamiha tiSThatha .
ityuktAste tataH sarve samantAdavabhASire . karNo ' haM bhImaseno ' hamarjuno ' hamiti prabho .
nakulaH sahadevo ' haM dhRSTadyumno ' hamityuta . draupadI draupadeyAzca ityevaM te vicukruzuH .
tA vAcaH sa tadA zrutvA taddezasadRzIrnRpa . tato vimamRze rAjA kiM tvidaM daivakAritam .
kiM tu tat kaluSaM karma kRtamebhirmahAtmabhiH . karNena draupadeyairvA pAJcAlyA vA sumadhyayA . ya ime pApagandhe ' smin deze santi sudAruNe . nAhaM jAnAmi sarveSAM duSkRtaM puNyakarmaNAm .
kiM kRtvA dhRtarASTrasya putro rAjA suyodhanaH . tathA zriyA yutaH pApaiH saha sarvaiH padAnugaiH .
mahendra iva lakSmIvAnAste paramapUjitaH . kasyedAnI vikAro ' yaM ya ime narakaM gatAH .
sarvadharmavidaH zUrAH satyAgamaparAyaNAH . kSatradharmaratAH santo yajvAno bhUridakSiNAH .
kiM nu supto ' smi jAgarmi cetayAmi na cetaye . ahocittavikAro ' yaM syAd vA me cittavibhramaH .
evaM bahuvidhaM rAjA vimamarza yudhiSThiraH . duHkhazokasamAviSTazcintAvyAkulitendriyaH .
krodhamAhArayaccaiva tIvra dharmasuto nRpaH . devAMzca garhayAmAsa dharmaM caiva yudhiSThiraH .
sa tIvragandhasaMtapto devadUtamuvAca ha . gamyatAM tatra yeSAM tvaM dUtasteSAmupAntikam .
na hyahaM tatra yAsyAmi sthito ' smIti nivedyatAm . matsaMzrayAdime dUtAH sukhino bhrAtaro hi me .
ityuktaH sa tadA dUtaH pANDuputreNa dhImatA . jagAma tatra yatrAste devarAjaH zatakratuH .
nivedayAmAsa ca tad dharmarAjacikIrSitam . yathoktaM dharmaputreNa sarvameva janAdhipa .
janamejaya uvAca . evaM te matsyanagare pracchannAH kurunandanAH . ata UrdhvaM mahAvIryAH kimakurvata vai dvijaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca evaM matsyasya nagare pracchannAH kurunandanAH . ArAdhayanto rAjAnaM yadakurvata tacchRNu .
tRNabinduprasAdAcca dharmasya ca mahAtmanaH . ajJAtavAsamevaM tu virATanagare ' vasan .
yudhiSThiraH sabhAstAro matsyAnAmabhavat priyaH . tathaiva ca virATasya saputrasya vizAmpate .
sa hyakSahRdayajJastAn krIDayAmAsa pANDavaH . akSavatyAM yathAkAmaM sUtrabaddhAniva dvijAn .
ajJAtaM ca virATasya vijitya vasu dharmarAT . bhrAtRbhyaH puruSavyAghro yathArha samprayacchati .
bhImaseno ' pi mAMsAni bhakSyANi vividhAni ca . atisRSTAni matsyena vikrINIte yudhiSThire .
vAsAMsi parijIrNAni labdhAnyantaHpure ' rjunaH . vikrINAnasca sarvebhyaH pANDavebhyaH prayacchati .
sahadevo ' pi gopAnAM veSamAsthAya pANDavaH . dadhi kSIraM ghRtaM caiva pANDavebhyaH prayacchati .
nakulo ' pi dhanaM labdhvA kRte karmaNi vAjinAm . tuSTe tasmin narapatau pANDavebhyaH prayacchati .
kRSNA tu sarvAn bhartRstAn nirIkSantI tapasvinI . yathA punaravijJAtA tathA carati bhAminI .
evaM sampAdayantaste tadAnyonyaM mahArathAH . virATanagare ceruH punargarbhadhRtA iva .
sAzaGkA dhArtarASTrasya bhayAt pANDusutAstadA . prekSamANAstadA kRSNAmUSuzchannA narAdhipa .
atha mAse caturthe tu brahmaNaH sumahotsavaH . AsIt samRddho matsyeSu puruSANAM susammataH .
tatra mallAH samApeturdigbhyo rAjan sahasrazaH . samAje brahmaNo rAjan yathA pazupateriva .
mahAkAyA mahAvIryAH kAlakhajA ivAsurAH . vIryonmattA balodagrA rAjJA samabhipUjitAH .
siMhaskandhakaTigrIvAH svAvadAtA manasvinaH . asakRllabdhalakSAste raGge pArthivasaMnidhau .
teSAmeko mahAnAsIt sarvamallAnathAhvayat . AvalgamAnaM taM raGge nopatiSThati kazcana .
yadA sarve vimanasaste mallA hatacetasaH . atha sUdena taM mallaM yodhayAmAsa matsyarAT . .
nodyamAnastadA bhImo duHkhenaivAkaronmatim . na hi zaknoti vivRte pratyAkhyAtuM narAdhipam .
tataH sa puruSavyAghraH zArdUlazithilazcaran . praviveza mahAraGgaM virATamabhipUjayan .
babandha kakSAM kaunteyastataH saMharSayaJjanam . tatastu vRtrasaMkAzaM bhImo mallaM samAhvayat .
jImUtaM nAma taM tatra mallaM prakhyAtavikramam . tAvubhau sumahotsAhAvubhau bhImaparAkramau . mattAviva mahAkAyau vAraNau SaSTihAyanau . tatastau narazArdUlo bAhuyuddhaM samIyatuH .
vIrau paramasaMhRSTAvanyonyajayakAkSiNau . AsIt subhImaH sampAto vajraparvatayoriva .
ubhau paramasaMhRSTau balenAtibalAvubhau . anyonyasyAntaraM prepsU parasparajayaiSiNau .
ubhau paramasaMhaSTau mattAviva mahAgajau . kRtapratikRtaizcitrairbAhubhizca susarUTaiH .
saMnipAtAvadhUtaizca pramauthonmathanaistathA . kSepaNairmuSTibhizcaiva varAhodbhUtani : svanaiH .
talairvajranipAtaizca prasRSTAbhistathaiva ca . zalAkAnasakhapAtaizca pAdodbhUtaizca dAruNaiH .
jAnubhizcAzmanirghoSaiH zirobhizcAvaghadanaiH . tad yuddhamabhavad ghoramazastraM bAhutejasA .
balaprANena zUrANAM samAjotsavasaMnidhau . arajyata jana : sarvaH sotkruSTaninadotthitaH .
balinoH saMyuge rAjan vRtravAsavayoriva . prakarSaNAkarSaNayorabhyAkarSavikarSaNaiH . AkarSaturadhAnyonyaM jAnubhizcApi jaghatuH . mahatA bhartsayantau parasparam .
vyUDhoraskau dIrghabhujau niyuddhakuzalAvubhau . bAhubhiH samasajjetAmAyasaiH paridhairiva .
cakarSa dordhyAmutpAtya bhImo mallamamitrahA . ninadantamabhikrozan zArdUla iva vAraNam . tataH zabdena
samudyamya mahAbAhUrdhAmayAmAsa vIryavAn . tato mallAca matsyAzcaM vismayaM cakrire param .
bhrAmayitvA zataguNaM gatasattvamacetanam . pratyapiMSanmahAbAhurmallaM bhuvi vRkodaraH .
tasmin vinihate vIre jImUte lokavizrUte . virATaH paramaM harSamagacchad bAndhavaiH saha .
praharSAt pradadau vittaM bahu rAjA mahAmanAH . ballavAya mahAraGge yathA vaizravaNastathA .
evaM sa subahUn mallAn puruSAMzca mahAbalAn . vinighnan matsyarAjasya prItimAharaduttamAm .
yadAsya tulyaH puruSo na kazcit tatra vidyate . tato vyApraizca siMhaizca dviradaizcApyayodhayat .
punarantaHpuragataH strANAM madhye vRkodaraH . yodhyate sa virATena siMhairmattairmahAbalaiH .
bIbhatsurapi gItena svanRtyena ca pANDavaH . virATaM toSayAmAsa sarvAzcAntaHpurastriyaH .
azvairvinItairjavanastatra tatra samAgataH . toSayAmAsa rAjAnaM nakulo nRpasattamam . tasmai pradeyaM prAyacchat prIto rAjA dhanaM bahu .
vinItAn vRSabhAn dRSTvA sahadevasya cAbhitaH . dhanaM dadau bahuvidhaM virATaH puruSarSabhaH .
draupadI prekSya tAn sarvAn klizyamAnAn mahArathAn . nAtiprItamanA rAjan niHzvAsaparamAbhavat .
evaM te nyavasaMstatra pracchannAH puruSarSabhAH . karmANi tasya kurvANA virATanRpatestadA .
janamejaya uvAca kathito dhArtarASTrANAmArSaH sambhava uttamaH . amanuSyo manuSyANAM bhavatA brahmavAdinA .
nAmadheyAni cApyeSAM kathyamAnAni bhAgazaH . tvattaH zrutAni me brahman pANDavAnAM ca kIrtaya .
te hi sarve mahAtmAno devarAjaparAkramAH . tvathaivAMzAvataraNe devabhAgAH prakIrtitAH .
etadicchAmyahaM zrotumatimAnuSakarmaNAm . teSAmAjananaM sarvaM vaizampAyana kIrtaya .
vaizampAyana uvAca rAjA pANDurmahAraNye mRgavyAlaniSevite . caran maithunadharmasthaM dadarza mRgayUthapam .
tatastAM ca mRgIM taM ca rukmapuDakhaiH supatribhiH . nirvibheda zaraistIkSNaiH pANDuH paJcabhirAzugaiH .
sa ca rAjan mahAtejA RSiputrastapodhanaH . bhAryayA saha tejasvI mRgarUpeNa saMgataH .
saMsaktazca tayA mRgyA mAnuSImIrayan giram . kSaNena patito bhUmau vilalApAkulendrayaH .
mRga uvAca kAmamanyuparItA hi buddhyA virahitA api . varjayanti nRzaMsAni pApeSvapi ratA narAH . na vidhiM grasate prajJA prajJAM tu grasate vidhiH . vidhiparyAgatAnAn prAjJo na pratipadyate .
zazvaddharmAtmanA mukhye kule jAtasya bhArata . kAmalobhAbhibhUtasya kathaM te calitA matiH .
pANDuruvAca zatrUNAM yA vadhe vRttiH sA mRgANAM vadhe smRtA . rAjJAM mRga na mAM mohAt tvaM garhayitumarhasi .
acchadmanA mAyayA ca mRgANAM vadha iSyate . sa eva dharmo rAjJAM tu taddhi tvaM kiM nu garhase .
agastyaH satramAsInazcakAra mRgayAmRSiH . AraNyAn sarvadevebhyo mRgAn preSan mahAvane . pramANadRSTadharmeNa kathamasmAn vigarhase . agastyasyAbhicAreNa yuSmAkaM vihito vadhaH .
mRga uvAca na ripUn vai samuddizya vimuJcanti narAH zarAn . randhra eSAM vizeSeNa vadhaH kAle prazasyate .
pANDuruvAca pramattamapramattaM vA vivRtaM janti caujasA . upAyairvividhaistIkSNaiH : kasmAnmRga vigarhase .
mRga uvAca nAhaM jantaM mRgAn rAjan vigarhe cAtmakAraNAt . maithunaM tu pratIkSyaM me tvayehAdyAnRzaMsyataH .
sarvabhUtahite kAle sarvabhUtepsite tathA . ko hi vidvAn mRgaM hanyAccarantaM maithunaM vane .
asyAM mRgyAM ca rAjendra harSAnmaithunamAcaram . puruSArthaphalaM kartuM tat tvayA viphalIkRtam .
pauravANAM mahArAja teSAmakliSTakarmaNAm . vaMze jAtasya kauravya nAnurUpamidaM tava .
nRzaMsaM karma sumahat sarvalokavigarhitam . asvay/amayazasyaM cApyadharmiSThaM ca bhArata .
strIbhogAnAM vizeSajJaH zAstradharmArthatattvavit . nArhastvaM surasaMkAza kartumasvay/amIdRzam .
tvayA nRzaMsakartAraH pApAcArAzca mAnavAH . nigrAhyAH pArthivazreSTha trivargaparivarjitAH .
kiM kRtaM te narazreSTha mAmihAnAgasaM jatA . muniM mUlaphalAhAraM mRgaveSadharaM nRpa . vasamAnamaraNyeSu nityaM zamaparAyaNam . tvayAhaM hiMsito yasmAt tasmAt tvAmapyahaM zape .
dvayornRzaMsakartAramavazaM kAmamohitam . jIvitAntakaro bhAva evamevAgamiSyati .
ahaM ki kiMdamo nAma tapasA bhAvito muniH . vyapatrapanmanuSyANAM mRgyAM maithunamAcaram . mRgo bhUtvA mRgaiH sArdhaM carAmi gahane vane . na tu te brahmahatyeyaM bhaviSyatyavijAnataH .
mRgarUpadharaM hatvA mAmevaM kAmamohitam . asya tu tvaM phalaM mUDha prApsyasIdRzameva hi .
priyayA saha saMvAsaM prApya kAmavimohitaH . tvamapyasyAmavasthAyAM pretalokaM gamiSyasi .
antakAle hi saMvAsaM yayA gantAsi kAntayA . pretarAjapuraM prAptaM sarvabhUtaduratyayam . bhaktyA matimatAM zreSTha saiva tvAnugamiSyati .
vartamAnaH sukhe duHkhaM yathAhaM prApitastvayA . tathA tvAM ca sukhaM prAptaM duHkhamabhyAgamiSyati .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktvA suduHkhArto jIvitAt sa vyamucyata . mRgaH pANDuzca duHkhArtaH kSaNena samapadyata .
vaizampAyana uvAca tataH satyavatI dInA kRpaNA putragRddhinI . putrasya kRtvA kAryANi snuSAbhyAM saha bhArata . samAzvAsya snuSe te ca bhISmaM zastrabhRtAM varam . dharmaM ca pitRvaMzaM ca mAtRvaMzaM ca bhAvinI . prasamIkSya mahAbhAgA gAGgeyaM vAkyamabravIt . zAntanodharmanityasya kauravyasya yazasvinaH . tvayi piNDazca kIrtizca saMtAnaM ca pratiSThitam .
yathA karma zubhaM kRtvA svargopagamanaM dhruvam . yathA cAyurbuvaM satye tvayi dharmastathA dhruvaH .
vettha dharmAMzca dharmajJa samAsenetareNa ca . vividhAstvaM zrutIrvettha vedAGgAni ca sarvazaH .
vyavasthAnaM ca te dharme kulAcAraM ca lakSaye . pratipattiM ca kRcchreSu zukrAGgirasayoriva .
tasmAt subhRzamAzvasya tvayi dharmabhRtAM vara . kArye tvAM viniyokSyAmi tacchutvA kartumarhasi .
mama putrastava bhrAtA vIryavAn supriyazca te . bAla eva gataH svargamaputraH puruSarSabha . ime mahiSyau bhrAtuste kAzirAjasute zubhe . rUpayauvanasampanne putrakAme ca bhArata . tayorutpAdayApatyaM saMtAnAya kulasya naH . manniyogAnmahAbAho dharmaM kartumihArhasi .
rAjye caivAbhiSicyasva bhAratAnanuzAdhi ca . dArAMzca kuru dharmeNa mA dharmeNa mA nimanjI : pitAmahAn .
vaizampAyana uvAca tathocyamAno mAtrA sa suhRddhizca paraMtapaH . ityuvAcAtha dharmAtmA dharmyamevottaraM vacaH .
asaMzayaM paro dharmastvayA mAtarudAhRtaH . rAjyArthe nAbhiSiJcayaM nopeyAM jAtu maithunam . tvamapatyaM prati ca me pratijJAM vettha vai parAm . jAnAsi ca yathAvRttaM zulkahetostvadantare . sa satyavati satyaM te pratijAnAmyahaM punaH .
parityajeyaM trailokyaM rAjyaM deveSu vA punaH . yad vApyadhikametAbhyAM na tu satyaM kathaMcana .
tyajeca pRthivI gandhamApazca rasamAtmanaH . jyotistathA tyajed rUpaM vAyuH sparzaguNaM tyajet . prabhAM samutsRjedarko dhUmaketustathopmatAm . tyajecchabdaM tathA ' ' kAzaM somaH zItAMzutAM tyajet .17 .
vikramaM vRtrahA jahyAd dharmaM jahyAca dharmarAT . na tvahaM satyamutssraSTuM vyavaseyaM kathaMcana .
mAtA satyavatI bhISmamuvAca tadanantaram . jAnAmi te sthitiM satye parAM satyaparAkramA icchan sRjethAstrIllokAnanyAMstvaM svena tejasA . jAnAmi caivaM satyaM tanmadarthe yacca bhASitam . ApaddharmaM tvamAvekSya vaha paitAmahI dhuram .
yathA te kulatantuzca dharmazca na parAbhavet . suhRdazca prahaSyeraMstathA kuru paraMtapa .
lAlapyamAnAM tAmevaM kRpaNAM putragRddhinIm . dharmAdapetaM bruvatIM bhISmo bhUyo ' bravIdidam .
rAjJi dharmAnavekSasva mA naH sarvAn vyanInazaH . satyAccyutiH kSatriyasya na dharmeSu prazasyate .
zAntanorapi saMtAnaM yathA syAdakSayaM bhuvi . tat te dharmaM pravakSyAmi kSAtraM rAjJi sanAtanam .
zrutvA taM pratipadyasva prAjJaiH saha purohitaiH . ApaddharmArthakuzalairlokatantramavekSya ca .
saMjaya uvAca tasmiMstathA vartamAne karNarAkSasayormadhe . alAyudho rAkSasendro vIryavAnabhyavartata .
mahatyA senayA yukto duryodhanamupAgamat . rAkSasAnAM virUpANAM sahasraH parivAritaH .
nAnArUpadharaivIraiH pUrvavairamanusmaran . tasya jJAtirhi vikrAnto brAhmaNAdo bako hataH .
kirmIrazca mahAtejA haiDimbazca sakhA tadA . sa dIrghakAlasadhyuSitaM pUrvavairamanusmaran .
vijJAyaitannizAyuddhaM jighAMsurbhImamAhave . sa matta iva mAtaGgaH saMkruddhaH iva coragaH .
duryodhanamidaM vAkyamabravId yuddhalAlasaH . viditaM te mahArAja yathA bhImena rAkSasAH . hiDimbabakakirmIrA nihatA mama bAndhavAH . parAmarzazca kanyAyA hiDimbAyAH kRtaH purA .
kimanyad rAkSasAnanyAnasmAMzca paribhUya ha . tamahaM sagaNaM rAjan savAjirathakuJjaram . haiDimbi ca sahAmAtyaM hantumabhyAgataH svayam . adya kuntIsutAn sarvAn vAsudevapurogamAn . hatvA sambhakSayiSyAmi sarvairanucaraiH saha . nivAraya balaM sarvaM vayaM yotsyAma pANDavAn .
tasyaitad vacanaM zrutvA hRSTo duryodhanastadA . pratigRhyAbravId vAkyaM bhrAtRbhiH parivAritaH .
tvAM puraskRtya sagarNa vayaM yotsyAmahe parAn . na hi vairAntamanasaH sthAsyanti mama sainikAH .
evamastviti rAjAnamuktvA rAkSasapuGgavaH . abhyayAt tvarito bhaimi sahitaH puruSAdakaiH .
dIpyamAnena vapuSA rathenAdityavarcasA . tAdRzenaiva rAjendra yAdRzena ghaTotkacaH .
tasyApyatulanirghoSo bahutoraNacitritaH . RkSacarmAvanaddhAGgo nalvamAtro mahArathaH .
tasyApi turagAH zIghrA hastikAyAH kharakhanAH . zataM yuktA mahAkAyA mAMsazoNitabhojanAH .
tasyApi sthanirghoSo mahAmegharavopamaH . tasyApi sumahacApaM dRDhajyaM kanakojavalam .
tasyApyakSasamA bANA rukmapuGkhAH zilAzitAH . so ' pi vIro mahAbAhuryathaiva sa ghaTotkacaH .
tasyApi gomAyubalAbhigupto babhUva keturvvalanArkatulyaH . sa cApi rUpeNa ghaTotkacasya zrImattamo vyAkuladIpitAsyaH .
dIptAGgado dIptakirITamAlI baddhasraguSNISanibaddhakhaGgaH . gadI bhuzuNDI musalI halI ca zarAsanI vAraNatulyavarNA .
rathena tenAnalavarcasA tadA . vidrAvayan pANDavavAhinIM tAm . rarAja saMkhye parivartamAno vidyunmAlI megha ivAntarikSa .
te cApi sarvapravarA narendrA mahAbalA varmiNazcarmiNazcA harSAnvitA yuyudhastasya rAjan samantataH pANDavayodhavIrAH .
saMjaya uvAca tato duryodhano rAjA lohitAyati bhAskare . saMgrAmarabhaso bhImaM hantukAmo ' bhyadhAvata .
tamAyAntamabhiprekSya nRvIraM dRDhavairiNam . bhImasenaH susaMkruddha idaM vacanamabravIt .
ayaM sa kAlaH samprApto varSapUgAbhivAJchitaH . adya tvAM nihaniSyAmi yadi notsRjase raNam .
adya kuntyAH pariklezaM vanavAsaM ca kRtsnazaH . draupadyAzca pariklezaM praNeSyAmi hate tvayi .
yat purA matsarI bhUtvA pANDavAnavamanyase . tasya pApasya gAndhAre pazya vyasanamAgatam .
karNasya matamAsthAya saubalasya ca yat purA . acintya pANDavAn kAmAd yatheSTaM kRtavAnasi .
yAcamAnaM ca yanmohAd dAzArhamavamanyase . ulUkasya samAdezaM yad dadAsi ca hRSTavat .
tena tvAM nihaniSyAmi sAnubandhaM sabAndhavam . samIkariSye tat pApaM yat purA kRtavAnasi .
evamuktvA dhanurghoraM vikRSyobhrAmya cAsakRt . samAdhatta zarAn ghorAn mahAzanisamaprabhAn .
SaDviMzatimatha saMkruddho mumocAzu suyodhane . jvalitAgnizikhAkArAn vajrakalpAnajihmagAn .
tato ' sya kArmukaM dvAbhyAM sUtaM dvAbhyAM ca vivyadhe . caturbhirazvAJjavanAnanayad yamasAdanam .
dvAbhyAM ca suvikRSTAbhyAM zarAbhyAmarimardanaH . chatraM ciccheda samare rAjJastasya narottama .
SaDbhizca tasya ciccheda jvalantaM dhvajamuttamam . chittvA taM ca nanAdoccaistava putrasya pazyataH .
rathAcca sa dhvajaH zrImAn nAnAratnavibhUSitAt . papAta sahasA bhUmau vidyujjaladharAdiva .
jvalantaM sUryasaMkAzaM nAgaM maNimayaM zubham . dhvajaM kurupatezchinnaM dadRzuH sarvapArthivAH .
athainaM dazabhirbANaistotrairiva mahAdvipam . AjaghAna raNe vIraM smayanniva mahArathaH .
tataH sa rAjA sindhUnA rathazreSTho mahArathaH . duryodhanasya jagrAha pArNi satpuruSairvRtaH .
kRpazca rathinAM zreSThaH kauramamitaujasam . Aropayad rathaM rAjan duryodhanamamarSaNam .
sa gADhaviddho vyathito bhImasenena saMyuge . niSasAda rathopasthe rAjan duryodhanastadA .
parivArya tato bhImaM jetukAmo jayadrathaH . rathairanekasAhaurbhImasyAvArayad dizaH .
dhRSTaketustato rAjannabhimanyuzca vIryavAn . kekayA draupadeyAzca tava putrAnayodhayan . citrasenaH sucitrazca citrAGgazcitradarzanaH . cArucitraH sucAraca tathA nandopanandakauH .
aSTAvete maheSvAsAH sukumArA yazasvinaH . abhimanyurathaM rAjan samantAt paryavArayan .
AjaghAna tatastUrNamabhimanyurmahAmanAH . ekaikaM paJcabhirvANaiH zitaiH saMnataparvabhiH . : .
vajramRtyupratIkAzairvicitrAyudhaniHsRtaH . amRSyamANAste sarve saubhadraM rathasattamam . vavRSurmAgaistIkSNairgiriM merumivAmbudAH . sa pIDyamAnaH samare kRtAstro yuddhadurmadaH .
abhimanyurmahArAja tAvakAn samakampayat . yathA devAsure yuddhe vajrapANirmahAsurAn .
vikarNasya tato bhallAn preSayAmAsa bhArata . caturdaza rathazreSTho ghorAnAzIviSopamAna .
sa tairvikarNasya rathAt pAtayAmAsa vIryavAn . dhvajaM sUtaM hayAMzcaiva nRtyamAna ivAhave .
punazcAnyAzarAn pItAnakuNThAgrAzilAzitAn . preSayAmAsa saMkruddho vikarNAya mahAbalaH .
te vikarNaM samAsAdya kaGkabarhiNavAsasaH . bhittavA dehaM gatA bhUmi jvalanta iva pannagAH .
te zarA hemapuGkhAgrA vyadRzyanta mahItale . vikarNarudhiraklinnA vamanta iva zoNitam .
vikarNaM vIkSya nirbhinnaM tasyaivAnye sahodarAH . abhyadravanta samare saubhadrapramukhAn rathAn .
abhiyAtvA tathaivAnyAn rathAMstAn sUryavarcasaH . avidhyan samare ' nyonyaM saMrambhAd yuddhadurmadAH .
durmukhaH zrutakarmANaM viddhvA saptabhirAzugaiH . dhvajamekena ciccheda sArathiM cAsya saptabhiH .
azvAJjAmbUnadairjAlaiH pracchannAn vAtaraMhasaH . jaghAn SaDbhirAsAdya sArathiM cAbhyapAtayat .
sa hatAzve rathe tiSThazrutakarmA mahArathaH . zaktiM cikSepa saMkruddho maholkA jvalitAmiva .
sA durmukhasya vimalaM varma bhittvA yazasvinaH . vidArya prAvizad bhUmiM dIpyamAnA svatejasA .
taM dRSTvA virathaM tatra sutasomo mahArathaH . pazyatAM sarvasainyAnAM rathamAropayat svakam .
zrutakIrtistathA vIro jayatsenaM sutaM tava . abhyayAt samare rAjan hantukAmo yazasvinam .
tasya vikSipatazcApaM zrutakIrtermahAsvanam . ciccheda samare tUrNaM jayatsenaH sutastava . kSurapreNa sutIkSNena prahasanniva bhArata . taM dRSTvA chinnadhanvAnaM zatAnIkaH sahodaram .
abhyapadyata tejasvI siMhavanninadan muhuH . zatAnIkastu samare dRDhaM visphArya kArmukam .
vivyAdha dazabhistUrNaM jayatsenaM zilImukhaiH . nanAda sumahAnAdaM prabhinna iva vAraNaH .
athAnyena sutIkSNena sarvAvaraNabhedinA . zatAnIko jayatsenaM vivyAdha hRdaye bhRzam .
tathA tasmin vartamAne duSkarNo bhrAturantike . ciccheda samare cApaM nAkuleH krodhamUrcchitaH .
athAnyad dhanurAdAya bhArasAhamanuttamam . samAdatta zarAn ghorAjzatAnIko mahAbalaH .
tiSTha tiSTheti cAmantrya duSkarNaM bhrAturagrataH . mumocAsmai zitAn bANAjvalitAn pannagAniva .
tato ' sya dhanurekena dvAbhyAM sUtaM ca mAriSa . ciccheda samare tUrNaM taM ca vivyAdha saptabhiH .
azvAn manojavAMstasya karburAn vAtaraMhasaH . jaghAna nizitaistUrNaM sarvAn dvAdazabhiH zaraiH .
athApareNa bhallena suyuktenAzupAtinA . duSkarNaM sudRDhaM kruddho vivyAdha hRdaye bhRzam .
sa papAta tato bhUmo vajrAhata iva drumaH . duSkarNaM vyathitaM dRSTvA paJca rAjan mahArathAH .
jighAMsantaH zatAnIkaM sarvataH paryavArayan . chAdyamAnaM zaravrAtaiH zatAnIkaM yazasvinam .
abhyadhAvanta saMkruddhAH kekayAH paJca sodarAH . tAnabhyApatataH prekSya tava putrA mahArathAH .
pratyudyayurmahArAja gajAniva mahAgajAH . durmukho durjayazcaiva tathA durmarSaNo yuvA .
zatrujayaH zatrusahaH sarve kruddhA yazasvinaH . pratyudyAtA mahArAja kekayAn bhrAtaraH samam .
rathairnagarasaMkAzairhayairyuktairmanojavaiH . nAnAvarNavicitrAbhiH patAkAbhiralaMkRtaiH .
varacApadharA vIrA vicitrakavacadhvajAH . vivizuste paraM sainyaM siMhA iva vanAd vanam .
teSAM sutamulaM yuddhaM vyatiSaktarathadvipam . avartata mahAraudraM nighnatAmitaretaram .
anyonyAgaskRtAM rAjan yamarASTravivardhanam . muhUrtAstamite sUrye cakruryuddhaM sudAruNam .
rathinaH sAdinazcAtha vyakIryanta sahasrazaH . tataH zAntanavaH kruddhaH zaraiH saMnataparvabhiH . nAzayAmAsa senAM tAM bhISmasteSAM mahAtmanAm . paJcAlAnAM ca sainyAni zarairninye yamakSayam .
evaM bhittvA maheSvAsaH pANDavAnAmanIkinIm . kRtvA ' vahAraM sainyAnAM yayau svazibiraM nRpa .
dharmarAjo ' pi samprekSya dhRSTadyumnavRkodarau . mUrdhni caitAvupAghrAya prahRSTaH zibiraM yayau .
vaizampAyana uvAca etat pRSTvA sUtaputraM hRcchokenArdito bhRzam . jaye nirAzaH putrANAM dhRtarASTro ' patat kSitau .
taM visaMjJaM nipatitaM siSicuH paricArikAH . jalenAtyarthazItena vIjantyaH puNyagandhinA .
patitaM cainamAlokya samantAd bharatastriyaH . parivarmahArujamaspRzaMzcaiva pANibhiH .
utthApya cainaM zanakai rAjAnaM pRthivItalAt . AsanaM prApayAmAsurvASpakaNThyo varAnanAH .
AsanaM prApya rAjA tu mUrchayAbhipariplutaH . nizceSTo ' tiSThata tadA vIjyamAnaH samantataH .
sa labvA zanakaiH saMjJAM vepamAno mahIpatiH . punargAvalgaNiM sUtaM paryapRcchad yathAtatham .
dhRtarASTra uvAca yaH sa udyannivAdityo jyotiSA praNudaMstamaH . ajAtazatrumAyAntaM kastaM droNAdavArayat . prabhinnamiva mAtaGgaM yathA kruddhaM tarasvinam . prasannavadanaM dRSTvA pratidviradagAminam . vAsitAsaMgame yadvadajayyaM prati yUthapaiH . nijadhAna raNe vIrAn vIraH puruSasattamaH .
yo hoko hi mahAvIryo nirdahed ghoracakSuSA . kRttraM duryodhanabalaM dhRtimAn satyasaMgaraH .
cakSurhaNaM jaye sakta miSvAsadharamacyutam . dAntaM bahumataM loke ke zUrAH paryavArayan .
ke duSpradharSe rAjAnamiSvAsadharamacyutam . samAsedunaravyAghraM kaunteyaM tatra mAmakAH .
tarasaivAbhipadyAtha yo vai droNamupAdravat . yaH karoti mahat karma zatrUNAM vai mahAbalaH . mahAkAyo mahotsAho nAgAyutasamo bale . taM bhImasenamAyAntaM ke zUrAH paryavArayan .
yadA ' ' yAjjaladaprakhyo rathaH paramavIryavAn . parjanya iva vIbhatsustumulAmazanIM sRjan .
visRjaJcharajAlAni varSANi maghavAniva . avasphUrjan dizaH sarvAstalanemisvanena ca .
cApavidyutprabho ghoro rathagulmavalAhakaH . sa nemighoSastanitaH zarazabdAtibanadhuraH .
roSAnilasamudbhUto mano ' bhiprAyazIghragaH . marmAtigo vANadharastumulaH zoNitodakaiH . samlAvayan dizaH sarvA mAnavairAstaran mahIm . bhImani : svanito raudro duryodhanapurogamAn . yuddhe ' bhyaSiJcad vijayo gApatraiH zilAzitaiH . gANDIvaM dhArayan dhImAn kIdRzaM vo manastadA . .
ighusambAdhamAkAzaM kurvan kapivaradhvajaH . yadA ' ' yAt kathamAsIt tu tadA pArthaM samIkSatAm .
kaccid gANDIvazabdena na praNazyati vaibalam . yadvaH sabhairavaM kurvannarjuno bhRzamanvayAt .
kaccinnApAnudat prANAniSubhivoM dhanaMjayaH . vAto vegAdivAvidhyanmedhAzaragaNairnRpAn .
ko hi gANDIvadhanvAnaM raNe soDhuM naro ' rhati . yamupazrutya senAgre jana : sarvo vidIryate .
yatsenAH samakampanta yadvIrAnaspRzad bhayam . ke tatra nAjahurdoNaM ke kSudrAH prAdravan bhayAt .
ke vA tatra tanUMstyaktvA pratIpaM mRtyumAvrajan . amAnuSANAM jetAraM yuddheSvapi dhanaMjayam .
na ca vegaM sitAzvasya visahiSyanti mAmakAH . gANDIvasya ca nirghoSaM prAvRDjaladani : svanam .
viSvakseno yasya yantA yasya yoddhA dhanaMjayaH . azakyaH sa ratho jetuM manye devAsurairapi .
sukumAro yuvA zUro darzanIyazca pANDavaH . medhAvI nipuNo dhImAn yudhi satyaparAkramaH .
ArAvaM vipulaM kurvan vyathayan sarvasainikAn . yadA ' ' yAnnakulo droNaM ke zUrAH paryavArayan .
AzIviSa iva kruddhaH sahadevo yadAbhyayAt . kadanaM kariSyaJchatrUNAM tejasA durjayo yudhi .
AryavratamamodheSu dvImantamaparAjitam . sahadevaM tamAyAntaM ke zUrAH paryavArayan .
yastu sauvIrarAjasya pramathya mahatIM camUm . Adatta mahiSIM bhojAM kAmyAM sarvAGgazobhanAm .
satyaM dhRtizca zaurye ca brahmacarye ca kevalam . sarvANi yuyudhAne ' smin nityAni puruSarSabhe .
balinaM satyakarmANamadInamaparAjitam . vAsudevasamaM yuddhe vAsudevAdanantaram .
dhanaMjayopadezena zreSThamiSvastrakarmaNi . pArthena samamastreSu kastaM droNAdavArayat .
vRSNInAM pravaraM vIraM zUraM sarvadhanuSmatAm . rAmeNa samamastreSu yazasA vikrameNa ca .
satyaM dhRtirmatiH zauryaM brAhmaM cAstramanuttamam . sAtvate tAni sarvANi trailokyamiva kezave .
tamevaMguNasampannaM durdhAramapi daivataiH . samAsAdya maheSvAsaM ke zUrAH paryavArayan .
paJcAleSUttamaM vIramuttamAbhijanapriyam . nityamuttamakarmANamuttamaujasamAhave .
yuktaM dhanaMjayahite mamAnArthamutthitam . yamavaizravaNAdityamahendravaruNopamam .
mahArathaM samAkhyAtaM droNAyodyatamAhave . tyajantaM tumule prANAn ke zUrAH samavArayan .
eko ' pasRtya cedibhyaH pANDavAn ya : samAzritaH . dhRSTaketuM samAyAntaM droNaM kastaM nyavArayat .
yo ' vadhIt ketumAn vIro rAjaputraM durAsadam . aparAntagiridvAre droNAt kastaM nyavArayat .
strIpuMsayornaravyAghro yaH sa veda guNAguNAn . zikhaNDinaM yAjJasenimamlAnamanasaM yudhi . devavratasya samare hetuM mRtyormahAtmanaH . droNAyAbhimukhaM yAntaM ke zUrAH paryavArayan .
yasminnabhyadhikA vIre guNAH sarve dhanaMjayAt . yasminnastrANi satyaM ca brahmacarye ca sarvadA .
vAsudevasamaM vIrye dhanaMjayasamaM bale . tejasA ' ' dityasadRzaM bRhaspatisamaM matau .
abhimanyuM mahAtmAnaM vyAttAnanamivAntakam . droNAyAbhimukhaM yAntaM ke zUrAH samavArayan .
taruNastaruNaprajJaH saubhadraH paravIrahA . yadAbhyadhAvadvai droNaM tadA ' ' sId vo manaH katham .
draupadeyA naravyAghrAH samudramiva sindhavaH . yad droNamAdravan saMkhye ke zUrAstAn nyavArayan .51 ete dvAdaza varSANi krIDAmutsRjya bAlakAH . astrArthamavasan bhISme vibhrato vratamuttamam .
kSatraMjayaH kSatradevaH kSatravarmA ca mAnadaH . dhRSTadyumnAtmajA vIrAH ke tAn droNAdavArayan .
zatAd viziSTaM yaM yuddhe samamanyanta vRSNayaH . cekitAnaM maheSvAsaM kastaM droNAdavArayat .
vArdhakSemiH kaliGgAnAM yaH kanyAmAharad yudhi . anAdhRSTiradInAtmA kastaM droNAdavArayat .
vIrAH
bhrAtaraH paJca kaikeyA dhArmikA : satyavikramAH . indragopakasaMkAzA raktavarmAyudhadhvajAH . mAtRSvasuH sutA pANDavAnAM jayArthinaH . tAn droNaM hantumAyAtAn ke vIrAH paryavArayan .
yaM yodhayanto rAjAno nAjayan vAraNAvate . SaNmAsAnapi saMrabdhA jighAMsanto yudhAmpatim . dhanuSmatAM varaM zUraM satyasaMgha mahAbalam . droNAt kastaM naravyAghraM yuyutsuM paryavArayat .
yaH putraM kAzirAjasya vArANasyAM mahAratham . samare strISu gRdhyantaM bhallenApAharadrathAt . dhRSTadyumnaM maheSvAsaM pArthAnAM mantradhAriNam . yuktaM duryodhanAnatheM sRSTaM droNavadhAya ca . nirdahantaM raNe yodhAn dArayantaM ca sarvataH . droNAbhimukhamAyAntaM ke zUrAH paryavArayan .
utsaGga iva saMvRddhaM drupadasyAstravittamam . zaikhaNDinaM zastraguptaM ke ca droNAdavArayan .
ya imAM pRthivIM kRtsnAM carmavat samaveSTayat . mahatA rathaghoSeNa mukhyArino mahArathaH . dazAzvamedhAnAjahe svannapAnAptadakSiNAn . nirargalAn sarvamedhAn putravat pAlayan prajAH . gaGgasrotasi yAvanyaH sikatA apyazeSataH . tAvatIrgA dadau vIra uzInarasuto ' dhvare .
na pUrve nApare cakuridaM kecana mAnavAH . itIdaM cukuzurdevAH kRte karmaNi duSkare .
pazyAmastriSu lokeSu na taM saMsthAsnucAriSu . jAtaM cApi janiSyantaM dvitIyaM cApi sAmpratam . anyamauzInarAcchaivyAd dhuro voDhAramityuta . gatiM yasya na yAsyanti mAnuSA lokavAsina. .
tasya saptAramAyAntaM zaibyaM kaH samavArayat . droNAyAbhimukhaM yattaM vyAttAnanamivAntakam .
virATasya rathAnIkaM matsyasyAmitraghAtinaH . prepsantaM samare droNaM ke vIrAH paryavArayan .
sadyo vRkodarAjjAto mahAbalaparAkramaH . mAyAvI rAkSaso vIro yasmAnmama mahad bhayam . pArthAnAM jayakAmaM taM putrANAM mama kaNTakam . ghaTotkacaM mahAtmAnaM kastaM droNAdavArayat .
ete cAnye ca bahavo yeSAmarthAya saMjaya . tyaktAraH saMyuge prANAn kiM teSAmajitaM yudhi .
yeSAM ca puruSavyAghraH zAIdhanvA vyapAzrayaH . hitArthI cApi pArthAnAM kathaM teSAM parAjayaH .
lokAnAM gururatyarthaM lokanAthaH sanAtanaH . nArAyaNo raNe nAthodivyo divyAtmakaH prabhuH .
yasya divyAni karmANi pravadanti manISiNaH . tAnyahaM kIrtayiSyAmibhaktyA sthairyArthamAtmanaH .
bhISma uvAca yamastu yAni zrAddhAni provAca zazavindave . tAni me zRNu kAmyAni nakSatreSu pRthak pRthak .
zrAddhaM yaH kRttikAyoge kurvIta satataM naraH . agnInAdhAya sApatyo yajeta vigatajvaraH .
apatyakAmo rohiNyAM tejaskAmo mRgottame . krUrakarmA dadacchrAddhamArdrAyAM mAnavo bhavet .
dhanakAmo bhavenmartyaH kurvaJchrAddhaM punarvasau . puSTikAmo ' tha puSyeNa zrAddhamIheta mAnavaH .
AzleSAyAM dadacchrAddhaM dhIrAn putrAn prajAyate . jJAtInAM tu bhavecchreSTho maghAsu zrAddhamAvapan .
phalgunISu dadacchrAddhaM subhagaH zrAddhado bhavet . apatyabhAguttarAsu hastena phalabhAg bhavet .
citrAyAM tu dadacchrAddhaM labhed rUpavataH sutAn . svAtiyoge pitRRnarcya vANijyamupajIvati .
bahuputro vizAkhAsu putramIhan bhavennaraH . anurAdhAsu kurvANo rAjacakra pravartayet .
AdhipatyaM vrajenmayo jyeSThAyAmapavarjayan . naraH kurukulazreSTha Rddho damapuraHsaraH .
mUle tvArogyamRccheta yazo ' ' SADhAsu cottamam . uttarAsu tvaSADhAsu vItazokakazcarenmahIm .
zrAddhaM tvabhijitA kurvan bhiSaksiddhimavApnuyAt . zravaNeSu dadacchrAddhaM pretya gacchet sa sadgatim .
rAjyabhAgI dhaniSThAyAM bhaveta niyataM naraH . nakSatre vAruNe kurvan bhiSaksiddhimavApnuyAt .
pUrvaproSThapadAH kurvan bahUn vindatyajAvikAn . uttarAsu prakurvANo vindate gAH sahasrazaH .
bahukupyakRtaM vittaM vindate revatIM zritaH . azvinISvazvAn vindeta bharaNISvAyuruttamam .
imaM zrAddhavidhiM zrutvA zazabindustathAkarot . aklezenAjayaccApi mahI so ' nuzazAsa ha .
yAjJavalkya uvAca avyaktasthaM paraM yat tat pRSTaste ' haM narAdhipa . paraM guhyamimaM praznaM zRNuSvAvahito nRpa .
yathA ' ' rSeNeha vidhinA caratAvanatena ha . mayA ' ' dityAdavAptAni yajUMSi mithilAdhipa .
mahatA tapasA devastapiSNuH sevito mayA . prItena cAhaM vibhunA sUryeNoktastadAnagha . varaM vRNISva viprarSe yadiSTaM te sudurlabham . tat te dAsyAmi prItAtmA matprasAdo hi durlabhaH .
tataH praNamya zirasA mayoktastapatAM varaH . yajUMSi nopayuktAni kSipramicchAmi veditum .
tato mAM bhagavAnAha vitariSyAmi te dvija . sarasvatIha vAgbhUtA zarIraM te pravekSyati .
tato mAmAha bhagavAnAsyaM svaM vivRtaM kuru . vivRtaM ca tato me ' ' syaM praviSTA ca sarasvatI .
tato vidahyamAno ' haM praviSTo ' mbhastadAnagha . avijJAnAdamarSAcca bhAskarasya mahAtmanaH .
tato vidahyamAnaM mAmuvAca bhagavAn raviH . muhUrtaM sahyatAM dAhastata : zItIbhaviSyati .
zItIbhUtaM ca mAM dRSTvA bhagavAnAha bhAskaraH . pratiSThAsyati te vedaH sakhilaH sottaro dvija .
kRsanaM zatapathaM caiva praNeSyasi dvijarSabha . tasyAnte cApunarbhAve buddhistava bhaviSyati .
prApsyase ca yadiSTaM tat sAMkhyayogepsitaM padam . etAvaduktvA bhagavAnastamevAbhyavartata .
tato ' nuvyAhRtaM zrutvA gate deve vibhAvasau . gRhamAgatya saMhRSTo ' cintayaM vai sarasvatIm .
tataH pravRttAtizubhA svaravyaJjanabhUSitA . oGkAramAditaH kRtvA mama devI sarasvatI .
tato ' hamayaM vidhivat sarasvatyai nyavedayam . tapatAM ca variSThAya niSaNNastatparAyaNaH .
tataH zatapathaM kRtsnaM sarahasyaM sasaMgraham . cakre saparizeSaM ca harSeNa parameNa ha .
kRtvA cAdhyayana teSAM ziSyANAM zatamuttamam . vipriyArthaM saziSyasya mAtulasya mahAtmanaH .
tataH saziSyeNa mayA sUryeNeva gabhastibhiH . vyasto yajJo mahArAja pitustava mahAtmanaH .
miSato devalasyApi tato ' rdhaM hRtavAnaham . svavedadakSiNAyArthe vimarde mAtulena ha .
sumantunAtha pailena tathA jaimininA ca vai . pitrA te munibhizcaiva tato ' hamanumAnitaH .
daza paJca ca prAptAni yajUMSyarkAnmayAnadha . tathaiva romaharSeNa purANamavadhAritam .
bIjametat puraskRtya devIM caiva sarasvatIm . sUryasya cAnubhAvena pravRtto ' haM narAdhipa . kartuM zatapathaM cedamapUrvaM ca kRtaM mayA . yathAbhilaSitaM mArga tathA taccopapAditam .
ziSyANAmakhilaM kRtsnamanujJAtaM sasaMgraham . sarve ca ziSyAH zucayo gatAH paramaharSitAH .
zAkhAH paJcadazemAstu vidyA bhAskaradezitAH . pratiSThApya yathAkAmaM vedyaM tadanucintayam .
kimatra brahmaNyamRtaM kiM ca vedyamanuttamam . cintayaM statra cAgatya gandharvo mAmapRcchata . vizvAvasustato rAjan vedAntajJAnakovidaH . caturviMzAstato ' pRcchat praznAn vedasya pArthiva . paJcaviMzatimaM praznaM papracchAnvIkSikI tadA . vizvAvizvaM tathAzvAzvaM mitraM varuNameva ca .
jJAnaM jJeyaM tathA jJo ' jJaH kastapA atapAstathA . sUryAtisUrya iti ca vidyAvidye tathaiva ca . vedyAvedyaM tathA rAjannacalaM calameva ca . apUrvamakSayaM kSayyametat praznamanuttamam .
athoktazca mahArAja rAjA gandharvasattamaH . pRSTavAnanupUrveNa praznamarthaviduttamam .
muhUrtamuSyatAM tAvad yAvadevaM vicintaye . bADhamityeva kRtvA ca tUSNIM gandharva AsthitaH .
tato ' nucintayamahaM bhUyo devI sarasvatIm . manasA sa ca me prazno dadhno ghRtamivoddhatam .
tatropaniSadaM caiva parizeSaM ca pArthiva . madhnAmi manasA tAta dRSTvA cAnvIkSikI parAm .
caturthI rAjazArdUla vidyaiSA sAmparAyikI . udIritA mayA tubhyaM paJcaviMzAdadhiSThitA . .
athoktastu mayA rAjan rAjA vizvAvasustadA . zrUyatAM yad bhavAnasmAn prazna sampRSTavAniha .
vizvAvizveti yadidaM gandharvendrAnupRcchasi . vizvAvyaktaM paraM vidyAd bhUtabhavyabhayaMkaram .
triguNaM guNakartRtvAdavizvo niSkalastathA . azvazcAzvA ca mithunamevamevAnudRzyate . avyaktaM prakRti prAhuH puruSeti ca nirguNam . tathaiva mitraM puruSaM varuNaM prakRti tathA .
jJAnaM tu prakRti prAhurteyaM niSkalameva ca . ajJazca jJazca puruSastasmAnniSkala ucyate .
kastapA atapAH proktaH ko ' sau puruSa ucyate . tapAstu prakRti prAhuratapA niSkalaH smRtaH .
tathaivAvedyamavyaktaM vedyaH puruSa ucyate . calAcalamiti proktaM tvayA tadapi me zRNu .
calAM tu prakRti prAhuH kAraNaM kSayasargayoH . AkSepasargayoH kartA nizcalaH puruSaH smRtaH .
tathaiva vedyamavyaktamavedyaH puruSastathA . ajJAvubhau dhruvau caiva akSayau cApyubhAvapi . ajau nityAvubhau prAhuradhyAtmagatinizcayAH .
akSayatvAt prajanane ajamatrAhuravyayam . akSayaM puruSaM prAhuH kSayo hyasya ca vidyate .
guNakSayatvAt prakRtiH kartRtvAdakSayaM budhAH . eSA te ' ' nvIkSikI vidyA caturthI sAmparAyikI .
vidyopetaM dhanaM kRtvA karmaNA nityakarmaNi . ekAntadarzanA vedAH sarve vizvAvaso smRtAH .
jAyante ca priyante ca yasminnete yatazcyutAH . vedArthaM ye na jAnanti vedyaM gandharvasattama . sAGgopAGgAnapi yadi yazca vedAnadhIyate . vedavedyaM na jAnIte vedabhAravaho hi saH .
yo ghRtArthI kharIkSIraM mathed gandharvasattama . viSThAM tatrAnupazyeta na maNDaM na ca vai ghRtam .
tathA vedyamavedyaM ca vedavidyo na vindati . sa kevalaM mUDhamatirjJAnabhAravahaH smRtaH .
draSTavyau nityamevaito tatpareNAntarAtmanA . tathAsya janmanidhane na bhavetAM punaH punaH .
ajasraM janmanidhanaM cintayitvA trayImimAm . parityajya kSayamiha akSayaM dharmamAsthitaH .
yadAnupazyate ' tyantamahanyahani kAzyapa . tadA sa kevalIbhUtaH SaDviMzamanupazyati .
anyazca zAzvato ' vyaktastathAnyaH paJcaviMzakaH . tasya dvAvanupazyetAM tamekamiti sAdhavaH .
te naitannAbhinandanti paJcaviMzakamacyutam . janmamRtyubhayAd yogAH sAMkhyAzca paramaiSiNaH .
vizvAvasuruvAca paJcavizaM yadetat te proktaM brAhmaNasattama . tathA tanna tathA ceti tad bhavAn vaktumarhati .
jaigISavyasyAsitasya devalasya mayA zrutam . parAzarasya viprarvArSagaNyasya dhImataH . bhRgoH paJcazikhasyAsya kapilasya zukasya ca . gautamasyArTiSeNasya gargasya ca mahAtmanaH . nAradasyAsurezcaiva pulastyasya ca dhImataH . sanatkumArasya tataH zukrasya ca mahAtmanaH . kazyapasya pituzcaiva pUrvameva mayA zrutam . tadanantaraM ca rudrasya vizvarUpasya dhImataH . daivatebhyaH pitRbhyazca daiteyebhyastatastataH . prAptametanmayA kRtsnaM vedyaM nityaM vadantyuta .
tasmAt tad vai bhavabuddhyA zrotumicchAmi brAhmaNa . bhavAn prabarhaH zAstrANAM pragalbhazcAtibuddhimAn .
na tavAviditaM kiMcid bhavAJcatinidhiH smRtaH . kathyate devaloke ca pitRloke ca brAhmaNa .
brahmalokagatAzcaiva kathayanti maharSayaH . patizca tapatAM zazvadAdityastava bhASitA .
sAMkhyajJAnaM tvayA brahmannavAptaM kRtsnameva ca . tathaiva yogazAstraM ca yAjJavalkya vizeSataH .
niHsaMdigdhaM prabuddhastvaM budhyamAnazcarAcaram . zrotumicchAmi tajjJAnaM ghRtaM maNDamayaM yathA .
yAjJavalkya uvAca kRtsnadhAriNameva tvAM manye gandharvasattama . jijJAsase ca mAM rAjaMstannibodha yathAzrutam .
abudhyamAnAM prakRti budhyate paJcaviMzakaH . na tu budhyati gandharva prakRtiH paJcaviMzakam .
anena pratibodhena pradhAnaM pravadanti tat sAMkhyayogAzca tattvajJA yathAzrutinidarzanAt .
pazyaMstathaiva cApazyan pazyatyanya : sadAnagha . SaDviMzaM paJcaviMzaM ca caturviMzaM ca pazyati .
na tu pazyati pazyaMstu yazcainamanupazyati . paJcaviMzo ' bhimanyeta nAnyo ' sti parato mama .
na caturviMzako grAhyo manujairjJAnadarzibhiH . matsyazcodakamanveti pravarteta pravartanAt .
yathaiva budhyate matsyastathaiSo ' pyanubudhyate . sa snehAt sahavAsAcca sAbhimAnAcca nityazaH . sa nimajjati kAlasya yadaikatvaM na budhyate . unmajjati hi kAlasya samatvenAbhisaMvRtaH .
yadA tu manyate ' nyo ' hamanya eSa iti dvijaH . tadA sa kevalIbhUtaH SaDviMzamanupazyati .
anyazca rAjannavarastathAnyaH paJcaviMzakaH . tatsthAnAccAnupazyanti eka eveti sAdhavaH .
te naitannAbhinandanti paJcaviMzakamacyutam . janmamRtyubhayAd bhItA yogAH sAMkhyAzca kAzyapa . . SaDviMzamanupazyantaH zucayastatparAyaNAH . yadA sa kevalIbhUtaH SaDviMzamanupazyati . tadA sa sarvavid vidvAn na punarjanma vindati . evamapratibuddhazca budhyamAnazca te ' nagha . buddhazcokto yathAtattvaM mayA zrutinidarzanAt . pazyApazyaM yo na pazyet kSemyaM tattvaM ca kAzyapa . kevalAkevalaM cAdyaM paJcavizaM paraM ca yat .
vizvAvasuruvAca tathyaM zubhaM caitaduktaM tvayA vibho samyak kSemyaM daivatAdyaM yathAvat . svastyakSayaM bhavatazcAstu nityaM buddhyA sadA buddhiyuktaM manaste .
yAjJavalkya uvAca evamuktvA samprayAto divaM sa vibhrAjan vai zrImatA darzanena . dRSTazca tuSTyA parayAbhinandya pradakSiNaM mama kRtvA mahAtmA .
ye brahmAdInAM khecarANAM kSitau ca cAdhastAt saMvasante narendra . tatraiva tadarzanaM darzayan vai samyak kSemyaM ye pathaM saMzritA vai .
sAMkhyAH sarve sAMkhyadharme ratAzca tadvad yogA yogadharme ratAzca . steSAmetadarzanaM jJAnadRSTam .
jJAnAnmokSo jAyate rAjasiMha nAstyajJAnAdevamAhurnarendra . tasmAjjJAnaM tattvato ' nveSitavyaM yenAtmAnaM mokSayejjanmamRtyoH .
prApya jJAnaM brAhmaNAt kSatriyAd vA vaizyAcchUdrAdapi nIcAdanIkSNam . zraddhAtavyaM zraddadhAnena nityaM na zraddhinaM janmamRtyU vizetAm .
sarve varNA brAhmaNA brahmajAzca sarve nityaM vyAharante ca brahmA tattvaM zAstraM brahmabuddhyA bravImi sarvaM vizvaM brahma caitat samastam .
brahmAsyato brAhmaNAH samprasUtA bAhubhyAM vai kSatriyAH samprasUtAH . nAbhyAM vaiSyAH pAdatazcApi zUdrAH . sarve varNA nAnyathA veditavyAH .
ajJAnataH karmayoni bhajante tAM tAM rAjaMste tathA yAntyabhAvam . tathA varNA jJAnahInAH patante ghorAdajJAnAtprAkRtaM yonijAlam .
tasmAjjJAnaM sarvato mArgitavyaM sarvatrasthaM caitaduktaM mayA te . tatstho stasmai nityaM mokSamAhurnarendra .
yat te pRSTaM tanmayA copadiSTa yAthAtathyaM tadvizoko bhavasva . rAjan gacchasvaitadarthasya pAraM samyak proktaM svasti te tvastu nityam .
bhISma uvAca sa evamanuzAstastu yAjJavalkyena dhImatA . prItimAnabhavad rAjA mithilAdhipatistadA .
gate munivare tasmin kRte cApi pradakSiNam . daivarAtirnarapatirAsInastatra mokSavit . gokoTiM sparzayAmAsa hiraNyaM tu tathaiva ca . ratnAJjalimathaikaM ca brAhmaNebhyo dadau tadA .
videharAjyaM ca tadA pratiSThApya sutasya vai . yatidharmamupAsaMzcApyavasanmithilAdhipaH .
sAMkhyajJAnamadhIyAno yogazAstraM ca kRtsnazaH . dharmAdharmaM ca rAjendra prAkRtaM parigarhayan .
ananta iti kRtvA sa nityaM kevalameva ca . dharmAdharmoM puNyapApe satyAsatye tathaiva ca . janmamRtyU ca rAjendra prAkRtaM tadacintayat . vyaktAvyaktasya karmedamiti nityaM narAdhipa .
