puSkaraM tvanyadevAtra tathAnyadudakaM smRtam . na codakasya sparzena lipyate tatra puSkaram .
eteSAM sahavAsaM ca nivAsaM caiva nityazaH . yAthAtathyena pazyanti na nityaM prAkRtA janAH .
ye tvanyathaiva pazyanti na samyak teSu darzanam . te vyaktaM nirayaM ghoraM pravizanti punaH punaH .
sAMkhyadarzanametat te parisaMkhyAnamuttamam . evaM hi parisaMkhyAya sAMkhyAH kevalatAM gatAH .
ye tvanye tattvakuzalAsteSAmetannidarzanam . ataH paraM pravakSyAmi yogAnAmanudarzanam .
bRhadazva uvAca utsRjya damayantI tu nalo rAjA vizAmpate . dadarza dAvaM dahyantaM mahAntaM gahane vane . .
tatra zuzrAva zabdaM vai madhye bhUtasya kasyacit . abhidhAva naletyuccaiH puNyazlAketi cAsakRt . mA bhairiti nalazcoktvA madhyamagneH pravizya tam . dadarza nAgarAjAnaM zayAnaM kuNDalIkRtam .
sa nAgaH prAJjalirbhUtvA vepamAno nalaM tadA . uvAca mAM viddhi rAjan nAgaM karkoTakaM nRpa . . mayA pralabdho brahmarSirnAradaH sumahAtapAH . tena manyuparItena zapto ' smi manujAdhipa . . tiSTha tvaM sthAvara iva yAvadeva nala : kvacit . ito netA hi tatra tvaM zApAnmokSyasi matkRtAt .
tasya zApAna zakto ' smi padAd vicalituM padam upadekSyAmi te zreyastrAtumarhati mAM bhavAn .
sakhA ca te bhaviSyAmi matsamo nAsti pannagaH . laghuzca te bhaviSyAmi zIghramAdAya gaccha mAm .
evamuktvA sa nAgendro babhUvAGguSThamAtrakaH . taM gRhItvA nalaH prAyAd dezaM dAvavivarjitam .
AkAzadezamAsAdya vimuktaM kRSNavarmanA . utsraSTukAmaM taM nAgaH puna : karkoTako ' bravIt .
padAni gaNayan gaccha svAni naiSadha kAnicit . tatra te ' haM mahAbAho zreyodhAsyAmi yat param .
tata : saMkhyAtumArabdhamadazad dazame pade . tasya daSTasya tad rUpaM kSipramantaradhIyata .
sa dRSTvA vismitastasthAvAtmAnaM vikRtaM nalaH . svarUpadhAriNaM nAgaM dadarza sa mahIpatiH .
tataH karkoTako nAgaH sAntvayan nalamabravIt . mayA te ' ntarhitaM rUpaM na tvAM vidyurjanA iti .
yatkRte cAsi nikRto duHkhena mahatA nala . viSeNa sa madIyena tvayi duHkhaM nivatsyati .
viSeNa saMvRtairgAtrairyAvat tvAM na vimokSyati . tAvat tvayi mahArAja duHkhaM vai sa nivatsyati .
anAgA yena nikRtastvamana ) janAdhipa . krodhAdasUyayitvA taM rakSA me bhavataH kRtA .
na te bhayaM naravyAghra daMSTribhyaH zatruto ' pi vA . brahmavidbhyazca bhavitA matprasAdAnnarAdhipa .
rAjan viSanimittA ca na te pIDA bhaviSyati . saMgrameSu ca rAjendra zazvajjayamavApsyasi .
gaccha rAjanita : sUto bAhuko ' hamiti bruvan . samIpamRtuparNasya sa hi caivAkSanaipuNaH . ayodhyA nagarI ramyAmadya vai niSadhezvara . sa te ' kSahRdayaM dAtA rAjAzcahRdayena vai .
ikSvAkukulajaH zrImAn mitraM caiva bhaviSyati . bhaviSyasi yadAkSajJaH zreyasA yokSyase tadA . .
samameSyasi dAraistvaM mA sma zoke manaH kRthAH . rAjyena tanayAbhyAM ca satyametad bravImi te .
svaM rUpaM ca yadA draSTumicchethAstvaM narAdhipa . saMsmartavyastadA te ' haM vAsazcedaM nivAsayeH .
anena vAsasAcchannaH svaM rUpaM pratipatsyase . ityuktvA pradadau tasmai divyaM vAsoyugaM tadA .
evaM nalaM ca saMdizya vAso dattvA ca kaurava . nAgarAjastato rAjaMstatraivAntaradhIyata . .
vaizampAyana uvAca tataH subalaputrastu rAjA duryodhanazca ha . duHzAsanazca karNazca duSTaM mantramamantrayan . te kauravyamanujJApya dhRtarASTra narAdhipam . dahane tu saputrAyaH kuntyA buddhimakArayan .
teSAmiGgittabhAvajJo vidurastattvadarzivAn . AkAreNa ca taM mantraM bubudhe duSTacetasAm .
tato viditavedyAtmA pANDavAnAM hite rataH . palAyane matiM cane kuntyAH putraiH sahAnaghaH .
tato vAtasahAM nAvaM yantrayuktAM pAtakinIm . UrmikSamA dRDhAM kRtvA kuntImidamuvAca ha .
eSa jAtaH kulasyAsya kIrtivaMzapraNAzanaH . dhRtarASTraH parItAtmA dharmaM tyajati zAzvatam . iyaM vAripathe yuktA taraGgapavanakSamA . nauryayA mRtyupAzAt saputrA mokSyase zubhe .
tacchrutvA vyathitA kuntI putraiH saha yazasvinI . nAvamAruhya gaGgAyAM prayayau bharatarSabha .
tato viduravAkyena nAvaM vikSipya pANDavAH . dhanaM cAdAya tairdattamariSTaM prAvizan vanam .
niSAdI paJcaputrA tu jAtuSe tatra vezmani . kAraNAbhyAgatA dagdhA saha putrairanAgasA .
sa ca mlecchAdhamaH pApo dagdhastatra purocanaH . vaJcitAzca durAtmAno dhArtarASTrA : sahAnugAH .
avijJAtA mahAtmAno janAnAmakSatAstathA . jananyA saha kaunteyA muktA viduramantritAH .
tatastasmin pure lokA nagare vAraNAvate . dRSTvA jatugRhaM dagdhamanvazocanta duHkhitAH .
rAjJe ca preSayAmAsuryathAvRttaM niveditum . saMvRttaste mahAn kAmaH pANDavAn dagdhavAnasi . sakAmo bhava kauravya bhuDkSva rAjyaM saputrakaH . tacchrutvA dhRtarASTrastu saha putreNa zocayan .
pretakAryANi ca tathA cakAra saha bAndhavaiH . pANDavAnAM tathA kSattA bhISmazca kurusattamaH : .
janamejaya uvAca punarvistarazaH zrotumicchAmi dvijasattama . dAhaM jatugRhasyaiva pANDavAnAM ca mokSaNam .
sunRzaMsamidaM karma teSAM krUropasaMhitam . kIrtayasva yathAvRttaM paraM kautUhalaM mama .
vaizampAyana uvAca zRNu vistarazo rAjan vadato me paraMtapa . dAhaM jatugRhasyaitat pANDavAnAM ca mokSaNam .
prANAdhikaM bhImasenaM kRtavidyaM dhanaMjayam . duryodhano lakSayitvA paryatapyata durmanAH .
tato vaikartanaH karNaH zakunizcApi saubalaH . anekairabhyupAyaiste jighAMsanti sma pANDavAn .
pANDavA api tat sarvaM praticakruryathAgatam . udbhAvanamakurvanto vidurasya mate sthitAH .
guNaiH samuditAn dRSTvA paurAH pANDusutAMstadA . kathayAMcakrire teSAM guNAn saMsatsu bhArata .
rAjyaprAptiM ca samprApta jyeSThaM pANDusutaM tadA . kathayanti sma sambhUya catvareSu sabhAsu ca .
prajJAcakSuracakSuSTvAd dhRtarASTro janezvaraH . rAjyaM na prAptavAn pUrvaM sa kathaM nRpatirbhavet .
tathA zAMtanavo bhISmaH satyasaMdho mahAvrataH . pratyAkhyAya purA rAjyaM na sa jAtu grahISyati .
te vayaM pANDavajyeSThaM taruNa vRddhazIlinam . abhiSiJcAm sAdhvadya satyakAruNyavedinam .
sa hi bhISmaM zAMtanavaM dhRtarASTraM ca dharmavit . saputraM vividhairbhogairyojayiSyati pUjayan .
teSAM duryodhanaH zrutvA tAni vAkyAni jalpatAm . yudhiSThirAnuraktAnAM paryatapyata durmatiH .
sa tapyamAno duSTAtmA teSAM vAco na cakSame . Iy/ayA cApi saMtapto dhRtarASTamupAgamat .
tato virahitaM dRSTvA pitaraM pratipUjya saH . paurAnurAgasaMtaptaH pazcAdidamabhASata .
duryodhana uvAca zrutA me jalpatAM tAta paurANAmazivA giraH . tvAmanAdRtya bhISmaM ca patimicchanti pANDavam .
matametacca bhISmasya na sa rAjyaM bubhukSati . asmAkaM tu parAM pIDAM cikIrSanti pure janAH .
pitRtaH prAptavAn rAjyaM pANDurAtmaguNaiH purA . tvamandhaguNasaMyogAt prAptaM rAjyaM na labdhavAn .
sa eSa pANDordAyAdyaM yadi prApnoti pANDavaH . tasya putro dhruvaM prAptastasya tasyApi cAparaH .
te vayaM rAjavaMzena hInAH saha sutairapi . avajJAtA bhaviSyAmo lokasya jagatIpate .
satataM nirayaM prAptAH parapiNDopajIvinaH . na bhavema yatA rAjaMstathA nItividhIyatAm .
yadi tvaM hi purA rAjannidaM rAjyamavAptavAn . dhruvaM prApsyAma ca vayaM rAjyamapyavaze jane .
dhRtarASTra uvAca sAGgA vedA yathAnyAyaM yenAdhItA mahAtmanA . yasmin sAkSAd dhanurvedo hrIniSeve pratiSThitaH .
yasya prasAdAt kurvanti karmANi puruSarSabhAH . amAnuSANi saMgrAme devairasukarANi ca .
taspinnAkruzyati droNe samakSaM pApakarmaNA . nIcAtmanA nRzaMsena kSudreNa gurughAtinA .
nAmarSaM tatra kurvanti dhik kSAtraM dhigamarSitAm . pArthAH sarve ca rAjAnaH pRthivyAM ye dhanurdharAH .
zrutvA kimAhuH pAJcAlyaM tanmamAcakSva saMjaya .
saMjaya uvAca zrutvA drupadaputrasya tA vAcaH krUrakarmaNaH . tUSNIM babhUvU rAjAnaH sarva eva vizAmpate .
arjunastu kaTAkSeNa jihyaM viprekSya pArSatam . sabASyaMmatiniHzvasya dhigdhigityeva cAbravIt .
yudhiSThirazca bhImazca yamau kRSNastathApare . Asan suvrIDitA rAjan sAtyakistvabravIdidam .
nehAsti puruSaH kazcid ya imaM pApapUruSam . bhASamANamakalyANaM zIghraM hanyAnnarAdhamam .
ete tvAM pANDavAH sarve kutsayanti vikutsayA . karmaNA tena pApena zvapAkaM brAhmaNa iva .
etat kRtvA mahat pApaM ninditaH sarvasAdhubhiH . na lajjase kathaM vaktuM samiti prApya zobhanAm .
kathaM ca zatadhA jihvA na te mUrdhA ca vIryate . gurumAkrozataH kSudra na cAdharmeNa pAtyase .
vAccastvamasi pArthazca sarvezcAndhakavRSNibhiH . yat karma kaluSaM kRtvA zlAghase janasaMsadi .
akAryaM tAdRzaM kRtvA punareva guruM kSipan . vadhyastvaM na tvayArtho ' sti muhUrtamapi jIvatA .
kastvetad vyavasedAryastvadanyaH puruSAdhama . nigRhya kezeSu vadhaM gurordharmAtmanaH sataH .
saptAvare tathA pUrve bAndhavAste nimajjitAH . yazasA ca parityaktAstvAM prApya kulapAMsanam .
uktavAMzcApi yat pArthe bhISmaM prati nararSabham . tathAnto vihitastena svayameva mahAtmanA .
tasyApi tava sodaryo nihantA pApakRttamaH . nAnyaH pAJcAlyaputrebhyo vidyate bhuvi pApakRt .
sa cApi sRSTaH pitrA te bhISmasyAntakaraH kila . zikhaNDI rakSitastena sa ca mRtyurmahAtmanaH .
paJcAlAzcalitA dharmAt kSudrA mitraguruduhaH . tvAM prApya sahasodaryaM dhikkRtaM sarvasAdhubhiH .
punazcedIdRzIM vAcaM matsamIpe vadiSyasi . ziraste pothayiSyAmi gadayA vajrakalpayA .
tvAM ca brahmahaNaM dRSTvA janaH sUryamavekSate . brahmahatyA hi te pApaM prAyazcittArthamAtmanaH .
pAJcAlaka sudurvRtta mameva gurumagrataH . gurorguruM ca bhUyo ' pi kSipannaiva hi lajase .
tiSTha tiSTha sahasvaikaM gadApAtamimaM mama . tava cApi sahiSye ' haM gadApAtAnanekazaH .
sAtvatenaivamAkSiptaH pArSataH paruSAkSaram . saMrabdhaM sAtyakiM prAha saMkruddhaH prahasanniva .
dhRSTadyumna uvAca zrUyate zrUyate ceti kSamyate ceti mAdhava . sadAnAryo ' zubhaH sAdhu puruSaM kSeptumicchati .
kSamA prazasyate loke na tu pApo ' rhati kSamAm . kSamAvantaM hi pApAtmA jito ' yamiti manyate .
sa tvaM kSudrasamAcAro nIcAtmA pApanizcayaH . AkezAgrAnnakhAgrAcca vaktavyo vaktumicchasi .
yaH sa bhUrizravAAzchinnabhujaH prAyagatastvayA . vAryamANena hi hatastataH pApataraM nu kim .
gAhamAno mayA droNo divyenAstreNa saMyuge . visRSTazasro nihataH kiM tatra krUra duSkRtam .
ayudhyamAnaM yastvAjau tathA prAyagataM munim . chinnabAhuM parairhanyAt sAtyake sa kathaM vedat .
nihatya tvAM padA bhUmau ca vikarSati vIryavAn . . kiM tadA na nihaMsyenaM bhUtvA puruSasattamaH .
tvayA punaranAryeNa pUrvaM pArthena nirjitaH . yadA tadA hataH zUraH saumadattiH pratApavAn .
yatra yatra tu pANDUnAM droNo drAvayate camUm . kiracharasahasrANi tatra tatra prayAmyaham .
sa tvamevaMvidhaM kRtvA karma cANDAlavat svayam . vaktumarhasi vaktavyaH kasmAt tvaM paruSANyatha .
kartA tvaM karmaNo hyasya nAhaM vRSNikulAdhama . pApAnAM ca tvamAvAsaH karmaNAM mA punarvadA
joSamAskha na mAM bhUyo vaktumarhasyataH param . adharottarametaddhi yanmAM tvaM vaktumarhasi .
atha vakSyasi mAM mauAd bhUyaH paruSamIdRzam . gamayiSyAmi bANaistvAM yudhi vaivasvatakSayam .
na caivaM mUrkha dharmeNa kevalenaiva zakyate . teSAmapi hyadharmeNa ceSTitaM zRNu yAdRzam .
vaJcitaH pANDavaH pUrvamadharmeNa yudhiSThiraH . draupadI ca parikliSTA tathA dharmeNa sAtyake .
pravrAjitA vanaM sarve pANDavAH saha kRSNayA . sarvasvamapakRSTaM ca tathAdharmeNa bAliza .
adharmeNApakRSTazca madrarAjaH pareritaH . adharmeNa tathA bAla : saubhadro vinipAtitaH .
ito ' pyadharmeNa hato bhISmaH parapuraMjayaH . bhUrizravA hyadharmeNa tvayA dharmavidA hataH .
evaM parairAcaritaM pANDaveyaizca saMyuge . rakSamANairjayaM vIrairdharmajJairapi sAtvata .
durjeyaH sa paro dharmastathAdharmazca durvidaH . yudhyasva kauravaiH sArdhaM mA gA pitRnivezanam .
saMjaya uvAca evamAdIni vAkyAni krUrANi paruSANi ca . zrAvitaH sAtyakiH zrImAnAkampita ivAbhavat .
tacchrutvA krodhatAmrAkSaH sAtyakistvAdade gadAm . viniHzvasya yathA sarpaH praNidhAya rathe dhanuH .
tato ' bhipatya pAJcAlyaM saMrambheNedamabravIt . na tvAM vakSyAmi paruSaM haniSye tvAM vadhakSamam .
tamApatantaM sahasA mahAbalamamarSaNam . pAJcAlyAyAbhisaMkruddhamantakAyAntakopamam .
codito vAsudevena bhImaseno mahAbalaH . avaplutya rathAt tUrNaM bAhubhyAM samavArayat .
dravamANaM tathA kruddhaM sAtyakiM pANDavo balI . praspandamAnamAdAya jagAma balinaM balAt .
sthitvA viSTabhya caraNau bhImena zinipuGgavaH . nigRhItaH pade SaSThe balena balinAM varaH .
avaruhya rathAt tUrNaM dhriyamANaM balIyasA . uvAca zlakSNayA vAcA sahadevo vizAmpate .
asmAkaM puruSavyAghra mitramanyanna vidyate . paramandhakavRSNibhyaH paJcAlebhyazca mAriSa .
tathaivAndhakavRSNInAM tathaiva ca vizeSataH . kRSNasya ca tathAsmatto mitramanyanna vidyate .
paJcAlAnAM ca vArSNeya samudrAntAM vicinvatAm . nAnyadasti paraM mitraM yathA pANDavavRSNayaH .
sa bhavAnIdRzaM mitraM manyate ca yathA bhavAn . bhavantazca yathAsmAkaM bhavatAM ca tathA vayam .
sa evaM sarvadharmajJa mitradharmamanusmaran . niyaccha manyu pAJcAlyAt prazAmya zinipuGgavA
pArSatasya kSamaM tvaM vai kSamatAM pArvatazca te . vayaM kSamayitAzca kimanyatra zamAd bhavet .
prazAmyamAne zaineya sahadevena mAriSa . pAJcAlarAjasya sutaH prahasannidamabravIt .
AsAdayatu mAmeSa dharAdharamivAnilaH .
yAvadasya zitairbANaiH saMrambhaM vinayAmyaham . yuddhazraddhAM ca kaunteya jIvitaM cAsya saMyuge .
kiM nu zakyaM mayA kartuM kAryaM yadidamudyatam . sumahat pANDuputrANAmAyAntyete hi kauravAH .
athavA phAlgunaH sarvAn vArayiSyati saMyuge . ahamapyasya mUrdhAnaM pAtayiSyAmi sAyakaiH .
manyate chinnabAhuM mAM bhUrizravasamAhave . utsRjainamahaM cainameSa vA mAM haniSyati .
zRNvan pAJcAlavAkyAni sAtyakiH sarpavacchasan .65 bhImabAhvantare sakto visphuratyanizaM balI .
tau vRSAviva nardantau balinau bAhuzalinau . tvarayA vAsudevazca dharmarAjazca mAriSa .
yatnena mahatA vIrau vArayAmAsatustataH . nivArya parameSvAsau kopasaMraktalocanau . yuyutsUnaparAn saMkhye pratIyuH kSatriyarSabhAH .
vaizampAyana uvAca zrutvA pANDusutAn vIrAn balodriktAn mahaujasaH . dhRtarASTro mahIpAlazcintAmagamadAturaH .
tata AhUya mantrajJaM rAjazAstrArthavittamam . kaNikaM mantriNAM zreSThaM dhRtarASTro ' bravId vacaH .
dhRtarASTra uvAca utsittAH pANDavA nityaM tebhyo ' sUye dvijottama . tatra me nizcitatamaM saMdhivigrahakAraNam . kaNika tvaM mamAcakSva kariSye vacanaM tava .
vaizampAyana uvAca sa prasannamanAstena paripRSTo dvijottamaH . uvAca vacanaM tIkSNaM rAjazAstrArthadarzanam .
zRNu rAjannidaM tatra procyamAnaM mayAnagha . na me ' bhyasUyA kartavyA zrutvaiva kurusattama . .
nityamudyatadaNDaH syAnnityaM vivRtapauruSaH . acchidrazchidradarzI syAt pareSAM vivarAnugaH .
nityamudyatadaNDAddhi bhRzamudvijate janaH . tasmAt sarvANi kAryANi daNDenaiva vidhArayet .
nAsyacchidraM paraH pazyecchidreNa paramanviyAt . gRhet kUrma ivAGgAni rakSed vivaramAtmanaH . nAsamyakkRtakArI syAdupakramya kadAcana . kaNTako hyapi duzchinna AsAvaM janayecciram .
vadhameva prazaMsanti zatrUNAmapakAriNAm . suvidIrNaM suvikrAntaM suyuddhaM supalAyitam . ApadyApadi kAle ca kurvIta na vicArayet . nAvajJeyo ripustAta durbalau ' pi kathaMcana . .
alpo ' pyagnirvanaM kRtsnaM dahatyAzrayasaMzrayAt . andhaH syAdandhavelAyAM vAdhiryamapi cAzrayet .
kuryAt tRNamayaM cApaM zayIta mRgazAyikAm . sAntvAdibhirupAyaistu hanyAcchatru vaze sthitam .
dayA na tasmin kartavyA zaraNAgata ityut . nirudvigno hi bhavati nahatAjjAyate bhayam .
hanyAdamitraM dAnena tathA pUrvApakAriNam . hanyAt trIn paJca sapteti parapakSasya sarvazaH .
mUlamevAditIzchindyAt parapakSasya nityazaH . tataH sahAyAMstatpakSAn sarvAMzca tadanantaram .
chinnamUle hyadhiSThAne sarve tajjIvino hatAH . kathaM nu zAkhAstiSTheraMzchinnamUle vanaspatau .
ekAgraH syAdavivRto nityaM vivaradarzakaH . rAjan nityaM sapatneSu nityodvignaH samAcaret .
agnyAdhAnena yajJena kASAyeNa jaTAjinaiH . lokAn vizvAsayitvaiva tato lumped yathA vRkaH .
asuzaM zaucamityAhurarthAnAmupadhAraNe . AnAmya phalitAM zAkhAM pakvaM pakvaM prazAtayet .
phalArtho ' yaM samArambho loke puMsAM vipazcitAm . vahedamitraM skandhena yAvat kAlasya paryayaH .
tataH pratyAgate kAle bhindyAd ghaTamivAzmani . amitro na vimoktavyaH kRpaNaM bapi bruvan . kRpA na tasmin kartavyA hanyAdevApakAriNam . hanyAdamitraM sAntvena tathA dAnena vA punaH . tathaiva bhedadaNDAbhyAM sarvopAyaiH prazAtayet .
dhRtarASTra uvAca kathaM sAntvena dAnena bhedairdaNDena vA punaH . amitraH zakyate hantuM tanme brUhi yathAtatham .
kaNika uvAca zRNu rAjan yathAvRttaM vane nivasataH purA . jambukasya mahArAja nItizAstrArthadarzinaH .
atha kazcit kRtaprajJaH zRgAla : svArthapaNDitaH . sakhibhiy/avasat sArdhaM vyAghrAkhuvRkababhrubhiH . te ' pazyan vipine tasmin balinaM mRgayUthapam . azaktA grahaNe tasya tato mantramamantrayan .
jambuka uvAca asakRd yatito hyeSa hantuM vyAghra vane tvayA . . yuvA vai javasampanno buddhizAlI na zakyate . mUSiko ' sya zayAnasya caraNau bhakSayatvayam . yathainaM bhakSitaiH pAdairvyAghro gRhaNAtu vai tataH . tato vai bhakSayiSyAmaH sarve muditamAnasAH .
jambukasya tu tad vAkyaM tathA cakruH samAhitAH . mUSikAbhakSitaiH pAdairmRgaM vyAghro ' vadhIt tadA .
dRSTvAceSTamAnaM tu bhUmau mRgakalavaram . snAtvA ' ' gacchata bhadraM vorakSAmItyAha jambukaH .
zRgAlavacanAt te ' pi gatAH sarve nadI tataH . sa cintAparamo bhUtvA tasthau tatraiva jambukaH .
athAjagAma pUrvaM tu snAtvA vyAghro mahAbalaH . dadarza jambukaM caiva cintAkulitamAnasam .
vyAghra uvAca kiM zocasi mahAprAjJa tvaM no buddhimatAM varaH . azitvA pizitAnyadya vihariSyAmahe vayam .
jamvuka uvAca zRNu me tvaM mahAbAho yad vAkyaM mUSiko ' bravIt . dhig balaM pRgarAjasya mayAdyAyaM mRgo hataH .
mAhubalamAzritya tRptimadya gamiSyati . garjamAnasya tasyaivamato bhakSyaM na rocaye .
vyAghra uvAca bravIti yadi sa hyevaM kAle hyasmin prabodhitaH . svabAhubalamAzritya haniSye ' haM vanecarAn . khAdiSye tatra mAMsAni ityuktvA prasthito vanam . etasminneva kAle tu mUSiko ' pyAjagAma ha . tamAgatamabhipretya zRgAlo ' pyabravavId vacaH .
jambuka uvAca zRNu mUSika bhadraM te nakulo yadihAbravIt .
mRgamAMsaM na khAdeyaM garametanna rocate . mUSikaM bhakSayiSyAmi tad bhavAnanumanyatAm .
tacchutvA mUSiko vAkyaM saMtrastaH pragato bilam . tataH snAtvA sa vai tatra AjagAma vRko nRpa .
tamAgatamidaM vAkyamabravIjjambukastadA . mRgarAjo hi saMkruddho na te sAdhu bhaviSyati . sakalatrastvihAyAti kuruSva yadanantaram . evaM saMceditastena jambukena tadA vRkaH . tato ' valumpanaM kRtvA prayAta : pizitAzanaH . etasminneva kAle tu nakulo ' pyAjagAma ha .
tamuvAca mahArAja nakulaM jambuko vane . svabAhubalamAzritya nirjitAste ' nyato gatAH . mama dattvA niyuddhaM tvaM bhuDkSva mAMsaM yathepsitam .
nakula uvAca mRgarAjo vRkzcaiva buddhimAnapi mUSikaH . nirjitA yat tvayA vIrAstamAd vIrataro bhavAn . na tvayApyutsahe yoddhamityuktvA so ' pyupAgamat .
kaNika uvAca evaM teSu prayAteSu jambuko hRSTamAnasaH . khAdati sma tadA mAMsamekaH san mantranizcayAt .
evaM samAcarannityaM sukhamedhate bhUpatiH . bhayena bhedayed bhIruM zUramaJjalikarmaNA . lubdhamarthapradAnena samaM nyUnaM tathaujasA . evaM te kathitaM rAjazRNu cApyaparaM tathA .
putraH sakhA vA bhrAtA vA pitA vA yadi vA guruH . ripusthAneSu vartanto hantavyA bhUtimicchatA .
zapathenApyariM hanyAdarthadAnena vA punaH . viSeNa mAyayA vApi nopekSate kathaMcana . ubhau cet saMzayopetau zraddhAvAMstatra varddhate .
gurorapyavilaptasya kAryAkAryamajAnataH . utpathapratipannasya nyAyyaM bhavati zAsanam .
kruddho ' pyakruddharUpaH syAt smitapUrvAbhibhASitA . na cApyanyamapadhvaMset kadAcit kopasaMyutaH . prahariSyan priyaM brUyAt praharannapi bhArata . prahatya ca kRpAyIta zoceta ca rudeta ca .
AzvAsayeccApi paraM sAntvadharmArthavRttibhiH . athAsya praharet kAle yadA vicalite pathi .
api ghorAparAdhasya dharmamAzritya tiSThataH . sa hi pracchAdyate doSaH zailo meghairivAsitaiH .
yaH syAdanuprAptavadhastasyAgAraM pradIpayet . adhanAn nAstikAMzcaurAna viSaye sve na vAsayet .
pratyutthAnAsanAdyena sampradAnena kenacit . prativizrabdhaghAtI syAt tIkSNadaMSTro nimagnakaH .
azasteibhyaH zaGketa zakhteibhyazca sarvazaH . azakyAd bhayamutpannamapi mUlaM nikRntati .
na vizvasedavizvaste vizvaste nAtivizvaset . vizvAsAd bhayamutpannaM mUlAnyapi nikRntatiH .
cAraH suvihita : kArya Atmanazca parasya vA . pASaNDAMstApasAdIMzca pararASTreSu yojayet .
udyAneSu vihAreSu devatAyataneSu ca . pAnAgAreSu rathyAsusarvatIrtheSu cApyatha . catvareSu ca kUpeSu parvateSu vaneSu ca . samavAyeSu sarveSu saritsu ca vicArayet .
vAcA bhRzaM vinItaH syAddhadayena tathA kSuraH . smitapUrvAbhibhASI syAt sRSTo raudrAya karmaNe .
aJjaliH zapathaH sAntvaM zirasA pAdavandanam . AzAkaraNamityevaM kartavyaM bhUtimicchatA .
supuSpitaH syAdaphalaH phalavAn syAd durAruhaH . AmaH syAt pakvasaMkAzo na ca jIryeta karhicit . .
trivarge trividhA pIDA hyanubandhastathaiva ca . anubandhAH zubhA jJeyAH pIDAstu parivarjayet .
dharmaM vicarataH pIDA sApi dvAbhyAM niyacchati . arthaM cApyarthalubdhasya kAmaM cAtipravartinaH .
agarvitAtmA yuktazca sAntvayukto ' nasUyitA . avekSitArthaH zuddhAtmA mantrayIta dvijaiH saha .
karmaNA yena kenaiva mRdunA dAruNena ca . uddhared dInamAtmAnaM samartho dharmamAcaret .
na saMzayamanAruhya naro bhadrANi pazyati . saMzayaM punarAruhya yadi jIvati pazyati .
yasya buddhiH paribhavet tamatItena sAntvayet . anAgatena durbuddhiM pratyutpannena paNDitam .
yo ' riNA saha saMdhAya zayIta kRtakRtyavat . sa vRkSAge yathA suptaH patitaH pratibudhyate .
mantrasaMvaraNe yatnaH sadA kAryo ' nasUyatA . AkAramabhirakSeta cAreNApyanupAlitaH . nAcchittvA paramarmANi nAkRtvA karma dAruNam . nAhatvA matsyaghAtIva prANoti mahatIM zriyam .
karzitaM vyAdhitaM klinnamapAnIyamaghAsakam . parivizvastamandaM ca prahartavyamarebalam .
nArthiko ' rthinamabhyeti kRtArthe nAsti saMgatam . tasmAt sarvANi sAdhyAni sAvazeSANi kArayet .
saMgrahe vigrahe caiva yatnaH kAryo ' nasUyatA . utsAhazcApi yatnena kartavyo bhUtimicchatA .
nAsya kRtyAni budhyeran mitrANi ripavastathA . ArabdhAnyeva pazyeran suparyavasitAnyapi .
bhItavat saMvidhAtavyaM yAvad bhayamanAgatam . AgataM tu bhayaM dRSTvA prahartavyamabhItavat .
daNDenopanataM zatrumanugRhaNAti yo naraH . sa mRtyumupagRhaNIyAd garbhamazvatarI yathAH .
anAgataM hi budhyeta yacca kAryaM puraH sthitam . na tu buddhikSayAt kiMcidatikrAmet prayojanam .
utsAhazcApi yatnena kartavyo bhUtimicchatA . vibhajya dezakAlau ca daivaM dharmAdayastrayaH . naiHzreyasau tu tau jJeyau dezakAlAviti sthitiH .
tAlavat kurute mUlaM bAlaH zatrurupekSitaH . gahane ' gnirivotsRSTaH kSipraM saMjAyate mahAn .
agniM stokamivAtmAnaM saMdhukSayati yo naraH . sa vardhamAno grasate mahAntamapi saMcayam .
AzAM kAlavatIM kuryAt kAlaM vighnena yojayet . vijaM nimittato brUyAnimittaM vApi hetutaH .
kSuro bhUtvA haret prANAn nizitaH kAlasAdhanaH . praticchanno lomahArI dviSatAM parikartanaH .
pANDaveSu yathAnyAyamanyeSu ca kurUdvaha . vartamAno na majjestvaM tathA kRtyaM samAcara . sarvakalyANasampanno viziSTa iti nizcayaH . tasmAt tvaM pANDuputrebhyo rakSAtmAnaM narAdhipa .9 . .
bhrAtRvyA balino yasmAt pANDuputrA narAdhipa . pazcAttApo yathA na syAt tathA nItirvidhIyatAm .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktvA sampratasthe kaNikaH savagRhaM tataH . dhRtarASTro ' pi kauravyaH zokArtaH samapadyata .
dhRtarASTra uvAca adhiSThitaH padA mUrdhni bhagnasaktho mahIM gataH . zauTIryamAnI putro me kimabhASata saMjaya . atyarthaM kopano rAjA jAtavairazca pANDuSu . vyasanaM paramaM prAptaH kimAha paramAhave .
saMjaya uvAca zRNu rAjan pravakSyAmi yathAvRttaM narAdhipa . rAjJA yaduktaM bhagnena tasmin vyasana Agate .
bhagnasaktho nRpo rAjan pAMsunA so ' vaguNThitaH . yamayan mUrdhajAstatra vIkSya caiva dizo daza .
kezAn niyamya yatnena niHzvasanurago yathA . saMrambhAzruparItAbhyAM netrAbhyAmabhivIkSya mAm . bAhU dharaNyAM niSyiSya sudurmatta iva dvipaH .
prakIrNAn mUrdhajAn dhunvan dantairdantAnupaspRzan . garhayan pANDavaM jyeSThaH niHzvasyedamathAbravIt . bhISme zAntanave nAthe karNe zastrabhRtAM vare . gautame zakunau cApi droNe cAstrabhRtAM vare . azvatthAmna tathA zalye zUre ca kRtavarmaNi . imAmavasthAM prApto ' smi kAlo hi duratikramaH .
samayaM hataH . ekAdazacamUbhartA so ' hametAM dazAM gataH . kAlaM prApya mahAbAho na kazcidativartate .
AkhyAtavyaM madIyAnAM ye ' smiJjIvanti saMyuge . yathAhaM bhImasenena vyutkramya
bahUni sunRzaMsAni kRtAni khalu pANDavaiH . bhUrizravasi karNe ca bhISme droNe ca zrImati .
idaM cAkIrtijaM karma nRzaMsaiH pANDavaiH kRtam . yena te satsu nirvedaM gamiSyanti hi me matiH .
kA prItiH sattvayuktasya kRtvopAdhikRtaM jayam . ko vA samayabhettAraM budhaH sammantumarhati .
adharmeNa jayaM labdhvA ko na hRSyeta paNDitaH . yathA saMhRSyate pApaH pANDuputro vRkodaraH .
kinnu citramitastvadya bhagnasakthasya yanmama . kruddhena bhImasenena pAdena mRditaM ziraH .
pratapantaM zriyA juSTaM vartamAnaM ca bandhuSu . evaM kuryAnnaro yo hi sa vai saMjaya pUjitaH .
abhijJau yuddhadharmasya mama mAtA pitA ca me . tau hi saMjaya duHkhArtI vijJApyau vacanAddhi me . iSTaM bhRtyA bhRtAH samyag bhUH prazAstA sasAgarA . mUrdhni sthitamamitrANAM jIvatAmeva saMjaya .
dattA dAyA yathAzakti mitrANAM ca priyaM kRtam . amitrA bAdhitAH sarve ko nu svantataro mayA .
mAnitA bAndhavAH sarve vazyaH sampUjito janaH . tritayaM sevitaM sarvaM ko nu svantataro mayA . AjJaptaM nRpamukhyeSu mAnaH prAptaH sudurlabhaH .
AjAneyaistathA yAtaM ko nu svantataro mayA . yAtAni pararASTrANi nRpA bhuktAzca dAsavat . priyebhyaH prakRtaM sAdhu ko nu svantataro mayA .
adhItaM vidhivad dattaM prAptamAyurnirAmayam . svadharmeNa jitA lokAH ko nu svantataro mayA .
diSTyA nAhaM jitaH saMkhye parAn preSyavadAzritaH . diSTyA me vipulA lakSmIp/ate tvanyagatA vibho .
yadiSTaM kSatrabandhUnAM svadharmamanutiSThatAm . nidhanaM tanmayA prAptaM ko na svantataro mayA .
diSTyA nAhaM parAvRtto vairAt prAkRtavanjitaH . diSTyA na vimati kAMcid bhajitvA tu parAjitaH . suptaM vAthaM pramattaM vA yathA hanyAd viSeNa vA . evaM vyutkrAntadharmeNa vyutkramya samayaM hataH .
azvatthAmA mahAbhAgaH kRtavarmA ca sAtvataH . kRpaH zAradvatazcaiva vaktavyA vacanAnmama . adharmeNa pravRttAnAM pANDavAnAmanekazaH . vizvAsaM samayaghnAnAM na yUyaM gantumarhatha . vArtikAMzcAbravId rAjA putraste satyavikramaH . adharmAd bhImasenena nihato ' haM yathA raNe .
so ' haM droNaM svargagataM karNazalyAvubhau tathA . vRSasenaM mahAvIryaM zakuni cApi saubalam . jalasaMdhaM mahAvIryaM bhagadattaM ca pArthivam . somadattaM maheSvAsaM saindhavaM ca jayadratham . duHzAsanapurogAMzca bhrAtRnAtmasamAMstathA . dauHzAsaniM ca vikrAntaM lakSmaNaM cAtmajAvubhau . etAMzcAnyAMzca subahUn madIyAMzca sahasrazaH . pRSThato ' nugamiSyAmi sArthahIno yathA ' dhvagaH .
kathaM bhrAtRRn hatAzrutvA bhartAraM ca svasA mama . rorUyamANA duHkhArtA duHzalA sA bhaviSyati .
snuSAbhiH prasnuSAbhizca vRddho rAjA pitA mama . gAndhArIsahitazcaiva kAM gatiM pratipatsyati .
nUnaM lakSmaNamAtApi hataputrA hatezvarA . vinAzaM yAsyati kSipraM kalyANI pRthalocanA .
yadi jAnAti cArvAkA parivAD vAgvizAradaH . kariSyati mahAbhAgo dhruvaM cApacitiM mama .
samantapaJcake puNye triSu lokeSu vizrute . ahaM nidhanamAsAdya lokAn prApsyAmi zAzvatAn . tato janasahasrANi bASpapUrNAni mAriSa . pralApaM nRpateH zrutvA vyadravanta dizo daza .
sasAgaravanA ghorA pRthivI sacarAcarA . cacAlAtha sanirhAdA dizazcaivAvilAbhavan .
te droNaputramAsAdya yathAvRttaM nyavedayan . vyavahAraM gadAyuddhe pArthivasya ca pAtanam .
tadAkhyAya tataH sarve droNaputrasya bhArata . dhyAtvA ca suciraM kAlaM jagmurArtA yathAgatam .
yudhiSThira uvAca zrutaM priyamidaM kRSNa yat tvamarhasi bhASitum . tanye ' mRtarasaM puNyaM mano hlAdayati prabho .
bahUni kila yuddhAni vijayasya narAdhipaiH . punarAsan hRSIkeza tatra tatra ca me zrutam .
kiM nimittaM sa nityaM hi pArthaH sukhavivarjitaH . atIva vijayo dhImanniti me dUyate manaH .
saMcintayAmi kaunteyaM raho jiSNuM janArdana . atIva duHkhabhAgI sa satataM pANDunandanaH .
kiM nu nasya zarIre ' sti sarvalakSaNapUjite . aniSTaM lakSaNaM kRSNa yena duHkhAnyupAznute .
atIvAsukhabhogI sa satataM kuntinandanaH . na hi pazyAmi bIbhatsornindyaM gAtreSu kiMcana . zrotavyaM cenmayai tad vai tanme vyAkhyAtumarhasi .
ityuktaH sa hRSIkezo dhyAtvA sumahaduttaram . rAjAnaM bhojarAjanyavardhano viSNurabravIt . na hyasya nRpate kiMcit saMzliSTamupalakSaye . Rte puruSasiMhasya piNDike ' syAdhike yataH .
sa tAbhyAM puruSavyAghro nityamadhvasu vartate . na cAnyadanupazyAmi yenAsau duHkhabhAjanam .
ityuktaH puruSazreSThastadA kRSNena dhImatA . provAca vRSNizArdUlamevametaditi prabho .
kRSNA tu draupadI kRSNaM tiryak sAsUyamaikSata . pratijagrAha tasyAstaM praNayaM cApi kezihA . sakhyuH sakhA hRSIkezaH sAkSAdiva dhanaMjayaH .
tatra bhImAdayaste tu kuravo yAjakAzca ye . remuH zrutvA vicitrAM tAM dhanaMjayakathaM zubhAm .
teSAM kathayatAmeva puruSo ' rjunasaMkathAH . upAyAd vacanAd dUto vijayasya mahAtmanaH .
so ' bhigamya kuruzreSThaM namaskRtya ca buddhimAn . upAyAtaM naravyAghraM phAlgunaM pratyavedayat .
tacchutvA nRpatistasya harSabAdhyAkulekSaNaH . priyAkhyAnanimittaM vai dadau bahudhanaM tadA .
tato dvitIye divase mahAzabdo vyavardhata . Agacchati naravyAghne kauravANAM dhuraMdhare .
tato reNuH samudbhUto vivabhau tasya vAjinaH . abhito vartamAnasya yathoccaiHzravasastathA .
tatra harSakarI vAco narANAM zuzruve ' rjunaH . diSTyAsi pArthakuzalI dhanyo rAjA yudhiSThiraH .
ko ' nyo hi pRthivIM kRtsnA jitvA hi yudhi pArthivAn . cArayitvA hayazreSThamupAgacchedRte ' rjunAt .
ye vyatItA mahAtmAno rAjAnaH sagarAdayaH . teSAmapIdRzaM karma na kadAcana zuzruma .
naitadanye kariSyanti bhaviSyA vasudhAdhipAH . yat tvaM kurukulazreSTha duSkaraM kRtavAnasi .
ityevaM vadatAM teSAM puMsAM karNasukhA giraH . zRNvan viveza dharmAtmA phAlguno yajJasaMstaram .
tato rAjA sahAmAtyaH kRSNazca yadunandanaH . dhRtarASTra puraskRtya taM pratyudyayatustadA .
so ' bhivAdya pituH pAdau dharmarAjasya dhImataH . bhImAdIMzcApi sampUjya paryadhvajata kezavam .
taiH sametyArcitastAMzca pratyAtha yathA vidhi . vizazcAma mahAbAhustIraM labveva pAragaH . etasminneva kAle tu sa rAjA babhruvAhanaH .
mAtRbhyAM sahito dhImAn kurUneva jagAma ha . tatra vRddhAn yathAvat sa kurUnanyAMzca pArthivAn .
abhivAdya mahAbAhustaizcApi pratinanditaH . praviveza pitAmahyAH kuntyA bhavanamuttamam .
vaizampAyana uvAca yathAgataM gate zakre bhrAtRbhiH saha saGgataH . kRSNayA caiva bIbhatsurdharmaputramapUjayat .
abhivAdayamAnaM taM mUryupAghrAya pANDavam . harSagadgadayA vAcA prahRSTo ' rjunamabravIt .
kathamarjuna kAlo ' yaM svarge vyatigatastava . kathaM cAstrANyavAptAni devarAjazca toSitaH .
samyag vA te gRhItAni kaccidastrANi pANDava . kaccit surAdhipaH prIto rudro vAstrANyadAd tava .
yathA dRSTazca te zakro bhagavAn vA pinAkadhRk . yathaivAstrANyavAptAni yathaivArAdhitazca te .
yathoktavAMstvAM bhagavAn zatakraturariMdama . kRtapriyastvayAsmIti tasya te kiM priyaM kRtam .
etadicchAmyahaM zrotuM vistareNa mahAdyute . yathA tuSTo mahAdevo devarAjastathAnagha .
yaccApi vajrapANestu priyaM kRtamariMdama . etadAkhyAhi me sarvamakhilenadhanaMjaya .
arjuna uvAca zRNu hanta mahArAja vidhinA yena dRSTavAn . zatakratumahaM devaM bhagavantaM ca zaGkaram .
vidyAmadhItya tAM rAjastvayoktAmarimardana . bhavatA ca samAdiSTastapase prasthito vanam .
bhRgutuGgamatho gatvA kAmyakAdAsthitastapaH . ekarAtroSitaH kaJcidapazyaM brAhmaNaM pathi .
sa mAmapRcchat kaunteya kvAsi gantA bravIhi me . tasmA avitathaM sarvamabruvaM kurunandana .
sa tathyaM mama tacchrutvA brAhmaNo rAjasattama . apUjayata mAM rAjan prItimAMzcAbhavanmayi .
tato mAmabravIt prItastapa AtiSTha bhArata . tapasvI nacireNa tvaM drakSyase vibudhAdhipam .
tato ' haM vacanAt tasya girimAruhya zaiziram . tapo ' tapyaM mahArAja mAsaM mUlaphalAzanaH .
dvitIyazcApi me mAso jalaM bhakSayato gataH . nirAhArastRtIye ' tha mAse pANDavanandana .
arzvabAhuzcaturthaM tu mAsamasmi sthitastadA . na ca me hIyate prANastadadbhutamivAbhavat .
paJcame tvatha samprApte prathame divase gate . varAhasaMsthitaM bhUtaM matsamIpaM samAgamat .
nighnan prothena pRthivIM vilikhaMcaraNairapi . sammArjaJjaThareNorvI vivartazca muhurmuhuH .
anu tasyAparaM bhUtaM mahat kairAtasaMsthitam . dhanurbANAsimat prAptaM strIgaNAnugataM tadA .
tato ' haMdhanurAdAya tathAkSayye maheSudhI . atADayaM zareNAtha tad bhUtaM lomaharSaNam .
yugapat taM kirAtastu vikRSya balavaddhanuH . abhyAjane dRDhataraM kampayatriva me manaH .
sa tu mAmabravId rAjan mama pUrvaparigrahaH . mRgayAdharmamutsRjya kimarthaM tADitastvayA .
eSa te nizitairbANairdap/a hanmi sthiro bhava . sadhanuSmAn mahAkAyastato mAmabhyabhASata .
tato girimivAtyarthamAvRNonmAM mahAzaraiH . taM cAhaM zaravarSeNa mahatA samavAkiram .
tataH zarairdIptamukhairyantritairanumantritaiH . pratyavidhyamahaM taM tu vajairiva ziloccayam .
tasya tacchatadhA rUpamabhavacca sahasradhA . tAni cAsya zarIrANi zarairahamatADayam .
punastAni zarIrANi ekIbhUtAni bhArata . adRzyanta mahArAja tAnyahaM vyadhamaM punaH .
aNuvRhacchirA bhUtvA bRhaccANuzirAH punaH . ekIbhUtastadA rAjan so ' bhyavartata mAM yudhi .
yadAbhibhavituM bANairna ca zaknomi taM raNe . tato mahAstramAtiSThaM vAyavyaM bharatarSabha .
na cainamazakaM hantuM tadadbhutamivAbhavat . tasmin pratihate cAstre vismayo me mahAnabhUt .
bhUya eva mahArAja savizeSamahaM tataH . astrapUgena mahatA raNe bhUtamavAkiram .
sthUNAkarNabhayo jAlaM zaravarSamatholbaNam . zalabhAstramazmavarSa samAsthAyAhamabhyayAm .
jagrAsa prasabhaM tAni sarvANyastrANi me nRpa . teSu sarveSu jagdheSu brahmAstraM mahadAdizam .
tataH prajvalitairbANaiH sarvataH sopacIyate . upacIyamAnazca mayA mahAstreNa vyavardhata . .
tata : saMtApitA lokA matprasUtena tejasA . kSaNena hi dizaH khaM ca sarvato hi vidIpitam .
tadapyastraM mahAtejAH kSaNenaiva vyazAtayat . brahmAstre tu hate rAjan bhayaM mAM mahadAvizat .
tato ' haMdhanurAdAya tathAkSayye maheSudhI . sahasAbhyahanaM bhUtaM tAnyapyastrANyabhakSayat .
hateSvastreSu sarveSu bhakSiteSvAyudheSu ca . mama tasya ca bhUtasya bAhuyuddhamavartata .
vyAyAma muSTibhiH kRtvA talairapi samAgataiH . apArayaMzca tad bhUtaM nizceSTamagamaM mahIm .
tataH prahasya tad bhUtaM tatraivAntaradhIyata . saha strIbhirmahArAja pazyato me ' ddhRtopamam .
evaM kRtvA sa bhagavAMstato ' nyad rUpamAsthitaH . divyameva mahArAja vasAno ' dbhutamambaram .
hitvA kirAtarUpaM ca bhagavAMstridazezvaraH . svarUpaM divyamAsthAya tasthau tatra mahezvaraH .
adRzyata tataH sAkSAd bhagavAn govRSadhvajaH . umAsahAyo vyAladhRg bahurUpaH pinAkadhUk .
sa mAmabhyetya samare tathaivAbhimukhaM sthitam . zUlapANirathovAca tuSTo ' smIti paraMtapa .
tatastaddhanurAdAya tUNau cAkSayyasAyako . prAdAnmamaiva bhagavAndhArayasveti cAvravIt .
