tasmin bhagne mahArAja kRpe zAradvate yudhi . azvatthAmApyapAyAsIt pANDaveyAd sthAntaram .
dRSTvA zAradvataM pArtho mUcchitaM zarapIDitam . ratha eva maheSvAsaH sakRpaM paryadevayat .
azrupUrNamukho dIno vacanaM cedamabravIt . pazyannidaM mahAprAjJaH kSattA rAjAnamuktavAn .
kulAntakaraNe pApe jAtamAtre suyodhane . nIyatAM paralokAya sAdhvayaM kulapAMsanaH .
asmAddhi kurumukhyAnAM mahadutpatsyate bhayam . tadidaM samanuprAptaM vacanaM satyavAdinaH .
tatkRte hyadya pazyAmi zaratalpagataM gurum . dhigastu kSAtramAcAraM dhigastu balapauruSam .
ko hi brAhmaNamAcAryamabhiduhyeta mAdRzaH . RSiputro mamAcAryo droNasya paramaH sakhA . .
eSa zete rathopasthe kRpo madbANapIDitaH . akAmayAnena mayA vizikhairardito bhRzam .
avasIdan rathopasthe prANAn pIDayatIva me . putrazokAbhitaptena zarairabhyarditena ca .
abhyasto bahubhirbANairdazadharmagatena vai . zocayatyeSa niyattaM bhUyaH putravadhAddhi mAm .
kRpaNaM svarathe sannaM pazya kRSNa yathAgatam . upAkRtya tu vai vidyAmAcAryebhyo nararSabhAH .
prayacchantIha ye kAmAn devatvamupayAnti te . ye ca vidyAmupAdAya gurubhyaH puruSAdhamAH .
pranti tAneva durvRttAste vai nirayagAminaH . tadidaM narakAyAdya kRtaM karma mayA dhruvam .
AcArya zaravarSeNa rathe sAdayatA kRpam . yat tat pUrvamupAkurvannatraM mAmabravIt kRpaH .
na kathaMcana kauravya prahartavyaM gurAviti . tadidaM vacanaM sAdhorAcAryasya mahAtmanaH .
nAnuSThitaM tamevAjau vizikhairabhivarSatA . namastasmai supUjyAya gautamAyApalAyine .
dhigastu mama vArSNeya yadasmai praharAmyaham . tathA vilayamAne tu savyasAcini taM prati .
saindhavaM nihitaM dRSTvA rAdheyaH samupAdravat . tamApatantaM rAdheyamarjunasya rathaM prati .
pAJcAlyau sAtyakizcaiva sahasA samupAdravan . upAyAntaM tu rAdheyaM dRSTvA pArtho mahArathaH .
prahasan devakIputramidaM vacanamabravIt . eSa prayAtyAdhirathiH sAtyakeH syandanaM prati .
na mRSyati hataM nUnaM bhUrizravasamAhave . yatra yAtyeSa tatra tvaM codayAzvAn janArdana .
na saumadattipadavIM gamayet sAtyakiM vRSaH . evamukto mahAbAhuH kezavaH savyasAcinA .
pratyuvAca mahAtejAH kAlayuktamidaM vacaH . alameSa mahAbAhuH karNAyaiko ' pi pANDava . .
kiM punadraupadeyAbhyAM sahitaH sAtvatarSabhaH . na ca tAvat kSamaH pArtha tava karNena saGgaraH .
prajvalantI maholkeva tiSThatyasya hi vAsavI . tvadarthe pUjyamAnaiSA rakSyate paravIrahan .
ataH karNaH prayAtvatra sAtvatasya yathAtathA . ahaM jJAsyAmi kaunteya kAlamasya durAtmanaH . yatrainaM vizikhaistIkSNaiH pAtayiSyasi bhUtale .
dhRtarASTra uvAca yo ' sau karNena vIrasya vArSNeyasya samAgamaH . hate tu bhUrizravasi saindhave ca nipAtite .
sAtyakizcApi virathaH kaM samArUDhavAn ratham . cakrarakSau ca pAJcAlyau tanmamAcakSva saMjaya .
saMjaya uvAca hanta te vartayiSyAmi yathA vRttaM mahAraNe . zuzrUSasva sthiro bhUtvA durAcaritamAtmanaH .
pUrvameva hi kRSNasya manogatamidaM prabho . vijetavyo yathA vIraH sAtyakiH saumadattinA .
atItAnAgate rAjan sa hi vetti janArdanaH . tataH sUtaM samAhUya dArukaM saMdideza ha . ratho me yujyatAM kalyamiti rAjan mahAbalaH . na hi devA na gandharvA na yakSoragarAkSasAH .
mAnavA vApi jetAraH kRSNayoH santi kecana . pitAmahapurogAzca devAH siddhAzca taM viduH . tayoH : prabhAvamatulaM zRNu yuddhaM tu tat tathA . sAtyakiM virathaM dRSTvA karNa cAbhyudyataM raNe .
dadhmau zaGkha mahAnAdamASabheNatha mAdhavaH . dAruko ' vetya sadezaM zrutvA zaGkhasya ca svanam .
sthamanvAnayat tasmai suparNocchritaketanam . sa kezavasyAnumate rathaM dArukasaMyutam . Aruroha zineH pautro jvalanAdityasanibham . kAmagaiH zaibyasugrIvameghapuSpabalAhakaiH . hayodagrairmahAvegairhemabhANDavibhUSitaiH . yuktaM samAruhya ca taM vimAnapratimaM ratham .
abhyadravat rAdheyaM pravapan sAyakAn bahUn . cakrarakSAvapi tadA yudhAmanyUttamaujasau .
dhanaMjayarathaM hitvA rAdheyaM pratyudIyatuH . rAdheyo ' pi mahArAja zaravarSa samutsRjan .
abhyadravat susaMkruddho raNe zaineyamacyutam . naiva daivaM na gAndharva nAsuraM na ca rAkSasam .
tAdRzaM bhuvi no yuddhaM divi vA zrutamityuta . upAramata tat sainyaM sarathAzvanaradvipam .
tayordRSTvA mahArAja karma sampUDhacetasaH . sarve ca samapazyanta tad yuddhamatimAnuSam .
tayortRvarayo rAjan sArathyaM dArukasya ca . gatapratyAgatAvRttairmaNDalaiH saMnivartanaiH .
sArathestu rathasthasya kAzyapeyasya vismitAH . nabhastalagatAzcaiva devagandharvadAnavAH .
atIvAvahitA draSTuM karNazaineyayo raNam . mitrArthe tau parAkrAntau zuSmiNo sparghinau raNe .
karNazcAmarasaMkAzo yuyudhAnazca sAtyakiH . anyonyaM tau mahArAja zaravarSairavarSatAm .
pramamAtha zineH pautraM karNaH sAyakavRSTibhiH . amRSyamANo nidhanaM kauravyajalasaMdhayoH .
karNaH zokasamAviSTo mahoraga iva zvasan . sa zaineyaM raNe kruddhaH pradahanniva cakSuSA .
abhyadhAvata vegena punaH punarariMdama . taM tu sakrodhamAlokya sAtyakiH pratyuyudhyata .
mahatA zaravarSeNa gajaM prati gajo yathA . tau sametau naravyAghrau vyAghrAviva tarasvinau . anyonyaM saMtatakSAte raNe ' nupamavikramau . tataH karNa zineH pautraH sarvapArasavaiH zaraiH . bibheda sarvagAtreSu punaH punarariMdama . sArathiM cAsya bhallena rathanIDAdapAtayat .
azvAMzca caturaH zvetAn nijaghAna zitaiH zaraiH . chittvA dhvajaM rathaM caiva zatadhA puruSarSabha .
cakAra visthaM karNa tava putrasya pazyataH . tato vimanaso rAjaMstAvakAste mahArathAH .
vRSasenaH karNasutaH zalyo madrAdhipastathA . droNaputrazca zaineyaM sarvataH paryavArayan .
tataH paryAkulaM sarva na prAjJAyata kiMcana . tathA sAtyakinA vIre visthe sUtaje kRte .
hAhAkArastato rAjan sarvasainyeSvabhUnmahAn . karNo ' pi viratho rAjan sAtvatena kRtaH zaraiH .
duryodhanarathaM tUrNaMmAruroha viniHzvasan . mAnayaMstava putrasya bAlyAt prabhRti sauhRdam .
kRtAM rAjyapradAnena pratijJA paripAlayan . tathA tu virathaM karNa putrAMzca tava pArthiva . duHzAsanamukhAn vIrAn nAvadhIt sAtyakirvazI . rakSan pratijJAM bhImena pArthena ca purAkRtAm .
virathAn vihvalAMzcakre na tu prANairvyayojayat . bhImasenena tu vadhaH putrANAM te pratizrutaH .
anudyUte ca pArthena vadha : karNasya saMzrutaH . vadhe tvakurvan yatnaM te tasya karNamukhAstadA .
nAzakuvaMstato hantuM sAtyakiM pravarA rathAH . drauNizca kRtavarmA ca tathaivAnye mahArathAH .
nirjitA dhanuSaikena zatazaH kSatriyarSabhAH . kAGkSatA paralokaM ca dharmarAjasya ca priyam .
kRSNayoH sadRzo vIrye sAtyakiH zatrutApanaH . jitavAn sarvasainyAni tAvakAni hasanniva .
kRSNo vApi bhavelloke pArtho vApi dhanurdharaH . zaineyo vA naravyAghra caturthastu na vidyate .
dhRtarASTra uvAca
ajayyaM vAsudevasya rathamAsthAya sAtyakiH . virathaM kRtavAn karNa vAsudevasamo yudhi . dArukeNa samAyuktaH svabAhubaladarpitaH . kacidanyaM samArUDhaH sAtyaki : zatrutApanaH .
etadicchAmyahaM zrotuM kuzalo hyAsi bhASitum . asA tamahaM manye tanmamAcakSva saMjaya .
zRNu rAjan yathAvRttaM rathamanyaM mahAmatiH . dArukasyAnujastUrNa kalpanAvidhikalpitam . AyasaiH kAJcanaizcApi paTTaiH saMnaddhakUbaram . tArAsahasrakhacitaM siMhadhvajapatAkinam . azvairvAtajavairyuktaM hemabhANDaparicchadaiH . saindhavairindusaMkAzaiH sarvazabdAtigaii~daiH .
citrakAJcanasaMnAhairvAjimukhyairvizAmpate . ghaNTAjAlAkularavaM zaktitomaravidyutam .
yuktaM sAMgrAmikairdravyairvahuzastraparicchadaiH . rathaM sampAdayAmAsa meghagambhIraniHsvanam . taM samAruhya zaineyastava sainyamupAdravat . dAruko ' pi yathAkAmaM prayayau kezavAntikam . karNasyApi rathaM rAjazaGkhagokSIrapANDuraiH . citrakAJcanasaMnAhaiH sadazvarvegavattaraiH .
hemakakSyAdhvajopetaM klRptayantrapatAkinam . agyaM rathaM suyantAraM bahuzastraparicchadam .
upAjahvastamAsthAya karNo ' pyabhyadravad ripUn . etat te sarvamAkhyAtaM yanAM tvaM paripRcchasi . bhUyazcApi nibodhemaM tavApanayajaM kSayam . ekatriMzat tava sutA bhImasenena pAtitAH . dumurkha pramukhe kRtvA satataM citrayodhinam .
zatazo nihatAH zUrAH sAtvatetArjunena ca . bhISmaM pramukhataH kRtvA bhagadattaM ca bhArata . evameSa kSayo vRtto rAjan durmantrite tava .
vaizampAyana uvAca yudhiSThirastu kaunteyo mArkaNDeyaM mahAmunim . puna : papraccha sAmrAjye bhaviSyAM jagato gatim .
yudhiSThira uvAca AzcaryabhUtaM 1 prataH zrutaM no vadatAM vara . mune bhArgava yad vRttaM yugAdau prabhavAtyayam .
asmin kaliyuge tvasti punaH kautUhalaM mama . samAkuleSudharmeSu kiM nu zeSaM bhaviSyati .
kiMvIryA mAnavAstatra kimAhAravihAriNaH . kimAyuSaH kiMvasanA bhaviSyanti yugakSaye . kAM ca kASThAMsamAsAdya punaH sampatsyate kRtam . vistareNa mune brUhi vicitrANIha bhASase .
ityuktaH sa munizreSThaH punarevAbhyabhASata . ramayan vRSNizArdUlaM pANDavAMzca mahAnRSiH .
mArkaNDeya uvAca zRNu rAjan mayA dRSTaM yat purA zrutameva ca . anubhUtaM ca rAjendra devadevaprasAdajam .
bhaviSyaM sarvalokasya vRttAntaM bharatarSabha . kaluSaM kAlamAsAdya kathyamAnaM nibodha me .
kRte catuSpAt sakalo nirvyAjopAdhivarjitaH . vRSaH pratiSThitodharmo manuSye bharatarSabha .
adharmapAdaviddhastu tribhiraMzaiH pratiSThitaH . tretAyAM dvApare ' rdhena vyAmizrodharma ucyate .
tribhiraMzairadharmastu lokAnAkramya tiSThati . tAmasaM yugamAsAdya tadA bharatasattama . caturthAMzenadharmastu manuSyAnupatiSThati . AyurvIryamatho buddhirbalaM tejazca pANDava . manuSyANAmanuyugaM hrasatIti nibodha me . rAjAno brAhmaNA vaizyAH zUdrAzcaiva yudhiSThira . vyAjairdharma cariSyantidharmavaitaMsikA narAH . satyaM saMkSepsyate loke naraiH paNDitamAnibhiH .
satyahAnyA tatasteSAmAyuralpaM bhaviSyati . AyuSaH prakSayAd vidyAM nAMzakSyantyupajIvitum .
vidyAhInAnavijJAnAllobho ' pyabhibhaviSyati . lobhakrodhaparA mUDhAH kAmAsaktAzca mAnavAH .
vairabaddhA bhaviSyanti parasparavadhaiSiNaH . brAhmaNAH kSatriyA vaizyAH saMkIryantaH parasparam . zUdratulyA bhaviSyanti tapa : satyavivarjitAH . antyA madhyA bhaviSyanti madhyAzAntyA na saMzayaH . .
IdRzo bhavitA loko yugAnte paryupasthite . vastrANAM pravarA zANIdhAnyAnAM koradUSakAH .
bhAryAmitrAzca puruSA bhaviSyanti yugakSaye . matsyAmiSeNa jIvanto duhantazcApyajaiDakam . goSu naSTAsu puruSA ye ' pi nityaMdhRtavratAH . te ' pi lobhasamAyuktA bhaviSyanti yugakSaye .
anyonyaM parimuSNAnto hiMsayantazca mAnavAH . ajapA nAstikA : stenA bhaviSyanti yugakSaye .
sarittIreSu kuddAlairvApayiSyanti cauSadhIH . tAzcApyalpaphalAsteSAM bhaviSyanti yugakSaye .
zrAddhe daive ca puruSA ye ' pi nityaMdhRtavratAH . te ' pi lobhasamAyuktA bhokSyantIha parasparam .
pitA putrasya bhoktA ca pituH putrastathaiva ca . atikrAntAni bhojyAni bhaviSyanti yugakSaye .
na vratAni cariSyanti brAhmaNA vedanindakAH . na yakSyanti na hoSyanti hetuvAdavimohitAH . nimneSvIhAM kariSyanti hetuvAdavimohitAH .
nimne kRSi kariSyanti yokSyantidhuridhenukAH . ekahAyanavatsAMzca yojayiSyanti mAnavAH .
putraH pitRvadhaM kRtvA pitA putravadhaM tathA . nisadvego bRhadvAdI na nindAmupalapsyate .
mlecchabhUtaM jagat sarvaM niSkriyaM yajJavarjitam . bhaviSyati nirAnandamanutsavamatho tathA .
prAyazaH kRpaNAnAM hi tathAbandhumatAmapi . vidhavAnAM ca vittAni hariSyantIha mAnavAH .
svalpavIryabalAH stabdhA lobhamohaparAyaNAH . tatkathAdAnasaMtuSTA duSTAnAmapi mAnavAH . parigrahaM kariSyanti mAyAcAraparigrahAH . samAhvayantaH kaunteya rAjAnaH pApabuddhayaH . parasparavadhoyuktA mUrkhAH paNDitamAninaH . bhaviSyanti yugasyAnte kSatriyA lokakaNTakAH .
arakSitAro lubdhAca mAnAhaGkAradarpitAH . kevalaM daNDarucayo bhaviSyanti yugakSaye .
AkramyAkramya sAdhUnAM dArAMzcApidhanAni ca . bhokSyante niranukrozA rudatAmapi bhArata .
na kanyAM yAcate kazciAtrApi kanyA pradIyate . svayaMgrAhA bhaviSyanti yugAnte samupasthitte .
rAjAnazcApyasaMtuSTAH parArthAn mUDhacetasaH . sarvopAyairhariSyanti yugAnte paryupasthite .
mlecchIbhUtaM jagat sarvaM bhaviSyati na saMzayaH . hasto hastaM parimuSed yugAnte samupasthite .
satyaM saMkSipyate loke naraiH paNDitamAnibhiH . sthavirA bAlamatayo bAlAH sthavirabuddhayaH .
bhIrustathA zUramAnI zUrA bhIruviSAdinaH . na vizvasanti cAnyonyaM yugAnte paryupasthite .
ekAhAryaM yugaM sarvaM lobhamohavyavasthitam . adharmo varddhate tatra na tudharmaH pravartate .
brAhmaNAH kSatriyA vaizyA na ziSyanti janAdhipa . ekavarNastadA loko bhaviSyati yugakSaye .
na kSasyati pitA putraM putrazca pitaraM tathA . bhAryAzca patizuzrUSAM na kariSyanti saMkSaya .
ye yavAnnA janapadA godhUmAnnAstathaiva ca . tAn dezAn saMzrayiSyanti yugAnte paryupasthite .
svairAcArAzca puruSA yoSitazca vizAmpate . anyonyaM na sahiSyanti yugAnte paryupasthite .
mlecchabhUtaM jagat sarvaM bhaviSyati yudhiSThira . na zrAddhaistarpayiSyanti daivatAnIha mAnavAH .
na kazcitkasyacicchrotA na kazcitkasyacid guruH . tamograstastadA loko bhaviSyati janAdhipa . .
paramAyuzca bhavitA tadA varSANi SoDaza . tataH prANAn vimokSyanti yugAnte samupasthite .
paJcame vAtha SaSThe vA varSe kanyA prasUyate . saptapavarSASTavarSAzca prajAsyanti narAstadA .
patyau strI tu tadA rAjan puruSo vA striyaM prati . yugAnte rAjazArdUla na toSamupayAsyati .
alpadravyA vRthAliGgA hiMsA ca prabhaviSyati . na kazcit kasyacid dAtA bhaviSyati yugakSaye .
aTTazUlA janapadAH zivazUlAzcatuSpathAH . kezazUlAH striyazcApi bhaviSyanti yugakSaye .
mlecchAcArAH sarvabhakSA dAruNAH sarvakarmasu . bhAvinaH pazcime kAle munaSyA nAtra saMzayaH .
krayavikrayakAle ca sarvaH sarvasya vaJcanam . yugAnte bharatazreSTha vittalobhAt kariSyati .
jJAnAni cApyavijJAya kariSyanti kriyAstathA . Atmacchandena vartante yugAnte samupasthite .
svabhAvAt krUrakarmANazcAnyonyamabhizaMsinaH . bhavitAro janAH sarve samprApte tu yugakSaye .
ArAmAMzcaiva vRkSAMzca nAzayiSyanti nirvyathAH . bhavitA saMzaye loke jIvitasya hi dehinAm .
tathA lobhAbhibhUtAzca bhaviSyanti narA nRpa . brAhmaNAMzca haniSyanti brAhmaNasvopabhoginaH .
hAhAkRtA dvijAzcaiva bhayArtA vRSalArditAH . trAtAramalabhanto vai bhramiSyanti mahImimAm .
jIvitAntakarA : krUrA raudrAH prANivihiMsakAH . yadA bhaviSyanti narAstadA saMkSepsyate yugam .
AzrayiSyanti ca nadI : parvatAn viSamANi ca . pradhAvamAnA vitrastA dvijAH kurukulodvaha . dasyubhiH pIDitA rAjan kAkA iva dvijottamAH . kurAjabhizca satataM karabhAraprapIDitAH .
dhairyaM tyaktvA mahIpAla dAruNe yugasaMkSaye . vikarmANi kariSyanti zUdrANAM paricArakAH .
zUdrAdharmaM pravakSyanti brAhmaNAH paryupAsakAH . zrotArazca bhaviSyanti prAmANyena vyavasthitAH .
viparItazca loko ' yaM bhaviSyatyadharottaraH . eDUkAn pUjayiSyanti varjayiSyanti devatAH .
zUdrAH paricariSyanti na dvijAn yugasaMkSaye . AzrameSu maharSINAM brAhmaNAvasatheSu ca .
devasthAneSu caityeSu nAgAnAmAlayeSu ca . eDUkacilA pRthivIM na devagRhabhUSitA .
bhaviSyati yuge kSINe tad yugAntasya lakSaNam . yadA raudrAdharmahInA mAMsAdAH pAnapAstathA . bhaviSyanti narA nityaM tadA saMkSepsyate yugam . puSpaM puSpe yadA rAjan phale vA phalamAzritam . prajAsyati mahArAja tadA saMkSepsyate yugam . akAlavarSI parjanyo bhaviSyati gate yuge .
akrameNa manuSyANAM bhaviSyanti tadA kriyAH . virodhamatha yAsyanti vRSalA brAhmaNaiH saha .
mahI mlecchajanAkIrNA bhaviSyati tato ' cirAt . karabhArabhayAd viprA bhajiSyanti dizo daza .
nirvizeSA janapadAstathA viSTikarArditAH . AzramAnupalasyanti phalamUlopajIvinaH .
evaM paryAkule loke maryAdA na bhaviSyati . na sthAsyantyupadeze ca ziSyA vipriyakAriNaH .
AcAryo ' panidhizcaiva bhay/ate tadanantaram . arthayuktyA pravatsyanti mitrasambandhibAndhavAH .
abhAvaH sarvabhUtAnAM yugAnte sambhaviSyati . dizaH prajvalitAH sarvA nakSatrANyaprabhANi ca . jyotIMSi pratikUlAni vAtAH paryAkulAstathA . ulkApAtAzca bahavo mahAbhayanidarzakAH .
SaDbhiranyaizca sahito bhAskaraH pratapiSyati . tumulAzcApi nirjhadA digdAhAzcApi sarvazaH .
kabandhAntarhito bhAnurudayAstamane tadA . akAlavarSI bhagavAn bhaviSyati sahasradRk .
sasyAni ca na rokSyanti yugAnte paryupasthite . abhIkSNaM krUravAdinyaH paruSA ruditapriyAH .
bhatRRNAM vacane caiva na sthAsyanti tataH striyaH . putrAzca mAtApitarau haniSyanti yugakSaye .
sUdayiSyanti ca patIn striyaH putrAnapAzritAH . aparvaNi mahArAja sUryaM rAhupaiSyati .
cApi sarvataH prajvaliSyati . pAnIyaM bhojanaM cApi yAcamAnAstadAdhvagAH . na lapsyante nivAsaM ca nirastAH pathi zerate . nirghAtavAyasA nAgAH zakunAH samRgaddhijAH . rUkSA vAco vimokSyanti yugAnte paryupasthite .
yugAnte hutabhuk mitrasambandhinazcApi saMtyakSyanti narAstadA . janaM parijanaM cApi yugAnte paryupasthite . atha dezAn dizazcApi pattanAni purANi ca . kramazaH saMzrayiSyanti yugAnte paryupasthite . hA tAta hA sutetyevaM tadA vAcaH sudAruNAH .
vikrozamAnazcAnyonyaM jano gAM paryaTiSyati . tatastumulasaGghAte vartamAne yugakSaye .
dvijAtipUrvako lokaH krameNa prabhaviSyati . tataH kAlAntare ' nyasmin punarlokavivRddhaye .
bhaviSyati punardaivamanukUlaM yadRcchayA . yadA sUryazca candrazca tathA tiSyabRhaspatI .
ekarAzau sameSyanti prapatsyati tadA kRtam . kAlavarSI ca parjanyo nakSatrANi zubhAni ca .
pradakSiNA grahAzcApi bhaviSyantyanulomagAH . kSemaM subhikSamArogyaM bhaviSyati nirAmayam .
kalkI viSNuyazA nAma dvijaH kAlapracoditaH . utpatsyate mahAvIryo mahAbuddhiparAkramaH .
sambhUtaH sambhalagrAme brAhmaNAvasathe zubhe . manasA tasya sarvANi vAhanAnyAyudhAni ca . upasthAsyanti yodhAzca zastrANi kavacAni ca . sadharmavijayI rAjA cakravartI bhaviSyati .
sa cemaM saMkulaM lokaM prasAdamupaneSyati . utthito brAhmaNo dIptaH kSayAntakRdudAradhIH . saMkSepako hi sarvasya yugasya parivartakaH . sa sarvatra gatAn kSudrAn brAhmaNaiH parivAritaH . utsAdayiSyati tadA sarvamlecchagaNAn dvijaH .
saMjaya uvAca
bhUristu samare rAjazaineyaM rathinAM varam . ApatantamapAsedhat prayANAdiva kuJjaram .
athainaM sAtyakiH kruddhaH paJcabhirnizitaiH zaraiH . vivyAdha hRdaye tasya prAsravat tasya zoNitam .
tathaiva kauravo yuddhe zaineyaM yuddhadurmadam . dazabhirnizitaistIkSNairavidhyata bhujAntare .
tAvanyonyaM mahArAja tatakSAte zarairbhRzam . krodhasaMraktanayanau krodhAd visphArya kArmuke .
tayorAsInmahArAja zastravRSTiH sudAruNA . kruddhayoH sAyakamucoryamAntakanikAzayoH .
tAvanyonyaM aura rAjan saMchAdya samavasthitau . muhUrtaM caiva tad yuddhaM samarUpamivAbhavat .
tataH kruddho mahArAja zaineyaH prahasanniva . dhanuzciccheda samare kauravyasya mahAtmanaH .
athainaM chinnadhanvAnaM navabhirnizitaiH zaraiH . vivyAdha hRdaye tUrNaM tiSTha tiSTheti cAbravIt .
so ' tividdho balavatA zatruNA zatrutApanaH . dhanuranyat samAdAya sAtvataM pratyavidhyata .
sa viddhvA sAtvataM bANaisibhireva vizAmpate . dhanuzciccheda bhallena sutIkSNena hasanniva .
chinnadhanvA mahArAja sAtyakiH krodhamUrchitaH . prajahAra mahAvegAM zaktiM tasya mahorasi .
sa tu zaktyA vibhinnAGgo nipapAta rathottamAt . lohitAGga ivAkAzAd dIptarazmiryadRcchayA .
taM tu dRSTvA hataM zUramazvatthAmA mahArathaH . abhyadhAvata vegena zaineyaM prati saMyuge .
tiSTha tiSTheti cAbhASya zaineyaM sa narAdhipa . abhyavarSaccharaugheNa meruM vRSTyA yathAmbudaH .
tamApatantaM saMrabdhaM zaineyasya rathaM prati . ghaTotkaco ' bravId rAjan nAdaM muktvA mahArathaH .
tiSTha tiSTha na me jIvan droNaputra gamiSyasi . eSa tvAM nihaniSyAmi mahiSaM SaNmukho yathA .
yuddhazraddhAmahaM te ' dya vineSyAmi raNAjire . ityuktvA krodhatAmrAkSo rAkSasaH paravIrahA . .
drauNimabhyadravat kruddho gajendramiva kesarI . rathAkSamAtrairiSubhirabhyavarSad ghaTotkacaH .
rathinAmRSabhaM drauNiM dhArAbhiriva toyadaH . zaravRSTiM tu tAM prAptAM zarairAzIviSopamaiH . zAtayAmAsa samare tarasA drauNirutsmayan . tataH zarazataistIkSNairmarmabhedibhirAzugaiH .
samAcinod rAkSasendraM ghaTotkacamariMdamam . sa zarairAcitastena rAkSaso raNamUrdhani .
vyakAzata mahArAja zvAvicchalalato yathA . tataH krodhasamAviSTo bhaimaseniH pratApavAn .
zarairavacakartogauNiM vajrAzaniprabhaiH . kSuraprairardhacandaizca nArAcaiHsazilImukhaiH . varAhakarNairnAlIkairvikarNaizcAbhyavIvRSat . tAM zasravRSTimatulAM vajrAzanisamasvanAm . patantImupari kruddho drauNiravyathitendriyaH . suduHsahAM zarai .rairdivyAsapratimantritaiH . vyadhamat sumahAtejA mahAbhrANIva mArutaH . tato ' ntarikSe bANAnAM saMgrAmo ' nya ivAbhavat .
ghorarUpo mahArAja yodhAnAM harSavardhanaH . tato ' srasaMgharSakRtairvisphuliGgaiH samantataH .
babhau nizAmukhe vyoma khadyotairiva saMvRtam . sa mArgeNagaNaiauNirdizaH pracchAdya sarvataH .
priyArthaM tava putrANAM rAkSasaM samavAkirat . tataH pravavRte yuddhaM drauNirAkSasayormadhe .
vigADhe rajanImadhye zakraprahlAdayoriva . tato ghaTotkaco bANairdazabhiauNimAhave . jadhAnorasi saMkruddhaH kAlajvalanasaMnibhaiH . sa tairabhyAyatairviddho rAkSasena mahAbalaH . cacAla samare drauNivArtanunna iva dumaH . sa mohamanusamprApto dhvajayaSTiM samAzritaH .
tato hAhAkRtaM sainyaM tava sava janAdhipa . hataM sma menire sarve tAvakAstaM vizAmpate .
taM tu dRSTvA tathAvasthamazvatthAmAnamAhave . paJcAlA : saMjayAzcaiva siMhanAdaM pracakrire .
pratilabhya tataH saMjJAmazvatthAmA mahAbalaH . dhanuH prapIDya vAmena kareNAmitrakarzanaH .
mumocAkarNapUrNena dhanuSA zaramuttamam . yamadaNDopamaM ghoramuddizyAzu ghaTotkacam .
sa bhittvA hRdayaM tasya rAkSasasya zarottamaH . viveza vasudhAmugraH sapuGkhaH pRthivIpate .
so ' tividdho mahArAja rathopastha upAvizat . rAkSasendraH ! subalavAn drauNinA raNazalinA .
dRSTvA vimUDhaM haiDimbaM sArathistu raNAjirAt . drauNe : sakAzAt sambhrAntastvapaninye tvarAnvitaH .
tathA tu samare viddhvA rAkSasendraM ghaTotkacam . nanAda sumahAnAdaM droNaputro mahArathaH .
pUjitastava putraizca sarvayodhaizca bhArata . vapuSAtiprajajvAla madhyAhna iva bhAskaraH .
bhImasenaM tu yudhyantaM bhAradvAjarathaM prati . svayaM duryodhano rAjA pratyavidhyacchitaiH zaraiH .
taM bhImaseno dazabhiH zarairvivyAdha mAriSa . duryodhano ' pi viMzatyA zarANAM pratyavidhyata .
tau sAyakairavacchinnAvadRzyetAM raNAjire . meghajAlasamAcchannau nabhasIvendubhAskarau . 144 .
atha duryodhano rAjA bhImaM vivyAdha patribhiH . paJcabhirbharatazreSTha tiSTha tiSTheti cAbravIt .
tasya bhImo dhanuzchittvA dhvajaM ca dazabhiH zaraiH . vivyAdha kauravazreSThaM navatyA navaparvaNAm .
tato duryodhanaH kruddho dhanuranyanmahattaram . gRhItvA bharatazreSTho bhImasenaM zitai zaraiH . apIDayad raNamukhe pazyatAM sarvadhanvinAm . tAn nihatya zarAn bhImo duryodhana dhanuzcyutAn .
kauravaM paJcaviMzatyA kSudrakANAM samArpayat . duryodhanastu saMkruddho bhImasenasya mAriSa . kSurapreNa dhanuzchittvA dazabhiH pratyavidhyata . athAnyad dhanurAdAya bhImaseno mahAbalaH .
vivyAdha nRpatiM tUrNaM saptabhirnizitaiH zaraiH . tadapyasya dhanuH kSipraM ciccheda laghuhastavat .
dvitIyaM ca tRtIyaM ca caturthaM paJcama tathA . AttamAttaM mahArAja bhImasya dhanurAcchinat . tava putro mahArAja jitakAzI madotkaTaH . sa tathA bhidyamAneSu kArmukeSu punaH punaH .
zaktiM cikSepa samare sarvapArazavIM zubhAm . mRtyoriva svasAraM hi dIptAM vahnizikhAmiva . sImantamiva kurvantI nabhaso ' gnisamaprabhAm . AprAptAmeva tAM zaktiM tridhA ciccheda kauravaH .
pazyataH sarvalokasya bhImasya ca mahAtmanaH . tato bhImo mahArAja gadAM gurvI mahAprabhAm . cikSepAvidhya vegena duryodhanasthaM prati . tataH sA sahasA vAhAMstava putrasya saMyuge . sArathiM ca gadA gurvI mamardAsya rathaM punaH . putrastu tava rAjendra bhImAd bhItaH praNazya ca .
Aruroha rathaM cAnyaM nandakasya mahAtmanaH . tato bhImo hataM matvA tava putraM mahAratham .
siMhanAdaM mahaccakre tarjayan nizi kauravAn . tAvakAH sainikAzcApi menire nihataM nRpam . . tato ' ticukruzuH sarve te hAheti samantataH .
teSAM tu ninadaM zrutvA trastAnAM sarvayodhinAm . bhImasenasya nAdaM ca zrutvA rAjan mahAtmanaH .
tato yudhiSThira rAjA hataM matvA suyodhanam . abhyavartata vegena yatra pArtho vRkodaraH .
paJcAlA : kekayA matsyAH saMjayAzca vizAmpate . sarvodyogenAbhijagmurdoNameva yuyutsayA .
tatrAsIt sumahad yuddhaM droNasyAtha paraiH saha . ghore tamasi magnAnAM nijatAmitaretaram .
saMjaya uvAca arjunasya vacaH zrutvA nocustatra mahArathAH . apriyaM vA priyaM vApi mahArAja dhanaMjayam .
tataH kruddho mahAbAhurbhImaseno ' bhyabhASata . kutsayanniva kaunteyamarjunaM bharatarSabha .
muniryathAraNyagato bhASase dharmasahitam . nyastadaNDo yathA pArthaM brAhmaNaH saMzitavrataH .
kSatatrAtA kSatAjjIvana kSantA strISvapi sAdhuSu . kSatriyaH kSitimApnoti kSipraM dharmaM yazaH zriyaH .
sa bhavAn kSatriyaguNairyuktaH sarvaiH kulodvahaH . avipazcid yathA vAcaM vyAharan nAdya zobhase .
parAkramaste kaunteya zakrasyeva zacIpateH . na cAti vartase dharmaM velAmiva mahodadhiH .
na pUjayet tvAM ko nvadya yat trayotazavArSikam . amarSaM pRSThataH kRtvA dharmamevAbhikAGkSase .
diSTyA tAta manaste ' dya svadharmamanuvartate . AnRzaMsye ca te diSTyA buddhiH satatamacyuta .
yat tu dharmapravRttasya hRtaM rAjyamadharmataH . draupadI ca parAmRSTA sabhAmAnIya zatrubhiH .
vanaM pravAjitAzcAsma valkalAjinavAsasaH . anarhamANAstaM bhAvaM trayodaza samA : paraiH .
etAnyamarSasthAnAni marSitAni mayAnagha . ! kSatradharmaprasaktena sarvametadanuSThitam .
tamadharmamapAkRSTaM smRtvAdya sahitastvayA . sAnubandhAn haniSyAmi kSudrAn rAjyaharAnaham .
tvayA hi kathitaM pUrvaM yuddhAbhyAgatA vayam . ghaTAmahe yathAzaktiM tvaM tu no ' dya jugupsase .
svadharmaM necchase jJAtuM mithyAvacanameva te . bhayArditAnAmasmAkaM vAcA marmANi kRntasi .
vapan braNe kSAramiva kSatAnAM zatrukarzana . vidIryate me hRdayaM tvayA vAkzalyapIDitam .
adharmamenaM vipulaM dhArmikaH san na buddhyase . yat tvamAtmAnamasmAMzca prazasyAn na prazaMsasi .
vAsudeve sthite cApi droNaputraM prazaMsasi . yaH kalAM SoDazI pUrNAM dhanaMjaya na te ' rhati .
svayamevAtmAno doSAn bruvANaH kinna lajjase . dArayeyaM mahIM krodhAd vikireyaM ca parvatAn .
AvidhyaitAM badAM gurvI bhImAM kAJcanamAlinIm . giriprakAzAn kSitijAn bhaJjayamanilo yathA .
drAvayeyaM zaraizcApi sendrAn devAn samAgatAn . sarAkSasagaNAn pArtha sAsuroragamAnavAn .
sa tvamevaMvidhaM jAnan bhrAtaraM mAM nararSabha . droNaputrAd bhayaM kartuM nArhasyamitavikrama .
athavA tiSTha bIbhatso saha sarvaiH sahodaraiH . ahamenaM gadApANirjeSyAmyeko mahAhave .
tataH pAJcAlarAjasya putraH pArthamathAbravIt . saMkruddhamiva nardantaM hiraNyakazipurharim .
dhRSTadyumna uvAca bIbhatso viprakarmANi viditAni manISiNAm . yAjanAdhyApane dAnaM tathA yajJapratigrahau .
SaSThamadhyayanaM nAma teSAM kasmin pratiSThitaH . hato droNo mayA hyevaM kiM mAM pArtha vigarhase .
apakrAntaH svadharmAca kSAtradharmaM vyapAzritaH . amAnuSeNa hantyasmAnasreNa kSudrakarmakRt .
tathA mAyA prayuJjAnamasahyaM brAhmaNabruvam . mAyayaiva vihanyAd yo na yuktaM pArtha tatra kim .
tasmistathA mayA zaste yadi drauNAyanI ruSA . kurute bhairavaM nAdaM tatra kiM mama hIyate .
na cAdbhutamidaM manye yada drauNiyuddhasaMjJayA . ghAtayiSyati kauravyAn paritrAtumazaknuvan .
yaca mAM dhArmiko bhUtvA bravISi gurughAtinam . tadarthamahamutpannaH pAJcAlyasya suto ' nalAt .
yasya kArya makAryaM vA yudhyataH syAt samaM raNe . taM kathaM brAhmaNaM brUyAH kSatriyaM vA dhanaMjaya .
yo hyanasravido hanyAd brahmAstraiH krodhamUchitaH . sarvopAyairna sa kathaM vadhyaH puruSasattama .
vidharmiNaM dharmavidbhiH proktaM teSAM viSopamam . jAnan dharmArthatattvajJa kiM mAmarjuna garhase .
nRzaMsaH sa mayA ' ' kramya ratha eva nipAtitaH . tanmAmanindyaM bIbhatso kimarthaM nAbhinandase .
kAlAnalasamaM pArtha jvalanArkaviSopamam . bhImaM droNazirazchinnaM na prazaMsasi me katham .
yo ' sau mamaiva nAnyasya vAndhavAn yudhi janivAn . chittvApi tasya mUrdhAnaM naivAsmi vigatajvaraH .
tacca me kRntate marma yanna tasya ziro mayA . niSAdaviSaye kSiptaM jayadrathaziro yathA . .
athAvadhazca zUtraNAmadharmaH zrUyate ' rjuna . kSatriyasya hi dharmo ' yaM hanyAddhanyeta vA punaH .
sa zatrunihataH saMkhye mayA dharmeNa pANDava . yathA tvayA hataH zUro bhagadattaH pittuH sakhA .
pitAmahaM raNe hatvA manyase dharmamAtmanaH . mayA zatrau hate kasmAt pApe dharmaM na manyase .
sambandhAvanataM pArtha na mAM tvaM vaktumarhasi . svagAtrakRtasopAnaM niSNNamiva dantinam .
kSamAmi te sarvameva vAgvyatikramamarjuna . draupadyA draupadeyAnAM kRte nAnyena hetunA .
kulakramAgataM vairaM mamAcAryeNa vizrutam . tathA jAnAtyayaM loko na yUyaM pANDunandanAH .
nAnRtI pANDavo jyeSTho nAhaM vAdhArmikorjuna . ziSyadrohI hata : pApo yudhyasva vijayastava .
vaizampAyana uvAca yayAti : svapuraM prApya mahendrapurasaMnibham . pravizyAntaHpuraM tatra devayAnI nyavezayat . devayAnyAzcAnumate sutAM tAM vRSaparvaNaH . azokavanikAbhyAze gRhaM kRtvA nyavezayat . vRtAM dAsIsahasreNa zarmiSThAM vArSaparvaNIm . vAsobhirannapAnaizca saMvibhajya susatkRtAm .
devayAnyA tu sahitaH sa nRpo nahuSAtmajaH . vijahAra bahUnabdAn devavanmuditaH sukhI .
RtukAle tu samprApte devayAnI varAGganA . lebhe garbhaM prathamataH kumAraM ca vyajAyata .
gate varSasahasra tu zarmiSThA vArSaparvaNI . dadarza yauvanaM prAptA RtuM sA cAnvacintayat .
RtukAlazca samprApto na ca me ' sti patirvRtaH . kiM prAptaM kiM nu kartavyaM kiM vA kRtvA kRtaM bhavet .
devayAnI prajAtAsau vRthAhaM prAptayauvanA . yathA tayA vRto bhartA tathaivAhaM vRNomi tam .
rAjJA putraphalaM deyamiti me nizcitA matiH . apIdAnI sa dharmAtmA iyAnme darzanaM rahaH .
atha niSkramya rAjAsau tasmin kAle yadRcchayA . azokavanikAbhyAze zarmiSThAM prekSya viSThitaH .
tamekaM rahite dRSTvA zarmiSThA cAruhAsinI . pratyudgamyAJjaliM kRtvA rAjAnaM vAkyamabravIt .
zarmiSThovAca somasyendrasya viSNorvA yamasya varuNasya ca . tava vA nAhuSa gRhe kaH striyaM draSTumarhati . rUpAbhijanazIlaihi tvaM rAjan vettha mAM sadA . sA tvAM yAce prasAdyAhamRtuM dehi narAdhipa .
yayAtiruvAca vedmi tvAM zIlasampannAM daityakanyAmaninditAm . rUpaM ca te na pazyAmi sUcyagramapi ninditam .
abravIduzanA kAvyo devayAnIM yadAvaham . neyamAhvayitavyA te zayane vArSaparvaNI .
zarmiSThovAca na narmayuktaM vacanaM hinasti na strISu rAjan na vivAhakAle . prANAtyaye sarvadhanApahAre paJcAnRtAnyAhurapAtakAni .
pRSTaM tu sAkSye pravadantamanyathA vadanti mithyA patitaM narendra . ekArthatAyAM tu samAhitAyAM mithyA vadantaM tvanRtaM hinasti .
yayAtiruvAca rAjA pramANaM bhUtAnAM sa nazyeta mRSA vadan . arthakRcchramapi prApya na mithyA kartumutsahe .
zarmiSThovAca samAvetau matau rAjan pati : sakhyAzca yaH patiH . samaM vivAhamityAhuH sakhyA me ' si vRtaH patiH .
yayAtiruvAca dAtavyaM yAcamAnebhya iti me vratamAhitam . tvaM ca yAcasi mAM kAmaM brUhi kiM karavANi te .
zarmiSThovAca adharmAt pAhi mAM rAjan dharmaM ca pratipAdaya . tvatto ' patyavatI loke careyaM dharmamuttamam .
traya evAdhanA rAjan bhAryA dAsastathA sutaH . yat te samadhigacchanti yasyaite tasya tad dhanam .
devayAnyA bhujiSyAsmi vazyA ca tava bhArgavI . sA cAhaM ca tvayA rAjan bhajanIye bhajasva mAm .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktastu rAjA sa tathyamityabhijajJivAn . pUjayAmAsa zarmiSThAM dharmaM ca pratyapAdayat .
sa samAgamya zarmiSThAM yathAkAmamavApya ca . anyonyaM cAbhisampUjya jagmatustau yathAgatam .
tasmin samAgame subhUH zarmiSThAH cAruhAsinI . lebhe garbhaM prathamatastasmAnRpatisattamAt .
prajajJe ca tataH kAle rAjan rAjIvalocanA . kumAraM devagarbhAbhaM rAjIvanibhalocanam .
saMjaya uvAca tataH parAnIkasahaM vyUhamapratimaM kRtam . samIkSya karNaH pArthanAM dhRSTadyummabhirakSitam .
prayayau rathaghoSeNa siMhanAdaraveNa ca . vAditrANAM ca ninadaiH kampayanniva medinIm .
vepamAna iva krodhAd yuddhazauNDaH paraMtapaH . prativyUhya mahAtejA yathAvad bharatarSabha . .
vyadhamat pANDavIM senAmAsurIM maghavAniva . yudhiSThiraM cAbhyahanadapasavyaM cakAra ha .
dhRtarASTra uvAca kathaM saMjaya rAdheyaH pratyavyUhata pANDavAn . dhRSTadyumnamukhAn sarvAn bhImasenAbhirakSitAn . sarvAneva maheSvAsAnajayyAnamarairapi . ke ca prapakSau pakSau vA mama sainyasya saMjaya .
pravibhajya yathAnyAyaM kathaM vA samavasthitAH . kathaM pANDusutAzcApi pratyavyUhanta mAmakAn .
kathaM caiva mahad yuddhaM prAvartata sudAruNam . kva ca bUbhatsurabhavad yat karNo ' yAd yudhiSThiram .
ko harjunasya sAnnidhye zakto ' bhyetuM yudhiSThiram . sarvabhUtAni yo hyekaH khANDave jitavAn purA . kastamanyastu rAdheyAt pratiyuddhyejijIviSuH .
saMjaya uvAca zRNu vyUhasya racanAmarjunazca yathA gataH . parivArya nRpaM svaM saMgrAmazcAbhavad yathA .
kRpaH zAradvato rAjan mAgadhAzca tarasvinaH . sAtvataH kRtavarmA ca dakSiNaM pakSamAzritAH .
teSAM prapakSe zakunirulUkazca mahArathaH . sAdibhirvimalaprAsaistavAnIkamarakSatAm . gAndhAribhirasambhrAntaH parvatIyaizca durjayaiH . zalabhAnAmiva vAtaiH pizAcairiva durdazaiH .
catustriMzatsahasrANi rathAnAmanivartinAm . saMzaptakA yuddhazauNDA vAma pArzvamapAlayan . samanvitAstava sutaiH kRSNArjunajighAMsavaH .
teSAM prapakSAH kAmbojAH zakAzca yavanaiH saha . nidezAt sUtaputrasya sarathAH sAzvapattayaH . Ahvayanto ' rjunaM tasthuH kezavaM ca mahAbalam .
madhye senAmukhe karNo ' pyavAtiSThata daMzitaH . citravarmAGgadaH stragvI pAlayan vAhinImukham .
rakSamANaiH susaMrabdhaiH putraiH zastrabhRtAM varaH . vAhinIM pramukha vIraH samprakarSannazobhata . abhyavartanmahAbAhuH sUryavaizvAnaraprabhaH .
mahAdvipaskandhagata : piGgAkSa priyadarzanaH . duHzAsano vRtaH sainyaiH sthitau vyUhasya pRSThataH .
tamanvayAnmahArAja svayaM duryodhana nRpaH . citrAstraicitrasaMnAhai : sodayairabhirakSitaH . rakSyamANo mahAvIryaiH sahitairmadrakekayaiH . azobhata mahArAja devairiva zatakratuH .
azvatthAmA kurUNAM ca ye pravIrA mahArathAH . nityamattAzca mAtaGgAH zUrairlecchaiH samAnvitAH . anvayustad sthAnIkaM kSaranta iva toyadA .
te dhvajairvaijayantIbhirvvaladbhiH paramAyudhaiH . sAdibhizcAsthitA rejurdramavanta ivAcalAH .
teSAM padAtinAgAnAM pAdarakSA sahasrazaH . paTTizAsidharAH zUrA babhUvuranivartinaH .
sAdibhiH syandanai gairadhikaM samalaGkRteH . sa vyUharAjo vibabhau devAsuracamUpamaH .
bArhaspatyaH suvihito nAyakena vipazcitA . nRtyatIva mahAvyUhaH pareSAM bhayamAdadhat .
tasya pakSaprapakSebhyo niSpatanti yuyutsavaH . patyazvaratamAtaGgAH prAvRSIva balAhakAH .
tataH senAmukhe karNaM dRSTvA rAjA yudhiSThiraH . dhanaMjayamamitraghnamekavIramuvAca ha .
pazyArjuna mahAvyUhaM karNena vihitaM raNe . yuktaM pakSaiH prapakSaizca parAnIkaM prakAzate .
tadetad vai samAlokya pratyamitraM mahad balam . yathA nAbhibhavatyasmAMstathA nItirvidhIyatAm .
evamukto ' rjuno rAjJA prAJjalirnupamabravIt . yathA bhavAnAha tathA tat sarvena tadanyathA . .
yastvasya vihito ghAtastaM kariSyAmi bhArata . pradhAnavadha evAsya vinAzastaM karomyaham .
yudhiSThira uvAca tasmAt tvameva rAdheyaM bhImasenaH suyodhanam . vRSasenaM ca nakulaH sahadevo ' pi saubalam . duHzAsanaM zatAnIko hArdikyaM zinipuGgavaH . dhRSTadyumno droNasutaM svayaM yotsyAmyahaM kRpam .
draupadeyA dhArtarASTraziSTAn saha zikhaNDinA . te te ca tAMstAnahitAnasmAkaM mantu mAmakAH .
