tvaM kAlarAtrImiva kazcidAturaH kiM mAM dRDhaM prArthayase ' dya kIcaka . zcandra jighRkSuriva manyase hi mAm .
teSAM priyAM prArthayato na te bhuvi gatvA divaM vA zaraNaM bhaviSyati . na vartate kIcaka te dRzA zubhaM yA tena saMjIvanamarthayet sA .
arjuna uvAca tato mAmativizvastaM saMrUDhazaravikSatam . devarAjo vigRhyedaM kAle vacanamabravIt .
divyAnyastrANi sarvANi tvayi tiSThanti bhArata . na tvAbhibhavituM zakto mAnuSo bhuvi kazcana .
bhISmo droNaH kRpaH karNaH zakuniH saha rAjabhiH . saMgrAmasthasya te putra kalAM nArhanti SoDazIm .
idaM ca me tanutrANaM prAyacchanmaghavAn prabhuH . abhedyaM kavacaM divyaM srajaM caiva hiraNmayIm .
devadattaM ca me zaGkha punaH prAdAnmahAravam . divyaM cedaM kirITaM me svayamindro yuyoja ha .
tato divyAni vastrANi divyAnyAbharaNAni ca . prAdAcchakro mamaitAni rucirANi bRhanti ca .
evaM sampUjitastatra sukhamasamyuSito nRpa . indrasya bhavane puNye gandharvazizubhiH saha .
tato mAmabravIcchakraH prItimAnamaraiH saha . samayo ' rjuna gantuM te bhrAtaro hi smaranti te .
evamindrasya bhavane paJca varSANi bhArata . uSitAni mayA rAjan smaratA dyUtajaM kalim .
tato bhavantamadrAkSaM bhrAtRbhiH parivAritam . gandhamAdanapAdasya parvatasyAsya mUrdhani . .
yudhiSThira uvAca diSTyAdhanaMjayAstrANi tvayA prAptAni bhArata . diSTyA cArAdhito rAjA devAnAmIzvaraH prabhuH .
diSTyA ca bhagavAn sthANurdevyA saha paraMtapa . sAkSAd dRSTaH svayuddhena toSitazca tvayAnagha .
diSTyA ca lokapAlaistvaM sameto bharatarSabha . diSTyA vardhAmahe pArtha diSTyAsi punarAgataH .
adya kRtsnAM mahIM devIM vijitAM puramAlinIm . manye ca dhRtarASTrasya putrAnapi vazIkRtAn .
icchAmi tAni cAstrANi draSTuM divyAni bhArata . yaistathA vIryavantaste nivAtakavacA hatAH .
arjuna uvAca zvaH prabhAte bhavAn draSTA divyAnyastrANi sarvazaH . nivAtakavacA ghorA yairmayA vinipAtitAH .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamAgamanaM tatra kathayitvAdhanaMjayaH . bhrAtRbhiH sahitaH sarvai rajanI tAmuvAsa ha .
brahmovAca ahaMkArAt prasUtAni mahAbhUtAni paJca vai . pRthivI vAyurAkAzamApo jyotizca paJcamam .
teSu bhUtAni muhyanti mahAbhUteSu paJcasu . zabdasparzanarUpeSu rasagandhakriyAsu ca .
mahAbhUtavinAzAnte pralaye pratyupasthite . sarvaprANabhRtAM dhIrA mahadabhyudyate bhayam .
yad yasmAjjAyate bhUtaM tatra tat pravilIyate . lIyante pratilomAni jAyante cottarottaram .
tataH pralIne sarvasmin bhUte sthAvarajaGgame . smRtimantastadA dhIrA na lIyante kadAcana .
zabdaH sparzastathA rUpaM raso gandhazca paJcamaH . kriyAH karaNanityAH syuranityA mohasaMjJitAH .
lobhaprajanasambhUtA nirvizeSA hyakiMcanAH . mAMsazoNitasaMghAtA anyonyaspopajIvinaH . bahirAtmAna ityete dInAH kRpaNajIvanaH . prANApAnAvudAnazca samAno vyAna eva ca . antarAtmani cApyete niyatAH paJca vAyavaH . vADmanobuddhibhiH sArddhamidamaSTAtmakaM jagat .
tvadhrANazrotracaDhUMSi rasanA vAk ca saMyatAH . vizuddhaM ca mano yasya buddhizcAvyabhicAriNI . aSTau yasyAgnayo hyete na dahante manaH sadA . sa tad brahma zubhaM yAti tasmAd bhUyo na vidyate .
ekAdaza ca yAnyAhurindriyANi vizeSataH . ahaMkArAt prasUtAni tAni vakSyAmyahaM dvijAH .
zrotraM tvakcakSuSI jihvA nAsikA caiva paJcamI . pAdau pAyurupasthazca hastau vAg dazamI bhavet .
indriyagrAma ityeSa mana ekAdazaM bhavet . etaM grAmaM jayet pUrvaM tato brahma prakAzate .
buddhIndriyANi paJcAhuH paJcakarmendriyANi ca . zrotrAdInyapi paJcAhuddhiyuktAni tattvataH .
avizeSANi cAnyAni karmayuktAni yAni tu . ubhayatra mano jJeyaM buddhistu dvAdazI bhavet .
ityuktAnIndriyANyetAnyekAdaza yathAkramam . manyante kRtamityevaM viditvA tAni paNDitAH .
ataH paraM pravakSyAmi sarvaM vividhamindriyam . AkAzaM prathamaM bhUtaM zrotramadhyAtmamucyate .
adhibhUtaM tathA zabdo dizastatrAdhidaivatam . dvitIyaM mAruto bhUtaM tvagadhyAtma ca vizrutA .
spaSTavyamadhibhUtaM ca vidyut tatrAdhidaivatam . tRtIyaM jyotirityAhuzcakSuradhyAtmamucyate .
adhibhUtaM tato rUpaM sUryastatrAdhidaivatam . caturthamApo vijJeyaM jihvA cAdhyAtmamucyate .
adhibhUtaM rasazcAtra somastatrAdhidaivatam . pRthivI paJcamaM bhUtaM ghrANazcAdhyAtmamucyate .
adhibhUtaM tathA gandho vAyustatrAdhidaivatam . eSu paJcasu bhUteSu triSu yazca vidhiH smRtaH .
ataH paraM pravakSyAmi sarvaM vividhamindriyam . pAdAvadhyAtmamityAhurbrAhmaNAstattvadarzinaH .
adhibhUtaM tu gantavyaM viSNustatrAdhidaivatam . avAggatirapAnazca pAyuradhyAtmamucyate .
adhibhUtaM visargazca mitrastatrAdhidaivatam . prajanaH sarvabhUtAnAmupastho ' dhyAtmamucyate .
adhibhUtaM tathA zukra daivataM ca prajApatiH . hastAvadhyAtmamityAhuradhyAtmaviduSo janAH .
adhibhUtaM ca karmANi zakrastatrAdhidaivatam . vaizvadevI tata : pUrvA vAgadhyAtmamihocyate .
vaktavyamadhibhUtaM ca bahvistatrAdhidaivatam . adhyAtmaM mana ityAhuH paJcabhUtAtmacArakam .
adhibhUtaM ca saMkalpazcandramAzcAdhidaivatam . ahaMkArastathAdhyAtma sarvasaMsArakArakam .
abhimAno ' dhibhUtaM ca rudrastatrAdhidaivatam . adhyAtmaM buddhirityAhuH ghaDindriyavicAriNI .
adhibhUtaM tu mantavyaM brahmA tatrAdhidaivatam . trINi sthAnAni bhUtAnAM caturthaM nopapadyate .
sthalamAstathA ' ' kAzaM janma cApi caturvidham . aNDajodbhijjasaMsvedajarAyujamathApi ca .
caturdhA janma ityetad bhUtagrAmasya lakSyate . aparANyatha bhUtAni khecarANi tathaiva ca .
aNDajAni vijAnIyAt sarvAzcaiva sarIsRpAn . svadejAH kRmayaH proktA jantavazca yathAkramam .
janma dvitIyamityejajjaghanyataramucyate . bhittvA tu pRthivIM yAni jAyante kAlaparyayAt . udbhijjAni ca tAnyAhurbhUtAni dvijasattamAH . dvipAdabahupAdAni tiryaggatimatIni ca . jarAyujAni bhUtAni vikRtAnyapi sattamAH . dvividhA khalu vijJeyA brahmayoniH sanAtanI . tapaH karma ca yatpuNyamityeSa viduSAM nayaH . vividhaM karma vijJeyamijyA dAnaM ca tanmakhe . jAtasyAdhyayanaM puNyamiti vRddhAnuzAsanam . etad yo vetti vidhivad yuktaH sa syAd dvijarSabhAH . .
vimuktaH sarvapApebhya iti caiva nivodhatA yathAvadadhyAtmavidhireSa vaH kIrtito mayA .
jJAnamasya hi dharmajJAH prAptaM jJAnavatAmiha . indriyANIndriyArthAzca mahAbhUtAni paJca ca . sarvANyetAni saMdhAya manasA sampradhArayet .
kSINe manasi sarvasmin ca janmasukhamiSyate . jJAnasampannasattvAnAM tat sukhaM viduSAM matam .
ataH paraM pravakSyAmi sUkSmabhAvakarIM zivAm . nivRttiM sarvabhUteSu mRdunA dAruNena ca .
guNAguNamanAsaGgamekacaryamanantaram . etad brahmamayaM vRttamAhurekapadaM sukham .
vidvAn kUrma ivAGgAni kAmAn saMhatya sarvazaH . virajAH sarvato mukto yo naraH sa sukhI sadA .
kAmAnAtmani saMyamya kSINatRSNaH samAhitaH . sarvabhUtasuhRnmitro brahmabhUyAya kalpate .
indriyANAM nirodhena sarveSAM viSayaiSiNAm . munerjanapadatyAgAdadhyAtmAgniH samidhyate .
yathAgnirindhanairiddho mahAjyotiH prakAzate . tathendriyanirodhena mahAnAtmA prakAzate .
yadA pazyati bhUtAni prasannAtmA ' ' tmano hRdi . svayaMjyotistadA sUkSmAt sUkSmaM pranpotyanuttamam .
agnI rUpaM payaH sroto vAyuH sparzanapeva ca . mahI paGkadharaM ghoramAkAzazravaNaM tathA . rogazokasamAviSTaM paJcasrotaHsamAvRtam . paJcabhUtasamAyuktaM navadvAraM dvidaivatam . rajasvalamathAdRzyaM triguNaM ca tridhAtukam . saMsargAbhirataM mUDhaM zarIramiti dhAraNA .
duzcaraM sarvaloke ' smin sattvaM prati samAzritam ! etadeva hi loke ' smin kAlacakra pravartate . etanmahArNavaM ghoramagAdhaM mohasaMjJitam . vikSipet saMkSipeccaiva bodhayet sAmaraM jagat .
kAmaM krodha bhayaM lobhamabhidrohamathAnRtam . indriyANAM nirodhena satastyajati dustyajAn .
yasyaite nirjitA loke triguNAH paJcadhAtavaH . vyomi tasya paraM sthAnamAnantyamatha labhyate .
paJcendriyamahAkUlAM manovegamahodakAm . nadIM mohahradAM tIrkhA kAmakrodhAvubhau jayet .
sa sarvadoSanirmuktastataH pazyati tatparam . mano manasi saMdhAya pazyannAtmAnamAtmani .
sarvavit sarvabhUteSu vindatyAtmAnamAtmani . ekadhA bahudhA caiva vikurvANastatastataH .
dhruvaM pazyati rUpANi dIpAd dIpazataM yathA . sa vai viSNuzca varuNo ' gniH prajApatiH .
sa hi dhAtA vidhAtA ca sa prabhuH sarvatomukhaH . hRdayaM sarvabhUtAnAM mahAnAtmA prakAzate .
taM viprasaMghAzca surAsurAzca yakSAH pizAcAH pitaro vayAMsi . rakSogaNA bhUtagaNAzca sarve maharSayazcaiva sadA stuvanti .
suparNa uvAca yasmAduttAryate pApAd yasmAnniHzreyaso ' znute . asmAduttAraNabalAduttaretyucyate dvija .
uttarasya hiraNyasya parivApazca gAlava . mArgaH pazcimapUrvAbhyAM digbhyAM vai madhyamaH smRtaH .
asyAM dizi variSThAyAmuttarAyAM dvijarSabha . nAsaumyo nAvidheyAtmA nAdharmo vasate janaH .
atra nArAyaNaH kRSNo jiSNuzcaiva narottamaH . badaryAmAzramapade tathA brahmA ca zAzvataH .
atra vai himavatpRSThe nityamAste mahezvaraH . prakRtyA puruSaH sArdhaM yugAntAgnisamaprabhaH .
na sa dRzyo munigaNaistathA devaiH savAsavaiH . gandharvayakSasiddhairvA naranArAyaNAdRte .
atra viSNuH sahasrAkSaH sahasracaraNo ' vyayaH . sahasrazirasaH zrImAnekaH pazyati mAyayA . .
atra rAjyena viprANAM candramAzcAbhyaSicyata . atra gaGgAM mahAdevaH patantIM gaganAccyutAm .
pratigRhya dadau loke mAnuSe brahmavittama . atra devyA tapastaptaM mahezvaraparIpsayA .
atra kAmazca roSazca zailacomA ca sambabhuH . atra rAkSasayakSANAM gandharvANAM ca gAlava . Adhipatyena kailAse dhanado ' pyabhiSecitaH . atra caitrarathaM ramyamatra vaikhAnasAzramaH .
atra mandAkinI caiva mandarazca dvijarSabha . atra saugandhikavanaM nairRtairabhirakSyate .
zAdvalaM kadalIskandhamatra saMtAnakA nagAH . atra saMyamanityAnAM siddhAnAM svairacAriNAm .
vimAnAnyanurUpANi kAmabhogyAni gAlava . atra te RSayaH sapta devI cArundhatI tathA .
vaizampAyana uvAca pitAmahaM guruM caiva pratyudgamya yudhiSThiraH . abhivAdyaH tato rAjannidaM vacanamabravIt .
bhISmaM droNaM kRpaM drauNiM duryodhanaviviMzatI . asmin yajJe bhavanto mAmanugRhaNantu sarvazaH .
idaM vaH sumahaccaiva yadihAsti dhanaM mama . praNayantu bhavanto mAM yatheSTamabhimantritAH .
evamuktvA sa tAn sarvAn dIkSitaH pANDavAgrajaH . yuyoja sa yathAyogamadhikAreSvanantaram .
bhakSyabhojyAdhikAreSu duHzAsanamayojayat . parigrahe brAhmaNAnAmazvatthAmAnamuktavAn .
rAjJAM tu pratipUjArthaM saMjayaM sa nyayojayat . kRtAkRtaparijJAne bhISmadroNau mahAmatI .
hiraNyasya suvarNasya ratnAnAM cAnvavekSaNe . dakSiNAnAM ca vai dAne kRpaM rAjA nyayojayat .
tathAnyAn puruSavyAghrAMstasmiMstasmin nyayojayat . vAhniko dhRtarASTrazca somadatto jayadrathaH . nakulena samAnItAH svAmivat tatra remire .
kSattA vyayakarastvAsId viduraH sarvadharmAvet . duryodhanastvarhaNAni pratijagrAha sarvazaH .
caraNakSAlane kRSNo brAhmaNAnAM svayaM hyabhUta . sarvalokasamAvRttaH piprISuH phalamuttamam .
draSTukAmAH sabhAM caiva dharmarAjaM yudhiSThiram . na kazcidAharat tatra sahasrAvaramarhaNam .
ratnaizca bahubhistatra dharmarAjamavardhayat kathaM tu mama kauravyo ratnadAnaiH samApnuyAt . yajJamityeva rAjanaH spardhamAnA dadurdhanam . bhavanaiH savimAnApraiH sodarbalasaMvRtaiH . lokarAjavimAnaizca brAhmaNAvasathaiH saha . kRtairAvasathairdivyairvimAnapramimaistathA . . vicitrai ratnavadbhizca RddhyA paramayA yutaiH . rAjabhizca samAvRttairatIva zrIsamRddhibhiH . azobhata sado rAjan kaunteyasya mahAtmanaH .
RddhyA tu varuNaM devaM spardhamAno yudhiSThiraH . SaDagninAtha yajJena so ' yajad dakSiNAvatA .
sarvAJjanAn sarvakAmaiH samRddhaiH samatarpayat . annavAn bahubhakSyazca bhuktavajjanasaMvRtaH . ratnopahArasampanno babhUva sa samAgamaH .
iDAjyahomAhutibhirmatrazikSAvizAradaiH . tasmin hi tatRpurdevAstate yajJe maharSibhiH .
yathA devAstathA viprA dakSiNAnnamahAdhanaiH . tatRpuH sarvavarNAzca tasmin yajJe mudAnvitAH .
saMjaya uvAca tato duryodhano dRSTvA bhImasenaM tathAgatam . pratyudyayAvadInAtmA vegena mahatA nadan .
samApetaturanyonyaM zRGgiNau vRSabhAviva . mahAnirghAtaghoSacaM prahArANAmajAyata .
abhavaca tayoryuddhaM tumulaM lomaharSaNam . jigISatoryathAnyonyamindraprahlAdayoriva .
rudhirokSitasarvAGgau gadAhastau manasvinau . dadRzAte mahAtmAnau puSpitAviva kiMzukau .
tathA tasmin mahAyuddhe vartamAne sudAruNe . khadyotasaMdhairiva khaM darzanIyaM vyarocata .
tathA tasmin vartamAne saMkule tumule bhRzam . ubhAvapi parizrAntau yudhyamAnAvariMdamau .
tau muhUrtaM samAzvasya punareva paraMtapau . abhyahArayatAnyonyaM sampragRhya gade zubhe .
tau tu dRSTvA mahAvI? samAzvastau nararSabhau . balinau vAraNau yadvadvAsitArthe madotkaTau .
samAnavI? samprekSya pragRhItagadAvubhau . vismayaM paramaM jagmurdevagandharvamAnavAH .
pragRhItagadau dRSTvA duryodhanavRkodarau . saMzayaH sarvabhUtAnAM vijaye samapadyata .
samAgamya tato bhUyo bhrAtaro balinAM varau . anyonyasyantaraprepsU pracakrAte ' ntaraM prati .
yamadaNDopamAM gurvImindrAzanimivodyatAm . dadRzuH prekSakA rAjan raudrI vizasanIM gadAm .
Aviddhyato gadAM tasya bhImasenasya saMyuge . zabdaH sutumulo ghoro muhUrtaM samapadyata .
AviddhyantamariM prekSya dhArtarASTro ' tha pANDavam . gadAmatulavegAM tAM vismitaH sambabhUvaha .
caraMzca vividhAnaM mArgAn maNDalAni ca bhArata . azobhata tadA vIro bhUya eva vRkodaraH .
tau parasparamAsAdya yattAvanyonyarakSaNe . mArjArAviva bhakSArye tatakSAte muhurmuhuH .
acarad bhImasenastu mArgAn bahuvidhAMstathA . maNDalAni vicitrANi gatapratyAgatAni ca . .
astrayantrANi citrANi sthAnAni vividhAni ca . parimokSaM prahArANAM varjanaM paridhAvanam .
abhidravaNamAkSepamavasthAnaM savigraham . parivartanasaMvartamavaplutamupaplutam .
upanyastamapanyastaM gadAyuddhavizAradau . evaM tau vicarantau tu parasparamavidhyatAm .
vaJjayAnau punazcaiva ceratuH kurusattamau . vikrIDantau subalinau maNDalAni viceratuH .
tau darzayantau samare yuddhakrIDAM samantataH . gadAbhyAM sahasAnyonyamAjaghnaturariMdamau . parasparaM samAsAdya daMSTrAbhyAM dviradau yathA . azobhetAM mahArAja zoNitena pariplutau .
evaM tadabhavad yuddhaM ghorarUpaM paraMtapa . parivRtte ' hani krUra vRtravAsavayoriva . gadAhastau tatastau tu maNDalAvasthitau balI .
dakSiNaM maNDalaM rAjan bhImaseno ' bhyavartata . savyaM tu maNDalaM tatra bhImaseno ' bhyavartata .
tathA tu caratastasya bhImasya raNamUrdhani . duryodhano mahArAja pArzvadeze ' bhyatADayat .
Ahatastu tato bhImaH putreNa tava bhArata . . Aviddhayata gadAM gurvI prahAraM tamacintayan .
indrAzanisamAM ghorAM yamadaNDamivodyatAm . dadRzuste mahArAja bhImasenasya tAM gadAm .
AvidhyantaM gadAM dRSTvA bhImasenaM tavAtmajaH . samudyamya gadAM ghorAM pratyavidhyat paraMtapaH .
gadAmArutavegena tava putrasya bhArata . zabda AsIt sutumulastejazca samajAyata .
sa caran vividhAn mArgAn maNDalAni ca bhAgazaH . . samazobhata tejasvI bhUyo bhImAt suyodhanaH .
AviddhA sarvavegena bhImena mahatI gadA . sadhUmaM sArciSaM cAgniM mumocogramahAsvanA .
AdhUtAM bhImasenena gadAM dRSTvA suyodhanaH . adrisAramayIM gurvImAvidhyan bahazobhatA
gadAmArutavegaM hi dRSTvA tasya mahAtmanaH . bhayaM viveza pANDUMstu sarvAneva sasomakAn .
tau darzayantau samare yuddhakrIDAM samantataH . gadAbhyAM sahasAnyonyamAjaghnaturariMdamau . tau parasparamAsAdya daMSTrAbhyAM dviradau yathA . azobhetAM mahArAja zoNitena pariplutau .
evaM tadabhavad yuddhaM ghorarUpamasaMvRtam . parivRtte ' hani krUraM vRtravAsavayoriva .
dRSTvA vyavasthitaM bhImaM tava putro mahAbalaH . caraMzcitratarAn mArgAn kaunteyamabhidudruve .
tasya bhImo mahAvegAM jAmbUnadapariSkRtAm . atikruddhasya kruddhastu tADayAmAsa tAM gadAm .
savisphuliGgo ni dastayostatrAbhighAtajaH . prAdurAsInmahArAja sRSTayorvajrayoriva .
vegavatyA tayA tatra bhImasenapramuktayA . nipatantyA mahArAja pRthivI samakampata .
tAM nAmRSyata kauravyo gadAM pratihatAM raNe . matto dvipa iva kruddhaH pratikuJjaradarzanAt .
sa savyaM maNDalaM rAjA udbhrAmya kRtanizcayaH . Ajamne mUrdhni kaunteyaM gadayA bhImavegayA .
tayA tvabhihato bhImaH putreNa tava pANDavaH . nAkampata mahArAja tadadbhutamivAbhavat .
AzcaryaM cApi tad rAjan sarvasainyAnyapUjayan . yad gadAbhihato bhImo nAkampata padAt padam . tato gurutarAM dIptAM gadAM hemapariSkRtAm . duryodhanAya vyasRjad bhImo bhImaparAkramaH .
taM prahAramasambhrAnto lAghavena mahAbalaH . moghaM duryodhanazcakre tatrAbhUd vismayo mahAn .
sA tu moghA gadA rAjan patantI bhImacoditA . cAlayAmAsa pRthivI mahAnirghAtani : svanA .
AsthAya kauzikAn mArgAnutpatan sa punaH punaH . gadAnipAtaM prajJAya bhImasenaM ca vaJcitam .
vaJcayitvA tadA bhImaM gadayA kurusattamaH . tADayAmAsa saMkruddho vakSodeze mahAbalaH .
gadayA nihato bhImo muhyamAno mahAraNe . nAbhyamanyata kartavyaM putreNAbhyAhatastava .
tasmiMstathA vartamAne rAjan somakapANDavAH . bhRzopahatasaMkalyA na hRSTamanaso ' bhavan .
sa tu tena prahAreNa mAtaGga iva rohitaH . hastivaddhastisaMkAzamabhidudrAva te sutam .
tatastu tarasA bhImo gadayA tanayaM tava . abhidudrAva vegena siMho vanagajaM yathA .
upasRtya tu rAjAnaM gadAmokSavizAradaH . Avidhyata gadAM rAjan samuddizya sutaM tava .
atADayad bhImasenaH pArzve duryodhanaM tadA . sa vihvalaH prahAreNa jAnubhyAmagamanmahIm .
tasmin kurukulazreSThe jAnubhyAmavanIM gate . udatiSThat tato nAdaH saMjayAnAM jagatpate .
teSAM tu ninadaM zrutvA saMjayAnAM nararSabhaH . amarSAd bharatazreSTha putraste samakupyatA
utthAya tu mahAbAhurmahAnAga iva zvasan . didhakSanniva netrAbhyAM bhImasenamavaikSata .
tataH sa bharatazreSTho gajApANirabhidravan . pramathiSyanniva ziro bhImasenasya saMyuge .
sa mahAtmA mahAtmAnaM bhImaM bhImaparAkramaH . atADayacchavadeze na cacAlAcalopamaH .
sa bhUyaH zuzubhe pArthastADito gadayA raNe . udbhinnarudhiro rAjanprabhinna iva kuJjaraH .
tato gadAM vIrahaNImayomayAM pragRhya vajrAzanitulyAni : svanAm . atADayacchatrumamitrakarSaNo balena vikramya dhanaMjayAgrajaH .
sa bhImasenAbhihatastavAtmajaH papAta saMkampitadehabandhanaH . supuSpito mArutavegatADito vane yathA zAla ivAvaghUrNitaH .
tataH praNedurjahaSuzca pANDavAH samIkSya putraM patitaM kSitau tava . tataH sutaste pratilabhya cetanAM samutpapAta dvirado yathA hradAt .
sa pArthivo nityamamarSitastadA mahArathaH zikSitavat paribhraman . atADayat pANDavamagrataH sthitaM sa vihvalAGgo jagatImupAspRzat .
sa siMhanAdaM vinanAda kauravo nipAtya bhUmau yudhi bhImamojasA . bibheda caivAzanitulyamojasA gadAnipAtena zarIrarakSaNam .
tato ' ntarikSe ninado mahAnabhUd divaukasAmapsarasAM ca neduSAm . papAta caucairamarapraveritaM vicitrapuSpotkaravarSamuttamam .
tataH parAnAvizaduttamaM bhayaM samIkSya bhUmau patitaM narottamam . ahIyamAnaM ca balena kauravaM nizAmya bhedaM sudRDhasya varmaNaH .
tato muhUrtAdupalabhya cetanAM pramRjya vaktraM rudhirAktamAtmanaH . dhRti samAlamvya vivRtya locane balena saMstabhya vRkodaraH sthitaH .
saMjaya uvAca zRNu rAjannavahito yathAvRtto mahAn kSayaH . kurUNAM pANDavAnAM ca samAsAdya parasparam .
nihate sUtaputre tu pANDavena mahAtmanA . vidruteSu ca sainyeSa samAnIteSu cAsakRt . ghore manuSyadehAnAmAjau naravara kSaye . yattat karNe hate pArthaH siMhanAdamathAkarot .
tadA tava sutAn rAjan prAvizat samuhad bhayam . na saMdhAtumanIkAni na caivAtha parAkrame .
AsId buddhirhate karNe tava yodhasya kasyacit . vaNijo nAvi bhinnAyAmagAdhe viplavA iva . apAre pAramicchanto hate dvIpe kirITinA .
sUtaputre hate rAjan vitrastAH zaravikSatAH . anAthA nAthamicchanto mRgAH siMhArditA iva .
bhagnazRGgA iva vRSA : zIrNadaMSTrA ivoragAH . pratyupAyAma sAyAhne nirjitA savyasAcinA .
hatapravIrA svistA nikRttA nizitaiH zaraiH . sUtaputre hate rAjan putrAste prAdravaMstataH .
vidhvastakavacAH sarve kAMdizIkA vicetasaH . anyonyamabhinighnanto vIkSamANA bhayAd dizaH .
mAmeva nUnaM bIbhatsurmAmeva ca vRkodaraH . abhiyAtIti manvAnA : peturmamluzca bhArata . azvAnanye gajAnanye sthAnanye mahArathAH . Aruhya javasampannA pAdAtAn prajahurbhayAt .
kuJjaraiH syandanA bhagnAH sAdinazca mahArathaiH . padAtisaMghAzcAzvodhaiH palAyadbhirbhRzaM hatAH .
vyAlataskarasaMkIrNe sArthahInA yathA vane . tathA tvadIyA nihate sUtaputre tadAbhavan .
hatArohAstathA nAgAzchinnahastAstathApare . sarvaM pArthamayaM lokamapazyan vai bhayArditAH .
tAn prekSya dravataH sarvAn bhImasenabhayArditAn . duryodhano ' tha svaM sUtaM hA hA kRtvaivamabravIt . nAtikramiSyate pArtho dhanuSpANimavasthitam . jaghane yuddhamAnaM mAM tUrNamazvAn pracodaya .
samare yuddhamAnaM hi kaunteyaM mAM dhanaMjayaH . notsahetApyatikrAntuM velAmiva mahArNavaH .
adyArjunaM sagovindaM mAninaM ca vRkodaram . nihatya ziSTAzatrUzca karNasyAnRNyamApnuyAm . tacchrutvA kururAjasya zUrAryasadRzaM vacaH . sUto hemaparicchannAzanairazvAnacodayat .
gajAzvarathahInAstu pAdAtAzcaiva mAriSa . paJcaviMzatisAhasrAH prAdravazanakairiva .
tAn bhImasenaH saMkruddho dhRSTadyumnazca pArSataH . balena caturaGgeNa parikSipyAhanaccharaiH .
pratyayudhyaMstu te sarve bhImasenaM sapArSatam . pArthapArSatayozcAnye jagRhustatra nAmanI .
akruddhyata raNe bhImastairmadhe pratyavasthitaiH . so ' vatIrya rathAttUrNaM gadApANirayudhyatA
na tAn rathastho bhUmiSThAn dharmApekSI vRkodaraH . yodhayAmAsa kaunteyo bhujavIryamupAzritaH .
jAtarUpaparicchannAM pragRhya mahatIM gadAm . nyavadhIt tAvakAn sarvAn daNDapANirivAntakaH .
padAtayo hi saMrabdhAstyaktajIvitabAndhavAH . bhImamabhyadravan saMkhye pataGgA iva pAvakam .
AsAdya bhImasenaM te saMrabdhA yuddhadurmadAH . vineduH sahasA dRSTvA bhUtagrAmA ivAntakam .
zyenavad vyacarad bhImaH khaDDena gadayA tathA . paJcaviMzatisAhasrAstAvakAnAM vyapothayat .
hatvA tat puruSAnIkaM bhImaH satyaparAkramaH . dhRSTadyumnaM puraskRsya punastasthau mahAbalaH .
dhanaMjayo sthAnIkamanvapadyata vIryavAn . mAdrIputro ca zakuni sAtyakizca mahAbalaH .
javenAbhyapatan hRSTA nanto dauryodhanaM balam . tasyAzvavAhAn suvahUMste nihatya zitaiH zaraiH . tamanvadhAvaMstvaritAstatra yuddhamavartata .
tato dhanaMjayo rAjan rathAnIkamagAhata . vizrutaM triSu lokeSu gANDIvaM vyAkSipan dhanuH .
kRSNasArathimAyantaM dRSTvA zvetahayaM ratham . arjunaM cApi yoddhAraM tvadIyAH prAdravan bhayAt .
viprahInarathAzvAzca zaraizca parivAritAH . paJcaviMzatisAhasrAH pArthamArchan padAtayaH .
hatvA tat puruSAnIkaM paJcAlAnAM mahArathaH . bhImasenaM puraskRtya nacirAt pratyadRzyata .
mahAdhanurdharaH zrImAnamitragaNamardanaH . putraH pAJcAlarAjasya dhRSTadyumno mahAyazAH .
pArAvatasavarNAzvaM kovidAravaradhvajam . dhRSTadyumnaM raNe dRSTvA tvadIyAH prAdravan bhayAt .
gAndhArarAjaM zIghrAstramanusRtya yazasvinau . acirAt pratyadRzyetAM mAdrIputrau sasAtyakI .
cekitAnaH zikhaNDI ca draupadeyAzca mAriSa . hatvA tvadIyaM sumahat sainyaM zaGkhAnathAdhaman .
te sarve tAvakAn prekSya dravato vai parAGmukhAn . abhyadhAvanta nighnanto vRSAJjitvA vRSA iva .
senAvazeSaM taM dRSTvA tava putrasya pANDavaH . avasthitaM savyasAcI cukrodha balAvannRpa .
tata enaM zarai rAjan sahasA samavAkirat . rajasA codgatenAtha na sma kiMcana dRzyate .
andhakArIkRte loke zarIbhUte mahItale . dizaH sarvA mahArAja tAvakAH prAdravan bhayAt .
bhajyamAneSu sarveSu kururAjo vizAmpate . pareSAmAtmanazcaiva sainye te samupAdravat .
tato duryodhanaH sarvAnAjuhAvAtha pANDavAn . yuddhAya bharatazreSTha devAniva purA baliH .
ta enamabhigarjantaM sahitAH samupAdravan . nAnAzastrasRjaH kruddhA bhartsayanto muhurmuhuH .
duryodhano ' pyasambhrAntastAnarIn vyadhamaccharaiH . tatrAdbhutamapazyAma tava putrasya pauruSam . yadenaM pANDavAH sarve na zekurativartitum . nAtidUrApayAtaM ca kRtabuddhiH palAyane . duryodhanaH svakaM sainyamapazyad bhRzavikSatam . tato ' vasthApya rAjendra kRtabuddhistavAtmajaH . harSayanniva tAn yodhAstato vacanamabravIt . na taM dezaM prapazyAmi pRthivyAM parvateSu ca . yatra yAtAnna vo hanyuH pANDavAH kiM sRtena vaH .
svalpaM caiva balaM teSAM kRSNau ca bhRzavikSatau . yadi sarve ' tra tiSThAmo dhruvaM no vijayo bhavet .
viprayAtAMstu vo bhinnAn pANDavAH kRtakilviSAn . . 53 anusRtya haniSyanti zreyoH na samare vadhaH .
sukhaH sAMgrAmiko mRtyuH kSatradharmeNa yudhyatAm . mRto duHkhaM na jAnIte pretya cAnantyamaznute .
zRNvantu kSatriyA : sarve yAvanto ' tra samAgatAH . dviSato bhImasenasya vazameSyatha vidrutAH . pitAmahairAcaritaM na dharmaM hAtumarhatha .
nAnyat karmAsti pApIyaH kSatriyasya palAyanAt . na yuddhadharmAccheyAn hi panthAH svargasya kauravAH .
sucireNArjitA~llokAn sadyo yuddhAt samazrute . tasya tad vacanaM rAjJaH pUjayitvA mahArathAH . punarevAmabhyavartanta kSatriyAH pANDavAn prati . parAjayamamRSyantaH kRtacittAzca vikrame .
tataH pravavRte yuddhaM punareva sudAruNam . tAvakAnAM pareSAM ca devAsuraraNopamam .
yudhiSThirapurogAMzca sarvasainyena pANDavAn . anvadhAvanmahArAja putro duryodhanastava .
janamejaya uvAca yat tat tadA mahad brahmalla~lomazo vAkyamabravIt . indrasya vacanAdeva pANDuputraM yudhiSThiram . yaccApi te bhayaM tIvra na ca kIrtayase kvacit . taccApyapahariSyAmi dhanaMjaya ito gate . kiM na tajjapatAM zreSTha karNaM prati mahad bhayam . AsInna ca sa dharmAtmA kathayAmAsa kasyacit . .3 .
vaizampAyana uvAca ahaM te rAjazArdUla kathayAmi kathAmimAm . pRcchato bharatazreSTha zuzrUSasva giraM mama .
dvAdaze samatikrAnte varSe prApte trayodaze . pANDUnAM hitakRcchakra : karNa bhikSitumudyataH .
abhiprAyamatho jJAtvA mahendrasya vibhAvasuH . kuNDalArthe mahArAja sUryaH karNamupAgataH .
mahArhe zayane vIraM spAstaraNasaMvRte . zayAnamativizvastaM brahmaNyaM satyavAdinam .
svapnAnte nizi rAjendra darzayAmAsa razmivAn . kRpayA parayA ' ' viSTaH putrasnehAcca bhArata .
brAhmaNo vedavid bhUtvA sUryo yogarddhirUpavAn . hitArthamabravIt karNaM sAntvapUrvamidaM vacaH .
karNa madvacanaM tAta zRNu satyabhRtAM vara . bruvato ' dya mahAbAho sauhRdAt paramaM hitam .
upAyAsyati zakrastvAM pANDavAnAM hitepsayA . brAhmaNacchadmanA karNa kuNDalApajihIrSayA .
viditaM tena zIlaM te sarvasya jagatastathA . yathA tvaM bhikSitaH sadbhirdadAsyeva na yAcase .
tu vai tvaM hi tAta dadAsyeva brAhmaNebhyaH prayAcitam . vittaM yaccAnyadapyAhuna pratyAkhyAsi kasyacit .
tvAM caivaMvidhaM jJAtvA svayaM pAkazAsanaH . AgantA kuNDalArthAya kavacaM caiva bhikSitum .
tasmai prayAcamAnAya na deye kuNDale tvayA . anuneyaH paraM zaktyA zreya etaddhi te param .
kuNDalArthe bruvaMstAta kAraNairbahubhistvayA . anyairbahuvidhairvittaiH sannivAryaH punaH punaH .
ratnaiH strIbhistathA gobhirdhanairbahuvidhairapi . nidarzanaizca bahubhiH kuNDalepsuH purandaraH .
yadi dAsyasi karNa tvaM sahaje kuNDale zubhe . AyuSaH prakSayaM gatvA mRtyorvazamupaiSyasi .
kavacena samAyuktaH kuNDalAbhyAM ca mAnada . avadhyastvaM raNe ' rINAmiti viddhi vaco mama .
amRtAdutthitaM hyetadubhayaM ratnasambhavam . tasmAd rakSyaM tvayA karNa jIvitaM cet priyaM tava .
karNa uvAca ko mAmevaM bhavAn prAha darzayan sauhRdaM param . kAmayA bhagavan brUhi ko bhavAn dvijaveSadhRk .
brAhmaNa uvAca ahaM tAta sahasrAMzuH sauhRdAt tvAM nidarzaye . kuruSvaitad vaco me tvametacchreyaH paraM hi te .
karNa uvAca zreya eva mamAtyantaM yasya me gopatiH : prabhuH . pravaktAdya hitAnveSI zRNu cedaM vaco mama .
prasAdaye tvAM varadaM praNayAcca bravImyaham . na nivAryo vratAsmAdahaM yadyasmi te priyaH .
vrataM vai mama loko ' yaM vetti kRtsnaM vibhAvaso . yathAhaM dvijamukhyebhyo dadyAM prANAnapi dhruvam .
yadyAgacchati mAM zakro brAhmaNacchadyanA vRtaH . hitArthaM pANDuputrANAM khecarottama bhikSitum . dAsyAmi vibudhazreSTha kuNDale varma cottamam . na me kIrtiH praNazyeta triSu lokeSu vizrutA . .
madvidhasya yazasyaM hi na yuktaM prANarakSaNam . yuktaM hi yazasA yuktaM maraNaM lokasammatam .
so ' hamindrAya dAsyAmi kuNDale saha varmaNA . yadi mAM balavRtraghno bhikSArthamupayAsyati .
hitArthaM pANDuputrANAM kuNDale me prayAcitum . tanme kIrtikaraM loke tasyAkIrtirbhaviSyati .
vRNomi kIrti loke hi jIvitenApi bhAnuman . kIrtimAnaznute svarga hInakIrtistu nazyati .
kIrtirhi puruSaM loke saMjIvayati mAtRvat . akIrtirjIvitaM hanti jIvato ' pi zarIriNaH .
ayaM purANaH zloko hi svayaM gIto vibhAvaso . dhAtrA lokezvara yathA kIrtirAyurnarasya ha .
puruSasya pare loke kItireva parAyaNam . iha loke vizuddhA ca kIrtirAyurvivarddhanI .
so ' haM zarIraje dattvA kIrti prApsyAmi zAzvatIm dattvA ca vidhivad dAnaM brAhmaNebhyo yathAvidhi . . hutvA zarIraM saMgrAme kRtvA karma suduSkaram . vijitya ca parAnAjau yazaH prApsyAmi kevalam .
bhItAnAmabhayaM dattvA saMgrAme jIvitArthinAm . vRddhAn bAlAn dvijAtIMzca mokSayitvA mahAbhayAt . prApsyAmi paramaM loke yazaH svargyamanuttamam . jIvitenApi me rakSyA kIrtistad viddhi me vratam .
so ' haM dattvA maghavate bhikSAmetAmanuttamAm . brAhmaNacchadine deva loke gantA parAM gatim .
zrIbhagavAnuvAca abhayaM sattvasaMzuddhirjJAnayogavyavasthitiH . dAnaM damazca yajJazca svAdhyAyastapa Arjavam .
ahiMsAM satyamakrodhastyAgaH zAntirapaizunam . dayA bhUteSvaloluptvaM mArdavaM hrIracApalam .
tejaH kSamAH dhRtiH zaucamadroho nAtimAnitA . bhavanti sampadaM daivImabhijAtasya bhArata .
dambho darpo ' bhimAnazca krodhaH pAruSyameva ca . ajJAnaM cAbhijAtasya pArtha sampadamAsurIm .
daivI sampad vimokSAya nibandhAyAsurI matA . mA zucaH sampadaM daivImabhijAto ' si pANDava .
dvau bhUtasa ! loke ' smin daiva Asura eva ca . daivo vistarazaH prokta AsuraM pArtha me zRNu . pravRttiM ca nivRttiM ca janA na vidurAsurAH . na zaucaM nApi cAcAro na satyaM teSu vidyate .
asatyamapratiSThaM te jagadAhuranIzvaram . aparasparasambhUtaM kimanyat kAmahaitukam .
etAM dRSTimavaSTabhya naSTAtmAno ' lpabuddhayaH . prabhavantyugrakarmANaH kSayAya jagato ' hitAH .
kAmamAzritya duSpuraM dambhamAnamadAnvitAH . mohAd gRhItvAsadgrAhAn pravartante ' zucivratAH .
cintAmaparimeyAM ca pralayAntAmupAzritAH . kAmopabhogaparamA etAvaditi nizcitAH .
AzApAzazatairbaddhAH kAmakrodhaparAyaNAH . Ihante kAmabhogArthamanyAyenArthasaMcayAn .
idamadya mayA labdhamimaM prApsye manoratham . idamastIdamapi me bhaviSyati punardhanam .
asau mayA hataH zatrurhaniSye cAparAnapi . Izvaro ' hamahaM bhogI siddho ' haM balavAnsukhI .
ADhyo ' bhijanavAnasmi ko ' nyo ' sti sadRzo mayA . akSye dAsyAmi modiSya ityajJAnavimohitAH .
anekacittavibhrAntA mohajAlasamAvRtAH . prasaktAH kAmabhogeSu patanti narake ' zucau .
AtmasambhAvitAH stabdhA dhanamAnamadAnvitAH . yajayante nAmayajJaiste dambhenAvidhipUrvakam .
ahaMkAraM balaM darpa kAmaM krodhaM ca saMzritAH . mAmAtmaparadeheSu pradviSanto ' bhyasUyakAH .
tAnahaM dviSataH krUrAn saMsAreSu narAdhamAn . kSipAmyajasramazubhAnAsurISveva yoniSu .
AsurIM yonimApannA mUDhA janmani janmani . mAmaprApyaiva kaunteya tato yAntyadhamA gatim .
trividhaM narakasyedaM dvAraM nAzanamAtmanaH . kAma : krodhastathA lobhastasmAdetat trayaM tyajet .
etairvimuktaH kaunteya tamodvAraistribhirnaraH . AcaratyAtmanaH zreyastato yAti parAM gatim .
yaH zAstravidhimutsRjya vartate kAmakArataH . na sa siddhimavApnoti na sukhaM na parAM gatim .
tasmAcchAstraM pramANa te kAryAkAryavyavasthitau . jJAtvA zAstravidhAnoktaM karma kartumihArhasi .
lomaza uvAca paradAreSu ye saktA akRtvA dArasaMgraham . nirAzAH pitarasteSAM zrAddhakAle bhavanti vai .
paradAraratiryazca yazca vandhyAmupAsate . brahmasvaM harate yazca samadoSA bhavanti te .
asambhASyA bhavantyete pitRRNAM nAtra saMzayaH . devatAH pitarazcaiSAM nAbhinandanti taddhaviH .
tasmAt parasya vai dArAMstyajed vanthyAM ca yoSitam . brahmasvaM hi nartavyamAtmano hitamicchatA .
zrUyatAM cAparaM guhyaM rahasyaM dharmasaMhitam . zraddadhAnena kartavyaM gurUNAM vacanaM sadA .
dvAdazyAM paurNamAsyAM ca mAsi mAsi ghRtAkSatam . brAhmaNebhyaH prayaccheta tasya puNyaM nibodhata .
somazca vardhate tena samudrazca mahodadhiH . azvamedhacaturbhAgaM phalaM sRjAti vAsavaH .
dAnenatena tejasvI vIryavAMzca bhavennaraH . prItazca bhagavAn soma iSTAn kAmAn prayacchati .
zrUyatAM cAparo dharma : sarahasyo mahAphalaH . idaM kaliyugaM prApya manuSyANAM sukhAvahaH .
kalyamutthAya yo martyaH snAtaH zuklena vAsasA . tilapAtraM prayaccheta brAhmaNebhyaH samAhitaH . tilodakaM ca yo dadyAt pitRRNAM madhunA saha . dIpakaM kRsaraM caiva zrUyatAM tasya yat phalam .
tilapAtre phalaM prAha bhagavAn pAkazAsanaH . gopradAnaM ca yaH kuryAd bhUmidAnaM ca zAzvatam . agniSTomaM ca yo yajJaM yajeta bahudakSiNam . tilapAtraM sahaitena samaM manyanti devatAH .
tilodakaM sadA zrAddhe manyante pitaro ' kSayam . dIpe ca kRsare caiva tuSyante ' sya pitAmahAH .
svarge ca pitRloke ca pitRdevAbhipUjitam . evametanmayoddiSTamRSidRSTaM purAtanam .
yudhiSThira uvAca sarveSAmupavAsAnAM yacchreyaH sumahatphalam . yaccApyasaMzayaM loke tanme tvaM vaktumarhasi .
bhISma uvAca zRNu rAjan yathA gItaM svayameva svayambhuvA . yat kRtvA nirvRto bhUyAt puruSo nAtra saMzayaH .
dvAdazyAM mArgazIrSe tu ahorAtreNa kezavam . aAzvamedhaM prApnoti duSkRtaM cAsya nazyati .
tathaiva pauSamAse tU pUjyo nArAyaNeti ca . vAjapeyamavApnoti siddhiM ca paramAM vrajet .
ahorAtreNa dvAdazyAM mAghamAse tu mAdhavam . rAjasUyamavApnoti kulaM caiva samuddharet .
tathaiva phAlgune mAsi govindeti ca pUjayan . atirAtramavApnoti somalokaM ca gacchati .
ahorAtreNa dvAdazyAM caitre viSNuriti smaran . pauNDarIkamavApnoti devalokaM ca gacchati .
vaizAkhamAse dvAdazyAM pUjayan madhusUdanam . agniSTomamavApnoti somalokaM ca gacchati .
ahorAtreNa dvAdazyAM jyeSThe mAsi trivikramam . gavAM medhamavApnoti apsarobhizca modate .
ASADhe mAsi dvAdazyAM vAmaneti ca pUjayan . naramedhamavApnoti puNyaM ca labhate mahat .
ahorAtreNa dvAdazyAM zrAvaNe mAsi zrIdharam . paJcayajJAnavApnoti vimAnasthazca modate .
tathA bhAdrapade mAsi hRSIkezeti pUjayan . sautrAmaNimavApnoti pUtAtmA bhavate ca hi .
dvAdazyAmAzvine mAsi padmanAbheti cArcayan . gosahasraphalaM pRNyaM prApnuyAnnAtra saMzayaH .
dvAdazyAM kArtike mAsi pUjya dAmodareti ca . gavAM yajJamavApnoti pumAn strI vA na saMzayaH .
arcayet puNDarIkAkSamevaM saMvatsaraM tu yaH . jAtismaratvaM prApnoti vindyAd bahu suvarNakam .
ahanyahani tadbhAvamupendraM yo ' dhigacchati . samApte bhojayed viprAnathavA dApayed ghRtam . ataH paraM nopavAso bhavatIti vinizcayaH . uvAca bhagavAn viSNuH svayameva purAtanam .
uvAca bhagavAn viSNuH svayameva purAtanam .
yudhiSThira uvAca asaumyAH saumyarUpeNa saumyAzcAsaumyadarzanAH . IdRzAn puruSAMstAta kathaM vidyAmahe vayam .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAMtanam . vyAghragomAyusaMvAdaM taM nibodha yudhiSThira .
purikAyAM puri purA zrImatyAM pauriko nRpaH . parahiMsArati : krUro babhUva puruSAdhamaH .
sa tvAyuSi parikSINe jagAmAnIpsitAM gatim . gomAyutvaM ca samprApto dUSitaH pUrvakarmaNA .
saMsmRtya pUrvabhUtiM ca nirvedaM paramaM gataH . na bhakSayati mAMsAni parairupahRtAnyapi .
ahiMsraH sarvabhUteSu satyavAk sudRDhavrataH . sa cakAra yathAkAlamAhAraM patitaiH phalaiH .
zmazAne tasya cAvAso gomAyoH sammato ' bhavat . janmabhUmyanurodhAcca nAnyavAsamarocayat .
tasya zaucamamRSyantaste sarve sahajAtayaH . cAlayanti sma tAM buddhiM vacanaiH prazrayottaraiH .
vasan pitRvane raudre zauce vartitumicchasi . iyaM vipratipattiste yadA tvaM pizitAzanaH .
tatsamAno bhavAsmAbhirbhojyaM dAsyAmahe vayam . bhukSava zaucaM parityajya yaddhi bhuktaM sadAstu te .
iti teSAM vacaH zrutvA pratyuvAca samAhitaH . madhuraiH prasRtairvAryahetumadbhiraniSThuraiH .
apramANA prasUtirme zIlataH kriyate kulam . prArthayAmi ca tatkarma yena vistIryate yazaH .
zmazAne yadi me vAsaH samAdhirme nizamyatAm . AtmA phalati karmANi nAzramo dharmakAraNam .
Azrame yo dvijaM hanyAd gAM vA dadyAdanAzrame . kiM tu tatpAtakaM na syAt tadvA dattaM vRthA bhavet .
bhavantaH svArthalobhena kevalaM bhakSaNe ratAH . anubandhe trayo doSAstAn na pazyanti mohitAH .
apratyayakRtAM gAmarthApanayadUSitAm . iha cAmutra cAnaSTAM tasmAd vRttiM na rocaye .
taM zuciM paNDitaM matvA zArdUlaH khyAtavikramaH . kRtvA ' ' tmasadRzIM pUjAM sAcivye ' varayat svayam . .
zArdUla uvAca saumya vijJAtarUpastvaM gaccha yAtrAM mayA saha . briyantAmIpsitAbhogAH parihAryAzca puSkalAH .
tIkSNA iti vayaM khyAtA bhavantaM jJApayAmahe . mRdupUrvaM hitaM caiva zreyazcAdhigamiSyasi .
atha sampUjya tad vAkyaM mRgendrasya mahAtmanaH . gomAyuH saMzritaM vAkyaM babhASe kiMcidAnataH .
gomAyuruvAca sadRzaM mRgarAjaitat tava vAkyaM madantare . yat sahAyAn mRgayase dharmArthakuzalAzucIn .
na zakyaM hyanamAtyena mahattvamanuzAsitum . duSTAmAtyena vA vIra zarIraparipanthinA . sahAyAnanuraktAMzca nayajJAnupasaMhitAn . parasparamasaMsRSTAn vijigISUnalolupAn . anatItopadhAn prAjJAn hite yuktAn manasvinaH . pUjayethA mahAbhAga yathA ' ' cAryAn yathA pitRn . .
na tveva mama saMtoSAd rocate ' nyanmRgAdhipa . na kAmaye sukhAn bhogAnaizvaryaM ca tadAzrayam .
na yokSyati hi me zIlaM tava bhRtyaiH purAtanaiH . te tvAM vibhedayiSyanti duHzIlAzca madantare .
sazrayaH zlAghanIyastvamanyeSAmapi bhAsvatAm . kRtAtmA sumahAbhAgaH pApakeSvaSyadAruNaH . dIrghadarzI mahotsAhaH sthUlalakSyo mahAbalaH . kRtI cAmodhakartAsi bhAgyaizca samalaMkRtaH .
kiM tu svenAsmi saMtuSTo duHkhavRttiranuSThitA . sevAyAM cApi nAbhijJaH svacchandena vanacaraH .
rAjopakrozadoSAzca sarve saMzrayavAsinAm . vratacaryA tu ni : saMgA nirbhayA vanavAsinAm .
nRpeNAhUyamAnasya yat tiSThati bhayaM hRdi . na tat tiSThati tuSTAnAM vane mUlaphalAzinAm .
pAnIyaM vA nirAyAsaM svAinnaM vA bhayottaram . vicArya khalu pazyAmi tatsukhaM yatra nirvRtiH .
aparAdhairna tAvanto bhRtyAH ziSTA narAdhipaH . upaghAtairyathA bhRtyA dUSitA nidhanaM gatAH .
yadi tvetanmayA kAryaM mRgendra yadi manyase . samayaM kRtamicchAmi vartitavyaM yathA mayi .
madIyA mAnanIyAste zrotavyaM ca hitaM vacaH . kalpittA yA ca me vRttiH sA bhavet tvayi susthirA . .35
na mantrayeyamanyaiste sacivaiH saha karhicit . nItimantaH parIpsanto vRthA brUyuH pare mayi .
eka ekena saMgamya raho brUyAM hitaM vacaH . na ca te jJAtikAryeSu praSTavyo ' haM hitAhite . .
mayA sammantrya pazcAcca na hiMsyAH sacivAstvayA . madIyAnAM ca kupito mA tvaM daNDaM nipAtayeH .
evamastviti tenAsau mRgendreNAbhipUjitaH . prAptavAn matisAcivyaM gomAyurvyAghrayonitaH .
taM tathA sukRtaM dRSTvA pUjyamAna svakarmasu . prAdviSan kRtasaMghAtAH pUrvabhRtyA muhurmuhuH . dhanena mahatA
mitrabuddhyA ca gomAyuM sAntvayitvA prasAdya ca . doSaistu samatAM netumaicchannazubhabuddhayaH .
anyathA jhuSitAH pUrvaM paradravyAbhihAriNaH . azaktAH kiJcidAdAtuM dravyaM gomAyuyantritAH .
vyutthAnaM ca vikAGkSadbhiH kathAbhiH pratilobhyate . caiva buddhirasya vilobhyate . na cApi sa mahAprAjJastasmAd dhairyAccacAla ha .
athAsya samayaM kRtvA vinAzAya tathA pare . IpsitaM tu mRgendrasya mAMsaM yat yatra saMskRtam . apanIya svayaM taddhi taiy/astaM tasya vezmani .
yadarthaM cApyapahRtaM yena taccaiva mantritam . tasya tad viditaM sarvaM kAraNArthaM ca marSitam .
samayo ' yaM kRtastena sAcivyamupagacchatA . nopaghAtastvayA kAryoM rAjan maitrImihecchatA .
bhISma uvAca kSudhitasya mRgendrasya bhoktumabhyutthitasya ca . bhojanAyopahartavyaM tanmAMsaM nopadRzyate . mRgarAjena cAjJaptaM dRzyatAM cora ityuta .
kRtakaizcApi tanmAMsaM mRgendrAyopavarNitam . sacivenApanItaM te viduSA prAjJamAninA .
saroSastvatha zArdUlaH zrutvA gomAyucApalam . babhUvAmarSito rAjA vadhaM cAsya vyarocayat .
chidraM tu tasya tad dRSTvA procuste pUrvamantriNaH . sarveSAmeva so ' smAkaM vRttibhaGge pravartate .
nizcityaiva punastasya te karmANyapi varNayan . . idaM tasyedRzaM karma kiM tena na kRtaM bhavet .
zrutazca svAminA pUrvaM yAdRzo naiva tAdRzaH . vAGmAtreNaiva dharmiSThaH svabhAvena tu dAruNaH .
dharmacchadyA hyayaM pApo vRthAcAraparigrahaH . kAryArtha bhojanArtheSu vrateSu kRtavAzramam .
yadi vipratyayo hyeSa tadidaM darzayAma te . tanmAMsaM caiva gomAyostaiH kSaNAdAzu Dhaukitam .
mAMsApanayanaM jJAtvA vyAghraH zrutvA ca tadvacaH . AjJApayAmAsa tadA gomAyurvadhyatAmiti .
zArdUlasya vacaH zrutvA zArdUlajananI tataH . mRgarAjaM hitairvAkyaiH sambodhayitumAgamat .
putra naitat tvayA grAhyaM kapaTArambhasaMyutam . karmasaMgharSajairdoSairduSyetAzucibhiH zuciH .
nocchritaM sahate kazcit prakriyA vairakArikA . zucerapi hi yuktasya doSa eva nipAtyate .
munerapi vanasthasya svAni karmANi kurvataH . utpAdyante trayaH pakSA mitrodAsInazatravaH .
lubdhAnAM zucayo dveSyAH kAtarANAM tarasvinaH . mUrkhANAM paNDitA dveSyA daridrANAM mahAdhanAH .
adhArmikANAM dharmiSThA virUpANAM surUpiNaH . bahavaH paNDitA mUrkhA lubdhA mAyo jIvinaH . kuryurdoSamadoSasya bRhaspatimaterapi .
zUnyAt tacca gRhAnmAMsaM yadyapyapahRtaM tava . necchate dIyamAnaM ca sAdhu tAvad vimRzyatAm .
asabhyA : sabhyasaMkAzA : sabhyAzcAsabhyadarzanAH . dRzyante vividhA bhAvAsteSu yuktaM parIkSaNam .
talavad dRzyate vyoma khadyoto havyavADiva . na caivAsti talaM vyomni khadyote na hutAzanaH .
tasmAt pratyakSadRSTo ' pi yukto hyarthaH parIkSitum . parIkSya jJApayatrarthAna pazcAt paritapyate .
na duSkaramidaM putra yat prabhurghAtayet param . zlAghanIyA yazasyA ca loke prabhavatAM kSamA .
sthApito ' yaM tvayA putra sAmanteSvapi vizrutaH . duHkhenAsAdyate pAtraM dhAryatAmeSa te suhRt .
dUSitaM paradoSairhi gRhIte yo ' nyathA zucim . svayaM saMdUSitAmAtyaH kSiprameva vinazyati .
tasmAdapyarisaMghAtAd gomAyoH kazcidAgataH . dharmAtmA tena cAkhyAtaM yathaitat kapaTaM kRtam .
tato vijJAtacarita : satkRtya sa vimokSitaH . pariSvaktazca sasnehaM mRgendreNa punaH punaH .
anujJApya mRgendraM tu gomAyurnItizAstravit . tenAmarSeNa saMtaptaH prAyamAsitumaicchata .
zArdUlastaM tu gomAyuM snehAt protphullalocanaH . avArayat sa dharmiSTha pUjayA pratipUjayan .
taM sa gomAyurAlokya snehAdAgatasambhramam . uvAca praNato vAkyaM bASpagadgadayA girA .
pUjito ' haM tvayA pUrvaM pazcAccaiva vimAnitaH . pareSAmAspadaM nIto vastuM nArhAmyahaM tvayi .
asaMtuSTAzca yutAH sthAnAnmAnAt pratyavaropitAH . svayaM copahRtA bhRtyA ye cApyupahitAH paraiH . parikSINAzca lubdhAzca kruddhA bhItAH pratAritAH . hatasvA mAnino ye ca tyaktAdAnA mahepsavaH . saMtApitAzca ye kecid vyasanaughapratIkSiNaH . antarhitA : sopahitAste sarve parasAdhanAH .
avamAnena yuktasya sthAnabhraSTasya vA punaH kathaM yAsyasi vizvAsamahaM tiSThAmi vA katham .
samartha iti saMgRhya sthApayitvA parIkSitaH . kRtaM ca samaya bhittvA tvayAhamavamAnitaH .
prathamaM yaH samAkhyAtaH zIlavAniti saMsadi . na vAcyaM tasya vaiguNyaM pratijJAM parirakSatA .
evaM cAvamatasyeha vizvAsa me na yAsyasi . tvayi cApetavizvAse mamodvego bhaviSyati .
zaMkitastvamahaM bhItaH paracchidrAnudarzinaH . asnigdhAzcaiva dustoSA : karma caitad bahucchalam .
duHkhena zliSyate bhinnaM zliSTaM duHkhena bhidyate . bhinnA zliSTA tu yA prItirna sA snehena vartate .
kazcideva hite bharturdRzyate na parAtmanoH . kAryApekSA hi vartante bhAvasnigdhAH sudurlabhAH .
sudu : khaM puruSajJAnaM cittaM hyeSAM calAcalam . samartho vApyazaGko vA zateSveko ' dhigamyate .
akasmAt prakriyA nRNAmakasmAccApakarSaNam . zubhAzubhe mahattvaM ca prakartuM buddhilAghavam .
bhISma uvAca evaMvidhaM sAntvamuktvA dharmakAmArthahetumat . prasAdayitvA rAjAnaM gomAyurvanamabhyagAt .
agRhyAnunayaM tasya mRgendrasya ca buddhimAn . gomAyuH prAyamAsthAya tyaktvA dehaM divaM yayau .
vaizampAyana uvAca etasminneva kAle tu yathAsampratyayaM kaviH . viduraH preSayAmAsa tad vanaM puruSaM zucim .
sa gatvA tu yadhoddezaM pANDavAn dadRze vane . jananyA saha kauravya mApayAnAn nadIjalam .
viditaM tanmahAbuddhervidurasya mahAtmanaH . tatastasyApi cAreNa ceSTitaM pApacetasaH . tataH pravAsito vidvAn vidureNa narastadA . pArthAnAM darzayAmAsa manomArutagAminIm . sarvavAtasahAM nAvaM yantrayuktAM patAkinIm . zive bhAgIrathItIre narairvistrambhibhiH kRtAm .
tataH punarathovAca jJApakaM pUrvacoditam . yudhiSThira nibodhedaM saMjJArthaM vacanaM kaveH .
kakSaghnaH ziziraghnazca mahAkakSe vilaukasaH . na hantItyevamAtmAnaM yo rakSati sa jIvati .
tena mAM preSitaM viddhi vizvastaM saMjJayAnayA ! bhUyazcaivAha mAM kSattA viduraH sarvato ' rthavit . karNaM duryodhanaM caiva bhrAtRbhiH sahitaM raNe . zakuni caiva kaunteya vijetAsi na saMzayaH .
iyaM vAripathe yuktA naurapsu sukhagAminI . mocayiSyati vaH sarvAnasmAd dezAnna saMzayaH .
atha tAn vyathitAn dRSTvA saha mAtrA narottamAn . nAvamAroSya gaGgAyAM prasthitAnabravIt punaH .
viduro mUryupAghrAya pariSvajya vaco muhuH . ariSTaM gacchatAvyagrAH panthAnamiti cAbravIt .
ityuktvA sa tu tAn vIrAn pumAn viduracoditaH . tArayAmAsa rAjendra gaGgAM nAvA nararSabhAn .
tArayitvA tato gaGgAM pAraM prAptAMzca sarvazaH . jayAziSaH prayujyAtha yathAgatamagAddhi saH .
pANDavAzca mahAtmAnaH pratisaMdizya vai kaveH . gaGgAmuttIrya vegena jagmurmUDhamalakSitAH .
sautiruvAca etatte kathitaM sarvamamRtaM mathitaM tathA . yatra so ' zvaH samutpannaH zrImAnatulavikramaH .
yaM nizamya tadA kadUrvinatAmidamabravIt . uccaiHzravA hi kiM varNo bhadre prabrUhi mA ciram .
vinatovAca zveta evAzvarAjo ' yaM kiM vA tvaM manyase zubhe . brUhi varNaM tvamapyasya tato ' tra vipaNAvahe .
kadUruvAca kRSNavAlamahaM manye hayamenaM zucismite . ehi sArdhaM mayA dIvya dAsIbhAvAya bhAmini .
sautiruvAca evaM te samayaM kRtvA dAsIbhAvAya vai mithaH . jagmatuH svagRhAneva zvo drakSyAva iti sma ha .
tataH putrasahasraM tu karjiA cikIrSatI . AjJApayAmAsa tadA vAlA bhUtvAcanaprabhAH .
AvizadhvaM hayaM kSipraM dAsI na syAmahaM yathA . nAvapadyanta ye vAkyaM tAzazApa bhujaMgamAn .
sarpasatre vartamAne pAvako vaH pradhakSyati . janamejayasya rAjarSeH pANDaveyasya dhImataH .
zApamenaM tu zuzrAva svayameva pitAmahaH . atikrUraM samutsRSTaM kavA daivAdatIva hi .
sArdhaM devagaNaiH sarvairvAcaM tAmanvamodata . bahutvaM prekSya sarpANAM prajAnAM hitakAmyayA .
tigmavIryaviSA hote dandazUkA mahAbalAH . teSAM tIkSNaviSatvAddhi prajAnAM ca hitAya ca . yuktaM mAtrA kRtaM teSAM parapIDopasarpiNAm . anyeSAmapi sattvAnAM nityaM doSaparAstu ye .
teSAM prANAntikI daNDo daivena vinipAtyate . evaM saMbhASya devastu pUjya kadUM ca tAM tadA .
AhUya kazyapaM deva idaM vacanamabravIt . yadete dandazUkAzca sarpA jAtastvayAnagha . viSolbaNA mahAbhogA mAtrA zaptAH paraMtapa . tatra manyustvayA tAta na kartavyaH kathaMcana .
dRSTaM purAtanaM hyetadyajJe sarpavinAzanam . ityuktvA sRSTikRdevastaM prasAdya prajApatim . prAdAdviSaharI vidyAM kazyapAya mahAtmane .
arjuna uvAca saMnyAsasya mahAbAho tattvamicchAmi veditum . tyAgasya ca hRSIkeza pRthak keziniSUdana .
zrIbhagavAnuvAca kAmyAnAM karmaNAM nyAsaM saMnyAsaM kavayo viduH . sarvakarmaphalatyAgaM prAhustyAgaM vicakSaNAH .
tyAjyaM doSavadityeke karma prAhurmanISiNaH . yajJadAnatapaHkarma na tyAjyamiti cApare .
me tatra tyAge bharatasattama . tyAgo hi puruSavyAghra trividhaH samprakIrtitaH .
yajJadAnatapaHkarma na tyAjyaM kAryameva tat . yajJo dAna tapazcaiva pAvanAni manISiNAm .
etAnyapi tu karmANi saGgaM tyaktvA phalAni ca . kartavyAnIti meM pArtha nizcitaM matamuttamam . nizcayaM zRNu
niyatasya tu saMnyAsaH karmaNo nopapadyate . mohAt tasya parityAgastAmasaH parikIrtitaH .
duHkhamityeva yat karma kAyaklezabhayAt tyajet . sa kRtvA rAjasaM tyAgaM naiva tyAgaphalaM labhet .
kAryamityeva yat karma niyataM kriyate ' rjuna . saGgatyaktvA phalaM caiva sa tyAgaH sAttviko mataH .
na dveSTyakuzalaM karma kuzale nAnuSajjate . tyAgI sattvasamAviSTo medhAvI chinnasaMzayaH .
na hi dehabhRtA zakyaM tyaktuM karmANyazeSataH . yastu karmaphalatyAgI sa tyAgItyabhidhIyate .
aniSTamiSTaM mizraM ca trividhaM karmaNaH phalam . bhavatyatyAginAM pretya na tu saMnyAsinAM kvacit .
paJcaitAni mahAbAho kAraNAni nibodha me . sAMkhye kRtAnte proktAni siddhaye sarvakarmaNAm .
adhiSThAna tathA kartA karaNaM ca pRthagvidham . vividhAzca pRthakceSTA daivaM caivAtra paJcamam .
zarIravADmanobhiryat karma prArabhate naraH . nyAyyaM vA viparItaM vA paJcaite tasya hetavaH .
tatraivaM sati kartAramAtmAnaM kevalaM tu yaH . pazyatyakRtabuddhityAnna sa pazyati durmatiH .
yasya nAhaMkRto bhAvo buddhiryasya na lipyate . hatvApi sa imA~llokAnna hanti na nibadhyate .
jJAnaM jJeyaM parijJAtA trividhA karmacodanA . karaNaM karma karteti trividhaH karmasaMgrahaH .
jJAnaM karma ca kartA ca tridhaiva guNabhedataH . procyate guNasaMkhyAne yathAvacchRNu tAnyapi .
sarvabhUteSu yenaikaM bhAvamavyayamIkSate . avibhaktaM vibhakteSu tajjJAnaM viddhi sAttvikam .
pRthaktvena tu yajjJAnaM nAnAbhAvAn pRthagvidhAn . vetti sarveSu bhUteSu tajjJAnaM viddhi rAjasam .
yattu kRtsnavadekasmin kArye saktamahaitukam . atattvArthavadalpaM ca tat tAmasamudAhRtama .
niyataM saGgarahitamarAgadveSataH kRtam . aphalaprepsunA karma yattat sAttvikamucyate .
yattu kAmepsunA karma sAhaMkAreNa vA punaH . kriyate bahulAyAsaM tad rAjasamudAhRtam .
anubandhaM kSayaM hiMsAmanavekSya ca pauruSam . mohAdArabhyate karma yattat tAmasamucyate .
muktasaGgo ' nahaMvAdI dhRtyutsAhasamanvitaH . siddhyasiddhyornirvikAraH kartA sAttvika ucyate .
rAgI karmaphalaprepsurlubdho hiMsAtmako ' zuciH . harSazokAnvitaH kartA rAjasaH parikIrtitaH .
ayuktaH prAkRtaH stabdhaH zaTho naikRtiko ' lasaH . viSAdI dIrghasUtrI ca kartA tAmasa ucyate .
buddherthedaM dhRtezcaiva guNatastrividhaM zRNu . procyamAnamazeSeNa pRthaktvena dhanaMjayaH .
pravRttiM ca nivRttiM ca kAryAkArye bhayAbhaye . bandhaM mokSaM ca yA vetti buddhiH sA pArtha sAttvikI .
yayA dharmamadharmaM ca kArya cAkAryameva ca . ayathAvat prajAnAti buddhiH sA pArtha rAjasI .
adharmaM dharmamiti yA manyate tamasA ' vRtA . sarvArthAn viparItAMzca buddhiH sA pArtha tAmasI .
dhRtyA yayA dhArayate manaHprANendriyakriyAH . yogenAvyabhicAriNyA dhRtiH sA pArtha sAttvikI .
yayA tu dharmakAmArthAn dhRtyA dhArayate ' rjuna . prasaGgena phalAkAkSI dhRtiH sA pArtha rAjasI .
yayA svapnaM bhayaM zokaM viSAdaM madameva ca . na vimuJcati durmedhA dhRtiH sA pArtha tAmasI .
sukhaM tvidAnI trividhaM zRNu me bharatarSabha . abhyAsAd ramate yatra duHkhAntaM ca nigacchati . yattadane viSamiva pariNAme ' mRtopamam . tatsukhaM sAttvikaM proktamAtmabuddhiprasAdajam .
viSayendriyasaMyogAd yattadace ' mRtopamam . pariNAme viSamiva tat sukhaM rAjasaM smRtam .
yadagre cAnubandhe ca sukhaM mohanamAtmanaH . nidrAlasyapramAdotthaM tattAmasamudAhRtam .
na tadasti pRthivyAM vA divi deveSu vA punaH . sattva prakRtijairmuktaM yadebhiH syAt tribhirguNaiH .
brAhmaNakSatriyavizAM zUdrANAM ca paraMtapa . karmANi pravibhaktAni svabhAvaprabhavairguNaiH .
zamo damastapaH zaucaM kSAntirArjavameva ca . jJAnaM vijJAnamAstikyaM brahmakarma svabhAvajam .
zauryaM tejo dhRtirdAkSyaM yuddhe cApyapalAyanam . dAnamIzvarabhAvazca kSAtraM karma svabhAvajam .
kRSigaurakSyavANijyaM vaizyakarma svabhAvajam . paricaryAtmakaM karma zUdrasyApi svabhAvajam .
sve sve karmaNyabhirataH saMsiddhi labhate naraH . svakarmanirataH siddhi yathA vindati tacchRNu . .
yataH pravRttirbhUtAnAM yena sarvamidaM tatam . svakarmaNA tamabhyarcya siddhi vindati mAnavaH .
zreyAn svadharmo viguNaH paradharmAt svanuSThitAt . svabhAvaniyataM karma kurvan nApnoti kilbiSam .
sahajaM karma kaunteya sadoSamapi na tyajet . sarvArambhA hi doSeNa dhUmenAgnirivAvRtAH .
asaktabuddhiH sarvatra jitAtmA vigataspRhaH . naiSkarmyasiddhi paramAM saMnyAsenAdhigacchati .
siddhi prApto yathA brahma tathA ' ' pnoti nibodha me . samAsenaiva kaunteya niSThA jJAnasya yA parA .
buddhyA vizuddhayA yukto dhRtyA ' ' tmAnaM niyamya ca . zabdAdIn viSayAMstyaktvA rAgadveSauvyudasya ca .
viviktasevI ladhvAzI yatavAkkAyamAnasaH . dhyAnayogaparo nityaM vairAgyaM samupAzritaH .
ahaMkAra balaM darpa kAmaM krodhaM parigraham . vimucya nirmamaH zAnto brahmabhUyAya kalpate .
brahmabhUtaH prasannAtmA na zocati na kAGkSati . samaH sarveSu bhUteSu madbhakti labhate parAm .
bhaktyA mAmabhijAnAti yAvAn yazcAsmi tattvataH . tato mAM tattvato jJAtvA vizate tadanantaram .
sarvakarmANyapi sadA kurvANo madyapAzrayaH . matprasAdAdavApnoti zAzvataM padamavyayam .
cetasA sarvakarmANi mayi saMnyasya matparaH . buddhiyogamupAzritya maccittaH satataM bhava .
maccittaH sarvadurgANi matprasAdAt tariSyasi . atha cet tvamahaMkArAnna zroSyasi vinakSyasi .
yadahaMkAramAzritya na yotsya iti manyase . mithyaiSa vyavasAyaste prakRtistvAM niyokSyati .
svabhAvajena kaunteya nibaddhaH svena karmaNA . kartunecchasi yanmohAt kariSyasyavazo ' pi tat .
IzvaraH sarvabhUtAnAM hRddeze ' rjuna tiSThati . bhrAmayan sarvabhUtAni yantrArUDhAni mAyayA .
tameva zaraNaM gaccha sarvabhAvena bhArata . tatprasAdAt parAM zAnti sthAna prApsyasi zAzvatam .
iti te jJAnamAkhyAtaM guhyAd guhyataraM mayA . vimRzyaitadazeSeNa yathecchasi tathA kuru .
sarvaguhyatamaM bhUyaH zRNu me paramaM vacaH . iSTo ' si me dRDhamiti tato vakSyAmi te hitam .
manmanA bhava madbhakto madyAjI mAM namaskuru . mAmevaiSyasi satyaM te pratijAne priyo ' si me .
sarvadharmAn parityajya mAmekaM zaraNaM vrajA ahaM tvA sarvapApebhyo mokSayiSyAmi mA zucaH .
idaM te nAtapaskAya nAbhaktAya kadAcana . na cAzuzrUSave vAcyaM na ca mAM yo ' bhyasUyati .
ya imaM paramaM guhyaM madbhakteSvabhidhAsyati . bhaktiM mayi parAM mAmevaiSyatyasaMzayaH .
na ca tasmAnmanuSyeSu kazcinme priyakRttamaH . bhavitA na ca me tasmAdanyaH priyataro bhuvi .
adhyeSyate ca ya imaM dharmyaM saMvAdamAvayoH . jJAnayajJena tenAhamiSTaH syAmiti me matiH .
zraddhAvAnanasUyazca zRNuyAdapi yo naraH . so ' pi muktaH zubhA~llokAn prApnuyAt puNyakarmaNAm . .
kaccidetacchrutaM pArtha tvayaikAgreNa cetasA . kaccidajJAnasammohaH pranaSTaste dhanaMjaya .
arjuna uvAca naSTo mohaH smRtirlabdhA tvatprasAdAnmayA ' cyuta . sthito ' smi gatasaMdehaH kariSye vacanaM tava .
saMjaya uvAca ityahaM vAsudevasya pArthasya ca mahAtmanaH . saMvAdamimamazrauSamadbhutaM romaharSaNam .
vyAsaprasAdAcchrutavAnetad guhyamahaM param . yogayogezvarAt kRSNAt sAkSAt kathayataH svayam .
rAjan saMsmRtya saMsmRtya saMvAdamimamadbhutam . kezavArjunayoH puNyaM hRSyAmi ca muhurmuhuH .
tacca saMsmRtya saMsmRtya rUpamatyadbhutaM hareH . vismayo me mahAn rAjan hRSyAmi ca punaH punaH .
yatra yogezvaraH kRSNo yatra pArtho dhanurdharaH . tatra zrIvijayo bhUtirbuvA nItirmatirmama .
saMjaya uvAca nyavartata . tAnabhidravato dRSTvA pANDavAMstAvakaM balam . duryodhana mahArAja vArayAmAsa sarvazaH . yodhAMzca svabalaM caiva samantAd bharatarSabha . krozatastava putrasya na sma rAjan
tataH pakSaH prapakSazca zakunizcApi saubalaH . tadA sazastrAH kuravo bhImamabhyadravan raNe .
karNo ' pi dRSTvA dravato dhArtarASTrAn sarAjakAn . padrarAjamuvAcedaM yAhi bhImarathaM prati .
evamuktazca karNena zalyo madrAdhipastadA . haMsavarNAn hayAngrayAn praiSId yatra vRkodarakaH .
te preritA mahArAja zalyenAhavazobhinA . bhImasenarathaM prApya samasajjanta vAjinaH .
dRSTvA karNa samAyAntaM bhImaH krodhasamanvitaH . matiM cakre vinAzAya karNasya bharatarSabha .
so ' bravIt sAtyakiM vIraM dhRSTadyumnaM ca pArSatam . yUyaM rakSata rAjAnaM dharmAtmAnaM yudhiSThiram . saMzayAnmahato muktaM kathaMcita prekSato mama .
agrato me kRtA rAjA chinnasarvaparicchadaH . duryodhana prItyarthaM rAdheyena durAtmanA .
antamadya gamiSyAmi tasya duHkhasya pArSataH . hantAsyadya raNe karNaM sa vA mAM nihaniSyati . saMgrAmeNa sughoreNa satyametad bravImi te .
rAjAnamadya bhavatAM nyAsabhUtaM dadAni vai . tasya saMrakSaNe sarve yatadhvaM vigatajvarAH .
evamuktvA mahAbAhuH prAyAdAdhirathiM prati . siMhanAdena mahatA sarvAH saMnAdayan dizaH .
dRSTvA tvaritamAyAntaM bhImaM yuddhAbhinandinam . sUtaputramathovAca madrANAmIzvaro vibhuH .
zalya uvAca pazya karNaM mahAbAhuM saMkruddhaM pANDunandanam . dIrghakAlArjita krodhaM moktukAmaM tvayi dhruvam .
IdRzaM nAsya rUpaM me dRSTa pUrva kadAcana . abhimanyau hate karNa rAkSase ca ghaTotkace .
trailokyasya samastasya zaktAH kruddho nivAraNe . bibhUti sadRzaM rUpaM yugAntAgnisamaprabham .
saMjaya uvAca iti bruvati rAdheyaM madrANAmIzvare nRpa . abhyavartata vai karNaM krodhadIpto vRkodaraH .
athAgataM tu samprekSya bhImaM yuddhAbhinandim . abravId vacanaM zalyaM rAdheyaM prahasanniva .
yaduktaM vacanaM me ' dya tvayA madrajanezvara . bhImasenaM prati vibho tat satyaM nAtra saMzayaH .
eSa zUraca vIrazca krodhanazca vRkodaraH . nirapekSa zarIre ca prANatazca balAdhikaH .
ajJAtavAsaM vasatA virATanagare tadA . draupadyAH priyakAmena kevalaM bAhusaMzrayAt . tu gUDhabhAvaM samAzritya kIcakaH sagaNo hataH .
so ' dya saMgrAmazirasi saMnaddhaH krodhamUrchitaH . kiM karodyatadaNDena mRtyunApi vrajed raNam .
cirakAlAbhilASito mAmayaM manorathaH . arjunaM samare hanyAM mAM vA hanyAd dhanaMjayaH . sa me kadAcidadyaiva bhaved bhImasamAgamAt .
nihate bhImasene vA yadi vA visthIkRte . abhiyAsyati mAM pArthastanme sAdhu bhaviSyati . atra yanmanyase prAptaM tacchIghraM sampradhArayA
etacchrutvA tu vacanaM rAdheyasyAmitaujasaH . uvAca vacanaM zalyaH sUtaputraM tathAgatam . abhiyAhi mahAbAho bhImasenaM mahAbalam . nirasya bhImasenaM tu tataH prApsyasi phAlgunam .
yaste kAmo ' bhilaSitazcirAt prabhRti hRdgataH . sa vai sampatsyate karNa satyametad bravImi te .
evamukte tataH karNaH zalyaM punarabhASataH . hantA ' hamarjuna saMkhye mAM vA hanyAd dhanaMjayaH . yuddhe manaH samAdhAya yAhi yatra vRkodaraH .
saMjaya uvAca tataH prAyAd rathenAzu zalyastatra vizAmpate . yatra bhImo maheSvAso vyadrAvayata vAhinIm .
tatastUryaninAdazca bherINAM ca mahAsvanaH . uditaSThaca rAjendra karNabhImasamAgame .
bhImaseno ' tha saMkruddhastasya sainyaM durAsadam . nArAcairvimalaistIkSNairdizaH prAdrAvayad balI .
sa saMnipAtastumulo ghorarUpo vizAmpate . AsId raudro mahArAja karNapANDavayormadhe .
tato muhUrtAd rAjendra pANDavaH karNamAdravat . samApatantaM samprekSya karNo vaikartano vRSaH . AjaghAna susaMkruddho nArAcena stanAntare . punazcainamameyAtmA zaravarSairavAkirat .
sa viddhaH sUtaputreNa chAdayAmAsa patribhiH . vivyAdha nizitaiH karNaM navabhinataparvabhiH .
tasya karNo dhanurmadhye dvidhA ciccheda patribhiH . athainaM chinnadhanvAnaM pratyavidhyat stanAntare . nArAcenaM sutIkSNena sarvAvaraNabhedinA .
so ' nyat kArmukamAdAya sUtaputraM vRkodaraH . rAjan marmasu marmajJo vivyAdha nizitaiH zaraiH . nanAda balavannAdaM kampayanniva rodasI .
taM karNaH paJcaviMzatyA nArAcena samArpayat . madotkaTaM vane dRptamulkAbhiriva kuJjaram .
tataH sAyakabhinnAGgaH pANDavaH krodhamUrchitaH . saMrambhASatAmrAkSaH sUtaputravadhepsayA . sa kArmuke mahAvegaM bhAratasAdhanamuktamam . girINAmapi bhettAraM sAyakaM samayojayat .
vikRtyabalavaccApamAkarNAdatimArutiH . taM mumoca maheSvAsaH kruddhaH karNajighAMsayA .
sa visRSTo balavatA bANo vanAzanisvanaH . adArayad raNe karNaM vajravego yathAcalam .
sa bhImasenAbhihata : sUtaputraH kurUdvaha . niSasAda rathopasthe visaMjJaH pRtanApatiH .
tato madrAdhipo dRSTvA visaMjJaM sUtanandanam . apovAha rathenAjau karNamAhavazobhinam .
tataH parAjite karNe dhAtarASTrIM mahAcamUm . vyadrAvadayad bhImaseno yathendro dAnavAn purA .
saMjaya uvAca sarvathA virathaH karNaH punarbhImena nirjitaH . rathamanyaM samAsthAya punarvivyAdha pANDavam .
mahAgajAvivAsAdya viSANApraiH parasparam . zaraiH pUrNAyatotsRSTairanyonyamabhijaghnatuH .
atha karNaH zaravrAtairbhImasenaM samArpayat . nanAda ca mahAnAdaM punarvivyAdha corasi .
taM bhImo dazabhirbANaiH pratyavidhyadajihmagaiH . punarvivyAdha saptatyA zarANAM nataparvaNAm .
karNa tu navabhirbhImo bhittvA rAjan stanAntare . dhvajamekena vivyAdha sAyakena zitena ha .
sAyakAnAM tataH pArthasriSaSTyA pratyavidhyata . totrairiva mahAnAgaM kazabhiriva vAjinam .
so ' tividdho mahArAja pANDavena yazasvinA . sRkkiNI lelihan vIraH krodharaktAntalocanaH .
tataH zaraM mahArAja sarvakAyAvadAraNam . prAhiNod bhImasenAya balAyendra ivAzanim .
sa nirbhidya raNe pArtha sUtaputradhanuzcyutaH . agacchad dArayan bhUmiM citrapulaH zilImukhaH .
tato bhImo mahAbAhuH krodhasaMraktalocanaH . vajrakalpAM catuSkiSkuMguvIM rukmAGgadAM gadAm . prAhiNot sUtaputrAya SaDasrAmavicArayan . tayA jaghAnAdhiratheH sadazvAn sAdhuvAhinaH . gadayA bhArataH kruddho vajraNendra ivAsurAn . tato bhImo mahAbAhuH kSurAbhyAM bharatarSabha .
dhvajamAdhirathezchittvA sUtamabhyahanaccharaiH . hatAzvasUtamutsRjya sarathaM patitadhvajam .
visphArayan dhanuH karNastasthau bhArata durmanAH . tatrAdbhutamapazyAma rAdheyasya parAkrasam .
viratho rathinAM zreSTho vArayAmAsa yad ripum . virathaM taM narazreSThaM dRSTvA ' ' dhirathimAhave .
duryodhanastato rAjannabhyabhASata durmukham . eSa durmukha rAdheyo bhImena virathIkRtaH .
taM rathena narazreSTha sampAdaya mahAratham . tato duryodhanavacaH zrutvA bhArata durmukhaH .
tvaramANo ' bhyayAt karNa bhImaM cAvArayaccharaiH . durmukhaM prekSya saMgrAme sUtaputrapadAnugam .
vAyuputraH prahRSTo ' bhUt sRkkiNI parisaMlihan . tataH karNa mahArAja vArayitvA zilImukhaiH .
durmukhAya rathaM tUrNa preSayAmAsa pANDavaH . tasmin kSaNe mahArAja navabhinataparvabhiH .
sumukhairdurmukhaM bhImaH zarairninye yamakSayam . tatastamevAdhirathiH syandanaM durmukhe hate . AsthitaH prababhau rAjan dIpyamAna ivAMzumAn . zayAnaM bhinnamarmANaM durmukhaM zoNitokSitam . dRSTvA karNo ' zrupUrNAkSo muhUrta nAbhyavartata . taM gatAsumatikramya kRtvA karNaH pradakSiNam .
dIrghamuSNaM zvasana vIro na kiMcit pratyapadyata . tasmiMstu vivare rAjan nArAcAn gArdhavAsasaH . prAhiNot sUtaputrAya bhImasenazcaturdaza . te tasya kavacaM bhittvA svarNacitraM mahaujasaH .
hemapuGkhA mahArAja vyazobhanta dizo daza . apiban sUtaputrasya zoNitaM raktabhojanAH .
kruddhA iva manuSyendra bhujaGgAH kAlacoditAH . prasarpamANA medinyAM te vyarocanta mArgaNAH .
ardhapraviSTAH saMrabdhA bilAnIva mahoragAH . taM pratyavidhyad rAdheyo jAmbUnadavibhUSitaiH . caturdazabhiratyugrairnArAcairavicArayan . te bhImasenasya bhujaM savyaM nirbhidya patriNaH .
prAvizan medinI bhImAH kraucaM patrarathA iva . te vyarocanta nArAvAH pravizanto vasuMdharAm .
gacchatyastaM dinakare dIpyamAnA ivAMzavaH . sa nirbhinno raNe bhImo nArAcairmarmabhedibhiH .
susrAva rudhiraM bhUri parvataH salilaM yathA . sa bhImanibhirAyatta : sUtaputraM patatribhiH .
suvarNavervivyAdha sArathiM cAsya saptabhiH . sa vihvalo mahArAja karNo bhImazarAhataH .
prAdravajjavanairazvai raNaM hitvA mahAbhayAt . bhImasenastu visphAryaM cApaM hemapariSkRtam . Ahave ' tiratho ' tiSThajjvalanniva hutAzanaH .
vidura uvAca rAjan ni : saMzayaM zreyo vAcyastvamasi bAndhavaiH . na tvazuzrUSamANe vai vAkyaM sampratiSThiti .
priyaM hitaM ca tad vAkyamuktavAn kurusattamaH . bhISmaH zAMtanavo rAjan pratigRhaNasi tanna ca . tathA droNena bahudhA bhASitaM hitamuttamam . tacca rAdhAsutaH karNo manyate na hitaM tava .
cintayaMzca na pazyAmi rAjaMstava suhRttamam . AbhyAM puruSasiMhAbhyaM yo vA syAt prajJayAdhikaH .
imau hi vRddhau vayasA prajJayA ca zrutena ca . samau ca tvayi rAjendra tathA pANDusuteSu ca .
dharme cAnavarau rAjan satyatAyAM ca bhArata . rAmAd dAzarathezcaiva gayAccaiva na saMzayaH .
na coktavantAvazreya purastAdapi kiMcana . na cApyapakRtaM kiMcidanayorlakSyate tvayi . tAvabhau puruSavyAghrAvanAgasi nRpe tvayi . na mantrayetAM tvacchreyaH kathaM satyaparAkramau .
prajJAvantau narazreSThAvasmaà¥…illoke narAdhipa . tvannimittapato nemau kiMcijjiA vadiSyataH .
iti me naiSThikI buddhivartate kurunandana . na cArthahetordharmau vakSyataH pakSasaMzritam .
etaddhi paramaM zreyo manye ' haM tava bhArata . duryodhanaprabhRtayaH putrA rAjan yathA tava . tathaiva pANDaveyAste putrA rAjan na saMzayaH . teSu cedahitaM kiMcinmantrayeyuratadvidaH . mantriNaste na ca zreyaH prapazyanti vizeSataH . atha te hRdaye rAjan vizeSa : sveSu vartate . te . antarasthaM vitRNvAnAH zreyaH kuryurna te dhruvam .
etadarthamimau rAjan mahAtmAnau mahAdyutI . nocaturvivRtaM kiMcinna hyeSa tava nizcayaH .
yaccApyazakyatAM teSAmahatuH puruSarSabhau . tat tathA puruSavyAghra tava tad bhadramastu
kathaM hi pANDavaH zrImAn savyasAcI dhanaMjayaH . zakyo vijetuM saMgrAme rAjan maghavatApi hi .
bhImaseno mahAbAhurnAgAyutabalo mahAn . kathaM sma yudhi zakyeta vijetumamarairapi .
tathaiva kRtinau yuddhe yamau yamasutAviva . kathaM vijetuM zakyau tau raNe jIvitumicchatA .
yasmin dhRtiranukrozaH kSamA satyaM parAkramaH . nityAni pANDave jyeSThe sa jIyeta raNe katham .
yeSAM pakSadharo rAmo yeSAM mantrI janArdanaH . kiM na tairajitaM saMkhye yeSAM pakSe ca sAtyakiH .
drupadaH zvazuro yeSAM yeSAM zyAlAzca pArSatAH . dhRSTadyumnamukhA vIrA bhrAtaro drupadAtmajAH . so ' zakyatAM ca vijJAya teSAmagre ca bhAratA dAyAdyatAM ca dharmeNa samyak teSu samAcara .
idaM nirdiSTamayazaH purocanakRtaM mahat . teSAmanugraheNAdya rAjan prakSAlayAtmanaH .
teSAmanugrahazcAyaM sarveSAM caiva naH kule . jIvitaM ca paraM zreyaH kSatrasya ca vivardhanam .
dupado ' pi mahAn rAjA kRtavaisca naH purA . tasya saMgrahaNaM rAjan svapakSasya vivardhanam .
balavantazca dAzArhA bahavazca vizAmpate . yataH kRSNastataH sarve yataH kRSNastato jayaH .
yacca sAmnaiva zakyeta kAryaM sAdhayituM nRpa . ko daivazaptastat kAryaM vigraheNa samAcaret .
zrutvA ca jIvataH pArthAn paurajAnapadA janAH . balavad darzane hRSTAsteSAM rAjan priyaM kuru .
duryodhanazca karNazca zakunizcApi saubalaH . adharmayuktA duSprajJA bAlA maiSAM vacaH kRthAH .
uktametat purA rAjan mayA guNavatastava . duryodhanAparAdhena prajeyaM vai vinakSyati .
vaizampAyana uvAca tena vikramamANena UruvegasamIritam . vanaM savRkSaviTapaM vyAghUrNitamivAbhavat .
jaGghAvAto vavau cAsya zucizukrAgame yathA . AvarjitalatAvRkSaM mArga cakre mahAbalaH .
sa mRdgan puSpitAMzcaiva phalitAMzca vanaspatIn . avarujya yayau gulmAn pathastasya samIpajAn .
sa roSita iva kruddho vane bhaJjan mahAdumAn . triprastrutamadaH zuSmI SaSTivarSI mataGgarAT .
gacchatastasya vegena tArkSyamArutaraMhasaH . bhImasya pANDuputrANAM mUcheva samajAyata . .
asakRccApi saMtIrya dUrapAraM bhujaplavaiH . pathi pracchannamAsedurdhArtarASTrabhayAt tadA .
kRcchreNa mAtaraM caiva sukumArI yazasvinIm . avahat sa tu pRSThena rodhassu viSameSu ca .
agamacca vanoddezamalpamUlaphalodakam . krUrapakSimRgaM ghoraM sAyAhne bharatarSabha . .
ghorA samabhavat saMdhyA dAruNA mRgapakSiNaH . aprakAzA dizaH sarvA vAtairAsannanArtavaiH .
zIrNaparNaphalai rAjan bahugulmakSupairdumaiH . bhagnAvabhagnabhUyiSThernAnAdrumasamAkulaiH .
te zrameNa ca kauravyAstRSNayA ca prapIDitAH . nAzaknuvaMstadA gantuM nidrayA ca pravRddhayA .
nyavizanta hi te sarve nirAsvAde mahAvane . tatastRSApariklAntA kuntI putrAnathAbravIt .
mAtA satI pANDavAnAM paJcAnAM madhyataH sthitA . tRSNayA hi parItAsmi putrAn bhRzamathAbravIt .
tacchrutvA bhImasenasya mAtRsnehAt prajalpitam . kAruNyena manastaptaM gamanAyopacakrame .
tato bhImo vanaM ghoraM pravizya vijanaM mahat . nyagrodhaM vipulacchAyaM ramaNIyaM dadarza ha .
tatra nikSipya tAn sarvAnuvAca bharatarSabhaH . pAnIyaM mRgayAmIha vizramadhvamiti prabho .
ete ruvanti madhuraM sArasA jalacAriNaH . dhruvamatra jalasthAnaM mahacceti matirmama .
anujJAtaH sa gaccheti bhrAtrA jyeSThena bhArata . jagAma tatra yatra sma sArasA jalacAriNaH .
sa tatra pItvA pAnIyaM snAtvA ca bharatarSabha . teSAmarthe ca jagrAha bhrAtRNAM bhrAtRvatsalaH . uttarIyeNa pAnIyamAnayAmAsa bhArata .
gavyUtimAtrAdAgatya tvarito mAtaraM prati . zokaduHkhaparItAtmA niHzazvAsorago yathA .
sa suptAM mAtaraM dRSTvA bhrAtUMzca vasudhAtale . bhRzaM zokaparItAtmA vilalApa vRkodaraH .
ataH kaSTataraM kiM nu draSTavyaM hi bhaviSyati . yat pazyAmi mahIsuptAn bhrAtRnadya sumandabhAk .
zayaneSu parAryeSu ye purA vAraNAvate . nAdhijagmustadA nidrAM te ' dya suptA mahItale .
svasAraM vasudevasya zatrusaGghAvamardinaH . kuntirAjasutAM kuntIM sarvalakSaNapUjitAm . snuSAM vicitravIryasya bhAryAM pANDormahAtmanaH . tathaiva cAsmajjananIM puNDarIkodaraprabhAm . sukumAratarAmenAM mahArhazayanocitAm . zayAnAM pazyatAyeha pRthivyAmatathocitAm .
dharmAdindrAcca vAtAcca suSuve yA sutAnimAn . seyaM bhUmau parizrAntA zete prAsAdazAyinI .
kiM nu duHkhataraM zakyaM mayA draSTumataH param . yo ' hamadya naravyAghrAn suptAn pazyAmi bhUtale .
triSu lokeSu yo rAjyaM dharmanityo ' rhate nRpaH . so ' yaM bhUmau parizrAntaH zete prAkRtavat katham .
ayaM nIlAmbudazyAmo nareSvapratimo ' rjunaH . zete prAkRtavad bhUmau duHkhataraM nu kim .
azvinAviva devAnAM yAvimau rUpasampadA . tau prAkRtavadadyamau prasuptau dharaNItale .
jJAtayo yasya naiva syurviSamAH kulapAMsanAH . sa jIveta sukhaM loke grAmadruma ivaikajaH .
eko vRkSo hi yo grAme bhavet parNaphalAnvitaH . caityo bhavati nirmAtirarcanIyaH supUjitaH .
yeSAM ca bahavaH zUrA jJAtayo dharmamAzritAH . te jIvanti sukhaM loke bhavanti ca nirAmayAH .
balavantaH samRddhArthA mitrabAndhavanandanAH . jIvantyanyonyAzritya dumAH kAnanajA iva .
vayaM tu dhRtarASTreNa saputreNa durAtmanA . vivAsitA na dagdhAzca kathaMcid daivasaMzrayAt .
tasmAnmuktaH vayaM dAhAdimaM vRkSamupAzritAH . kAM dizaM pratipatsyAmaH prAptAH klezamanuttamam .
