nAtidUrega nagaraM vanAdasmAddhi lakSaye . jAgartavye svapantIme hanta jAgarmyahaM svayam . pAsyantIme jalaM pazcAt pratibuddhA jitaklamAH . iti bhImo vyavasyaiva jajAgAra svayaM tadA .
