tato ruddhe zakRnmUtre sainyamAnAha duHkhitam . . tathAgatamabhiprekSya paryapRcchat sa pArthivaH . taponityasya vRddhasya roSaNasya vizeSataH . kenApakRtamadyeha bhArgavasya mahAtmanaH .
jJAtaM vA yadi vAjJAtaM tad drutaM brUta mA ciram . tamUcuH sainikAH sarve na vidmo ' pakRtaM vayam .
