ajJAnAd bAlayA yat te kRtaM tat kSantumarhasi . tato ' bravInmahIpAlaM cyavano bhArgavastadA . apamAnAdahaM viddho hyanayA darpapUrNayA . rUpaudAryasamAyuktAM lobhamohabalAtkRtAm . tAmeva pratigRhyAhaM rAjan duhitaraM tava . kSasyAmIti mahIpAla satyametad bravImi te .
lomaza uvAca RServacanamAjJAya zaryAtiravicArayan . dadau duhitaraM tasmai cyavanAya mahAtmane .
