saMjaya uvAca te sene zibiraM gatvA nyavizetAM vizAmpate . yathAbhAgaM yathAnyAyaM yathAgulmaM ca sarvazaH .
kRtvAvahAraM sainyAnAM droNaH paramadurmanAH . duryodhanamabhiprekSya savrIDamidamabravIt .
uktametanmayA pUrvaM na tiSThati dhanaMjaye . zakyo grahItuM saMgrAme devairapi yudhiSThiraH .
iti tad vaH prayatatAM kRtaM pArthena saMyuge . mA vizaGkIrvaco mahyamajeyau kRSNapANDavau .
apanIte tu yogena kenacicchvetavAhane . tata eSyati me rAjan vazameSa yudhiSThiraH .
kazcidAhUya taM saMkhye dezamanyaM prakarSatu . tamajitvA na kaunteyo nivarteta kathaMcana .
etasminnantare zUnye dharmarAjamahaM nupa . grahISyAmi camUM bhittvA dhRSTadyumnasya pazyataH .
arjunena vihInastu yadi notsRjate raNam . mAmupAyAntamAlokya gRhItaM viddhi pANDavam .
evaM te ' haM mahArAja dharmaputraM yudhiSThiram . samAneSyAmi sagaNaM vazamadya na saMzayaH . yadi tiSThati saMgrAme muhUrtamapi pANDavaH . athApayAti saMgrAmAd vijayAt tad viziSyate .
saMjaya uvAca droNasya tad vacaH zrutvA trigartAdhipatistadA . bhrAtRbhiH sahito rAjannidaM vacanamabravIt .
vayaM vinikRtA rAjan tadA gANDIvadhanvanA . anAga : svapi cAgastat kRtamasmAsu tena vai .
te vayaM smaramANAstAn vinikArAn pRthagvidhAn . krodhAgninA dahyamAnA na zemahi sadA nizi .
sa no diSTyAstrasamapannazcakSurviSayamAgataH . kartAraH sma vayaM karma yaccikIrSAma hRdgatam .
