saMjaya uvAca anujJAtastato rAjJA pariSvaktazca phAlgunaH . premNA dRSTazca bahudhA hyAziSazcAsya yojitAH .
vihAyainaM tataH pArthastrigartAn pratyayAd balI . kSudhitaH kSudvighAtArthaM siMho mRgagaNAniva .
tato doryodhanaM sainyaM mudA paramayA yutam . Rte ' rjunaM bhRzaM kruddha dharmarAjasya nigrahe .
tato ' nyonyena te sainye samAjagmaturojasA . gaGgAsarayvau vegena prAvRSIvolvaNodake .
vAyu ruvAca kiMcid dharmaM pravakSyAmi mAnuSANAM sukhAvaham . sarahasyAzca ye doSAstAzRNudhvaM samAhitAH .
agnikAryaM ca kartavyaM paramAnnena bhojanam . dIpakazcApi kartavyaH pitRRNAM satilodakaH . etena vidhinA martyaH zraddadhAnaH samAhitaH . caturo vArSikAn mAsAn yo dadAti tilodakam . bhojanaM ca yathAzaktyA brAhmaNe vedapArage . pazubadhazatasyeha phalaM prApnoti puSkalam .
idaM caivAparaM guhyamaprazastaM nibodhata . agnestu vRSalo netA havirmUDhAzca yoSitaH . manyate dharma eveti sa cAdharmeNa lipyate .
agnayastasya kupyanti zUdrayoni sa gacchati . pitarazca na tuSyanti saha devairvizeSataH .
prAyazcittaM tu yat tatra bruvatastannibodha me . yat kRtvA tu naraH samyak sukhI bhavati vijvaraH .
gavAM mUtrapurISeNa payasA ca ghRtena ca . agnikAryaM tryahaM kuryAtrirAhAraH samAhitaH .
tataH saMvatsare pUrNe pratigahNanti devatAH . hRSyanti pitarazcAsya zrAddhakAla upasthite .
eSa hyadharmo dharmazca sarahasyaH prakIrtitaH . mAnAM svargakAmAnAM pretya svargasukhAvahaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tato yudhiSThiro rAjA zizupAlamupAdravat . uvAca cainaM madhuraM sAntvapUrvamidaM vacaH .
nedaM yuktaM mahIpAla yAdRzaM vai tvamuktavAn . adharmazca paro rAjan pAruSyaM ca nirarthakam .
na hi dharmaM paraM jAtu nAvabudhyeta pArthivaH . bhISmaH zAntanavastvenaM mAvamaMsthAstvamanyathA .
pazya caitAn mahIpAlAMstvatto vRddhatarAn bahUn . mRSyante cArhaNAM kRSNe tadvat tvaM kSantumarhasi .
veda tattvena kRSNaM hi bhISmazcedipate bhRzam . na hyenaM tvaM tathA vettha yathainaM veda kauravaH .
bhISma uvAca nAsmai deyo hyanunayo nAyamarhati sAntvanam . lokavRddhatame kRSNe yo ' rhaNAM nAbhimanyate .
kSatriyaH kSatriyaM jitvA raNe raNakRtAM varaH . yo muJcati vaze kRtvA gururbhavati tasya saH .
asyAM hi samitau rAjJAmekamapyajitaM yudhi . na pazyAmi mahIpAlaM sAtvatIputratejasA .
na hi kevalamasmAkamayamarcyatamo ' cyutaH . trayANAmapi lokAnAmarcanIyo mahAbhujaH .
kRSNena hi jitA yuddhe bahavaH kSatriyarSabhAH . jagat sarvaM ca vArSNeya nikhilena pratiSThitam .
tasmAt satsvapi vRddheSu kRSNamarcAma netarAn . evaM vaktuM na cArhastvaM mA te bhUd buddhirIdRzI .
jJAnavRddhA mayA rAjan bahavaH paryupAsitAH . teSAM kathayatAM zaurerahaM guNavato guNAn . samAgatAnAmazrauSaM bahUn bahumatAn satAm . karmANyapi ca yAnyasya janmaprabhRti dhImataH . bahuzaH kathyamAnAni narairbhUyaH zrutAni me . na kevalaM vayaM kAmAccedirAja janArdanam .
na sambandhaM puraskRtya kRtArthaM vA kathaMcana . arcAmahe ' rcitaM sadbhirbhuvi bhUtasukhAvaham .
yazaH zauryaM jayaM cAsya vijJAyArcA prayuJjamahe . na ca kazcidihAsmAbhiH subAlo ' pyaparIkSitaH .
guNavRddhAnatikramya harirarcyatamo mataH . jJAnavRddho dvijAtInAM kSatriyANAM balAdhikaH .
vaizyAnAM dhAnyadhanavAJchUdrANAmeva janmataH . pUjyatAyAM ca govinde hetU dvAvapi saMsthitau .
vedavedAGgavijJAnaM balaM cAbhyadhikaM tathA . nRNAM loke hi ko ' nyo ' sti viziSTaH kezavAdRte .
dAnaM dAkSyaM zrutaM zauryaM hrIH kIrtirbuddhiruttamA . sannatiH zrIkRtistuSTiH puSTizca niyatAcyute .
tamimaM guNasampannamAryaM ca pitaraM gurum . arghyamarcitamarcAha~ sarve saMkSantumarhatha .
Rtvig gurustathA ' ' cAryaH snAtako nRpatiH priyaH . sarvametaddhRSIkezastasmAdabhyarcito ' cyutaH .
kRSNa eva hi lokAnAmutpattirapi cApyayaH . kRSNasya hi kRte vizvamidaM bhUtaM carAcaram .
eSa prakRtiravyaktA kartA caiva sanAtanaH . parazca sarvabhUtebhyastasmAt pUjyatamo ' cyutaH .
buddhirmano mahad vAyustejo ' mbhaH khaM mahI ca yA . caturvidhaM ca yad bhUtaM sarvaM kRSNe pratiSThitam .
AdityazcandramAzcaiva nakSatrANi grahAzca ye . dizazca vidizazcaiva sarvaM kRSNe pratiSThitam .
agnihotramukhA vedA gAyatrI chandasAM mukham . rAjA mukhaM manuSyANAM nadInAM sAgaro mukham . nakSatrANAM mukhaM candra AdityastejasAM mukham . parvatAnAM mukhaM merurgaruDaH patatAM mukham .
UrdhvaM tiryagadhazcaiva yAvatI jagato gatiH . sadevakeSu lokeSu bhagavAn kezavo mukham .
ayaM tu puruSo bAlaH zizupAlo na budhyate . sarvatra sarvadA kRSNaM tasmAdevaM prabhASate .
yo hi dharmaM vicinuyAdutkRSTaM matiman naraH . sa vai pazyed yathA dharmaM na tathA cedirADayam .
savRddhabAleSvathavA pArthiveSu mahAtmasu . ko nAIM manyate kRSNaM ko vApyenaM na pUjayet .
athainAM duSkRtAM pUjAM zizupAlo vyavasyati . duSkRtAyAM yathAnyAyaM tathAyaM kartumarhati .
zalya uvAca atha tAmabravId dRSTvA nahuSo devarAT tadA . trayANAmapi lokAnAmahamindraH zucismite .
bhajasva mAM varArohe patitve varavarNini . evamuktA tu sA devI nahuSeNa pativratA .
prAvepata bhayodvignA pravAte kadalI yathA . praNamya sA hi brahmANaM zirasA tu kRtAJjaliH .
devarAjamathovAca nahuSaM ghoradarzanam . kAlamicchAmyahaM labdhaM tvattaH kaMcit surezvara .
na hi vijJAyate zakraH kiMvA prAptaH kva vA gataH . tattvametat tu vijJAya yadi na jJAyate prabho .
tato ' haM tvAmupasthAsye satyametad bravImi te . evamuktaH sa indrANyA nahuSaH prItimAnabhUt .
nahuSa uvAca evaM bhavatu suzroNi yathA mAmiha bhASase . jJAtvA jAgamanaM kAryaM satyametadanusmareH .
nahuSeNa visRSTA ca nizcakrAma tataH zubhA . bRhaspatiniketaM ca sA jagAma yazasvinI .
tasyAH saMzrutyaM ca vaco devAzcAgnipurogamAH . cintayAmAsurekAgrAH zanArthaM rAjasattama .
