tat te vRkodaramayaM bhayaM vyetu mahAhave . vyapaneSyAmyahaM hyenaM mA rAjan vimanA bhava .
tasmin mayA hate kSipramarjunaM bahavo rathAH . tulyarUpA viziSTAzca kSepsyanti bharatarSama .
bhISmo droNaH kRpo drauNiH karNo bhUrizravAstathA . prAgjyotiSAdhipaH zalyaH sindhurAjo jayadrathaH .
ekaika eSAM zaktastu hantuM bhArata pANDavAn . sametAstu kSaNainaitAn neSyanti yamasAdanam . samagrA pArthivo senA pArthamekaM dhanaMjayam .
kasmAdazaktA nirjetumiti heturna vidyate . zaravAtaistu bhISmeNa zatazo nicito ' vazaH .
droNadrauNikRpaizcaiva gantA pArtho yamakSayam . pitAmaho ' pi gAGgeyaH zAntanoradhi bhArata .
brahmarSisadRzo jajJe devairapi suduHsahaH . na hantA vidyate cApi rAjan bhISmasya kazcana .
pitrA hyuktaH prasannena nAkAmastvaM mariSyasi . brahmarSeca bharadvAjAd droNo droNyAmajAyata .
droNAjjajJe mahArAja drauNizca paramAstravit . kRpazcAcAryamukhyo ' yaM maharSe ! tamAdapi .
zarastambodbhavaH zrImAnavadhya iti me matiH . ayonijAstrayo hote pitA mAtA ca mAtulaH .
azvatthAmno mahArAja sa ca zUraH sthito mama . sarva ete mahArAja devakalpA mahArathAH .
zakrasyApi vyathAM kuryuH saMyuge bharatarSabha . naiteSAmarjunaH zakta ekaikaM prati vIkSitum .
sahitAstu naravyAghrA haniSyanti dhanaMjayam . bhISmadroNakRpANAM ca tulyaH karNo mato mama .
anujJAtazca rAmeNa matsamo ' sIti bhArata . kuNDale rucire cAstAM karNasya sahaje zubhe .
te zacyarthaM mahendreNa yAcitaH sa paraMtapaH . amoghayA mahArAja zaktyA paramabhImayA .
tasya zaktyopagUDhasya kasmAjjIved dhanaMjayaH . vijayo me dhruvaM rAjan phalaM pANAvivAhitam .
abhivyaktaH pareSAM ca kRtsno bhuvi parAjayaH . ahnA Tekena bhISmo ' yaM prayutaM hanti bhArata .
tatsamAzca maheSvAsA droNadrauNikRpA api . saMzaptakAnAM vRndAni kSatriyANAM paraMtapa . arjunaM vayamasmAn vA nihanyAt kapiketanaH . taM cAlamiti manyante savyasAcivadhe dhRtAH .
pArthivAH sa bhavAMstebhyo hakasmAd vyathate katham . bhImasene ca nihate ko ' nyo yudhyeta bhArata .
pareSAM tanmamAcakSva yadi vettha paraMtapa . paJca te bhrAtaraH sarve dhRSTadyumno ' tha sAtyakiH . pareSAM sapta ye rAjan yodhAH sAraM balaM matam . asmAkaM tu viziSTA ye bhISmadroNakRpAdayaH .
drauNirvikartanaH karNaH somadatto ' tha bAhnikaH . prAgjyotiSAdhipaH zalya Avantyau ca jayadrathaH . duHzAsano durmukhazca duHsahazca vizAmpate . zrutAyuzcitrasenazca purumitro viviMzatiH . zalo bhUrizravAzcaiva vikarNazca tavAtmajaH . akSauhiNyo hi me rAjan dazaikA ca samAhRtAH . nyUnAH pareSAM saptaiva kasmAnme syAt parAjayaH .
balaM triguNato hInaM yodhyaM prAha bRhaspatiH . parebhyastriguNA ceyaM mama rAjannanIkinI .
guNahInaM pareSAM ca bahu pazyAmi bhArata . guNodayaM bahuguNamAtmanazca vizAmpate .
etat sarvaM samAjJAya balAgyaM mama bhArata . nyUnatAM pANDavAnAM ca na mohaM gantumarhasi .
ityuktvA saMjayaM bhUyaH paryapRcchata bhArata . vivitsuH prAptakAlAni jJAtvA parapuraMjayaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tato dizaH sampravihRtya pArthA mRgAn varAhAn mahiSAMzca hatvA . dhanurdharAH zreSThatamAH pRthivyAM pRthak carantaH sahitA babhUvuH .
tato mRgajyAlagaNAnukIrNa mahAvanaM tad vihagopaghuSTam . bhrAtUMzca tAnabhyavadad yudhiSThiraH zrutvA giro vyAharatAM mRgANAm .
AdityadIptAM dizamabhyupetya mRgA dvijAH krUramime vadanti . AyAsamucaM prativedayanto mahAvanaM zatrubhirbAdhyamAnam .
mano hi me dUyati dahyate ca . ruddhUyate prANapatiH zarIre .
saraH suparNena hRtoragaM yathA rASTraM yathArAjakamAttalakSmi . evaMvidhaM me pratibhAti kAmyakaM zauNDairyathA pItarasazca kumbhaH .
mahAjavairvAjibhiruhyamAnAH . stadA ' ' zramAyAbhimukhA babhUvuH .
teSAM tu gomAyuranalpaghoSo nivartatAM vAmamupetya pArzvam . pravyAharat tat pravimRzya rAjA provAca bhImaM ca dhanaMjayaM ca .
yathA vadatyeSa vihInayoniH zAlAvRko vAmamupetya pArzvam . suvyaktamasmAnavamanya pApaiH kRto ' bhimardaH kurubhiH prasahya .
ityeva te tad vanamAvizanto mahatyaraNye mRgayAM caritvA . bAlAmapazyanta tadA rudantI dhAtreyikAM preSyavadhU priyAyAH .
tAmindrasenastvarito ' bhisRtya rathAdavaplutya tato ' bhyadhAvat . provAca cainAM vacanaM narendra dhAtreyikAmantitarastadAnIm .
kiM rodiSi tvaM patitA dharaNyAM kiM te mukhaM zuSyati dInavarNam . kaccinna pApaiH sunRzaMsakRdbhiH pramAthitA draupadI rAjaputrI .
acintyarUpA suvizAlanetrA zarIratulyA kurupuGgavAnAm . yadyeva devI pRthivIM praviSTA divaM ppapannApyazcavA samudram . tasyA gamiSyanti pade hi pArthA yathA hi saMtapyati dharmaputraH .
ko hIdRzAnAmarimardanAnAM klezakSamAnAmaparAjitAnAm . danuttamaM ratnamiva pramUDhaH .
na budhyate nAthavataumihAdya bahizcaraM hRdayaM pANDavAnAm . kasyAdya kAyaM pratibhidya ghorA mahIM pravekSyanti zitAH zarAgryAH .
mA tvaM zucastAM prati bhIru viddhi yathAdya kRSNA punareSyatIti . nihatya sarvAn dviSataH samagrAn pArthAH sameSyantyathA yAjJasenyA .
athAbravIccAru mukhaM pramRjya dhAtreyikA sArathimindrasenam . jayadrathenApahRtA pramathya paJcendrakalpAn paribhUya kRSNA . tiSThanti vAni navAnyamUni vRkSAzca na mlAnti tathaiva bhagnAH .
AvartayadhvaM hyanuyAta zIghraM na dUrayAtaiva hi rAjaputrI . saMnahyadhvaM sarva evendrakalpA mahAnti cArUNi ca daMzanAni .
gRNIta cApAni mahAdhanAni zarAMzca zIghraM padavIM caradhvam . purA hi nirbhartsanadaNDamohitA pramohacittA vadanena zuSyatA . dadAti kasmaicidanarhate tanuM varAjyapUrNAmiva bhasmani srucam . purA tuSAgnAviva hUyate haviH purA zmazAne sragivApaviddhyate . purA ca somo ' dhvarago ' valiAte zunA yathA viprajane pramohite . mahatyaraNye mRgayAM caritvA purA zRgAlo nalinI vigAhate .
mA vaH priyAyAH sunasaM sulocanaM candraprabhAcchaM vadanaM prasannam . spRzyAcchubhaM kazcidakRtyakArI zvA vai puroDAzamivAdhvarastham . etAni vAnyanuyAta zInaM mA vaH kAlaH kSipramihAtyagAd vai .
yudhiSThira uvAca bhadre pratikrAma niyaccha vAcaM mAsmatsakAze paruSANyavocaH . rAjAno vA yadi vA rAjaputrA balena mattA vaJcanAM prApnuvanti .
vaizampAyana uvAca etAvaduktvA prayayurhi zIghraM tAnyeca vAnyanuvartamAnAH . muhurmahAlavaducchvasanto jyAM vikSipantazca mahAdhanuryaH .
mudbhUtaM vai vAjikhurapraNunnam . padAtInAM madhyagataM ca dhaumyaM vikrozantaM bhImamabhidraveti .
te sAntvya dhaumyaM paridInasattvAH sukhaM bhavAnetviti rAjaputrAH . zyenA yathaivAmiSasamprayuktA javena tat sainyamathAbhyadhAvan . .
teSAM mahendropamavikramANAM saMrabdhAnAM dharSaNAd yAjJasenyAH . krodhaH prajajvAla jayadrathaM ca dRSTvA priyAM tasya rathe sthitAM ca .
pracukuzuzcApyatha sindhurAja vRkodarazcaiva dhanaMjayazca . stato dizaH sammumuhuH pareSAm .
dhRtarASTra uvAca bhagavan nAhamapyetad rocaye dyUtasambhavam . manye tadvidhinA ' ' kRSya kArito ' smIti vai mune .
naitad rocayate bhISmo na droNo viduro na ca . gAndhArI necchati dyUtaM tatra mohAt pravartimam .
parityaktuM na zaknomi duryodhanamacetanam . putrasnehena bhagavaJjAnannapi priyavrata .
vyAsa uvAca vaicitravIrya nRpate satyamAha yathA bhavAn . dRDhaM vidmaH paraM putraM paraM putrAnna vidyate .
indro ' pyazrunipAtena surabhyA pratibodhitaH . anyaiH samRddhairapyarthairna sutAnmanyate param .
atra te kIrtayiSyAmi mahadAkhyAnamuttamam . surabhyAzcaiva saMvAdamindrasya ca vizAmpate . .
triviSTapagatA rAjan surabhI prArudat kila . gavAM mAtA purA tAta tAmindro ' nvakRpAyata .
indra uvAca kimidaM rodiSi zubhe kaccit kSemaM divaukasAm . mAnuSeSvatha vA goSu naitadalpaM bhaviSyati .
surabhiruvAca vinipAto na vaH kazcid dRzyate tridazAdhipa . ahaM tu putraM zocAmi tena rodimi kauzika .
pazyainaM karSakaM kSudraM durbalaM mama putrakam . pratodenAbhinighnantaM lAgalena ca pIDitam . niSIdamAnaM sotkaNThaM vadhyamAnaM surAdhipa . kRpAviSTAsmi devendra manazcodvijate mama . ekastatra balopetodhuramudvahate ' dhikAm . aparo ' pyabalaprANaH kRzodhamanisaMtataH . kRcchrAdudvahate bhAraM taM vai zocAmi vAsava . vadhyamAnaH pratodena tudyamAnaH punaH punaH . naiva zaknoti taM bhAramudvoDhuM pazya vAsava .
tato ' haM tasya zokArtA viraumi bhRzaduHkhitA . azrUNyAvartayantI ca netrAbhyAM karuNAyatI .
zakra uvAca tava putrasahasreSu pIDyamAneSu zobhane . kiM kRpAyitavatyatra putra ekatra hanyati .
surabhiruvAca yadi putrasahasrANi sarvatra samataiva me . dInasya tu sataH zakra putrasyAbhyadhikA kRpA .
vyAsa uvAca tadindraH surabhIvAkyaM nizamya bhRzavismita ; . jIvitenApi kauravya mene ' bhyadhikamAtjam .
pravavarSa ca tatraiva sahasA toyamulbaNam . karSakasyAcaran vighnaM bhagavAn pAkazAsanaH .
tad yathA surabhiH prAha samavetAstu te tathA . suteSu rAjan sarveSu hIneSvabhyadhikA kRpA .
yAdRzo me sutaH pANDustAdRzo me ' si putrakA vidurazca mahAprAjJaH snehAdetad bravImyaham .
cirAya tava putrANAM zatamekazca bhArata . pANDoH paJcaiva lakSyante te ' pi mandAH suduHkhitAH .
kathaM jIveyuratyantaM kathaM vardhayurityapi . iti dIneSu pArtheSu mano me paritapyate .
yadi pArthiva kauravyAJjIvamAnAnihecchasi . duryodhanastava sutaH zamaM gacchatu pANDavaiH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tataH pUrvApare sainye samIkSya bhagavAnRSiH . sarvavedavidAM zreSTho vyAsaH satyavatIsutaH . bhaviSyati raNe ghora bharatAnAM pitAmahaH . pratyakSadarzI bhagavAn bhUtabhavyabhaviSyavit . vaicitravIryaM rAjAnaM sa rahasyaM bravIdidam . zocantamArtaM dhyAyantaM putrANAmanayaM tadA .
vyAsa uvAca rAjan parItakAlAste putrAzcAnye ca pArthivAH . te hiMsantIva saMgrAme samAsAdyetaretaram .
teSu kAlaparIteSu vinazyatsveva bhArata . kAlaparyAyamAjJAya mA sma zoke manaH kRthAH .
yadi cecchasi saMgrAme draSTumetAn vizAmpate . cakSurdadAni te putra yuddhaM tatra nizAmaya .
dhRtarASTra uvAca na rocaye jJAtivadhaM draSTuM brahmarSisattama . yuddhametat tvazeSeNa zRNuyAM tava tejasA .
vaizampAyana uvAca etasmin necchati draSTuM saMgrAmaM zrotumicchati . varANAmIzvaro vyAsaH saMjayAya varaM dadau .
eSa te saMjayo rAjan yuddhametad vadiSyati . etasya sarvasaMgrAme na parokSaM bhaviSyati .
cakSuSA saMjayo rAjan divyenaiva samanvitaH . kathayiSyati te yuddhaM sarvajJazca bhaviSyati .
prakAzaM vAprakAzaM vA divA vA yadi vA nizi . manasA cintitamapi sarvaM vetsyati saMjayaH .
nainaM zastrANi chetsyanti nainaM bAdhiSyate zramaH . gAvalgaNirayaM jIvan yuddhAdasmAd vimokSyate .
ahaM tu kIrtipeteSAM kurUNAM bharatarSabha . pANDavAnAM ca sarveSAM prathayiSyAmi mA zucaH .
diSTametannaravyAghra nAbhizocitumarhasi . na caiva zakyaM saMyantuM yato dharmastato jayaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktvA sa bhagavAn kurUNAM prapitAmahaH . punareva mahAbhAgo dhRtarASTramuvAca ha .
iha yuddhe mahArAja bhaviSyati mahAn kSayaH . tatheha ca nimittAni bhayadAnyupalakSaye .
zyenAgRdhrAzca kAkAzca kaGkAzca sahitA bakaiH . sampatanti nagAgreSu samavAyAMzca kurvate .
abhyagraM ca prapazyanti yuddhamAnandino dvijAH . kravyAdA bhakSayiSyanti mAMsAni gajavAjinAm .
nirdayaM cAbhivAzanto bhairavA bhayavedinaH . kaGkAH prayAnti madhyena dakSiNAmabhito dizam .
ubhe pUrvApare saMdhye nityaM pazyAmi bhArata . udayAstamane sUrya kabandhaiH parivAritam .
zvetalohitaparyantAH kRSNagrIvA : savidyutaH . vivarNAH parighAH saMdhau bhAnumantamavArayan . .
jvalitArkendunakSatraM nirvizeSadinakSayam . ahorAtraM mayA dRSTaM tad bhayAya bhaviSyati .
alakSyaH prabhayAhInaH paurNamAsI ca kArtikIm . candro ' bhUdagnivarNazca padmavarNanabhastale .
svapsyanti nihatA vIrA bhUmimAvRtya pArthivAH . rAjAno rAjaputrAzca zUrAH parighabAhavaH .
antarikSe varAhasya vRSadaMzasya cobhayoH . praNAdaM yuddhyato rAtro raudraM nityaM pralakSaye .
devatApratimAzcaiva kampanti ca hasanti ca . vamanti rudhiraM cAsyaiH khidyanti prapatanti ca .
anAhatA dundubhayaH praNadanti vizAmpate . ayuktAzca pravartante kSatriyANAM mahArathAH .
kokilAH zatapatrAzca cASA bhAsAH zukAstathA . sArasAzca mayUrAzca vAco muJcanti dAruNAH .
gRhItazastrAH krozanti carmiNo vAjipRSThagAH . aruNodaye pradRzyante zatazaH zalabhavrajAH .
ubhe saMdhye prakAzante dizAM dAhasamanvite . parjanyaH pAMsuvarSI ca mAMsavarSI ca bhArata .
yA caiSA vizrutA rAjaMstrailokye sAdhusammatA . arundhatI tayApyeSa vasiSThaH pRSThataH kRtaH .
rohiNI pIDayanneSa sthito rAjazanaizcaraH . vyAvRttaM lakSma somasya bhaviSyati mahad bhayam .
anabhre mahAghoraH stanitaH zrUyate svanaH . vAhanAnAM ca rudatAM nipatantyazrubindavaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca dhanyA dhanyA iti janAH sarve ' smAn pravadantyuta . na duHkhitataraH kazcit pumAnasmAbhirasti ha .
lokasambhAvitairduHkhaM yat prAptaM kurusattama . prApya jAti manuSyeSu devairapi pitAmaha . kadA vayaM kariSyAmaH saMnyAsaM duHkhasaMjJakam . duHkhametaccharIrANAM dhAraNaM kurusattama .
vimuktAH saptadazabhirhetubhUtaizca paJcabhiH . indriyArthairguNaizcaiva aSTAbhizca pitAmaha . na gacchanti punarbhAvaM munayaH saMzitavratAH . kadA vayaM gamiSyAmo rAjyaM hitvA paraMtapa .
bhISma uvAca nAstyanantaM mahArAja sarvaM saMkhyAnagocaraH . punarbhAvo ' pi vikhyAto nAsti kiMcidihAcalam .
na cApi manyase rAjanneSa doSaH prasaGgataH . udyogAdeva dharmajJA kAlenaiva gamiSyatha . .
nareze ' yaM satataM dehI nRpate puNyapApayoH . tata eva samutthena tamasA rudhyate ' pi ca .
yathAJjamanayo vAyuH punarmAnaHzilaM rajaH . anupravizya tadvarNo dRzyate raJjayan dizaH . tathA karmaphalairdehI raJjitastamasA ' ' vRtaH . vivarNo varNamAzritya deheSu parivartate .
jJAnena hi yadA janturajJAnaprabhavaM tamaH . vyapohati tadA brahma prakAzati sanAtanam .
ayatnasAdhyaM munayo vadanti ye cApi muktAsta upAsitavyAH . tvayA ca lokena ca sAmareNa tasmAnnamasyAmi maharSisaGghAn .
asminnarthe purA gItaM zRNuSvaikamanA nRpa . yathA daityena vRtreNa bhraSTaizvaryeNa ceSTitam .
nirjitenAsahAyena hRtarAjyena bhArata . azocatA zatrumadhye buddhimAsthAya kevalAm .
bhraSTaizvaryaM purA vRtramuzanA vAkyamabravIt . kAcit parAjitasyAdya na vyathA te ' sti dAnava .15 . .
vRtra uvAca satyena tapasA caiva viditvAsaMzayaM hyaham . na zocAmi na hRSyAmi bhUtAnAmAgatiM gatim .
kAlasaMcoditA jIvA majjanti narake ' vazAH . parituSTAni sarvANi divyAnyAhurmanISiNaH .
kSapayitvA tu taM kAlaM gaNitaM kAlacoditAH . sAvazeSeNa kAlena sambhavanti punaH punaH .
tiryagyonisahasrANi gatvA narakameva ca . nirgacchantyavazA jIvAH kAmabandhanabandhanAH .
evaM saMsaramANAni jIvAnyahamadRSTavAn . yathA karma tatha lAbha iti zAstranidarzanam .
tiryag gacchanti narakaM mAnuSyaM daivameva ca . sukhaduHkhe priye dveSye caritvA pUrvameva ha . kRtAntavidhisaMyuktaH sarvo lokaH prapadyate . gataM gacchanti cAdhvAnaM sarvabhUtAni sarvadA . kAlasaMkhyAnasaMkhyAtaM sRSTisthitiparAyaNam . taM bhASamANaM bhagavAnuzanA pratyabhASata . dhImAn duSTapralApAMstvaM tAta kasmAt prabhASase .
vRtra uvAca pratyakSametad bhavatastathAnyeSAM manISiNAm . mayA yajjayalubdhena purA taptaM mahat tapaH .
gandhAnAdAya bhUtAnAM rasAMzca vividhAnapi . avardhaM trIn samAkramya lokAn vai svena tejasA .
jvAlAmAlAparikSipto vaihAyasacarastathA . ajeyaH sarvabhUtAnAmAsaM nityamapetabhIH .
aizvaryaM tapasA prAptaM bhraSTaM tacca svakarmabhiH . dhRtimAsthAya bhagavan na zocAmi tatastvaham .
yuyutsunA mahendreNa puMsA sArdhaM mahAtmanA . tato me bhagavAn dRSTo harirnArAyaNaH prabhuH . vaikuNThaH puruSo ' nantaH zuklo viSNuH sanAtanaH . muJjakezo harizmazruH sarvabhUtapitAmahaH .
nUnaM tu tasya tapasaH sAvazeSamihAsti vai . yadahaM praSTumicchAmi bhagavan karmaNaH phalam .
aizvaryaM vai mahad brahma varNe kasmin pratiSThitam . nivartate cApi punaH kathamaizvaryamuttamam .
kasmAd bhUtAni jIvanti pravartante tathA punaH . kiMvA phalaM paraM prApya jIvastiSThati zAzvataH .
