hate sudakSiNe rAjan vIre caiva zrutAyudhe . javenAbhyadravan pArthaM kupitAH sainikAstava .
abhISAhAH zUrasenAH zibayo ' tha vasAtayaH . abhyavarSestato rAjazaravarSerdhanaMjayam .
teSAM SaSTizatAnanyAn prAmathnAt pANDavaH zaraiH . te sma bhItAH palAyante vyAghrAt kSudramRgA iva .
te nivRttAH punaH pArthaM sarvataH paryavArayan . raNe sapanAn nighnantaM jigISantaM parAn yudhi .
teSAmApatatAM tUrNaM gANDIvapreSitaiH zaraiH . zirAMsi pAtayAmAsa bAhUMzcApi dhanaMjayaH .
zirobhiH pAtitaistatra bhUmirAsInirantarA . abhracchAyeva caivAsIt dhvAkSagRghrabalaiyudhi .
teSu tUtsAdyamAneSu krodhAmarSasamanvitau . zrutAyuzcAcyutAyuzca dhanaMjayamayudhyatAm .
balino spardhinau vIro kulajau bAhuzAlinau . tAvenaM zaravarSANi savyadakSiNamasyatAm .
tvarAyuktau mahArAja prArthayAnau mahad yazaH . arjunasya vadhaprepsU putrArtha tava dhanvinau .
tAvarjunaM sahasreNa patriNAM nataparvaNAm . pUrayAmAsatuH kruddhau taTAgaM jaladau yathA .
zrutAyuzca tataH kruddhastomareNa dhanaMjayam . AjaghAna rathazreSThaH pItena nizitena ca .
so ' tividdho balavatA zatruNA zatrukarzanaH . jagAma paramaM mohaM mohayan kezavaM raNe .
etasminneva kAle tu so ' cyutAyurmahArathaH . zUlena bhRzatIkSNena tADayAmAsa pANDavam .
kSate kSAraM sa hi dadau pANDavasya mahAtmanaH . pArtho ' pi bhRzaMsaMviddho dhvajayaSTiM samAzritaH .
