hatvA jitvA ca maghavan yaH kazcit puruSAyate . akartA hova bhavati kartA hyeva karoti tat .
ko hi lokasya kurute vinAzaprabhavAvubhau . kRtaM hi tat kRtenaiva kartA tasyApi cAparaH .
pRthivI jyotirAkAzamApo vAyuzca paJcamaH . etadyonIni bhUtAni tatra kA paridevanA .
mahAvidyo ' lpavidyazca balavAn durbalazca yaH . darzanIyo virUpazca subhago durbhagazca yaH . sarvaM kAla : samAdatte gambhIraH svena tejasA . tasmin kAlavazaM prApte kA vyathA me vijAnataH .
dagdhamevAnudahati hatamevAnuhanyate . nazyate naSTamevAgre labdhavyaM labhate naraH .
nAsya dvIpa : kutaH pAro nAvAraH sampradRzyate . nAntamasya prapazyAmi vidherdivyasya cintayan .
yadi me pazyataH kAlo bhUtAni na vinAzayet . syAnme harSazca darpazca krodhazcaiva zacIpate .
tuSabhakSaM tu mAM jJAtvA praviviktajane gRhe . bibhrataM gArdabhaM rUpamAgatya parigarhase .23 .
icchannahaM vikuryAM hi rUpANi bahudhA ' ' tmanaH . vibhISaNAni yAnIkSya palAyethAstvameva me .
kAlaH sarvaM samAdatte kAlaH sarvaM prayacchati . kAlena vihitaM sarvaM mA kRthAH zakra pauruSam .
purA sarvaM pravyathitaM mayi kruddhe puraMdara . avaimi tvasya lokasya dharmaM zakra sanAtanam .
tvamapyevamavekSasva mA ' ' tmanA vismayaM gamaH . prabhavazca prabhAvazca nAtmasaMsthaH kadAcana . .
kaumArameva te cittaM tathaivAdya yathA purA . samavekSasva maghavan buddhiM vindasva naiSThikIm .
devA manuSyAH pitaro gandharvoragarAkSasAH . Asan sarve mama vaze nat sarvaM vettha vAsava .
namastasyai dize ' pyastu yasyAM vairocano baliH iti mAmabhyapadyanta buddhimAtsaryamohitAH . . nAhaM tadanuzocAmi nAtmabhraMzaM zacIpate . evaM me nizcitA buddhiH zAstustiSThAmyahaM vaze .
dRzyate hi kule jAto darzanIyaH pratApavAn . duHkhaM jIvan sahAmAtyo bhavitavyaM hi tat tathA .
dauSkuleyastathA mUDho durjAtaH zakra dRzyate . sukhaM jIvan sahAmAtyo bhavitavyaM hi tat tathA .
kalyANI rUpasampannA durbhagA zakra dRzyate . alakSaNA virUpA ca subhagA dRzyate parA .
naitadasmatkRtaM zakra naitacchaka tvayA kRtam . yat tvamevaMgato jin yaccApyevaMgatA vayam .
na karma bhavitApyetat kRtaM mama zatakrato . RddhirvApyathavA naddhiH paryAyakRtameva tat .
pazyAmi tvAM virAjatvaM devarAjamavasthitam . zrImantaM dyutimantaM ca garjamAnaM mamopari .
evaM naiva na cet kAlo mAmAkramya sthito bhavet . pAtayeyamahaM tvAdya savajramapi muSTinA .
na tu vikramakAlo ' yaM zAntikAlo ' yamAgataH . kAlaH sthApayate sarvaM kAla : pacati vai tathA .
mAM cedabhyAgataH kAlo dAnavezvarapUjitam . garjantaM pratapantaM ca kamanyaM nAgamiSyati .
dvAdazAnAM tu bhavatAmAdityAnAM mahAtmanAm . tejAMsyekena sarveSAM devarAja dhRtAni me .
ahamevodvahAmyApo visRjAmi ca vAsava . tapAmi caiva trailokyaM vidyotAmyahameva ca .
saMrakSAmi vilumpAmi dadAmyahamathAdade . saMyacchAmi niyacchAmi lokeSu prabhurIzvaraH .
tadadya vinivRttaM me prabhutvamamarAdhipa . kAlasainyAvagADhasya sarvaM na pratibhAti me .
nAhaM kartA na caiva tvaM nAnyaH kartA zacIpate . paryAyeNa hi bhujyante lokAH zakra yadRcchayA .
mAsamAsArdhavezmAnamahorAtrAbhisaMvRtam . RtudvAraM varSamukhamAyurvedavido janAH .
AhuH sarvamidaM cintyaM janAH kecinmanISayA . asyAH paJcaiva cintAyAH paryeSyAmi ca paJcadhA .
gambhIraM gahanaM brahma mahattoyArNavaM yathA . anAdinidhanaM cAhurakSaraM kSarameva ca .
sattveSu liGgamAvezya nirliGgamapi tat svayam . manyante dhruvamevainaM ye janAstattvadarzinaH .
bhUtAnAM tu viparyAsaM kurute bhagavAniti . na hyetAvad bhaved gamyaM na yasmAt prabhavet punaH .
gatiM hi sarvabhUtAnAmagatvA kva gamiSyati . yo dhAvatA na hAtavyastiSThannapi na hIyate .
tamindriyANi sarvANi nAnupazyanti paJcadhA . Ahuzcai kecidagni kecidAhuH prajApatim . RtUn mAsArdhamAsAMzca divasAMzca kSaNAMstathA . pUrvAhlamaparAhaM ca madhyAhnamapi cApare . muhUrtamapi caivAhurekaM santamanekadhA . taM kAlamiti jAnIhi yasya sarvamidaM vaze .
bahUnIndrasahasrANi samatItAni vAsava . balavIryopapannAni yathaiva tvaM zacIpate . .
tvAmapyatibalaM zakra devarAja balotkaTam . prApte kAle mahAvIryaH kAlaH saMzamayiSyati .
ya idaM sarvamAdatte tasmAcchaka sthiro bhava . mayA tvayA ca pUrvezca na sa zakyo ' tivartitum .
yomatAM prApya jAnISe rAjyazriyamanuttamAm . sthitA mayIti tanmithyA naiSA hokatra tiSThati .
sthitA hIndra sahasreSu tvadviziSTatameSviyam . mAM ca lolA parityajya tvAmagAd vibudhAdhipa .
maivaM zakra punaH kArSIH zAnto bhavitumarhasi . tvAmapyevaMvidhaM jJAtvA kSipramanyaM gamiSyati .
saMjaya uvAca tasmiMstu nihate zUre zAlve samiti zobhane . tavAbhajyad balaM vegAd vAteneva mahAdrumaH .
tat prabhagnaM balaM dRSTvA kRtavarmA mahArathaH . dadhAra samare zUraH zatrusainyaM mahAbalaH .
sannivRttAstu te zUrA dRSTvA sAtvatamAhave . zailopamaM sthiraM rAjan kIryamANaM zarairyudhi .
tataH pravavRte yuddhaM kurUNAM pANDavaiH saha . nivRttAnAM mahArAja mRtyuM kRtvA nivartanam .
tatrAzcaryamabhUd yuddhaM sAtvatasya paraiH saha . yadeko vArayAmAsa pANDusenAM durAsadAm .
teSAmanyonyasuhRdAM kRte karmaNi duSkare . siMhanAdaH prahRSTAnAM divispRk sumahAnabhUt .
tena zabdena vitrastAH paJcAlAn bharatarSabha . zinernaptA mahAbAhuranvapadyata sAtyakiH .
sa samAsAdya rAjAnaM kSemadhUrti mahAbalam . saptabhirnizitairbANairanayad yamasAdanam .
tamAyAntaM mahAbAhuM pravapantaM zitAzarAn . javenAbhyapatad dhImAn hArdikyaH zinipuGgavam .
sAtvatau ca mahAvI? dhanvinau rathinAM varau . anyonyamabhidhAvetAM zastrapravaradhAriNau .
pANDavAH sahapaJcAlA yodhAzcAnye nRpottamAH . prekSakAH samapadyanta tayoghari samAgame .
nArAcairvatsadantaizca vRSNyandhakamahArathau . abhijaghnaturanyonyaM prahRSTAviva kuJjarau .
carantau vividhAn mArgAn hArdikyazinipuGgavau . muhurantardadhAte tau bANavRSTyA parasparam .
cApavegabaloddhRtAn mArgaNAn vRSNisiMhayoH . AkAze samapazyAma pataGgAniva zIghragAn .
tamekaM satyakarmANamAsAdya hRdikAtmajaH . avidhyannizitairbANaizcaturbhizcaturo hayAn .
sa dIrghabAhuH saMkruddhastotrAdita iva dvipaH . aSTabhiH kRtavarmANamaviddhyat parameSubhiH .
tataH pUrNAyatotsRSTaiH kRtavarmA zilAzitaiH . sAtyaki tribhirAhatya dhanurekena cicchide .
nikRttaM tad dhanuH zreSThamapAsya zinipuGgavaH . anyadAdatta vegena zaineyaH sazaraM dhanuH .
tadAdAya dhanuH zreSThaM variSThaH sarvadhanvinAm . Arogya ca dhanuH zIghraM mahAvIryo mahAbalaH . amRSyamANo dhanuSazchedanaM kRtavarmaNA . kupito ' tirathaH zIghraM kRtavarmANamabhyayAt .
tataH sunizitairbANairdazabhiH zinipuGgavaH . jaghAna sUtaM cAzvAMzca dhvajaM ca kRtavarmaNaH .
tato rAjan maheSvAsaH kRtavarmA mahArathaH . hatAzvasUtaM samprekSya rathaM hemapariSkRtam . roSeNa mahatA ' ' viSTaH zUlamudyamya mAriSa . cikSepa bhujavegena jighAMsuH zinipuGgavam .
tacchUlaM sAtvato hyAjau nirbhidya nizitaiH zaraiH . cUrNitaM pAtayAmAsa mohayanniva mAdhavam .
tato ' pareNa bhallena hRdyenaM samatADayat . sa yuddhe yuyudhAnena hatAzvo hatasArathiH .
kRtavarmA kRtastena dharaNImanvapadyata . tasmin sAtyakinA vIre dvairathe virathIkRte . samapadyata sarveSAM sainyAnAM sumahad bhayam .
putrasya tava cAtyarthaM viSAdaH samajAyata . hatasUte hatAzve tu virathe kRtavarmaNi .
hatAzvaM ca samAlakSya hatasUtamariMdama . abhyadhAvat kRpo rAjaJjighAMsuH zinipuGgavam .
tamAropya rathopasthe miSatAM sarvadhanvinAm . apovAha mahAbAhuM tUrNamAyodhanAdapi .
zaineye ' dhiSThite rAjan virathe kRtavarmaNi . duryodhanabalaM sarvaM punarAsIt parAGmukham .
tat pare nAnvabudhyanta sainyena rajasA vRtAH . tAvakAH pradrutA rAjan duryodhanamRte nRpam .
duryodhanastu samprekSya bhagnaM svabalamantikAt . javenAbhyapat tUrNaM sarvAMzcaiko nyavArayat .
pANDUMzca sarvAn saMkruddho dhRSTadyumnaM ca pArSatam . zikhaNDinaM draupadeyAn paJcAlAnA ca ye gaNAH . kekayAn somakAMzcaiva sRJjayAMzcaiva mAriSa . asambhramaM durAdharSaH zitairvANairavAkirat . atiSThadAhave yattaH putrastava mahAbalaH .
yathA yajJe mahAnagnimantrapUtaH prakAzavAn . tathA duryodhano rAjA saMgrAme sarvato ' bhavat .
taM pare nAbhyavartanta mA mRtyumivAhave . athAnyaM rathamAsthAya hArdikyaH samapadyata .
nArada uvAca nAbhAgamambarISaM ca mRtaM sRJjaya zuzruma yaH sahasraM sahasrANAM rAjJAM caikastvayodhayat .
jigISamANAH saMgrAme samantAd vairiNo ' bhyayuH . astrayuddhavido ghorAH sRjantazcAzivA giraH .
balalAghavazikSAbhisteSAM so ' strabalena ca . chatrAyudhadhvajarathAMzchittvA prAsAn gatavyathaH .
ta enaM muktasaMnAhAH prArthayan jIvitaiSiNaH . zaraNyamIyuH zaraNaM tavAsma iti vAdinaH .
sa tu tAn vazagAn kRtvA jitvA cemAM vasundharAm . Ije yajJazatairiSTairyathAzAstraM tathA ' nadha .
bubhujuH sarvasampannamannamanye janAH sadA . tasmin yajJe tu viprendrAH saMtRptAH paramArcitAH .
modakAn pUrikApUpAn svAdupUrNAzca zaSkulIH . karambhAn pRthumRdvIkA annAni sukRtAni ca . sUpAn maireyakApUpAn rAgakhANDavapAnakAn . mRSTAnnAni suyuktAni mRdUni surabhINi ca . ghRtaM madhu payastoyaM dadhIni rasavanti ca . phalaM mUlaM ca susvAdu dvijAstatropabhuJjate .
mAdanIyAni pApAni viditvA cAtmanaH sukham . apibanta yathAkAmaM pAnayA gItavAditaiH .
tatra sma gAthA gAyanti kSIbA hRSTAH paThanti ca . nAbhAgastutisaMyuktA nanRtuzca sahasrazaH .
teSu yajJeSvambarISo dakSiNAmatyakAlayat . rAjJAM zatasahasrANi daza prayutayAjinAm .
hiraNyakavacAn sarvAzvetacchatraprakIrNakAn . hiraNyasyandanArUDhAn sAnuyAtraparicchadAn . IjAno vitate yajJe dakSiNAmatyakAlayat . mUrdhAbhiSiktAMzca nRpAn rAjaputrazatAni ca . sadaNDakozanicayAn brAhmaNebhyo hmamanyata . naivaM pUrve janAcakurna kariSyanti cApare .
yadambarISo nRpatiH karotyamitadakSiNaH . ityevamanumodante prItA yasya maharSayaH .
sa cenmamAra sRJjaya caturbhadratarastvayA . putrAt puNyatarastubhyaM mA putramanutapyathAH . ayajavAnamadAkSiNyamabhi zvaityetyudAharat .
sUta uvAca etasminneva kAle tu bhaginyau te tapodhana . apazyatAM samAyAte uccaiHzravasamantikAt .
yaM taM devagaNAH sarve hRSTarUpamapUjayan . mathyamAne ' mRte jAtamazvaratnamanuttamam .
amoghabalamazvAnAmuttamaM jagatAM varam . zrImantamajaraM divyaM sarvalakSaNapUjitam .
zaunaka uvAca kathaM tadamRtaM devairmathitaM kva ca zaMsa me . yatra jajJe mahAvIryaH so ' zvarAjo mahAdyutiH .
sautiruvAca jvalantamacalaM melaM tejorAzimanuttamam . AkSipantaM prabhAM bhAno : svazRMgaiHkAJcanojvalaiH .
kanakAbharaNaM citraM devagandharvasevitam . aprameyamanAdhRSyamadharmabahulairjanaiH .
vyAlairAvAritaM ghorairdivyauSadhividIpitam . nAkamAvRtya tiSThantamucchrayeNa mahAgirim .
agamyaM manasA ' pyanyairnadIvRkSasamanvitam . nAnApatagasabaizca nAditaM sumanoharaiH .
tasya zRGgamupAruhya bahuratnAcitaM zubham . anantakalpamudviddhaM surA : sarve mahaujasaH . .
te mantrayitumArabdhAstatrAsInA divaukasaH . amRtAya samAgamya taponiyamasaMyutAH . tatra nArAyaNo devo brahmANamidamabravIt . cintayatsu sureSvevaM mantrayatsu ca sarvazaH .
devairasurasaMDbaizca mathyatAM kalazodadhiH . bhaviSyatyamRtaM tatra mathyamAne mahodadhau . sarvoSadhI : samAvApya sarvaratnAni caiva ha . manyadhvamudadhiM devA vetsyadhvamamRtaM tataH .
vaizampAyana uvAca indratIrthaM tato gatvA yadUnAM pravaro balaH . viprebhyo dhanaratnAni dadau snAtvA yathAvidhi .
tatra hyamararAjo ' sAvIje Rtuzatena ca . bRhaspatezca devezaH pradadau vipulaM dhanam .
niranlAn sajArUthyAn sarvAn vividhadakSiNAn . AjahAra kratUMstatra yathoktAn vedapAragaiH .
tAn kratUn bharatazreSTha zatakRtvo mahAdyutiH . pUrayAmAsa vidhivat tataH khyAtaH zatakratuH .
tasya nAmnA ca tat tIrthaM zivaM puNyaM sanAtanam . indratIrthamiti khyAtaM sarvapApapramocanam .
upaspRzya ca tatrApi vidhivanmusalAyudhaH . brAhmaNAn pUjayitvA ca sadAcchAdanabhojanaiH . zubhaM tIrthavaraM tasmAd rAmatIrthaM jagAma ha
yatra rAmo mahAbhAgo bhArgavaH sumahAtapAH . asakRt pRthivIM jitvA hatakSatriyapuGgavAm .
upAdhyAyaM puraskRtya kazyapaM munisattamam . ayaja vAjapeyena so ' zvamedhazatena ca . pradadau dakSiNAM caiva pRthivIM vai sasAgarAm .
dattvA ca dAnaM vividhaM nAnAratnasamanvitam . sagohastikadAsIkaM sAjAvi gatavAn vanam .
puNye tIrthavare tatra devabrahmarSisevite . munIMzcaivAbhivAdyAtha yamunAtIrthamAgamat .
yatrAnayAmAsa tadA rAjasUyaM mahIpate . putro ' ditermahAbhAgo varuNo vai sitaprabhaH .
tatra nirjitya saMgrAme mAnuSAn devatAstathA . varaM kratuM samAjahe varuNaH paravIrahA . tasmin kratuvare vRtte saMgrAma : samajAyata . devAnAM dAnavAnAM ca trailokyasya bhayAvahaH .
rAjasUye RtuzreSThe nivRtte janamejaya . jAyate sumahAghora : saMgrAmaH kSatriyAn prati .
tatrApi lAgalI deva RSInabhyarcya pUjayA . itarebhyo ' pyadAd dAnamarthibhyaH kAmado vibhuH .
vanamAlI tato hRSTaH stUyamAno maharSibhiH . tasmAdAdityatIrthaM ca jagAma kamalekSaNaH .
yatreSTavA bhagavAjyotirbhAskaro rAjasattama . jyotiSAmAdhipatyaM ca prabhAvaM cAbhyapadyata .
tasyA nadyAstu tIre vai sarve devAH savAsavAH . vizvedevAH samaruto gandharvApsarasazca ha . dvaipAyanaH zukazcaiva kRSNAzca madhusUdanaH . yakSAzca rAkSasAzcaiva pizAcAzca vizAmpate . ete cAnye ca bahavo yogasiddhAH sahasrazaH . tasmiMstIrthe sarasvatyAH zive puNye paraMtapa . tatra hatvA purA viSNurasurau madhukaiTabhau . Aplutya bharatazreSTha tIrthapravara uttame .
dvaipAyanazca dharmAtmA tatraivAplutya bhArata . samprApya paramaM yogaM siddhiM ca paramAM gataH .
asito devalazcaiva tasminneva mahAtapAH . paramaM yogamAsthAya RSiryogamavAptavAn .
zuka uvAca vartamAnasthaivAtra vAnaprasthAzrame yathA . yoktavyo ' ' tmA kathaM zaktyA vedyaM vai kAsatA param .
vyAsa uvAca prApya saMskArametAbhyAmAzramAbhyAM tataH param . yatkAryaM paramArtha tadihaikamanAH zRNu . tu
kaSAyaM pAcayitvA ' ' zu zreNisthAneSu ca triSu . pravrajecca paraM sthAnaM pArivAjyamanuttamam .
tad bhavAnevamabhyasya vartatAM zrUyatAM tathA . eka eva cared dharmaM siddhyarthamasahAyavAn .
ekazcarati yaH pazyan na jahAti na hIyate . anagniraniketazca grAmamannArthamAzrayet .
azvastanavidhAtA syAnmunirbhAvasamAhitaH . ladhvAzI niyatAhAraH sakRdannaniSevitA .
kapAlaM vRkSamUlAni kucailamasahAyatA . upekSA sarvabhUtAnAmetAvad bhikSulakSaNam .
yasmin vAcaH prAvizanti kUpe trastA dvipA iva . na vaktAraM punaryAnti kaivalyAzrame vaset .
naiva pazyenna zRNuyAdavAcyaM jAtu kasyacit . brAhmaNAnAM vizeSeNa naiva brUyAt kathaMcana .
yad brAhmaNasya kuzalaM tadeva satataM vadet . tUSNImAsIta nindAyAM kurvan bhaiSajyamAtmanaH .
yena pUrNamivAkAzaM bhavatyekena sarvadA . zUnyaM yena janAkIrNaM taM devA brAhmaNaM viduH .
yena kenacidAcchanno yena kenacidAzitaH . yatra kvacana zAyI ca taM devA brAhmaNaM viduH .
aheriva gaNAd bhItaH sauhityAnarakAdiva . kuNapAdiva ca strIbhyastaM devA brAhmaNaM viduH .
na kruddhyena prahRSyecca mAnito ' mAnitazca yaH . sarvabhUteSvabhayadastaM devA brAhmaNaM viduH .
nAbhinandeta maraNaM nAbhinandeta jIvitam . kAlamegha pratIkSate nidezaM bhRtako yathA .
anabhyAhatacitta syAdanabhyAhatavAg bhavet . nirmuktaH sarvapApebhyo niramitrasya kiM bhayam .
abhayaM sarvabhUtebhyo bhUtAnAmabhayaM tataH . tasya mohAd vimuktasya bhayaM nAsti kutazcana .
yathA nAgapade ' nyAni padAni padagAminAm . sarvANyevApidhIyante padajAtAni kauJjare .
evaM sarvamahiMsAyAM dharmArthamapidhIyate . amRtaH sa nityaM vasati yo hiMsAM na prapadyate .
ahiMsakaH samaH satyo dhRtimAn niyatendriyaH . zaraNyaH sarvabhUtAnAM gatimApnotyanuttamAm .
evaM prajJAnatRptasya nirbhayasya nirAziSaH . na mRtyuratigo bhAvaH sa mRtyumadhigacchati .
vimuktaM sarvasaGgebhyo munimAkAzavat sthitam . asvamekacaraM zAntaM taM devA brAhmaNaM viduH .
jIvitaM yasya dharmArthaM dharmo haryarthameva ca . ahorAtrAzca puNyArthaM taM devA brAhmaNaM viduH .
nirAziSamanArambhaM nirnamaskAramastutim . nirmuktaM bandhanaiH sarvaistaM devA brAhmaNaM viduH .
sarvANi bhUtAni sukhe ramante sarvANi duHkhasya bhRzaM trasante . teSAM bhayotpAdanajAtakhedaH kuryAnna karmANi hi zraddadhAnaH .
dAnaM hi bhUtAbhayadakSiNAyAH sarvANi dAnAnyadhitiSThatIha . tIkSNAM tanuM yaH prathamaM jahAti so ' ' nantyamApnotyabhayaM prajAbhyaH .
uttAna Asyena havirjuhoti lokasya nAbhirjagataH pratiSThA . tasyAGgamaGgAni kRtAkRtaM ca vaizvAnaraH sarvamidaM prapede .
prAdezamAne hRdi niHsRtaM yat tasmin prANAnAtmayAjI juhoti . tasyAgnihotraM hutamAtmasaMsthaM sarveSu lokeSu sadevakeSu .
devaM tridhAtuM trivRtaM suparNaM ye vidyuragrayAM paramAtmatAM ca . te sarvalokeSu mahIyamAnA devAH samAH sukRtaM vadanti .
matho niruktaM paramArthatAM ca . sarvaM zarIrAtmani yaH praveda tasyaiva devAH spRhayanti nityam .
bhUmAvasaktaM divi cAprameyaM hiraNmayaM yo ' NDajamaNDamadhye . patatriNaM pakSiNamantarikSa yo veda bhogyAtmani razmidIptaH .
AvartamAnamajaraM vivartanaM SaNNAbhikaM dvAdazAraM suparva . yasyedamAsye pariyAti vizvaM tatkAlacakraM nihitaM guhAyAm .
yaH samprasAdo jagataH zarIraM sarvAnsa lokAnadhigacchatIha . ste vai tRptAstarpayantyAsyamasya .
tejomayo nityamayaH purANo lokAnanantAnabhayAnupaiti . bhUtAni yasmAnna vasante kadAcitsa bhUtAnAM na trasate kadAcit .
agarhaNIyo na ca garhate ' nayAnsa vai vipraH paramAtmAnamIkSet . vinItamoho vyapanItakalmaSo na ceha nAmutra ca so ' nnamRcchati .
aroSamohaH samaloSTakAJcanaH prahINakozo gatasaMdhivigrahaH . zvarannudAsInavadeSa bhikSukaH .
saMjaya uvAca te kirantaH zaravAtAn sarve yattAH prahAriNaH . tvaramANA mahArAja yuyudhAnamayodhayan .
taM droNaH sapta saptatyA jaghAna nizitaiH zaraiH . durmarSaNo dvAdazabhirduHsaho dazabhiH zaraiH .
vikarNazcApi nizitaistriMzadbhiH kaGkapatribhiH . vivyAdha savye pArzve tu stanAbhyAmantare tathA .
durmukho dazabhirbANaistathA duHzAsano ' STabhiH . citrasenazca zaineya dvAbhyAM vivyAdha mAriSa .
duryodhanazca mahatA zaravarSeNa mAdhavam . apIDayadraNe rAjazUrAzcAnye mahArathAH .
sarvataH pratividdhastu tava putrairmahArathaiH . tAn pratyavidhyadvASNaiyaH pRthak pRthagajihmagaiH .
bhAradvAjaM tribhirbANairduHsahaM navabhiH zaraiH . vikarNe paJcaviMzatyA citrasenaM ca saptabhiH .
durmarSaNaM dvAdazabhiraSTAbhizca viviMzAtema . satyavrataM ca navabhirvijayaM dazabhiH zaraiH .
tato rukmAMgadaM cAraM vidhunvAno mahArathaH . abhyayAt sAtyakistUrNaM putraM tava mahAratham .
rAjAnaM sarvalokasya sarvalokamahAratham . zarairabhyAhanagaDhaM tato yuddhamabhUttayoH .
vimuJcantau zarAMstIkSNAn saMdadhAnau ca sAyakAn . adRzyaM samare ' nyonyaM cakratustau mahArathau .
sAtyakiH kururAjane nirviddho bahvazobhata . asravadudhiraM bhUri svarasaM candano yathA .
sAtvatena ca bANaudhairnirviddhastanayastava . zAtakuMbhamayApIDo babhau yUpa ivocchritaH .
mAdhavastu raNe rAjan kururAjasya dhanvinaH . dhanuzciccheda samare kSurapreNa hasanniva .
athainaM chinnadhanvAnaM zarairbahubhirAcinot . nirbhinnazca zaraistena dviSatA kSiprakAriNA .
nAmRSyata raNe rAjA zatrovijayalakSaNam . athAnyaddhanurAdAya hemapRSThaM durAsadam . -
vivyAdha sAtyakiM tUrNe sAyakAnAM zatena ha . so ' tividdho balavatA tava putreNa dhanvinA .
amarSavazamApannastava putramapIDayat . pIDitaM nRpatiM dRSTvA tava putrA mahArathAH .
sAtyaki zaravarSeNa chAdayAmAsurojasA . sa cchAdyamAno bahubhistava putrairmahArathaiH .
ekaikaM paJcabhirviddhvA punarvivyAdha saptabhiH . duryodhanaM ca tvarito vivyAdhASTabhirAzugaiH .
prahasaMzcAsya ciccheda kArmukaM ripubhISaNam . nAgaM maNimayaM caiva zarairdhvajamapAtayat .
hatvA tu caturo vAhAMzcaturbhinizitaiH zaraiH . sArathiM pAtayAmAsa kSurapreNa mahAyazAH .
etasminnantare caiva kururAjaM mahAratham . avAkiraccharairhaSTo bahubhirmarmabhedibhiH .
sa vadhyamAnaH samare zaineyasya zarottamaiH . prAdravat sahasA rAjan putro duryodhanastava .
Aplutazca tato yAnaM citrasenasya dhanvinaH . hAhAbhUtaM jagazcAsId dRSTvA rAjAnamAhave .
grasyamAnaM sAtyakinA khe somamiva rAhuNA . taM tu zabdamatha zrutvA kRtavarmA mahArathaH .
abhyayAt sahasA tatra yatrAste mAdhavaH prabhuH . vidhunvAno dhanuH zreSThaM codayaMzcaiva vAjinaH .
bhartsayan sArathiM cAgre yAhi yAhIti satvaraM . tamApatantaM saMprekSya vyAditAsyamivAntakam .
yuyudhAno mahArAja yantAramidamabravIt . kRtavarmA rathenaiSa drutamApatate zarI .
pratyudyAhi rathenainaM pravaraM sarvadhanvinAm . tataH prajavitAzvena vidhivat kalpitena ca .
AsasAda raNe bhoja pratimAnaM dhanuSmatAm . tataH paramasaMkruddhau jvalitAviva pAvakau .
sameyAtAM naravyAghrau vyAghrAviva tarasvinau . kRtavarmA tu zaineyaM SaDvizatyA samArpamat .
nizitaiH sAyakaistIkSNairyantAraM cAsya paJcabhiH . caturazcaturo vAhAMzcaturbhiH parameSubhiH . avidhyat sAdhudAntAn vai saindhavAn sAtvatasya hi . rukmadhvajo rukmapRSThaM mahad visphArya kArmukam .
rukmAGgadI rukmavarmA rukmapuGkharavArayat . tato ' zItiM zineH pautraH sAyakAn kRtavarmaNe . prAhiNot tvarayA yukto draSTakAmo dhanaMjayam . so ' tividdho balavatA zatruNA zatrutApanaH .
samakampata durgharSaH kSitikampe yathAcalaH . triSaSTyA caturo ' syAzvAn saptabhiH sArathiM tathA . vivyAdha nizitaistUrNaM sAtyakiH satyavikramaH . suvarNapuGkha vizikhaM samAdhAya ca sAtyakiH .
vyasRjat taM mahAjvAlaM saMkruddhamiva pannagam . so ' vidhyat kRtavarmANaM yamadaNDopamaH zaraH .
jAmbUnadavicitraM ca varma nirbhidya bhAnumat . abhyagAda dharaNImuno rudhireNa samukSitaH .
saMjAtarudhirazcAjau sAtvateSubhirarditaH . sazaraM dhanurutsRjya nyapatat syandanottamAt .
sa siMhadaMSTro jAnubhyAM patito ' mitavikramaH . zarAditaH sAtyakinA rathopasthe nararSabhaH .
sahasrabAhusadRzamakSobhyamiva sAgaram . nivArya kRtavarmANaM sAtyakiH prayayau tataH .
khaGgazaktidhanuHkIrNo gajAzvarathasaMkulAm . pravartitograrudhirAM zatazaH kSatriyarSabhaiH . prekSatAM sarvasainyAnAM madhyena zinipuGgavaH . abhyagAdvAhinIM hitvAvRtrahevAsurIMcamUm .
samAzvasya ca hArdikyo gRhya cAnyanmahad dhanuH . tasthau sa tatra balavAn vArayan yudhi pANDavAn .
samAzvasya ca hArdikyo gRhya cAnyanmahad dhanuH . tasthau sa tatra balavAn vArayan yudhi pANDavAn .
mArkaNDeya uvAca tasyAM rAtryAM vyatItAyAmudite sUryamaNDale . kRtapaurvANikAH sarvaM sameyuste tapodhanAH .
tadeva sarvaM sAvitryA mahAbhAgyaM maharSayaH . dhumatsenAya nAtRpyan kathayantaH punaH punaH .
tataH prakRtayaH sarvAH zAlvebhyo ' bhyAgatA nRpa . AcakhyunihataM caiva svenAmAtyena taM dviSam .
taM mantriNA hataM zrutvA sasahAyaM sabAndhavam . nyavedayan yathAvRttaM vidrutaM ca dviSadbalam . aikamatyaM ca sarvasya janasyAtha nRpaM prati . sacakSurvApyacakSurvA sa no rAjA bhavatviti .
anena nizcayeneha vayaM prasthApitA nRpa . prAptAnImAni yAnAni caturaGgaM ca te balam .
prayAhi rAjan bhadraM te ghuSTaste nagare jayaH . adhyAssva cirarAtrAya pitRpaitAmahaM padam .
cakSuSmantaM ca taM dRSTvA rAjAnaM vapuSAnvitam . mUrdhA nipatitAH sarve vismayotphullalocanAH .
tato ' bhivAdya tAn vRddhAn dvijAnAzramavAsinaH . taizcAbhipUjitaH sarvaiH prayayau nagaraM prati .
zaibyA ca saha sAvitryA svAstIrNena suvarcasA . narayuktena yAnena prayayau senayA vRtA .
tato ' bhiSiSicuH prItyA dhumatsenaM purohitAH . putraM cAsya mahAtmAnaM yauvarAjye ' bhyaSecayan .
tataH kAlena mahatA sAvitryAH kIrtivardhanam . tad vai putrazataM jajJe zUrANAmanivartinAm .
bhrAtRNAM saudarANAM ca tathaivAsyAbhavacchatam . madrAdhipasyAzvapatermAlabyAM sumahad balam .
evamAtmA pitA mAtA zvazrUH zvazura eva ca . bhartuH kulaM ca sAvitryA sarvaM kRcchrAt samudbhutam .
tathaivaiSA hi kalyANI draupadI zIlasammatA . tArayiSyati vaH sarvAn sAvitrIva kulAGganA .
vaizampAyana uvAca evaM sa pANDavastena anunIto mahAtmanA . vizoko vijvaro rAjan kAmyake nyavasat tadA .
yazcedaM zRNuyAd bhaktyA sAvitryAkhyAnamuttamam . sa sukhI sarvasiddhArtho na duHkhaM prApnuyAnaraH .
janamejaya uvAca kathamArTiSeNo bhagavAn vipulaM taptavAMstapaH . sindhudvIpaH kathaM cApi brAhmaNyaM labdhavAMstadA .
devApizca kathaM brahman vizvAmitrazca sattama . tanmamAcakSva bhagavan paraM kautUhalaM hi me .
vaizampAyana uvAca purA kRtayuge rAjannArTiSeNo dvijottamaH . vasan gurukale nityaM nityamadhyayane rataH .
tasya rAjan gurukule vasato nityameva ca . samApti nAgamad vidyA nApi vedA vizAmpate . .
sa nirviNastato rAjaMstapastepe mahAtapAH . tato vai tapasA tena prApya vedAnanuttamAn .
varAn prAdAt trIneva sa vidvAn vedayuktazca siddhazcApyaSisattamaH . tatra tIrthe sumahAtapAH .
asmiMstIrthe mahAnadyA adyaprabhRti mAnavaH . Apluto vAjimedhasya phalaM prApsyati puSkalam .
adyaprabhRti naivAtra bhayaM vyAlAd bhaviSyati . api cAlpena kAlena phalaM prApsyati puSkalam .
evamuktvA mahAtejA jagAma tridivaM muniH . evaM siddhaH sa bhagavAnArTiSeNaH pratApavAn .
tasminneva tadA tIrthe sindhudvIpaH pratApavAn . devApizca mahArAja brAhmaNyaM prApaturmaha .
tathA ca kauzikastAn taponityo jitendriyaH . tapasA vai sutaptena brAhmaNatvamavAptavAn .
gAdhirnAma mahAnAsIt kSatriyaH prathito bhuvi . tasya putro ' bhavad rAjan vizvAmitraH pratApavAn .
sa rAjA kauzikastAta mahAyogyabhavat kilA sa putramabhiSicyAtha vizvAmitraM mahAtapAH . dehanyAse manazcakre tamUcuH praNatAH prajAH . na gantavyaM mahAprAjJa trAhi cAsmAn mahAbhayAt .
evamuktaH pratyuvAca tato gAdhiH prajAstataH . vizvasya jagato goptA bhaviSyati suto mama .
ityuktvA tu tato gAdhirvizvAmitraM nivezya ca . jagAma tridivaM rAjanaM vizvAmitro ' bhavannRpaH . na sa zaknoti pRthivIM yatnavAnapi rakSitum .
tataH zuzrAva rAjA sa rAkSasebhyo mahAbhayam . niryayau nagarAcApi caturaGgabalAnvitaH .
sa gatvA dUramadhvAnaM vasiSThAzramamabhyayAt . tasya te sainikA rAjaMzcakrustatrAnayAn bahUn .
tatastu bhagavAn vipro vasiSTho ' ' zramamabhyayAt . dadRzo ' tha tataH sarvaM bhajyamAnaM mahAvanam .
tasya kruddho mahArAja vasiSTho munisattamaH . sRjasva zavarAn ghorAniti svAM gAmuvAca ha .
tathoktA sA ' sRjad dhenuH puruSAn ghoradarzanAn . te tu tadbalamAsAdya babhaJjuH sarvatodizam .
tacchutvA vidrutaM sainyaM vizvAmitrastu gAdhijaH . tapaH paraM manyamAnastapasyeva mano dadhe .
so ' smiMstIrthavare rAjan sarasvatyAH samAhitaH . niyamaizcopavAsaizca karSayan dehamAtmanaH .
jalAhAro vAyubhakSaH parNAhArazca so ' bhavat . tathA sthANDilazAyI ca ye cAnye niyamAH pRthak .
asakRttasya devAstu vratavighnaM pracakrire . na cAsya niyamAd buddhirapayAti mahAtmanaH .
tataH pareNa yatnena taptvA bahuvidhaM tapaH . tejasA bhAskarAkAro gAdhijaH samapadyata .
tapasA tu tathA yuktaM vizvAmitraM pitAmahaH . amanyata mahAtejA varado varamasya tat .
sa tu vave varaM rAjan syAmahaM brAhmaNAstviti . tatheti cAbravId brahmA sarvalokapitAmahaH .
sa lamvA tapasogreNa brAhmaNatvaM mahAyazAH . vicacAra mahIM kRtsnAM kRtakAmaH suropamaH .
atha vastrANyalaGkAraM bhakSyaM peyaM ca zobhanam . adadanmudito rAjan pUjayitvA dvijottamAn . tasmiMstIrthavare rAmaH pradAya vividhaM vasu .
payasvinIstathA dhenUryAnAni zayanAni ca . yayau rAjaMstato rAmo bakasyAzramamantikAt . yatra tepe tapastIvra dAlbhyo baka iti zrutiH .
vaizampAyana uvAca evaM te samayaM kRtvA nyavasaMstatra pANDavAH . vaze zastrapratApena kurvanto ' nyAn mahIkSitaH .
teSAM manujasiMhAnAM paJcAnAmamitaujasAm . babhUva kRSNA sarveSAM pArthAnAM vazavartinI .
te tayA taizca sA vIraiH patibhiH saha paJcabhiH . babhUva paramaprItA nAgairbhovatI yathA .
vartamAneSu dharmeNa pANDaveSu mahAtmasu . vyavardhan kuravaH sarve hInadoSA : sukhAnvitAH .
atha dIrgheNa kAlena brAhmaNasya vizAmpate . kasyacit taskarA jahvaH kecid gA nRpasattama .
hriyamANe dhane tasmin brAhmaNaH krodhamUrcchitaH . Agamya khANDavaprasthamuda krozat sa pANDavAn .
hriyate godhanaM kSudairnRzaMsairakRtAtmabhiH . prasahya cAsmadviSayAdabhyadhAvata pANDavAH .
brAhmaNasya prazAntasya havirdhvAkSaiH pralupyate . zArdUlasya guhAM zUnyAM nIcaH kroSTAbhimardati .
arakSitAraM rAjAnaM baliSaDbhAgahAriNam . tamAhuH sarvalokasya samagraM pApacAriNam .
brAhmaNasve hRte caurerdharmArthe ca vilopite . rorUyamANaM ca mayi kriyatAmastradhAraNam .
vaizampAyana uvAca rorUyamANasyAbhyAze bhRzaM viprasya pANDavaH . tAni vAkyAni zuzrAva kuntIputro dhanaMjayaH .
zrutvaiva ca mahAbAhurmA bhairityAha taM dvijam . AyudhAni ca yatrAvasan pANDavAnAM mahAtmanAm . kRSNayA saha tatrAste dharmarAjo yudhiSThiraH . sampravezAya cAzakto gamanAya ca pANDavaH .
tasya cArtasya tairvAkyaizcodyamAnaH punaH punaH . Akrande tatra kaunteyazcintayAmAsa duHkhitaH .
hriyamANe dhane tasmin brAhmaNasya tapasvinaH . azrupramArjanaM tasya kartavyamiti nizcayaH .
upakSepaNajo ' dharmaH sumahAn syAnmahIpateH . yadyasya rudatAM dvAri na karomyadya rakSaNam .
anAstikyaM ca sarveSAmasmAkamapi rakSaNe . pratitiSTheta loke ' sminnadharmazcaiva no bhavet .
anAdRtya tu rAjAnaM gate mayi na saMzayaH . ajAtazatrornRpatermama caivAnRtaM bhavet .
anupraveze rAjJastu vanavAso bhavenmama . sarvamanyat parihataM dharSaNAt tu mahIpateH . adharmo vai mahAnastu vane vA maraNaM mama . zarIrasya vinAzena dharma eva viziSyate .
evaM vinizcitya tataH kuntIputro dhanaMjayaH . anupravizya rAjAnamApRcchya ca vizAmpate . dhanurAdAya saMhRSTo brAhmaNa pratyabhASata .
brAhmaNAgamyatAM zIghraM yAvat paradhanaiSiNaH . na dUre te gatAH kSudrAstAvad gacchAvahe saha . yAvanivartayAmyadya caurahastAd dhanaM tava .
so ' nusRtya mahAbAhurdhanvI varmI rathI dhvajI . zarairvidhvasya tAMzcaurAnavajitya ca tad dhanam .
brAhmaNaM samupAkRtya yazaH prApya ca pANDavaH . tatastad godhanaM pArtho dattvA tasmai dvijAtaye . AjagAma puraM vIraH savyasAcI dhanaMjayaH . so ' bhivAdya gurUn sarvAn sarvaizcApyabhinanditaH .
dharmarAjamuvAcedaM vratamAdiza me prabho . samayaH samatikrAnto bhavatsaMdarzane mayA . . vanavAso gamiSyAmi samayo hyeSa naH kRtaH .
ityukto dharmarAjastu sahasA vAkyamapriyam . kathamityabravId vAcA zokArtaH sajjamAnayA . yudhiSThiro guDAkezaM bhrAtA bhrAtaramacyutam . uvAca dIno rAjA ca dhanaMjayamidaM vacaH . pramANamasmi yadi te mattaH zRNu vaco ' nagha .
anupraveze yad vIra kRtavAMstvaM mama priyam . sarvaM tadanujAnAmi vyalIkaM na ca me hRdi .
guroranupravezo hi nopaghAto yavIyasaH . yavIyaso ' nupravezo jyeSThabhya vidhilopakaH .
nivartasva mahAbAho kuruSva vacanaM mama . na hi te dharmalopo ' sti na ca te dharSaNA kRtA .
arjuna uvAca na vyAjena cared dharmamiti me bhavataH zrutam . na satyAd vicaliSyAmi satyenAyudhamAlabhe .
vaizampAyana uvAca so ' bhyanujJAya rAjAnaM vanacaryAya dIkSitaH . vane dvAdaza varSANi vAsAyAnujagAma ha .
yudhiSThira uvAca AnRzaMsyasya dharmajJa guNAn bhaktajanasya ca . zrotumicchAmi dharmajJa tanme brUhi pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . vAsavasya ca saMvAdaM zukasya ca mahAtmanaH .
viSaye kAzirAjasya grAmAniSkramya lubdhakaH . saviSaM kANDamAdAya mRgayAmAsa vai mRgam .
tatra cAmiSalubdhena lubdhakena mahAvane . avidUre mRgAn dRSTvA bANaH pratisamAhitaH .
tena durvAritAstreNa nimittacapaleSuNA . mahAn vanatarustatra viddho mRgajighAMsayA .
sa tIkSNaviSadigdhena zareNAtivalAt kSataH . utsRjya phalapatrANi pAdapaH zoSamAgataH .
tasmin vRkSe tathAbhUte koTareSu ciroSitaH . na jahAti zuko vAsaM tasya bhaktyA vanaspateH .
niSpracAro nirAhAro glAna : zithilavAgapi . kRtajJaH saha vRkSaNa dharmAtmA so ' pyazuSyata .
tamudAraM mahAsattvamatimAnuSaceSTitam . samaduHkhasukhaM dRSTvA vismita : pAkazAsanaH .
tatazcintAmupagataH zakraH kathamayaM dvijaH . tiryagyonAvasambhAvyamAnRzaMsyamavasthitaH .
athavA nAtra citraM hi abhavad vAsavasya tu . prANinAmapi sarveSAM sarvaM sarvatra dRzyate .
tato brAhmaNaveSeNa mAnuSaM rUpamAsthitaH . avatIrya mahIM zakrastaM pakSiNamuvAca ha .
zuka bho pakSiNAM zreSTha dAkSeyI suprajA tvayA . pRcche tvAM zukamenaM tvaM kasmAnna tyajasi dumam .
atha pRSTaH zukaH prAha mUrdhA samabhivAdya tam . svAgataM devarAja tvaM vijJAtastapasA mayA .
tato dazazatAkSeNa sAdhu sAdhviti bhASitam . aho vijJAnamityevaM manasA pUjitastataH .
tamevaM zubhakarmANaM zukaM paramadhArmikam . vijAnannapi tAM prItiM papraccha balasUdanaH .
niSpatramaphalaM zuSkamazaraNyaM patatriNAm . kimarthaM sevase vRkSaM yadA mahadidaM vanam . anye ' pi bahavo vRkSAH patrasaMcchannakoTarAH . paryAptasaMcArA vidyante ' smin mahAvane .
gatAyuSamasAmarthya kSINasAraM hatazriyam . vimRzya prajJayA dhIra jahImaM sthaviraM dumam .
bhISma uvAca tadupazrutya dharmAtmA zukaH zakreNa bhASitam . zubhAH paryA sudIrghamatiniHzvasya dIno vAkyamuvAca ha . anatikramaNIyAni daivatAni zacIpate . yatrAbhavat tava praznastannibodha surAdhipa .
asminnahaM dume jAtaH sAdhubhizca guNairyutaH . bAlabhAvena saMguptaH zatrubhizca na dharSitaH .
kimanukrozya vaiphalyamutpAdayasi me ' nagha . AnRzaMsyAbhiyuktasya bhaktasyAnanyagasya ca .
anukrozo hi sAdhUnAM mahaddharmasya lakSaNam . anukrozazca sAdhUnAM sadA prItiM prayacchati .
tvameva daivataiH sarvaiH pRcchase dharmasaMzayAt . atastvaM devadevAnAmAdhipatye pratiSThitaH .
nArhase mAM sahastrAkSa dumaM tyAjayituM cirAt . samarthamupajIvyemaM tyajeyaM kathamadya vai . tasya vAkyena saumyena harSita : pAkazAsanaH . zukaM provAca dharmAtmA AnRzaMsyena toSitaH .
varaM vRNISveti tadA sa ca vane varaM zukaH . AnRzaMsyaparo nityaM tasya vRkSasya sambhavam .
viditvA ca dRDhAM bhaktiM tAM zuke zIlasampadam . prItaH kSipramatho vRkSamamRtenAvasiktavAn .
tataH phalAni patrANi zAkhAzcApi manoharAH . zukasya dRDhabhaktitvAcchrImatAM prApa sa dumaH . zukazca karmaNA tena AnRzaMsyakRtena vai . AyuSo ' nte mahArAja prApa zakrasalokatAm .
evameva manuSyendra bhaktimantaM samAzritaH . sarvArthasiddhiM labhate zukaM prApya yathA drumaH .
zizupAla uvAca sa me bahumato rAjA jarAsaMdho mahAbalaH . yo ' nena yuddhaM neyeSa dAso ' yamiti saMyuge .
kezavena kRtaM karma jarAsaMdhavadhe tadA . bhImasenArjunAbhyAM ca kastat sAdhviti manyate .
advAreNa praviSTena chadmanA brahmavAdinA . dRSTaH prabhAvaH kRSNena jarAsaMdhasya bhUpateH .
yena dharmAtmanA ' ' tmAnaM brahmaNyamavijAnatA . neSitaM pAdyamasmai tad dAtumagre durAtmane . .
bhujyatAmiti tenoktAH kRSNabhImadhanaMjayAH . jarAsaMdhena kauravya kRSNena vikRtaM kRtam .
yadyayaM jagataH kartA yathainaM mUrkha manyase . kasmAnna brAhmaNaM samyagAtmAnamavagacchati .
idaM tvAzcaryabhUtaM me yadime pANDavAstvayA . apakRSTAH satAM mArgAnpranyante tacca sAdhviti .
atha vA naitadAzcaryaM yeSAM tvamasi bhArata . strIsadharmA ca vRddhazca sarvArthAnAM pradarzakaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tasya tad vacanaM zrutvA rUkSaM rUkSAkSaraM bahu . cukopa balinAM zreSTho bhImasenaH pratApavAn .
tathA padmapratIkAze svabhAvAyatavistRte . krodhAbhitAmrAkSe rakte netre babhUvatuH .
