tatra jAmbUnadAGgAni spardhyAstaraNavanti ca . maNividumacitrANi jvalitAgniprabhANi ca . bhejire puruSavyAghrA vRSNyandhakamahArathAH . siMhAsanAni zatazo dhiSNyAnIva hutAzanAH .
teSAM samupaviSTAnAM devAnAmiva saMnaye . Acakhyau ceSTitaM jiSNoH sabhApAla : sahAnugaH .
tacchrutvA vRSNivIrAste madasaMraktalocanAH . amRSyamANAH pArthasya samutpeturahaMkRtAH .
yojayavaM rathAnAzu prAsAnAharateti ca . dhanUMSi ca mahArhANi kavacAni bRhanti ca . sUtAnuccukruzuH kecid rathAn yojayateti ca . svayaM ca turagAn kecidayuJjan hemabhUSitAn .
ratheSvAnIyamAneSu kavaceSu dhvajeSu ca . abhikrande nRvIrANAM tadAsIt tumulaM mahat .
vanamAlI tataH kSIbaH kailAsazikharopamaH . nIlavAsA madosikta idaM vacanamabravIt .
kimidaM kuruthAprajJAstUSNIbhUte janArdane . asya bhAvamavijJAya saMkruddhA moghagarjitAH .
eSa tAvadabhiprAyamAkhyAtu svaM mahAmatiH . yadasya ruciraM kartuM tat kurudhvamatandritAH .
tataste tad vacaH zrutvA grAhyarUpaM halAyudhAt . tUSNImbhUtAstataH sarve sAdhu sAdhviti cAbruvan .
samaM vaco nizamyaiva baladevasya dhImataH . punareva sabhAmadhye sarve te samupAvizan .
tato ' bravId vAsudevaM vaco rAmaH paraMtapaH . kimavAgupaviSTo ' si prekSamANo janArdana .
satkRtastvatkRte pArthaH sarvairasmAbhiracyuta . na ca so ' rhati tAM pUjAM durbuddhiH kulapAMsanaH .
ko hi tatraiva bhuktvAnnaM bhAjanaM bhettumarhasi . manyamAnaH kule jAtamAtmAnaM puruSaH kvacit .
icchanneva hi sambandhaM kRtaM pUrvaM ca mAnayan . ko hi nAma bhavenArthI sAhasena samAcaret .
so ' vamanya tathAsmAkamanAdRtya ca kezavam . prasahya hRtavAnadya subhadrAM mRtyumAtmanaH .
kathaM hi ziraso madhye kRtaM tena padaM mama . marSayiSyAmi govinda pAdasparzamivoragaH .
adya niSkauravAmekaH kariSyAmi vasuMdharAm . na hi me marSaNIyo ' yamarjunasya vyatikramaH .
taM tathA garjamAnaM tu meghadundubhiniHsvanam . anvapadyanta te sarve bhojavRSNyandhakAstadA .
yudhiSThira uvAca kathaM dharme sthAtumicchan rAjA varteta dhArSikaH . pRcchAmi tvaM kuruzreSTha tanme brUhi pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . gItaM dRSTArthatattvena vAmadevena dhImatA .
rAjA vasumanA nAma jJAnavAn dhRtimAzuciH . maharSi paripapraccha vAmadevaM tapasvinam .
yena vRttena vai tiSThan na hIyeyaM svadharmataH .
tamabravId vAmadevastejasvI tapatAM varaH . hemavarNaM sukhAsInaM yayAtimiva nAhuSam .
vAsudeva uvAca dharmamevAnuvartasva na dharmAd vidyate param . dharme sthitA hi rAjAno jayanti pRthivImimAm .
arthasiddheH paraM dharmaM manyate yo mahIpatiH . vRddhyAM ca kurute buddhiM sa dharmeNa virAjate .
adharmadarzI yo rAjA balAdeva pravartate . kSipramevApayAto ' smAdubhau prathamamadhyamau .
asatpApiSThasacivo vadhyo lokasya dharmahA . sahaiva parivAreNa kSipramevAvasIdati .
arthAnAmananuSThAtA kAmacArI vikatyanaH . api sarvAM mahIM labdhvA kSiprameva vinazyati .
athAdadAnaH kalyANamanasUyurjitendriyaH . vardhate matimAn rAjA strotobhiriva sAgaraH .
na pUrNo ' smIti manyeta dharmataH kAmato ' rthataH . buddhito mitratazcApi satataM vasudhAdhipaH .
eteSveva hi sarveSu lokayAtrA pratiSThitA . etAni zRNvallabhate yazaH kIrti zriyaM prajAH .
evaM yo dharmasaMrambhI dharmArthaparicintakaH . arthAn samIkSya bhajate sa dhruvaM mahadaznute .
adAtA hyanatisneho daNDenAvartayan prajAH . sAhasaprakRtI rAjA kSiprameva vinazyati .
atha pApakRtaM buddhyA na ca pazyatyabuddhimAn . akIrtyAbhisamAyukto bhUyo narakamaznute .
atha mAnayiturdAmnaH zlakSNasya vazavartinaH . vyasanaM svamivotpannaM vijighAMsanti mAnavAH .
yasya nAsti gururdharme na cAnyAnapi pRcchati . sukhatantro ' rthalAbheSu na ciraM sukhamaznute .
gurupradhAno dharmeSu svayamarthAnavekSitA . dharmapradhAno lAbheSu sa ciraM sukhamaznute .
dhRtarASTra uvAca evaM bahuguNaM sainyamevaM pravicitaM balam . vyUDhamevaM yathAnyAyamevaM bahu ca saMjaya .
nityaM pUjitamasmAbhirabhikAmaM ca naH sadA . prauDhamatyadbhutAkAraM purastAd dRSTavikramam .
nAtivRddhamabAlaM ca nAkRzaM nAtipIvaram . laghuvRttAyataprAyaM sAragAtrapanAmayam . AttasaMnAhasaMchannaM bahuzastraparicchadam . zastragrahaNavidyAsu bahvISu pariniSThitam .
Arohe paryavaskande saraNe sAntaraplute . samyakpraharaNe yAne vyapayAne ca kovidam .
nAgeSvazveSu bahuzo ratheSu ca parIkSitam . parIkSya ca yathAnyAyaM vetanenopapAditam .
na goSThyA nopakAreNa na sambandhanimittataH . nAnAhUtaM nApyabhRtaM mama sainyaM babhUva ha .
kulInAryajanopetaM tuSTapuSTamanuddhatam . kRtamAnopacAraM ca yazakhi ca manakhi ca .
sacivaizcAparairmukhyairbahubhiH puNyakarmabhiH . lokapAlopamaistAta pAlitaM narasattamaiH .
bahubhiH pArthivairguptasmatpriyacikAryubhiH . asmAnabhisRtaiH kAmAt sabalaiH sapadAnugaiH .
mahodadhimivApUrNamApagabhiH samantataH . apakSaiH pakSisaMkAze rathairazvaizca saMvRtam .
prabhinnakaraTaizcaiva dviradairAvRtaM mahat . yadahanyata me sainyaM kimanyad bhAgadheyataH .
yodhAkSayyajalaM bhImaM vAhanormitaraGgiNam . kSepaNyasigadAzaktizaraprAsajhaSAkulam .
dhvajabhUSaNasambAgharatnopalasusaMcitam . vAhanairabhidhAvadbhirvAyuvegavikampitam .
droNagambhIrapAtAlaM kRtavarmamahAhradam . jalasaMdhamahAgrAhaM karNacandrodayoddhatam .
gate sainyArNavaM bhittvA tarasA pANDavarSabhe . saMjayaikarathenaiva yuyudhAne ca mAmakam .
tatra zeSaM na pazyAmi praviSTe savyasAcini . sAtvate ca rathodAre mama sainyasya saMjaya .
tau tatra samatikrAntau dRSTvAtIva tarakhinau . sindhurAjaM tu samprekSya gANDIvasyeSugocare .
kiM nu vA kuravaH kRtyaM vidadhuH kAlacoditAH . dAruNaikAyane kAlaM kathaM vA pratipedire .
grastAn hi kauravAn manye mRtyunA tAta saMgatAn . vikramo ' pi raNe teSAM na tathA dRzyate hi vai .
akSatau saMyuge tatra praviSTau kRSNapANDavau . na ca vArayitA kazcit tayorastIha saMjaya .
bhRtAzca bahavo yodhAH parIkSyaiva mahArathAH . vetanena yathAsogaM priyavAdena cApare .
asatkArabhRtastAta mama sainye na vidyate . karmaNA hyanurUpeNa labhyate bhaktavetanam .
na cAyodho ' bhavat kazcinmama sainye tu saMjaya . alpadAnabhRtastAta tathA cAbhRtako naraH .
pUjito hi yathAzaktyA dAnamAnAsanairmayA . tathA putraizca me tAta jJAtibhizca sabAndhavaiH .
te ca prApyaiva saMgrAme nirjitAH savyasAcinA . zaineyana parAmRSTAH kimanyad bhAgadheyataH .
rakSyate yazca saMgrAme ye ca saMjaya rakSiNaH . ekaH sAdhAraNaH panthA rakSyasya saha rakSibhiH .
arjunaM samare dRSTvA saindhavasyAgrataH sthitam . putro mama bhRzaM mUDhaH kiM kArya pratyapadyata .
sAtyakiM ca raNe dRSTvA pravizantamabhIvat . kiM nu duryodhanaH kRtyaM prAptakAlamamanyata .
sarvazastrAtigau senAM praviSTau rathitasattamau . dRSTvA kAM vai dhRti yuddhe pratyapadyanta mAmakAH .
dRSTvA kRSNaM tu dAzArhamarjunArthe vyavasthitam . zinInAmRSabhaM caiva manye zocanti putrakAH .
dRSTvA senAM vyatikrAntAM sAtvatenArjunena ca . palAyamAnAMzca kurUn manye zocanti putrakAH .
vidutAn rathino dRSTvA nirutsAhAn dviSajaye . palAyanakRtotsAhAn manye zocanti putrakAH .
zUnyAn kRtAn rathopasthAn sAtvatenArjunena ca . hatAMzca yodhAn saMdRzya manye zocanti putrakAH .
vyazvanAgarathAn dRSTvA tatra vIrAn sahasrazaH . dhAvamAnAn raNe vyagrAn manye zocanti putrakAH .
mahAnAgAn vidravato dRSTvArjunazarAhatAn . patitAn patatazcAnyAn manye zocanti putrakAH .
vihInAMzca kRtAnazvAn visthAMzca kRtAn narAn . tatra sAtyakipArthAbhyAM manye zocanti putrakAH .
hayaudhAn nihatAn dRSTvA dravamANAMstatastataH . raNe mAdhavapArthAbhyAM manye zocanti putrakAH .
pattisaMghAn raNe dRSTvA dhAvamAnAMzca sarvazaH . nirAzA vijaye sarve manye zocanti putrakAH .
droNasya samatikrAntAvanIkamaparAjitau . kSaNena dRSTvA tau vIrau manye zocanti putrakAH .
sammUDho ' smi bhRzaM tAta zrutvA kRSNadhanaMjayau . praviSTau mAmakaM sainyaM sAtvatena sahAcyutau .
tasmin praviSTe pRtanAM zinInAM pravare rathe . bhojAnIkaM vyatikrAnte kimakurvata kauravAH . .
tathA droNena samare nigRhIteSu pANDuSu . kathaM yuddhamabhUt tatra tanmamAcakSva saMjaya .
droNo hi balavAzreSThaH kRtAstro yuddhadurmadaH . paJcAlAste maheSvAsaM pratyavidhyan kathaM raNe .
paddhavairAstato droNe dhanaMjayajayaiSiNA . bhAradvAjasutasteSu dRDhavairo mahArathaH .
arjunazcApi yacakre sindhurAjavadhaM prati . tanme sarva samAcakSva kuzalo hyasi saMjaya .
saMjaya utAca AtmAparAdhAt sambhUtaM vyasanaM bharatarSabha . prApya prAkRtavad vIra na tvaM zocitumarhasi .
purA yaducyase prAjJaiH suhRdbhirvidurAdibhiH . mA hArSIH pANDavAn rAjaniti tanna tvayA zrutam .
suhRdAM hitakAmAnAM vAkyaM yo na zRNoti ha . samahad vyasanaM prApya zocate vaiyathAbhavAn .
yAcito ' si purA rAjan dAzArheNa zamaM prati . na ca taM labdhavAn kAmaM tvattaH kRSNomahAyazAH .
tava nigurNatAM jJAtvA pakSapAtaM suteSu ca . dvaidhIbhAvaM tathA dharme pANDaveSu ca matsaram .5 tava jihmamabhiprAyaM viditvA pANDavAn prati . AprilApAMzca bahUn manujAdhipasattama .
sarvalokasya tattvajJaH sarvalokezvaraH prabhuH . vAsudevastato yuddhaM kurUNAmakaronmahat .
AtmAparAdhAt sumahAn prAptaste vipulaH kSayaH . nainaM duryodhane doSaM kartumarhasi mAnada .
na hi te sukRtaM kiMcidAdau madhye ca bhArata . dRzyate pRSThatazcaiva tvanmUlo hi parAjayaH .
tasmAdavasthito bhUtvA jJAtvA lokasya nirNayam . zRNu yuddhaM yathAvRttaM ghoraM devAsuropamam .
praviSTe tava sainyaM ta zaineya satyavikrame . bhImasenamukhAH pArthAH pratIyurvAhinIM tava .
AgacchatastAn sahasA kruddharUpAn sahAnugAn . dadhAraiko raNe pANDUn kRtavarmA mahArathaH .
yathodvattaM vArayate velA vai salilArNavam . pANDusainyaM tathA saMkhye hArdikyaH samavArayat .
tatrAdbhutamapazyAma hArdikyasya parAkramam . yadenaM sahitAH pArthA nAticakramurAhave .
tato bhImastribhirviddhavA kRtavarmANamAzugaiH . zaGkha dadhmau mahAbAhurharpayan sarvapANDavAn .
sahadevastu viMzatyA dharmarAjazca paJcabhiH . zatena nakulazcApi hArdikyaM samavidhyata .
draupadeyAstrisaptatyA saptabhizca ghaTotkacaH . dhRSTadyumnastribhizcApi kRtavarmANamArdayat .
virATo drupadazcaiva yAjJasenizca paJcabhiH . zikhaNDI caiva hArdikyaM viddhavA paJcabhirAzugaiH .
punarvivyAdha viMzatyA sAyakAnAM hasanniva . kRtavarmA tato rAjan sarvatastAn mahArathAn . ekaikaM paJcabhirviddhavA bhImaM vivyAdha saptabhiH . dhanurdhvajaM cAsya tathA rathAd bhUmAvapAtayat .
athainaM chinnadhanvAnaM tvaramANo mahArathaH . AjaghAnorasi kruddhaH saptatyA nizitaiH zaraiH .
sa gADhaviddho balavAn hArdikyasya zarottamaiH . cacAla sthamadhyasthaH kSitikampe yathAcalaH .
bhImasenaM tathA dRSTvA dharmarAjapurogamAH . visRjantaH zarAn rAjan kRtavarmANamArdayan .
taM kathA koSThakIkRtya rathavaMzena mAriSa . vivyadhuH sAyakaiISTA rakSArtha mAruterpadhe .
pratilabhya tataH saMjJAM bhImaseno mahAbalaH . zaktiM jagrAha samare hemadaNDAmayasmayIm .
cikSepa ca rathAt tUrNa kRtavarmarathaM prati . sA bhImabhujanirmuktA nirmuktoragasaMnibhA .
kRtavarmANamabhitaH prajajvAla sudAruNA . tAmApatantI sahasA yugAntAgnisamaprabhAm .
dvAbhyAM zarAbhyAM hArdikyo nijaghAna dvidhA tadA . sA chinnA patitA bhUmau zaktiH kanakabhUSaNA .
dyotayantI dizo rAjan maholkeva nabhazcayutA . zaktiM vinihatAM dRSTvA bhImazcukrodha vaibhRzam .
tato ' nyad dhanurAdAya vegavat sumahAsvanam . bhImaseno raNe kruddho hArdikyaM samavArayat .
athainaM paJcabhirbANairAjadhAna stanAntare . bhImo bhImabalo rAjaMstva durmatritena ca .
bhojastu kSatasarvAGgo bhImasenena mAriSa . raktAzoka ivotphullo vyabhrAjata raNAjire .
tataH kruddhastribhirbANaibhImasenaM hasanniva . abhihatya dRDhaM yuddhe tAn sarvAn pratyavidhyata .
tribhistribhirmaheSvAso yatamAnAn mahArathAn . te ' pi taM pratyavidhyanta saptabhiH saptabhiH zaraiH .
zikhaNDinastataH kruddhaH kSurapreNa mahArathaH . dhanuzciccheda samare prahasanniva sAtvataH .
zikhaNDI tu tataH kruddhazchinne dhanuSi satvaraH . asiM jagrAha samare zatacandraM ca bhAkharam .
bhrAmayitvA mahacarma cAmIkaravibhUSitam . tamasiM preSayAmAsa kRtavarmarathaM prati .
sa tasya sazaraM cApaM chittvA rAjan mahAnasiH . abhyagAd dharaNI rAjaMzcyutaM jyotirivAmbarAt .
etasminneva kAle tu tvaramANaM mahArathAH . vivyadhuH sAyakairgADhaM kRtavarmANamAhave .
athAnyad dhanurAdAya tyaktvA taca mahad dhanuH . vizIrNa bharatazreSTha hArdikyAH paravIrahA .
vivyAdha pANDavAn yuddhe tribhistribhirajihmagaiH . zikhaNDinaM ca vivyAdha tribhiH paJcabhireva ca .
dhanuranyat samAdAya zikhaNDI tu mahAyazAH . avArayan kUrmanakhairAzugairhakitmajam .
tataH kruddho raNe rAjan hRdikasyAtmasambhavaH . abhidudrAva vegena yAjJaseniM mahAratham .
bhISmasya samare rAjan mRtyorhatuM mahAtmanaH . vidarzayan balaM zUraH zArdUla iva kuJjaram .
tau dizAM gajasaMkAzau jvalitAviva pAvakau . samApetaturanyonyaM zarasaGgharariMdamau .
vidhunvAnau dhanuHzreSThe saMdadhAnau ca sAyakAn . visRjantau ca zatazo gabhastIniva bhAsvarau .
tApayantau zaraistIkSNairanyonyaM tau mahArathau . yugAntapratimau vIrau rejaturbhAskarAviva .
kRtavarmA ca samare yAjJaseniM mahAratham . viddhveSubhistrisaptasyA punarvivyAgha saptabhiH .
sa gADhaviddho vyathito rathopastha upAvizat . virAjya sazaraM cApaM mUrcchayAbhipariplutaH .
taM viSaNNaM raNe dRSTvA tAvakAH puruSarSabha . hArdikyaM pUjayAmAsurvAsAMsyAdudhuvuzca ha .
zikhaNDinaM tathA jJAtvA hArdikyazarapIDitam . apovAha raNAd yantA tvaramANo mahAratham .
sAditaM tu rathopasthe dRSTvA pArthAH zikhaNDinam . parivravU rathaistUrNaM kRtavarmANamAhave .
tatrAdbhutaM paraM cakre kRtavarmA mahArathaH . yadekaH samare pArthAn vArayAmAsa sAnugAn .
pArthAJjitvAjayacedIn paJcAlAn sRJjayAnapi . kekayAMzca mahAvIryAn kRtavarmA mahArathaH .
te vadhyamAnAH samare hArdikyena sma pANDavAH . itazcetazca dhAvanto naiva cakrutiM raNe .
jitvA pANDusutAn yuddhe bhImasenapurogamAn . hArdikyaH samare ' tiSThad vidhUma iva pAvakaH .
te drAvyamANAH samare hArdikyena mahArathAH . vimukhAH samapadyanta zaravRSTibhirArditAH .
vaizampAyana uvAca vanaM praviSTaSvatha pANDaveSu prajJAcakSustapyamAno ' mbikeyaH . dharmAtmAnaM viduramagAdhabuddhiM sukhAsIno vAkyamuvAca rAjA .
dhRtarASTra uvAca prajJA ca te bhArgavasyeva zuddhA dharma ca tvaM paramaM vettha sUkSmam . samazca tvaM sammataH kauravANAM pathyaM caiSAM mama caiva bravIhi .
evaMgate vidura yadadya kArya paurAzca me kathamasmAn bhajeran . stattvaM brUyAH sAdhu kAryANi vetsi .
vidura uvAca trivargo ' yaMdharmamUlo narendra rAjyaM cedaMdharmamUlaM vadanti . dharme rAjan vartamAnaH svazaktyA putrAna sarvAn pAhi pANDoH sutAMzca .
sa vaidharmo vipralabdhaH sabhAyAM pApAtmabhiH saubaleyapradhAnaiH . AhUya kuntIsutamakSavatyAM parAjaiSIt satyasaMdhaM sutaste .
cheSasyAhaM paripazyAmyupAyam . mukto loke pratitiSTheta sAdhu .
tad vai sarvaM pANDuputrA labhantAM yat tad rAjannabhisRSTaM tvayA ' ' sIt . eSadharmaH paramo yat svakena rAjA tuSyenna parasveSu gRdhyet .
yazo na nazyejjJAtibhedazca na syAd dharmo na syAnaiva caivaM kRte tvAm . etat kAryaM tava sarvapradhAna teSAM tuSTiH zakunezcAvamAnaH .
detad rAjaMstvaramANaH kuruSva . tathaitadevaM na karoSi rAjan dhruvaM kurUNAM bhavitA vinAzaH .
na hi kruddho bhImaseno ' rjuno vA zeSaM kuryAcchAtravANAmanIke . yeSAM yoddhA savyasAcI kRtAstro dhanuryeSAM gANDivaM lokasAram . yeSAM bhImo bAhuzAlI ca yoddhA teSAM loke kiM nu na prApyamasti . uktaM pUrvaM jAtamAtre sute te mayA yat te hitamAsIt tadAnIm .
putraM tyajemamahitaM kulasya hitaM paraM na ca tat tvaM cakartha . mevaM kartA paritaptAsi pazcAt .
yadyetadevamanumantA sutaste samprIyamANaH pANDavairekarAjyam . na cennigRhaNISva sutaM sukhAya .
duryodhanaM tvahitaM vai nigRhya pANDoH putraM kuruSvAdhipatye . ajAtazatrurhi vimuktarAgo dharmeNemAM pRthivIM zAstu rAjan . duHzAsano
tato rAjan pArthivAH sarva eva vaizyA ivAsmAnupatiSThantu sadyaH . duryodhanaH zakuniH sUtaputraH prItyA rAjan pANDuputrAn bhajantu .
yAcatu bhImasenaM sabhAmadhye dupadasyAtmajAM ca . yudhiSThiraM tvaM parisAntvayasva rAjye cainaM sthApayasvAbhipUjya .
metat kRtvA kRtakRtyo ' si rAjan .
dhRtarASTra uvAca miha proktaM pANDavAn prApya mAM ca . metat sarvaM mama nAvaiti cetaH .
idaM tvidAnI gata eva nizcitaM teSAmarthe pANDavAnAM yadAstha ! tenAdya manye nAsi hito mameti kathaM hi putraM pANDavArthe tyajeyam .
asaMzayaM te ' pi mamaiva putrA duryodhanastu mama dehAt prasUtaH . svaM vai dehaM parahetostyajota ko nu brUyAt samatAmanvavekSya .
sa mAM jihyaM vidura sarvaM bravISi mAnaM ca te ' hamadhikaMdhArayAmi . yathecchakaM gaccha vA tiSTha vA tvaM susAntvyamAnApyasatI strI jahAti .
vaizampAyana uvAca dantarvezma sahasotthAya rAjan . nedamastItyatha viduro bhASamANaH samprAdravad yatra pArthA babhUvuH .
yudhiSThira uvAca asmAnabhiAtAMstAta bhayArtAJcharaNaiSiNaH . kauravAn viSamaprAptAn kathaM brUyAstvamIdRzam .
yadA tu bhavanti bhedA jJAtInAM kalahAzca vRkodara . prasaktAni ca vairANi kuladharmo na nazyati .
kazcijjJAtInAM bAhyaH pothayate kulam . na marSayanti tat santo bAhyenAbhipradharSaNam .
jAnAtyeSa hi durbuddhirasmAniha ciroSitAn . sa evaM paribhUyAsmAnakAdidamapriyam .
duryodhanasya grahaNAd gandharveNa balAt prabho . strINAM bAhyAbhimarzAcca hataM bhavati naH kulam .
zaraNaM ca prapannAnAM trANArthaM ca kulasya ca . uttiSThata naravyAghrAH sajjIbhavata mA ciram .
arjunazca yamau caiva tvaM ca vIrAparAjitaH . mokSayadhvaM naravyAghrA hriyamANaM suyodhanam .
