tatra puSpodakA nAma nadI teSAM vidhIyate . zItalaM salilaM tatra pibanti hyamRtopamam .
ye ca duSkRtakarmANaH pUyaM teSAM vidhIyate . evaM nadI mahArAja sarvakAmapradA hi sA .
tasmAt tvamapi rAjendra pUjayanAn yathAvidhi . adhvani kSINagAtrazca pathi pAMsusamanvitaH . pRcchate hyannadAtAraM gRhamAyAti cAzayA . taM pUjayAtha yatnena so ' tithirbrAhmaNazca saH .
taM yAntamanugacchanti devAH sarve savAsavAH . tasmin sampUjite prItA nirAzA yAntyapUjite .
tasmAt tvamapi rAjendra pUjayainaM yathAvidhi . etat te zatazaH proktaM kiM bhUyaH zrotumicchasi .
yudhiSThira uvAca punaH punarahaM zrotuM kathAM dharmasamAzrayAm . puNyAmicchAmi dharmajJa kathyamAnAM tvayA vibho .
mArkaNDeya uvAca dharmAntaraM prati kathAM kathyamAnAM mayA nRpa . sarvapApaharAM nityaM zRNuSvAvahito mama .
kapilAyAM tu dattAyAM yat phalaM jyeSThapuSkare . tat phalaM bharatazreSTha viprANAM pAdadhAvane .
dvijapAdodakaklinnA yAvat tiSThati medinI . tAvat puSkaraparNena pibanti pitaro jalam .
svAgatenAgnayastRptA Asanena zatakratuH . pitaraH pAdazaucena annAdyena prajApatiH .
yAvad vatsasya vai pAdau zirazcaiva pradRzyate . tasmin kAle pradAtavyA prayatnenAntarAtmanA . antarikSagato vatso yAvad yonyAM pradRzyate . tAvad gau pRthivI jJeyA yAvad garbhaM na muJcati .
yAvanti tasyA romANi vatsasya ca yudhiSThira . tAvad yugasahasrANi svargaloke mahIyate .
suvarNanAsAM yaH kRtvA sukhurAM kRSNadhenukAm . tilaiH pracchAditAM dadyAt sarvaratnairalaMkRtAm .
pratigrahaM gRhItvA yaH punardadati sAdhave . phalAnAM phalamaznAti tadA dattvA ca bhArata . sasamudraguhA tena sazailavanakAnanA . caturantA bhaved datta pRthivI nAtra saMzayaH .
antarjAnuzayo yastu bhuGkte saMsaktabhAjanaH . yo dvijaH zabdarahitaM sa kSamastAraNAya vai .
apAnapA na gaditAstathAnye ye dvijAtayaH . japanti saMhitAM samyak te nityaM tAraNakSamAH .
havyaM kavyaM ca yat kiMcit sarvaM tacchrotriyo ' rhati . dattaM hi zrotriye sAdhau jvalite ' gnau yathA hutam .
manyupraharaNA viprA na viprAH zastrayodhinaH . nihanyurmanyunA viprA vajrapANirivAsurAn .
dharmAzriteyaM ta kathA kathiteyaM tavAnagha . yAM zrutvA munayaH prItA naimiSAraNyavAsinaH .
vItazokabhayakrodhA vipApmAnastathaiva ca . zrutvemAM tu kathAM rAjan na bhavantIha mAnavAH .
yudhiSThira uvAca kiM tacchaucaM bhaved yena vipraH zuddhaH sadA bhavet . tadicchAmi mahAprAjJa zrotuM dharmabhRtAM vara .
mArkaNDeya uvAca vAk zaucaM karmazaucaM ca yacca zaucaM jalAtmakam . tribhiH zaucairupeto yaH sa svargI nAtra saMzayaH .
sAyaM prAtazca saMdhyAM yo brAhmaNo ' bhyupasevate . prajapan pAvanI devIM gAyatrI vedamAtaram . sa tayA pAvito devyA brAhmaNo naSTakilbiSaH . na sIdet pratigRhaNano mahImapi sasAgarAm .
ye cAsya dAruNAH kecid grahAH sUryAdayo divi . te cAsya saumyA jAyante zivAH zivatarAH sadA .
cainaM dAruNAH pizitAzanAH . ghorarUpA mahAkAyA dharSayanti dvijottamam .
nAdhyApanAd yAjanAd vA anyasmAd vA pratigrahAt . doSo bhavati viprANAM jvalitAgnisamA dvijAH .
sarve nAnugataM durvedA vA suvedA vA prAkRtAH saMskRtAstathA . brAhmaNA nAvamantavyA bhasmacchannA ivAgnayaH .
yathA zmazAne dIptaujAH pAvako naiva duSyati . evaM vidvAnavidvAn vA brAhmaNo daivataM mahat .
prAkAraizca puradvAraiH prAsAdaizca pRthagvidhaiH . nagarANi na zobhante hInAni brAhmaNottamaiH .
vedADhyA vRttasampannA jJAnavantastapasvinaH . yatra tiSThati vai viprAstannAma nagaraM nRpa .
vraje vApyathavAraNye yatra santi bahuzrutAH . tat tannagaramityAhuH pArtha tIrthaM ca tad bhavet .
rakSitAraM ca rAjAnaM brAhmaNaM ca tapasvinam . abhigamyAbhipUjyAtha sadyaH pApAt pramucyate .
puNyatIrthAbhiSekaM ca pavitrANAM ca kIrtanam . sadbhiH sambhASaNaM caiva prazastaM kIrtyate budhaiH .
sAdhusaGgamapUtena vAksubhASitavAriNA . pavitrIkRtamAtmAnaM santo manyanti nityazaH .
tridaNDadhAraNaM maunaM jaTAbhAro ' tha muNDanam . valkalAjina saMveSTaM vratacaryAbhiSecanam . agnihotraM vane vAsaH zarIraparizoSaNam . sarvANyetAni mithyA syuryadi bhAvo na nirmalaH .
na duSkaramanAzitvaM sukara hyazanaM vinA . vizuddhiM cakSurAdInAM SaNNAmindriyagAminAm .
vikAri teSAM rAjendra suduSkarakaraM manaH . ye pApAni na kurvanti manovAkkarmabuddhibhiH . te tapanti mahAtmAno na zarIrasya zoSaNam .
na jJAtibhyo dayA yasya zukladeho ' vikalmaSaH . hiMsA sA tapasastasya nAnAzitvaM tapaH smRtam .
tiSThan gRhe caiva munirnityaM zuciralaMkRtaH . yAvajjIvaM dayAvAMzca sarvapApaiH pramucyate .
na hi pApAni karmANi zuddhyantyanazanAdibhiH . sIdatyanazanAdeva mAMsazoNitalepanaH .
ajJAtaM karma kRtvA ca klezo nAnyat prahIyate . nAgnirdahati karmANi bhAvazUnyasya dehinaH .
puNyAdeva pravrajanti zuddhyantyanazanAni ca . na mUlaphalabhakSitvAnna maunAnnAnilAzanAt . ziraso muNDanAd vApi na sthAnakuTikAsanAt . na jaTAdhAraNAd vApi na tu sthaNDilazayyayA . nityaM hyanazanAd vApi nAgnizuzrUSaNAdapi . na codakapravezena na ca kSamAzayanAdapi .
jJAnena karmaNA vApi jarAmaraNameva ca . vyAdhayazca prahIyante prApyate cottamaM padam .
bIjAni hyagnidagdhAni na rohanti punaryathA . jJAnadagdhaistathA klezairnAtmA saMyujyate punaH .
AtmanA viprahINAni kASThakuDyopamAni ca . vinazyanti na saMdehaH phenAnIva mahArNave .
AtmAnaM vindate yena sarvabhUtaguhAzayam . zlokena yadi vArdhena kSINaM tasya prayojanam .
vyakSarAdabhisaMdhAya kecicchlokapadAGkitaiH . zatairanyaiH sahasrazca pratyayo mokSalakSaNam .
nAyaM loko ' sti na paro na sukhaM saMzayAtmanaH . UcurjJAnavido vRddhAH pratyayo mokSalakSaNam .
viditArthastu vedAnAM pariveda prayojanam . udvijet sa tu vedebhyo dAvAgneriva mAnavaH .
zuSkaM tarkaM parityajya Azrayasva zrutiM smRtim . ekAkSarAbhisambaddhaM tattvaM hetubhiricchasi . buddhirna tasya siddhyeta sAdhanasya viparyayAt .
vedapUrvaM veditavyaM prayatnAt tad vai vedastasya vedaH zarIram . vedastattvaM tatsamAsopalabdhau klIbastvAtmA tat sa vedyasya vedyam .
vedoktamAyurdevAnAmAziSazcaiva karmaNAm . phalatyanuyugaM loke prabhAvazca zarIriNAm .
indriyANAM prasAdena tadetat parivarjayet . tasmAdanazanaM divyaM niruddhendriyagocaram .
tapasA svargagamanaM bhogo dAnena jAyate . jJAnena mokSo vijJeyastIrthasnAnAdadhakSayaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktastu rAjendra pratyuvAca mahAyazAH . bhagavan zrotumicchAmi pradhAnavidhimuttamam .
mArkaNDeya uvAca yat tvamicchasi rAjendra dAnadharmaM yudhiSThira . iSTaM cedaM sadA mahyaM rAjan gauravatastathA .
zRNu dAnarahasyAni zrutismRtyuditAni ca . chAyAyAM kariNaH zrAddhaM tat karNaparivIjite . daza kalpAyutAnIha na kSIyeta yudhiSThira .
jIvanAya samAklinnaM vasu dattvA mahIyate . vaizyaM tu vAsayed yastu sarvayajJaiH sa iSTavAn .
pratisrotazcitravAhAH parjanyo ' nnAnusaMcaran . mahAdhuri yathA nAvA mahApApaiH pramucyate .
viplave vipradattAni dadhimastvakSayANi ca . parvasu dviguNaM dAnamRtau dazaguNaM bhavet .
ayane viSuve caiva SaDazItimukheSu ca . candrasUryoparAge ca dattamakSayamucyate .
RtuSu dazaguNaM vadanti dattaM zataguNamRtvayanAdiSu dhruvam . rviSuvati cAkSayamaznute phalam .
nAbhUmido bhUmimaznAti rAjan nAyAnado yAnamAruhya yAti . yAn yAn kAmAn brAhmaNebhyo dadAti tAMstAn kAmAn jAyamAnaH sa bhuGkte .
agnerapatyaM prathamaM suvarNa bhUvaiSNavI sUryasutAzca gAvaH . lokAstrayastena bhavanti dattA yaH kAJcanaM gAzca mahIM ca dadyAt .
paraM hi dAnAnna babhUva zAzvattaM bhavyaM triloke bhavate kutaH punaH . tasmAt pradhAnaM paramaM hi dAnaM vadanti lokeSu viziSTabuddhayaH .
vasiSTha uvAca evamapratibuddhatvAdabuddhajanasevanAt . sargakoTisahasrANi patanAntAni gacchati .
dhAmnA dhAmasahasrANi maraNAntAni gacchati . tiryagyonimanuSyatve devaloke tathaiva ca . .
candramA iva bhUtAnAM punastatra sahasrazaH . lIyate ' pratibuddhatvAdevameSa hyabuddhimAn . kalA paJcadazI yonistaddhAma pratibudhyate . nityametad vijAnIhi somaM vai SoDazI kalAm .
kalAyAM jAyate ' jasraM punaH punarabuddhimAn . dhAma tasyopayuJjanti bhUya evopajAyate .
SoDazI tu kalA sUkSmA sa soma upadhAryatAm . na tUpayujyate devairdevAnupayunakti sA .
etAmakSapayitvA hi jAyate nRpasattama . sA hyasya prakRtirdRSTA tatkSayAnmokSa ucyate .
tadeva SoDazakalaM dehamavyaktasaMjJakam . mamAyamiti manvAnastatraiva parivartate . paJcaviMzo mahAnAtmA tasyaivApratibodhanAt . vimalasya vizuddhasya zuddhAzuddhaniSevaNAt . azuddha eva zuddhAtmA tAdRg bhavati pArthiva . abuddhasevanAccApi buddho ' ' pyabuddhatAM vrajet .
tathaivApratibuddho ' pi vijJeyo nRpasattama . prakRtestriguNAyAstu sevanAt triguNo bhavet .
bhISma uvAca punarbharatavaMzasya hetuM saMtAnavRddhaye . vakSyAmi niyataM mAtastanme nigadataH zRNu . brAhmaNo guNavAn kazcid dhanenopanimantryatAm . vicitravIryakSetreSu yaH samutpAdayet prajAH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tataH satyavatI bhISmaM vAcA saMsajamAnayA . vihasantIva sanIDamidaM vacanamabravIt .
satyavatI uvAca satyametanmahAbAho yathA vadasi bhArata . vizvAsAt te pravakSyAmi saMtAnAya kulasya naH .
na te zakyamanAkhyAtumApaddharmaM tathAvidham . tvameva naH kule dharmastvaM satyaM tvaM parA gatiH .
tasmAnizamya satyaM me kuruSva yadanantaram . dharmayuktasya dharmArthaM piturAsIt tarI mama .
sA kadAcidahaM tatra gatA prathamayauvanam . atha dharmavidAM zreSThaH paramarSiH parAzaraH . AjagAma tarI dhImAMstariSyan yamunA nadIm . sa tAryamANo yamunAM mAmupetyAbravIt tadA . sAntvapUrvaM munizreSThaH kAmArto madhuraM vacaH . uktaM janma kulaM mahyamasmi dAzasutetyaham .
tamahaM zApabhItA ca piturbhItA ca bhArata . varairasulabhairuktA na pratyAkhyAtumutsahe .
abhibhUya sa mAM bAlAM tejasA vazamAnayat . tamasA lokamAvRtya naugatAmeva bhArata . matsyagandho mahAnAsIt purA mama jugupsitaH . tamapAsya zubhaM gandhamimaM prAdAt sa me muniH .
tato mAmAha sa munirgarbhamutsRjya mAmakam . dvIpe ' syA eva saritaH kanyaiva tvaM bhaviSyasi .
pArAzaryo mahAyogI sa babhUva mahAnRSiH . kanyAputro mama purA dvaipAyana iti zrutaH .
yo vyasya vedAMzcaturastapasA bhagavAnRSiH . loke vyAsatvamApede kAryAt kRSNatvameva ca .
satyavAdI zamaparastapasvI dagdhakilbiSaH . samutpannaH sa tu mahAn saha pitrA tato gataH .
sa niyukto mayA vyaktaM tvayA cApratimadyutiH . bhrAtuH kSetreSu kalyANamapatyaM janayiSyati .
sa hi mAmuktavAMstatra smareH kRcchreSu mAmiti . taM smariSye mahAbAho yadi bhISma tvamicchasi .
tava hanumate bhISma niyataM sa mahAtapAH . vicitravIryakSetreSu putrAnutpAdayiSyati .
vaizampAyana uvAca maharSeH kIrtane tasya bhISmaH prAJjalirabravIt . dharmamarthaM ca kAmaM ca trInetAn yo ' nupazyati . arthamarthAnubandhaM ca dharmaM dharmAnubandhanam . kAmaM kAmAnubandhaM ca viparItAn pRthak pRthak . yo vicintya dhiyA dhIro vyavasyati sa buddhimAn . tadidaM dharmayuktaM ca hitaM caiva kulasya naH . uktaM bhavatyA yacchreyastanmahyaM rocate bhRzam .
vaizampAyana uvAca tatastasmin pratijJAte bhISmeNa kurunandana . kRSNadvaipAyanaM kAlI cintayAmAsa vai munim . sa vedAn vibruvan dhImAn mAturvijJAya cintitam . prAdurbabhUvAviditaH kSaNena kurunandana . tasmai pUjAM tataH kRtvA sutAya vidhipUrvakam . pariSvajya ca bAhubhyAM prasravairabhyaSiJcatA mumoca bASpaM dAzeyI putraM dRSTvA cirasya tu .
tAmadbhiH pariSicyArtA maharSirabhivAdya ca . mAtaraM pUrvaja : putro vyAso vacanamabravIt .
bhavatyA yadabhipretaM tadahaM kartumAgataH . zAdhi mAM dharmatattvajJe karavANi priyaM tava .
tasmai pUjAM tato ' kArSIt purodhAH paramarSaye . sa ca tAM pratijagrAha vidhivanmantrapUrvakam .
pUjito mantrapUrvaM tu vidhivat prItimApa saH . tamAsanagataM mAtA pRSTvA kuzalamavyayam . satyavatyatha vIkSyainamuvAcedamanantaram .
mAtApitroH prajAyante putrAH sAdhAraNAH kave . teSAM pitA yathA svAmI tathA mAtA na saMzayaH . vidhAnavihitaH satyaM yathA me prathamaH sutaH . vicitravIryo brahmarSe tathA me ' varajaH sutaH . yathaiva pitRto bhISmastathA tvamapi mAtRtaH . bhrAtA vicitravIryasya yathA vA putra manyase . ayaM zAntanavaH satyaM pAlayan satyavikramaH . buddhiM na kurute ' patye tathA rAjyAnuzAsane . sa tvaM vyapekSayA bhrAtuH saMtAnAya kulasya ca .
bhISmasya cAsya vacanAniyogAcca mamAnagha . anukrozAca bhUtAnAM sarveSAM rakSaNAya ca . AnRzaMsyAca yad brUyAM tacchutvA kartumarhasi . yavIyasastava bhrAturbhArye surasutopame . rUpayauvanasampanne putrakAme ca dharmataH . tayorutpAdayApatyaM samartho hyasi putraka . anurUpaM kulasyAsya saMtatyAH prasavasya ca .
vyAsa uvAca vettha dharmaM satyavati paraM cAparameva ca . tathA tava mahAprAjJe dharme praNihitA matiH . tasmAdahaM tvanniyogAd dharmamuddizya kAraNam . IpsitaM te kariSyAmi dRSTaM hyetat sanAtanam . bhrAtuH putrAn pradAsyAmi mitrAvaruNayoH samAn .
vrataM caretAM te devyau nirdiSTamiha yanmayA . saMvatsaraM yathAnyAyaM tataH zuddhe bhaviSyataH . na hi mAmavratopetA upeyAt kAcidaGganA .
satyavatyuvAca sadyo yathA prapadyete devyau garbhaM tathA kuru . arAjakeSu rASTreSu prajAnAthA vinazyati . nazyanti ca kriyAH sarvA nAsti vRSTirna devatA .
kathaM cArAjakaM rASTra zakyaM dhArayituM prabho . tasmAd garbha samAdhatsva bhISmaH saMvardhayiSyati .
vyAsa uvAca yadi putraH pradAtavyo mayA bhrAturakAlikaH . virUpatAM me sahatAM tayoretat paraM vratam .
yadi me sahate gandhaM rUpaM veSaM tathA vapuH . adyaiva garbha kausalyA viziSTaM pratipadyatAm .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktvA mahAtejA vyAsaH satyavatIM tadA . zayane sA ca kausalyA zucivastrA hyalaMkRtA . samAgamanamAkA diti so ' ntarhito muniH . tato ' bhigamya sA devI snuSAM rahasi saMgatAm . dharmyamarthasapAyuktamuvAca vacanaM hitam . kausalye dharmatantraM tvAM yad bravImi nibodha tat .
bharatAnAM samucchedo vyaktaM madbhAgyasaMkSayAt . vyathitAM mAM ca samprekSya pitRvaMzaM ca pIDitam . bhISmo buddhimadAnmahyaM kulasyAsya vivRddhaye . sA ca buddhistvayyadhInA putri prApaya mAM tathA . naSTaM ca bhArataM vaMzaM punareva samuddhara . putraM janaya suzroNi devarAjasamaprabham . sa hi rAjyadhuraM gurvImudvakSyati kulasya naH .
sA dharmato ' nunIyainAM kathaMcid dharmacAriNIm . bhojayAmAsa viprAMzca devarSInatithIMstathA .
vaizampAyana uvAca ajinAni vidhu - vantaH karakAMzca dvijarSabhAH . Ucuste bhIrna kartavyA vayaM yotsyAmahe parAn .
tAnevaM vadato viprAnarjunaH prahasanniva . uvAca prekSakA bhUtvA yUyaM tiSThatha pArzvataH .
ahamenAnajihmAtraiH zatazo vikirajcharaiH . vArayiSyAmi saMkruddhAn mantrairAzIvipAniva .
iti tad dhanurAnamya zulkAvAptaM mahAbalaH . bhrAtrA bhImena sahitastasthau giririvAcalaH .
tataH karNamukhAn dRSTvA kSatriyAn yuddhadurmadAn . sampetaturabhItau tau gajau pratigajAniva .
Ucuzca vAcaH parupAste rAjAno yuyutsavaH . Ahave hi dvijasyApi vadho dRSTo yuyutsataH .
ityevamuktvA rAjAnaH sahasA dudrubuddhijAn . tataH karNo mahAtejA jiSNuM prati yayau raNe .
yuddhArthI vAsitAhetorgajaH pratigajaM yathA . bhImasenaM yayau zalya madrANAmIzvaro balI .
duryodhanAdayaH sarve brAhmaNaiH saha saMgatAH . mRdupUrvamayatnena pratyayudhyaMstadAhave .
tato ' rjunaH pratyavidhyadApatantaM zitaiH zaraiH . karNaM vaikartanaM zrImAn vikRSya balavad dhanuH .
teSAM zarANAM vegena zitAnAM tigmatejasAm . vimuhyamAno rAdheyo yatnAt tamanudhAvati .
tAvubhAvapyanirdezyau lAghavAjjayatAM varau . ayudhyetAM susaMrabdhAvanyonyavijigISiNau .
kRte pratikRtaM pazya pazya bAhubalaM ca me . iti zUrArthavacanairabhASetAM parasparam .
tato ' rjunasya bhujayorvIryamapratimaM bhuvi . jJAtvA vaikartanaH karNaH saMrabdhaH samayodhayat .
arjunena prayuktAMstAn bANAn vegavatastadA . pratihatya nanAdoccaiH sainyAni tadapUjayan .
karNa uvAca tuSyAmi te vipramukhya bhujavIryasya saMyuge . aviSAdasya caivAsya zastrAstravijayasya ca .
kiM tvaM sAkSAd dhanurvedo rAmo vA viprasattama . atha sAkSAddharihayaH sAkSAd vA viSNuracyutaH .
AtmapracchAdanArthaM vai bAhuvIryamupAzritaH . viprarUpaM vidhAyedaM manye mAM pratiyudhyase .
na hi mAmAhave kruddhamanyaH sAkSAcchacIpateH . pumAn yodhayituM zaktaH pANDavAd vA kirITinaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tamevaM vAdinaM tatra phAlgunaH pratyabhASata . nAsmi karNa dhanurvedo nAsmi rAmaH pratApavAn .
brAhmaNo ' smi yudhAM zreSThaH sarvazastrabhRtAM varaH . brAhme pauraMdare cAstre niSThito guruzAsanAt .
sthito ' smyadya raNe jetuM tvAM vai vIra sthiro bhava . evamuktastu rAdheyo yuddhAt karNo nyavartata .
brAhyaM tejastadAjayyaM manyamAno mahArathaH . aparasmin vanoddeze vIrau zalyavRkodarau .
balinau yuddhasampannau vidyayA ca balena ca . anyonyamAhvayantau tu mattAviva mahAgajau .
muSTibhirjAnubhizcaiva nighnantAvitaretaram . prakarSaNAkarSaNayorabhyAkarSavikarSaNaiH .
AcakarSaturanyonyaM muSTibhizcApi jaghnatuH . tatazcaTacaTAzabdaH sughoro hyabhavat tayoH .
pASANasampAtanibhaiH prahArairabhijaghnatuH . muhUrtaM tau tadAnyonyaM samare paryakarSatAm . tato bhImaH samukSipya bAhubhyAM zalyamAhave . apAtayat kuruzreSTho brAhmaNA jahasustadA . tatrAzcaryaM bhImasenazcakAra puruSarSabhaH . yacchalyaM pAtitaM bhUmau nAvadhId balinaM balI .
pAtite bhImasenena zalye karNe ca zarUite . zarUitAH sarvarAjAnaH parivartRkodaram .
Ucuzca sahitAstatra sAdhvimau brAhmaNarSabhau . vijJAyetAM kvajanmAnau kvanivAsau tathaiva ca .
ko hi rAdhAsutaM karNaM zakto yodhayituM raNe . anyatra rAmAd droNAdvA pANDavAdvA kirITinaH .
kRSNAd vA devakIputrAt kRpAd vApi zaradvataH . ko vA duryodhanaH zaktaH pratiyodhayituM raNe .
tathaiva madrAdhipati zalyaM balavatAM varam . baladevAdRte vIrAt pANDavAd vA vRkodarAt . vIrAd duryodhanAd vAnyaH zaktaH pAtayituM raNe . kriyatAmavahAro ' smAd yuddhAd brAhmaNasaMvRtAt .
brAhmaNA hi sadA rakSyAH sAparAdhApi nityadA . athainAnupalabhyeha punaryotsyAma hRSTavat . tAMstathAvAdinaH sarvAn prasamIkSya kSitIzvarAn . athAnyAn puruSAMzcApi kRtvA tat karma saMyuge .
