syUmarazmiruvAca bhavanto jJAnaniSThA vai gRhasthAH karmanizcayAH . AzramANAM ca sarveSAM niSThAyAmaikyamucyate .
ekatvena pRthaktvena vizeSo nAtra dRzyate . tad yathAvad yathAnyAyaM bhagavAn prabravItu me .
kapila uvAca zarIrapaktiH karmANi jJAnaM tu paramA gatiH . kaSAye karmabhiH pakve rasajJAne ca tiSThati . . AnRzaMsyaM kSamA zAntirahiMsA satyamArjavam . adroho ' nabhimAnazca hrIstitikSA zamastathA .
panthAno brahmaNastvete etaiH prApnoti yatparam . tad vidvAnanubuddhyeta manasA karmanizcayam .
yAM viprAH sarvataH zAntA vizuddhA jJAnanizcayAH . gatiM gacchanti saMtuSTAstAmAhuH paramAM gatim .
vedAMzca veditavyaM ca viditvA ca yathAsthitim . evaM vedavidityAhurato ' nyo vAtarecakaH .
sarvaM vidurvedavido vede sarvaM pratiSThitam . vede hi niSThA sarvasya yad yadasti ca nAsti ca .
eSaiva niSThA sarvatra yat tadasti ca nAsti ca . etadanta ca madhyaM ca saccAsacca vijAnataH .
samAptaM tyAga ityeva sarvavedeSu niSThitam . saMtoSa ityanugatamapavarge pratiSThitam . RtaM satyaM viditaM veditavyaM sarvasyAmA sthAvaraM jaGgamaM ca . sarvaM sukhaM yacchivamuttaraM ca brahmAvyaktaM prabhavazcAvyayaM ca .
tejaH kSamA zAntiranAmayaM zubhaM tathAvidhaM vyoma sanAtanaM dhruvam . stasmai namo brahmaNe brAhmaNAya .
dAnavA UcuH bhoH suyodhana rAjendra bharatAnAM kulodvaha . zUraiH parivRto nityaM tathaiva ca mahAtmabhiH .
akArSIH sAhasamidaM kasmAt prAyopavezanam . AtmatyAgI hyadho yAti vAcyatAM cAyazaskarIm .
na hi kAryaviruddheSu bahupApeSu karmasu . mUlaghAtiSu sajjante buddhimanto bhavadvidhAH .
niyacchainAM ma. . rAjan dharmArthasukhanAzinIm . yazaH pratApavIryaghnIM zatrUNAM harSavardhanIm .
zrUyatAM tu prabho tattvaM divyatAM cAtmano nRpa . nirmANaM ca zarIrasya tato dhairyamavApnuhi .
purA tvaM tapasAsmAbhirlabdho rAjan mahezvarAt . pUrvakAyazca pUrvaste nirmito valAsaMcayaiH .
astrairabhedyaH zastraizcApyadhaH kAyazca te ' nagha . kRtaH puSpamayo devyA rUpataH strImanoharaH .
evamozvarasaMyuktastava deho nRpottama . devyA ca rAjazArdUla divyastvaM hi na mAnuSaH .
kSatriyAca mahAvIryA bhagadattapurogamAH . divyAstraviduSaH zUrAH kSapayiSyanti te ripUn . .
tadalaM te viSAdena bhayaM tava na vidyate . sAhAyyArthaM ca te vIrAH sambhUtA bhuvi dAnavAH .
bhISmadroNakRpAdIMzca pravekSyantyapare ' surAH . yairAviSTA ghRNAM tyaktvA yotsyante tava vairibhiH .
naiva putrAn na ca bhrAtRn na pitRRn na ca bAndhavAn . naiva ziSyAn na ca jJAtIn na bAlAn sthavirAn na ca . . yudhi samprahariSyanto mokSyanti kurusattama . ni : snehA dAnavAviSTAH samAkrAnte ' ntarAtmani .
prahariSyanti vivazA : snehamutsRjya dUrataH . hRSTAH puruSazArdUlA : kaluSIkRtamAnasAH . avijJAnavimUDhAzca daivAcca vidhinirmitAt . vyAbhASamANAzyAnyonyaM na me jIvan vimokSyase sarve zastrAstramokSeNa pauruSe samavasthitAH . zlAghamAnAH kuruzreSTha kariSyanti janakSayam . te ' pi paJca mahAtmAnaH pratiyotsyanti pANDavAH .
vadhaM caiSAM kariSyanti daivayuktA mahAbalAH . daityarakSogaNAzcaiva sambhUtAH kSatrayoniSu . yotsyanti yudhi vikramya zatrubhistva pArthiva . gadAbhirmusalaiH zUlaiH zastrairuccAvacaistathA .
yacca te ' ntargataM vIra bhayamarjunasambhavam . tatrApi vihito ' smAbhirvadhopAyo ' rjunasya vai .
hatasya narakasyAtmA karNamUrtimupAzritaH . tad vairaM saMsmaran vIra yotsyate kezavArjunau .
sa te vikramazauTIro raNe pArthaM vijeSyati . karNaH praharatAM zreSThaH sarvAMzcArIn mahArathaH .
jJAtvaitacchadmanA valI rakSArthaM savyasAcinaH . kuNDale kavacaM caiva karNasyApahariSyati .
tasmAdasmAbhirapyatra daityAH zatasahasrazaH . niyuktA rAkSasAzcaiva ye te saMzaptakA iti .
prakhyAtAste ' rjunaM vIraM haniSyanti ca mA zucaH . asapatnA tvayA hIyaM bhoktavyA vasudhA nRpa .
mA viSAdaM gamastasmAnnaitattvayyupapadyate . vinaSTe tvayi cAsmAkaM pakSo hIyeta kaurava .
gaccha vIra na te buddhiranyA kAryA kathaJcana . tvamasmAkaM gatirnityaM devatAnAM ca pANDavAH .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktvA pariSvajya daityAstaM rAjakuJjaram . samAzvAsya ca durdharSaM putravad dAnavarSabhAH .
sthirAM kRtvA buddhimasya priyANyuktvA ca bhArata . gamyatAmityanujJAya jayamApnuhi cetyatha .
tairvisRSTaM mahAbAhuM kRtyA saivAnayat punaH . tameva dezaM yatrAsau tadA prAyamupAvizat .
pratinikSipya ta vIraM kRtyA samabhipUjya ca . anujJAtA ca rAjJA sA tathaivAntaradhIyata .
gatAyAmatha tasyAM tu rAjA duryodhanastadA . svapnabhUtamidaM sarvamacintayata bhArata . vijeSyAmi raNe pANDUniti cAsyAbhavanmatiH .
karNa saMzaptakAMzcaiva pArthasyAmitraghAtinaH . amanyata vadhe yuktAn samarthAMzca suyodhanaH .
evamAzA dRDhA tasya dhArtarASTrasya durmateH . vinijaye pANDavAnAmabhavad bharatarSabha .
karNo ' pyAviSTacittAtmA narakasyAntarAtmanA . arjunasya vadhe krUrAM karoti sma tadA matim .
saMzaptakAca te vIrA rAkSasAviSTacetasaH . rajastamobhyAmAkrAntA : phAlgunasya vadhaiSiNaH .
bhISmadroNakRpAdyAzca dAnavAkrAntacetasaH . na tathA pANDuputrANAM snehavanto vizAmpate . na cAcacakSe kasmaicidetad rAjA suyodhanaH .
duryodhanaM nizAnte ca karNo vaikartano ' bravIt . smayannivAJjaliM kRtvA pArthivaM hetumad vacaH .
na mRto jayate zatrUJjIvan bhadrANi pazyati . mRtasya bhadrANi kutaH kauraveya kuto jayaH .
na kAlo ' dya viSAdasya bhayasya maraNasya vA . pariSvajyAbravIccainaM bhujAbhyAM sa mahAbhujaH .
uttiSTha rAjan kiM zeSe kasmAcchocasi zatruin . zatrun pratApya vIryeNa sa kathaM mRtyumicchasi .
athavA te bhayaM jAtaM dRSTvArjunaparAkramam . satyaM te pratijAnAmi vadhiSyAmi raNe ' rjunam .
gate trayodaze varSe satyenAyudhamAlabhe . AnayiSyAmyahaM pArthAn vazaM tava janAdhipa .
evamuktastu karNena daityAnAM vacanAt tathA . praNipAtena cApyeSAmudatiSThat suyodhanaH .
daityAnAM tad vacaH zrutvA hadi kRtvA sthirAM matim . tato manujazArdUlo yojayAmAsa vAhinIm . rathanAgAzvakalilA padAtijanasaMkulAm . gagaughapratimA rAjan sA prayAtA mahAcamUH .
zvetacchatraiH patAkAbhizcAmaraizca supANDuraiH . sthairnAgaiH padAtaizca zuzubhe ' tIva saMkulA . vyapetAbhraghane kAle dyaurivAvyaktazAradI .
jayAzIbhirdvijendraiH sa stUyamAno ' dhirAjavat . gRhaNannaJjalimAlAzca dhArtarASTro janAdhipaH . suyodhano yayAvace zriyA paramayA jvalan . .
karNena sArdhaM rAjendra saubalena ca devinA . duHzAsanAdayazcAsya bhrAtaraH sarva eva te . bhUrizravAH somadatto mahArAjazca bAhnikaH . sthairnAnAvidhAkArairhayairgajadharaistathA . prayAntaM nRpasiMhaM tamanujagmuH kurUdvahAH . kAlenAlpena rAjendra svapuraM vivizustadA .
aSTaka uvAca caran gRhasthaH kathameti dharmAn kathaM bhikSuH kathamAcAryakarmA . vAnaprasthaH satpathe saMniviSTo bahUnyasmin samprati vedayanti .
yayAtiruvAca AhUtAdhyAyI gurukarmasvacodyaH pUrvotthAyI caramaM copazAyI . mRdurdAnto dhRtimAnapramattaH dhyAyazIla : sidhyati brahmacArI .
dharmAgataM prApya dhanaM yajeta dadyAt sadaivAtithIn bhoyajecca . anAdadAnazca parairadattaM saiSA gRhasthopaniSat purANI .
svavIryajIvI vRjinAnnivRtto dAtA parebhyo na paropatApI . tAdRGmuniH siddhimupaiti mukhyAM vasannaraNye niyatAhAraceSTaH .
azilpajIvI guNavAMzcaiva nityaM jitendriyaH sarvato viprayuktaH . zcaran dezAnekacaraH sa bhikSuH .
rAtryA yayA vAbhijitAca lokA bhavanti kAmAbhijitAH sukhAcA naraNyasaMstho bhavituM yatAtmA . dazaiva pUrvAn daza cAparAMzca jJAtInathAtmAnamathaikaviMzam . araNyavAsI sukRte dadhAti vimucyAraNye svazarIradhAtUn .
aSTaka uvAca katisvideva munayaH kati maunAni cApyuta . bhavantIti tadAcakSva zrotucchiAmahe vayam .
yayAtiruvAca araNye vasato yasya grAmo bhavati pRSThataH . grAme vA vasato ' raNyaM sa muniH syAjanAdhipa .
aSTaka uvAca kathaMsvid vasato ' raNye grAmo bhavati pRSThataH . grAme vA vasato ' raNyaM kathaM bhavati pRSThataH .
yayAtiruvAca na grAmyamupayuJjIta ya AraNyo munirbhavet . tathAsya vasato ' raNye grAmo bhavati pRSThataH .
anagniraniketazcApyagotracaraNo muniH . kaupInAcchAdanaM yAvat tAvadiccheca cIvaram . yAvat prANAbhisaMdhAnaM tAvadiccheca bhojanam . tathAsya vasato grAme ' raNyaM bhavati pRSThataH . yastu kAmAn parityajya tyaktakarmA jitendriyaH . AtiSTheca munirmInaM sa loke siddhimApnuyAt .
dhautadantaM kRttanakhaM sadA snAtamalaMkRtam . asitaM sitakarmANaM kastamarhati nArcitum .
tapasA karzitaH kSAmaH kSINamAMsAsthizoNitaH . sa ca lokamimaM jitvA lokaM vijayate param .
yadA bhavati nirdvandvo munirmaunaM samAsthitaH . atha lokamimaM jitvA lokaM vijayate param .
Asyena tu yadAhAraM govanmRgayate muniH . athAsya lokaH sarvo ' yaM so ' mRtatvAya kalpate .
sautiruvAca sa cApi cyavano brahmambhArgavo ' janayatsutam . sukanyAyAM mahAtmAnaM pramatiM dIptatejasam .
pramatistu ruruM nAma ghRtAcyAM samajIjanat . ruruH pramadvarAyAM tu zunakaM samajIjanat .
tasya brahman ruroH sarvaM caritaM bhUritejasaH . vistareNa pravakSyAmi tacchRNu tvamazeSataH .
RSirAsInmahAnpUrvaM tayovidyAsamanvitaH . sthUlakeza iti khyAtaH sarvabhUtahite rataH .
etasminneva kAle tu menakAyAM prajajJivAn . gandharvarAjo viprarSe vizvAvasuriti smRtaH .
apsarA menakA tasya taM garbhaM bhRgunandana . utsasarja yathAkAlaM sthUlakezAzramaM prati .
utsRjya caiva taM garbha nadyAstIre jagAma sA . apsarA menakA brahmannirdayA nirapatrapA .
kanyAmaragarbhAbhA jvalantImiva ca zriyA . tAM dadarza samutsRSTAM nadItIre mahAnRSiH . sthUlakezaH sa tejasvI vijane bandhuvarjitAm . sa tAM dRSTvA tadA kanyAM sthUlakezo mahAdvijaH .
jagrAha ca munizreSThaH kRpAviSTaH pupoSa ca . vavRdhe sA varArohA tasyAzramapade zubhe .
jAtakAdyAH kriyAzcAsyA vidhipUrvaM yathAkramam . sthUlakezo mahAbhAgazcakAra sumahAnRSiH .
pramadAbhyo varA sA tu sattvarUpaguNAnvitA . tataH pramadvaretyasyA nAma cakre mahAnRSiH .
tAmAzramapade tasya rururdRSTvA pramadvarAm . babhUva kila dharmAtmA madanohatastadA .
pitaraM sakhibhiH so ' tha zrAvayAmAsa bhArgavam . pramatizcAbhyayAcattAM sthUlakezaM yazasvinam .
tataH prAdAtpitA kanyAM rurave tAM pramadvarAm . vivAhaM sthApayitvA ' gre nakSatre bhagadaivate .
tataH katipayAhasya vivAhe samupasthite . sakhIbhiH krIDatI sArdhaM sA kanyA varavarNinI .
nApazyatsaMprasuptaM vai bhujaMgaM tiryagAyatam . padA cainaM samAkrAmanmumUrSuHkAlacoditA .
sa tasyAH saMpramattAyAzcoditaH kAladharmaNA . viSopaliptAndazanAmbhRzamaGge nyapAtayat .
sA daSTA tena sarpaNa papAta sahasA bhuvi . vivarNA vigatazrIkA bhraSTAbharaNacetanA .
nirAnandakarI teSAM badhUnAM muktamUrdhajA . vyasuraprekSaNIyA sA prekSaNIyatamA ' bhavat .
prasuptevAbhavaccApi bhuvi sarpaviSArditA . bhUyo manoharatarA babhUva tanumadhyamA .
dadarza tAM pitA caiva ye caivAnye tapasvinaH . viceSTamAnAM patitAM bhUtale padmavarcasam .
tataH sarve dvijavarAH samAjagmuH kRpAnvitAH . svastyAtreyo mahAjAnuH kuzikaH zaMkhamekhalaH .
uddAlakaH kaThazcaiva zvetazcaiva mahAyazAH . . bharadvAjaH kauNakutsya ArTiSeNo ' tha gautamaH .
pramati : sahaputreNa tathA ' nye vanavAsinaH . tAM te kanyAM vyasuM dRSTvA bhujaMgasya viSArditAm . . ruruduH kRpayAviSTA rurustvArto bahiryayau . te ca sarve dvijazreSThAstatraivopAvizaMstadA . .
vaizampAyana uvAca sa zatrusenAM tarasA praNudya gAstA vijityAtha dhanurdharA. goSu prayAtAsu duryodhanAyAbhimukhaM prayAto bhUyo raNaM so ' bhicikIrSamANaH .
javena matsyAn kirITinaM kRtakAryaM ca matvA . duryodhanAyAbhimukhaM prayAtaM kurupravIrAH sahasA nipetuH .
teSAmanIkAni bahUni gADhaM vyUDhAni dRSTvA bahuladhvajAni . matsyasya putraM dviSatAM nihantA vairATimAmantrya tato ' bhyuvAca .
etena tUrNaM pratipAdayemAn zvetAn hayAn kAJcanarazmiyoktrAn . javena sarveNa kuru prayatnamAsAdaye ' haM kurusiMhavRndam .
gajo gajeneva mayA durAtmA yoddhaM samAkAGkSati sUtaputraH . tameva mAM prApaya rAjaputra duryodhanApAzrayajAtadarpam .
sa tairhayairvAtajavairvRhaddhiH putro virATasya suvarNakaH . vyadhvaMsayat tad rathinAmanIkaM tato ' vahat pANDavamAjimadhye .
taM citraseno vizikhairvipAThaH saMgrAmajicchatrusaho jayazca . pratyudyayurbhAratamApatantaM mahArathAH karNamabhIpsamAnAH .
tataH sa teSAM puruSapravIraH zarAsanArciH zaravegatApaH . vAtaM rathAnAmadahat samanyurvanaM yathAgniH kurupuGgavAnAm .
tasmiMstu yuddhe tumule pravRtte pArtha vikarNo ' tirathaM rathena . vipAThavarSeNa kurupravIro bhImena bhImAnujamasasAda .
tato vikarNasya dhanurvikRSya jAmbUnadAGmayopacitaM dRDhajyam . cchinnadhvajaH so ' pyapayAjjvena . .
taM zAtravANAM gaNabAdhitAraM karmANi kurvantamamAnupANi . zatrutapaH pArthamamRSyamANa : samArdayacchara varSeNa pArtham .
sa tena rAjJAtirathena viddho vigAhamAno dhvajinI kurUNAm . zatapaM paJcabhirAzu viddhA ' tato ' sya sUtaM dazabhirjaghAna .
tataH sa viddho bharatarSabheNa bANena gAtrAvaraNAtigena . gatAsurAjau nipapAta bhUmau nago nagAgrAdiva vAtarugNaH .
nararSabhAstena nararSabheNa vIrA raNe vIratareNa bhagnAH . cakampire vAtavazena kAle prakampitAnIva mahAvanAni .
tAstu pArthena narapravIrA gatAsavortyAM suSupuH suveSAH . vasupradA vAsavatulyavIryAH parAjitA vAsavajena saMkhye .
suvarNakArNAyasavarmanaddhA nAgA yatA haimavatA : pravRddhAH . tathA sa zatrUn samare vinighnan . gANDIvadhanvA puruSapravIraH .
cacAra saMkhye vidizo dizazca dahannivAgnirvanamAtapAnte . prakIrNaparNAni yathA vasante vizAtayitvA pavano ' mbudAMzca .
tathA sapatnAn vikiran kirITI cacAra saMkhye ' tiratho rathena . zoNAzvavAhasya hayAn nihatya vaikartanabhrAturadInasattvaH . ekena saMgrAmajitaH zareNa kirITamAlI . .
tasmin hate bhrAtari sUtaputro vaikartano vIryamathAdadAnaH . pragRhya dantAviva nAgarAjo maharSabhaM vyAghra ivAbhyadhAvat . ( kartanaH zIghramatho jaghAna . ziro jahArAtha
vivyAdha gAtreSu hayAMzca sarvAn virATaputraM ca kare nijaghne . tamApatantaM sahasA kirITI vaikartanaM vai tarasAbhipatya . pragRhya vegaM nyapatajjavena nAgaM garutmAniva citrapakSaH .
tAvuttamau sarvadhanurdharANAM mahAbalau sarvasapatnasAhau . karNasya pArthasya nizamya yuddhaM didRkSamANAH kuravo ' bhitasthuH .
sa pANDavastUrNamudIrNakopaH kRtAgasaM karNamudIkSya harSAt . mantardadhe ghorazaraughavRSTyA .
tataH suviddhAH sarathAH sanAgA yodhA vinedurbharatarSabhANAm . antarhitA bhISmamukhAH sahAzvAH kirITinA kIrNarathAH pRSatkaiH .
charAjcharaughaiH pratihatya vIraH . tasthau mahAtmA sadhanuH sabANaH savisphuliGgo ' gnirivAzu karNaH .
tatastvabhUd vai talatAlazabdaH sazaGkhabherIpaNavapraNAdaH . prakSveDitajyAtalanisvanaM taM vaikartanaM pUjayatAM kurUNAm .
dhvajottamAMsAkulabhISaNAntam . gANDIvanirhAdakRtapraNAdaM kirITinaM prekSya nanAda karNaH .
sa cApi vaikartanamardayitvA sAzvaM sasUtaM sarathaM pRSatkaiH . tamAvavarSa prasabhaM kirITI pitAmahaM droNakRpau ca dRSTvA . ( kartano megha ivAbhyavarSat . tathaiva karNaM ca kirITamAlI saMchAdayAmAsa zitaiH pRSatkaiH .
tayoH sutIkSNAn sRjatoH zaraudhAn mahAzaraughAstravivardhane raNe . rathe vilagnAviva candrasUryo ghanAntareNAnudadarza lokaH .
athAzukArI caturo hayAMzca vivyAdha ko nizitaiH kirITinaH . tribhizca yantAramamRSyamANo vivyAdha tUrNaM tribhirasya ketum .
tato ' bhividdhaH samarAvamardI prabodhitaH siMha iva prasuptaH . majihmagaiH karNamiyAya jiSNuH .
zarAstravRSTyA nihato mahAtmA prAduzcakArAtimanuSyakarma . rlokAnimAn sUryaM ivAMzujAlaiH .
sa hastinevAbhihato gajendraH pragRhya bhallAn nizitAn niSaGgAt . AkarNapUrNaM ca dhanurvikRSya vivyAdha gAtreSvatha sUtaputram .
aMthAsya bAhUruzirolalATa grIvAM varAGgAni parAvamardI . zitaizca bANairyudhi nirbibheda gANDIvamuktairazaniprakAzaiH .
sa pArthamuktairiSubhiH praNunno gajo gajeneva jitastarasvI . vihAya saMgrAmaziraH prayAto vaikartanaH pANDavabANataptaH .
bhISma uvAca evamuktaH pratyuvAca taM muni janamejayaH . gIM bhavAn garhayate nindyaM nindati mAM punaH .
dhikkAryaM mAM dhikkurute tasmAt tvAhaM prasAdaye . sarvaM hIdaM duSkRtaM me jvalAmyagnAvivAhitaH .
svakarmANyabhisaMdhAya nAbhinandati me manaH . prApyaM ghoraM bhayaM nUnaM mayA vaivasvatAdapi .
tattu zalyamanirhatya kathaM zakSyAmi jIvitum . sarvaM manyu vinIya tvamabhi mAM vada zaunaka .
mahAnAsaM brAhmaNAnAM bhUyo vakSyAmi sAmpratam . astu zeSaM kulasyAsya mA parAbhUdidaM kulam .
na hi no brahmazaptAnAM zeSaM bhavitumarhati . stutIralabhamAnAnAM saMvidaM vedanizcitAn .
nirvidyamAnaH subhRzaM bhUyo vakSyAmi zAzvatam . bhUyazcaivAbhirakSantu nirdhanAn nirjanA iva .
na hyayajJA amuM lokaM prApnuvanti kathaJcana . ApAtAn pratitiSThanti pulindazabarA iva .
avijJAyaiva me prajJA bAlasyeva sa paNDitaH . putrasya prItimAn bhava zaunaka .
zaunaka uvAca kimAzcaryaM yadaprAjJo bahu kuryAdasAmpratam . iti vai paNDito bhUtvA bhUtAnAM nAnukupyate . brahman piteva
prajJAprAsAdamAruhya azocyaH zocate janAn . jagatIsthAnivAMdristhaH prajJayA pratipatsyati .
na copalabhyate tena na cAzcaryANi kurvate . niviNNAtmA parokSo vA dhikkRtaH pUrvasAdhuSu .
viditaM bhavato vIryaM mAhAtmyaM veda Agame . kuruSveha yathAzAnti brahmA zaraNamastu te . tad vai pAratrikaM tAta brAhmaNAnAmakupyatAm . athavA tapyase pApe dharmamevAnupazya vai .
janamejaya uvAca anutapye ca pApena na ca dharmaM vilopaye . bubhUdhU bhajamAnaM ca prItimAn bhava zaunaka .
zaunaka uvAca chittvA dambhaM ca mAnaM ca prItimicchAmi te nRpa . sarvabhUtahitaM tiSTha dharmaM caiva pratismaran .
na bhayAnna ca kArpaNyAnna lobhAt tvAmupAhaye . tAM me daivIM giraM satyAM zRNu tvaM brAhmaNaiH saha .
so ' haM na kenaciccArthI tvAM ca dharmAdupAhvaye . krozatAM sarvabhUtAnAM hAhA dhigiti jalpatAm .
vakSyanti mAmadharmajJaM tyakSyanti suhRdo janAH . tA vAcaH suhRdaH zrutvA saMjvariSyanti me bhRzam .
