tataste kathayAmAsuH kathAstAstA manoramAH . dhanyA divyAzca rAjendra prItiharSamudA yutAH .
tataH kathAnte rAjarSirmahAtmA hotravAhanaH . rAma zreSThaM maharSINAmapRcchadakRtavraNam .
