tataH kila mahAvIryo bhISmaH zAntanavo nRpAn . adhikSipya mahAtejAstisraH kanyA jahAratAH .
nirjitya pRthivIpAlAnathaM bhISmo gajAhvayam . AjagAma vizuddhAtmA kanyAbhiH saha bhArataH .
satyavatyai nivedyAtha vivAhaM samanantaram . bhrAturvicitravIryasya samAjJApayata prabhuH .
taM tu vaivAhikaM dRSTvA kanyeyaM samupArjitam . abravIt tatra gAGgeyaM mantrimadhye dvijarSabha .
mayA zAlvapatirvIro manasAbhivRtaH patiH . na mAmarhasi dharmajJa dAtuM bhrAtre ' nyamAnasAm .
tacchrutvA vacanaM bhISmaH sammantrya saha mantribhiH . nizcitya visasarjemAM satyavatyA mate sthitaH .
anujJAtA tu bhISmeNa zAlvaM saubhapatiM tataH . kanyeyaM muditA tatra kAle vacanamabravIt .
visarjitA ' smi bhISmeNa dharmaM mAM pratipAdaya . manasAbhivRtaH pUrvaM mayA tvaM pArthivarSabha .
pratyAcakhyau ca zAlvo ' syAzcAritrasyAbhizaGkitaH . seyaM tapovanaM prAptA tApasye ' bhiratA bhRzam .
mayA ca pratyabhijJAtA vaMzasya parikIrtanAt . asya duHkhasya cotpattiM bhISmameveha manyate .
ambovAca bhagavannevameveha yathA ' ' ha pRthivIpatiH . zarIrakartA mAturme sRJjayo hotravAhanaH .
na jhutsahe svanagaraM pratiyAtuM tapodhana . apamAnabhayAccaiva vrIDayA ca mahAmune .
yat tu mAM bhagavAn rAmo vakSyati dvijasattama . tanme kAryatamaM kAryamiti me bhagavan matiH .
dhRtarASTra uvAca ninadantaM tathA taM tu bhImasenaM mahAbalam . meghastanitanirghoSa ke vIrAH paryavArayan .
na hi pazyAmyahaM taM vai triSu lokeSu kaMcana . kruddhasya bhImasenasya yastiSThedagrato raNe .
gadAM yuyutsamAnasya kAlasyeveha saMjaya . na hi pazyAmyahaM yuddhe yastiSThedagrataH pumAn .
rathaM rathena yo hanyAt kuJjaraM kuJjareNa ca . kastastha samare sthAtA sAkSAdapi puraMdaraH .
kruddhasya bhImasenasya mama putrAn jighAMsataH . duryodhanahite yuktAH samatiSThanta ke ' grataH .
bhImasenadavAgnestu mama putrAMstRNopamAn . pradhakSato raNamukhe ke ' tiSThannagrato narAH .
kAlyamAnAMstu putrAn me dRSTvA bhImena saMyuge . kAleneva prajAH sarvAH ke bhImaM paryavArayan .
na me ' rjunAd bhayaM tAdRk kRSNAnnApi ca sAtvatAt . hutabhugjanmano naiva yAdRgmImAd bhayaM mama .
bhImavahneH pradIptasya mama putrAn didhakSataH . ke zUrAH paryavartanta tanmamAcakSva saMjaya .
saMjaya uvAca tathA tu nardamAnaM taM bhImasenaM mahAbalam . tumulenaiva zabdena karNo ' pyabhyadravadbalI .
vyAkSipan sumahacAtamatimAtramamarSaNaH . karNaH suyuddhamAkAGkSan darzayiSyan balaM mRdhe .
rurodha mArga bhImasya vAtasyeva mahIruhaH . bhImo ' pi dRSTvA sAvegaM puro vaikartanaM sthitam .
cukopa balavadvIrazcikSepAsya zilAzitAn . tAn pratyagRhNAt karNo ' pi pratIpaM prApayaccharAn .
tatastu savaryAdhAnAM yatatAM prekSatAM tadA . prAvepanniva gAtrANi karNabhImasamAgame . rathinAM sAdinAM caina tayoH : zrutvA talakhanam . bhImasenasya ninadaM zrutvA ghoraM raNAjire .
khaM ca bhUmiM ca saMruddhAM menire kSatriyarSabhAH . punariNa nAdena pANDavasya mahAtmanaH .
samare sarvayodhAnAM dhanUMSyabhyapatan kSitau . zastrANi nyapatan dorthyaH keSAMcicAsavo ' dravan . vitrastAni ca sarvANi zakRnmUtraM prasusravuH . vAhanAni ca sarvANi babhUvurvimanAMsi ca . prAdurAsan nimittAni ghorANi subahUnyuta .
gRdhrakaGkabalaizcAsIdantarikSaM samAvRtam . tasmin sutumale rAjan karNabhImasamAgame .
tataH karNastu viMzatyA zarANAM bhImamArdayat . . vivyAdha cAsya tvaritaH sUtaM paJcabhirAzugaiH .
prahasya bhImaseno ' pi karNa pratyAdravad raNe . sAyakAnAM catuHSTyA kSiprakArI mahAyazAH .
tasya karNo maheSvAsaH sAyaMkAzcaturo ' kSipat . asamprAptAMzca tAn bhImaH sAyakairnaptaparvabhiH .
ciccheda bahudhA rAjan darzayan pANilAghavam . taM karNazchAdayAmAsa zaravAtairanekazaH .
saMchAdyamAnaH karNena bahudhA pANDunandanaH . ciccheda cApaM karNasya muSTideze mahArathaH .
vivyAdha cainaM bahubhiH sAyakairnataparvabhiH . athAnyad dhanurAdAya sajyaM kRtvA ca sUtajaH .
vivyAdha samare bhImaM bhImakarmA mahArathaH . tasya bhImo bhRzaM kruddhastrIzarAn nataparvaNaH .
nicakhAnorasi kruddhaH sUtaputrasya vegataH . taiH karNo ' rAjata zarairurormadhyagataistadA .
mahIdhara ivodagrastrizRGgo bharatarSabha . . susrAva cAsya rudhiraM viddhasya parameSubhiH .
dhAtuprasyandinaH zailAd yathA gairikadhAtavaH . kiMcid vicalitaH karNaH suprahArAbhipIDitaH .
AkarNapUrNamAkRSya bhImaM vivyAdha sAyakaiH . cikSepa ca punarbANAzatazo ' tha sahasrazaH .
