mA tvaM sarvavinAzAya snehaM kArSIH suteSu naH . na hIdaM karma moghaM syAllokakAmasya naH pituH .
jaritovAca idamAkhorbilaM bhUmau vRkSasyAsya samIpataH . tadAvizadhvaM tvaritA vaDheratra na vo bhayam .
tato ' haM pAMsunA chidramapidhAsyAmi putrakaH . evaM pratikRtaM manye jvalataH kRSNavartmanaH .
tata eSyAmyatIte ' gnau vihantuM pAMsusaMcayam . rocatAmeSa vo vAdo mokSArthaM ca hutAzanAt .
zAIkA UcuH abarhAn mAMsabhUtAn naH kravyAdAkhurvinAzayet . pazyamAnA bhayamidaM praveSTuM nAA zaknumaH .
kathamagnirna ne dhakSyet kathamAkhu nAzayet . kathaM na syAt pitA moghaH kathaM mAtA dhriyeta naH .
bila AkhorvinAzaH syAdagnerAkAzacAriNAm . anvavekSyaitadubhayaM zreyAn dAho na bhakSaNam .
garhitaM maraNaM naH syAdAkhunA bhakSite bile . ziSTAdiSTaH parityAgaH zarIrasya hutAzanAt .
vaizampAyana uvAca saindhavairabhavad yuddhaM tatastasya kirITinaH . hatazeSairmahArAja hatAnAM ca sutairapi .
te ' vatIrNamupazrutya viSayaM zvetavAhanam . pratyudyayuramRSyanto rAjAnaH pANDavarSabham .
azvaM ca taM parAmRzya viSayAnte viSopamAH . na bhayaM cakrire pArthAd bhImasenAdanantarAt .
te ' vidUrAd dhanuSpANiM yajJiyasya hayasya ca . bIbhatsuM pratyapadyanta padAtinamavasthitam .
tataste taM mahAvIryA rAjAnaH paryavArayan . jigISanto naravyAghra pUrvaM vinikRtA yudhi .
te nAmAnyapi gotrANi karmANi vividhAni ca . kIrtayantastadA pArthaM zaravaSairavAkiran .
te kirantaH zaravAtAn bAraNaprativAraNAn . raNe jayamabhIpsantaH kaunteyaM paryavArayan .
te samIkSya ca taM kRSNamugrakarmANamAhave . sarve yayudhire vIrA rathasthAstaM padAtinam .
te tamAjanjire vIraM nivAtakavacAntakam . saMzaptakanihantAraM hantAraM saindhavasya ca . .
tato rathasahasreNa hayAnAmayutena ca . koSThakIkRtya bIbhatsuM prahRSTamanaso ' bhavan .
taM smaranto vadhaM vIrA : sindhurAjasya cAhave . jayadrathasya kauravya samare savyasAcinA . tataH parjanyavat sarve zaravRSTIravAsRjan . tai : kIrNaH zuzubhe pArtho ravirmeghAntare yathA .
sa zaraiH samavacchannazcakAze pANDavarSabhaH . paJjarAntarasaMcArI zakunta iva bhArata .
tato hAhAkRtaM sarvaM kaunteye zarapIDite . trailokyamabhavad rAjan ravirAsIcca niSprabhaH .
tato vavau mahArAja mAruto lomaharSaNaH . rAhuragrasadAdityaM yugapat somameva ca .
ulkAzca jadhire sUryaM vikIryantyaH samantataH . vepathuzcAbhavad rAjan kailAsasya mahAgireH .
mumucuH zvAsamatyuSNaM duHkhazokasamanvitAH . saptarSayo jAtabhayAstathA devarSayo ' pi ca .
zazaM cAzu vinirbhidya maNDalaM zazino ' patat . viparItA dizazcApi sarvA dhUmAkulAstathA .
rAsabhAruNasaMkAzA dhanuSmantaH savidyutaH . AvRtya gaganaM meghA mumucurmosazoNitam .
evamAsIt tadA vIre zaravarSeNa saMvRte . phAlgune bharatazreSTha tadyutamivAbhavat . .
tasya tenAvakIrNasya zarajAlena sarvataH . mohAt papAta gANDIvamAvApazca karAdapi . .
tasmin mohamanuprApte zarajAlaM mahat tadA . saindhavA mumucustUrNaM gatasattve mahArathe .
tato mohasamApannaM jJAtvA pArthaM divaukasaH . sarve vitrastamanasastasya zAntikRto ' bhavan .
tato devarSayaH sarve tathA saptarSayo ' pi ca . brahmarSayazca vijayaM jepuH pArthasya dhImataH .
tataH pradIpite devaiH pArthatejasi pArthiva . tasthAvacalavad dhImAn saMgrAme paramAstravit .
vicakarSa dhanurdivyaM tataH kauravanandanaH . yantrasyeveha zabdo ' bhUnmahAMstasya punaH punaH .
tataH sa zaravarSANi pratyamitrAn prati prabhuH . vavarSa dhanuSA pArtho varSANIva puraMdaraH .
tataste saindhavA yodhAH sarva eva sarAjakAH . nAdRzyanta zaraiH kIrNAH zalabhairiva pAdapAH .
tasya zabdena vitresurbhayArtAzca vidudruvuH . mumucuzcAzru zokArtAH zuzucuzcApi saindhavAH .
tAMstu sarvAn naravyAghraH saindhavAn vyacarat balI . alAtacakravad rAjazarajAlaiH samArpayat .
tadindrajAlapratima bANajAlamamitrahA . visRjya dikSu sarvAsu mahendra iva vajrabhRt .
meghajAlanibhaM sainyaM vidArya zaravRSTibhiH . vibabhau kauravazreSThaH zaradIva divAkaraH .
kRSNa uvAca mUrjA nipatya niyatastejaHsaMnicaye tataH . paramaM harSamAgatya bhagavantamathAbruvam .
dharme dRDhatvaM yudhi zatrughAtaM yazastathAgryaM paramaM balaM ca . yogapriyatvaM tava saMnikarSa vRNe sutAnAM ca zataM zatAni .
evamastviti tadvAkyaM mayoktaH prAha zaGkaraH . tato mAM jagato mAtA dhAriNI sarvapAvanI . uvAcomA praNihitA zarvANI tapasAM nidhiH . datto bhagavatA putraH sAmbo nAma tavAnagha . .
matto ' pyaSTau varAniSTAn gRhANa tvaM dadAmi te . praNamya zirasA sA ca mayoktA pANDunandana . .
dvijeSvakopaM pitRtaH prasAda zataM sutAnAM paramaM ca bhogam . kule prItiM mAtRtazca prasAda zamaprAptiM pravRNe cApi dAkSyam .
umA uvAca evaM bhaviSyatyamaraprabhAva nAhaM mRSA jAtu vade kadAcit . bhAryAsahasrANi ca SoDazaiva tAsu priyatvaM ca tathAkSayaM ca .
prItiM cAgryAM bAndhavAnAM sakAzAd dadAmi te ' haM vapuSaH kAmyatAM ca . bhokSyante vai saptatiM vai zatAni gRhe tubhyamatithInAM ca nityam .
evaM dattvA varAn devo mama devI ca bhArata . antarhitaH kSaNe tasmin sagaNo bhImapUrvaja .
etadatyadbhutaM pUrvaM brAhmaNAyAtitejase . upamanyave mayA kRtsnaM vyAkhyAtaM pArthivottama . namaskRtvA tu sa prAha devadevAya suvrata .
upamanyuruvAca nAsti zarvasamo devo nAsti zarvasamA gatiH . nAsti zarvasamo dAne nAsti zarvasamo raNe .
vaizampAyana uvAca dhRtarASTrAbhyanujJAtAstataste kurupANDavAH . abhyayurdhAtaraH sarve gAndhArI saha kezavAH .
tato jJAtvA hatAmitraM yudhiSThiramupAgatam . gAndhArI putrazokArtA zaptumaicchadaninditA .
tasyAH pApamabhiprAyaM viditvA pANDavAn prati . RSiH satyavatIputraH prAgeva samabudhyata .
sa gaGgAyAmupaspRzya puNyagandhi payaH zuci . taM dezamupasampede paramarSirmanojavaH .
divyena cakSuSA pazyan manasA tadgatena ca . sarvaprANabhRtAM bhAvaM sa tatra samabudhyata .
sa snuSAmabravIt kAle kalyavAdI mahAtapAH . zApakAlamavAkSipya zamakAlamudIrayan .
na kopaH pANDave kAryo gAndhAri zamabhApnuhi ! vaco nigRhyatAmetacchRNu cedaM vaco mama .
uktAsyaSTAdazAhAni putreNa jayamicchatA . zivamAzAsva me mAtayudhyamAnasya zatrubhiH . sA tathA yAcyamAnA tvaM kAle kAle jayaiSiNA . uktavatyasi gAndhAri yato dharmastato jayaH . na cApyatItAM gAndhAri vAcaM te vitathAmaham . smarAmi bhASamANAyAstathA prANihitA hyasi .
vigrahe tumule rAjJAM gatvA pAramasaMzayam . jitaM pANDusutairyuddhe nUnaM dharmastato ' dhikaH .
kSamAzIlA purA bhUtvA sAdya na kSamase katham . adharmaM jahi dharmajJe yato dharmastato jayaH .
svaM ca dharma parismRtya vAcaM coktA manasvini . kopaM saMyaccha gAndhAri maivaM bhUH satyavAdini . bhagavannAbhyasUyAmi naitAnicchAmi nazyataH . putrazokena tu balAnmano vihvalatIva me .
yathaiva kuntyA kaunteyA rakSitavyAstathA mayA . tathaiva dhRtarASTreNa rakSitavyA yathA tvayA .
duryodhanAparAdhena zakuneH saubalasya ca . kaNaMduHzAsanAbhyAM ca kRto ' yaM kurusaMkSayaH .
nAparAdhyati bIbhatsurna ca pArtho vRkodaraH . nakulaH sahadevazca naiva jAtu yudhiSThiraH .
yudhyamAnA hi kauravyAH kRntamAnAH parasparam . nihatAH sahitAzcAnyaistaca nAstyapriyaM mama .
kiM tu karmAkarod bhImo vAsudevasya pazyataH . duryodhanaM samAhUya gadAyuddhe mahAmanAH . zikSayAbhyadhikaM jJAtvA carantaM bahudhA raNe . adho nAbhyAH prahatavAMstanme kopamavardhayat .
kathaM nu dharma dharmajJaiH samuddiSTaM mahAtmabhiH . tyajeyurAhave zUrAH prANahetoH kathaMcana .
karNa uvAca yA naH zrutA manuSyeSu striyo rUpeNa sammatAH . tAsAmetAdRzaM karma na kasyAzcana zuzruma .
krodhAviSTeSu pArtheSu dhArtarASTreSu cApyati . draupadI : pANDuputrANAM kRSNA zAntirihAbhavat .
aplave ' mbhasi magnAnAmapratiSThe nimajjatAm . pAJcAlI pANDuputrANAM naureSA pAragAbhavat .
vaizampAyana uvAca tad vai zrutvA bhImasenaH kurumadhye ' tyamarSaNaH . strIgatiH pANDuputrANAmityuvAca sudurmanAH .
bhIma uvAca trINi jyotIMSi puruSa iti vai devalo ' bravIt . apatyaM karma vidyA.ca yataH sRSTAH prajAstataH .
amedhye vai gataprANe zUnye jJAtibhirujjhite . dehe tritayamevaitat puruSasyopayujyate .
tanno jyotirihataM dArANAmabhimarzanAt . dhanaMjaya kathaMsvin syAdapatyamabhimRSTajam .
arjuna uvAca na caivoktA na cAnuktA hInata : paruSAH giraH . bhArata pratijalpanti sadA tUttamapUruSAH . smaranti sukRtAnyeva na vairANi kRtAnyapi . santaH prativijAnanto labdhasambhAvanAH svayam .
bhIma uvAca ihaivaitAMstvahaM sarvAn hanmi zatrUn samAgatAn . atha niSkramya rAjendra samUlAn hanmi bhArata .
kiM no vivaditeneha kimuktena ca bhArata . adyaivaitAn nihanmIha prazAdhi pRthivImimAm .
ityuktvA bhImasenastu kaniSThairdhAtRbhiH saha . mRgamadhye yathA siMho muhurmuhurudaikSata .
sAntvyamAno vIkSamANaH pArthenAkliSTakarmaNA . khidyatyeva mahAbAhurantardAhena vIryavAn .
kruddhasya tasya srotAbhyaH karNAdibhye narAdhipa . sadhUmaH sasphuliGgajrircaH pAvakaH samajAyata .
bhRkuTIkRtaduSprekSyamabhavat tasya tanmukham . yugAntakAle samprApte kRtAntasyeva rUpiNaH .
yudhiSThirastamAvArya bAhunA bAhuzAlinam . maivamityabravIccainaM joSamAssveti bhArata .
nivArya ca mahAbAhuM kopasaMraktalocanam . pitaraM samupAtiSThad dhRtarASTraM kRtAJjaliH .
dhRtarASTra uvAca bANe tasmin nikRtte tu dhRSTadyumne ca mokSite . tena vRSNipravIreNa yuyudhAnena saMjaya .
amarSito maheSvAsaH sarvazastrabhRtAM varaH . naravyAghraH zineH pautre droNaH kimakarod yudhi .
saMjaya uvAca sampradrutaH krodhaviSo vyAditAsyazarAsanaH . tIkSNadhAreSudazanaH zitanArAcadaMSTravAn . saMrambhAmarSatAmrAkSo mahoraga iva zvasan . naravIraH pramuditaH zauNairazvairmahAjavaiH . utpatadbhirivAkAze krAmadbhiriva parvatam . rukmapuGkhAJcharAnasyan yuyudhAnamupAdravat .
zarapAtamahAvarSaM rathaghoSabalAhakam . kArmukAkarSavikSepaM nArAcabahuvidyutam . zaktikhaDgAzanidharaM krodhavegasamutthitam . droNameghamanAvArya hayamArutacoditam .
dRSTvaivAbhipatantaM taM zUraH parapuraMjayaH . uvAja sUtaM zaineyaH prahasan yuddhadurmadaH .
enaM vai brAhmaNaM zUraM svakarmaNyanavasthitam . AzrayaM dhArtarASTrasya rAjJo duHkhabhayApaham .
zIghraM prajavitairazvaiH pratyudyAhi prahRSTavat . AcAryaM rAjaputrANAM satataM zUramAninam .
tato rajatasaMkAzA mAdhavasya hayottamAH . droNasyAbhimukhAH zIghramagacchan vAtaraMhasaH .
tatastau droNazaineyo yuyudhAte paraMtapau . zarairanekasAhasrestADayantau parasparam .
iSujAlAvRtaM vyoma cakratuH puruSarSabhau . pUrayAmAsaturvIrAvubhau daza dizaH zaraiH .
meghAvivAtapAyAye dhArAbhiritaretaram . na sma sUryastadA bhAti na vavau ca samIraNaH .
iSujAlAvRtaM ghoramandhakAraM samantataH . anAdhRSyamivAnyeSAM zUrANAmabhavat tadA .
andhakArIkRte loke droNazaineyayoH zaraiH . tayoH zIghrAstraviduSooNasAtvatayostadA .
nAntaraM zaravRSTInAM dadRze narasiMhayoH .
ipUNAM saMnipAtena zabdo dhArAbhighAtajaH . zuzruve zakramuktAnAmazanInAmiva svanaH .
nArAcairvyatividdhAnAM zarANAM rUpamAbabhau . AzIviSavidaSTAnAM sarpANAmiva bhArata .
tayordhyAtalanirghoSaH zuzruve yuddhazauNDayoH . ajasraM zailazRGgANAM vajreNAhanyatAmiva .
ubhayostau rathau rAjaMste cAzvAstau ca sArathI . rukmapukaiH zaraizchinnAzcitrarUpA babhustadA .
nirmalAnAmajihyAnAM nArAcAnAM vizAmpate . nirmuktAzIviSAbhAnAM sampAtobhUt sudAruNaH .
ubhayoH patite chatre tathaiva patito dhvajau . ubhau rudhirasiktAGgAvubhau ca vijayaiSiNau .
navadbhiH zoNitaM gAtraiH prasrutAviva vAraNau . anyonyamabhyavidhyetAM jIvitAntakaraiH zaraiH .
garjitotkRSTasaMnAdAH zaGkhadundubhiniHsvanAH . upAraman mahArAja vyAjahAra na kazcana .
tUSNImbhUtAnyanIkAni yodhA yuddhAdupAraman . dadarza dvairathaM tAbhyAM jAtakautUhalo janaH .
rathino hastiyantAro hayArohA : padAtayaH . avaikSantAcalaitraH parivArya nararSabhau .
hastyanIkAnyatiSThanta tathAnIkAni vAjinAm . tathaiva rathavAhinyaH prativyUhya vyavasthitAH .
muktAvidrumacitraizca maNikAJcanabhUSitaiH . dhvajairAbharaNaizcitraiH kavacaizca hiraNmayaiH . vaijayantIpatAkAbhiH paristomAGgakambalaiH . vimalairnizitaiH zastrairhayAnAM ca prakIrNakaiH . jAtarUpamayIbhizca rAjanItibhazca mUrdhasu . gajAnAM kumbhamAlAbhirdantaveSTaizca bhArata . sabalAkAH sakhadyotAH sairAvatazatahradAH . adRzyantoSNaparyAye meghAnAmiva vAgurAH .
apazyannasmadIyAzca te ca yaudhiSThirAH sthitAH . tad yuddhaM yuyudhAnasya droNasya ca mahAtmanaH .
vimAnAgragatA devA brahmasomapurogamAH . siddhacAraNasaMghAzca vidyAdharamahoragAH .
gatapratyAgatAkSepaizciaurastravighAtibhiH . vividhairvismayaM jagmustayoH puruSasiMhayoH .
hastalAghavamastreSu darzayantau mahAbalau . anyonyamabhividhyetAM zaraistau droNasAtyakI .
tato droNasya dAzArhaH zarAMzciccheda saMyuge . patribhiH sudRDharAzu dhanuzcaiva mahAdyuteH .
nimeSAntaramAtreNa bhAradvAjo ' paraM dhanuH . sajyaM cakAra tadapi cicchedAsya ca sAtyakiH . tatastvaran punardoNo dhanurhasto vyatiSThata . sajyaM sajyaM dhanuzcAsya ciccheda nizitaiH zaraiH .
evamekazataM chinnaM dhanuSAM dRDhadhanvinA . na cAntaraM tayordRSTaM saMdhAne chedane ' pi ca .
tato ' sya saMyuge droNo dRSTvA karmAtimAnuSam . yuyudhAnasya rAjendra manasaitadacintayat .
etadastrabalaM rAme kArtavIrye dhanaMjaye . bhISme ca puruSavyAghra yadidaM sAtvatAM vare . taM cAsya manasA droNaH pUjayAmAsa vikramam .
lAghavaM vAsavasyeva samprekSya dvijasattamaH . tutoSAstravidAM zreSThastathA devAH savAsavAH .
na tAmAlakSayAmAsurlaghutAM zIghracAriNaH . gandharvAzca vizAmpate . siddhAcAraNasaMghAzca viduyNasya karma tat .
devAzca yuyudhAnasya tato ' nyad dhanurAdAya droNaH kSatriyamardanaH . astrairastravidAM zreSTho yodhayAmAsa bhArata .
tasyAstrANyastramAyAbhiH pratihatya sa sAtyakiH . jaghAna nizitairbANaistadadbhutamivAbhavat .
tasyAtimAnuSaM karma dRSTvAnyairasamaM raNe . yuktaM yogena yogajJAstAvakAH samapUjayan .
yadastramasyati droNastadevAsyati sAtyakiH . tamAcAryo ' pyasambhrAnto ' yodhayacchatrutApanaH
tataH kruddho mahArAja dhanurvedasya pAragaH . vadhAya yuyudhAnasya divyamastramudairayat .
tadAgneyaM mahAghoraM ripughnamupalakSya saH . divyamastraM maheSvAso vAruNaM samudairayat .
hAhAkAro mahAnAsId dRSTvA divyAstradhAriNau . na vicerustadAkAze bhUtAnyAkAzagAmyapi .
astre te vAruNAgneye tAbhyAM bANasamAhite . na yAvadabhyapadyetAM vyAvartadatha bhAskaraH .
tato yudhiSThiro rAjA bhImasenazca pANDavaH . nakulaH sahadevazca paryarakSanta sAtyakim .
dhRSTadyumnamukhaiH sArdha virATazca sakekayaH . matsyAH zAlveyasenAzca droNamAjagmuraJjasA .
droNamabhyupapadyanta duHzAsanaM puraskRtya rAjaputrAH sahasrazaH . sapanaiH parivAritam .
tato yuddhamabhUd rAjesteSAM tava ca dhanvinAm . rajasA saMvRte loke zarajAlasamAvRte .
sarvamAvignamabhavanna prAjJAyata kiMcana . sainyena rajasA dhvaste nirmaryAdamavartata .
vaizampAyana uvAca pratijJAya tu duSyante pratiyAte zakuntalAm . garbhaM suSAva vAmorU : kumAramamitaujasam . triSu varSeSu pUrNeSu dIptAnalasamadyutim . rUpaudAryaguNopetaM dauSyanti janamejaya .
jAtakarmAdisaMskAraM kaNvaH puNyakRtAM varaH . vidhivat kArayAmAsa vardhamAnasya dhImataH .
dantaiH zukaiH zikharibhiH siMhasaMhanano mahAn . cakrAGkitakaraH zrImAn mahAmUrdhA mahAbalaH .
kumAro devagarbhAbhaH sa tatrAzu vyavardhata . SaDvarSa eva bAlaH sa kaNvAzramapadaM prati . siMhavyAghrAn varAhAMzca mahiSAMzca gajAMstathA . babandha vRkSe balavAnAzramasya samIpataH .
Arohan damayaMzcaiva krIDaMzca paridhAvati . tato ' sya nAma cakruste kaNvAzramanivAsinaH . astvayaM sarvadamanaH sarvaM hi damayatyasau . sa sarvadamano nAma kumAraH samapadyata . vikrameNaujasA caiva balena ca samanvitaH .
taM kumAramRSirdRSTvA karma cAsyAtimAnuSam . samayo yauvarAjyAyetyabravIca zakuntalAm .
tasya tad balamAjJAya kaNvaH ziSyAnuvAca ha . zakuntalAmimAM zIghraM sahaputrAmito gRhAt . bhartuH prApayatAgAraM sarvalakSaNapUjitAm .
nArINAM ciravAso hi bAndhaveSu na rocate . kIrticAritradharmajastasmAnnayata mA ciram .
tathetyuktvA tu te sarve prAtiSThanta mahaujasaH . zakuntalAM puraskRtya duSyantasya puraM prati .
gRhItvAmaragarbhAbhaM putraM kamalalocanam . AjagAma tataH subhUrduSyantaM viditAd vanAt .
abhisRtya ca rAjAnaM viditA ca pravezitA . saha tenaiva putreNa bAlArkasamatejasA .
nivedayitvA te sarve AzramaM punarAgatAH . pUjayitvA yathAnyAyamabravIca zakuntalA .
zakuntalovAca ayaM putrastvayA rAjan yauvarAjye ' bhiSicyatAm . tvayA hyayaM suto rAjan mayyutpannaH suropamaH . yathAsamayametasmin vartasva puruSottama .
yathA matsaGgame pUrvaM yaH kRtaH samayastvayA . taM smarasva mahAbhAga kaNvAzramapadaM prati .
so ' tha zrutvaiva tad vAkyaM tasyA rAjA smarannapi . abravInna smarAmIti kasya tvaM duSTatApasi .
dharmakAmArthasambandhaM na smarAmi tvayA saha . gaccha vA tiSTha vA kAmaM yad vApIcchasi tat kuru .
saivamuktA varArohA vIDiteva tapasvinI . ni : saMjJeva ca duHkhena tasthau sthUNeva nizcalA .
saMrambhAmarSatAmrAkSI sphuramANauSThasampuTA . kaTAkSairnirdahantIva tiryag rAjAnamaikSata .
AkAraM gUhamAnAM ca manyunA ca samIritA . tapasA sambhRtaM tejo dhArayAmAsa vai tadA . .
sA muhUrtamiva dhyAtvA duHkhAmarSasamanvitA . bhartAramabhisamprekSya kruddhA vacanamabravIt . jAnannapi mahArAja kasmAdevaM prabhASase . na jAnAmIti niHzaGkaM yathAnyaH prAkRto janaH .
atra te hRdayaM veda satyasyaivAnRtasya ca . kalyANaM vada sAkSyeNa mA ' ' tmAnamavamanyathAH .
yo ' nyathA santamAtmAnamanyathA pratipadyate . kiM tena na kRtaM pApaM caureNAtmApahAriNA .
eko ' hamasmIti ca manyase tvaM na hRcchayaM vetsi muni purANam . yo veditA karmaNaH pApakasya tasyAntike tvaM vRjinaM karopi .
manyate pApakaM kRtvA na kazcid vetti mAmiti . vidanti cainaM devAzca yazcaivAntarapUruSaH .
AdityacandrAvanilAnalau ca dyaurbhUmirApo hRdayaM yamazca . ahazca rAtrizca ubhe ca saMdhye dharmazca jAnAti narasya vRttam .
yamo vaivasvatastasya niryAtayati duSkRtam . hRdi sthitaH karmasAkSI kSetrajJo yasya tuSyati .
na tu tuSyati yasyaiSa puruSasya durAtmanaH . taMyamaH pApakarmANaM viyAtayati duSkRtam .
yo ' vamanyAtmanA ' ' tmAnamanyathA pratipadyate . na tasya devAH zreyAMso yasyAtmApi na kAraNam . svayaM prApteti mAmevaM mAvamaMsthAH pativratAm . arcAhIM nArcayasi mAM svayaM bhAryAmupasthitAm .
kimarthaM mAM prAkRtavadupaprekSasi saMsadi . na khalvahamidaM zUnye raumi kiM na zRNoSi me .
yadi me yAcamAnAyA vacanaM na kariSyasi . duSyanta zatadhA mUrdhA tataste ' dya sphuTiSyati .
bhAryAM patiH sampravizya sa yasmAjAyate punaH . jAyAyAstaddhi jAyAtvaM paurANAH kavayo viduH .
yadAgamavataH puMsastadapatyaM prajAyate . tat tArayati saMtatyA pUrvapretAn pitAmahAn .
putrAmno narakAd yasmAt pitaraM trAyate sutaH . tasmAt putra iti proktaH svayameva svayambhuvA .
( putreNa lokAJjayati pautreNAnantyamaznute . atha pautrasya putreNa modante prapitAmahaH . . )
sA bhAryA yA gRhe dakSA sA bhAryA yA prajAvatI . sA bhAryA yA patiprANA sA bhAryA yA pativratA .
ardhaM bhAryA manuSyasya bhAryA zreSThatamaH sakhA . bhAryA mUlaM trivargasya bhAryA mUlaM tariSyataH .
bhAryAvanta : kriyAvantaH sabhAryA gRhamedhinaH . bhAryAvantaH pramodante bhAryAvantaH zriyAnvitAH .
sakhAyaH pravivikteSu bhavantyetAH priyaMvadAH . pitaro dharmakAryeSu bhavantyArtasya mAtaraH .
kAntAreSvapi vizrAmo janasyAdhvanikasya vai . yaH sadAraH sa vizvAsyastasmAd dArAH parAgatiH .44 .
saMsarantamapi pretaM viSameSvekapAtinam . bhAvAnveti bhartAraM satataM yA pativratA .
prathamaM saMsthitA bhAryA patiM pretya pratIkSate . pUrvaM mRtaM ca bhartAraM pazcAt sAdhvyanugacchati .
etasmAt kAraNAd rAjan pANigrahaNamiSyate . yadApnoti patirbhAryAmihaloke paratra ca .
AtmA ' ' tmanaiva janitaH putra ityucyate budhaiH . tasmAd bhAryAM naraH pazyenmAtRvat putramAtaram .
bhAryAyAM janitaM putramAdarzeSviva cAnanam . hlAdate janitA prekSya svargaM prApyeva puNyakRt .
dahyamAnA manoduHkhairvyAdhibhizcAturA narAH . hlAdante sveSu dAreSu dharmArtAH salileSviva .
susaMrabdho ' pi rAmANAM na kuryAdapriyaM naraH . ratiM prItiM ca dharmaM ca tAsvAyattamavekSya hi .
Atmano janmanaH kSetraM puNyaM rAmAH sanAtanam . RSINAmapi kA zaktiH sraSTuM rAmAmRte prajAm .
pratipadya yadA sUnurdharaNIreNuguNThitaH . piturAzliSyate ' GgAni kimastyabhyadhikaM tataH .
sa tvaM svayamabhiprAptaM sAbhilASamimaM sutam . prekSamANaM kaTAkSeNa kimarthamavamanyase . aNDAni bibhrati svAni na bhindanti pipIlikAH . na bharethAH kathaM na tvaM dharmajJaH san svamAtmajam .
na vAsasAM na rAmANAM nApAM sparzastathAvidhaH . zizorAliGgyamAnasya sparzaH sUnoryathA sukhaH .
brAhmaNo dvipadAM zreSTho gaurvariSThA catuSpadAm . gururgarIyasAM zreSThaH putraH sparzavatAM varaH .
spRzatu tvAM samAzliSya putro ' yaM priyadarzanaH . putrasparzAt sukhataraH sparzo loke na vidyate .
triSu varSeSu pUrNeSu prajAtAhamariMdama . imaM kumAraM rAjendra tava zokavinAzanam . AhartA vAjimedhasya zatasaMkhyasya paurava . iti vAgantarikSe mAM sUtake ' bhyavadat purA .
nanu nAmAGkamAropya snehAd grAmAntaraM gatAH . mUrdhni putrAnupAghrAya pratinandanti mAnavAH .
vedeSvapi vadantImaM mantragrAmaM dvijAtayaH . jAtakarmANi putrANAM tavApi viditaM tathA .
aGgAdaGgAt sambhavasi hRdayAdadhijAyase . AtmA vai putranAmAsi sa jIva zaradaH zatam .
jIvitaM tvadadhInaM me saMtAnamapi cAkSayam . tasmAt tvaM jIva me putra susukhI zaradAM zatam .
tvadaGgebhyaH prasUto ' yaM puruSAt puruSo ' paraH . vai sarasIvAmale ' ' tmAnaM dvitIyaM pazya sutam .
yathA hyAhavanIyo ' gnirgArhapatyAt praNIyate . tathA tvattaH prasUto ' yaM tvamekaH san dvidhA kRtaH . mRgAvakRSTena purA mRgayAM paridhAvatA . ahamAsAditA rAjan kumArI piturAzrame .
urvazI pUrvacittizca sahajanyA ca menakA . vizvAcI ca ghRtAcI ca SaDevApsarasAM varAH .
tAsAM sA menakA nAma brahmayonirvarApsarAH . divaH samprApya jagatIM vizvAmitrAdajIjanat .
sA mAM himavataH prasthe suSuve manekApsarAH . avakIrya ca mAM yAtA parAtmajamivAsatI .
kiM nu karmAzubhaM pUrvaM kRtavatyanyajanmani . yadahaM bAndhavaistyaktA bAlye samprati ca tvayA . .
kAmaM tvayA parityaktA gamiSyAmi svamAzramam . imaM tu bAlaM saMtyaktuM nArhasyAtmajamAtmanaH .
duSyanta uvAca na putramabhijAnAmi tvayi jAtaM zakuntale . asatyavacanA nAryaH kaste zraddhAsyate vacaH . menakA niranukrozA bandhakI jananI tava . yayA himavataH pRSThe nirmAlyamiva cojjhitA .
sa cApi niranukrozaH kSatrayoniH pitA tava . vizvAmitro brAhmaNatve lubdhaH kAmavazaM gataH .
menakApsarasAM zreSThA maharSINAM pitA ca te . tayorapatyaM kasmAt tvaM puMzcalIva prabhASase .
azraddheyamidaM vAkyaM kathayantI na lajase . vizeSato matsakAze duSTatApasi gamyatAm .
