zuzruve tumulaH zabdaH krozatAmitaretaram . putrAnanye pitRRnanye bhrAtRnanye ca mAtulAn .
bhAgineyAn vayasyAMzca tathA sambandhibAndhavAn . utsRjyotsRjya gacchanti tvaritA jIvitepsavaH .
apare mohitA mohAt tamevAbhimukhA yayuH . pANDavAnAM raNe yodhAH paralokaM gatAH pare .
sA tathA pANDavI senA pIDyamAnA mahAtmana . nizi samprAdravad rAjannutsRjyolkAH sahasrazaH .
pazyato bhImasenasya vijayasyAcyutasya ca . yamayodharmaputrasya pArSatasya ca pazyataH .
tamasA saMvRte loke na prAjJAyata kiMcana . kauravANAM prakAzena dRzyante vidrutAH pare .
dravamANaM tu tat sainyaM droNakarNI mahArathau . jaghnatuH pRSThato rAjan kirantau sAyakAn bahUn .
paJcAleSu prabhagneSu kSIyamANeSu sarvataH . janArdano dInamanAH pratyabhASata phAlgunam .
paJcAlAMzcaiva sahitau jaghnatuH sAyakai zam .
etayoH zaravarSeNa prabhagnA no mahArathAH . vAryamANApi kaunteya pRtanA nAvatiSThate .
tAM tu vidravatIM dRSTvA UcatuH kezavArjunau . mA vidravata vitrastA bhayaM tyajata pANDavAH .
tAvAvAM sarvasainyaizca vyUhaiH samyagudAyudhaiH . droNaM ca sUtaputraM ca prayatAvaH prabAdhitum .
etau hi balinau zUrau kRtAsro jitakAzinau . upekSitau tava balairnAzayetAM nizAmimAbh .
tayoH saMvadatorevaM bhImakarmA mahAbalaH . AyAd vRkodaraH zIghraM punarAvartya vAhinIm .
vRkodaramathAyAntaM dRSTvA tatra janArdanaH . punarevAbravId rAjan harSayanniva pANDavam .
eSa bhImo raNazlAghI vRtaH somakapANDavaiH . abhyavartata vegena droNakarNI mahArathau .
etena sahitau yuddhya paJcAlaizca mahArathaiH . AzvAsanArthaM sainyAnAM sarveSAM pANDunandana .
tatastau puruSavyAghrAvubhau mAdhavapANDavau . droNakarNI samAsAdya ghiSThitau raNamUrdhani .
saMjaya uvAca tatastat punarAvRttaM yudhiSThirabalaM mahat . tato droNazca karNazca parAn mamRdaturyudhi .
sa samprahArastumulo nizi pratyabhavanmahAn . yathA sAgarayo rAjazcandrodayavivRddhayoH .
tata utsRjya pANibhyAM pradIpAMstava vAhinI . yuyudhe pANDavaiH sArdhamunmattavadasaMkulA .
rajasA tamasA caiva saMvRte bhRzadAruNe . kevalaM nAmagotreNa prAyudhyanta jayaiSiNaH .
azrUyanta hi nAmAni zrAvyamANAni pArthivaiH . praharadbhirmahArAja svayaMvara ivAhave .
niHzabdamAsIt sahasA punaH zabdo mahAnabhUt . kruddhAnAM yudhyamAnAnAM jIyatAM jayatAmapi .
yatra yatra sma dRzyante pradIpajJaH kurusattamA tatra tatra sma zUrAste nipatanti etagavat .
tathA saMyudhyamAnAnAM vigADhAsInmahAnizA . pANDavAnAM ca rAjendra kauravANAM ca sarvazaH .
saMjaya uvAca dharmarAjasya tad vAkyaM nizamya zinipuGgavaH . sa pArthAd bhayamAzaMsan parityAgAnmahIpateH .
apavAda hyAtmanazca lokAt pazyan vizeSataH . te mAM bhItamiti brUyurAyAntaM phAlgunaM prati .
nizcitya bahudhaivaM sa sAtyakiyuddhadurmadaH . dharmarAjamidaM vAkyamabravIt puruSarSabhaH .
kRtAM cenmanyase rakSAM svasti te ' stu vizAmpate . anuyAsyAmi bIbhatsuM kariSye vacanaM tava .
na hi me pANDavAt kazcit triSu lokeSu vidyate . yo me priyataro rAjan satyametad bravImi te .
tasyAhaM padavIM yAsye saMdezAt tava mAnada . tvatkRte na ca me kiMcidakartavyaM kathaMcana .
yathA hi me gurorvAkyaM viziSTaM dvipadAM vara . tathA tavApi vacanaM viziSTatarameva me .
priye hi tava vartate bhrAtarau kRSNapANDavau . tayoH priye sthitaM caiva viddhi mAM rAjapuGgava .
tavAjJAM zirasA gRhya pANDavArthamahaM prabho . bhittvedaM durbhidaM sainyaM prayAsye parapuGgava .
droNAnIkaM vizAmyeSa kruddho jhaSa ivArNavam . tatra yAsyAmi yatrAsau rAjan rAjA jayadrathaH .
yatra senAM samAzritya bhItastiSThati pANDavAt gupto rathavarazreSThaidrauNikarNakRpAdibhiH .
itastriyojanaM manye tamadhvAnaM vizAmpate . yatra tiSThati pArtho ' sau jayadrathavadhodyataH .
triyojanagatasyApi tasya yAsyAmyahaM padam . AsaindhavavadhAna rAjan sudRDhenAntarAtmanA .
anAdiSTastu guruNA ko nu yudhyeta mAnavaH . AdiSTastu yathA rAjan ko na yudhyeta mAdRzaH .
abhijAnAmi taM dezaM yatra yAsyAmyahaM prabho . halazaktigadAprAsacarmakhaDgaTitomaram .
iSvasravarasambAdhaM kSobhayiSye balArNavam . yadeta . kuJjarAnIkaM sAhasramanupazyasi .
kulamAJjanakaM nAma yatraite vIryazalinaH . AsthitA bahubhirlecchairyuddhazauNDaiH prahAribhiH .
nAgA meghanibhA rAjan kSaranta iva toyadAH . naite jAtu nivarteran preSitA hastisAdibhiH .
anyatra hi vadhAdeSAM nAsti rAjan parAjayaH . atha yAn rathino rAjan sahasramanupazyasi .
ete rukmarathA nAma rAjaputrA mahArathAH . ratheSvasreSu nipuNA nAgeSu ca vizAmpate .
dhanurveda gatAH pAraM muSTiyuddhe ca kovidAH . gadAyuddhavizeSajJA niyuddhakuzalAstathA .
khaDgapraharaNe yuktAH sampAte cAsicarmaNoH . zUrAzca kRtavidyAzca spardhante ca parasparam .
nityaM hi samare vijigISanti mAnavAn . karNena vihitA rAjan duHzAsanamanuvratAH .
etAMstu vAsudevo ' pi rathodArAn prazaMsati . satataM priyakAmAzca karNasyaite vaze sthitAH .
tasyaiva vacanAd rAjan nivRttAH zvetavAhanAt . te na klAntA na ca zrAntA dRDhAvaraNakArmukAH .
madarthe ' dhiSThitA nUnaM dhArtarASTrasya zAsanAt . etAn pramathya saMgrAme priyArthe tava kaurava .
prayAsyAmi tataH pazcAt padavIM savyasAcinaH . yAMstvetAnaparAn rAjan nAgAn sapta zatAnimAn .
prekSase varmasaMchannAn kirAtaiH samadhiSThitAn . kirAtarAjo yAn prAdAd dviradAn savyasAcinaH . svalaMkRtAMstadA preSyAnicchaJjIvitamAtmanaH . Asannete purA rAjasva karmakarA dRDham .
tvAmevAdya yuyutsante pazya kAlasya paryayam . eSAmete mahAmAtrAH kirAtA yuddhadurmadAH . hastizikSAvidazcaiva sarve caivAgniyonayaH . ete vinirjitA : saMkhye saMgrAme savyasAcinA .
madarthamadya saMyattA duryodhavazAnugA : etAn hatvA zare rAjan kirAtAn yuddhadurmadAn .
saindhavasya vadhe yattamanuyAsyAmi pANDavam . ye tvete sumahAnAgA aJjanasya kulodbhavAH .
karkazAzca vinItAzca prabhinnakaraTAmukhAH . jAmbUnadamayaiH sarve varmabhiH suvibhUSitAH .
labdhalakSyA raNe rAjannairAvaNAsamA yudhi . uttarAt parvatAdete tIkSNairdusyubhirAsthitAH .
karkazaiH pravarairyodhaiH kArNAyasatanucchaiH . santi goyonayazcAtra santi vAnarayonayaH . anekayonayazcAnye tathA mAnuSayonayaH . anIkaM samavetAnAM dhUmravarNamudIryate . mlecchAnA pApakartRNA himadurganivAsinAm . etad duryodhano labdhvA samagraM rAja maNDalam .
kRpaM ca saumadattiM ca droNaM ca rathinAM varam . sindhurAjaM tathA karNamavamanyata pANDavAn .
kRtArthamatha cAtmAnaM manyate kAlacoditaH . te tu sarve ' dya samprAptA mama nArAcagocaram .
na vimokSyanti kaunteya yadyapi syurmanojavAH . tena sambhAvitA nityaM paravIryopajIvinA .
vinAzumupayAsyanti maccharaughanipIDitAH . ye tvete rathino rAjan dRzyante kAJcanadhvajAH .
ete durvAraNA nAma kAmbojA yadi te zrutAH . zUrAzca kRtavidyAzca dhanurveda ca niSThitAH .
saMhatAzca bhRzaM hyete anyonyasya hitaiSiNaH . akSauhiNyazca saMrabdhA dhArtarASTrasya bhArata .
yattA madarthe tiSThanti kuruvIrAbhirakSitAH . apramattA mahArAja mAmeva pratyupasthitAH .
tAnahaM pramathiSyAmi tRNAnIva hutAzanaH . tasmAt sarvAnupAsaMgAn sarvopakaraNAni ca . rathe kurvanta te rAjan yathAvad rathakalpakAH . asmistu kila samma grAhyaM vividhamAyudham .
yathopadiSTamAcAryaiH kAryaH paJcaguNo rathaH . kAmbojairhi sameSyAmi tIkSNairAzIviSopamaiH .
nAnAzastrasamAvAyairvividhAyudhayodhibhiH . kirAtaizca sameSyAmi viSakalpaiH prahAribhiH .
lAlitaiH satataM rAjJA duryodhanahitaiSibhiH . zakaizcApi sameSyAmi zakratulyaparAkramaiH .
agnikalpairdurAdharSaH pradIptairiva pAvakaiH . tathAnyairvividhairyodhaiH kAlakalpairdurAsadaiH .
sameSyAmi raNe rAjan bahubhiryuddhadurmadaiH . tasmAd vaivAjino vizrAntAH zubhalakSaNAH .
saMjaya uvAca upAvRttAzca pItAzca punaryujyayantu me rathe . tasya sarvAnupAsaMgAn sarvopakaraNAni ca .
rathe cAsthApayad rAjA zastrANi vividhAni ca . tatastAn sarvato yuktAn sadazvAMzcaturo janAH .
rasavat pAyayAmAsuH pAnaM madasamIraNam . pItopavRttAn snAtAMzca jagdhAnnAn samalaMkRtAn .
vinItazalyAMsturagAMzcaturo hemamAlinaH . tAn yuktAn rukmavarNAbhAn vinItvzIghragAminaH .
saMhRSTamanaso ' vyagrAn vidhivatkalpitAn rathe . mahAdhvajena siMhena hemakesaramAlinA . saMvRte ketakaimairmaNivadvimacitritaiH pANDurAbhraprakAzAbhiH patAkAbhiralaMkRte . hemadaNDocchritacchatre bahuzastraparicchade . yojayAmAsa vidhivaddhemabhANDavibhUSitAn . dArukasyAnujo bhrAtA sUtasyasya priyaH sastrA . nyavedayad rathaM yuktaM vAsavasyeva mAtaliH .
tataH snAtaH zucirbhUtvA kRtakautukamaGgalaH . snAtakAnAM sahastrasya svarNaniSkAnatho dadau .
AzIrvAdaiH pariSvaktaH sAtyakiH zrImatAMvaraH . tataH sa madhuparkArhaH pItvA kailAtakaM madhu . lohitAkSo babhau tatra madavihvalalocanaH . Alabhya vIrakAMsyaM ca harSeNa mahatAnvitaH .
dviguNIkRtatejA hi prajvalanniva pAvakaH . utsaGge dhanurAdAya sazaraM rathinAM varaH .
kRtasvastyayano vipraiH kavacI samalaMkRtaH . lAjairgandhaistathA mAlyaiH kanyAbhizcAbhinanditaH . yudhiSThirasya caraNAvabhivAdya kRtAJjaliH . tena mUrdhanyupAghrAta Aruroha mahAratham . tataste vAjino hRSTAH supuSTAH vAtaraMhasaH . ajayyA jaitramUhustaM vikurvANAH sma saindhavAH .
tathaiva bhImaseno ' pi dharmarAjena pUjitaH . prAyAt sAtyakinA sArdhabhivAdya yudhiSThiram .
tau hRSTavA pravivikSantau tava senAmariMdamau . saMyattAstAvakAH sarve tasthuTTaiNapurogamAH .
saMnaddhamanugacchantaM dRSTavA bhImaM sa sAtyakiH . abhinandyAbravId vIrastadA harSakaraM vacaH . tvaM bhIma rakSa rAjAnametat kAryatamaM hi te . ahaM bhittvA pravakSyAmi kAlapakvamidaM balam .
AyatyAM ca tadAtve ca zreyo rAjJo ' bhirakSaNam . jAnISe mama vIrye tvaM tava cAhamariMdama .
tasmAd bhIma nivartakha mama cedicchasi priyam . tathoktaH sAtyakiM prAha vraja tvaM kAryasiddhaye .
ahaM rAjJaH kariSyAmi rakSAM puruSasattama . evamuktaH pratyuvAca bhImesanaM sa mAdhavaH .
yanme guNAnuraktazca tvamadya vazamAsthitaH .
nimittAni ca dhanyAni yathA bhIma vadanti mAm . nihate saindhave pApe pANDavena mahAtmanA .
pariSvajiSye rAjAnaM dharmAtmAnaM yudhiSThiram . etAvaduktvA bhImaM tu visRjya ca mahAyazAH . samprekSat tAvakaM sainyaM vyAghro mRgagaNAniva .
taM dRSTvA pravivikSantaM sainyaM tava janAdhipa . bhUya evAbhavanmUDhaM subhRzaM cApyakampata . tataH prayAtaH sahasA tava sainyaM sa sAtyakiH . dihakSurarjunaM rAjan dharmarAjasya zAsanAt .
vaizampAyana uvAca tathA tu dRSTvA bahu tatra devIM rorUyamANAM kurarImivArtAm . nocurvacaH sAdhvatha vApyasAdhu mahIkSito dhArtarASTrasya bhItAH .
stUSNIbhUtAn dhRtarASTrasya putraH . smayannivedaM vacanaM babhASe pAJcAlarAjasya sutAM tadAnIm .
duryodhana uvAca tiSThatvayaM prazna udArasattve bhIme ' rjune sahadeve tathaiva . patyau ca te nakule yAjJaseni vadantvete vacanaM tvatprasUtam .
anIzvaraM vibruvantvAryamadhye yudhiSThiraM tava pAJcAli hetoH . kurvantu sarve cAnRtaM dharmarAja pAJcAli tvaM mokSyase dAsabhAvAt .
dharme sthito dharmasuto mahAtmA svayaM cedaM kathayatvindrakalpaH . Izo vA te hyanIzo ' tha vaiSa vAkyAdasya kSipramekaM bhajasva .
sarve hIme kauraveyAH sabhAyAM duHkhAntare vartamAnAstavaiva . na vibruvantyAryasattvA yathAvat patIMzca te samavekSyAlpabhAgyAn .
vaizampAyana uvAca tataH sabhyAH kururAjasya tasya vAkyaM sarve prazazaMsustathoccaiH . celAvedhAMzcApi cakrurnadanto hAhetyAsIdapi caivArtanAdaH .
ddharSazcAsIt kauravANAM sabhAyAm . sarve cAsan pArthivAH prItimantaH kuruzreSThaM dhArmikaM pUjayantaH .
yudhiSThiraM ca te sarve samudaikSanta pArthivAH . kiM nu vakSyati dharmajJa iti sAcIkRtAnanAH .
kiM nu vakSyati bIbhatsurajito yudhi pANDavaH . bhImaseno yamau cobhau bhRzaM kautUhalAnvitAH .
tasminnaparate zabde bhImaseno ' bravIdidam . pragRhya ruciraM divyaM bhujaM candanacarcitam .
bhImasena uvAca yoSa gururasmAkaM dharmarAjo mahAmanAH . na prabhuH syAt kulasyAsya na vayaM marSayemahi .
Izo naH puNyatapasAM prANAnAmapi cezvaraH . manyate ' jitamAtmAnaM yadyeSa vijitA vayam .
na hi mucyeta me jIvan padA bhUmimupaspRzan . martyadharmA parAmRzya pAJcAlyA mUrdhajAnimAn .
pazyadhvaM hyAyatau vRttau bhujau me parighAviva . tayorantaraM prApya mucyetApi zatakratuH .
dharmapAzasitastvevaM nAdhigacchAmi saMkaTam . goraveNa viruddhazca nigrahAdarjunasya ca .
dharmarAjanisRSTastu siMhaH kSudramRgAniva . dhArtarASTrAnimAn pApAn niSpidheyaM talAsibhiH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tamuvAca tadA bhISmo droNo vidura eva ca . kSamyatAmidamityevaM sarvaM sambhAvyate tvayi .
bhISma uvAca samAgatasya rAmeNa punarevAtidAruNam . anyedhustumulaM yuddhaM tadA bharatasattama .
tato divyAstravicchUro divyAnyastrANyanekazaH . ayojayat sa dharmAtmA divase divase vibhuH .
tAnyahaM tatpratIghAtairastrairastrANi bhArata . vyadhamaM tumule yuddhe prANAMstyaktvA sudustyajAn .
astrairastreSu bahudhA hateSveva ca bhArata . akrudhyata mahAtejAstyaktaprANaH sa saMyuge .
tataH zaktiM prAhiNod ghorUpAmastre ruddha jAmadagnyo mahAtmA . kAlotsRSTAM prajvalitAmivolkA saMdIptAnAM tejasA vyApya lokam .
tato ' haM tAmiSubhirdIpyamAnAM samAyAntImantakAlArkadIptAm . chittvA tridhA pAtayAmAsa bhUmau tato vavau pavanaH puNyagandhiH .
tasyAM chinnAyAM krodhadIpto ' tha rAmaH zaktI?rAH prAhiNod dvAdazAnyAH . tAsAM rUpaM bhArata nota zakyaM tejasvitvAllAghavAccaiva vaktum .
kiM tvevAhaM vihvalaH sampradRzya digbhyaH sarvAstA maholkA ivAgneH . nAnArUpAstejasogreNa dIptA yathA ' ' dityA dvAdaza lokasaMkSaye .
tato jAlaM bANamayaM vivRttaM saMdRzya bhittvA zarajAlena rAjan . dvAdazeSUn prAhiNavaM raNe ' haM tataH zaktIrapyadhamaM ghorarUpAH .
tato rAjaJjAmadagnyo mahAtmA zaktI?rA vyAkSipaddhemadaNDAH . vicitritAH kAJcanapaTTanaddhA yathA maholkA jvalitAstathA tAH .
tAzcApyucAzcamarNA vArayitvA khaDDrenAjau pAtayitvA nerandra . bANairdivyairjAmadagnyasya saMkhye divyAnazvAnabhyavarSa sasUtAn .
nirmuktAnAM pannAgAnAM sarUpA dRSTvA zaktIhemacitrA nikRttAH . prAduzcakre divyamastraM mahAtmA krodhAviSTo haihayezapramAthI .
tataH zreNyaH zalabhAnAmivogrAH samApeturvizikhAnA pradIptAH . samAcinoccApi bhRzaM zarIraM hayAn sUtaM sarathaM caiva mahyam .
rathaH zarairme nicitaH sarvato ' bhUt tathA vAhAH sArathizcaiva rAjan . yugaM ratheSAM ca tathaiva cakre tathaivAkSaH zarakRtto ' tha bhagnaH .
tatastasmin bANavarSe vyatIte zaraugheNa pratyavarSaM guruM tam . sa vikSato mArgaNairbrahmarAzidehAdasaktaM mumuce bhUri raktam .
stathaivAhaM subhRzaM gADhaviddhaH . tato yuddhaM vyaramaccAparAve bhAnAvastaM prati yAte mahIdhram .
vaizampAyana uvAca sa zvetaparvataM vIraH samatikramya vIryavAn . dezaM kimpuruSAvAsaM dumaputreNa rakSitam .
mahatA saMnipAtena kSatriyAntakareNa ha . ajayat pANDavazreSThaH kare cainaM nyavezayat .
taM jitvA hATakaM nAma dezaM guhyakarakSitam . pAkazAsaniravyagraH sahasainyaH samAsadat .
tAMstu sAntvena nirjitya mAnasaM sara uttamam . RSikulyAstathA sarvA dadarza kurunandanaH .
saro mAnasamAsAdya hATakAnabhitaH prabhuH . gandharvarakSitaM dezamajayat pANDavastataH .
tatra tittirikalmASAn maNDUkAkhyAn hayottamAn . lebhe sa karamatyantaM gandharvanagarAt tadA .
uttaraM kuruvarSaM tu samAsAdya pANDavaH . iyeSa jetuM taM dezaM pAkazAsananandanaH .
tata enaM mahAvIryaM mahAkAyA mahAbalAH . dvArapAlA : samAsAdya hRSTAH vacanamabruvan .
pArtha nedaM tvayA zakyaM puraM jetuM kathaMcana . upAvartasva kalyANa paryAptamidamacyuta .
idaM puraM yaH pravized dhruvaM na sa bhavennaraH . prIyAmahe tvayA vIra paryApto vijayastava .
na cAtra kiMcijjetavyamajunAtra pradRzyate . uttarAH kuravo hyete nAtra yuddhaM pravartate .
praviSTo ' pi hi kaunteya neha drakSyasi kiMcana . na hi mAnuSadehena zakyamatrAbhivIkSitum .
atheha puruSavyAghra kiMcidanyaccikIrSasi . tat prabrUhi kariSyAmo vacanAt tava bhArata .
tatastAnabravId rAjannarjunaH prahasannivA pArthivatvaM cikIrSAmi dharmarAjasya dhImataH .
na pravekSyAmi vo dezaM viruddhaM yadi mAnuSaiH . yudhiSThirAya yat kiMcit karapaNyaM pradIyatAm .
tato divyAni vastrANi divyAnyAbharaNAni ca . kSaumAjinAni divyAni tasya te pradaduH karam .
evaM sa puruSavyAghro vijitya dizamuttarAm . saMgrAmAn subahUn kRtvA kSatriyairdasyubhistathA .
sa vinirjitya rAjJastAn kare ca vinivezya tu . dhanAnyAdAya sarvebhyo ratnAni vividhAni ca .
hayAMstittirikalmASAJchukapatranibhAnapi . mayUrasadRzAnanyAn sarvAnanilaraMhasaH .
vRtaH sumahatA rAjan balena caturaGgiNA . AjagAma punarvIraH zakraprasthaM purottamam .
dharmarAjAya tat pArtho dhanaM sarvaM savAhanam . nyavedayadanujJAtastena rAjJA gRhAn yayau .
vaizampAyana uvAca evaM sa nAhuSo rAjA yayAtiH putramIpsitam . rAjye ' bhiSicya mudito vAnaprastho ' bhavanmuniH .
uSitvA ca vane vAsaM brAhmaNaiH saMzitavrataH . phalamUlAzano dAntastata : svargamito gataH .
sa gataH svarnivAsaM taM nivasan muditaH sukhI . kAlena cAtimahatA punaH zakreNa pAtitaH . nipatan pracyutaH svargAdaprApto medinItalam . sthita AsIdantarikSe sa tadeti zrutaM mayA .
tata eva punazcApi gataH svargamiti zrutam . rAjJA vasumatA sArdhamaSTakena ca vIryavAn . pratardanena zibinA sametya kila saMsadi .
janamejaya uvAca karmaNA kena sa divaM punaH prApto mahIpatiH .6 .
sarvametadazeSeNa zrotumicchAmi tattvataH . kathyamAnaM tvayA vipra viprarSigaNasaMnidhau . devarAjasamo hyAsId yayAtiH pRthivIpatiH . vardhanaH kuruvaMzasya vibhAvasusamadyutiH . tasya vistIrNayazasaH satyakIrtermahAtmanaH . caritaM zrotumicchAmi divi ceha ca sarvazaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca hanta te kathayiSyAmi yayAteruttamAM kathAm . divi ceha ca puNyArthI sarvapApapraNAzinIm .
yayAti huSo rAjA pUrUM putraM kanIyasam . rAjye ' bhiSicya muditaH pravavrAja vanaM tadA . antyeSu sa vinikSipya putrAn yadupurogamAn . phalamUlAzano rAjA vane saMnyavasaciram .
zaMsitAtmA jitakrodhastarpayan pitRdevatAH agnIMzca vidhivatruhvan vAnaprasthavidhAnataH .
atithIn pUjayAmAsa vanyena haviSA vibhuH . zilocchavRttimAsthAya zeSAnnakRtabhojanaH .
pUrNa varSasahasraM ca evaMvRttirabhUnRpaH . abbhakSaH zaradastriMzadAsIniyatavAGganAH . tatazca vAyubhakSo ' bhUt saMvatsaramatandritaH . tathA paJcAgnimadhye ca tapastepe sa vatsaram . ekapAdaH sthitazcAsIt SaNmAsAnanilAzanaH . puNyakIrtistataH svarge jagAmAvRtya rodasI .
bhImasena uvAca paurogavo bruvANo ' haM ballavo nAma bhArata . upasthAsyAmi rAjAnaM virATamiti me matiH . . . .
sUpAnasya kariSyAmi kuzalo ' smi mahAnase . kRtapUrvANi yAnyasya vyaJjanAni suzikSitaiH . tAnyapyabhibhaviSyAmi prItiM saMjanayantraham . AhariSyAmi dArUNAM nicayAn mahato ' pi ca . yat prekSya vipulaM karma rAjA saMyokSyate sa mAm . amAnuSANi kurvANastAni karmANi bhArata . rAjJastasya pare preSyA maMsyante mAM yathA nRpam . bhakSyAnnarasapAnAnAM bhaviSyAmi tathezvaraH .
dvipA vA balino rAjan vRSabhA vA mahAbalAH . vinigrAhyA yadi mayA nigrahISyAmi tAnapi . ye ca kecinniyotsyanti samAjeSu niyodhakAH . tAnahaM hi niyotsyAmi ratiM tasya vivardhayan . na tvetAn yuddhyamAnAn vai haniSyAmi kathaJcana . tathaitAn pAtayiSyAmi yathA yAsyanti na kSayam .
ArAliko govikartA sUpakartA niyodhakaH . AsaM yudhiSThirasyAhamiti vakSyAmi pRcchataH . AtmAnamAtmanA rakSazcariSyAmi vizAmpate . ityetat pratijAnAmi vihariSyAmyahaM yathA .
yudhiSThira uvAca yamagnirbrAhmaNo bhUtvA samAgacchannRNAM varam . didhakSuH khANDavaM dAvaM dAzArhasahitaM purA . mahAbalaM mahAbAhumajitaM kurunandanam . so ' yaM kiM karma kaunteyaH kariSyati dhanaMjayaH .
yo ' yamAsAdya taM dAvaM tarpayAmAsa pAvakam . vijityaikarathenendraM hatvA pannagarAkSasAn . vAsukeH sarparAjasya svasAraM hRtavAMzca yaH . zreSTho yaH pratiyodhAnAM so ' rjunaH kiM kariSyati .
sUryaH pratapatAM zreSTho dvipadAM brAhmaNo varaH . AzIviSazca sarpANAmagnistejasvinAM varaH . AyudhAnAM varaM vajraM kakudmI ca gavAM varaH . hradAnAmudadhiH zreSThaH parjanyo varSatAM varaH . dhRtarASTrazca nAgAnAM hastiSvairAvaNo varaH . putraH priyANAmadhiko bhAryA ca suhRdAM varA . yathaitAni viziSTAni jAtyAM jAtyAM vRkodara . evaM yuvA guDAkeza : zreSThaH sarvadhanuSmatAm .
so ' yamindrAdanavaro vAsudevAnmahAdyutiH . gANDIvadhanvA bIbhatsuH zvetAzvaH kiM kariSyati .
uSitvA paJca varSANi sahasrAkSasya vezmani . astrayogaM samAsAdya svavIryAnmAnuSAdbhutam . divyAnyastrANi cAptAni devarUpeNa bhAsvatA . yaM manye dvAdazaM rudramAdityAnAM trayodazam . vasUnAM navamaM manye grahANAM dazamaM tathA . yasya bAhU samau dI? jyAghAtakaThinatvacau . dakSiNe caiva savye ca gavAmiva vahaH kRtaH . himavAniva zailAnAM samudraH saritAmiva . tridazAnAM yathA zakro vasUnAmiva havyavAT . mRgANAmiva zArdUlo garuDaH patatAmiva . varaH saMnyamAnAnAM so ' rjunaH kiM kariSyati .
arjuna uvAca pratijJA ghaNDhako ' smIti kariSyAmi mahIpate . jyAghAtau hi mahAntau me saMvartuM nRpa duSkarau .
valayaizchAdayiSyAmi bAhU kiNakRtAvimau . karNayoH pratimucyAhaM kuNDale jvalanaprabhe .
pinaddhakambuH pANibhyAM tRtIyAM prakRtiM gataH . veNIkRtazirA rAjan nAmnA caiva bRhannalA . . paThannAkhyAyikAzcaiva strIbhAvena punaH punaH . ramayiSye mahIpAlamanyAMzcAntaHpure janAn .
