yudhiSThirasya gehe vai draupadyAH paricArikA . uSitAsmIti vakSyAmi pRSTo rAjJA ca pANDava .
etena vidhinA channaH kRtakena yathAnalaH . vihariSyAmi rAjendra virATabhavane sukham .
sanatsujAta uvAca zokaH krodhazca lobhazca kAmo mAnaH parAsutA . IrSyA moho vidhitsA ca kRpA ' sUyA jugupsutA . dvAdazaite mahAdoSA manuSyaprANanAzanAH .
ekaikamete rAjendra manuSyAn paryupAsate . yairAviSTo naraH pApaM mUDhasaMjJo vyavasyati .
