dravyavAn guNavAneva tyAgI bhavati sAttvikaH . paJca bhUtAni paJcabhyo nivartayati tAdRzaH .
etat samRddhamapyUrdhvaM tapo bhavati kevalam . sattvAt pracyavamAnAnAM saMkalpena samAhitam .
