saMkalpasiddhaM puruSamasaMkalpo ' dhitiSThati . brAhmaNasya vizeSeNa kiJcAnyadapi me zRNu .
adhyApayenmahadetad yazasyaM vAco vikArAH kavayo vadanti . asmin yoge sarvamidaM pratiSThitaM ye tad viduramRtAste bhavanti .
na karmaNA sukRtenaiva rAjan satyaM jayejjuhuyAd vA yajed vA . naitena bAlo ' mRtyumabhyeti rAjan rati cAsau na labhatyantakAle .
tUSNImeka upAsIta ceSTeta manasA ' pi na . tathA saMstutinindAbhyAM prItiroSau vivarjayet .
