manuruvAca akSarAt khaM tato vAyustato jyotistato jalam . jalAt prasUtA jagatI jagatyAM jAyate jagat .
etaiH zarIrairjalameva gatvA jalAcca tejaH pavano ' ntarikSam khAd vai nivartanti na bhAvinaste mokSaM ca te vai paramApnuvanti .
noSNaM na zItaM mRdu nApi tIkSNaM nAmlaM kaSAyaM madhuraM na tiktam . nna rUpavattat paramasvabhAvam .
sparza tanurveda rasaM ca jihvA ghrANaM ca gandhAn zravaNau ca zabdAn . rUpANi cakSurna ca tatparaM yad gRhNantyanadhyAtmavido manuSyAH .
nivartayitvA rasanAM rasebhyoH ghrANaM ca gandhAcchravaNau ca zabdAt . stataH paraM pazyati svaM svabhAvam .
yato gRhItvA hi karoti yacca yasmizca tAmArabhate pravRttim . yasmizca yad kena ca yazca kartA yat kAraNaM te samudAyamAhuH .
yad vyApyabhUd vyApakaM sAdhakaM ca yanmantravat sthAsyati cApi loke . yaH sarvahetuH paramAtmakArI tat kAraNaM kAryamato yadanyat .
yathA hi kazcit sukRtairmanuSyaH zubhAzubhaM prApnute ' thAvirodhAt . evaM zarIreSu zubhAzubheSu svakarmajainimidaM nibaddham .
yathA pradIptaH purataH pradIpaH prakAzamanyasya karoti dIpyan . tatheha paJcendriyadIpavRkSA jJAnapradIptAH paravanta eva .
yathA ca rAjJA bahavo hyamAtyAH pRthak pramANaM pravadanti yuktAH . tadvaccharIreSu bhavanti paJca jJAnaikadezaH paramaH sa tebhyaH .
yathArciSo ' gneH pavanasya vego marIcayo ' rkasya nadISu cApaH . stadvaccharIrANi zarIriNAM tu .
yathA ca kazcit parazuM gRhItvA dhUmaM ca pazyejjvalanaM ca kASThe . tadvaccharIrodarapANipAdaM chittvA na pazyanti tato yadanyat .
tAnyeva kASThAni yathA vimathya dhUmaM ca pazyejjvalanaM ca yogAt . tadvat sabuddhiH samamindriyAtmA budhaH paraM pazyati taM svabhAvam .
yathAtmano ' GgaM patitaM pRthivyAM svapnAntare pazyati cAtmano ' nyat . rliGgAttathA gacchati liGgamanyat .
na yujyate ' sau paramaH zarIrI . anena liGgena tu liGgamanyad gacchatyadRSTaH phalasaMniyogAt .
na cakSuSA pazyati rUpamAtmano na cApi saMsparzamupaiti kiMcit . na cApi taiH sAdhayate tu kArya te taM na pazyanti sa pazyate tAn .
yathA samIpe jvalato ' nalasya saMtApajaM rUpamupaiti kazcit . na cAntaraM rUpaguNaM bibharti tathaiva tad dRzyati rUpamasya .
madRzyamanyad vizate zarIram . visRjya bhUteSu mahatsu dehaM tadAzrayaM caiva bibharti rUpam .
khaM vAyumagni salilaM tathorvI samantato ' bhyAvizate zarIrI . nAnAzrayAH karmasu vartamAnAH zrotrAdayaH paJca guNAn zrayante . .
stejomayaM rUpamatho vipAkaH . jalAzrayaM svedamuktaM rasaM ca vAyvAtmakaH sparzakRto guNazca .
mahatsu bhUteSu vasanti paJca paJcendriyArthAzca tathendriyANi . sarvANi caitAni mano ' nugAni buddhiM mano ' nveti matiH svabhAvam .
zubhAzubhaM karma kRtaM yadanyat tadeva pratyAdadate svadehe . mano ' nuvartanti parAvarANi jalaukasaH srota ivAnukUlam .
calaM yathA dRSTipathaM parati sUkSmaM mahada rUpamivAbhibhAti . svarUpamAlocayate ca rUpaM paraM tathA buddhipathaM paraiti .
yudhiSThira uvAca gRhastho brahmacArI vA vAnaprastho ' tha bhikSukaH . ya icchet siddhimAsthAtuM devatAM kAM yajeta saH .
kuto hyasya dhruvaH svargaH kuto naiHzreyasaM param . vidhinA kena juhuyAd daiva pitryaM tathaiva ca .
muktazca kAM gatiM gacchenmokSacaiva kimAtmakaH . svargatazcaiva kiM kuryAd yena na cyavate diva .
devatAnAM ca ko devaH pitRRNAM ca pitA tathA . tasmAt parataraM yacca tanme brUhi pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca gUDhaM mAM praznavit praznaM pRcchase tvamihAnagha . na hyetat tarkayA zakyaM vaktuM varSazatairapi .
Rte devaprasAdAd vA rAjan jJAnAgamena vA . gahanaM hyedAkhyAnaM vyAkhyAtavyaM tavArihan .
atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . nAradasya ca saMvAdamRSernArAyaNasya ca .
nArAyaNo hi vizvAtmA caturmUrtiH sanAtanaH . dharmAtmajaH sambabhUva pitaivaM me ' bhyabhASata . kRte yuge mahArAja purA svAyambhuve ' ntare . naro nArAyaNazcaiva hariH kRSNaH svayambhuvaH .
teSAM nArAyaNanarau tapastepaturavyayau . badaryAzramamAsAdya zakaTe kanakAmaye .
aSTacakraM hi tad yAnaM bhUtayuktaM manoramam . tatrAdyau lokanAthau tau kRzau dhamanisaMtatau . tapasA tejasA caiva durnirIkSyau surairapi . yasya prasAdaM kurvAte sa devau draSTumarhati .
nUnaM tayoranumate hRdi hRcchayacoditaH . mahAmerogireH zRGgAt pracyuto gandhamAdanam .
nAradaH sumahadbhUtaM sarvalokAnacIcarat . taM dezamagamad rAjan badaryAzramamAzugaH .
tayorAhnikavelAyAM tasya kautUhalaM tvabhUt . idaM tadAspadaM kRtsnaM yasmillokAH pratiSThitAH . sadevAsuragandharvAH sakinnaramahoragAH .
ekA mUrtiriyaM pUrvaM jAtA bhUyazcaturvidhA . dharmasya kulasaMtAne dharmAdebhirvivardhitaH .
aho hyanugRhIto ' dya dharma ebhiH surairaha . naranArAyaNAbhyAM ca kRSNena hariNA tathA .
atra kRSNo harizcaiva kasmiMzcit kAraNAntare . sthitau dharmottarau hoto tathA tapasi dhiSThitau .
etau hi paramaM dhAma kAnayorAhnikakriyA . pitarau sarvabhUtAnAM daivataM ca yazasvinau . kAM devatAM tu yajataH pitRRn vA kAn mahAmatI .
iti saMcintya manasA bhaktyA nArAyaNasya tu . sahasA prAdurabhavat samIpe devayostadA .
kRte daive ca pitrye ca tatastAbhyAM nirIkSitaH . pUjitazcaiva vidhinA yathAproktena zAstrataH .
tad dRSTvA mahadAzcaryamapUrvaM vidhivistaram . upopaviSTaH suprIto nArado bhagavAnRSiH .
nArAyaNaM saMnirIkSya prasannenAntarAtmanA . namaskRtvA mahAdevamidaM vacanamabravIt .
nArada uvAca vedeSu sapurANeSu sAGgopAGgeSu gIyase . tvamajaH zAzvato dhAtA mAtAmRtamanuttamam . pratiSThitaM bhUtabhavyaM tvayi sarvamidaM jagat .
catvAro hyAzramA deva sarve gArhasthyamUlakAH . yajante tvAmaharaharnAnAmUrtisamAsthitam .
pitA mAtA ca sarvasya jagataH zAzvato guruH . kaM tvadya yajase devaM pitaraM kaM na vidmahe .
zrI bhagavAnuvAca avAcyametad vaktavyamAtmaguhyaM sanAtanam . tava bhaktimato brahman vakSyAmi tu yathAtatham .
