balaM jijJAsamAnasya AcakSIthA yathAtatham . atha mantraM mantrayitvA yAthAtathyena hRSTavat .
gAvalgaNe kurUn gatvA dhRtarASTra mahAbalam . abhivAdyopasaMgRhya tataH pRccheranAmayam .
brUyAzcainaM tvamAsInaM kurubhiH parivAritam . tavaiva rAjan vIryeNa sukhaM jIvanti pANDavAH .
tava prasAdAda bAlAste prAptA rAjyamariMdam . rAjye tAn sthApayitvAgre nopekSasva vinazyataH .
sarvamapyetadekasya nAlaM saMjaya kasyacit . tAta saMhatya jIvAmo dviSatAM mA vazaM gamaH .
tathA bhISmaM zAntanavaM bhAratAnAM pitAmaham . zirasAbhivadethAstvaM mama nAma prakIrtayan .
abhivAdya ca vaktavyastato ' smAkaM pitAmahaH . bhavatA zantanovaMzo nimagnaH punaruddhRtaH .
sa tvaM kuru tathA tAta svamatena pitAmaha . yathA jIvanti te pautrAH prItimantaH parasparam .
tathaiva viduraM brUyAH kurUNAM mantradhAriNam . ayuddhaM saumya bhASasva hitakAmo yudhiSThire .
atha duryodhanaM brUyA rAjaputramamarSaNam . madhye kurUNAmAsInamanunIya punaH punaH .
apApAM yadupaikSastvaM kRSNAmetAM sabhAgatAm . tad duHkhamatitikSAma mA vadhISma kurUniti .
evaM pUrvAparAn klezAnatitikSanta pANDavAH . balIyAMso ' pi santo yat tat sarvaM kuravo viduH .
yannaH pravrAjayaH saumya ajinaiH prativAsitAn . tad duHkhamatitikSAma mA vadhiSma kurUniti .
yat kuntI samatikramya kRSNAM kezeSvadharSayat . duHzAsanaste ' numate taccAsmAbhirupekSatam .
athocitaM svakaM bhAgaM labhemahi paraMtapa . nivartaya paradravyAd buddhiM gRddhAM nararSabha .
zAntirevaM bhaved rAjan prItizcaiva parasparam . rAjyaikadezamapi naH prayaccha zamamicchatAm .
avisthalaM vRkasthalaM mAkandI vAraNAvatam . avasAnaM bhavatvatra kiMcidekaM ca paJcamam .
bhrAtRNAM dehi paJcAnAM paJca grAmAn suyodhana . zAnti ! ' stu mahAprAjJa jJAtibhiH saha saMjayA .
bhrAtA bhrAtaramanvetu pitA putreNa yujyatAm . smayamAnAH samAyAntu pAJcAlAH kurubhiH saha . .
akSatAn kurupAJcAlAn pazyeyamiti kAmaye . sarve sumanasastAta zAmyAma bharatarSabha .
alameva zamAyAsmi tathA yuddhAya saMjaya . dharmArthayoralaM cAhaM mRdave dAruNAya ca .
akRtavraNa uvAca sa vedAdhyayane yukto jamadagnirmahAtapAH . tapastepe tato devAn niyamAd vazamAnayat .
sa prasenajitaM rAjannadhigamya narAdhipam . reNukAM varayAmAsa sa ca tasmai dadau nRpaH .
reNukAM tvatha samprApya bhAryAM bhArgavanandanaH . AzramasthastayA sArdhaM tapastepe ' nukUlayA .
tasyAH kumArAzcatvAro jajJire rAmapaJcamAH . sarveSAmajaghanyastu rAma AsIjjaghanyajaH .
phalAhAreSu sarveSu gateSvatha suteSu vai . reNukA snAtumagamat kadAcinniyatavratA .
sA tu citrarathaM nAma mArtikAvatakaM nRpam . dadarza reNukA rAjannAgacchantI yadRcchayA . . krIDantaM salile dRSTvA sabhAryaM padmamAlinam . RddhimantaM tatastasya spRhayAmAsa reNukA .
vyabhicArAcca tasmAt sA klinnAmbhasi vicetanA . pravivezAzramaM trastA tAM vai bhartAnvabudhyata .
sa tAM dRSTvA cyutAM dhairyAd brAhmayA lakSmyA vivarjitAm . dhikachabdena mahAtejA garhayAmAsa vIryavAn .
tato jyeSTho jAmadagnyo rumaNvAn nAma nAmataH . AjagAma suSeNazca vasurvizvAvasustathA .
tAnAnupUrvyAd bhagavAn vadhe mAturacodayat . na ca te jAtasaMsnehAH kiMcidUcurvicetasaH .
tataH zazApa tAn krodhAt te zaptAzcetanA jahuH . mRgapakSisadharmANaH kSipramAsaJjaDopamAH .
tato rAmo ' bhyayAt pazcAdAzramaM paravIrahA . tamuvAca mahAbAhurjamadagnirmahAtapAH .
jahImAM mAtaraM pApAM mA ca putra vyathAM kRthAH . tata AdAya parazuM rAmo mAtuH ziro ' harat .
tatastasya mahArAja jamadagnermahAtmanaH . kopo ' bhyagacchat sahasA prasannazcAbravIdidam .
mamedaM vacanAt tAta kRtaM te karma duSkaram . vRNISva kAmAndharmajJa yAvato vAJchase hRdA . sa vavre mAturutthAnamasmRtiM ca vadhasya vai . pApena tena cAsparza bhrAtRNAM prakRti tathA . apratidvandvatAM yuddhe dIrghamAyuzca bhArata . dadau ca sarvAn kAmAMstAJjamadagnirmahAtapAH .
kadAcit tu tathaivAsya viniSkrAntAH sutAH prabho . athAnUpapatirvIraH kArtavIryo ' bhyavartata .
tamAzramapadaM prAptamRrbhAryA samArcayat . sa yuddhamadasammatto nAbhyanandat tathArcanam . pramathya cAzramAt tasmAddhomadhenostathA balAt . jahAra vatsaM krozantyA babhaJja ca mahAdumAn .
AgatAya ca rAmAya tadAcaSTa pitA svayam . gAM ca rorudatIM dRSTvA kopo rAmaM samAvizat .
sa mRtyuvazamApannaM kArtavIryamupAdravat . tasyAtha yudhi vikramya bhArgavaH paravIrahA . ciccheda nizitairbhallairvAhUn parighasaMnibhAn . sahasrasammitAn rAjan pragRhya ruciraMdhanuH .
abhibhUtaH sa rAmeNa saMyuktaH kAladharmaNA . arjunasyAtha dAyAdA rAmeNa kRtamanyavaH .
AzramasthaM vinA rAmaM jagadagnimupAdravan . te taM jaghnurmahAvIryamayudhyantaM tapasvinam .
asakRd rAmarAmeti vikrozantamanAthavat . kArtavIryasya putrAstu jamadagniM yudhiSThira . . pIDayitvA zarairjagmuryathAgatamaridamAH . apakrAnteSu vai teSu jamadagnau tathA gate . samitpANirupAgacchadAzramaM bhRgunandanaH . sa dRSTvA pitaraM vIrastathA mRtyuvazaM gatam . anarhantaM tathAbhUtaM vilalApa suduHkhitaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktvA yudhAM zreSThaH sarvayAdavanandanaH . sarvAyudhavaropetamAruroha rathottamam .
yuktaM paramakAmbojaisturagairhemamAlibhiH . AdityodayavarNasya dhuraM rathavarasya tu .
dakSiNAmavahacchabyaH sugrIvaH savyato ' bhavat . pANivAhau tu tasyAstAM meghapuSpabalAhakau .
vizvakarmakRtA divyA ratnadhAtuvibhUSitA . ucchriteva rathe mAyA dhvajayaSTiradRzyata .
vainateyaH sthitastasyAM prabhAmaNDalarazmivAn . tasya satyavataH keturbhujagAriradRzyata .
athArohaddhRSIkezaH ketuH sarvadhanuSmatAm . arjunaH satyakarmA ca kururAjo yudhiSThiraH .
azobhetAM mahAtmAnau dAzArhamabhitaH sthitau . rathasthaM zArGgadhanvAnamazvinAviva vAsavam .
tAvupAropya dAzArhaH syandanaM lokapUjitam . pratodena javopetAn paramAzcAnacodayat .
te hayAH sahasotpeturgRhItvA syandanottamam . AsthitaM pANDaveyAbhyAM yadUnAmRSabheNa ca .
vahatAM zArGgadhanvAnamazvAnAM zIghragAminAm . prAdurAsInmahAzabdaH pakSiNAM patatAmiva .
te samAInaravyAghrAH kSaNena bharatarSabha . bhImasenaM maheSvAsaM samanudrutya vegitAH .
krodhadIptaM tu kaunteyaM dviSadarthe samudyatam . nAzaknuvan vArayituM sametyApi mahArathAH .
sa teSAM prekSatAmeva zrImatAM dRDhadhanvinAm . yayau bhAgIrathItIraM haribhi zavegitaiH .
yatra sma zrUyate drauNiH putrahantA mahAtmanAm . sa dadarza mahAtmAnamudakAnte yazasvinam .
kRSNadvaipAyanaM vyAsamAsInamRSibhiH saha . taM caiva krUrakarmANaM ghRtAktaM kuzacIriNam . rajasA dhvastamAsInaM dadarza drauNimantike .
tamabhyadhAvat kaunteyaH pragRhya sazaraM dhanuH . bhImaseno mahAbAhustiSTha niSTheti cAbravIt .
sa dRSTvA bhImadhanvAnaM pragRhItazarAsanam . bhrAtarau pRSThatazcAsya janArdanarathe sthitau . vyathitAtmAbhavad drauNiH prAptaM cedamamanyata . sa tad divyamadInAtmA paramAstramacintayat .
jagrAha ca sa caiSIkAM drauNiH savyena pANinA . sa tAmApadamAsAdya divyamastramudairayat .
amRSyamANastAJchUrAn divyAyudhavarAn sthitAn . apANDavAyeti ruSA vyasRjad dAruNaM vacaH .
ityuktvA rAjazArdUla droNaputraH pratApavAn . sarvalokapramohArthaM tadastraM pramumoca ha .
tatastasyAmiSIkAyAM pAvakaH samajAyata . pradhakSyanniva lokAMstrIn kAlAntakayamopamaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca sa naM dRSTvA tathAbhUtaM rAjAnaM ghoradarzanam . dIrghazmazrudharaM nRNAM zoNitena samukSitam .
cakAra na vyathAM vipro rAjA tvenamathAbravIt . pratyutthAya mahAtejA bhayakartA yamopamaH . diSTyA tvamasi kalyANa SaSThe kAle mamAntikam . bhakSyaM mRgayamANasya samprApto dvijasattama .
rAjan gurvarthinaM viddhi carantaM mAmihAgatam . na ca gurvarthamudyuktaM hiMsyamAhurmanISiNaH .
SaSThe kAle mamAhAro vihito dvijasattama . na zakyastvaM samutsraSTuM kSudhitena mayAdya vai .
evamastu mahArAja samayaH kriyatAM ta me . gurvarthamabhinivartya punareSyAmi ne vazam .
saMzrutazca mayA yo ' rtho gurave rAjasattama . tvadadhInaH sa rAjendra taM tvAM bhikSe narezvara .
dadAsi vipramukhyebhyastvaM hi ratnAni nityadA . dAtA ca tvaM naravyAghra pAtrabhUtaH kSitAviha . pAtraM pratigrahe cApi viddhi mAM nRpasattama .
upAhRtya gurArarthaM tvadAyattamariMdama . samayeneha rAjendra punareSyAmi te vazam . satyaM te pratijAnAmi nAtra mithyA kathaMcana . anRtaM noktapUrvaM me svaireSvapi kuto ' nyathA . .
saudAsa uvAca yadi mattastavAyatto gurvathaiH kRta eva saH . yadi cAsmi pratigrAhyaH sAmprataM tad vadasva me .111 ! 
uttaGka uvAca pratigrAhyo mato me tvaM sadaiva puruSarSabha . so ' haM tvAmanusamprApto bhikSituM maNikuNDale .
patnyAste mama viprarSe ucite maNikuNDale . varayArthaM tvamanyaM vai taM te dAsyAmi suvrata .
alaM te vyapadezena pramANA yadi te vayam . prayaccha kuNDale mahyaM satyavAg bhava pArthiva .
ityuktastvabravId rAjA tamuttakaM punarvacaH . gaccha madvacanAd devIM brUhi dehIti sattama . saivamuktA tvayA nUnaM madvAkyena zucivratA . pradAsyati dvijazreSTha kuNDale te na saMzayaH .
uttaGka uvAca kva patnI bhavataH zakyA mayA draSTuM narezvara . svayaM vApi bhavAn patnI kimarthaM nopasarpati .
saudAsa uvAca tAM drakSyati bhavAnadya kasmiMzcid vananirjhare . SaSThe kAle na hi mayA sA zakyA draSTumadya vai .
vaizampAyana uvAca uttaGkastu tathoktaH sa jagAma bharatarSabha . madayantIM ca dRSTvA sa jJApayat svaprayojanam .
saudAsavacanaM zrutvA tataH sA pRthulocanA . pratyuvAca mahAbuddhimuttakaM janamejaya .
evametad vada brahman nAnRtaM vadase ' nagha . abhijJAnaM tu kiMcit tvaM samAnayituparhasi .
ime hi divye maNikuNDale me devAzca yakSAzca maharSayazca . taistairupAyairamahartukAmA zchidreSu nityaM paritarkayanti .
nikSiptametad bhuvi pannagAstu ratnaM samAsAdya parAmazeyuH . yakSAstethocchiSTadhRtaM surAzca nidrAvazAd vA paridharSayeyuH .
chidreSveteSvime nityaM hviyete dvijasattama . devarAkSasanAgAnAmapramattena dhAryate .
syandete hi divA rukmaM rAtrau ca dvijasattama . naktaM nakSatratArANAM prabhAmAkSipya vartataH .
ete hyamucya bhagavan kSutpipAsAbhayaM kutaH . viSAgnizvApadebhyazca bhayaM jAtu na vidyate .
hrasvena caite Amukte bhavato hrasvake tadA . anurUpeNa cAmukte jAyete tatpramANake .
evaMvidhe mamaite vai kuNDale paramArcita . triSu lokeSu vijJAte tadabhijJAnamAnaya .
janamejaya uvAca atyadbhutamidaM brahman zrutavAnasmi tattvataH . abhiSekaM kumArasya vistareNa yathAvidhi .
yacchrutvA pUtamAtmAnaM vijAnAmi tapodhana . prahRSTAni ca romANi prasannaM ca mano mama .
abhiSekaM kumArasya daityAnAM ca vadhaM tathA . zrutvA me paramA prItirbhUyaH kautUhalaM hi me .
apAM patiH kathaM hyasminnabhiSiktaH purA suraiH . tanme brUhi mahAprAjJa kuzalo hyasi sattama . .
vaizampAyana uvAca zRNu rAjannidaM citraM pUrvakalpe yathAtatham . Adau kRtayuge rAjan vartamAne yathAvidhi .
varuNaM devatAH sarvA yametyedapathAbruvan . yathAsmAn surarATchakro bhayebhyaH pAti sarvadA .
tathA tvamapi sarvAsAM saritAM vai patirbhava . vAsazca te sadA deva sAgare makarAlaye .
samudro ' yaM tava vaze bhaviSyati nadIpatiH . somena sArdhaM ca tava hAnivRddhI bhaviSyataH .
evamastviti tAn devAn varuNo vAkyamabravIt . samAgamya tataH sarve varuNaM sAgarAlayam .
apAM patiM pracakrurhi vidhidRSTena karmaNA . abhiSicya tato devA varuNaM yAdasAM patim .
jagmuH svAnyeva sthAnAni pUjayitvA jalezvaram . abhiSiktastato devairvaruNo ' pi mahAyazAH .
saritaH sAgarAMzcaiva nadAMzcApi sarAMsi ca . pAlayAmAsa vidhinA yathA devAzatakratuH . tatastatrApyupaspRzya dattvA ca vividhaM vasu . agnitIrthaM mahAprAjJo jagAmAtha pralambahA . naSTo na dRzyate yatra zamIgarbhe hutAzanaH .
lokAlokavinAze ca prAdurbhUte tadAnagha . upatasthuH surA yatra sarvalokapitAmaham .
agniH pranaSTo bhagavAn kAraNaM ca na vidmahe . sarvabhUtakSayo rAjan sampAdaya vibho ' nalam .
janamejaya uvAca kimarthaM bhagavAnagniH pranaSTo lokabhAvanaH . vijJAtazca kathaM devaistanmamAcakSva tattvataH .
vaizampAyana uvAca bhRgoH zApAd bhRzaM bhIto jAtavedAH pratApavAn . zamIgarbhamathAsAdya nanAza bhagavAMstataH .
pranaSTe tu sadA vahnau devAH sarve savAsavAH . anvaiSanta tadA naSTaM jvalanaM bhRzaduHkhitAH .
tato ' gnitIrthamAsAdya zamIgarbhasthameva hi . dadRzurvvalanaM tatra vasamAnaM yathAvidhi .
devAH sarve naravyAghra bRhaspatipurogamAH . jvalanaM taM samAsAdya prItA ' bhUvan savAsavAH .
punaryathAgataM jagmuH sarvabhakSazca so ' bhavat . bhRgoH zApAnmahAbhAga yaduktaM brahmavAdinA .
tatrApyAplutya matimAn brahmayoniM jagAma ha . sasarja bhagavAn yatra sarvalokapitAmahaH .
tatrAplutya tato brahmA saha devaiH prabhuH purA . sasarja tIrthAni tathA devatAnAM yathAvidhi .
tatra snAtvA ca datvA ca vasUni vividhAni ca . . kauberaM prayayau tIrthaM tatra taptvA mahattapaH . dhanAdhipatyaM samprApto rAjannailabila prabhuH .
tatrasthameva taM rAjan dhanAni nidhayastathA . upatasthurnarazreSTha tat tIrthaM lAgalI balaH . gatvA datvA ca vidhivad brAhmaNebhyo dhanaM dadau .
dadRze tatra tat sthAnaM kaubere kAnanottame . purA yatra tapastaptaM vipulaM sumahAtmanA . yakSarAjJA kubereNa varA labdhAzca puSkalAH .
dhanAdipatyaM sakhyaM ca rudreNAmitatejasA . suratvaM lokapAlatvaM putraM ca nalakUbaram .
yatra lebhe mahAbAho dhanAdhipatiraJjasA ! abhiSiktazca tatraiva samAgamya marudgaNaiH .
vAhanaM cAsya tad dattaM haMsayuktaM manojavam . vimAnaM puSpakaM divyaM naiRtaizcaryameva ca . . tatrAplutya balo rAjan dattvA dAyAMzca puSkalAn .
jagAma tvarito rAmastIrthaM zvetAnulepanaH . niSevitaM sarvasattvairnAmnA badarapAcanam . nAnartukavanopetaM sadApuSpaphalaM zubham .
nArada uvAca tato devarSayaH sarve siddhAzca paramarSayaH . jagmustadA parAmArti dRSTvA tat kadanaM mahat .
te ' bhijagmurjitakrodhA jitAtmAno jitendriyAH . pitAmahasya bhavanaM jagataH kRpayA tadA .
tato dadRzurAsInaM saha devaiH pitAmaham . siddhairbrahmarSibhizcaiva samantAt parivAritam .
tatra devo mahAdevastatrAgnirvAyunA saha . candrAdityau ca zakrazca pArameSThyAstatharSayaH . vaikhAnasA bAlakhilyA vAnaprasthA marIcipAH . ajAzcaivAvimUDhAzca tejoga stapasvinaH . RSayaH sarva evaite pitAmahamupAgaman . tato ' bhigamya te dInAH sarva eva maharSayaH . sundopasundayoH karma sarvameva zazaMsire . yathA hRtaM yathA caiva kRtaM yena krameNa ca . nyavedayaMstataH sarvamakhilena pitAmahe . tato devagaNAH sarve te caiva paramarSayaH . tamevArthaM puraskRtya pitAmahamacodayan . tataH pitAmahaH zrutvA sarveSAM tad vacastadA . muhUrtamiva saMcintya kartavyasya ca nizcayam . tayorvadhaM samuddizya vizvakarmANamAhvayat .
dRSTvA ca vizvakarmANaM vyAdideza pitAmahaH . sRjyatAM prArthanIyaikA pramadeti mahAtapAH .
pitAmahaM namaskRtya tadvAkyamabhinandya ca . nirmame yoSitaM divyAM cintayitvA punaH punaH .
triSu lokeSu yat kiMcid bhUtaM sthAvarajaGgam . samAnayad darzanIyaM tat tadatra sa vizvajit .
koTizazcaiva ratnAni tasyA gAtre nyavezayat . tAM ratnasaMghAtamayImasRjad devarUpiNIm .
sA prayatnena mahatA nirmitA vizvakarmaNA . triSu lokeSu nArINAM rUpeNApratimAbhavat .
na tasyAH sUkSmamapyasti yad gAtre rUpasampadA . niyuktA yatra vA dRSTirna sajjati nirIkSatAm .
sA vigrahavatIva zrIH kAmarUpA vapuSmatI . jahAra sarvabhUtAnAM caDhUMSi ca manAMsi ca .
tilaM tilaM samAnIya ratnAnAM yad vinirmita . . tilottameti tat tasyA nAma cakre pitAmahaH .
brahmANaM sA namaskRtya prAJjalirvAkyamabravIt . kiM kAryaM mayi bhUteza yenAsmyoha nirmitA .
pitAmaha uvAca gaccha sundopasundAbhyAmasurAbhyAM tilottame . prArthanIyena rUpeNa kuru bhadre pralobhanam .
tvatkRte darzanAdeva rUpasampatkRtena vai . virodhaH : syAd yathA tAbhyAmanyonyena tathA kuru .
nArada uvAca sA tatheti pratijJAya namaskRtya pitAmaham . cakAra maNDalaM tatra vibudhAnAM pradakSiNam .
prAGmukho bhagavAnAste dakSiNena mahezvaraH . devAzcaivottareNAsan sarvatastvRSayo ' bhavan .
kurvatyA tu tadA tatra maNDalaM tat pradakSiNam . indraH sthANuzca bhagavAn dhairyeNa pratyavasthitau .
draSTukAmasya cAtyarthaM gatayA pArzvatastayA . anyadaJcitapadmAkSaM dakSiNaM niHsRtaM mukham .
pRSThataH parivartantyA pazcimaM niHsRtaM sukham . gatayA cottaraM pArzvamuttaraM niHsRtaM mukham . mahendrasyApi netrANAM pRSThataH pArzvato ' grataH . raktAntAnAM vizAlAnAM sahasraM sarvato ' bhavat .
evaM caturmukhaH sthANurmahAdevo ' bhavat purA . tathA sahasranetrazca babhUva balasUdanaH .
tathA devanikAyAnAM maharSINAM ca sarvazaH . mukhAni cAbhyavartanta yena yAti tilottamA .
tasyA gAtre nipatitA dRSTisteSAM mahAtmanAm . sarveSAmeva bhUyiSThamRte devaM pitAmaham .
gacchantyA tu tayA sarve devAzca paramarSayaH kRtamityeva tat kArya menire rUpasampadA .
tilottamAyAM tasyAM tu gatAyAM lokabhAvanaH . sarvAn visarjayAmAsa devAnRSigaNAMzca tAn .
vaizampAyana uvAca rAjJastu vacanaM zrutvA dhRtarASTrasya saMjayaH . upaplavyaM yayau draSTuM pANDavAnamitaujasaH .
sa tu rAjAnamAsAdya kuntIputraM yudhiSThiram . abhivAdya tataH pUrvaM sUtaputro ' bhyabhASata .
rajAtazatrumavadat pratItaH . diSTyA rAjaMstvAmarogaM prapazye sahAyavantaM ca mahendrakalpam .
anAmayaM pRcchati tvA ' ' mbikeyo vRddho rAjA dhRtarASTro manISI . kaccid bhImaH kuzalI pANDavAgryo dhanaMjayastau ca mAdrItanUjau .
kaccit kRSNA draupadI rAjaputrI satyavratA vIrapatnI saputrA . miSTAn kAmAn bhArata svastikAmaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca gAvalgaNe saMjaya svAgataM te prIyAmahe te vayaM darzanena . anAmayaM pratijAne tavAhaM sahAnujai : kuzalI cAsmi vidvan .
cirAdidaM kuzalaM bhAratasya zrutvA rAjJaH kuruvRddhasya sUta . manye sAkSAd dRSTamahaM narendra dRSTvaiva tvAM saMjaya prItiyogAt .
pitAmaho naH sthaviro manasvI mahAprAjJaH sarvadharmopapannaH . sa kauravyaH kuzalI tAta bhISmo yathApUrvaM vRttirastyasya kaccit .
kaccid rAjA dhRtarASTraH saputro vaicitravIryaH kuzalI mahAtmA . mahArAjo bAhnikaH prAtipeyaH kaccid vidvAn kuzalI sUtaputra .
sa somadattaH kuzalI tAta kaccid bhUrizravAH satyasaMdhaH zalazca . droNaH saputrazca kRpazca vipro maheSvAsAH kaccidete ' pyarogAH .
sarve kurubhyaH spRhayanti saMjaya dhanurdharA ye pRthivyA pradhAnAH . mahAprAjJAH sarvazAstrAvadAtA dhanurbhUtA mukhyatamAH pRthivyAm .
kaccinmAnaM tAta labhanta ete dhanurbhUtaH kaccidete ' pyarogAH . yeSAM rASTre nivasati darzanIyo maheSvAsaH zIlavAn droNaputraH .
mahAprAjJo rAjaputro yuyutsuH . karNo ' mAtyaH kuzalI tAta kaccit suyodhano yasya mando vidheyaH .
striyo vRddhA bhAratAnAM jananyo mahAnasyo dAsabhAryAzca sUta . vadhvaH putrA bhAgineyA bhaginyo dauhitrA vA kaccidapyavyalIkAH .
kaccid rAjA brAhmaNAnAM yathAvat pravartate pUrvavat tAta vRttim . kaccid dAyAn mAmakAn dhArtarASTro dvijAtInAM saMjaya nopahanti .
kaccid rAjA dhRtarASTraH saputra upekSate brAhmaNAtikramAn vai . mupekSate teSu sadaiva vRttim .
etajjyotizcottamaM jIvaloke zuklaM prajAnAM vihitaM vidhAtrA . te ced doSaM na niyacchanti mandA : kRtsnonAzo bhavitA kauravANAm .
kaccid rAjA dhRtarASTraH saputro bubhUSate vRttimamAtyavarge . kaccinna bhedena jijIviSanti suhRdUpA durhadaizcaikamatyAt . .
kaccinna pApaM kathayanti tAta te pANDavAnAM kuravaH sarva eva . droNaH saputrazca kRpazca vIro nAsmAsu pApAni vadanti kaccit .
kaccid rAjye dhRtarASTra saputraM sametyAhuH kuravaH : kuravaH sarva eva . kaccid dRSTvA dasyusaGghAn sametAn smaranti pArthasya yudhAM praNetu .
maurvIbhujAgraprahitAn sma tAta dodhUyamAnena dhanurdhareNa . najihmagAn kaccidanusmaranti .
na cApazyaM kacidahaM pRthivyAM yodhaM samaM vAdhikamarjunena . yasyaikaSaSTinizitAstIkSNadhArAH suvAsasaH sammato hastavApaH .
gadApANirbhImasenastarasvI pravepayaJchatrusaGghAnanIke . nAgaH prabhinna iva naDvaleSu caMkramyate kaccidenaM smaranti .
mAdrIputraH sahadevaH kaliGgAn samAgatAnajayad dantakare . vAmenAsyan dakSiNenaiva yo vai mahAbalaM kaccidenaM smaranti .
purA jetuM nakulaH preSito ' yaM zibIMstrigartAn saMjaya pazyataste . dizaM pratIcI vazamAnayanme mAdrIsutaM kaccidenaM smaranti .
parAbhavo dvaitavane ya AsId durmantrite ghoSayAtrAgatAnAm . yatra mandAJchatruvazaM prayAtAnamocayad bhImaseno jayazca . .
ahaM pazcAdarjunamabhyarakSaM mAdrIputrau bhImaseno ' pyarakSat . gANDIvadhanvA zatrusaGghAnudasya svastyAgamat kaccidenaM smaranti .
na karmaNA sAdhunaikena nUnaM sukhaM zakyaM vai bhavatIha saMjaya . na zaknumo dhRtarASTrasya putram .
bhISma uvAca tasyAM nizAyAM vyuSTAyAM gate tasmin dvijottame . niSkramya gautamo ' gacchat samudraM prati bhArata .
sAmudrikAn sa vaNijastato ' pazyat sthitAn pathi . sa tena saha sArthena prayayau sAgaraM prati .
sa tu sArtho mahAn rAjan kasmiMzcid girigahvare . mattena dviradenAtha nihataH prAyazo ' bhavat .
sa kathaMcid bhayAt tasmAd vimukto brAhmaNastathA . kAMdigbhUto jIvitArthI pradudrovAttarAM dizam .
sa tu sArthaparibhraSTastasmAd dezAt tathA cyutaH . ekAkI vyavarat tatra vane kiMpuruSo yathA . .
sa panthAnamathAsAdya samudrAbhisaraM tadA . AsasAda vanaM ramyaM divyaM puSpitapAdapam .
sarvartukairAmravaNaiH puSpitairupazobhitam . nandanoddezasadRzaM yakSakinnarasevitam . .7 .
zAlaistAlaistamAlaizca kAlAguruvanaistathA . candanasya ca mukhyasya pAdapairupazobhitam .
giriprastheSu ramyeSu teSu teSu sugandhiSu . samantato dvijazreSThAstatrAkUjanta vai tadA .
manuSyavadanAzcAnye bhAruNDA iti vizrutAH . bhUliGgazakunAzcAnye sAmudrAH parvatodbhavAH .
sa tAnyatimanojJAni vihagAnAM rutAni vai . zRNvan suramaNIyAni vipro ' gacchat gautamaH .
tato ' pazyat suramyeSu suvarNasikatAcite . deze same sukhe citre svarNoddezasame nRpa .
zriyA juSTaM mahAvRkSaM nyagrodhaM ca sumaNDalam . zAkhAbhiranurUpAbhirbhUyiSThaM kSatrasaMnibham .
sukhaH zivaH . tasya mUlaM ca saMsiktaM varacandanavAriNA . divyapuSpAnvitaM zrImat pitAmahasabhopamama .
taM dRSTvA gautamaH prIto mana : kAntamanuttamama . medhyaM suragRhaprakhyaM puSpitaiH pAdapairvRtam .
tamAsAdya mudA yuktastasyAdhastAdupAvizat . tatrAsInasya kaunteya gautamasya puSpANi samupampRzya pravavAvanila : zubhaH . hlAdayan sarvagAtrANi gautamasya tadA nRpa .
sa tu vipraH prazAntazca spRSTaH puNyena vAyunA . sukhamAsAdya suSvApa bhAskarazcAstamabhyayAt .
tato ' staM bhAskare yAte saMdhyAkAla upasthite . AjagAma svabhavanaM brahmalokAt khagottamaH .
nADIjaGgha iti khyAto dayito brahmaNaH sakhA . bakarAjo mahAprAjJaH kazyapasyAtmasambhavaH .
rAjadharmeti vikhyAto babhUvApratimo bhuvi . devakanyAsutaH zrImAn vidvAn devasamaprabhaH .
pRSTAbharaNasampanno bhUSaNairarkasaMnibhaiH . SitaH sarvagAtreSu devagarbhaH zriyA jvalan .
tamAgataM khagaM dRSTvA gautamo vismito ' bhavat . kSutpipAsAparizrAnto hiMsArthI cAbhyavekSata .
rAjadharmovAca svAgataM bhavato vipra diSTyA prApto ' si me gRham . astaM ca savitA yAtaH saMdhyeyaM samupasthitA . .
mama tvaM nilaya prAptaH priyAtithiraninditaH . pUjito yAsyasi prAtarvidhidRSTena karmaNA .
bhImasena uvAca brahmazAnendravaruNAnavahad yaH purA rathaH . tamAsthAya gatau kRSNau na tayorvidyate bhayam .
AjJAM tu zirasA bibhradeSa gacchAmi mA zucaH . sametya tAn naravyAghrAMstava dAsyAmi saMvidam .
saMjaya uvAca etAvaduktvA prayayau paridAya yudhiSThiram . dhRSTadyumnAya balavAn suhadbhyazca punaH punaH .
dhRSTadyumnaM cedamAha bhImaseno mahAbalaH . viditaM te mahAbAho yathA droNo mahArathaH .
grahaNe dharmarAjasya sarvopAyena vartate . na ca me gamane kRtyaM tAdRk pArSata vidyate .
yAdRzaM rakSaNe rAjJaH kAryamAtyayikaM hi naH . evamukto ' smi pArthena prativaktuM na cotsahe .
prayAsye tatra yatrAsau mumUrSuH saindhavaH sthitaH . dharmarAjasya vacane sthAtavyamavizaGkayA .
yAsyAmi padavIM bhrAtuH sAtvatasya ca dhImataH . so ' dya yatto raNe pArtha parirakSa yudhiSThiram .
etaddhi sarvakAryANAM paramaM kRtyamAhave . tamabravInmahArAja dhRSTadyumno vRkodaram .
IpsitaM te kariSyAmi gaccha pArthAvicArayan . nAhatvA samare droNo dhRSTadyumnaM kathaJcana .
nigrahaM dharmarAjasya prakariSyati saMyuge . tato nikSipya rAjAnaM dhRSTadyumne ca pANDavam .
abhivAdya guruM jyeSThaM prayayau yena phAlgunaH . pariSvaktazca kaunteyo dharmarAjena bhArata .
AghrAtazca tathA mUrdhni zrAvitazcAziSaH zubhAH . kRtvA pradakSiNAn viprAnarcitAMstuSTamAnasAn .
Alabhya maGgalAnyaSTau pItvA kairAtakaM madhu . dviguNadraviNo vIro madaraktAntalocanaH .
vipraiH kRtasvastyayano vijayotpAdasUcitaH . pazyannevAtmano buddhiM vijayAnandakAriNIm .
anulomAnilaizcAzu pradarzitajayodayaH . bhImaseno mahAbAhuH kavacI zubhakuNDalI .
sAGgadaH satalatrANaH saratho rathinAM varaH . tasya kArNAyasaM varma hemacitraM maharddhimat .
vibabhau sarvataH zliSTaM savidyudiva toyadaH . pItaraktAsitasitairvAsobhizca suveSTitaH .
kaNThamAtreNa ca babhau sendrAyudha ivAmbudaH . prayAte bhImasene tu tava sainayaM yuyutsayA .
pAJcajanyaravo ghoraH punarAsId vizAmpate . taM zrutvA ninadaM ghora trailokyatrAsanaM mahat .
punarbhImaM mahAbAhuM dharmaputro ' bhyabhASata . eSa vRSNipravIreNa dhmAtaH salilajo bhRzam .
pRthivIM cAntarikSaM ca vinAdayati zaGkharAT . nUnaM vyasanamApanne sumahat savyasAcini .
kurubhiyudhyate sArdha sarvezcakragadAdharaH . Aha kuntI nUnamAryA pApamadya nidarzanam . draupadI ca subhadrA ca pazyantyau saha bandhubhiH . sa bhIma tvarayA yukto yAhi yatra dhanaMjayaH .
muhyantIva hi me sarvA dhanaMjayadidRkSayA . dizazca pradizaH pArtha sAtvatasya ca kAraNAt .
gaccha gaccheti guruNA so ' nujJAto vRkodaraH . tataH pANDusuto rAjan bhImasenaH pratApavAn .
baddhagodhAGgulitrANaH pragRhItazarAsanaH . jyeSThena prahito bhrAtrA bhrAtA bhrAtuH priyaMkaraH .
Ahatya dundubhiM bhImaH zaGkha pradhamApya cAsakRt . vinadya siMhanAdena jyAM vikarSan punaH punaH .
tena zabdena vIrANAM pAtapitvA manAMsyuta . darzayan ghoramAtmAnamamitrAn sahasAbhyayAt .
tahUmurjavA dAntA viruvanto hayottamAH . vizokenAbhisampannA manomArutaraMhasaH .
Arujan virujan pArtho jyAM vikarSazca pANinA . samprakarSan vimarSazca senAgraM samaloDayat .
taM prayAntaM mahAbAhuM paJcAlAH sahasomakAH . pRSThato ' nuyayuH zUrA maghavantamivAmarAH .
taM sametya mahArAja tAvakAH paryavArayan . duHzalazcitrasenazca kuNDabhedI viviMzatiH . durmukho duHsahazcaiva vikarNazca zalastathA . vindAnuvindau sumukho dIrghabAhuH sudarzanaH . vRndArakaH suhastazca suSeNo dIrghalocanaH . abhayo raudrakarmA ca suvarmA durvimocanaH .
zobhanto rathinAM zreSThAH sahasainyapadAnugAH . saMyattaH samare vIrA bhImasenamupAdravan .
taiH samantAd vRtaH zUraiH samareSu mahArathaH . tAn samIkSya tu kaunteyo bhImasenaH parAkramI . abhyavartata vegena siMhaH kSudramRgAniva .
te mahAsrANi divyAni tatra vIrA adarzayan . chAdayantaH zarairbhImaM meghAH sUryamivoditam .
sa tAnatItya vegena droNAnIkamupAdravat . apratazca gajAnIkaM zaravarSairavAkirat .
so ' cireNaiva kAlena tad gajAnIkamAzugaiH . dizaH sarvAH samabhyasya vyadhamat pavanAtmajaH .
trAsitAH zarabhasyeva garjitena vane mRgAH . prAdravan dviradAH sarve nadanto bhairavAn ravAn .
punazcAtIva vegena droNAnIkamupAdravat . tamavArayadAcAryo velodvRttamivArNavam .
lalATe ' tADyaccainaM nArAcena smayanniva . UrdhvarazmirivAdityo vibabhau tena pANDavaH .
sa manyamAnastvAcAryo mamAyaM phAlguno yathA . bhImaH kariSyate pUjAmityuvAca vRkodaram .
bhImasena na te zakyA praveSTumarivAhinI . mAmanirjitya samare zatrumadya mahAbala .
yadi te so ' nujaH kRSNaH praviSTo ' numate mama . anIkaM na tu zakyaM me praveSTumiha vai tvayA .
atha bhImastu tacchutvA gurorvAkyamapetabhIH . kruddhaH provAca vai droNaM raktatAprekSaNastvaran .
tavArjuno nAnumate brahmabandho raNAjiram . praviSTaH sa hi durdharSaH zakrasyApi vized balam . tena vai paramAM pUjAM kurvatA mAnito hyasi . nArjuno ' haM ghRNI droNa bhImaseno ' smi .
pitA nastvaM gururbandhustathA putrAstu te vayam . iti manyAmahe sarve bhavantaM praNatA sthitAH .
adya tadviparItaM te vadato ' smAsu dRzyate . yadi tvaM zatrumAtmAnaM manyase tattathAstviha .
eSa te sadRzaM zatroH karma bhImaH karomyaham . athodbhAmya gadAM bhImaH kAladaNDamivAntakaH .
droNAya vyasRjad rAjan sa rathAdavapupluve . sAzvasUtadhvajaM yAnaM droNasyApothayat tadA .
prAmRgAca bahUn yodhAn vAyurvRkSAnivaujasA . taM punaH parivav\aste tava putrA rathottamam .
anyaM tu rathamAsthAya droNaH praharatAM varaH . vyUhadvAraM samAsAdya yuddhAya samupasthitaH .
tataH kruddho mahArAja bhImasenaH parAkramI . agrataH syandanAnIkaM zaravarSairavAkirat .
te vadhyamAnAH samare tava putrA mahArathAH . bhImaM bhImabalA yuddhe yodhyanti jyaiSiNaH .
tato duHzAsana kruddho rathazaktiM samAkSipat . sarvapArasavIM tIkSNAM jighAMsuH pANDunandanam . ApatantIM mahAzaktiM tava putrapraNoditAm . dvidhA ciccheda tAM bhImastadadbhutamivAbhavat .
athAnyairvizikhaistIkSNaiH saMkruddhaH kuNDabhedinam . suSeNaM dIrghanetraM ca tribhitrInavadhId balI . tato vRndArakaM vIraM kurUNAM kIrtivardhanam . putrANAM tava vIrANAM yudhyatAmavadhIt punaH . abhayaM raudrakarmANaM durvimocanameva ca . tribhitrInavadhId bhImaH punareva sutAMstava . vadhyamAnA mahArAja putrAstava balIyasA . bhImaM praharatAM zreSThaM samantAt paryavArayan .
te zarairbhImakarmANaM vavarSaH pANDavaM yudhi . meghA ivAtapApAye dhArAbhirdharaNIdharam .
sa tad bANamayaM varSamazmavarSamivAcalaH . pratIcchan pANDudAyAdo na prAvyathata zatruhA . vindAnuvindau sahitau suvarmANaM ca te sutam . prahasanneva kaunteyaH zarairninye yamakSayam . tataHsudarzanaM vIraM putraM te bharatarSabha . vivyAdha samare tUrNa sa papAta mamAra ca . so ' cireNaiva kAlena tadrathAnIkamAzugaiH . dizaH sarvAH samAlokya vyadhamat pANDunandanaH . tato vai sthaghoSeNa garjitena mRgA iva . bhajyamAnAzca samare tava putrA vizAmpate .
prAdravan sahasA sarve bhImasenabhayArditAH . anuyAyAca kaunteyaH putrANAM te mahad balam .
vivyAdha samare rAjan kauraveyAn samantataH . vadhyamAnA mahArAja bhImasenena tAvakAH .
tyaktvA bhImaM raNAjagmuzcodayanto hayottamAn . tAMstu nirjitya samare bhImaseno mahAbalaH .
siMhanAdaravaM cakre bAhuzabdaM ca pANDavaH . talazabdaM ca sumahat kRtvA bhImo mahAbalaH .
bhISayitvA sthAnIkaM hatvA yodhAn varAn varAn . vyatItya rathinazcApi droNAnIkamupAdravat .
sUrya uvAca naiSa devo ' nilasakho nAsuro na ca pannagaH . ucchavRttivrate siddho munireva divaM gataH .
eSa mUlaphalAhAraH zIrNaparNAzanastathA . abhakSo vAyubhakSazca AsId vipraH samAhitaH .
bhavazcAnena vipreNa saMhitAbhirabhiSTutaH . svargadvAre kRtodyogo yenAsau tridivaM gataH .
asaGgatiranAkAGkSI nityamucchazilAzanaH . sarvabhUtahite yukta eSa vipro bhujaGgama .
na hi devA na gandharvA nAsurA na ca pannagAH . prabhavantIha bhUtAnAM prAptAnAmuttamAM gatim . etadevaMvidhaM dRSTamAzcaryaM tatra me dvija .
saMsiddho mAnuSa : kAmaM yo ' sau siddhagatiM gataH . sUryeNa sahito brahman pRthivIM parivartate .
arjuna uvAca brahma yatparamaM jJeyaM tanme vyAkhyAtumarhasi . bhavato hi prasAdena sUkSme me ramate matiH .
vAsudeva uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . saMvAdaM mokSasaMyuktaM ziSyasya guruNA saha .
kazcid brAhmaNamAsInamAcAryaM saMzitavratam . ziSyaH prapraccha medhAvI kiMsvicchreyaH paraMtapa .
bhagavantaM prapanno ' haM niHzreyasaparAyaNaH . yAce tvAM zirasA vipra yad brUyAM brUhi tanmama .
tabhevaMvAdinaM pArtha ziSyaM gururuvAca ha . sarve tu te pravakSyAmi yatra vai saMzayo dvija .
ityuktaH sa kuruzreSTha guruNA guruvatsalaH . prAJjaliH paripapraccha yattacchRNu mahAmate .
ziSya uvAca kutazcAhaM kutazca tvaM tatsatyaM brUhi yatparam . kuto jAtAni bhUtAni sthAvarANi carANi ca .
kena jIvanti bhUtAni teSAmAyuzca kiM param . kiM satya kiM tapo vipra ke guNAH sadbhirIritAH .
ke panthAna : zivAzca syuH kiM sukhaM kiM ca duSkRtam . etAn me bhagavan prazcAn yAthAtathyena suvrata . vaktumarhasi viprarSe yathAvadiha tattvataH . tvadanyaH kazcana prazcAnetAn vaktumihArhati .
brUhi dharmavidAM zreSTha paraM kautUhalaM mama . mokSadharmArthakuzalo bhavA~llokeSu gIyate .
sarvasaMzayasaMcchettA tvadanyo na ca vidyate . saMsArabhIravazcaiva mokSakAmAstathA vayam .
vAsudeva uvAca tasmai sampratipannAya yathAvat paripRcchate . ziSyAya guNayuktAya zAntAya priyavartine . chAyAbhUtAya dAntAya yatate brahmacAriNe . tAn praznAnabravIt pArtha medhAvI sa dhRtavrataH . guruH kurukulazreSTha samyak sarvAnariMdama .
gururuvAca brahmaNoktamidaM sarvamRSipravarasevitam . vedavidyAM samAzritya tattvabhUtArthabhAvanam .
jJAnaM tveva paraM vidyaH saMnyAsaM tapa uttamam . yastu veda nirAbAdhaM jJAnatattvaM vinizcayAt . sarvabhUtasthamAtmAnaM sa sarvagatiriSyate . yo vidvAn sahasaMvAsaM vivAsaM caiva pazyati . tathaivaikatvanAnAtve sa duHkhAt parimucyate . yo na kAmayate kiMcinna kiMcidabhimanyate . ihalokastha evaiSa brahmabhUyAya kalpate . pradhAnaguNatattvajJaH sarvabhUtavidhAnavit . nirmamo nirahaGkAro mucyate nAtra saMzayaH . avyaktabIjaprabhavo buddhiskandhamayo mahAn . mahAhaGkAraviTapa indriyAkurakoTaraH . mahAbhUtavizeSazca vizeSapratizAkhavAn . sadAparNaH sadApuSpaH sadA zubhaphalodayaH . ajIvaH sarvabhUtAnAM brahmabIjaH sanAtanaH . etajjJAtvA ca tattvAni jJAnena paramAsinA . chittvA cAmaratAM prApya jahAti mRtyujanmanI .
bhUtabhavyabhaviSyAdi dharmakAmArthanizcayam . siddhasaMghaparijJAtaM purAkalpaM sanAtanam . pravakSye ' haM mahAprAjJa padamuttamamadya te . buddhvA yadiha saMsiddhA bhavantIha manISiNaH .
upagamyarSayaH pUrvaM jijJAsantaH parasparam . prajApatibharadvAjau gautamo bhArgavastathA . vasiSThaH kazyapazcaiva vizvAmitro ' trireva ca . mArgAn sarvAn parikramya parizrAntAH svakarmabhiH .26
RSimAGgirasaM vRddhaM puraskRtya tu te dvijAH . dadRzurbrahmabhavane brahmANaM vItakalmaSam .
taM praNamya mahAtmAnaM sukhAsInaM maharSayaH . papracchurvinayopetA naiHzreyasamidaM param .
kathaM karma kriyAt sAdhu kathaM mucyeta kilbiSAt . ke no mArgAH zivAzca syuH kiM satyaM kiM ca dupkRtam .
ko cobhau karmaNAM mArgoM prApnuyurdakSiNottarau . pralayaM cApavargaM ca bhUtAnAM prabhavApyayau .
ityuttAH sa munizreSThairyadAha prapitAmahaH . tat te ' haM sampravakSyAmi zRNu ziSya yathAgamam .
brAhmaNa uvAca satyAd bhUtAni jAtAni sthAvarANi carANi ca . tapasA tAni jIvanti iti tad vitta suvratAH . svAM yoni samatikramya vartante stena karmaNA .
satyaM hi guNasaMyuktaM niyataM paJcalakSaNam . brahma satyaM tapaH satyaM satyaM caiva prajApatiH .
satyAd bhUtAni jAtAni satyaM bhUtamayaM jagat . tasmAt satyamayA viprA nityaM yogaparAyaNAH . atItakrodhasaMtApA niyatA dharmasevina : . anyonyaniyatAn vaidyAn dharmasetupravartakAn . tAnahaM sampravakSyAmi zAzvatAllokabhAvanAn . cAturvidyaM tathA varNAzcAturAzramikAn pRthak .
dharmamekaM catuSpAdaM nityamAhurmanISiNaH . panthAnaM vaH pravakSyAmi zivaM kSemakaraM dvijAH .
niyataM brahmabhAvAya gataM pUrvaM manISibhiH . gadantastaM mayAdyeha panthAnaM durvidaM param .
nibodhata mahAbhAgA nikhilena paraM padam . brahmacArikamevAhurAzramaM prathamaM padam .
gArhasthyaM tu dvitIyaM syAd vAnaprasthamataH param . tataH paraM tu vijJeyamadhyAtmaM paramaM padam .
jyotirAkAzamAdityo vAyurindraH prajApatiH . nopaiti yAvadadhyAtma tAvadetAn na pazyati .
tasyopAyaM pravakSyAmi purastAt taM nibodhata . phalamUlAnilabhujAM munInAM vasatAM vane . . vAnaprasthaM dvijAtInAM trayANAmupadizyate . sarveSAmeva varNAnAM gArhasthyaM tad vidhIyate .
zraddhAlakSaNamityevaM dharmaM dhIrAH pracakSate . ityevaM devayAnA vaH panthAnaH parikIrtitAH . sadbhiradhyAsitA dhIraiH karmabhirdharmasetavaH .
eteSAM pRthagadhyAste yo dharmaM saMzitavrataH . kAlAt pazyati bhUtAnAM sadaiva prabhavApyayau .
atastattvAni vakSyAmi yAthAtathyena hetunA . viSayasthAni sarvANi vartamAnAni bhAgazaH .
mahAnAtmA tathAvyaktamahaMkArastathaiva ca . indriyANi dazaikaM ca mahAbhUtAni paJca ca . vizeSAH paJcabhUtAnAmiti sargaH sanAtanaH . caturviMzatirekA ca tattvasaMkhyA prakIrtitA .
tattvAnAmatha yo veda sarveSAM prabhavApyayau . sa dhIraH sarvabhUteSu na mohamadhigacchati .
tattvAni yo vedayate yathAtathaM guNAMzca sarvAnakhilAMzca devatAH . vidhUtapApmA pratimucya bandhanaM sa sarvalokAnamalAn samaznute .
saMjaya uvAca vidArya karNastAM senAM yudhiSThiramathAdravat . rathahastyazvapattInAM sahasraH parivAritaH .
nAnAyudhasahasrANi preritatAnyaribhirvRSaH . chitvA bANazatairugaistAnavidhyadasambhramAt .
nicakarta zirAMsyeSAM bAhUnUrUMzca sUtajaH . te hatA vasudhAM peturbhagnAzcAnye vidudruvaH .
drAviDAstu niSAdAstu punaH sAtyakicoditAH . abhyadravaJjighAMsantaH pattayaH karNamAhave .
te vibAhuzirastrANAH prahatAH karNasAyakaiH . petuH pRthivyAM yugapacchinnaM zAlavanaM yathA .
evaM yodhazatAnyAjau sahasrANyayutAni caH . tAnIyurmahIM dehairyazasA pUrayandizaH .
ata vaikartanaM karNaM raNe kruddhamivAntakam . rurudhuH pANDupAJcAlA vyArghi mantrauSadhairiva .
sa tAn pramRdyAbhyapatat punareva yudhiSThiram . mantrauSadhikriyAtIto vyAdhiratyulbaNau yathA .
sa rAjagRddhibhI rudaH pANDupaJcAlAkekayauH . nAzakat tAnatikrAntuM mRtyubrahmavido yathA .
tato yudhiSThiraH karNamadUrasthaM nivAritam . abravIt paravIranaM krodhasaMraktalocanaH .
karNa karNa vRthAdRSTe sUtaputra vacaH zRNu . sadA spardhasi saMgrAme phAlgunena tarasvinA . tathAsmAn bAdhase nityaM dhArtarASTramate sthitaH .
yad balaM yaca te vIryaM pradveSo yastu pANDaSu . tat sarvaM darzayasvAdya pauruSaM mahadAsthitaH . yuddhazraddhAM ca te ' dyAhaM vineSyAmi mahAhave .
evamuktvA mahArAja karNaM pANDusutastadA . suvarNapubairdazabhirvivyAdhAyasmayaiH zaraiH .
taM sUtaputro dazabhiH pratyaviddhyadariMdamaH . vatsadantairmaheSvAsaH prahasanniva bhArata .
so ' vajJAya tu nirviddhaH sUtaputreNa mAriSa . prajajvAla tataH krodhAddhaviSeva hutAzanaH .
jvAlAmAlAparikSipto rAjJo deho vyadRzyata . yugAnte dagdhukAmasya saMvartAgnerivAparaH .
tato visphArya sumahacApaM hemapariSkRtam . samAdhatta zitaM bANaM girINAmapi dAraNam .
tataH pUrNAyatotkRSTaM yamadaNDanibhaM zaram . mumoca tvarito rAjA sUtaputrajighAMsayA .
sa tu vegavatA mukto bANo vajrAzanisvanaH . viveza sahasA karNa savye pArzve mahAratham .
sa tu tena prahAreNa pIDitaH pramumoha vai . strastagAtro mahAbAhurdhanarutsRjya syandane .
gatAsuriva nizcetAH zalyasyAbhimukho ' patat . rAjApi bhUyo nAjaghne karNa pArthahitepsayA .
tato hAhAkRtaM sarva dhArtarASTrabalaM mahat . vivarNamukhabhUyiSThaM karNaM dRSTvA tathAgatam .
siMhanAdazca saMjajJe zvelA : kilakilAstathA . pANDavAnAM mahArAja dRSTvA rAjJaH parAkramam .
pratilabhya tu rAdheyaH saMjJA nAticirAdiva . dane rAjavinAzAya manaH krUraparAkramaH .
sa hemavikRtaM cApaM visphArya vijayaM mahat . avAkiradameyAtmA pANDavaM nizitaiH zarai .
tataH kSurAdhyAM pAJcAlyau cakrarakSau mahAtmanaH . jaghAna candradevaM ca daNDadhAraM ca saMyuge .
tAvubhau dharmarAjasya pravIrau paripArzvataH . sthAbhyAze cakAzete candrasyeva punarvasU .
yudhiSThiraM : puna : karNamaviddhayataM triMzatA zaraiH . suSeNaM satyasenaM ca tribhistribhiratADayat .
zalyaM navatyA vivyAdha trisaptayA ca sUtajam . tAMstasya goptan vivyAdha tribhistribhirajihmagaiH .
tataH prahastAdhirathirvidhunvAnaH sa kArmukam . bhitvA bhallena rAjAnaM viddhvA SaSTayA ' nadattadA .
tata : pravIrAH pANDUnAmabhyadhAvannamarSitAH . yudhiSThiraM parIpsantaH karNamabhyardayaJcharaiH .
sAtyakizcekitAnazca yuyutsuH pANDava eva ca . dhRSTadyumnaH zikhaNDI ca draupadeyAH prabhadrakA . yamau ca bhImasenazca zizupAlasya cAtmajaH . kArUSA matsyazeSAzca kekathAH kAzikosalAH . ete ca tvaritA vIrA vasuSeNamatADayan .
janamejayazca pAJcAlyaH karNaM vivyAdha sAyakaiH . vArAhAkarNanArAcairnAlIkairnizitaiH zaraiH . vatsadantairvipAThaizca kSurapraizcaTakAmukhaiH . nAnApraharaNaizcotrai rathahastazvasAdibhiH . sarvato ' bhyadravat karNaM parivArya jighAMsayA .
sa pANDavAnAM pravaraiH sarvataH samabhidrutaH . udIrayan brAhmamastraM zarairApUrayad dizaH .
tataH zaramahajvAlau vIryoSmA karNapAvakaH . nirdahan pANDavavanaM vIraH paryacarad raNe .
sa saMdhAya mahAstrANi maheSvAsA mahAmanAH . prahasya puruSendrasya zaraizciccheda kArmukam .
tata : saMdhAya navati nimeSAnnataparvaNAm . bibheda kavacaM rAjJo raNe karNaH zitaiH zarai .
tad varma hemavikRtaM ratnacitraM babhau patat . savidyudabhraM savituH zliSTaM vAtahataM yathA .
tadaGgAt puruSendrasya bhraSTaM varma vyarocata . ratnalaMkRta citrairvyabhraM nizi yathA nabhaH . chinnavarmA zaraiH pArtho rudhireNa samukSitaH .
tataH sarvAyasIM zaktiM cikSepAdhirathiM prati . tAM jvalantImivAkAze zaraizciccheda saptabhiH . sA chinnA bhUmimagamanmaheSvAsasya sAyakaiH .
tato bAhvorlalATe ca hRdi caiva yudhiSThiraH . caturbhistomaraiH karNaM tADayitvAnadanmudA .
udbhinarudhiraH karNaH kruddhaH sarpa iva zvasan . dhvajaM ciccheda bhallena tribhirvivyAdha pANDavam . iSudhI cAsya ciccheda rathaM ca tilazo ' cchinat .
kAlavAlAstu ye pArthaM dantavarNAvahan hayAH . tairyuktaM rathamAsthAya prAyAd rAjA parAGamukhaH .
evaM pArtho ' bhyupAyAt sa nihataH pANiMsArathiH . azaknuvan pramukhataH sthAtuM karNasya durmanAH .
abhidrutya tu rAdheyaH pANDuputraM yudhiSThiram . vajracchatrAMkuzairmatasyairdhvajakUrmambujAdibhiH . lakSaNairupapannena pANDunA pANDunandanam . pavitrIkartumAtmAnaM skandhe saMspRzya pANinA . grahItumicchan sa balAt kuntIvAkyaM ca so ' smarat .
taM zalyaH prAha mA karNa gRhIthAH pArthivottamam . gRhItamAtro hatvA tvAM mA kariSyati bhasmasAt .
abravIta prahasan rAjan kutsayanniva pANDavam . kathaM nAma kule jAtaH kSatradharme vyavasthitaH . prajahyAt samaraM bhItaH prANAn rakSan mahAhave . na bhavAn kSatradharmeSu kuzalo hIti me matiH .
brAhme bale bhavAn yuktaH svAdhyAye yajJakarmaNi . mA sma yuddhyasva kaunteya mA sma vIrAn samAsadaH .
mA caitAnapriyaM brUhi mA vai vraja mahAraNam . vaktavyA mAriSAnse tu na vaktavyAstu mAdRzAH .
mAdRzAn vidvAvan yuddhe etadanyacca lapsyase . svagRhaM gaccha kaunteya yatra tau kezavArjunau . na hi tvAM samare rAjan hanyAt karNaH kathaJcana .
evamuktvA tataH pArtha visRjya ca mahAbalaH . nyahanat pANDavIM senAM vajrahasta ivAsurIm .
tato ' pAyAd dutaM rAjan vIDanniva narezvaraH . athApayati rAjAnaM matvAnvIyustamacyutam . cedipANDavapaJcAlAH sAtyakzci mahArathaH . draupadeyAstathA zUrA mAdrIputrau ca pANDavau .
tato yudhiSThirAnIkaM dRSTvA parAGmukham . kurubhiH sahitA vIraH prahRSTaH pRSThato ' nvagAt .
bherIzaGgamRdaGgAnAM kArmukANAM ca niHsvanaH . babhUva dhArtarASTrANAM siMhanAdaravastathA .
karNa : yudhiSThirastu kauravya rathamArudya satvaram . zrutakIrtermahArAja dRSTvAn karNavikramam .
kAlyamAnaM balaM dRSTvA dhamarAjo yudhiSThiraH . svAn yodhAnabravIt kruddho nighnataitAn kimAsata .
tato rAjJAbhyanujJAtAH pANDavAnAM mahArathaH . bhImasenamukhAH sarve putrAste pratyupAdravan .
abhavat tumulaH zabdo yodhAnAM tatra bhArata . rathahastyazvapattInAM zastrANAM ca tatastataH .
uttiSThata praharata pretAbhipatateti ca . iti bruvANA hyanyonyaM jaghnuryodhA mahAraNe .
abhracchAyeva tannAsIccharavRSTibhirambare . samAvRtairnaravarairninadbhiritaretaram .
vipatAkadhvacchatrA vyazvasUtAyudhA raNe . vyaGgAGgAvayavAH petuH kSitau kSINA : kSitIzvarAH .
pravaNAdiva zailAnAM zikharANi dvipottamAH . sArohA nihatAH peturvavabhinnA ivAdrayaH .
chinnabhinnaviparyastairvarmAlaGkArabhUSaNaiH . sArohAsturagAH peturharavIrAH sahasrazaH .
vipraviddhAyudhAzcaiva dviradAzvarathairhatAH . prativIraizca samma pattisaMghAH sahasrazaH .
vizAlAyatatAmrAkSaiH padmendusadRzAnanaiH . zirobhiyuddhazauNDAnAM sarvataH saMvRttA mahI . yathA bhuvi tathA vyomni ni : svanaM zuzruvurjanAH . vimAnairapsaraH saGgairgItavAdini : svanaiH .
hatAnabhimukhAn vIrAn vIraiH zatasahasrazaH . AropyAropya gacchanti vimAneSvapsarogaNAH .
tad dRSTvA mahadAzcaryaM pratyakSaM svargalipsayA . prahaSTamanasaH zUrAH kSipraM jaghnuH parasparam .
rathino rathibhiH sArdhaM citra yuyudhurAhave . pattayaH pattibhirnAgA : saha nAgairhayairhayAH .
evaM pravRtte saMgrAme gajavAdinarakSaye . sainyena rajasA vyApte sve svAJjaghnuH pare parAn .
kacAkaci yuddhamAsId dantAdanti nakhAnakhi . muSTiyuddhaM niyuddhaM ca dehapApmAsunAzanam .
tathA vartati saMgrAme gajavAjinarakSaye . narAzvanAgadehebhyaH prasRtA lohitApagA . gajAzvanaradehAn sA vyuvAha patitAn bahUn .
narAzvagajasambAdhe narAzvagajasAdinAm . lohitodA mahAghorA mAMsazoNitakardamA . narAzvagajadehAnAM sA vahantI bhIrubhISaNA .
tasyAH pAramapAraM ca vrajanti vijayaiSiNaH . gAdhena coplavantazca nimajyonmajya cApare .
tu lohitadigdhAGgA raktavarmAyudhAmbarAH . zastrustasyAM papuzcAsyAM mamluzca bharatarSabha .
te rathAnazvAn narAna nAgAnAyudhAbharaNAni ca . vasanAnyatha varmANi vadhyamAnAn hatAnApi . bhUmi khaM dyAM dizazcaiva prAyaH pazyAma lohitAH .
lohitya tu gandhena sparzena ca rasena ca . rUpeNa cAtiraktena zabdena ca visarpatA . viSAdaH sumahAnAsIt prAya : sainyasya bhArata .
tat tu viprahataM sainyaM bhImasenamukhAstadA . bhUyaH samAdravanaM vIrAH sAtyakipramukhAstadA .
teSAmApatatAM vegamaviSahyaM nirIkSya ca . putrANAM te mahAsainyamAsId rAjan parAGmukham .
tat prakIrNarathAzvebhaM naravAjisamAkulam . vidhvastavarmakavacaM praviddhAyudhakArmukam . vyadravat tAvakaM sainyaM loDyamAnaM samantataH . siMhArditamivAraNye yathA gajakulaM tathA .
rAjovAca na nikRtyA na dambhena brahmannicchAmi jIvitum . nAdharmayuktAniccheyamarthAn sumahato ' pyaham .
purastAdeva bhagavan mayaitadapavarjitam . yena mAM nAbhizaGketa yena kRtsnaM hitaM bhavet . AnRzaMsyena dharmeNa loke hyasmin jijIviSuH . nAhametadalaM kartuM naitat tvayyupapadyate .
muniruvAca upapannastvametena yathA kSatriya bhASase . prakRtyA hyupapanno ' si buddhyA vA bahudarzanaH .
ubhayoreva vAmarthe yatiSye tava tasya ca . saMzleSaM vA kariSyAmi zAzvataM panapAyinam .
tvAdRzaM ki kule jAtamanRzaMsaM bahuzrutam . amAtyaM ko na kurvIta rAjyapraNayakovidam .
yastvaM pracyAvito rAjyAd vyasanaM cottamaM gataH . AnRzaMsyena vRttena kSatriyecchasi jIvitum .
AgantA madgahaM tAta vaidehaH satyasaMgaraH . athAhaM taM niyokSyAmi tat kariSyatyasaMzayam .
tata AhUya vaidehaM munirvacanamabravIt . ayaM rAjakule jAto viditAbhyantaro mama .
Adarza iva zuddhAtmA zAradazcandramA yathA . nAsmin pazyAmi vRjinaM sarvato me parIkSitaH .
tena te saMdhirevAstu vizvasAsmin yathA mayi . na rAjyamanamAtyena zakyaM zAstumapi tryaham .
amAtyaH zUra eva syAd buddhisampanna eva vA . tAbhyAM caivobhayaM rAjan pazya rAjyaprayojanam .
dharmAtmanAM kva cilloke nAnyAsti gatirIdRzI . mahAtmA rAjaputro ' yaM satAM mArgamanuSThitaH .
susaMgRhItastvevaiSa tvayA dharmapurogamaH . saMsevyamAnaH zatrUste gRhNIyAnmahato gaNAn .
yadyayaM pratiyuddhyet tvAM svakarma kSatriyasya tat . jigISamANastvAM yuddhe pitRpaitAmahe pade . tvaM cApi pratiyuddhyethA vijigISuvrate sthitaH . ayudhvaiva niyogAnme vaze kuru hite sthitaH .
sa tvaM dharmamavekSasva hitvA lobhamasAmpratam . na ca kAmAnna ca drohAt svadharmaM hAtumarhasi .
naiva nityaM jayastAta naiva nitvaM parAjayaH . tasmAd bhojayativyazca bhoktavyazca paro janaH .
Atmanyapi ca saMdRzyAvubhau jayaparAjayau . niHzeSakAriNAM tAta niHzeSakaraNAd bhayam .
ityuktaH pratyuvAcedaM vacanaM brAhmaNarSabham . pratipUjyAbhisatkRtya pUjArhamanumAnya ca . yathA brUyAnmahAprAjJo yathA brUyAnmahAzrutaH . zreyaskAmo yathA brUyAdubhayoreva tat kSamam . yad yad vacanamukto ' smi kariSyAmi ca tat tathA . etaddhi paramaM zreyo na me ' trAsti vicAraNA .
tataH kausalyamAhUya maithilo vAkyamabravIt . dharmato nItitazcaiva lokazca vijito mayA .
ahaM tvayA cAtmaguNairjitaH pArthivasattama . AtmAnamanavajJAya jitavad vartatAM bhavAn .
nAvamanyAmi te buddhiM nAvamanye ca pauruSam . nAvamanye jayAmiti jitavad vartatAM bhavAn . .
yathAvat pUjito rAjan gRhaM gantAsi me bhRzam . tataH sampUjya tau vipraM vizvastau jagmaturgrahAn .
vaidehastvatha kausalyaM pravezya gRhamaJjasA . pAdyArghyamadhuparkestaM pUjAha~ pratyapUjayat .
dadau duhitaraM cAsmai ratnAni vividhAni ca . eSa rAjJAM paro dharmo ' nityau jayaparAjayau .
vaizampAyana uvAca prabhAtAyAM tu zarvaryAM teSAmakliSTakarmaNAm . vanaM yiyAsatAM viprAstasthurbhikSAbhujo ' cataH .
tAnuvAca tato rAjA kuntIputro yudhiSTharaH . vayaM hi hRtasarvasvA hRtarAjyA hRtazriyaH . phalamUlAzanAhArA vanaM gacchAma duHkhitAH . vanaM ca doSabahulaM bahuvyAlasarIsRpam .
pariklezazca vo manyedhruvaM tatra bhaviSyati . brAhmaNAnAM pariklezo daivatAnyapi sAdayet . kiM punarmAmito viprA nivartadhvaM yatheSTataH .
brAhmaNA Ucu : gatiryA bhavatAM rAjastAM vayaM gantumudyatAH . nArhasyasmAn parityaktuM bhaktAn saddharmadarzinaH .
anukampAM hi bhakteSu devatA hyapi kurvate . vizeSato brAhmaNeSu sadAcArAvalambiSu .
yudhiSThira uvAca mamApi paramA bhaktirbrAhmaNeSu sadA dvijAH . sahAyaviparibhraMzastvayaM sAdayatIva mAm . Ahareyurime ye ' pi phalamUlamadhUni ca . ta ime zokajairduHkhairdhAtaro me vimohitAH . draupadyA viprakarSaNa rAjyApaharaNena ca . duHkhArditAnimAn klezairnAhaM yoktumihotsahe .
brAhmaNA UcuH asmatpoSaNajA cintA mA bhUt te hRdi pArthiva . svayamAhatya cAnnAni tvAnuyAsyAmahe vayam .
anudhyAnena japyena vidhAsyAmaH zivaM tava . kathAbhizcAbhiramyAbhiH saha raMsyAmahe vayam .
yudhiSThira uvAca evametatra saMdeho rame ' haM satataM dvijaiH . nyUnabhAvAt tu pazyAmi pratyAdezamivAtmanaH .
kathaM drakSyAmi vaH sarvAn svayamAhRtabhojanAn . madbhaktyA klizyato ' narhAn dhik pApAndhRtarASTrajAn .
vaizampAyana uvAca ityuktvA sa nRpaH zocana niSasAda mahItale . yAtmarato vidvAJchaunako nAma vai dvijaH . yoge sAMkhye ca kuzalo rAjAnamidamabravIt .
zokasthAnasahasrANi bhayasthAnazatAni ca . divase divase mUDhamAvizanti na paNDitam .
na hi jJAnaviruddheSu bahudoSeSu karmasu . zreyoghAtiSu sajjante buddhimanto bhavadvidhAH .
aSTAGgAM buddhimAhuryAM sarvAzreyo ' bhighAtinIm . zrutismRtisamAyuktAM rAjan sA tvayyavasthitA .
arthakRcchreSu durgeSu vyApatsu svajanasya ca . zArIramAnasairduHkhaina sIdanti bhavadvidhAH .
zrUyatAM cAbhidhAsyAmi janakena yathA purA . AtmavyavasthAnakarA gItAH zlokA mahAtmanA .
manodehasamutthAbhyAM duHkhAbhyamarditaM jagat . tyorvyAsasamAsAbhyAM zamopAyamimaM zRNu .
vyAdheraniSTasaMsparzAcchramAdiSTavirvajanAt . duHkhaM caturbhiH zArIraM kAraNaiH sampravartate .
tadA tatpratikArAcca satataM cAvicintanAt . AdhivyAdhiprazamanaM kriyAyogadvayena tu .
matimanto hyato vaidyAH zamaM prAgeva kurvate . mAnasasya priyAkhyAnaiH sambhogopanayairnRNAm .
mAnasena hi duHkhena zarIramupatapyate . aya : piNDena taptena kumbhasaMsthamivodakam .
mAnasaM zamayet tasmAjjJAnenAgnimivAmbunA . prazAnte mAnase hyasya zArIramupazAmyati .
manaso duHkhamUlaM tu sneha ityupalabhyate . snehAt tu sajjate janturduHkhayogamupaiti ca .
snehamUlAni duHkhAni snehajAni bhayAni ca . zokaharSoM tathA ' ' yAsaH sarvaM snehAt pravartate . snehAd bhAvo ' nurAgazca prajajJe viSaye tathA . azreyaskAvubhAvetau pUrvastatra guruH smRtaH .
koTarAgniryathAzeSaM samUlaM pAdapaM dahet . dharmArtho tu tathAlpo ' pi rAgadoSo vinAzayet .
viprayoge na tu tyAgI doSadarzI samAgame . virAgaM bhajate janturnivairo niravagrahaH .
tasmAt snehaM na lipseta mitrebhyodhanasaMcayAt . svazarIrasamutthaM ca jJAnena vinivartayet .
jJAnAnviteSu yukteSu zAstrajJeSu kRtAtmasu . na teSu sajjate snehaH padmapatreSvivodakam .
rAgAbhibhUtaH puruSaH kAmena parikRSyate . icchA saMjAyate tasya tatastRSNA vivardhate . tRSNA hi sarvapApiSThA nityodvegakarI smRtA . adharmabahulA caiva ghorA pApAnubandhinI .
yA dustyajA durmatibhiryA na jIryati jIryataH . yo ' sau prANAntiko rogastAM tRSNAM tyajataH sukham .36
anAdyantA tu sA tRSNA antardehagatA nRNAm . vinAzayati bhUtAni ayonija ivAnalaH .
yathaidhaH svasamutthena vahninA nAzamRcchati . tathAkRtAtmA lobhena sahajena vinazyati .
rAjataH salilAdagnezcorataH svajanAdapi . bhayamarthavatAM nityaM mRtyoH prANabhRtAmiva .
yathA hyAmiSamAkAze pakSibhiH zvApadairbhuvi . bhakSyate salile matsyaistathA sarvatra vittavAn .
artha eva hi keSAMcidanarthaM bhajate nRNAm . arthazreyasi cAsakto na zreyo vindate naraH .
tasmAdarthAgamAH sarve manomohavivardhanAH . kArpaNyaM darpamAnau ca bhayamudvega eva ca . arthajAni viduH prAjJA duHkhAnyetAni dehinAm . arthasyotpAdane caiva pAlane ca tathA kSaye . . sahanti ca mahad duHkhaM pranti caivArthakAraNAt . arthA duHkhaM parityaktuM pAlitAzcaiva zatravaH .
duHkhena cAdhigamyante tasmAnnAzaM na cintayet . asaMtoSaparA mUDhAH saMtoSaM yAnti paNDitAH .
anto nAsti pipAsAyAH saMtoSaH paramaM sukham . tasmAt saMtoSameveha paraM pazyanti paNDitAH .
anityaM yauvanaM rUpaM jIvitaM ratnasaMcayaH . aizparya priyasaMvAso gRdhyet tatra na paNDitaH .
