AtmApi cAyaM na mama sarvA vA pRthivI mama . yathA mama tathA ' nyeSAmiti cintya na me vyathA . .
etAM buddhimahaM prApya na prahRSye na ca vyathe . yathA kASThaM ca kASThaM ca sameyAtAM mahodadhau . sametya ca vyapeyAtAM tadvadbhUtasamAgamaH .
evaM putrAzca pautrAzca jJAtayo bAndhavAstathA . teSAM sneho na kartavyo viprayogo dhruvo hi taiH .
adarzanAdApatitaH punazcAdarzanaM gataH . na tvAsau veda na tvaM taM kaH san kimanuzocasi .
tRSNArtiprabhavaM duHkhaM duHkhArtiprabhavaM sukham . sukhAt saMjAyate duHkhaM duHkhamevaM punaH punaH .
sukhasyAnantaraM duHkhaM duHkhasyAnantaraM sukham . sukhaduHkhe manuSyANAM cakravat parivartataH .
sukhAt tvaM duHkhamApanna punarApatsyase sukham . na nityaM labhate duHkhaM na nityaM labhate sukham .
zarIramevAyatanaM sukhasya duHkhasya cApyAyatanaM zarIram . yadyaccharIreNa karoti karma tenaiva dehI samupAznute tat . .
jIvitaM ca zarIreNa jAtyaiva saha jAyate . ubhe saha vivartete ubhe saha vinazyataH .
snehapAzairbahuvidhairAviSTaviSayA janAH . akRtArthAzca sIdante jalaiH saikatasetavaH .
snehena tilavat sarvaM sargacakre nipIDyate . tilapIDairivAkramya klezairajJAnasambhavaiH .
saMcinotyazubhaM karma kalatrApekSayA naraH . ekaH klezAnavApnoti paratreha ca mAnavaH .
putradArakuTumbeSu prasaktAH sarvamAnavAH . zokapaGkArNave magnA jIrNA vanagajA iva .
putranAze vittanAze jJAtisambandhinAmapi . prApyate sumahad duHkhaMdAvAgnipratimaM vibho .
daivAyattamidaM sarvaM sukhaduH : khe bhavAbhavau . asRhat sasuhRccApi sazatrurmitravAnapi . saprajJaH prajJayA hIno daivena labhate sukham .
nAlaM sukhAya suhRdo nAlaM duHkhAya zatravaH . na ca prajJAlamarthAnAM na sukhAnAmalaM dhanam .
na buddhirdhanalAbhAya na jADyamasamRddhaye . lokaparyAyavRttAntaM prAjJo jAnAti netaraH .
buddhimantaM ca zUraM ca mUDhaM bhIruM jaDaM kavim . durbalaM balavantaM ca bhAginaM bhajate sukham .
dhenurvatsasya gopasya svAminastaskarasya ca . payaH pibati yastasyA dhenustasyeti nizcayaH .
ye ca mUDhatamA loke ye ca buddheH paraM gatAH . te narAH sukhamedhante klizyatyantarito janaH .
antyeSu remire dhIrA na te madhyeSu remire . antyaprAptiM sukhAmAhurduHkhamantaramantyayoH .
ye ca buddhisukhaM prAptA dvandvAtItA vimatsarAH . tAn naivArthA na cAnA vyathayanti kadAcana .
atha ye buddhimaprAptA vyatikrAntAzca mUDhatAm . te ' tivelaM prahRSyanti saMtApamupayAnti ca .
nityaM pramuditA mUDhA divi devagaNA iva . avalepena mahatA paribhUtyA vicetasaH .
sukhaM duHkhAntamAlasyaM duHkhaM dAkSyaM sukhodayam . bhUtistvevaM zriyA sArdhaM dakSe vasati nAlase .
sukhaM vA yadi vA duHkhaM priyaM vA yadi vApriyam . prAptaM prAptamupAsIta hRdayenAparAjitaH .
zokasthAnasahastrANi bhayasthAnazatAni ca . divase divase mUDhamAvizanti na paNDitam .
buddhimantaM kRtaprajJaM zuzrUSumanasUyakam . dAntaM jitendriyaM cApi zoko na spRzate naram .
etAM buddhiM samAsthAya guptacittazcared budhaH . udayAstamayajJaM hi na zokaH spaSTumarhati .
yannimittaM bhavecchokastApo vA duHkhameva ca . AyAso vA yato mUlamekAGgamapi tat tyajet .
kiMcideva mamatvena yadA bhavati kalpitam . tadeva paritApArthaM sarvaM sampadyate tathA .
yad yat yajati kAmAnAM tat sukhasyAbhipUryate . kAmAnusArI puruSaH kAmAnanuvinazyati .
yacca kAmasukhaM loke yacca divyaM mahat sukham . tRSNAkSayasukhasyaite nArhataH SoDazI kalAm .
pUrvadehakRtaM karma zubhaM vA yadi vAzubham . prAjJaM mUDhaM tathA zUraM bhajate yAdRzaM kRtam .
evameva kilaitAni priyANyevApriyANi ca . jIveSu parivartante duHkhAni ca sukhAni ca .
etAM buddhiM samAsthAya sukhamAste guNAnvitaH . sarvAn kAmAn jugupseta kAmAn kurvIta pRSThataH .
vRtta eSa hRSi prauDho mRtyureSa manobhavaH . krodho nAma zarIrastho dehinAM procyate budhaiH .
yadA saMharate kAmAn kUrmo ' GgAnIva sarvazaH . tadA ' ' tmajyotirAtmAyamAtmanyeva prapazyati .
na bibheti yadA cAyaM yadA cAsmAnna bibhyati . yadA necchati na dRSTi brahma sampadyate tadA .
ubhe satyAnRte tyaktvA zokAnandau bhayAbhaye . priyApriye parityajya prazAntAtmA bhaviSyati .
yadA na kurute dhIraH sarvabhUteSu pApakam . karmaNA manasA vAcA brahma sampadyate tadA .
yA dustyajA durmatibhiryA na jIryati jIryataH . yo ' sau prANAntiko rogastAM tRSNAM tyajataH sukham . .55
atra piGgalayA gItA gAthAH zrUyanti pArthiva . yathA sA kRcchrakAle ' pi lebhe dharmaM sanAtanam .
saMkete piGgalA vezyA kAntenAsId vinAkRtA . atha kRcchragatA zAntA buddhimAsthApayat tadA .
piGgalovAca unmattAhamanunmattaM kAntamanvavasaM ciram . antike ramaNaM santaM nainamadhyagamaM purA .
ekasthUNaM navadvAramapidhAsyAmyagArakam . kA hi kAntamihAyAntamayaM kAnteti maMsyate .
akAmAM kAmarUpeNa dhUrtA narakarUpiNaH . na punarvaJcayiSyanti pratibuddhAsmi jAgRmi .
anartho hi bhavedartho daivAt pUrvakRtena vA . sambuddhAhaM nirAkArA nAhamadyAjitendriyA .
sukhaM nirAzaH svapiti nairAzyaM paramaM sukham . AzAmanAzAM kRtvA hi sukhaM svapiti piGgalA .
bhISma uvAca etaizcAnyaizca viprasya hetumadbhiH prabhASitaiH . paryavasthApito rAjA senajinmumude sukhI .
vaizampAyana uvAca asiddhAnunaye kRSNe kurubhyaH pANDavAn gate . abhigamya pRthAM kSattA zanaiH zocannivAbravIt .
jAnAsi me jIvaputri bhAvaM nityamavigrahe . krozato na ca gRhNIte vacanaM me suyodhanaH .
upapanno hyasau rAjA cedipAJcAlakekayaiH . bhImArjunAbhyAM kRSNena yuyudhAnayamairapi . .
upaplevya niviSTo ' pi dharmameva yudhiSThiraH . kAkSate jJAtisauhArdAd balavAn durbalo yathA .
rAjA tu dhRtarASTro ' yaM vayovRddho na zAmyati . mattaH putramadenaiva vidharmaM pathi vartate .
jayadrathasya karNasya tathA duHzAsanasya ca . saubalasya ca durbuddhyA mitho bhedoH prapatsyate .
adharmeNa hi dharmiSThaM kRtaM vaikAryamIdRzam . yeSAM teSAmayaM dharmaH sAnubandho bhaviSyati .
kriyamANe balAd dharmaM kurubhiH ko na saMjvaret . asAmnA kezave yAte samudyokSyanti pANDavAH .
tataH kurUNAmanayo bhavitA vIranAzanaH . cintayan na labhe nidrAmahaH su ca nizAsu ca .
zrutvA tu kuntI tadvAkyamarthakAmena bhASitam . sA niHzvasantI duHkhArtA manasA vimamarza ha .
dhigastvarthaM yatkRte ' yaM mahAn jJAtivadhaH kRtaH . vay/ate suhRdAM caivaM yuddhe ' smin vai parAbhavaH .
pANDavAzcedipaJcAlA yAdavAzca samAgatAH . bhArataiH saha yotsyanti kiM nu duHkhamataH param .
pazye doSaM dhruvaM yuddhe tathA ' yuddhe parAbhavam . adhanasya mRtaM zreyo na hi jJAtikSayo jayaH .
iti me cintayantyA vai hRdi duHkhaM pravartate . pitAmahaH zAntanava AcAryazca yudhAM patiH .
karNazca dhArtarASTrArthaM vardhayanti bhayaM mama . AcAryaH kAmavAn ziSyaioNo yuddhayeta jAtucit .
pANDaveSu kathaM hArda kuryAnna ca pitAmahaH . ayaM tveko vRthAdRSTirdhArtarASTrasya durmateH .
mohAnuvartI satataM pApo dveSTi ca pANDavAn . mahatyanarthaM nirbandho balavAMzca vizeSataH .
karNaH sadA pANDavAnAM tanme dahati samprati . AzaMse tvadya karNasya mano ' haM pANDavAn prati .
prasAdayitumAsAdya darzayantI yathAtatham . toSito bhagavAn yatra durvAsA me varaM dadau .
AhvAnaM mantrasaMyuktaM vasantyAH pitRvezmani . sAhamantaHpure rAjJaH kuntibhojapuraskRtA .
cintayantI bahuvidhaM hRdayena vidUyatA . balAbalaM ca mantrANAM brAhmaNasya ca vAgbalam .
strIbhAvAd bAlabhAvAcca cintayantI punaH punaH . dhAcyA visrabdhayA guptA sakhIjanavRtA tadA .
me doSaM pariharantI ca pituzcAritryarakSiNI . kathaM nu sukRtaM syAnAparAdhavatI katham .
bhaveyamiti saMcintya brAhmaNaM taM namasya ca . kautUhalAt tu taM labdhvA bAlizyAdAcaraM tadA . kanyA satI devamarkamAsAdayamahaM tataH .
yo ' sau kAnInagarbho me putravat parirakSitaH . kasmAnna kuryAd vacanaM pathyaM bhrAtRhitaM tathA .
iti kuntI vinizcitya kAryanizcayamuttamam . kAryArthamabhinizcitya yayau bhAgIrathI prati .
Atmajasya tatastasya ghRNinaH satyasaGginaH . gaGgAtIre pRthA ' zrauSId vedAdhyayananiHsvanam .
prAGmukhasyordhvabAhoH sA paryatiSThata pRSThataH . japyAvasAnaM kAryArthaM pratIkSantI tapasvinI .
atiSThat sUryatApArtA karNasyottaravAsasi . kauravyapatnI vArSNeyI padmamAleva zuSyatI .
ApRSThatApAjjaptvA sa parivRtya yatavrataH . dRSTvA kuntImupAtiSThadabhivAdya kRtAJjaliH .
yathAnyAyaM mahAtejA mAnI dharmabhRtAM varaH . utsamayan praNataH prAha kuntIM vaikartano vRSaH .
bhISma uvAca atropAyaM pravakSyAmi yathAvacchAstracakSuSA . tattvajJAnAccaran rAjan prApnuyAtparamAM gatim .
sarveSAmeva bhUtAnAM puruSaH zreSTha ucyate . puruSebhyo dvijAnAhurdvijebhyo mantradarzinaH .
sarvabhUtAtmabhUtAste sarvajJAH sarvadarzinaH . brAhmaNA vedazAstrajJAstattvArthagatanizcayAH .
netrahIno yathA hyekaH kRcchrANi labhate ' dhvani . jJAnahInastathA loke tasmAjjJAnavido ' dhikAH .
tAMstAnupAsate dharmAn dharmakAmA yathAgamam . na tveSAmarthasAmAnyamantareNa guNAnimAn .
vAgdehamanasAM zaucaM kSamA satyaM dhRtiH smRtiH . sarvadharmeSu dharmajJA jJApayanti guNAJchubhAn .
yadidaM brahmaNo rUpaM brahmacaryamiti smRtam . paraM tat sarvadharmebhyastena yAnti parAM gatim .
liGgasaMyogahInaM yacchabdasparzavivarjitam . zrotreNa zravaNaM caiva cakSuSA caiva darzanam .
vAksambhASApravRttaM yat tanmanaHparivarjitam . buddhyA cAdhyavasIyIta brahmacaryamakalmaSam .
samyagvRttirbrahmalokaM prApnuyAnmadhyamaH surAn . dvijAgrayo jAyate vidvAn kanyasI vRttimAsthitaH .
suduSkaraM brahmacaryamupAyaM tatra me zRNu . sampradIptamudIrNaM ca nigRhNIyAd dvijo rajaH .
yoSitAM na kathA zrAvyA na nirIkSyA nirambarAH . kathaJcid darzanAdAsAM durbalAnAM vizedrajaH .
rAgotpannazcaret kRcchaM mahArtiH pravizedapaH . magnaH svapne ca manasA virjapedaghamarSaNam .
pApmAnaM nirdahedevamantarbhUtarajomayam . jJAnayuktena manasA saMtatena vicakSaNaH .
kuNapAmadhyasaMyuktaM yadvadacchidrabandhanam . tadvad dehagataM vidyAdAtmAnaM dehabandhanam .
vAtapittakaphAd raktaM tvaDamAMsaM snAyumasthi ca . majjAM dehaM zirAjAlaistarpayanti rasA nRNAm .
daza vidyAd dhamanyo ' tra paJcendriyaguNAvahAH . yAbhiH sUkSmAH pratAyante dhamanyo ' nyAH sahasrazaH .
evametAH zirA nadyo rasodA dehasAgaram . tarpayanti yathAkAlamApagA iva sAgaram .
madhye ca hRdayasyaikA zirA tatra manovahA . zukra saMkalpajaM nRNAM sarvagAtrairvimuJcati .
sarvagAtrapratAyinyastasyA hyanugatAH zirAH . netrayoH pratipadyante vahantyastaijasaM guNam .
payasyantarhitaM sarpiryadvannirmathyate khajaiH . zukra nirmathyate tadvad dehasaMkalpajaiH khajaiH .
svapne ' pyevaM yathAbhyeti mana : saMkalpajaM rajaH . zukra saMkalpajaM dehAt sRjatyasya manovahA .
maharSirbhagavAnatrirveda tacchukrasambhavam . tribIjamindradaivalyaM tasmAdindriyamucyate .
ye vai zukragati vidyubhUtasaMkarakArikAm . virAgA dagdhadoSAste nApnuyurdehasambhavam .
guNAnAM sAmyamAgamya manasaiva manovaham . dehakarmA nudan prANAnantakAle vimucyate .
bhavitA manaso jJAnaM mana eva prajAyate . jyotiSmadvirajo nityaM mantrasiddhaM mahAtmanAm .
tasmAt tadabhighAtAya karma kuryAdakalmaSam . rajastamazca hitveha yatheSTAM gatimApnuyAt .
taruNAdhigataM jJAnaM jarAdurbalatAM gatam . vipakvabuddhiH kAlena Adatte mAnasaM balam .
sudurgamiva panthAnamatItya guNabandhanam . yathA pazyet tathA doSAnatItyAmRtamaznute .
yudhiSThira uvAca janma mAnuSyakaM prApya karmakSetraM sudurlabham . zreyo ' rthinA daridreNa kiM kartavyaM pitAmaha .
dAnAnAmuttamaM yacca deyaM yacca yathA yathA . mAnyAn pUjyAMzca gAGgeya rahasyaM vaktumarhasi .
vaizampAyana uvAca evaM pRSTo narendreNa pANDavena yazasvinA . dharmANAM paramaM guhyaM bhISmaH provAca pArthivam .
bhISma uvAca zRNuSvAvahito rAjan dharmaguhyAni bhArata . yathA hi bhagavAn vyAsaH purA kathitavAn mayi .
devaguhyamidaM rAjan yamenAkliSTakarmaNA . niyamasthena yuktena tapaso mahataH phalam .
yena yaH prIyate devaH prIyante pitarastathA . RSayaH pramathA : zrIzca citragupto dizAM gajAH . RSidharmaH smRto yatra sarahasyo mahAphalaH . mahAdAnaphalaM caiva sarvayajJaphalaM tathA . yazcaitadevaM jAnIyAjjJAtvA vA kurute ' nagha . sadoSo ' doSavAMzceha tairguNaiH saha yujyate .
dazasUnAsamaM cakraM dazacakrasamo dhvajaH . dazadhvajasamA vezyA dazavezyAsamo nRpaH .
ardhenaitAni sarvANi nRpatiH kathyate ' dhikaH . trivargasahitaM zAstraM pavitraM puNyalakSaNam . dharmavyAkaraNaM puNyaM rahasyazravaNaM mahat . zrotavyaM dharmasaMyuktaM vihitaM tridazaiH svayam .
pitRRNAM yatra guhyAni procyante zrAddhakarmaNi . devatAnAM ca sarveSAM rahasyaM kathyate ' khilam .
RSidharmaH smRto yatra sarahasyo mahAphalaH . mahAyajJaphalaM caiva sarvadAnaphalaM tathA .
ye paThanti sadA mA yeSAM caivopatiSThati . zrutvA ca phalamAcaSTe svayaM nArAyaNaH prabhuH .
gavAM phalaM tIrthaphalaM yajJAnAM caiva yat phalam . etat phalamavApnoti yo naro ' tithipUjakaH .
zrotAraH zraddadhAnAzca yeSAM zuddha ca mAnasam . teSAM vyakta jitA lokAH zraddadhanena sAdhunA . mucyate kilbiSAccaica na sA pApena lipyate . dharme ca labhate nityaM pretya lokagato naraH .
kasyacit tvatha kAlasya devadUto yadRcchayA . sthito hyantarhito bhUtvA paryabhASata vAsavam .
yau tau kAmaguNopetAvazvinau bhiSajAM varau . AjJayAhaM tayoH prAptaH sanarAn pitRdaivatAn .
kasmAddhi maithunaM zrAddhe dAturbhoktuzca varjitam . kimarthaM ca trayaH piNDAH pravibhaktAH pRthak pRthak . .
prathamaH kasya dAtavyo madhyamaH kva ca gacchati . uttarazca smRtaH kasya etadicchAgi veditum .
zraddadhanena dUtena bhASitaM dharmasaMhitam . pUrvasthAstridazAH sarve pitaraH pUjya khecaram .
pitara UcuH svAgataM te ' stu bhadraM te zrUyatAM khecarottama . gUDhArthaH paramaH prazno bhavatA samudIritaH .
zrAddhaM dattvA ca bhuktvA ca puruSo yaHstriyaM vrajet . pitarastasya taM mAsaM tasmin retasi zerate . .
pravibhAgaM tu piNDAnAM pravakSyAmyanupUrvazaH . piNDo hyadhastAd gacchaMstu apa Avizya bhAvayet . .
piNDaM tu madhyamaM tatra patnI tvekA samaznute . piNDastRtIyo yasteSAM taM dadyAjjAtavedasi .
eSa zrAddhavidhiH prokto yathA dharmo na lupyate . pitarastasya tuSyanti prahRSTamanasaH sadA . prajA vivardhate cAsya akSayaM copatiSThati .
devadUta uvAca AnupUrveNa piNDAnAM pravibhAgaH pRthak pRthak . pitRRNAM triSu sarveSAM niruktaM kathitaM tvayA .
eka : samuddhRtaH piNDo hyadhastAt kasya gacchati . kaM vA prINayate devaM kathaM tArayate pitRRna .
madhyamaM tu tadA patnI bhuGkte ' nujJAtameva hi . kimarthaM pitarastasya kavyameva ca bhuJjate .
atra yastvantimaH piNDo gacchate jAtavedasam . bhavate kA gatistasya kaM vA samanugacchati .
etadicchAmyahaM zrotuM piNDeSu triSu za gatiH . phalaM vRttiM ca mArgaM ca yazcainaM pratipadyate .
pitaraH UcuH sumahAneSa prazno vai yastvayA samudIritaH . rahasyamadbhutaM cApi pRSTAH sma gaganecara .
etadeva prazasaMnti devAzca munayastathA . te ' pyevaM nAbhijAnanti pitRkAryavinizcayam .
varjayitvA mahAtmAnaM cirajIvinamuttamam . pitRbhaktastu yo vipro varalabdho mahAyazAH .
trayANAmapi piNDAnAM zrutvA bhagavato gatim . devadUtena yaH pRSTaH zrAddhasya vidhinizcayaH .
gatiM trayANAM piNDAnAM zRNuSvAvahito mama . apo gacchati yo hyatra zazinaM hyeSa prINayet .
zazI prINayate devAn pitazcaiva mahAmate . bhuGkte tu patnI yaM caiSAmanujJAtA tu madhyamam .
putrakAmAya putraM tu prayacchanti pitAmahAH . piNDo dIyate tannibodha me .
pitarastena tRSyanti prItAH kAmAn dizanti ca . etat te kathitaM sarve triSu piNDeSu yA gatiH .
Rtvigyo yajamAnasya pitRtvamanugacchati . havyavAhe tu yaH tasminnahani manyante parihArye hi maithunam .
zucinA tu sadA zrAddhaM bhoktavya khecarottama . ye mayA kathitA doSAste tathA syurna cAnyathA .
tasmAt snAtaH zuciH kSAntaH zrAddhaMbhuJjIta vai dvijaH . . prajA vivardhate cAsya yazcaivaM samprayacchati .
bhISma uvAca tato vidyutprabho nAma RSirAha mahAtapAH . AdityatejasA tasya tulyaM rUpaM prakAzate . sa ca dharmarahasyAni zrutvA zakramathAbravIt .
tiryagyonigatAn sattvAn mA hiMsanti mohitAH . kITAn pipIlikAn sarpAn meSAn samRgapakSiNaH . . kilbiSaM subahu prAptAH kiMsvideSAM pratikriyA . tato devagaNAH sarve RSayazca tapodhanAH .
pitarazca mahAbhAgAH pUjayanti sma taM munim .
zakra uvAca kurukSetraM gayAM gaGgAM prabhAsaM puSkarANi ca . etAni manasA dhyAtvA avagAhet tato jalam . tathA mucyati pApena rAhuNA candramA yathA .
tryahaM snAtaMH sa bhavati nirAhArazca vartate . spRzate yo gavAM pRSThaM bAladhiM ca namasyati .
tato vidyutprabho vAkyamabhyabhASata vAsavam . ayaM sUkSmataro dharmastaM nibodha zatakrato .
ghRSTo vaTakaSAyeNa anuliptaH priyaMguNA . kSIreNa SaSTikAn bhuktvA sarvapApaiH pramucyate .
zrUyatAM cAparaM gRhyaM rahasyamRSicintitam . zrutaM me bhASamANasya sthANoH sthAne bRhaspateH .
rudreNa saha deveza tannibodha zacIpate . parvatArohaNaM kRtvA ekapAdo vibhAvasum . nirIkSeta nirAhAra urdhvabAhuH kRtAJjaliH . tapasA mahatA yukta upavAsaphalaM labhet .
razmibhistApito ' rkasya sarvapApamapohati . grISmakAle ' tha vA zIte evaM pApamapohati .
tataH pApat pramuktasya dyutirbhavati zAzvatI . tejasA sUryavad dIpto bhrAjate somavat punaH .
madhye tridazavargasya devarAjaH zatakratuH . uvAca madhuraM vAkyaM bRhaspatimanuttamam .
dharmaguhyaM tu bhagavan mAnuSANAM sukhAvaham . sarahasyAzca ye doSAstAn yathAvadudIraya .
bRhaspati ruvAca pratimehanti ye sUryamanilaM dviSate ca ye . havyavAhe pradIpte ca samidhaM ye na juhvati . bAlavatsAM ca ye dhenuM duhanti kSIrakAraNAt . teSAM doSAn pravakSyAmi tAn nibodha zacIpate .
bhAnumAnanilazcaiva havyavAhazca vAsava . lokAnAM mAtarazcaiva gAvaH sRSTAH svayambhuvA . lokAMstArayituM zaktA matryeSveteSu devatAH . sarve bhavantaH zRNvantu ekaikaM dharmanizcayam .
varSANi SaDazIti tu durvattAH kulapAMsanAH . striyaH sarvAzca durvRttA : pratimehanti yA ravim .
aniladveSiNaH zakra garbhasthA cyavate prajA . havyavAhasya dIptasya samidhaM ye na juhvati . .
agnikAryeSu vai teSAM havyaM nAznAti pAvakaH . kSIraM tu bAlavatsAnAM ye pibantIha mAnavAH .
na teSAM kSIrapAH kecijjAyante kulavardhanAH . prajAkSayeNa yujyante kulavaMzakSayeNa ca .
evametat purA dRSTaM kulavRddhaurdvijAtibhiH . tasmAd vAni vAni kAryaM kAryaM ca nityazaH . .
bhUtikAmena ma]na satyametad bravImi te . tataH sarvA mahAbhAga devatAH samarudgaNAH . RSayazca mahAbhAgAH pRcchanti sma pitUMstataH . pitaraH kena tuSyanti martyAnAmalpacetasAm . akSayaM ca kathaM dAnaM bhaveccaivordhvadehikam .
AnRNyaM vA kathaM mA gaccheyuH kena karmaNA . etadicchAmahe zrotuM paraM kautUhalaM hi naH .
pitara UcuH nyAyato vai mahAbhAgAH saMzayaH samudAhRtaH . zrUyatAM yena tuSyAmo mAnAM sAdhukarmaNAm .
nIlapaNDapramokSeNa amAvAsyAM tilodakaiH : . varSAsu dIpakaizcaiva pitRRNAmanRNo bhavet .
akSayaM niLalIkaM ca dAnametanmahAphalam . asmAkaM paritoSazca akSayaH parikIrtyate .
zraddadhAnAzca ye martyA AhariSyanti saMtatim . durgAt te tArayiSyanti narakAt prapitAmahAn .
pitRRNAM bhASitaM zrutvA hRSTaromA tapodhanaH . vRddhagAryo mahAtejAstAnevaM vAkyamabravIt . ke guNA nIlapaNDasya pramuktasya tapodhanAH . varSAsu dIpadAnena tathaiva ca tilodakaiH .
pitara UcuH nIlaSaNDasya lAGgulaM toyamabhyuddhared yadi . SaSTiM varSasahasrANi pitarastena tarpitA : .
yastu zRGgagataM padaM kUlAdUddhRtya tiSThati . . pitarastena gacchanti somalokamasaMzayam .
varSAsu dIpadAnena zazivacchobhate naraH . tamorUpaM na tasyAsti dIpakaM yaH prayacchati .
amAvAsyAM tu ye mAH prayacchanti tilodakam . pAtramaudumbaraM gRhya madhumizraM tapodhana . kRtaM bhavati taiH zrAddhaM sarahasyaM yathArthavat . hRSTapuSTamanAsteSAM prajA bhavati nityadA .
kulavaMzasya vRddhistu piNDadasya phalaM bhavet . zraddadhAnastu yaH kuryAt pitRRNAmanRNo bhavet .
evameva samudviSTaH zrAddhakAlakramastathA . vidhiH pAtraM phalaM caiva yathAvadanukIrtimam .
vaizampAyana uvAca sa tu vAjI samudrAntAM paryetya vasudhAmimAm . nivRtto ' bhimukho rAjan yena vAraNasAhvayam .
anugacchaMzca turagaM nivRtto ' tha kirITabhRt . yadRcchayA samApede puraM rAjagRhaM tadA .
tamabhyAzagataM dRSTvA sahadevAtmajaH prabho . kSatradharme sthito vIraH samarAyAjuhAva ha .
tataH purAt saniSkramya rathI dhanvI zarI talI . meghasandhiH padAti taM dhanaMjayamupAdravat .
AsAdya ca mahAtejA meghasandhirdhanaMjayam . bAlabhAvAnmahArAja provAcedaM na kauzalAt .
kimayaM cAryate bAjI strImadhya iva bhArata . hyamenaM hariSyAmi prayatasva vimokSaNe .
adattAnunayo yuddhe yadi tvaM pitRbhirmama . kariSyAmi tavAtithyaM prahara praharAmi ca .
ityuktaH pratyuvAcainaM prahasanniva pANDavaH . vinakartA mayA vArya iti me vratamAhitam . bhrAtrA jyeSThena nRpate tavApi viditaM dhruvam . praharasva yathAzakti na manyurvidyate mama .
ityuktaH prAharat pUrve pANDavaM magadhezvaraH . kiran zarasahasrANi varSANIva sahasradRk .
tato gANDIvabhRcchUro gANDIvaprahitaiH zaraiH . cakAra moghAMstAn bANAn sayalAn bharatarSabha .
sa moghaM tasya bANaudhaM kRtvA vAnaraketanaH . zarAn mumoca jvalitAn dIptAsyAniva pannagAn .12
dhvaje patAkAdaNDeSu rathe yantre hayeSu ca . anyeSu ca rathAGgeSu na zarIre na sArathau .
saMrakSyamANaH pArthena zarIre savyasAcinA . manyamAnaH svavIryaM tanmAgadhaH prAhiNoccharAn .
tato gANDIvadhanvA tu mAgadhena bhRzAhataH . babhau vasantasamaye palAzaH puSpito yathA .
avadhyamAnaH so ' bhayananmAgadhaH pANDavarSabham . tena tasthau ya kauravya lokavIrasya darzane .
savyasAcI tu saMkruddho vikRSya balavad dhanuH . hayAMzcakAra nirjIvAn sArathezca ziro ' harat .
dhanuzcAsya mahaccitraM kSureNa pracakarta ha . hastAvApaM patAkAM ca dhvajaM cAsya nyapAtayat .
sa rAjA vyathito vyazvo vidhanurhatasArathiH . gadAmAdAya kaunteyamabhidudrAva vegavAn .
tasyApatata evAzu gadAM hemapariSkRtAm . zaraizcakarta bahudhA bahubhirgRdhravAjitaiH .
sA gadA zakalIbhUtA vizIrNamaNibandhanA . vyAlI vimucyamAneva papAta dharaNItale .
virathaM vidhanuSkaM ca gadayA parivarjitam . sAntvapUrvamidaM vAkyamabravIt kapiketanaH . paryAptaH kSatradharmo ' yaM darzitaH putra gamyatAm . bahvetat samare karma tava bAlasya pArthiva .
yudhiSThirasya saMdezo na hantavyA nRpA iti . tena jIvasi rAjaMstvamaparAddho ' pi me raNe . .
iti matvA tadAtmAnaM pratyAdiSTaM sma mAgadhaH . tathyamityabhigamyainaM prAJjaliH pratyapUjayat .
parAjito ' smi bhadraM te nAhaM yodhumihAtsahe . yad yat kRtyaM mayA te ' dya tad brUhi kRtameva tu .
tamarjUnaH samAzvAsya punarevedamabravIt . AgantavyaM parAM caitrImazvamedhe nRpasya naH .
ityuktaH sa tathetyuktvA pUjayAmAsa taM hayam . phAlgunaM ca yudhi zreSThaM vidhivat sahadevajaH .
tato yatheSTamagamat punareva sa kesarI . tataH samudratIreNa vaGgAn puNDrAn sakosalAn .
tatra tatra ca bhUrINi mlecchasainyAnyanekazaH . vijigye dhanuSA rAjan gANDIvena dhanaMjayaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca keSAM prabhavate rAjA vittasya bharatarSabha . kayA ca vRttyA varteta tanme brUhi pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca abrAhmaNAnAM vittasya svAmI rAjeti vaidikam . brAhmaNAnAM ca ye kecid vikarmasthA bhavantyuta .
vikarmasthAzca nopekSyA viprA rAjJA kathaJcana . iti rAjJAM purAvRttamAbhijalpanti sAdhavaH .
yasya sma viSaye rAjJaH steno bhavati vai dvijaH . rAjJa evAparAdhaM taM manyante kilbiSaM nRpa .
abhizastamivAtmAnaM manyante yena karmaNA . tasmAd rAjarSayaH sarve brAhmaNAnanvapAlayan .
atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . gItaM kaikeyarAjena hriyamANena rakSasA .
kekayAnAmadhipatiM rakSo jagrAha dAruNam . svAdhyAyenAnvitaM rAjannaraNye saMzitavratam .
rAjovAca na me steno janapade na kadaryo na madyapaH . nAnAhitAgni yajvA mAmakAntaramAyizaH .
na ca me brAhmaNo ' vidvAnnAvratI nApyasomapaH . nAnAhitAgnita yajvA mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
nAnApradakSiNairyajJairyajante viSaye mama . nAdhIte nAvratI kazcinmAmakAntaramAvizaH .
adhIyate ' dhyApayanti yajante yAjayanti ca . dadati pratigRhNanti SaTsu karmasvavasthitAH .
pUjitAH saMvibhaktAzca mRdavaH satyavAdinaH . brAhmaNA me svakarmasthA mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
na yAcante prayacchanti satyadharmavizAradAH . nAdhyApayantyadhIyate yajante yAjayanti na . brAhmaNAn parirakSanti saMgrAmeSvapalAyinaH . kSatriyA me svakarmasthA mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
kRSigorakSavANijyamupajIvantyamAyayA . apramattAH kriyAvantaH suvratAH satyavAdinaH .
saMvibhAgaM damaM zaucaM sauhadaM ca vyapAzritAH . mama vaizyAH svakarmasthA mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
trIn varNAnupajIvanti yathAvadanasUyakAH . mama zUdrAH svakarmasthA mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
kRpaNAnAthavRddhAnAM durbalAturayoSitAm . saMvibhaktAsmi sarveSAM mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
kuladezAdidharmANAM prathitAnAM yathAvidhi . avyucchettAsmi sarveSAM mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
tapasvino me viSaye pUjitA : paripAlitAH . saMvibhaktAzca satkRtya mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
nAsaM vibhajya bhoktAsmi nAvizAmi parastriyam . svatantra jAtu na krIDe mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
nAbrahmacArI bhikSAvAmbhikSurvA ' brahmacaryavAn anRtvijA hutaM nAsti mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
nAvajAnAmyahaM vaidyAnna vRddhAnna tapasvinaH . rASTre svapati jAgarmi mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
AtmavijJAnasampannastapasvI sarvadharmavit . svAmI sarvasya rASTrasya dhImAn mama purohitaH .
dAnena vidyAmabhivAJchayAmi satyenArthaM brAhmaNAnAM ca guptyA . zuzrUSayA cApi gurUnupaimi na me bhayaM vidyate rAkSasebhyaH .
na me rASTre vidhavA brahmabardU brAhmaNaH kitavo nota coraH . ayAjyayAjI na ca pApakarmA na meM bhayaM vidyate rAkSasebhyaH .
na me zastrairanirbhinnaM gAtre vyaGgaddhalamantaram . dharmArthaM yudhyamAnasya mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
gobrAhmaNebhyo yajJebhyo nityaM svastyayanaM mama . AzAsate janA rASTre mAmakAntaramAvizaH .
rAkSasa uvAca yasmAt sarvAsvavasthAsu dharmamevAnvavekSase . tasmAt prApnuhi kaikeya gRhaM svasti vrajAmyaham .
yeSAM gobrAhmaNaM rakSyaM prajA rakSyAzca kekaya . na rakSobhyo bhayaM teSAM kuta eva tu pAvakAt .
yeSAM purogamA viprA yeSAM brahma paraM balam . atithipriyAstathA paurAste vai svargajito nRpAH .
bhISma uvAca tasmAd dvijAtIn rakSeta te hi rakSanti rakSitAH . AzIreSAM bhaved rAjan rAjJAM samyakpravartatAm .
tasmAd rAjJA vizeSeNa vikarmasthA dvijAtayaH . niyamyAH saMvibhajyAzca tadanugrahakAraNAt .
evaM yo vartate rAjA paurajAnapadeSviha . anubhUyeha bhadrANi prApnotIndrasalokatAm .
bhISma uvAca sa vanAni vicitrANi tIrthAni ca sarAMsi ca . abhigacchan krameNa sama kaMcinmunimupasthitaH .
taM sa tena yathoddiSTaM nAgaM vipreNa brAhmaNaH . paryapRcchad yathAnyAyaM zrutvaiva ca jagAma saH .
so ' bhigamya yathAnyAyaM nAgAyatanamarthavit . proktavAhamasmIti bhoHzabdAlaMkRtaM vacaH .
tat tasya vacanaM zrutvA rUpiNI dharmavatsalA . darzayAmAsa taM vipraM nAgapatnI pativratA .
sA tasmai vidhivat pUjAM cakre dharmaparAyaNA . svAgatenAgataM kRtvA kiM karomIti cAbravIt .
brAhmaNa uvAca vizrAnto ' bhyarcitazcAsmi bhavatyA zlakSNayA girA . draSTumicchAmi bhavati devaM nAgamanuttamam .
etaddhi paraM kAryametAnme paramepsitam . anena cArthenAmyadya samprApta : pannAgAzramam .
nAgabhAryovAca AryaH sUryarathaM voDhuM gato ' sau mAsacArikaH . saptASTabhirdinaivipra darzayiSyatyasaMzayam .
etadviditamAryasya vivAsakaraNaM tava . bharturbhavatu kiM cAnyat kriyatAM tad vadasva me .
brAhmaNa uvAca anena nizcayenAhaM sAdhvi samprAptavAniha . pratIkSannAgamaM devi vatsyApyasmin mahAvane .
samprAptasyaiva cAvyagramAvedyo ' hamihAgataH . mamAbhigamanaM prApto vAcyazca vacanaM tvayA .
