krUraH kauravya mRdave mRduH krUre ca kaurava . sAdhuzcAsAdhave sAdhuH sAdhave nApnuyAt katham .
kRtaM zataguNaM kuryAnnAsti deveSu nirNayaH . auzInaraH sAdhuzIlo bhavato vai mahIpatiH .
jayet kadaryaM dAnena satyenAnRtavAdinam . kSamayA krUrakarmANa - masAdhu sAdhunA jayet .
tadubhAveva bhavantAvudArau ya idAnIM bhavadbhyAmanyatamaH so ' pasarpatu etad vai nidarzanamityuktvA tUSNIM nArado babhUva . etacchrutvA tu kauravyaH zibiM pradakSiNaM kRtvA dattvA panthAnaM bahukarmabhiH prazasya prayayau .
