yudhiSThira uvAca bhagavan zrotumicchAmi nAmAnyasya mahAtmanaH . triSu lokeSu yAnyasya vikhyAtAni dvijottama .
vaizampAyana uvAca ityuktaH pANDaveyena mahAtmA RSisaMnidhau . uvAca bhagavAMstatra mArkaNDeyo mahAtapAH .
mArkaNDeya uvAca Agneyazcaiva skandazca dIptakIrtiranAmayaH . mayUraketurdharmAtmA bhUtezo mahiSArdanaH . kAmajit kAmadaH kAntaH satyavAg bhuvenazvaraH . zizuH zIghraH zucizcaNDo dIptavarNaH zubhAnanaH . amoghastvanadho raudraH priyazcandrAnanastathA . dIptazaktiH prazAntAtmA bhadrakRt kUTamohanaH . SaSThIpriyazca dharmAtmA pavitro mAtRvatsalaH . kanyAbhartA vibhaktazca svAheyo revatIsutaH . prabhurnetA vizAkhazca naigameyaH suduzcaraH . suvrato lalitazcaiva bAlakrIDanakapriyaH . khacArI brahmacArI ca zUraH zaravaNodbhavaH . vizvAmitrapriyazcaiva devasenApriyastathA . . vAsudevapriyazcaiva priya : priyakRdeva tu . nAmAnyetAni divyAni kArtikeyasya yaH paThet . svarga kIrtiM dhanaM caiva sa labhennAtra saMzayaH .
stoSyAmi devairRSibhizca juSTaM zaktyA guhaM nAmabhiraprameyam . SaDAnanaM zaktidharaM suvIraM nibodha caitAni kurupravI .
brahmaNyo vai brahmajo brahmavicca brahmezayo brahmavatAM variSThaH . brahmapriyo brAhmaNasavratI tvaM brahmajJo vai brAhmaNAnAM ca netA .
svAhA svadhA tvaM paramaM pavitraM mantrastutastvaM prathitaH SaDarciH . saMvatsarastvamRtavazca ghaD vai mAsArdhamAsAvayanaM dizazca .
tvaM puSkarAkSastvaravindavaktraH sahasravaktro ' si sahasrabAhuH . tvaM lokapAlaH paramaM havizva tvaM bhAvanaH sarvasurAsurANAm .
tvameva senAdhipatiH pracaNDaH prabhurvibhuzcApyatha zatrujetA . sahasrabhUstvaM dharaNI tvameva sahasratuSTizca sahasrabhuk ca .
sahasrazIrSastvamanantarUpaH sahasrapAt tvaM guha zaktidhArI . gaGgAsutastvaM svamatena deva svAhAmahIkRttikAnAM tathaiva .
tvaM krIDase SaNmukha kukkuTena yatheSTanAnAvidhakAmarUpI . dIkSAsi somo marutaH sadaiva dharmo ' si vAyuracalendra indraH .
sanAtanAnAmapi zAzvatastvaM prabhuH prabhUNAmapi cocadhanvA . Rtasya kartA ditijAntakastvaM jetA ripUNAM pravaraH surANAm .
sUkSmaM tapastat paramaM tvameva parAvarajJo ' si parAvarastvam . dharmasya kAmasya parasya caiva tvattejasA kRtstramidaM mahAtman .
vyAptaM jagat sarvasurapravIra zaktyA mayA saMstuta lokanAtha . namo ' stu te dvAdazanetrabAho ataH paraM vedmi gatiM na te ' ham .
skandasya ya idaM vipraH paThejjanma samAhitaH . zrAvayed brAhmaNebhyo yaH zRNuyAd vA dvijeritam . dhanamAyuryazo dIptaM putrAJchatrujayaM tathA . sa puSTituSTI samprApya skandasAlomyamApnuyAt .
vaizampAyana uvAca bhojAH pravrajitAJchrutvA vRSNayazcAndhakaiH saha . pANDavAn duHkhasaMtaptAn samAjagmurmahAvane .
pAJcAlasya ca dAyAdodhRSTaketuzca cedipaH . kekayAzca mahAvIryA bhrAtaro lokavizrutAH . vane draSTuM yayuH pArthAn krodhAmarSasamanvitAH . garhayantodhArtarASTrAn kiM kurma iti cAbruvan .
vAsudevaM puraskRtya sarve te kSatriyarSabhAH . parivAryopavivizurdharmarAja yudhiSThiram . . abhivAdya kuruzreSThaM viSaNNaH kezavo ' bravIt .
vAsudeva uvAca duryodhanasya karNasya zakunezca durAtmanaH . duHzAsanacaturthAnAM bhUmiH pAsyati zoNitam .
etAn nihatya samare ye ca tasya padAnugAH . tAMzca sarvAn vinirjitya sahitAn sanarAdhipAn . tataH sarve ' bhiSiJcAmodharmarAja yudhiSThiram . nikRtyopacaran vadhya eSadharmaH sanAtanaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca pArthAnAmabhiSaGgeNa tathA kruddhaM janArdanam . arjunaH zamayAmAsa didhakSantamiva prajAH . saMkruddhaM kezavaM dRSTvA pUrvadeheSu phAlgunaH . kIrtayAmAsa karmANi satyakIrtermahAtmanaH . puruSasyAprameyasya satyasyAmitatejasaH . prajApatipateviSNorlokanAthasyadhImataH .
arjuna uvAca daza varSasahasrANi yatrasAyaMgRho muniH . vyacarastvaM purA kRSNa parvate gandhamAdane .
daza varSasahasrANi daza varSazatAni ca . puSkareSvavasaH kRSNa tvamapo bhakSayan purA .
UrdhvabAhurvizAlAyAM badaryAM madhusUdana . atiSTha ekapAdena vAyubhakSaH zataM samAH .
avakRSTottarAsaGgaH kRzodhamanisaMtataH . AsIH kRSNa sarasvatyAM satre dvAdazavArSike .
prabhAsamapyathAsAdya tIrthaM puNyajanocitam . tathA kRSNa mahAtejA divyaM varSasahasrakam . atiSThastvamathaikena pAdena niyamasthitaH . lokapravRttihetustvamiti vyAso mamAbravIt .
kSetrajJaH sarvabhUtAnAmAdirantazca kezava . nidhAnaM tapasAM kRSNA yajJastvaM ca sanAtanaH .
nihatya narakaM bhaumamAhatya maNikuNDale . prathamotpatitaM kRSNA medhyamazvamavAsRjaH .
kRtvA tat karma lokAnAmRSabhaH sarvalokajit . avadhIstvaM raNe sarvAn sametAn daityadAnavAn .
tataH sarvezvaratvaM ca sampradAya zacIpateH . mAnuSeSu mahAbAho prAdurbhUto ' si kezava .
sa tvaM nArAyaNo bhUtvA harirAsIH paraMtapa . brahmA somazca sUryazcadharmodhAtA yamo ' nalaH . vAyurvaizravaNo rudraH kAlaH khaM pRthivI dizaH . ajazcarAcaraguruH sraSTA tvaM puruSottama .
