yaH kRzArthaH kRzagavaH kRzabhRtyaH kRzAtithiH . savai rAjan kRzo nAma na zarIrakRzaH kRzaH .
avekSasva yathAnyAyaM pazya devAsuraM yathA . rAjan kimanyajjAtInAM vadhAd gRddhyanti devatAH .
na ceddhartavyamanyasya kathaM taddharmamArabhet . etAvAneva vedeSu nizcayaH kavibhiH kRtaH .
adhyetavyA trayI nityaM bhavitavyaM vipazcitA . sarvathA dhanamAhAryaM yaSTavyaM cApi yatnataH .
drohAd devairavAptAni divi sthAnAni sarvazaH . drohAt kimanyajjJAtInAM gRddhyante yena devatAH .
iti devA vyavasitA vedavAdAzca zAzvatAH . adhIyate ' dhyApayante yajante yAjayanti ca . kRtsnaM tadeva taccherUyo yadapyAdadate ' nyataH . na pazyAmo ' napakRtaM dhanaM kiMcit kvacid vayam .
evameva hi rAjAno jayanti pRthivImimAm . jitvA mameyaM bruvate putrA iva piturdhanam .
rAjarSayo ' pi te svaryo dharmo hyeSAM nirucyate . yathaiva pUrNAdudadheH syandantyApo dizo daza .
evaM rAjakulAd vittaM pRthivIM prati tiSThati . AsIdiyaM dilIpasya nRgasya nahuSasya ca . .
ambarISasya mAndhAtuH pRthivI sA tvayi sthitA . sa tvAM dravyamayo yajJaH samprAptaH sarvadakSiNaH .
taM cenna yajase rAjan prAptastvaM rAjyakilbiSam . yeSAM rAjA ' zvamedhena yajate dakSiNAvatA .
upetya tasyAvabhRthe pUtAH sarve bhavanti te . vizvarUpo mahAdevaH sarvamedhe mahAmakhe . juhAva sarvabhUtAni tathaivAtmAnamAtmanA .
zAzvato ' yaM bhUtipatho nAsyAntamanuzuzruma . mahAn dAzarathaH panthA mA rAjan kupathaM gamaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca indraprasthe vasantaste jaghnuranyAn narAdhipAn . zAsanAd dhRrASTrasya rAjJaH zAntanavasya ca .
Azritya dharmarAjAnaM sarvaloko ' vasat sukham . puNyalakSaNakarmANaM svadehamiva dehinaH .
sa samaM dharmakAmArthAn siSeve bharatarSabha . trInivAtmasamAn bandhUna nItimAniva mAnayan .
teSAM samavibhaktAnAM kSitau dehavatAmiva . babhau dharmArthakAmAnAM caturtha iva pArthivaH .
adhyetAraM paraM vedAn prayoktAraM mahAdhvare . rakSitAraM zubhA~llokAn lebhire taM janAdhipam .
adhiSThAnavatI lakSmIH parAyaNavatI matiH . vardhamAno ' khilo dharmastenAsIt pRthivIkSitAm .
bhrAtRbhiH sahito rAjA caturbhirAdhikaM babhau . prayujyamAnairvitato vedairiva mahAdhvaraH .
taM tu dhaumyAdayo viprAH parivAryopatasthire . bRhaspatIsamA mukhyAH prajApatimivAmarAH .
dharmarAje hyatiprItyA pUrNacandra ivAmale . prajAnAM remire tulyaM netrANi hRdayAni ca .
na ta kevaladaivena prajA bhAvena remire . yad babhUva mana : kAntaM karmaNA sa cakAra tat .
na hyayuktaM na cAsatyaM nAsahyaM na ca vApriyam . bhASitaM cArubhASasya jajJe pArthasya dhImataH .
sa hi sarvasya lokasya hitamAtmana eva ca . cikIrSan sumahAtejA reme bharatasattama . .
tathA tu muditAH sarve pANDavA vigatajvarAH . avasan pRthivIpAlAMstApayantaH svatejasA .
tataH katipayAhasya bIbhatsuH kRSNamabravIt . uSNAni kRSNa vartantaM gacchAvo yamunAM prati .
suhRjjanavRtau tatra vihRtya madhusUdana . sAyAhne punareSyAvo rocatAM te janArdanA .
vAsudeva uvAca kuntImAtarmamApyetad rocate yad vayaM jale . suhaja ranavRtaH pArtha viharema yathAsukham .
vaizaMpAyana uvAca Amantrya tau dharmarAjamanujJASya ca bhArata . jagmatuH pArthagovindau suhRjjanavRtau tataH .
vihAradezaM samprApya nAnAdrumamanuttamam . gRhairuccAvacaiyuktaM purandarapuropamam . bhakSyairbhojyaizca peyaizca rasavadbhirmahAdhanaiH . mAlyaizca vividhairgadhairyuktaM vArSNeyapArthayoH . vivezAntaHpuraM tUrNaM ratnairuccAvacaiH zubhaiH . yathopajoSaM sarvazca janazcinIDa bhArata .
striyazca vipulazroNyazcArupInapayodharAH . madaskhalitagAminyazcikrIDurvAmalocanAH .
vane kAzcijjale kAzcit kAzcid vezmanu cAGganAH . yathAyogyaM yathAprIti cikrIDuH pArthakRSNayoH .
draupadI ca subhadrA ca vAsAMsyAbharaNAni ca . prAyacchatAM mahArAja te tu tasmin madotkaTe .
kAzcit prahRSTA nanRtuzcakruzuzca tathAparAH . jaguzcAnyA varastriyaH .
rurudhuzcAparAstatra prajaghnuzca parasparam . mantrayAmAsuranyAzca rahasyAni parasparam .
jahasuzca parA nAryo veNuvINAmRdaGgAnAM manojJAnAM ca sarvazaH . zabdena pUryate hah tad vanaM sumaharddhimat .
tasmiMstadA vartamAne kurudAzArhanandanau . samIpaM jagmatuH kaMciduddezaM sumanoharam .
tatra gatvA mahAtmAnau kRSNau parapuraMjayau . mahArhAsanayo rAjaMstatastau saMniSIdatuH .
tatra pUrvavyatItAni vikrAntAnItarANi ca . bahUni kathayitvA tau remAte pArthamAdhavau .
tatropaviSTau muditau nAkapRSThe ' zvinAviva . abhyAgacchat tadA vipro vAsudevadhanaMjayau .
bRhacchAlapratIkAzaH prataptakanakaprabhaH . haripiGgojjavalazmazruH pramANAyAmataH samaH .
taruNAdityasaMkAzazcIravAsA jaTAdharaH . padmapatrAnanaH piGgastejasA prajvalanniva .
upasRSTaM tu taM kRSNau bhrAjamAnaM dvijottamam . arjuno vAsudevazca tUrNamutpatya tasthatuH .
vaizampAyana uvAca prayAntaM devakIputraM paravIrarujo daza . mahArathA mahAbAhumanvayuH zastrapANayaH .
padAtInAM sahasraM ca sAdinAM ca paraMtapa . bhojyaM ca vipulaM rAjan preSyAca zatazo ' pare .
janamejaya uvAca kathaM prayAto dAzArho mahAtmA madhusUdanaH . kAni vA vrajatastasya nimittAni mahaujasaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tasya prayANe yAnyAsan nimittAni mahAtmanaH . tAni me zRNu sarvANi daivAnyautyAtikAni ca .
anabhre ' zaninirghoSaH savidyut samajAyata . anvageva ca parjanyaH prAvarSad vighane bhRzam .
pratyagUhurmahAnadyaH prAGmukhAH sindhusaptamAH . viparItA diza : sarvA na prAjJAyata kiMcana .
prAjvalannagnayo rAjan pRthivI samakampata . udapAnAzca kumbhAzca prAsiJcaJchatazo jalam .
tamaH saMvRtamapyAsIt sarvaM jagadidaM tathA . na dizo nAdizo rAjan prajJAyante sma reNunA .
prAdurAsInmahAJchabdaH khe zarIraMdRzayate . sarveSu rAjan dezeSu tadadbhutamivAbhavat .
prAmathnAddhAstinapuraM vAto dakSiNapazcimaH . Arujan gaNazo vRkSAn paruSo ' zaninisvanaH .
yatra yatra ca vArSNeyo vartate pathi bhArata . tatra tatra sukho vAyuH sarvaM cAsIt pradakSiNam .
vavarSa puSpavarSaM ca kamalAni ca bhUrizaH . samazca panthA nirduHkho vyapetakuzakaNTakaH .
saMstuto brAhmaNairgIrbhistatra tatra sahasrazaH . arcyate madhupazca vasubhizca vasupradaH .
taM kiranti mahAtmAnaM vanyaiH puSpaiH sugandhibhiH . striyaH pathi samAgamya sarvabhUtahite ratam .
sa zAlibhavanaM ramyaM sarvasasyasamAcitam . sukhaM paramarmiSThamabhyagAd bharatarSabha .
pazyan bahupazUn grAmAn ramyAn hRdayatoSaNAn . purANi ca vyatikrAman rASTrANi vividhAni ca .
nityaM hRSTAH sumanaso bhAratairabhirakSitAH . nodvignAH paracakrANAM vyasanAnAmakovidAH . upaplavyAdathAgamya janAH puranivAsinaH . pathyatiSThanta sahitA viSvaksenadidRkSayA .
te tu sarve samAyAntamagnimiddhamiva prabhum . arcayAmAsurarcAha~ dezAtithimupasthitam .
vRkasthalaM samAsAdya kezavaH paravIrahA . prakIrNarazmAvAditye vyomni vai hohitAyati .
avatIrya rathAt tUrNaM kRtvA zaucaM yathAvidhi . rathamocanamAdizya saMdhyAmupaviveza ha .
dAruko ' pi hayAn muktvA paricarya ca zAstrataH . mumoca sarvayoktrAdi muktvA caitAnavAsRjat .
abhyatItya tu tat sarvamuvAca madhusUdanaH . yudhiSThirasya kAryArthamiha vatsyAmahe kSapAm .
tasya tanmatamAjJAya cakrurAvasathaM narAH . kSaNena cAnnapAnAni guNavanti samArjayan .
tasmin grAme pradhAnAstu ya Asan brAhmaNA nRpa . AryAH kulInA hrImanto brAhmI vRttimanuSThitAH .
te ' bhigamya mahAtmAnaM hRSIkezamariMdamam . pUjAM cakruryathAnyAyamAzIrmaGgasaMyutAm .
te pUjayitvA dAzArha sarvalokeSu pUjitam . nyavedayanta vezmAni ranavanti mahAtmane .
tAn prabhuH kRtamityuktvA satkRtya ca yathArhataH . abhyetya caiSAM vezmAni punarAyAt sahaiva taiH .
sumRSTaM bhojayitvA ca brAhmaNAMstatra kezavaH . bhuktvA ca saha taiH sarvairavasat tAM kSapAM sukham .
vaizampAyana uvAca pravizannarjuno rAjannAzramaM satyavAdinaH . dadarzAsInamekAnte muni satyavatIsutam .
sa tamAsAdya dharmajJamupatasthe mahAvratam . arjuno ' smIti nAmAsmai nivedyAbhyavadat tataH .
svAgataM te ' stviti prAha muniH satyavatIsutaH . AsyatAmiti hovAca prasannAtmA mahAmuniH .
tamapratItamanasaM niHzvasantaM punaH punaH nirviNNamanasaM dRSTvA pArthaM vyAso ' bravIdidam . nakhakezadazAkumbhavAriNA kiM samukSitaH . AvIrajAnugamanaM brAhmaNo vA hatastvayA .
yuddhe parAjito vAsi gatazrIriva lakSyase . na tvAM prabhinnaM jAnAmi kimidaM bharatarSabha . zrotavyaM cenmayA pArtha kSipramAkhyAtumarhasi .
arjuna uvAca yaH sa meghavapuH zrImAn bRhatpaMkajalocanaH . sa kRSNa : saha rAmeNa tyaktvA dehaM divaM gataH . ( tadvAkyasparzanAlokasukhaM tvamRtasaMtibham . saMsmRtya devadevasya pramuhyAmyamRtAtmanaH . ) mausale bRSNivIrANAM vinAzo brahmazApajaH .
babhUva vIrAntakaraH prabhAse lomaharSaNaH . ete zUrA mahAtmAnaH siMhadarpA mahAbalAH .
bhojavRSNyandhakA brahmannanyonyaM tairhataM yudhi . gadAparighazaktInAM sahAH parighabAhavaH . ta erakAbhirnihatAH pazya kAlasya paryayam . hataM paJcazataM teSAM sahasraM bAhuzAlinAm . nidhanaM samanuprAptaM samAsAdyetaretaram .
punaH punarna mRSyAmi vinAzamamitaujasAm . cintayAno yadUnAM ca kRSNasya ca yazasvinaH .
zoSaNaM sAgarasyeva parvatasyeva cAlanam . nabhasaH patanaM caiva zaityamagnestathaiva ca . azraddheyamahaM manye vinAzaM zArGgadhanvanaH . na ceha sthAtumicchAmi loke kRSNavinAkRt .
itaH kaSTataraM cAnyacchRNu tad vai tapodhana . mano me dIryate yena cintayAnasya vai muhuH .
pazyato vRSNidArAzca mama brahman sahasrazaH . AbhIrairanusRtyAjau hatAH paJcanadAlayaiH .
dhanurAdAya tatrAhaM nAzakaM tasya pUraNe . yathA purA ca me vIryaM bhujayorna tathA ' bhavat .
astrANi me pranaSTAni vividhAni mahAmune . zarAzca kSayamApannAH kSaNenaiva samantataH .
puruSazcAprameyAtmA zaMkhacakragadAdharaH . caturbhujaH pItavAsAH zyAmaH padmadalekSaNaH . yazca yAti purastAnme rathasya sumahAdyutiH .
pradahana ripusainyAni na pazyAmyahamacyutam . yena pUrvaM pradagdhAni zatrUsainyAni tejasA .
zarairgANDIvanirmuktairahaM pazcAcca nAzayam . tamapazyan viSIdAmi ghUrNAmIva ca sattama .
vinA janArdanaM vIraM nAhaM jIvitumutsahe . zrutvaiva hi gataM viSNuM mamApi mumuhurdizaH .
praNaSTajJAtivIryasya zUnyasya paridhAvataH . upadeSTuM mama zreyo bhavAnarhati sattama .
vyAsa uvAca brahmazApavinirdagdhA vRSNyandhakamahArathAH . vinaSTAH kuruzArdUla na tAzocitumarhasi .
bhavitavyaM tathA tacca diSTametanmahAtmanAm . upekSitaM ca kRSNena zaktenApi vyapohitum .
trailokyamapi govindaH kRtsnaM sthAvarajaGgamam . prasahedanyathAkartuM kutaH zApaM mahAtmanAm .
rathasya purato yAti yaH sa cakragadAdharaH . tava snehAt purANarSirvAsudevazcaturbhuja .
kRtvA bharAvataraNaM pRthivyAH pRthulocanaH . mokSayitvA tanuM prAptaH kRSNaH svasthAnamuttamam .
tvayApIha mahat karma devAnAM puruSarSabha . kRtaM bhImasahAyena yamAbhyAM ca mahAbhuja .
kRtakRtyAMzca vo manye saMsiddhAn kurupuGgava . gamanaM prAptakAlaM va ihaM zreyaskara vibho .
evaM buddhizca tejazca pratipattizca bhAratA . bhavanti bhavakAleSu vipadyante viparyaye .
kAlamUlamidaM sarvaM jagadbIjaM dhanaJjaya . kAla eva samAdatte punareva yadRcchayA .
sa eva balavAn bhUtvA punarbhavati durbalaH . sa evezazca bhUtveha parairAjJApyate punaH .
kRtakRtyAni cAstrANi gatAnyadya yathAgatam . punareSyanti te haste yadA kAlo bhaviSyati .
kAlo gantuM gatiM mukhyAM bhavatAmapi bhArata . etacchreyo hi vo manye paramaM bharatarSabha .
vaizampAyana uvAca etad vacanamAjJAya vyAsasyAmitatejasaH . anujJAto yayau pArtho nagaraM nAgasAhrayam .
pravizya ca purI vIraH samAsAdya yudhiSThiram . AcaSTa tad yathAvRttaM vRSNyandhakakulaM prati .
nArada uvAca azokaM zokanAzArthaM zAstraM zAntikaraM zivam . nizamya labhate buddhiM tAM labdhvA sukhamedhate .
zokasthAnasahasrANi bhayasthAnazatAni ca . divase divase mUDhamAvizanti na paNDitam .
tasmAdaniSTanAzArthamitihAsaM nibodha me . tiSThate ced vaze buddhirlabhate zokanAzanam .
aniSTasamprayogAcca viprayogAt priyasya ca . manuSyA mAnasairduHkhairyujyante svalpabuddhayaH .
dravyeSu samatIteSu ye guNAstAn na cintayet . na tAnAdriyamANasya snehabandhaH pramucyate .
doSadarzI bhavet tatra yatra rAgaH pravartate . aniSTavardhitaM pazyet tathA kSipra virajyate .
nArtho na dharmo na yazo yo ' tItamanuzocati . apyabhAvena yujyeta taccAsya na nivartate . .
guNairbhUtAni yujyante viyujyante tathaiva ca . sarvANi naitadekasya zokasthAnaM hi vidyate .
mRtaM vA yadi vA naSTaM yo ' tItamanuzocati . duHkhena labhate du : khaM dvAvanoM prapadyate .
nAzru kurvanti ye buddhyA dRSTvA lokeSu saMtatim . samyak prapazyataH sarvaM nAzrukarmopapadyate .
duHkhopaghAte zArIre mAnase cApyupasthite . yasmin na zakyate kartuM yatnastannAnucintayet .
bhaiSajyametad duHkhasya yadetannAnucintayet . cintyamAnaM hi na vyeti bhUyazcApi pravardhate .
prajJayA mAnasaM duHkhaM hanyAcchArIramauSadhaiH . etad vijJAnasAmarthya na bAlaiH samatAmiyAt .
anityaM yauvanaM rUpaM jIvitaM dravyasaMcayaH . ArogyaM priyasaMvAso gRdhyet tatra na paNDitaH .
na jAnapadikaM duHkhamekaH zocitumarhati . azocan pratikurvIta yadi pazyedupakramam .
sukhAd bahutaraM duHkhaM jIvite nAtra saMzayaH . snigdhatvaM cendriyArtheSu mohAnmaraNamapriyam .
parityajati yo duHkhaM sukhaM vApyubhayaM naraH . abhyeti brahma so ' tyantaM na taM zocanti paNDitAH .17 . .
tyajyante duHkhamarthA hi pAlane na ca te sukhAH . duHkhena cAdhigamyate nAzameSAM na cintayet .
anyAmanyAM dhanAvasthAM prApya vaizeSikI narAH . atRptA yAnti vidhvaMsaM saMtoSaM yAnti paNDitA .
sarve kSayAntA nicayAH patanAntAH samucchrayAH . saMyogA viprayogAntA maraNAntaM hi jIvitam .
anto nAsti pipAsAyAstuSTistu paramaM sukham . tasmAt saMtoSameveha dhanaM pazyanti paNDitAH .
nimeSamAtramapi hi vayo gacchanna tiSThati . svazarIreSvanityeSu nityaM kimanucintayet .
bhUteSu bhAvaM saMcintya ye buddhvA manasa : param . na zocanti gatAdhvAnaH pazyantaH paramAM gatim .
saMcinvAnakamevainaM kAmAnAmavitRptakam . vyAghraH pazumivAsAdya mRtyurAdAya gacchati . .
tathApyupAyaM sampazyed duHkhasya parimokSaNam . azocan nArabheccaiva muktazcAvyasanI bhavet .
zabde sparze ca rUpe ca gandheSu ca raseSu ca . nopabhogAt paraM kiMcid dhanino vAdhanasya ca .
prAksamprayogAd bhUtAnAM nAsti duHkhaM parAyaNam . viprayogAt tu sarvasya na zocet prakRtisthitaH .
dhRtyA ziznodaraM rakSet pANipAdaM ca cakSuSA . cakSuHzrotre ca manasA mano vAcaM ca vidyayA .
praNayaM pratisaMhRtya saMstuteSvitareSu ca . vicaredasamunnaddhaH sa sukhI sa ca paNDitaH .
adhyAtmaratirAsIno nirapekSo nirAmiSaH . Atmanaiva sahAyena yazcaret sa sukhI bhavet .
duryodhana uvAca vAsudevo mahad bhUtaM sarvalokeSu kathyate . tasyAgamaM pratiSThAM ca jJAtumicche pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca vAsudevo mahad bhUtaM sarvadaivatadaivatam . na paraM puNDarIkAkSAd dRzyate bharatarSabha .
mArkaNDeyazca govinde kathayatyadbhutaM mahat . sarvabhUtAni bhUtAtmA mahAtmA puruSottamaH .
Apo vAyuzca tejazca trayametadakalpayat . sa sRSTvA pRthivIM devIM sarvalokezvaraH prabhuH .
apsu vai zayanaM cakre mahAtmA puruSottamaH . sarvatejomayo devo yogAt suSvApa tatra ha .
mukhataH so ' gnimasRjat prANAd vAyumathApi ca . sarasvatI ca vedAMzca manasaH sasRje ' cyutaH .
eSa lokAn sasarjAdau devAMzca RSibhiH saha . nidhanaM caiva mRtyuM ca prAjAnAM prabhavApyayau .
eSa dharmazca dharmajJo varadaH sarvakAmadaH . eSa kartA ca kAryaM ca pUrvadevaH svayamprabhuH .
bhUtaM bhavyaM bhaviSyacca pUrvametadakalpayat . ubhe saMdhye dizaH khaM ca niyamAMzca janArdanaH . RSIMzcaiva hi govindastapazcaivAbhyakalpayat . sraSTAraM jagatazcApi mahAtmA prabhuravyayaH .
agrajaM sarvabhUtAnAM saMkarSaNakalpayat . tasmAnnArAyaNo jajJe devadevaH sanAtanaH . nAbhau padmaM babhUvAsya sarvalokasya sambhavAt . tasmAt pitAmaho jAtastasmAjjAtAstvimAH prajAH .12 . zeSaM cAkalpayad devamanantaM vizvarUpiNam .
yo dhArayati bhUtAni dharAM cemAM saparvatAm . dhyAnayogena viprAzca taM vidanti mahaujasam .
karNasrotobhavaM cApi madhuM nAma mahAsuram . tamugramugrakarmANamugrAM buddhiM samAsthitam . brahmaNo ' pacitiM kurvaJ jaghAna puruSottamaH . tasya tAta vadhAdeva devadAnavamAnavAH .
madhusUdanamityAhurRSayazca janArdanam . varAhazcaiva siMhazca trivikramagatiH prabhuH .
eSa mAtA pitA caiva sarveSAM prANinAM hariH . paraM hi puNDarIkAkSAnna bhUtaM na bhaviSyati .
mukhataH so ' sRjad viprAn bAhubhyAM kSatriyAMstathA . vaizyAMzcApyUsto rAjazUdrAn vai pAdatastathA .
tapasA niyato devaM vidhAnaM sarvadehinAm . brahmabhUtamamAvAsyAM paurNamAsyAM tathaiva ca . yogabhUtaM paricaran kezavaM mahadApnuyAt . kezavaH paramaM tejaH sarvalokapitAmahaH .
enamAhurhaSIkezaM munayo vai narAdhipa . evamenaM vijAnIhi AcAryaM pitaraM gurum .
kRSNo yasya prasIdeta lokAstenAkSayA jitAH . yazcaivainaM bhayasthAne kezavaM zaraNaM vrajet .
sadA naraH paThaMzcedaM svastimAn sa sukhI bhavet . ye ca kRSNaM prapadyante te na muhyanti mAnavAH .
bhaye mahati magnAMzca pAti nityaM janArdanaH . sa taM yudhiSThiro jJAtvA yAthAtathyena bhArata .
sarvAtmanA mahAtmAnaM kezavaM jadIzvaram . prapannaH zaraNaM rAjan yogAnAM prabhumIzvaram .
yudhiSThira uvAca bhImasena yamau cobhau pAJcAli ca nibodhata . nAsti bhUtasya nAzo vai pazyatAsmAn vanecarAn .
durbalA : klezitAH smeti yad bruvAmetaretaram . azakye ' pi vrajAmo yaddhanaMjayadidRkSayA . .
tanme dahati gAtrANi tUlarAzimivAnalaH . yacca vIraM na pazyAmidhanaMjayamupAntikAt .
tasya darzanatRSNaM mAM sAnujaM vanamAsthitam . yAjJasenyAH parAmarza sa ca vIra dahatyuta .
nakulAt pUrvajaM pArthaM na pazyAmyamitaujasam . ajeyamugradhanvAnaM tena tapye vRkodara .
tIrthAni caiva ramyANi vanAni ca sarAMsi cA carAmi saha yuSmAbhistasya darzanakAjhayA . . paJcavarSANyahaM vIraM satyasaMdhaMdhanaMjayam . yanna pazyAmi bIbhatsuM tena tapye vRkodara .
taM vai zyAmaM guDAkezaM siMhavikrAntagAminam . na pazyAmi mahAbAhuM tena tapye vRkodara .
kRtAstraM nipuNaM yuddhe ' pratimAnadhanuSmatAm . na pazyAmi kuruzreSTha tena tapye vRkodara .
carantamarisaMgheSu kAle kruddhamivAntakam . prabhinnamiva mAtaGgaM siMhaskandhaMdhanaMjayam . yaH sa zakrAdanavaro vIryeNa draviNena ca . yamayoH pUrvajaH pArthaH zvetAzvo ' mitavikramaH . duHkhena mahatAviSTastaM na pazyAmi phAlgunam . ajeyamugradhanvAnaM tena tapye vRkodara .
satataM yaH kSamAzIlaH kSipyamANo ' pyaNIyasA . RjumArgaprapannasya zarmadAtAbhayasya ca .
sa tu jihmapravRttasya mAyayAbhijighAMsataH . api vajradharasyApi bhavet kAlaviSopamaH .
zatrorapi prapannasya so ' nRzaMsaH pratApavAn . dAtAbhayasya bIbhatsuramitAtmA mahAbalaH .
sarveSAmAzrayo ' smAkaM raNe ' rINAM pramarditA . AhartA sarvaratnAnAM sarveSAM naH sukhAvahaH .
ratnAni yasya vIryeNa divyAnyAsan purA mama . bahUni bahujAtIni yAni prAptaH suyodhanaH .
yasya bAhubalAd vIra sabhA cAsIt purA mama . sarvaratnamayI khyAtA triSu lokeSu pANDava .
vAsudevasamaM vIrye kArtavIryasamaM yudhi . ajeyamamitaM yuddhe taM na pazyAmi phAlgunam .
saMkarSaNaM mahAvIryaM tvAM ca bhImAparAjitam . anuyAtaH svavIryeNa vAsudevaM ca zatruhA . .
yasya bAhubale tulyaH prabhAve ca puraMdaraH . jave vAyurmukhe somaH krodhe mRtyuH sanAtanaH .
te vayaM taM naravyAghraM sarve vIra didRkSavaH . pravekSyAmo mahAbAho parvataM gandhamAdanam .
vizAlA badarI yatra naranArAyaNAzramaH . taM sadAdhyuSitaM yaHkSyAmo girimuttamam .
kuberanalinI ramyAM rAkSasairabhisevitAm . padbhireva gamiSyAmastapyamAnA mahat tapaH .
na ca yAnavatA zakyo gantuM dezo vRkodara . na nRzaMsena lubdhena nAprazAntena bhArata .
tatra sarve gamiSyAmo bhImArjunagaveSiNaH . sAyudhA baddhanistriMzAH sArdhaM viprairmahAvrataiH .
makSikAdaMzamazakAn siMhAn vyAghrAn sarIsRpAn . prApnotyaniyataH pArtha niyatastAn na pazyati .
te vayaM niyatAtmAnaH parvataM gandhamAdanam . pravekSyAmo mitAhArAdhanaMjayadidRkSavaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca na vai niguNamAtmAnaM manye devarSisattama . tathAsmi duHkhasaMtapto yathA nAnyo mahIpatiH .
parAMzca nirguNAn manye na cadharmagatAnapi . te ca lomaza loke ' sminnRdhyante kena hetunA .
lomaza uvAca nAtra duHkhaM tvayA rAjan kAryaM pArtha kathaMcana . yadadharmeNa vardheyuradharmarucayo janAH .
vardhatyadharmeNa narastato bhadrANi pazyati . tataH sapatnAJjayati samUlastu vinazyati .
mayA hi dRSTA daiteyA dAnavAzca mahIpate . vardhamAnA hyadharmeNa kSayaM copagatAH punaH .
purA devayuge caiva hRSTaM sarvaM mayA vibho . arocayan surAdharmadharma tatyajire ' surAH .
tIrthAni devA vivizu vizan bhAratAsurAH . tAnadharmakRto darpaH pUrvameva samAvizat .
darpAnmAnaH samabhavanmAnAt krodho vyajAyata . krodhAdahrIstato ' lajjA vRttaM teSAM tato ' nazat .
tAnalajjAn gatahrIkAn hInavRttAn vRthAvratAn . kSamA lakSmIH svadharmazca na cirAt prajahustataH .
lakSmIstu devAnagamadalakSmIrasurAn nRpa . tAnalakSmI samAviSTAn darpopahatacetasaH .
daiteyAn dAnavAMzcaiva kalirapyAvizat tataH . tAnalakSmIsamAviSTAn dAnavAn kalinA hatAn .
dabhibhUtAn kaunteya kriyAhInAnacetasaH . mAnAbhibhUtAnacirAd vinAzaH samapadyata .
niryazaskAstathA daityAH kRtsnazo vilayaM gatAH . devAstu sAgarAMzcaiva saritazca sarAMsi ca . abhyagacchandharmazIlA : puNyAnyAyatanAni ca . tapobhiH kratubhirdAnairAzIrvAdaizca pANDava . prajahuH sarvapApAni zreyazca pratipedire . evamAdAnavantazca nirAdAnAzca sarvazaH .
tIrthAnyagacchan vibudhAstenApubhUtimuttamAm . tathA tvamapi rAjendra snAtvA tIrtheSu sAnujaH . punarvetsyasi tAM lakSmImeSa panthAH sanAtanaH .
yatheva hi nRgo rAjA zibirauzInaro yathA . bhagIratho vasumanA gayaH pUruH purUravAH . caramANAstapo nityaM sparzanAdambhasazca te . tIrthAbhigamanAt pUtA darzanAcca mahAtmanAm . alabhanta yazaH puNyaMdhanAni ca vizAmpate .
tathA tvamapi rAjendra labdhAsi vipulAM zriyanta . yathA cekSvAkurabhavat saputrajanabAndhavaH . mucukundo ' tha mAndhAtA maruttazca mahIpatiH . kIrti puNyAmavindanta yathA devAstapobalAt . devarSayazca kAtsnyena tathA tvamapi vetsyasi . dhArtarASTrAstvadharmeNa mohena ca vazIkRtAH . na cirAd vai vinaikSyanti daityA iva na saMzayaH .
bhISma uvAca proktA gRhasthavRttiste vihitA yA manISibhiH . tadanantaramuktaM yat tannibodha yudhiSThira .
kramazastvavadhUyainAM tRtIyAM vRttimuttamAm . saMyogavratakhinnAnAM vAnaprasthAzramaukasAm .
zrUyatAM putra bhadraM te sarvalokAzramAtmanAm . prekSApUrvaM pravRttAnAM puNyadezanivAsinAm .
vyAsa uvAca gRhasthastu yadA pazyed valIpalitamAtmanaH . apatyasyaiva cApatyaM vanameva tadA zrayet .
tRtIyamAyuSo bhAgaM vAnaprasthAzrame vaset . tAnevAgnIn paricared yajamAno divaukasaH .
niyato niyatAhAraH SaSThabhukto ' pramattavAn . tadagnihotraM tA gAvo yajJAGgAni ca sarvazaH .
aphAlakRSTaM vrIhiyavaM nIvAraM vighasAni ca . hIMSi samprayaccheta makheSvatrApi paJcasu .
vAnaprasthAzrame ' pyetAzcatasro vRttayaH smRtAH . sadya : prakSAlakAH kecit kecinmAsikasaMcayAH .
vArSikaM saMcayaM kecit kecid dvAdazavArSikam . kurvantyatithipUjArthaM yajJatantrArthameva vA .
abhrAvakAzA varSAsu hemante jalasaMzrayAH . grISme ca paJca tapasaH zazvacca mitabhojanAH .
bhUmau viparivartante tiSThanti prapadairapi . sthAnAsanairvartayanti savaneSvabhiSiJcate .
dantolUkhalikAH kecidazmakuTTAstathA pare . zuklapakSe pibantyeke yavAgU kvathitAM sakRt .
kRSNapakSe pibantyanye bhujate vA yathAgatam . mUlaireke phalaireke yuSpaireke dRDhavratAH . vartayanti yathAnyAyaM vaikhAnasagatiM zritAH .
etAzcAnyAzca vividhA dIkSAsteSAM manISiNAm . caturthazcaupaniSado dharma : sAdhAraNaH smRtaH . vAnaprasthAd gRhasthAcca tato ' nyaH sampravartate .
asminneva yuge tAta vipraiH sarvArthadarzibhiH . agastyaH sapta RSayo madhucchando ' ghamarSaNaH . sAMkRtiH sudivA taNDiyathAvAso ' kRtazramaH . ahovIryastathA kAvyastANDyo medhAtithirbudhaH . balavAn karNanirvAka : zUnyapAlaH kRtazramaH . enaM dharma kRtavantastataH svargamupAgamana .
tAta pratyakSadharmANastathA yAyAvarA gaNAH . RSINAmugratapasAM dharmanaipuNadarzinAm . anye cAparimeyAzca brAhmaNA vanamAzritAH . vaikhAnasA vAlakhilyAH saikatAzca tathA pare . karmabhiste nirAnandA dharmanityA jitendriyAH . gatAH pratyakSadharmANaste sarve vanamAzritAH .
anakSatrAstvanAdhRSyA dRzyante jyotiSAM gaNAH . jarayA ca paridhano vyAdhinA ca prapIDitaH . caturthe cAyuSaH zeSe vAnaprasthAzramaM tyajet . sadyaskArAM nirUpyeSTiM sarva vedasadakSiNAm . AtmayAjI so ' ' tmaratirAtmakrIDAtmasaMzrayaH . AtmanyagnIn samAropya tyaktvA sarvaparigrahAn .
sAdharakAMzca yajed yajJAniSTIzcaiveha sarvadA . yadaiva yAjinAM yajJAdAtmanIjyA pravartate . . trIMzcaivAgnIn yajet samyagAtmanyevAtmamokSaNAt . prANebhyo yajuSaH paJca SaT prAznIyAdakutsayan .
kezalomanakhAn vApya vAnaprastho munistataH . AzramAdAzramaM puNyaM pUto gacchati karmabhiH .
abhayaM sarvabhUtebhyo dattvA yaH pravrajed dvijaH . lokAstejomayAstasya pretya cAnantyamaznute .
suzIlavRtto vyapanItakalmaSo na ceha nAmutra ca kartumIhate . aroSamoho gatasaMdhivigraho bhavedudAsInavadAtmavinnaraH .
yameSu caivAnugateSu na vyathe svazAstrasUtrAhutimantravikramaH . bhaved yatheSTAgatirAtmavedini na saMzayo dharmapare jitendriye . .
radhiSThitaM trInadhivRttimuttamam . caturthamuktaM paramAzramaM zRNu prakIrtyamAnaM paramaM parAyaNam .
kuntI uvAca evametanmahAbAho yathA vadasi pANDavA kRtamuddharSaNaM pUrvaM mayA vaH sIdatAM nRpAH .
dyUtApahRtarAjyAnAM patitAnAM sukhAdapi . jJAtibhiH paribhUtAnAM kRtamuddharSaNaM mayA . .
kathaM pANDorna nazyeta saMtatiH puruSarSabhAH . yazazca vo na nazyeta iti coddharSaNaM kRtam .
yUyamindrasamAH sarve devatulyaparAkramAH . mA pareSAM mukhaprekSAH sthetyevaM tat kRtaM mayA .
kathaM dharmabhRtAM zreSTho rAjA tvaM vAsavopamaH . punarvane na duHkhI syA iti coddharSaNaM kRtam .
nAgAyutasamaprANaH khyAtavikramapauruSaH . nAyaM bhImo ' tyayaM gacchediti cauddharSaNaM kRtam .
bhImasenAdavarajastathAyaM vAsavopamaH . vijayo nAvasIdeta iti coddharSaNaM kRtam .
nakulaH sahadevazca tathemau guruvartinau . kSudhA kathaM na sIdetAmiti coddharSaNaM kRtam .
iyaM ca bRhatI zyAmA tathAtyAyatalocanA . vRthA sabhAtale kliSTA mA bhUditi ca tat kRtam .
prekSatAmeva vo bhIma vepantIM kadalImiva . strIdharmiNImariSTAGgI tathA dyUtaparAjitAm . duHzAsano yadA mAd dAsIvat paryakarSata . tadaiva viditaM mahyaM parAbhUtamidaM kulam .
niSaNNAH kuravazcaiva tadA me zvazurAdayaH . sA daivaM nAthamicchantI vyalapat kurarI yathA .
kezapakSe parAmRSTA pApena hatabuddhinA . yadA duHzAsanenaiSA tadA muhyAmyahaM nRpAH .
yuSmattejovivRddhyarthaM mayA huddharSaNaM kRtam . tadAnIM vidulAvAkyairiti tad vitta putrakAH .
kathaM na rAjavaMzo ' yaM nazyet prApya sutAn mam . pANDoriti mayA putrAstasmAduddharSaNaM kRtam .
na tasya putrAH pautrA vA kSatavaMzasya pArthiva . . labhante sukRtA~llokAn yasmAd vaMzaH praNazyati . .16 .
bhuktaM rAjyaphalaM putrA bharturme vipulaM purA . mahAdAnAni dattAni pItaH somo yathAvidhi .
nAhamAtmaphalArthaM vai vAsudevamacUcudam . vidulAyAH pralApaistaiH pAlanArthaM ca tat kRtam .
nAhaM rAjyaphalaM putrAH kAmaye putranirjitam . patilokAnahaM puNyAn kAmaye tapasA vibho .
zvazrUzvazurayoH kutvA zuzrUSAM vanavAsinoH . tapasA zoSayiSyAmi yudhiSThira kalevaram .
nivartasva kuruzreSTa bhImasenAdibhiH saha . dharme te dhIyatAM buddhirmanastu mahadastu ca .
zalya uvAca evamuktaH sa bhagavAJchacyA tAM punarabravIt . vikramasya na kAlo ' yaM nahuSo balavattaraH .
vivardhitazca RSibhirhavyakavyaizca bhAvini . nItimatra vidhAsyAmi devi tAM kartumarhasi .
guhyaM caitat tvayA kAryaM nAkhyAtavyaM zubhe kvacit . gatvA nahuSamekAnte bravIhi ca sumadhyame .
RSiyAnena divyena mAmupaihi jagatpate . evaM tava vaze prItA bhaviSyAmIti taM vadA .
ityuktvA devarAjena patnI sA kamalekSaNA . evamastvityathoktvA tu jagAma nahuSaM prati .
nahuSastAM tato dRSTvA sasmito vAkyamabravIt . svAgataM te varArohe kiM karomi zucismite .
bhaktaM mAM bhaja kalyANi kamicchasi manasvini . tava kalyANi yat kAryaM tat kariSye sumadhyame .
na ca vrIDA tvayA kAryA suzroNi mayi vizvaseH . satyena vai zape devi kariSye vacanaM tava .
indrANyuvAca yo me kRtastvayA kAlastamAkAGkSe jagatpate . tatastvameva bhartA me bhaviSyasi surAdhipa .
kAryaM ca hRdi me yat tad devarAjAvadhAraya . vakSyAmi yadi me rAjan priyametat kariSyasi . vAkyaM praNayasaMyuktaM tataH syAM vazagA tava .
indrasya vAjino vAhA hastino ' tha rathAstathA . icchAmyahamathApUrvaM vAhanaM te surAdhipa . yanna viSNorna rudrasya nAsurANAM na rakSasAm .
vahantu tvAM mahAbhAgA RSayaH saMgatA vibho . sarve zibikayA rAjannetaddhi mama rocate .
nAsureSu na deveSu tulyo bhavitumarhasi . sarveSA teja Adatse svena vIryeNa darzanAt . na te pramukhataH sthAtuM kazcicchaknoti vIryavAn .
zalya uvAca evamuktastu nahuSaH prAhRSyat tadA kila . uvAca vacanaM cApi surendrastAmaninditAm .
nahuSa uvAca apUrvaM vAhanamidaM tvayoktaM varavarNini . dRDhaM me rucitaM devi tvadvazo ' smi varAnane .
na hyalpavIryo bhavati yo vAhAn kurute munIn . ahaM tapasvI balavAn bhUtabhavyabhavatprabhuH .
mayi kruddhe jaganna syAnmayi sarvaM pratiSThitam . devadAnavagandharvAH kinnaroragarAkSasAH . na me kruddhasya paryAptAH sarve lokAH zucismite . cakSuSA yaM prapazyAmi tasya tejo harAmyaham .
tasmAt te vacanaM devi kariSyAmi na saMzayaH . saptarSayo mAM vakSyanti sarve brahmarSayastathA . pazya mahAtmyayogaM me RddhiM ca varavarNini .
zalya uvAca evamuktvA tu tAM devIM visRjya ca varAnanAm . vimAne yojayitvA ca RSIn niyamamAsthitAn . abrahmaNyo balopeto matto madabalena ca . kAmavRttaH sa duSTAtmA vAhayAmAsa tAnRSIn .
nahuSeNa visRSTA ca bRhaspatimathAbravIt . samayo ' lpAvazeSo me nahuSeNeha yaH kRtaH .
zakraM mRgaya zIghraM tvaM bhaktAyAH kuru me dayAm . bADhamityeva bhagavAn bRhaspatiruvAca tAm .
na bhetavya tvayA devi nahuSAd duSTacetasaH . na hoSa sthAsyati ciraM gata eSa narAdhamaH .
adharmajJo maharSINAM vAhanAcca tataH zubhe . iSTiM cAhaM kariSyAmi vinAzAyAsya durmateH . zakraM cAdhigamiSyAmi mA bhaistvaM bhadramastu te .
tataH prajvAlya vidhivajjuhAva paramaM haviH . bRhastapatirmahAtejA devarAjopalabdhaye . hutvAgniM so ' bravId rAjaJchakramanviSyatAmiti .
tasmAcca bhagavAn devaH svayameva hutAzanaH . strIveSamadbhutaM kRtvA tatraivAntaradhIyata .
sa dizaH pradizazcaiva parvatAni vanAni ca . pRthivIM cAntarikSaM ca vicintyAtha manogatiH . nimeSAntaramAtreNa bRhaspatimupAgamat .
agniruvAca bRhaspate na pazyAmi devarAjamiha kvacit . ApaH zeSAH sadA cApaH praveSTuM notsahAmyaham .
na me tatra gatirbrahman kimanyat karavANi te ! tamabravId devagururapo viza mahAyute .
agniruvAca nApaH praveSTuM zakSyAmi kSayo me ' tra bhaviSyati . zaraNaM tvAM prapanno ' smi svasti te ' stu mahAdyute .
adbhayo ' gnirbrahmataH kSatramazmano lohamutthitam . teSAM sarvatragaM tejaH svAsu yoniSu zAmyati .
janamejaya uvAca evaM hRtAyAM bhAryAyAM prApya klezamanuttamam . pratipadya tataH kRSNAM kimakurvata pANDavAH .
vaizampAyana uvAca evaM hRtAyAM kRSNAyAM prApya klezamanuttamam . vihAya kAmyakaM rAjA saha bhrAtRbhiracyutaH . punadvaitavanaM ramyamAjagAma yudhiSThiraH . svAdumUlaphalaM ramyaM vicitrabahupAdapam .
anubhuktaphalAhArAH sarva eva mitAzanAH . nyavasan pANDavAstatra kRSNayA saha bhAryayA .
vasan dvaitavane rAjA kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . bhImaseno ' rjunazcaiva mAdrIputrau ca pANDavau . brAhmaNArthe parAkrAntA dharmAtmAno yatavratAH . klezamArchanta vipulaM sukhodaka paraMtapAH .
tasmin prativasantaste yat prApuH kurusattamAH . vane klezaM sukhodakaM tat pravakSyAmi te zRNu .
araNIsahitaM manthaM brAhmaNasya tapasvinaH . gharSamANasya viSANe viSANe samasajjataH .
tadAdAya gato rAjaMstvaramANo mahAmRgaH . AzramAntaritaH zIghraM plavamAno mahAjavaH .
hriyamANaM tu taM dRSTvA sa vipraH kurusattama . tvarito ' bhyAgamat tatra agnihotraparIpsayA .
mRgasya gharSamANasya ajAtazatrumAsInaM bhrAtRbhiH sahitaM vane . Agamya brAhmaNastUrNaM saMtaptazcedamabravIt .
araNIsahitaM manyaM samAsaktaM vanaspatau . mRgasya gharSamANasya viSANe samasajjata .
tamAdAya gato rAjaMstvaramANo mahAmRgaH . AzramAt tvaritaH zIghraM plavamAno mahAjavaH .
tasya gatvA padaM rAjannAsAdya ca mahAmRgam . agnihotraM na lupyeta tadAnayata pANDavAH .
brAhmaNasya vacaH zrutvA saMtapto ' tha yudhiSThiraH . dhanurAdAya kaunteyaH prAdravad bhrAtRbhiH saha .
sannaddhA dhanvinaH sarve prAdravan narapuGgavAH . brAhmaNArthe yatantaste zIghramanvagaman mRgam .
karNinAlIkanArAcAnutsRjanto mahArathAH . nAvidhyan pANDavAstatra pazyanto mRgamantikAt .
teSAM prayatamAnAnAM nAdRzyata mahAmRgaH . apazyanto mRgaM zAntA duHkhaM prAptA manasvinaH .
zItalacchAyamAgamya nyacodhaM gahane vane . kSutpipAsAparItAGgAH pANDavAH samupAvizan .
teSAM samupaviSTAnAM nakulo duHkhitastadA . abravId bhrAtaraM zreSThamamarSAt kurunandanam .
nAsmin kule jAtu mamajja dharmo na cAlasyAdarthalopo babhUva . anuttarAH sarvabhUteSu bhUyaH samprAptAH smaH saMzayaM kiM nu rAjan .
vyAsa uvAca dvandvAni mokSajijJAsurarthadharmAvanuSThitaH . vaktrA guNavatA ziSyaH zrAvyaH pUrvamidaM mahat .
AkAzaM mAruto jyotirApaH pRthvI ca paJcamI . bhAvAbhAvau ca kAlazca sarvabhUteSu paJcasu .
antarAtmakamAkAzaM tanmayaM zrotramindriyam . tasya zabdaM guNaM vidyAnmUrtizAstravidhAnavit .
caraNaM mArutotmeti prANApAnau ca tanmayau . sparzanaM cendriyaM vidyAt tathA sparza ca tanmayam .
tApa : pAkaH prakAzazca jyotizcakSuzca paJcamam . tasya rUpaM guNaM vidyAt tAmragaurAsitAtmakam .
prakledaH kSudratA sneha ityapAmupadizyate . asRGmajjA ca yaccAnyat snigdhaM vidyAt tadAtmakam .6
rasanaM cendriyaM jihvA rasazcApAM guNo mataH . saMghAtaH pArthivo dhAturasthidantanakhAni ca . .
zmazru roma ca kezAzca zirA snAyu ca carma ca . indriyaM ghrANasaMjJAtaM nAsiketyabhisaMjJitA .
gandhazcevendriyArtho ' yaM vijJeyaH pRthivImayaH . uttareSu guNAH santi sarvasattveSu cottarAH . paJcAnAM bhUtasaMghAnAM saMtatiM munayo viduH .
mano navamameSAM tu buddhistu dazamI smRtA . ekAdazastvanantAtmA sa sarvaH para ucyate .
vyavasAyAtmikA buddhirmano vyAkaraNAtmakam . karmAnumAnAd vijJeyaH sa jIvaH kSetrasaMjJakaH .
ebhiH kAlAtmakairbhAvairyaH sarvaiH sarvamanvitam . pazyatyakaluSaM karma sa mohaM nAnuvartate .
yudhiSThira uvAca kimuttaraM tadA tau sma cakratustasya bhASite . brAhmaNo vAthavA rAjA tanme brUhi pitAmaha .
athavA tau gatau tatra yadetat kIrtitaM tvayA . saMvAdo vA tayoH ko ' bhUt kiM vA tau tatra cakratuH .
bhISma uvAca tathetyevaM pratizrutya dharmaM sampUjya ca prabho . yamaM kAlaM ca mRtyuM ca svarga sampUjya cArhataH .
pUrvaM ye cApare tatra sametA brAhmaNarSabhAH . sarvAn sampUjya zirasA rAjAnaM so ' bravId dvijaH . phalenAnena saMyukto rAjarSe gaccha mukhyatAm . bhavatA cAbhyanujJAto japeyaM bhUya eva ha .
varaca mama pUrvaM hi datto devyA mahAbalA zraddhA te japato nityaM bhavatviti vizAmpate .
rAjovAca yadyevamaphalA siddhiH zraddhA ca japituM tava . gaccha vipra mayA sAdhu jApakaM phalamApnuhi .
brAhmaNa uvAca kRtaH prayatnaH sumahAn sarveSAM saMnidhAviha . saha tulyaphalAvAvAM gacchAvo yatra nau gatiH .
bhISma uvAca vyavasAyaM tayostatra viditvA tridazezvaraH . saha devairupayayau lokapAlaistathaiva ca .
sAdhyAzca vizve maruto vAdyAni sumahAnti ca . nadyaH zailA : samudrAzca tIrthAni vividhAni ca . . tapAMsi saMyogavidhirvedAH stobhAH sarasvatI . nAradaH parvatazcaiva vizvAvasurhahAhuhUH . gandharvazcitrasenazca parivAragaNairyutaH . nAgAH siddhAzca munayo devadevaH prajApatiH . viSNuH sahasrazIrSazca devo ' cintyaH samAgamat . avAdyantAntarikSe ca bheryastUryANi vA vibho .
puSpavarSANi divyAni tatra teSAM mahAtnAm . nanRtuzcApsaraHsaMghAstatra tatra samantataH .
atha svargastathA rUpI brAhmaNaM vAkyamabravIt . saMsiddhastvaM mahAbhAga tvaM ca siddhastathA nRpa .
atha tau sahitau rAjannanyonyavidhinA tataH . viSayapratisaMhAramubhAveva pracakratuH . .16
prANApAnau tathodAnaM samAnaM vyAnameva ca . evaM tau manasi sthApya dadhatuH prANayormanaH .
upasthitakRtau tau ca nAsikAgramadho bhruvoH . bhRkuTyA caiva manasA zanairdhArayatastadA .
nizceSTAbhyAM zarIrAbhyAM sthiradRSTI samAhitau . jitAtmAnau tathA ' ' dhAya mUrdhanyAtmAnameva ca .
tAludezamathoddAlya brAhmaNasya mahAtmanaH . jyotircAlA sumahatI jagAma tridivaM tadA .
hAhAkArastathA dikSu sarveSAM sumahAnabhUt . tajjyotiH stUyamAnaM sma brAhmaNaM prAvizat tadA .
tataH svAgatamityAha tat tejaH prapitAmahaH . prAdezamAtraM puruSaM pratyudgamya vizAmpate .
bhUyazcaivAparaM prAha vacanaM madhura tadA . jApakaistulyaphalatA yogAnAM nAtra saMzayaH .
yogasya tAvadetebhyaH pratyakSaM phaladarzanam . jApakAnAM viziSTaM tu pratyutthAnaM samAhitam .
uSyatAM mayi cetyuktvAcetayat satataM punaH . athAsyaM pravivezAsya brAhmaNo vigatajvaraH .
rAjApyetena vidhinA bhagavantaM pitAmaham . yathaiva dvijazArdUlastathaiva prAvizat tadA .
svayambhuvamatho devA abhivAdya tato ' bruvan . jApakAnAM viziSTaM tu pratyutthAnaM samAhitam .
jApakArthamayaM yatno yadarthaM vayamAgatAH . kRtapUjAvimau tulyau tvayA tulyaphalAvimau .
yogajApakayodRSTaM phalaM sumahadadya vai . sarvA llokAnatikramya gacchetAM yatra vAJchitam .
brahmovAca mahAsmRtiM paThed yastu tathaivAnusmRtiM zubhAm . tAvapyetena vidhinA gacchetAM matsalokatAm .
yazca yoge bhaved bhaktaH so ' pi nAstyatra saMzayaH . vidhinAnena dehAnte mama lokAnavApnuyAt . sAdhaye gamyatAM caiva yathAsthAnAni siddhaye .
bhISma uvAca ityuktvA sa tadA devastatraivAntaradhIyatA Amantrya ca tato devA yayuH svaM svaM nivezanam .
te ca sarve mahAtmAno dharma satkRtya tatra vai . pRSThato ' nuyayU rAjan sarve suprItacetasaH .
etat phalaM jApakAnAM gatizcaiSA prakIrtitA . yathAzrutaM mahArAja kiM bhUyaH zrotumicchasi .
vaizampAyana uvAca gate tasmin harivare bhImo ' pi balinAM varaH . tena mArgeNa vipulaM vyacarad gandhamAdanam .
anusmaran vapustasya zriyaM cApratimAM bhuvi . mAhAtmyamanubhAvaM ca smaran dAzaratheryayau .
sa tAni ramaNIyAni vAnyupavanAni ca . vilokayAmAsa tadA saugandhikavanepsayA . phulladrumavicitrANi sarAMsi saritastathA . nAnAkusumacitrANi puSpitAni vanAni ca .
mattavAraNayUthAni paGkaklinnAni bhArata . varSatAmiva meghAnAM vRndAni dadRze tadA .
hariNaizcapalApAGgairhariNIsahitairvanam . sazaSpakavalaiH zrImAn pathi dRSTvA drutaM yayau .
mahiSaizca varAhaizca zArdUlaizca niSevitam . vyapetabhIrgiri zauryAd bhImaseno vyagAhata . kusumAnantagandhaizca tAmrapallavakomalaiH . . yAcyamAna ivAraNye dumairmArutakampitaiH . kRtapadmAJjalipuTA mattaSaT padasevitAH . priyatIrthavanA mArge padminI : samatikrama .
majjmAnamanodRSTiH phulleSu girisAnuSu . draupadIvAkyapAtheyo bhImaH zIghrataraM yayau .
parivRtte ' hani tataH prakIrNahariNe vane . kAJcanairvimalaiH paurdadarza vipulAM nadIm .
haMsakAraNDavayutAM cakravAkopazobhitAm . racitAmiva tasyAdrermAlAM vimalApaGkajAm .
tasyAM nadyAM mahAsattvaH saugandhikavanaM mahat . apazyat prItijananaM bAlArkasadRzadyuti .
tad dRSTvA labdhakAmaH sa manasA pANDunandanaH . vanavAsaparikliSTAM jagAma manasA priyAm .
lomaza uvAca draSTAraH parvatAH sarve nadyaH sapurakAnanAH . tIrthAni caiva zrImanti spRSTaM ca salila karaiH .
parvataM mandaraM divyameSa panthAH prayAsyati . samAhitA nirudvignAH sarve bhavata pANDavAH .
ayaM devanivAso vai gantavyo vo bhaviSyati . RSINAM caiva divyAnAM nivAsaH puNyakarmaNAma .
eSA zivajalA puNyA yAti saumya mahAnadI . badarIprabhavA rAjan devarSigaNasevitA .
eSA vaihAyasainityaM bAlakhilyairmahAtmabhiH . arcitA copayAtA ca gandharvaizca mahAtmabhiH .
atra sAma sma gAyanti sAmagAH puNyani : svanAH . marIciH pulahazcaiva bhRguzcaivAGgirAstathA .
atrAchikaM surazreSTho japate samarudgaNaH . sAdhyAzcaivAzvinau caiva paridhAvanti taM tadA .
candramAH saha sUryeNa jyotISi ca grahaiH saha . ahorAtravibhAgena nadImenAmanuvrajan .
etasyAH salilaM mUrdhni vRSAGkaH paryadhArayat . gaGgAdvAre mahAbhAga yena lokasthitirbhavet .
etAM bhagavatI devIM bhavantaH sarva eva hi . prayatenAtmanA tAta pratigamyAbhivAdata .
tasya tad vacanaM zrutvA lomazasya mahAtmanaH . AkAzagaGgAM prayatAH pANDavAste ' bhyavAdayan .
abhivAdya ca te sarve pANDavAdharmacAriNaH . punaH prayAtAH saMhRSTAH sarvairRSigaNaiH saha .
tato dUrAt prakAzantaM pANDuraM merusaMnibham . dadRzuste narazreSThA vikIrNaM sarvatodizam .
tAn praSTukAmAn vijJAya pANDavAn sa tu lomazaH . uvAca vAkyaM vAkyajJaH zRNudhvaM pANDunandanAH .
etad bikIrNaM suzrImat kailAsazikharopamam . yat pazyasi narazreSTha parvatapratimaM sthitam . etAnyasthIni daityasya narakasya mahAtmanaH . parvatapratimaM bhAti parvataprastarAzritam .
purAtanena devena viSNunA paramAtmanA . daityo vinihatastena surarAjahitaiSiNA .
dazavarSasahasrANi tapastapyan mahAmanAH . aindraM prArthayate sthAnaM tapa : svAdhyAyavikramAt .
tapobalena mahatA bAhuvegabalena ca . nityameva durAdharSodharSayan sa diteH sutaH .
sa tu tasya balaM jJAtvAdharme ca caritavratam . bhayAbhibhUtaH saMvignaH zakra AsIt tadAnagha .
tena saMcintito devo manasA viSNuravyayaH . sarvatragaH prabhuH zrImAnAgatazca sthitau babhau .
RSayazcApi taM sarve tuSTuvuzca divaukasaH . taM dRSTvA jvalamAnazrIbhagavAn havyavAhanaH . naSTatejAH samabhavat tasya tejo ' bhibhartsitaH . taM dRSTvA varadaM devaM viSNuM devagaNezvaram .
prAJjaliH praNato bhUtvA namaskRtya ca vajrabhRt . prAha vAkyaM tatastattvaM yatastasya bhayaM bhavet .
viSNuruvAca jAnAmi te bhayaM zakra daityendrAnnarakAt tataH . aindraM prArthayate sthAnaM tapa : siddhena karmaNA .
so ' hamenaM tava prItyA tapa : siddhamapidhruvam . viyunajmi dehAd devendra muhUrta pratipAlaya .
tasya viSNurmahAtejAH pANinA cetanAM harat . sa papAta tato bhUmau girirAja ivAhataH .
tasyaitadasthisaMghAtaM mAyAvinihatasya vai . idaM dvitIyamaparaM viSNoH karma prakAzate .
naSTA vasumatI kRtsnA pAtAle caiva majjitA . punaruddharitA tena vArAheNaikaGgiNA .
yudhiSThira uvAca bhagavan vistareNemAM kathAM kathaya tattvataH . kathaM tena surezena naSTA vasumatI tadA . yojanAnAM zataM brahman punaruddharitA tadA . kena caiva prakAreNa jagatodharaNIdhruvA . zivA devI mahAbhAgA sarvasasyaprarohiNI . kasya caiva prabhAvAddhi yojanAnAM zataM gatA . kena tad vIryasarvasvaM darzitaM paramAtmanaH . etat sarvaM yathAtattvamicchAmi dvijasattama . zrotuM vistarazaH sarvaM tvaM hi tasya pratizrayaH .
lomaza uvAca yat te ' haM paripRSTo ' smi kathAmetAM yudhiSThira . tat sarvamakhileneha zrUyatAM mama bhASataH . purA kRtayuge tAta vartamAne bhayaMkare . yamatvaM kArayAmAsa AdidevaH purAtanaH .
yamatvaM kurvatastasya devadevasyadhImataH . na tatra mriyate kazcijjAyate vA tathApyuta .
vardhante pakSisaMghAzca tathA pazugaveDakam . gavAMzvaM ca mRgAzcaiva sarve te pizitAzanAH .
tathA puruSazArdUla mAnuSAzca paraMtapa . sahasrazo hyayutazo vardhante salilaM yathA . .
etasmin saMkule tAta vartamAne bhayaMkare . atibhArAd basumatI yojanAnAM zataM gatA .
sA vai vyathatasarvAGgI bhAreNAkrAntacetanA . nArAyaNaM varaM devaM prapannA zaraNaM gatA .
pRthivyuvAca bhagavaMstvatprasAdAddhi tiSTheyaM suciraM tviha . bhAreNAsmi samAkrAntA na zaknomi sma vartimum .
mamemaM bhagavan bhAraM vyapanetuM tvamarhasi . zaraNAgatAsmi te deva prasAdaM kuru me vibho .
tasyAstad vacanaM zrutvA bhagavAnakSaraH prabhuH . provAca vacanaM hRSTaH zravyAkSarasamIritam .
viSNuruvAca na te mahi bhayaM kAryaM bhArArte vasudhAriNi . ahamevaM tathA kurmi yathA laghvI bhaviSyasi .
lomaza uvAca sa tAM visarjayitvA tu vasudhAM zailakuNDalAm . tato varAhaH saMvRtta ekazRGgo mahAdyutiH .
raktAbhyAM nayanAbhyAM tu bhayamutpAdayanniva . dhUmaM ca jvalayallkSmyA tatra deze vyavardhata .
sa gRhItvA vasumatI zRGgeNekena bhAsvatA . yojanAnAM zataM vIra samuddharati so ' kSaraH .
tasyAM coddhAryamANAyAM saMkSobhaH samajAyata . devAH saMkSubhitAH sarve RSayazca tapodhanAH . hAhAbhUtamabhUt sarvaM tridivaM vyoma bhUstadA . na parya vasthitaH kazcid devo vA mAnuSo ' pi vA .
tato brAhmaNAmAsInaM jvalamAnamiva zriyA . devAH sarSigaNAzcaiva upatasthuranekazaH .
upasarpya ca devezaM brahmANaM lokasAkSikam . bhUtvA prAJjalayaH sarve vAkyamuccArayaMstadA . .
lokAH saMkSubhitAH sarve vyAkulaM ca carAcaram . samudrANAM ca saMkSobhastridazeza prakAzate . .
saiSA vasumatI kRtsnA yojanAnAM zataM gatA . kimetad kiM prabhAveNa yenedaM vyAkulaM jagat . AkhyAtu no bhavAzIghraM visaMjJAH smeha sarvazaH .
brahmovAca asurebhyo bhayaM nAsti yuSmAkaM kutracit kvacit . zrUyatAM yatkRteSveSa saMkSobho jAyate ' marAH .
yo ' sau sarvatragaH zrImAnakSarAtmA vyavasthitaH . tasya prabhAvAt saMkSobhastridivasya prakAzate .
yaiSA vasumatI kRtsnA yojanAnAM zataM gatA . samuddhatA punastena viSNunA paramAtmanA . .
tasyAmuddhAryamANAyAM saMkSobhaH samajAyata . evaM bhavanto jAnantu chidyatAM saMzayazca vaH .
devA UcuH kva tad bhUtaM vasumatI samuddharati hRSTavat . taM dezaM bhagavan brUhi tatra yAsyAmahe vayam .
brahmovAca hanta gacchata bhadraM vo nandane pazyata sthitam . eSo ' tra bhagavAzrImAn suparNaH samprakAzate .
vArAheNaiva rUpeNa bhagavaà¥‰llokabhAvanaH . kAlAnala ivAbhAti pRthivItalamuddharam .
etasyorasi suvyaktaM zrIvatsamabhirAjate . pazyadhvaM vibudhAH sarve bhUtametadanAmayam .
lomaza uvAca tato dRSTvA mahAtmAnaM zrutvA cAmantrya cAmarAH . pitAmahaM puraskRtya jagmurdevA yathAgatam .
vaizampAyana uvAca zrutvA tu tAM kathAM sarve pANDavA janamejaya . lomazAdezitenAzu pathA jagmuH prahRSTavat .
zaunaka uvAca yadapRcchattadA rAjA mantriNo janamejayaH . pituH svargagatiM tanme vistareNa punarvada .
sautikavAca zRNu brahmanyathApRcchanmantriNo nRpatistadA . yathA cAkhyAtavantaste nidhanaM tatparIkSitaH .
janamejaya uvAca jAnanti sma bhavantastadyathA vRttaM piturmama . AsIdyathA sa nidhanaM gataH kAle mahAyazAH .
zrutvA bhavatsakAzAddhi piturvRttamazeSataH . kalyANaM pratipatsyAmi viparItaM na jAtucit .
sautiruvAca mantriNo ' thAbruvanvAkyaM pRSTAstena mahAtmanA . sarve dharmavidaH prAjJA rAjAnaM janamejayam .
mantriNaH UcuH zRNu pArthiva yadbhaSe pitustava mahAtmanaH . caritaM pArthivendrasya yathA niSThAM gatazca saH .
dharmAtmA ca mahAtmA ca prajApAla : pitA tava . AsIdiha yathAvRttaH sa mahAtmA zRNuSva tat .
cAturvaryaM svadharmasthaM sa kRtvA paryarakSata . dharmato dharmavidrAjA dharmo vigrahavAniva .
rarakSa pRthivIM devIM zrImAnatulavikramaH . dveSTArastasya naivAsansa ca dveSTi na kaMcana .
samaH sarveSu bhUteSu prajApatirivAbhavat . brAhmaNaH kSatriyA vaizyAH zUdrAzcaiva svakarmasu .
sthitAH sumanaso rAjaMstena rAjJA svadhiSThitAH . vidhavAnAthavikalAnkRpaNAMzca babhAra saH .
sudarzaH sarvabhUtAnAmAsItsoma ivAparaH . tuSTapuSTajanaH zrImAnsatyavAgdRDhavikramaH .
dhanurveda tu ziSyo ' bhUnnRpaH zAradvatasya saH . govindasya priyazcAsItpitA te janamejaya .
lokasya caiva sarvasya priya AsInmahAyazAH . parikSINeSu kuruSu sottarAyAmajIjanat .
parikSidabhavattena saubhadrasyAtmajo balI . rAjadharmArthakuzalo yuktaH sarvaguNairvRtaH .
jitendriyazcAtmavAMzca medhAvI dharmasevitA . SaDvargajinmahAbuddhirnItizAstraviduttamaH .
prajA imAstava pitA SaSTivarSANyapAlayat . tato diSTAntamApannaH sarveSAM duHkhamAvahan . tatastvaM puruSazreSTha dharmeNa pratipedivAn . idaM varSasahasrANi rAjyaM kurukulAgatam . bAla evAbhiSiktastvaM sarvabhUtAnupAlakaH .
janamejaya uvAca nAsminkule jAtu babhUva rAjA yo na prajAnAM priyakRtpriyazca . vizeSataH prekSya pitAmahAnAM vRttaM mahadvRttaparAyaNAnAm .
kathaM nidhanamApannaH pitA mama tathAvidhaH . AcakSadhvaM yathAvanme zrotumicchAmi tattvataH .
sAMtiruvAca evaM saMcoditA rAjJA mantriNaste narAdhipam . UcuH sarve yathAvRttaM rAjJaH priyahitaiSiNaH .
mantriNaH UcuH sa rAjA pRthivIpAlaH sarvazastrabhRtAM varaH . babhUva mRgayAzIlastava rAjan pitA sadA . yathA pANDurmahAbAhurdhanurdharavaro yudhi . asmAsvAsajya sarvANi rAjakAryANyazeSataH .
sa kadAcidvanagato mRgaM vivyAdha patriNA . viddhavA cAnvasaratUrNaM taM mRgaM gahane vane .
padAtibaddhanistriMzastatAyudhakalApavAn . na cAsasAda gahane mRgaM naSTaM pitA tava .
parizrAnto vayasthazca SaSTivarSo jarAnvitaH . kSudhitaH sa mahAraNye dadarza munisattamam .
sa taM papraccha rAjendro muni maunavrate sthitam . na ca kiMciduvAcedaM pRSTo ' pi sa munistadA .
tato rAjA kSucchramArtastaM muni sthANuvasthitam . maunavratadharaM zAntaM sadyo manyuvazaMgataH .
na bubodha ca taM rAjA maunavratadharaM munim . sa taM krodhasamAviSTo dharSayAmAsa te pitA .
mRtaM sarpa dhanuSkoTyA samutkSipya dharAtalAt . tasya zuddhAtmanaH prAdAtskandhe bharatasattama .
na covAca sa medhAvI tamatho sAdhvasAdhu vA . tasthau tathaiva cAkruddhaH sarpa skandhena dhArayan .
saMjaya uvAca evaM duryodhane rAjan garjamAne muhurmuhuH . yudhiSThirasya saMkruddho vAsudevo ' bravIdidam .
yadi nAma hyayaM yuddhe varayet tvAM yudhiSThira . arjunaM nakulaM caiva sahadevamathApi vA . kimidaM sAhasaM rAjaMstvayA vyAhRtamIdRzam . ekameva nihatyAjau bhava rAjA kuruSviti .
na samarthAnahaM manye gadAhastasya saMyuge . etena hi kRtA yogyA varSANIha trayodaza . Ayase puruSe rAjan bhImasenajighAMsayA .
kathaM nAma bhavet kAryamasyAbhirbharatarSabha . sAhasaM kRtavAstvaM tu hyanukrozAnRpottama .
nAnyamasyAnupazyAmi pratiyoddhAramAhave . Rte vRkodarAt pArthAt sa ca nAtikRtazramaH .
tadidaM dyUtamArabdhaM punareva yathA purA . viSamaM zakuMnezcaiva tava caiva vizAmpate .
balI bhImaH samarthazca kRtI rAjA suyodhanaH . balavAn vA kRtI veti kRtI rAjan viziSyate .
so ' yaM rAjaMstvayA zatruH same pathi nivezitaH . nyastazcAtmA suviSame kRcchramApAditA vayam .
ko nu sarvAna vinirjitya zatrUnekena vairiNA . kRcchaprAptena ca tathA hArayed rAjyamAgatam .
paNitvA caikapANena rocayedevamAhavam . na hi pazyAmi taM loke yo ' dya duryodhanaM raNe .
gadAhastaM vijetuM vai zaktaH syAdamaro ' pi hi . na tvaM bhImo na nakulaH sahadevo ' tha phAlgunaH . jetuM nyAyena zaktoH vai kRtI rAjA suyodhanaH .
sa kathaM vadase zatru yudhyasva gadayeti hi . ekaM ca no nihatyAjau bhava rAjeti bhArata .
vRkodaraM samAsAdya saMzayo vai jaye hi naH . nyAyato yudhyamAnAnAM kRtI hyeSa mahAbalaH .
ekaM vAsmAn nihatya tvaM bhava rAjeti vai punaH . nUnaM na rAjyabhAgeSA pANDoH kuntyAzca saMtatiH . atyantavanavAsAya sRSTA bhaikSyAya vA punaH .
bhImasena uvAca madhusUdana mA kArSIrviSAdaM yadunandana . adya pAraM gamiSyAmi vairasya bhRzadurgamam .
ahaM suyodhanaM saMkhye haniSyAmi na saMzayaH . vijayo vai dhruvaH kRSNa dharmarAjasya dRzyate .
adhyardhena guNeneyaM gadA gurutarI mama . na tathA dhArtarASTrasya mA kArSIrmAdhava vyathAm .
ahamenaM hi gadayA saMyuge yoddhamutsahe . bhavantaH prekSakAH sarve mama santu janArdana .
sAmarAnapi lokAMstrIn nAnAzastradharAn yudhi . yodhayeyaM raNe kRSNa kimutAdya suyodhanam .
saMjaya uvAca tathA sambhASamANaM tu vAsudevoM vRkodaram . hRSTaH sampUjayAmAsa vacanaM cedamabravIt . tvAmAzritya mahAbAho dharmarAjo yudhiSThiraH . nihatAriH svakAM dIptA zriyaM prApto na saMzayaH .
tvayA vinihatAH sarve dhRtarASTrasutA raNe . rAjAno rAjaputrAzca nAgAzca vinipAtitAH .
kaliGgA mAgadhAH prAcyA gAndhArAH kuravastathA . tvAmAsAdya mahAyuddhe nihataH pANDunandana .
hatvA duryodhana cApi prayacchorvI sasAgarAm . dharmarAjAya kaunteya yathA viSNuH zacIpateH .
tvAM ca prApya raNe pApo dhArtarASTro vinaDakSyati . tvamasya sakthinI bhaktvA pratijJA pAlayiSyasi .
tatastu sAtyakI yatnena tu sadA pArtha yoddhavyo dhRtarASTrajaH . kRtI ca balavAMzcaiva yuddhazauNDazca nityadA .
rAjan pUjayAmAsa pANDavam .
paJcAlAH pANDaveyAzca dharmarAjapurogamAH . tad vaco bhImasenasya sarva evAbhyapUjayan .
tato bhImabalo bhImo yudhiSThiramathAbravIt . saMjayaiH saha tiSThantaM tapantamiva bhAskaram . ahametena saMgamya saMyuge yoddhamutsahe . na hi zakto raNe jetuM mAmeSa puruSAdhamaH .
adya krodhaM vimokSyAmi nihitaM hRdaye bhRzam . suyodhane dhArtarASTre khANDave ' gnimivArjunaH .
zalyamadyoddhariSyAmi tava pANDava hRcchayam . nihatya gadayA pApamadya rAjan sukhI bhava .
adya kIrtimayIM mAlA pratimokSye tavAnagha . prANAzriyaM ca rAjyaM ca mokSyate ' dya suyodhanaH .
rAjA ca dhRtarASTro ' dya zrutvA putraM mayA hatam . smariSyatyazubhaM karma yat tacchakunibuddhijam .
ityuktvA bharatazreSTho gadAmudyamya vIryavAn . udatiSThata yuddhAya zakro vRtramivAhvayan .
tadAhvAnamamRSyan vai tava putro ' tivIryavAn . pratyupasthita evAzu matto mattamiva dvipam .
gadAhasta tava sutaM yuddhAya samupasthitam . dadRzuH pANDavAH sarve kailAsamiva zRGgiNam .
tamekAkinamAsAdya dhArtarASTra mahAbalam . viyUthamiva mAtaGgaM samahaSyanta pANDavAH .
na sambhramo na ca bhayaM na ca glAnina ca vyathA . AsId duryodhanasyApi sthitaH siMha ivAhave .
samudyatagadaM dRSTvA kailAsamiva zRGgiNam . bhImasenastadA rAjan duryodhanamathAbravIt . rAjJApi dhRtarASTreNa tvayA cAsmAsu yat kRtam . smara tad dRSkRtaM karma yad bhUtaM vAraNAvate .
draupadI ca parikiSTA sabhAmadhye rajasvalA . dyUte yad vijito rAjA zakunebuddhinizcayAt .
yAni cAnyAni duSTAtman pApAni kRtavAnasi . anAga : su ca pArtheSu tasya pazya mahat phalam .
tvakRte nihataH zete zaratalpe mahAyazAH . gAGgeyo bharatazreSThaH sarveSAM naH pitAmahaH .
hato droNazca karNazca hataH zalyaH pratApavAn . vairasta cAdikartA ' sau zakuninihato raNe .
bhrAtaraste hatAH zUrAH putrAzca sahasainikAH . rAjAnazca hatAH zUrAH samareSvanivartinaH .
ete cAnye ca nihatA bahavaH kSatriyarSabhAH . prAtikAmI tathA pApo draupadyAH kezakRddhataH .
avaziSTastvamevaikaH kulamo ' dhamapUruSaH . tvAmapyadya haniSyAmi gadayA nAtra saMzayaH .
adya te ' haM raNe darpaM sarvaM nAzayitA nRpa . rAjyAzAM vipulA rAjan pANDaveSu ca duSkRtam .
duryodhana uvAca kiM katthitena bahunA yuddhyasvAdya mayA saha . adya te ' haM vineSyAmi yuddhazraddhAM vRkodara .
kiM na pazyami mAM pApa gadAyuddhe vyavasthitam . himavacchikharAkArAM pragRhya mahatIM gadAm .
gadinaM ko ' dha mAM pApa hantumutsahate ripuH . nyAyato yuddhyamAnazca deveSvapi purandaraH .
mA vRthA garja kaunteya zAradAbhramivAjalam . darzayasva balaM yuddhe yAvat tat te ' dya vidyate .
tasya tad vacan zrutvA pANDavAH sahasaMjayAH . sarve sampUjayAmAsustadvaco vijigISavaH .
unmattamiva mAtaGgaM talazabdena mAnavAH . bhUyaH saharSayAmAsU rAjan duryodhanaM nRpam .
bRMhanti kuJjarAstatra hayA dveSanti cAsakRt . zastrANi sampradIpyante pANDavAnAM jayaiSiNAm .
vaizampAyana uvAca dhanaMjayotsukAnAM tu bhrAtRNAM kRSNayA saha . zrutvA vAkyAni vimanAdharmarAjo ' pyajAyat .
athApazyanmahAtmAnaM devarSi tatra nAradam . dIpyamAnaM zriyA brAhmayA hutArciSamivAnalam .
tamAgatamabhiprekSya bhrAtRbhiH sahadharmarAT . pratyutthAya yathAnyAyaM pUjAM cakre mahAtmane .
sa taiH parivRtaH zrImAn bhrAtRbhiH kurusattamaH . vibabhAvatidIptaujA devairiva zatakratuH .
yathA ca vedAn sAvitrI yAjJasenI tathA patIn . na jahaudharmataH pArthAn merumarkaprabhA yathA .
pratigRhya ca tAM pUjAM nArado bhagavAnRSiH . AzvAsayad dharmasutaM yuktarUpamivAnagha .
uvAca ca mahAtmAnaMdharmarAja yudhiSThiram . brUhidharmabhRtAM zreSTha kenArthaH kiM dadAni te .
athadharmasutA rAjA praNamya bhrAtRbhiH saha . uvAca prAJjalirbhUtvA nAradaM devasammitam .
tvayi tuSTe mahAbhAga sarvalokAbhipUjite . kRtamityeva manye ' haM prasAdAt tava suvrata .
yadi tvahamanugrAhyo bhrAtRbhiH sahito ' nagha . saMdehaM me munizreSTha tattvatazchettumarhasi .
pradakSiNAM yaH kurute pRthivIM tIrthatatparaH . kiM phalaM tasya kAtsyena tadbhavAn vaktumarhati .
nArada uvAca zRNu rAjannavahito yathA bhISmeNadhImatA . pulastyasya sakAzAd vai sarvametadupazrutam .
purA bhAgIrathItIre bhISmodharmabhRtAM varaH . pitryaM vrataM samAsthAya nyavasanmunibhiH saha . zubhe deze tathA rAjan puNye devarSisevite . gaGgAdvAre mahAbhAga devagandharvasevite .
sa pitRRstarpayAmAsa devAMzca paramadyutiH . RSIMzca tarpayAmAsa vidhidRSTena karmaNA .
kasyacit tvatha kAlasya japanneva mahAyazAH . dadarzAdbhutasaMkAzaM pulastyamRSisattamAm .
sa taM dRSTvogratapasaM dIpyamAnamiva zriyA . praharSamatulaM lebhe vismayaM paramaM yayau .
upasthitaM mahAbhAgaM pUjayAmAsa bhAratA bhISmodharmabhRtAM zreSTho vidhidRSTena karmaNA .
zirasA cArghyamAdAya zuciH prayatamAnasaH . nAma saMkIrtayAmAsa tasmin brahmarSisattame .
bhISmo ' hamasmi bhadraM te dAso ' smi tava suvrata . tava saMdarzanAdeva mukto ' haM sarvakilbiSaiH .
evamuktvA mahArAja bhISmodharmabhRtAM paraH . vAgyataH prAJjalirbhUtvA tRSNImAsId yudhiSThira .
taM dRSTvA niyamenAtha svAdhyAyAmnAyakarzitam . bhISmaM kurukulazreSTha muniH prItamanAbhavat .
gAlava uvAca mahAvIryo mahIpAla : kAzInAmIzvaraH prabhuH . divodAsa iti khyAto bhaimaseninarAdhipaH .
tatra gacchAvahe bhadre zanairAgaccha mA zucaH . dhArmikaH saMyame yuktaH satye caiva janezvaraH .
nArada uvAca tamupAgamya sa muniyA/yatastena satkRtaH . gAlava : prasavasyArthaM taM nRpaM pratyacodayat .
divodAsa uvAca zrutametanmayA pUrvaM kimuktvA vistaraM dvija . kAkSito hi mayaiSo ' rthaH zrutvaiva dvijasattama .
etacca me bahumataM yadutsRjya narAdhipAn . mAmevamupayAto ' si bhAvi caitadasaMzayam .
sa eva vibhavo ' smAkamazvAnAmapi gAlava . ahamepyekamevAsyAM janayiSyAmi pArthivam .
tathetyuktvA dvijazreSThaH prAdAt kanyAM mahIpateH . vidhipUrvAM ca tAM rAjA kanyAM pratigRhItavAn .
reme sa tasyAM rAjarSiH prabhAvatyAM yathA raviH . svAhAyAM ca yathA vahniryathA zacyAM ca vAsavaH .
yathA candrazca rohiNyAM yathA dhUmorNayA yamaH . varuNazca yathA gauryAM yathA cA dhanezvaraH .
yathA nArAyaNo lakSyAM jAhravyAM ca yathodadhiH . yathA rudrazca rudrANyAM yatA vedyAM pitAmahaH .
adRzyantyAM ca vAsiSTho vasiSThazcAkSamAlayA . cyavanazca sukanyAyAM pulastyaH saMdhyayA yathA .
agastyazcApi vaida( sAvitryAM satyavAn yathA . yathA bhRguH pulomAyAmadityAM kazyapo yathA . .
reNukAyAM yathA ' ' rcIko haimavatyAM ca kauzikaH . bRhaspatizca tArAyAM zukrazca zataparvaNA .
yathA bhUmyAM bhUmipatisarvazyAM ca purUravAH . RcIkaH satyavatyAM ca sarasvatyAM yathA manuH .
zakuntalAyAM duSyanto dhRtyAM dharmazca zAzvataH . damayantyAM nalazcaiva satyavatyAM ca nAradaH .
jaratkArurjaratkArvAM pulastyazca pratIcyayA . menakAyAM yathorNAyustumbuszcaiva rambhayA .
vAsukiH zatazIrSAyAM kumAryAM ca dhanaMjayaH . vaidehyAM ca yathA rAmo rukmiNyAM ca janArdanaH .
tathA tu ramamANasya divodAsasya bhUpateH . mAdhavI janayAmAsa putramekaM pratardanam .
athAjagAma bhagavAn divodAsaM sa gAlavaH . samaye samanuprApte vacanaM cedamabravIt .
niryAtayatu me kanyAM bhavAMstiSThantu vAjinaH . yAvadanyatra gacchAmi zulkArthaM pRthivIpate .
divodAso ' tha dharmAtmA samaye gAlavasya tAm . kanyAM niryAtayAmAsa sthitaH satye mahIpatiH .
bRhannalovAca yanmAM pUrvamihApRcchaH zatrusenApahAriNam . gANDIvametat pArthasya lokeSu viditaM dhanuH .
sarvAyudhamahAmAtraM zAtakumbhapariSkRtam . etat tadarjunasyAsId gANDIvaM paramAyudham .
yat tacchatasahasreNa sammitaM rASTravarddhanam . yena devAn manuSyAMzca pArtho vijayate mRdhe .
citramuccAvacaivarNaiH zlakSNamAyatamavraNam . devadAnavagandharvaiH pUjitaM zAzvatIH samAH .
etad varSasahasraM tu brahmA pUrvamadhArayat . tato ' nantaramevAtha prajApatiradhArayat . trINi paJcazataM caiva zakro ' zIti ca paJca ca . somaH paJcazataM rAjA tathaiva varuNaH zatam .
pArthaH paJca ca SaSTiM ca varSANi zvetavAhanaH . mahAvIryaM mahAdivyametat tad dhanuruttamam .
etat pArthamanuprAptaM varuNAccArudarzanam . pUjitaM suramatryeSu bibharti paramaM vapuH .
supArzva bhImasenasya jAtarUpagrahaM dhanuH . yena pArtho ' jayat kRtsnAM dizaM prAcI paraMtapaH .
indragopakacitraM ca yadetaccArudarzanam . rAjJo yudhiSThirasyaitad vairATe dhanuruttamam .
sUryA yasmiMstu sauvarNAH prakAzante prakAzinaH . tejasA prajvalanto vai nakulasyaitadAyudham .
zalabhA yatra sauvarNAstapanIya vicitritAH . etanmAdrIsutasyApi sahadevasya kArmukam .
ye tvime kSurasaMkAzAH sahasrA lomavAhinaH . ete ' rjunasya vairATe zarAH sarpaviSopamAH .
ete jvalantaH saMgrAme tejasA zIghragAminaH . bhavanti vIrasyAkSayyA vyUhataH samare ripUn . .
ye ceme pRthavo dIrghAzcandrabimbArdhadarzanAH . ete bhImasya nizitA ripukSayakarAH zarAH .
hAridravarNA ye tvete hemapuGkhAH zilAzitAH . nakulasya kalApo ' yaM paJcazArdUlalakSaNaH .
yenAsau vyajayat kRtsnA pratIcI dizamAhave . kalApo hyeSa tasyAsInmAdrIputrasya dhImataH .
ye tvime bhAskarAkArAH sarvapArasavAH zarAH . ete citrakriyopetAH : sahadevasya dhImataH .
ye tvime nizitAH pItAH pRthavo dIghavAsasaH . hemapuGkhAstriparvANo rAjJa ete mahAzarAH .
yastvayaM sAyako dIrghaH zilIpRSThaH zilImukhaH . arjunasyaiSa saMgrAme gurubhArasaho dRDhaH .
vaiyAghrakozaH sumahAn bhImasenasya sAyakaH . gurubhArasaho divyaH zAtravANAM bhayaMkaraH .
suphalacitrakozazca hematsaruranuttamaH . nistriMzaH kauravasyaiSa dharmarAjasya dhImataH .
yastu pAJcanakhe koze nihitAzcitrayodhane . nakulasyaiSa nistriMzo gurubhArasaho dRDhaH .
yastvayaM vipulaH khaDgo gavye koze samarpitaH sahadevasya viddhyenaM sarvabhArasahaM dRDham .
janamejaya uvAca uttaGkasya varaM dattvA govindo dvijasattama . ata UrdhvaM mahAbAhuH kiM cakAra mahAyazAH .
vaizampAyana uvAca uttaGkasya varaM dattvA prAyAt sAtyakinA saha . dvArakAmeva govindaH zIghravegairmahAhayaiH .
sarAMsi saritazcaiva vanAni ca girIstathA . atikramyAsasAdAtha ramyAM dvAravatIM purIm .
vartamAne mahArAja mahe raivatakasya ca . upAyAt puNDarIkAkSo yuyudhAnAnupastadA .
alaMkRtastu sa giri nArUpairvicitritaiH . babhau ratnamayaiH kozaiH saMvRtaH puruSarSabha .
kAJcanasragbhiragryAbhiH sumanobhistathaiva ca . vAsobhizca mahAzailaH kalpavRkSaistathaiva ca . dIpavRkSaizca sauvarNairabhIkSNamupazobhitaH . guhAnirjharadezeSu divAbhUto babhUva ha .
patAkAbhirvicitrAbhiH saghaNTAbhiH samantataH . pumbhiH strIbhizca saMghuSTaH pragIta iva cAbhavat .
atIva prekSaNIyo ' bhUnmerurmunigaNairiva . mattAnAM hRSTarUpANAM strINAM puMsAM ca bhArata . gAyatAM parvatendrasya divaspRgiva niHsvanaH . pramattamatta sammattakSveDitotkruSTasaMkulaH .
tathA kilakilAzabdairbhUdharo ' bhUnmanoharaH . vipaNApaNavAn ramyo bhakSyabhojyavihAravAn .
vastramAlyotkarayuto vINAveNumRdaGgavAn . surAmairaiyamizreNa bhakSyabhojyena caiva ha .
dInAndhakRpaNAdibhyo dIyamAnena cAnizam . babhau paramakalyANo mahastasya mahAgireH .
puNyAvasathavAn vIra puNyakRdbhirniSevitaH . vihAro vRSNivIrANAM mahe raivatakasya ha .
sa nago vezmasaMkIrNo devaloka ivAbabhau . tadA ca kRSNa sAMnidhyamAsAdya bharatarSabha . zakrasadmapratIkAzo babhUva sa hi zailarAT . tataH sampUjyamAnaH sa viveza bhavanaM zubham . govindaH sAtyakizcaiva jagAma bhavanaM svakam . viveza ca prahRSTAtmA cirakAlapravAsataH . kRtvA nasukaraM karma dAnaveSviva vAsavaH . upAyAntaM tu vArSNeyaM bhojavRSNyandhakAstathA . . abhyagacchan mahAtmAnaM devA iva zatakratum .
sa tAnabhyarcya medhAvI pRSTvA ca kuzalaM tadA . abhyavAdayata prItaH pitaraM mAtaraM tadA .
tAbhyAM sa sampariSvaktaH sAntvitazca mahAbhujaH . upopaviSTaiH sarvaistairvRSNibhiH parivAritaH .
sa vizrAnto mahAtejAH kRtapAdAvanejanaH . kathayAmAsa tatsarvaM pRSTaH pitrA mahAhavam .
vaizampAyana uvAca tato duryodhano rAjA sarvAH prakRtayaH zanaiH . arthamAnapradAnAbhyAM saMjahAra sahAnujaH . dhRtarASTraprayuktAste kecit kuzalamantriNaH . kathayAMcakrire ramyaM nagaraM vAraNAvatam . ayaM samAjaH sumahAn ramaNIyatamo bhuvi . upasthitaH pazupatenagare vAraNAvate .
sarvaratnasamAkIrNe puMsAM deze manorame . ityevaM dhRtarASTrasya vacanAccakrire kathAH .
kathyamAne tathA ramye nagare vAraNAvate . gamane pANDuputrANAM jajJe tatra matirnupa .
yadA tvamanyata nRpo jAtakautUhalA iti . uvAcaitAnetya tadA pANDavAnambikAsutaH .
mamaite puruSA nityaM kathayanti punaH punaH . ramaNIyatamaM loke nagaraM vAraNAvatam .
te tAtA yadi manyadhvamutsavaM vAraNAvate . sagaNAH sAnvayAzcaiva viharadhvaM yathAmarAH .
brAhmaNebhyazca ratnAni gAyakebhyazca sarvazaH . prayacchadhvaM yathAkAmaM devA iva suvarcasaH . kaMcit kAlaM vihRtyaivamanubhUya parAM mudam . idaM vai hAstinapuraM sukhinaH punareSyata .
vaizampAyana uvAca dhRtarASTrasya taM kAmamanubudhya yudhiSThiraH . AtmanazcAsahAyatvaM tatheti pratyuvAca tam .
tato bhISmaM zAntanavaM viduraM ca mahAmatim . droNaM ca bAhnikaM caiva somadattaM ca kauravam . kRpamAcAryaputraM ca bhUrizravasameva ca . mAnyAnanyAnamAtyAMzca brAhmaNAMzca tapodhanAn . purohitAMzca paurAMzca gAndhArI ca yazasvinIm . yudhiSThiraH zanairdIna uvAcedaM vacastadA .
ramaNIye janAkIrNe nagare vAraNAvate . sagaNAstatra yAsyAmo dhRtarASTrasya zAsanAt .
prasannamanasaH sarve puNyA vAco vimuJcata . AzIbhibRMhitAnasmAn na pApaM prasahiSyate .
evamuktAstu te sarve pANDuputreNa kauravAH . prasannavadanA bhUtvA te ' nvavartanta pANDavAn . svastyastu vaH pathi sadA bhUtebhyazcaiva sarvazaH . mA ca vo ' stvazubhaM kiMcit sarvazaH pANDunandanAH .18 .
tataH kRtasvastyayanA rAjyalambhAya pArthivAH . kRtvA sarvANi kAryANi prayayurvAraNAvatam .
nArada uvAca bandhutvAdathavA sakhyAcchAlmale nAtra saMzayaH . pAlayatyeva satataM bhImaH sarvatrago ' nilaH .
nyagbhAvaM paramaM vAyoH zAlmale tvamupAgataH . tavAhamasmIti sadA yena rakSati mArutaH .
na taM pazyAmyahaM vRkSaM parvataM vezma cedRzam . yaM na vAyubalAd bhagnaM pRthivyAmiti me matiH .
tvaM punaH kAraNainaM rakSyase zAlmale yathA . vAyunA saparIvArastena tiSThasyasaMzayam .
zAlmaliruvAca na me vAyuH sakhA brahmanna bandhurna ca suhRt . parameSThI tathA naiva yena rakSati vAnilaH . me
mama tejo balaM bhImaM vAyorapi hi nArada . kalAmaSTAdazI prANairna me prApnoti mArutaH .
Agacchan paruSo vAyurmayA viSTambhito balAt . bhaJjan dumAn parvatAMzca yaccAnyadapi kiMcana .
sa mayA bahuzo bhagnaH prabhaJjan vai prabhaJjanaH . tasmAnna bibhye devarSe kruddhAdapi samIraNAt .
nArada uvAca zAlmale viparItaM te darzanaM nAtra saMzayaH . na hi vAyorbalenAsti bhUtaM tulyabalaM kvacit .
indro yamo vaizravaNo varuNazca jalezvaraH . naite ' pi tulyA marutaH kiM punastvaM vanaspate .
yacca kiMcidiha prANI ceSTate zAlmale bhuvi . sarvatra bhagavAn vAyuzceSTAprANakaraH prabhuH .
eSa cezyate samyak prANinaH samyagAyataH . asamyagAyato bhUyazceSTate vikRtaM nRSu .
sa tvamevaMvidhaM vAyuM sarvasattvabhRtAM varam . na pUjayasi pUjyaM taM kimanyad buddhilAghavAt .
asArazcApi durmedhAH kevalaM bahu bhASase . krodhAdibhiravacchanno mithyA vadasi zAlmale .
mama roSaH samutpannastvayyevaM samprabhASati . bravImyeSa svayaM vAyostava durbhASitaM bahu .
candanaiH syandanaiH zAlaiH saralairdevadArubhiH . vetasairdhanvanaizcApi ye cAnye balavattarAH .
taizcApi naivaM durbuddhe kSipto vAyuH kRtAtmabhiH . te ' pi jAnanti vAyozca balamAtmana eva ca . tasmAt taM vai namasyanti zvasanaM tarusattamAH .
tvaM tu mohAnna jAnISe vAyorbalamanantakam . evaM tasmAd gamiSyAmi sakAzaM mAtarizvanaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca pravizantaM mahArAja sUtAstuSTuvuracyutam . janAzcApi maheSvAsaM tuSTuvU rAjasattama .
lAjaizcandanacUrNaizca vikIrya ca janAstataH . UcurdiSTyA nRpAvighnaH samApto ' yaM kratustava .
apare tvabruvaMstatra vAtikAstaM mahIpatim . yudhiSThirasya yajJena na samo hyeSa te kratuH .
naiva tasya kratoreSa kalAmarhati SoDazIm . evaM tatrAnuvan kecid vAtikAstaM janezvaram .
suhRdastvabruvaMstatra ati sarvAnayaM kratuH . yayAtinahuSazcApi mAndhAtA bharatastathA . kratumenaM samAhatya pUtAH sarve divaM gatAH .
etA vAcaH zubhAH zRNvan suhRdAM bharatarSabha . praviveza puraM hRSTaH svavezma ca narAdhipaH .
abhivAdya tataH pAdau mAtApitrovizAmpate . . bhISmadroNakRpAdInAM vidurasya ca dhImataH . abhivAditaH kanIyobhirdhAtRbhirdhAtanandanaH .
niSasAdAsane mukhya bhrAtRbhiH parivAritaH . tamutthAya pahArAjaM sUtaputro ' bravId vacaH .
diSTyA te bharatazreSTha samApto ' yaM mahAkratuH . hateSu yudhi pArtheSu rAjasUye tathA tvayA . Ahate ' haM narazreSTha tvAM sabhAjayitA punaH .
tamabravInmahArAjo dhArtarASTro mahAyazAH . satyametat tvayoktaM hi pANDaveSu durAtmasu . nihateSu narazreSTha prApte cApi mahAkratau . rAjasUye punarvIra tvamevaM vardhayiSyasi .
evamuktvA mahArAja karNamAzliSya bhArata . . rAjasUyaM kratuzreSThaM cintayAmAsa kauravaH .
so ' bravIt kauravAMzcApi pArzvasthAn nRpasattamaH . kadA tu taM kratuvaraM rAjasUyaM mahAdhanam . nihatya pANDavAn sarvAnAhariSyAmi kauravAH .
tamabravIt tadA karNaH zRNu me rAjakuJjara . pAdau na dhAvaye tAvad yAvanna nihato ' rjunaH . kIlAlajaM na khAdeyaM kariSye cAsuravratam . nAstIti naiva vakSyAmi yAcito yena kenacit .
athotkruSTaM maheSvAsairdhArtarASTrairmahArathaiH . pratijJAte phAlgunasya vadhe karNena saMyuge .
vijitAMzcApyamanyanta pANDavAn dhRtarASTrajAH . duryodhano ' pi rAjendra visRjya narapuGgavAn . praviveza gRhaM zrImAn yathA caitrarathaM prabhuH . te ' pi sarve maheSvAsA jagmurvezmAni bhArata .
pANDavAzca maheSvAsA dUtavAkyapracoditAH . cintayantastamevArthaM nAlabhanta sukhaM kvacit .
bhUyazca cArai rAjendra pravRttirupapAditA . pratijJA sUtaputrasya vijayasya vadhaM prati .
etacchrutvA dharmasutaH samudvigno narAdhipa . abhedyakavacaM matvA karNamadbhutavikramam . anusmaraMzca saMklezAn na zAntimupayAti saH .
tasya cintAparItasya buddhirjajJe mahAtmanaH . bahuvyAlamRgAkIrNaM tyaktuM dvaitavanaM vanam .
dhArtarASTro ' pi nRpatiH prazazAsa vasundharAm . bhrAtRbhiH sahito vIrairbhISmadroNakRpaistathA . saGgamya sUtaputreNa karNenAhavazobhinA .
duryodhana : priye nityaM vartamAno mahIbhRtAm . pUjayAmAsa viprendrAn kratubhirbhUridakSiNaiH .
bhrAtRNAM ca priyaM rAjan sa cakAra paraMtapaH . nizcitya manasA vIro dattabhuktaphalaM dhanam .
zalya uvAca tataH zakraH stUyamAno gandharvapsarasAM gaNaiH . airAvataM samAruhya dvipendraM lakSaNairyutam . pAvakaH sumahAtejA maharSizca bRhaspatiH . yamazca varuNazcaiva kubezca dhanezvaraH . sarvairdevaiH parivRtaH zakro vRtraniSUdanaH . gandharvairapsarobhizca yAtastribhuvanaM prabhuH .
sa sametya mahendrANyA devarAjaH zatakratuH . mudA paramayA yuktaH pAlayAmAsa devarAT .
tataH sa bhagavAMstatra aGgirAH samadRzyatA atharvavedamantraizca devendraM samapUjayat .
tatastu bhagavAnindraH saMhRSTaH samapadyata . varaM ca pradadau tasmai atharvAGgirase tadA .
atharvAGgiraso nAma vedo ' smin vai bhaviSyati . udAharaNametaddhi yakSabhAgaM ca lapsyase .
evaM sampUjya bhagavAnatharvAGgirasaM tadA . vyasarjayanmahArAja devarAjaH zatakratuH .
sampUjya sarvAstridazAnRSIzcApi tapodhanAn . indraH pramudito rAjan dharmeNApAlayat prajAH .
evaM duHkhamanuprAptamindreNa saha bhAryayA . ajJAtavAsazca kRtaH zatrUNAM vadhakAjhyA .
nAtra manyustvayA kAryo yat kliSTo ' si mahAvane . draupadyA saha rAjendra bhrAtRbhizca mahAtmabhiH .
evaM tvamapi rAjendra rAjyaM prApsyasi bhAratA vRtraM hatvA yathA prAptaH zakraH kauravanandana .
durAcArazca nahuSo brahmaviT pApacetanaH . agastyazApAbhihato vinaSTaH zAzvatI : samAH .
evaM tava durAtmAnaH zatravaH zatrusUdan . kSipraM nAzaM gamiSyanti karNaduryodhanAdayaH .
tataH sAgaraparyantAM bhokSyase medinImimAm . bhrAtRbhiH sahito vIra draupadyA ca sahAnayA .
upAkhyAnamidaM zakravijayaM vedasammitam . rAjJA vyUDheSvanIkeSu zrotavyaM jayamicchatA .
tasmAt saMzrAvayAmi tvAM vijayaM jayatAM vara . saMstUyamAnA vardhante mahAtmAno yudhiSThira .
kSatriyANAmabhAvo ' yaM yudhiSThira mahAtmanAm . duryodhanAparAdhena bhImArjunabalena ca .
AkhyAnamindravijayaM ya idaM niyataH paThet . dhUtapApmA jitasvargaH paratreha ca modate .
na cArijaM bhayaM tasya nAputro vA bhavennaraH . nApadaM prApnuyAt kAMcidaM dIrghamAyuzca vindati . sarvatra jayamApnoti na kadAcit parAjayam .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamAzvAsito rAjA zalyena bharatarSabha . pUjayAmAsa vidhivacchalyaM dharmabhRtAM varaH .
zrutvA tu zalyavacanaM kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . pratyuvAca mahAbAhurmadrarAjamidaM vacaH .
bhavAn karNasya sArathyaM kariSyati na saMzayaH . tatra tejovadhaH kAryaH karNasyArjunasaMstavaH .
zalya uvAca evametat kariSyAmi yathA mAM samprabhASase . yaccAnyadapi zakSyAmi tat kariSyAmyahaM tava . .
vaizampAyana uvAca tatastvAmantrya kaunteyAJchalyo madrAdhipastadA . jagAma sabalaH zrImAn duryodhanamariMdama .
saMjaya uvAca tamabravIda vAsudevo rathastho rAdheya diSTyA smarasIha dharmam . prAyeNa nIcA vyamaneSu magnA nindati daivaM kukRtaM na tu svam .
mAnAyayestvaM ca suyodhanazca . duHzAsanaH zakuniH saubalazca na te karNa pratyabhAttatra dharma : .
yadA sabhAyAM rAjAnamanakSajJaM yudhiSThiram . ajaiSIcchakuni nAt kva te dharmastadA gataH .
vanavAse vyatIte ca karNa varSe trayodaze . na prayacchasi yad rAjyaM kva te dharmastadA gataH .
yad bhImasenaMna sapaizca viSayuktaizca bhojanaiH . Acarat tvanmate rAjA kva te dharmastadA gataH .
yad vAraNAvate pArthAna suptAJjatugRhe tadA . AdIpayastvaM rAdheya kva te dharmastadA gataH .
yadA rajasvalAM kRSNAM duHzAsanavaze sthitAm . sabhAyAMna prAhasaH karNa kva te dharmastadA gataH .
tadanAryaiH purA kRSNAM klizyamAnAmanAgasam . upaprekSasi rAdheya kva te dharmastadA gataH .
vinaSTAH pANDavaH kRSNe zAzvataM narakaM gatA . patimanyaM vRNISveti vadaMstvaM gajasAminIm . upaprekSasi rAdheya kva te dharmastadA gataH .
rAjyalubdhaH punaH karNa samAvyathasi pANDavAn . yadA zakunimAzritya kka te dharmastadA gataH .
yadAbhimanyuM bahavo yudde jaghnurmahArathAH . parivArya raNe bAlaM kka te dharmastadA gataH .
yadyeSa dharmastatra na vidyate hi kiM sarvathA tAluvizoSaNena . adyeha dhANi vidhatsva sUta tathApi jIvana vimokSyase hi .
nalo hyakSairnirjitaH puSkareNa punaryazo rAjyamavApa vIryAt . sarveH sametAH parivRttalobhAH . nihatya zUtran samare pravRddhAn sasomakA rAjyamavApnuyuste . tathA gatA dhArtarASTrA vinAzaM dharmAbhiguptaiH satataM nRsiMhaH .
saMjaya uvAca evamuktastadA karNo vAsudevena bhArata . lajjayAvanato bhUtvA nottaraM kiJciduktavAn .
krodhAt prasphuramANaiSTo dhanurudyamya bhArata . yodhayAmAsa vai pArtha mahAvegaparAkramaH .
tato ' bravId vAsudeva : phAlgunaM pururSabham . divyAstreNaiva nirbhidya pAtayasva mahAbala .
evamuktastu devena krodhamAgAtadArjunaH . manyumabhyAvizad ghoraM smRtvA tattu dhanaMjayaH .
tasya kruddhasya sarvebhyaH srotobhyastejaso ' tiSaH . prAdurAsaMstadA rAjaMstadadbhutamivAbhavat .
tat samIkSya tataH karNo brahmAstreNa dhanaMjayam . abhyavarSat punaryanamakarod rathasarjane .
brahmAstreNaiva taM pArtho vavarSa zaravRSTibhiH . tadastramastreNAvArya prajahAra ca pANDavaH .
tato ' nyadastraM kaunteyo dayitaM jAtavedasaH . mumoca karNamuddizya tat prajajvAla tejasA .
vAruNena tataH karNaH zamayAmAsa pAvakam . jImUtaizca dizaH sarvAzcake timiradurdinAH .
pANDevayastvasambhrAto vAyavyAstreNa vIryavAn . apovAha tadAbhrANi rAdheyasya prapazyataH .
tataH zaraM mahAghoraM jvalantamiva pAvakam . Adade pANDuputrasya sUtaputro jighAMsayAM .
yojyamAne tatastasmin bANe dhanuSi pUjite . cacAla pRthivI rAjan sazailavanakAnanA .
vavau sazarkaro vAyurdizazca rajasA vRtAH . hAhAkArazca saMjajJe surANAM divi bhArata .
tamiSu saMdhitaM dRSTvA sUtapatreNa mAriSa . viSAdaM paramaM jagmuH pANDavA dInacetasaH .
sa sAyakaH karNabhujapramuktaH zakrAzaniprakhyaruciH zitAgraH . bhujAntaraM prApya dhanaMjayasya viveza valmIkamivoragottamaH .
sa gADhaviddhaH samare mahAtmA vighUrNamAnaH zlathahastagANDivaH . cacAla bIbhatsuramitramardanaH kSiteH prakampe ca yathA calottamaH .
tadantaraM prApya vRSo mahAratho rathAGgamurvIgatamujjihISuH . rathAdavalputya nigRhya dordhyA zazAka daivAna mahAbalo ' pi .
tataH kirITI pratilabhya saMjJA jagrAha bANaM yamadaNDakalpam . tato ' rjunaH prAJjalikaM mahAtmA tato ' bravId vAsudevo ' pi pArtham . chinthyasya mUrdhAnamareH zareNa na yAvadArohati vai rathaM vRSaH .
stata : zaraM prajvalitaM pragRhya . jaghAna kakSAmamalArkavarNA mahArathe rathacakre vimagne .
taM hastikakSApravahaM ca ketuM suvarNamuktAmaNivajrapRSTham . jJAnaprakarSottamazilpiyuktaiH kRtaM surUpaM tapanIyacitram .
mamitravitrAsanamIDayarUpam . vikhyAtamAdityasamaM sma loke tviSA samaM pAvakabhAnucandraiH .
tataH kSurapreNa susaMzitena suvarNapuDvena hutAgnivarcasA . zriyA jvalantaM dhvajamunmamAtha mahArathasyAdhistheH kirITI .
yazazca darpazca tathA priyANi sarvANi kAryANi ca tena ketunA . sAkaM kurUNAM hRdayAni cApatan babhUva hAheti ca niHsvano mahAn .
dRSTvA dhvajaM pAtitamAzukAriNA kurupravIreNa nikRttamAhave . nAzaMsire sUtaputrasya sarve jayaM tadA bhArata ye tvadIyA : : .
atha tvaran karNavadhAya pArtho mahendravajrAnaladaNDasaMnibham . Adatta cAthAJjalikaM niSaGgAt sahasrarazmeriva razmimuttamam .
marmacchidaM zoNitamAMsadigdhaM vaizvAnarArkapratimaM mahArham . narAzvanAgAsuharaM tryaratna SaDvAjamaJjogatimugravegam . sahasranetrAzatitulyavIrya kAlAnalaM vyAttamivAtighoram . pinAkanArANacakrasaMnibhaM bhayaGkaraM prANabhRtAM vinAzanam .
jagrAha pArthaH sa zaraM prahRSTo yo devasaGgharapi durnivAryaH . sampUjito yaH satataM mahAtmA devAsurAn yo vijayenmaheSuH .
taM vai pramRSTaM prasamIkSya yuddhe cacAla sarvaM sacarAcaraM jagat . stamudyataM prekSya mahAhaveSum .
tatastu taM vai zaramaprameyaM gANDIvadhanvA dhanuSi vyayojayat . yuktavA mahAstreNa pareNa cApaM vikRSya gANDIvamuvAca satvaram .
ayaM mahAstraprahito mahAzaraH zarIrahavAsuharazca durhadaH . tapo ' sti taptaM guravazca toSitA payA yadISTaM suhRdAM zrutaM tathA . anena satyena nihantvayaM zaraH susaMhitaH karNamariM mamorjitam . ityUcivAMstaM pramumoca bANaM dhanaMjayaH karNavadhAya ghoram .
kRtyAmatharrAGgirasImivogrAM dIptAmasahyAM yudhi mRtyunApi . bruvana kirITI tamatiprahRSTo hyayaM zaro me vijayAvahostu . jighAMsurarkandusamaprabhAvaH karNa mayAsto nayatAM yamAya .
teneSuvaryeNa kirITamAlI prahRSTarUpo vijayAvahena . jighAMsurarkendusamaprabheNa cakre viSaktaM ripumAtatAyI .
tathA vimukto balinArkatejAH prajvAlayAmAsa dizo nabhazca . tato ' rjunastasya ziro jahAra vRtrasya vajreNa yathA mahendraH .
stadA mahAstrapratimantritena . pAtho ' parAhne zira uccakarta vaikartanasyAtha mahendrasUnuH .
mathAsya kAyo nipapAta pazcAt . tadudyatAdityasamAnatejasaM zarannabhomadhyagabhAskaropamam . varAGgamukmapataJcamUmukhe divAkaro ' stAdivaraktamaNDalaH .
tato ' sya dehaM satataM sukhocitaM surUpamatyarthamudArakarmamaH . pareNa kRcchreNa ziraH samatyajad gRhaM mahardhIva susaGgamIzvaraH .
zarairvibhinnaM vyasu tat suvarcasaH papAta karNasya zarIramucchritam . stravavraNaM gairikatoyavistravaM gireryathA vajrahataM mahAziraH . dehAca karNasya nipAtitasya tejaH sUrya khaM vitatyAviveza .
tadadbhutaM sarvamanuSyayodhAH saMdRSTavanto nihate sma karNe . dRSTvA karNaM pAtitaM phAlgunana .
tathaiva kRSNazca danaMjayazca hRSTau yamau dadhmaturvArijAtau . taM somakAH prekSya hataM zayAnaM sainyaiH sArdha siMhanAdAn pracakruH .
tUryANi saMjaghnuratIva hRSTA vAsAMsi caivAdudhuvarbhujAMzca . saMvardhayantazca narendra yodhAH pArthaM samAjagmuratIva hRSTAH . nanyonyamAzliSya nadanta UcuH . dRSTvA tu karNa bhuvi vA vipannaM kRtaM rathAt sAyakairarjunasya .
mahAnilenAdimirApaviddhaM yajJAvasAne ' gnimiva prazAntam . mastaM gataM bhAskarasyeva bimbam .
zarairAcitasarvAGgaH zoNitaidhapariplutaH . vibhAti dehaH karNasya svarazmibhirivAMzumAn .
pratApya senAmAmitrI dIptaiH zaragabhastibhiH . balinArjunakAlena nIto ' staM karNabhAskaraH .
astaM gacchan yathAdityaH prabhAmAdAya gacchati . tathA jIvitamAdAya karNasyeSurjagAma saH .
aparAhne ' parAho ' sya sUtaputrasya mAriSa . chinnamaJjalikenAjau sotsedhamapatacchiraH .
uparyupari sainyAnAmasya zatrostadaJjasA . zira : karNasya sotsedhamiSuH so ' pyaharad drutam .
karNaM tu zUraM patitaM pRthivyAM zarAcitaM zoNitadigdhagAtram . zchinnadhvajenAtha yayau rathena .
hate karNe kuravaH prAdravanta bhayArditA gADhaviddhAzca saMkhye . avekSamANA muhurarjunasya dhvajaM mahAntaM vapuSA jvalantam .
sahasranekSapratimAnakarmaNaH sahasrapatrapratimAnanaM zubham . sahasrarazmirdinasaMkSaye yathA tathApatat karNaziro vasuMdharAm .
dhRtarASTra uvAca vyathayeyurime senAM devAnAmapi saMjaya . Ahave ye nyavartanta vRkodaramukhA nRpAH .
samprayuktaH kilaivAyaM diSTairbhavati pUruSaH . tasminneva ca sarvArthAH pradRzyante pRthagvidhAH .
dIrgha viproSitaH kAlamaraNye jaTilo ' jinI . ajJAtazcaiva lokasya vijahAra yudhiSThiraH .
sa eva mahatIM senAM samAvartayadAhave . kimanyad daivasaMyogAnmama putrasya cAbhavat .
yukta eva hi bhAgyena dhruvamutpadyate naraH . sa tathA ' ' kRSyate tena na yathA svayamicchati .
dyUtavyasanamAsAdya klezito hi yudhiSThiraH . sa punarbhAgadheyena sahAyAnupalabdhavAn .
adya me kekayA labdhAH kAzikA : kosalAza me . cedayazcApare vaGgA mAmeva samupAzritAH .
pRthivI bhUyasI tAta mama pArthasya no tathA . iti mAmabravIt sUta mando duryodhanaH purA .
tasya senAsamUhasya madhye droNaH surakSitaH . nihataH pArSatenAjau kimanyad bhAgadheyataH .
madhye rAjJAM mahAbAhuM sadA yuddhAbhinandinam . sarvAstrapAragaM droNaM kathaM mRtyurupeyivAn .
samanuprAptakRccho ' haM mohaM paramamAgataH . bhISmadroNau hatau zrutvA nAhaM jIvitumutsahe .
yanmAM kSattAbravIt tAta prapazyan putragRddhinam . duryodhanena tat sarve prAptaM sUta mayA saha .
nRzaMsaM tu paraM nu syAt tayaktvA duryodhanaM yadi . putrazeSaM cikIrSeyaM kRtsnaM na maraNaM vrajet .
yo hi dharmaM parityajya bhavatyarthaparo naraH . so ' smAcca hIyate lokAt kSudrabhAvaM ca gacchati .
adya cApyasya rASTrasya hatotsAhasya saMjaya . avazeSaM na pazyAmi kakude mRdite sati .
kathaM syAdavazeSo hi dhuryayorabhyatItayoH . yo nityamupajIvAmaH kSamiNau puruSarSabhau .
vyaktameva ca me zaMsa yathA yuddhamavartata . ke ' yudhyan ke vyApakurvan ke kSudrAH prAdravan bhayAt .17
dhanaMjayaM ca me zaMsa yad yaccakre ratharSabhaH . tasmAd bhayaM no bhUyiSThaM bhrAtRvyAcca vRkodarAt .
yathA ' ' sIcca nivRtteSu pANDaveyeSu saMjaya . mama sainyAvazeSasya saMnipAtaH sudAruNaH .
kathaM ca vo manastAta nivRtteSvabhavat tadA . mAmakAnAM ca ye zUrAH ke kAMstatra nyavArayan .
nArada uvAca gAlavaM vainateyo ' tha prahasannidamabravIt . diSTyA kRtArthaM pazyAmi bhavantamiha vai dvija . . . .
gAlavastu vacaH zrutvA vainateyena bhASitam . caturbhAgAvaziSTaM tadAcakhyau kAryamasya hi .
suparNastvabravIdenaM gAlavaM vadatAM varaH . prayatnastena kartavyo naiSa sampatsyate tava .
purA hi kAnyakubje vai gAdheH satyavatIM sutAm . bhAryArthe ' varayat kanyAmRcIkastena bhASitaH .
ekataH zyAmakarNAnAM hayAnAM candravarcasAm . bhagavan dIyatAM mahyaM sahasramiti gAlava .
RcIkastu tathetyuktvA varuNasyAlayaM gataH . azvatIrthaM hayA~llabdhvA dattavAn pArthivAya vai .
iSTvA te puNDarIkeNa dattA rAjJA dvijAtiSu . tebhyo dve dve zate krItvA prApte taiH pArthivaistadA .
aparANyapi catvAri zatAni dvijasattama . nIyamAnAni saMtAre hRtAnyAsan vitastayA .
evaM na zakyamaprApyaM prAptuM gAlava karhicit . imAmazvazatAbhyAM vai dvAbhyAM tasmai nivedaya .
vizvAmitrAya dharmAtman SaDbhirazvazataiH saha . tato ' si gatasammohaH kRtakRtyo dvijottama .
gAlavastaM tathetyuktvA suparNasahitastataH . AdAyAzvAMzca kanyAM ca vizvAmitramupAgamat .
azvAnAM kAkSitArthAnAM SaDimAni zatAni vai . zatadvayena kanyeya bhavatA pratigRhyatAm .
asyAM rAjarSibhiH putrA jAtA vai dhArmikAstrayaH . caturthaM janayatvekaM bhavAnapi narottamam .
pUrNAnyevaM zatAnyaSTau turagANAM bhavantu te . bhavato hyanRNo bhUtvA tapaH kuryAM yathAsukham .
vizvAmitrastu taM dRSTvA gAlavaM saha pakSiNA . kanyAM ca tAM varArohAmidamityabravId vacaH .
kimiyaM pUrvameveha na dattA mama gAlavA putrA mamaiva catvAro bhaveyuH kulabhAvanAH .
pratigRhNAmi te kanyAmekaputraphalAya vai . azvAzcAzramamAsAdya carantu mama sarvazaH .
sa tayA ramamANo ' tha vizvAmitro mahAdyutiH . AtmajaM janayAmAsa mAdhavI putramaSTakam .
jAtamAtraM sutaM taM ca vizvAmitro mahAmuniH . saMyojyArthastathA dharmairazvaistaiH samayojayat .
athASTakaH puraM prAyAt tadA somapuraprabham . niryAtya kanyAM ziSyAya kauziko ' pi vanaM yayau .
gAlavo ' pi suparNena saha niryAtya dakSiNAm . manasA ' tipratItena kanyAmidamuvAca ha .
jAto dAnapatiH putrastvayA zUrastathAparaH . satyadharmaratazcAnyo yajvA cApi tathA ' paraH .
tadAgaccha varArohe tAritaste pitA sutaiH . catvArazcaiva rAjAnastathA cAhaM sumadhyame .
gAlavastvabhyanujJAya suparNaM pannagAzanam . piturniryAtya tAM kanyAM prayayau vanameva ha .
dhRtarASTra uvAca tathA prayAte ziviraM droNaputre mahArathe . kaccit kRpazca bhojazca bhayArtI na vyavartatAm .
kaccinna vAritau kSudai rakSibharnopalakSitau . asahyamiti manvAnau na nivRttI mahArathau .
kaccidunmathya ziviraM hatvA somakapANDavAn . duryodhanasya padavIM gatau paramiko raNe .
paJcAlainihatau vIrau kaccinnAsvapatAM kSitau . kaccit tAbhyAM kRtaM karma tanmamAcakSva saMjaya .
saMjaya uvAca tasmin prayAte ziviraM droNaputre mahAtmani . kRpazca kRtavarmA ca ziviradvaryatiSThatAm .
azvatthAmA tu ta. dRSTvA yatnavantau mahArathau . prahRSTaH zanakai rAjannidaM vacanamabravIt .
yattau bhavantau paryAptau sarvakSatrasya nAzane . kiM punaryodhazeSasya prasuptasya vizeSataH .
ahaM pravekSye ziviraM cariSyAmi ca kAlavat . yathA na kazcidapi vA jIvan mucyeta mAnavaH .
tathAbhavadbhyA kAryaM syAdita me nizcitAmatiH . ityuktavAprAvizad drauNiH pArthAnAM ziviraM mahat . advAreNAbhyavaskandha vihAya bhayamAtmanaH .
sa pravizya mahAbAhuruddezajJazca tasya ha . dhRSTadyumnasya nilayaM zanakairabhyupAgamat .
te tu kRtvA mahat karma zrAntAca balavad raNe . prasuptAzcaiva vizvastAH svasainyaparivAritAH .
atha pravizya tad vezma dhRSTadyumnasya bhArata . pAJcAlyaM zayanedrauNipazyat suptamantikAt .
kSaumAvadAte mahati spAstaraNasaMvRte . mAlyapravarasaMyukte dhUpaizcUrNaizca vAsite .
taM zayAnaM mahAtmAnaM vizrabdhamakutobhayam . prAbodhayata pAdena zayanasthaM mahIpate .
sambudhya caraNasparzAdutthAya raNadurmadaH . abhyajAnAdameyAtmA droNaputraM mahAratham .
tamutpatantaM zayanAdazvatthAmA mahAbalaH . kezeSvAlabhya pANibhyAM niSpipeSa mahItale .
sabalaM tena niSpiSTaH sAdhvasena ca bhArata . nidrayA caiva pAJcAlyo nAzakacceSTituM tadA .
tamAkramya padA rAjan kaNThe corasi cobhayoH . nadantaM visphurantaM ca pazumApamamArayat . tudannakhaistu sa drANiM nAtivyaktamudAharat .
AcAryaputra zastreNa jahi mAM mA ciraM kRthAH . tvatkRte sukRtA~llokAn gaccheyaM dvipadAM vara .
evamuktvA tu vacana virarAma paraMtapaH . sutaH pAJcAlarAjasya AkrAnto balinA bhRzam .
tasyAvyaktAM tu tAM vAcaM saMzrutya drauNirabravIt . te AcAryaghAtinA lokA na santi kulapAMsana . tasmAcchastreNa nidhanaM na tvamarhasi durmate .
evaM bruvANastaM vIraM siMho mattamiva dvipam . marmasvabhyavadhIt kruddhaH pAdASThIlaiH sudAruNaiH .
tasya vIrasya zabdena mAryamANasya vezmani . abudhyanta mahArAja striyo ye cAsya rakSiNaH .
dRSTvA dharSayantaM tamatimAnuSavikramam . bhUtamevAdhyavasyanto na sma pravyAharan bhayAt .
taM tu tenAbhyupAyena gamayitvA yamakSayam . adhyatiSThata tejasvI rathaM prApya sudarzanam .
sa tasya bhavanAd rAjan niSkramyAnAdayanaMdizaH . rathena ziviraM prAyAjjighAMsurdviSato balI .
