tathA naSTaM tamo ghoraM dIpairdIptaritastataH . dyozcaiva pRthivI cApi dizazca pradizastathA .
rajasA tamasA vyAptA dyotitAH prabhayA punaH . astrANAM kavacAnAM ca maNInAM ca mahAtmanAm .
antardadhuH prabhAH sarvA dIpaistairavabhAsitAH . tasmin kolAhale yuddhe vartamAne nizAmukhe .
na kiMcid vidurAtmAnamayamasmIti bhArata . avadhIt samare putraM pitA bharatasattam .
putrazca pitaraM mohAt sakhAyaM ca sakhA tathA . svasnIyaM mAtulazcApi svasrIyazcApi mAtulam .
sve svAn pare parAMzcApi nijatruritaretaram . nirmaryAdamabhUd yuddhaM rAtrau bhIrubhayAnakam .
yudhiSThira uvAca brAhmaNasvAni ye mandA haranti bharatarSabha . nRzaMsakAriNo mUDhAH kva te gacchanti mAnavAH .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . cANDAlasya ca saMvAdaM kSAbandhozca bhArata .
vRddharUpo ' si cANDAla bAlavacca viceSTase . zvakharANAM raja : sevI kasmAdudvijase gavAm .
sAdhubhirgarhitaM karma cANDAlasya vidhIyate . kasmAd gorajasAdhvastamapAM kuNDe niSiJcasi .
cANDAla uvAca brAhmaNasya gavAM rAjan hiyatInAM rajaH purA . somamudhvaMsayAmAsa taM somaM ye ' piban dvijAH . dIkSitazca sa rAjApi kSipraM narakamAvizat . saha tairyAjakaiH sarvairbrahmasvamupajIvya tat .
ye ' pi tatrApiban kSIraM ghRtaM dadhi ca mAnavAH . brAhmaNAH saharAjanyAH sarve narakamAvizan .
janastAH payasA putrAMstathA pautrAn vidhuvantIH . pazUnavekSamANAzca sAdhRvRttena dampatI .
ahaM tatrAvasaM rAjan brahmacArI jitendriyaH . tAsAM me rajasA dhvasta bhaikSamAsInnarAdhipa .
cANDAlo ' haM tato rAjan bhuktvA tadabhavaM nRpa . brahmasvahArI ca nRpaH so ' pratiSThAM gatiM yayau . .
tasmAddharena viprasvaM kadAcidapi kiMcana . brahmasvaM rajasA dhvastuM bhuktvA mAM pazya yAdRzam .
tasmAt somo ' pyavikreyaH puruSeNa vipazcitA . vikrayaM tviha somasya garhayanti manISiNaH .
ye cainaM krINate tAta ye ca vikrINate janAH . te ta vaivasvataM prApya rauravaM yAnti sarvazaH .
somaM tu rajasA dhvastaM vikrINan vidhipUrvakam . zrotriyo vAdhuSI bhUtvA na ciraM sa vinazyati .
narakaM triMzataM prApya svaviSThAmupajIvati . zrucaryAmabhimAnaM ca sakhidAre ca viplavam . tulayA dhArayan dharmamabhimAnyatiricyate . zvAnaM vai pApinaM pazya vivarNaM hariNa kRzam .
abhimAnena bhUtAnAmimAM gatimupAgatam . ahaM vai vipule tAta kule dhanasamanvite . anyasmijanmani vibho jJAnavijJAnapAragaH . abhavaM tatra jAnAno hyetAn doSAn madAt sadA . saMrabdha eva bhUtAnAM pRSThamAMsamabhakSayam . so ' haM tena ca vRttena bhojanena ca tena vai . imAmavasthAM samprAptaH pazya kAlasya paryayam . AdIptamiva cailAntaM bhramariva cArditam . dhAvamAnaM susaMrabdhaM pazya mAM rajasAnvitam . svAdhyAyaistu mahAtpApaM haranti gRhamedhinaH . dAnaiH pRthagvidhaizcApi yathA prAhurmanISiNaH . tathA pApakRtaM vipramAzramasthaM mahIpate . sarvasaGgavinirmuktaM chandAMsyuttArayantyuta . ahaM hi pApayonyAM vai prasUtaH kSatriyarSabha . nizcayaM nAdhigacchAmi kathaM mucyeyamityuta .
jAtismaratvaM ca mama kenacit pUrvakarmaNA . zubhena yena mokSaM vai prAptumicchAmyahaM nRpa . .
tvamimaM samprapannAya saMzayaM brUhi pRcchate . cANDAlatvAt kathamahaM mucyeyamiti sattama .
rAjanya uvAca cANDAla pratijAnIhi yena mokSamavApsyasi . brAhmaNArthe tyajan prANAn gatimiSTAmavApsyasi .
dattvA zarIraM kravyAdbhayo raNAgnaudvijahetukam . hatvA prANAn pramokSaste nAnyathA mokSamarhasi .
bhISma uvAca ityuktaH sa tadA tena brahmasvArthe paraMtapa . hatvA raNamukhe prANAn gatimiSTAmavApa ha .
tasmAd rakSyaM tvayA putra brahmasvaM bharatarSabha . yadIcchasi mahAbAho zAzvatIM gatimAtmanaH .
zukra uvAca yaH pareSAM naro nityamativAdAMstitikSate . devayAni vijAnIhi tena sarvamidaM jitam . ucyate . yaH samutpatitaM krodhaM nigRhNAti hayaM yathA . sa yantetyucyate sadbhirna yo razmiSu lambate .21.
yaH samutpatitaM krodhamakrodhena nirasyati . devayAni vijAnIhi tena sarvamidaM jitam .
yaH samutpatitaM krodhaM kSamayeha nirasyati . yathoragastvacaM jIrNA sa vai puruSa
yaH saMdhArayate manyu yo ' tivAdAMstitikSate . yazca tapto na tapati dRDhaM so ' rthasya bhAjanam .
yo yajedaparizrAnto mAsi mAsi zataM samAH . na kruddheyad yazca sarvasya tayorakrodhano ' dhikaH .
yat kumArAH kumAryazca vairaM kuryuracetasaH . na tat prAjJo ' nukurvIta na viduste balAbalam .
devayAnyuvAca vedAhaM tAta bAlApi dharmANAM yadihAntaram . akrodhe cAtivAde ca veda cApi balAbalam .
ziSyasyAziSyavRttestu na kSantavyaM bubhUSatA . tasmAt saMkIrNavRtteSu vAso mama na rocate .
pumAMso ye hi nindanti vRttenAbhijanena ca . na teSu nivaset prAjJaH zreyo ' rthI pApabuddhiSu .
ye tvenapabhijAnanti vRttenAbhijanena vA . teSu sAdhuSu vastavyaM sa vAsaH zreSTha ucyate .
vAg duruktaM mahAghoraM duhiturvRSaparvaNaH . mama manAti hRdayamagnikAma ivAraNim .
yaH sapatnazriyaM dIptAM hInazrIH paryupAsate . maraNaM zobhanaM tasya iti vidvajjanA viduH .
vaizampAyana uvAca so ' bravIdarjunaM caiva vAsudevaM ca sAtvatam . lokapravIrau tiSThantau khANDavasya samIpataH .
brAhmaNo bahubhoktAsmi bhuJje ' parimitaM sadA . bhikSe vArSNeyapArtho vAmekAM tRptiM prayacchatam .
evamuktau tamabrUtAM tatastau kRSNapANDavau . kenAnnena bhavAMstRpyet tasyAnnasya yatAvahe .
evamuktaH sa bhagavAnabravIt tAvubhau tataH . bhASamANau tadA vIrau kimannaM kriyatAmiti .
brAhmaNa uvAca nAhamannaM bubhukSe vai pAvakaM mAM nibodhatam . yadannamanurUpaM me tad yuvAM samprayacchatam .
idamindraH sadA dAvaM khANDavaM parirakSati . na ca zakromyahaM dagdhuM rakSyamANaM mahAtmanA .
vasatyatra sakhA tasya takSakaH pannagaH sadA . sagaNastatkRte dAvaM parirakSati vajrabhRt .
tatra bhUtAnyanekAni rakSate ' sya prasaGgataH . taM didhakSurna zaknomi dagdhuM zakrasya tejasA .
sa mAM prajvalitaM dRSTvA meghAmbhobhiH pravarSati . tato dagdhuM na zaknomi didhakSurdAvamIpsitAm .
sa yuvAbhyAM sahAyAbhyAmastravidbhyAM samAgataH . daheyaM khANDavaM dAvametadannaM vRtaM mayA .
yuvAM hyadakadhArAstA bhUtAni ca samantataH . uttamAstravidau samyak sarvato vArayiSyathaH .
janamejaya uvAca kimarthaM bhagavAnagniH khANDavaM dagdhumicchati . rakSyamANaM mahendreNa nAnAsattvasamAyutam .
na hyetat kAraNaM brahmannalpaM sampratibhAti me . yad dadAha susaMkruddhaH khANDavaM havyavAhanaH . etad vistarazo brahmaJchrotumicchAmi tattvataH . khANDavasya purA dAho yathA samabhavanmune .
vaizampAyana uvAca zRNu me bruvato rAjan sarvametad yathAtatham . yanimittaM dadAhAgniH khANDavaM pRthivIpate .
hanta te kathayiSyAmi paurANImRSisaMstutAm . kathAmimAM narazreSTha khANDavasya vinAzinIm .
paurANaH zrUyate rAjan rAjA harihayopamaH . zvetakirnAma vikhyAto balavikramasaMyutaH .
yajvA dAnapatirthImAn yathA nAnyo ' sti kaJcana . Ije ca sa mahAyajJaiH kratubhizcAptadakSiNaiH .
tasya nAnyAbhavad buddhirdivase divase nRpa . satre kriyAsamArambhe dAneSu vividheSu ca . RtvigbhiH sahito dhImAnevamIje sa bhUmipaH . tatastu RtvijazcAsya dhUmavyAkulalocanAH . kAlena mahatA khinnAstatyajuste narAdhipam . tataH pracodayAmAsa RtvijastAn mahIpatiH . cakSurvikalatAM prAptA na prapeduzca te kratum .
tatasteSAmanumate tad vipraistu narAdhipaH . satraM samApayAmAsa RtvigbhiparaiH saha .
tasyaivaM vartamAnasya kadAcit kAlapayaye . satramAhartukAmasya savaMtsarazataM kila . Rtvijo nAbhyapadyanta samAhartuM mahAtmanaH .
sa ca rAjAkarod yatnaM mahAntaM sasuhRjjanaH . praNipAtena sAntvena dAnena ca mahAyazAH . Rtvijo ' nunayAmAsa bhUyo bhUyastvatandritaH . te cAsya tamabhiprAyaM na cakruramitaujasaH .
sa cAzramasthAn rAjarSistAnuvAca ruSAnvitaH . yadyahaM patito viprAH zuzrUSAyAM na ca sthitaH . Azu tyAjyo ' smi yuSmAbhirbrAhmaNaizca jugupsitaH . tannArhatha kratuzraddhAM vyAghAtayitumadya tAm .
asthAne vA parityAgaM kartuM me dvijasattamAH . prapanna eva vo viprAH prasAdaM kartumarhatha . sAntvadAnAdibhirvAkyestattvataH kAryavattayA . prasAdayitvA vakSyAmi yannaH kAryaM dvijottamAH . athavAhaM parityakto bhavadbhide\SakAraNAt . Rtvijo ' nyAn gamiSyAmi yAjanArthaM dvijottamAH .
etAvaduktvA vacanaM virarAma sa pArthivaH . yadA na zekU rAjAnaM yAjanArthaM paraMtapaH . tataste yAjakaH kruddhAstamUcurnRpasattamam . tava karmANyajasraM vai vartante pArthivottama .
tato vayaM parizrAntAH satataM karmavAhinaH . zramAdasmAt parizrAntAn sa tvaM nastyaktumarhasi . buddhimohaM samAsthAya tvarAsambhAvito ' nagha . gaccha rudrasakAzaM tvaM sa hi tvAM yAjayiSyati .
sAdhikSepaM vacaH zrutvA saMkruddhaH zvetakirnRpaH . kailAsa parvataM gatvA tapa ugraM samAsthitaH . ArAdhayan mahAdevaM niyataH saMzitavrataH . upavAsaparo rAjan dIrghakAlamatiSThata .
kadAcid dvAdaze kAle kadAcidapi SoDaze . AhAramakarod rAjA mUlAni ca phalAni ca .
UrdhvabAhustvanimiSastiSThan sthANurivAcalaH . SaNmAsAnabhavad rAjA zvetakiH susamAhitaH .
taM tathA nRpazArdUlaM tapyamAnaM mahat tapaH . zaMkaraH paramaprItyA darzayAmAsa bhArata .
uvAca cainaM bhagavAn snigdhagambhIrayA girA . prIto ' smi narazArdUla tapasA te paraMtapa .
varaM vRNISva bhadraM te yaM tvamicchasi pArthiva . etacchrutvA tu vacanaM rudrasyAmitatejasaH .
praNipatya mahAtmAnaM rAjarSiH pratyabhASata . yadi me bhagavAn prItaH sarvalokanamaskRtaH . svayaM mAM devadeveza yAjayasva surezvara . etacchrutvA tu vacanaM rAjJA tena prabhASitam .
uvAca bhagavAn prItaH smitapUrvamidaM vacaH . nAsmAkameSa viSayo vartate yAjanaM prati . tvayA ca sumahat taptaM tapo rAjan varArthinA . yAjayiSyAmi rAjAMstvAM samayena paraMpata .
rudra uvAca samA dvAdaza rAjendra brahmacArI samAhitaH . satataM tvAjyadhArAbhiryadi tarpayase ' nalam . kAmaM prArthayase yaM tvaM mattaH prApsyasi taM nRpa .
evamuktazca rudreNa zvetakirmanujAdhipaH . tathA cakAra tat sarvaM yathoktaM zUlapANinA . pUrNe tu dvAdaze varSe punarAyAnmahezvaraH .
dRSTvaiva ca sa rAjAnaM zaMkaro lokabhAvanaH . uvAca paramaprItaH zvetakiM nRpasattamam .
toSito ' haM nRpazreSTha tvayehAdyena karmaNA . yAjanaM brAhmaNAnAM tu vidhidRSTaM paraMtapa .
ato ' haM tvAM svayaM nAdya yAjayAmi paraMtaya . mamAMzastu kSititale mahAbhAgo dvijottamaH .
durvAsA iti vikhyAtaH sa hi tvAM yAjayiSyati . manniyogAnmahAtejAH sambhArAH sambhriyantu te .
etacchrutvA tu vacanaM rudreNa samudAhRtam . svapuraM punarAgamya sambhArAn punarArjayat .
tataH sambhRtasambhAro bhUyo rudramupAgamat . sambhRtA mama sambhArA : sarvopakaraNAni ca . tvatprasAdAnmahAdeva zvo me dIkSA bhavediti . etacchrutvA tu vacanaM tasya rAjJo mahAtmanaH . durvAsasaM samAhUya rudro vacanamabravIt . eSa rAjA mahAbhAgaH zvetakirdvijasattama . enaM yAjaya viprendra manniyogena bhUmipam . bADhamityeva vacanaM rudraM tvRSiruvAca ha .
tataH satraM samabhavat tasya rAjJo mahAtmanaH . yathAvidhiH yathAkAlaM yathoktaM bahudakSiNam .
tasmin parisamApte tu rAjJaH satre mahAtmanaH . durvAsasAbhyanujJAtA vipratasthuH sma yAjakaH . ye tatra dIkSitAH sarve sadasyAzca mahaujasaH . so ' pi rAjan mahAbhAgaH svapuraM prAvizat tadA .
pUjyamAno mahAbhAgaiAhmaNairvedapAragaiH . vandibhiH stUyamAnazca nAgaraizcAbhinanditaH .
evaMvRttaH sa rAjarSiH zvetakirnRpasattamaH . kAlena mahatA cApi yayau svargamabhiSTutaH . RtvigbhiH sahitaH sarvaiH sadasyaizca samanvitaH . tasya satre papau vahnirhavidaza vatsarAn .
satataM cAjyadhArAbhiraikAtmye tatra karmaNi . haviSA ca tato vahniH parAM tRptimagacchata .
na caicchat punarAdAtuM haviranyasya kasyacit . pANDuvarNo vivarNazca na yathAvat prakAzate .
tato bhagavato vahnarvikAraH samajAyata . tejasA viprahINazca glAnizcainaM samAvizat .
sa lakSayitvA cAtmAnaM tejohInaM hutAzanaH . jagAma sadanaM puNyaM brahmaNo lokapUjitam .
tatra brahmANamAsInamidaM vacanamabravIt . bhagavan paramA prItiH kRtA me zvetaketunA . arucizcAbhavat tIvrA tAM na zaknobhyapohitum . tejasA viprahINo ' smi balena ca jagatpate . iccheya tvatprasAdena svAtmanaH prakRti sthirAm .
etacchrutvA hutavahAd bhagavAn sarvalokakRta . havyavAhamidaM vAkyamuvAca prahasanniva . tvayA dvAdaza varSANi vasordhArAhutaM haviH . upayuktaM mahAbhAga tena tvAM glAnirAvizat . tejasA viprahINatvAt sahasA havyavAhana . mA gamastvaM yathA vahne prakRtistho bhaviSyasi . aruciM nAzayiSye ' haM samayaM pratipadya te .
purA devaniyogena yat tvayA bhasmasAt kRtam . AlayaM devazatrUNAM sughoraM khANDavaM vanam . tatra sarvANi sattvAni nivasanti vibhAvaso . teSAM tvaM medasA tRptaH prakRtistho bhaviSyasi .
gaccha zIghraM pradagdhuM tvaM tato mokSyasi kilbiSAt . etacchrutvA tu vacanaM parameSThimukhAccyutam . uttamaM javamAsthAya pradudrAva hutAzanaH . Agamya khANDavaM dAvamuttamaM vIryamAsthitaH . sahasA prAjvalaccAgniH kruddho vAyusamIritaH .
pradIptaM khANDavaM dRSTvA ye syustatra nivAsinaH . paramaM yatnamAtiSThan pAvakasya prazAntaye .
karaistu kariNaH zIghraM jalamAdAya satvarAH . siSicuH pAvakaM kruddhAH zatazo ' tha sahasrazaH .
bahuzIrSAstato nAgAH zirobhirjalasaMtatim . mumucuH pAvakAbhyAze satvarAH krodhamUrcchitAH .
tathaivAnyAni sattvAni nAnApraharaNodyamaiH . vilayaM pAvakaM zIghramanayan bharatarSabha .
anena tu prakAreNa bhUyo bhUyazca prajvalan . saptakRtvaH prazamitaH khANDave havyavAhanaH .
saMjaya uvAca tat prabhagnaM balaM dRSTvA kuntIputro dhanajayaH . nyavArayadameyAtmA droNaputrajayepsayA .
tataste sainikA rAjan naiva tatrAvatasthire . saMsthApyamAnA yatnena govindenArjunena ca .
eka eva ca bIbhatsuH somakAvayavaiH saha . matsyairanyaizca saMdhAya kauravAn saMnyavartata .
tato drutamatikramya siMhalAGkalaketanam . savyasAcI maheSvAsamazvatthAmAnamabravIt .
yA zaktiryaca vijJAnaM yad vIrya yaca pauruSam . dhArtarASTreSu yA prItirddhaSo ' smAsu ca yazca te .
yaca bhUyo ' sti tejaste tat sarvaM mayi darzaya . sa eva droNahantA te darpa chetsyati pArSataH .
kAlAnalasamaprakhyaM dviSatAmantakopamam . samAsAdaya pAJcAlyaM mAM cApi sahakezavam . darpa nAzayitAsmyadya tavottasya saMyuge .
dhRtarASTra uvAca AcAryaputro mAnArho balavAMzcApi saMjaya . prItidhanaMjaye cAsya priyazcApi mahAtmanaH .
na bhUtapUrvaM bIbhatsorvAkyaM paruSamIdRzam . atha kasmAt sa kaunteyaH sakhAyaM rUkSamuktavAn .
saMjaya uvAca yuvarAje hate caiva vRddhakSatre ca paurave . iSvasravidhisampanne mAlave ca sudarzane .
dhRSTadyumne sAtyakau ca bhIme cApi parAjite . yudhiSThirasya tairvAkyairmarmaNyapi ca ghaTTite .
antarbhede ca saMjAte duHkhaM saMsmRtya ca prabho . abhUtapUrvo bIbhatsorduHkhAnmanyurajAyata .
tasmAdanahamazlIlamapriyaM drauNimuktavAn . mAnyamAcAryatanayaM rUkSaM kApuruSaM yathA .
evamuktaH zvasana krodhAnmaheSvAsatamo nRpa . pArthena paruSaM vAkyaM sarvamarmabhidA girA .
drauNizcukopa pArthAya kRSNAya ca vizeSataH . sa tu yatto rathe sthitvA vAryupaspRzya vIryavAn .
devairapi sudurdharSamasramAgneyamAdade . dRzyAdRzyAnariMgaNAnuddizyAcAryanandanaH .
so ' bhimanvya zaraM dIptaM vidhUmamiva pAvakam . sarvataH krodhamAvizya cikSepa paravIrahA .
tatastumulamAkAze zaravarSamajAyata . pAvakArciH parItaM tat pArthamevAbhipupluve .
ulkAzca gaganAt peturdizazca na cakAzire . tamazca sahasA raudraM camUmavatatAra tAm .
rakSAMsi ca pizAcAzca vineduratisaGgatAH . vavuzcAzizirA vAtAH sUryo naiva tatApa ca .
vAyasAzcApi cAkrandan dikSu sarvAsu bhairavam . rudhiraM cApi varSanto vinedustoyadA divi .
pANiH pazavo gAvo vineduzcApi suvratAH . paramaM prayatAtmAno na zAntimupalebhire .
bhrAntasarvamahAbhUtamAvartitadivAkaram . trailokyamabhisaMtaptaM jvarAviSTamivAbhavat .
asratejo ' bhisaMtaptA nAgA bhUmizayAstathA . niHzvasantaH samutpetustejo ghoraM mumukSavaH .
jalajAni ca sattvAni dahyamAnAni bhArata . na zAntimupajagmurhi tapyamAnairjalAzayaiH .
digbhyaH pradigbhyaH khAd bhUmeH sarvataH zaravRSTyaH . uccAvacA nipeturvai garuDAnilaraMhasaH .
taiH zarairdoNaputrasya vajravegaiH samAhatAH . pradagdhA ripava : peturagnidagdhA iva drumAH .
dahyamAnA mahAnAgAH peturuAM samantataH . nadanto bhairavAn nAdAJjaladopamani : svanAn .
apare pradrutA nAgA bhayatrastA vizAmpate . bhremurdizo yathA pUrvaM vane dAvAgnisaMvRtAH .
dumANAM zikharANIva dAvadagdhAni mAriSa . azvavRndAnyadRzyanta rathavRndAni bhArata .
apatanta rathaughAzca tatra tatra sahasrazaH . tat sainyaM bhayasaMvignaM dadAha yudhi bhArata .
yugAnte sarvabhUtAni saMvartaka ivAnalaH . dRSTvA tu pANDavIM senAM dahyamAnAM mahAhave .
prahRSTAstAvakA rAjan siMhanAdAn vinedire . tatastUryasahasrANi nAnAliGgAni bhArata .
tUrNamAjajire hRSTAstAvakA jitakAzinaH . kRtsnA hyakSauhiNI rAjan savyasAcI ca pANDavaH . . 34
tamasA saMvRte loke nAdRzyanta mahAhave . naiva nastAdRzaM rAjan dRSTapUrvaM na ca zrutam . yAdRzaM droNaputreNa sRSTamasramamarSiNA . arjunastu mahArAja brAhmamasramudairayat .
sarvAsapratighAtArthaM vihitaM padmayoninA . tato muhUrtAdiva tat tamo vyupazazAma ha .
pravavau cAnilaH zIto dizazca vimalA babhuH . tatrAdbhutamapazyAma kRtsnAmakSauhiNI hatAm .
anabhijJeyarUpAM ca pradagdhAmasratejasA . tato vIrau maheSvAsau vimuktau kezavArjunau .
sahitau pratyadRzyetAM nabhasIva tamonudau . tato gANDIvadhanvA ca kezavazcAkSatAvubhau .
sapatAkadhvajahayaH sAnukarSavarAyudhaH . prababhau sa ratho muktastAvakAnAM bhayaMkaraH .
tataH kilakilAzabdaH zaGkhabherIsvanaiH saha . pANDavAnAM prahRSTAnAM kSaNena samajAyata .
hatAviti tayorAsIt senayorubhayormatiH . tarasAbhyAgatau dRSTvA sahitau kezavArjunau .
tAvakSatau pramuditau dadhmaturvArijottamau . dRSTavA pramuditAn pArthAMstvadIyA vyathitA bhRzam .
vimuktau ca mahAtmAnau dRSTvA drauNiH suduHkhitaH . muhUrtaM cintayAmAsa kiM tvetaditi mAriSa .
cintayitvA tu rAjendra dhyAnazokaparAyaNaH . niHzvasan dIrghamuSNaM ca vimanAzcAbhavat tataH .
tato drauNirdhanustyaktvA rathAt praskandha vegitaH . dhig dhik sarvamidaM mithyetyuktvA samprAdravad raNAt . .
tataH snigdhAmbudAbhAsaM vedAvAsamakalmaSam . vedavyAsaM sarasvatyAvAsaM vyAsaM dadarza ha .
taM drauNiragrato dRSTvA sthitaM kurukulodvaha . sannakaNTho ' bravId vAkyamabhivAdya sudInavat .
bho bho mAyA yadRcchA vA na vidyaH kimidaM bhavet . asaM tvidaM kathaM mithyA mama kazca vyatikramaH .
adharottarametad vA lokAnAM vA parAbhavaH . yadimau jIvataH kRSNau kAlo hi duratikramaH .
nAsurA na ca gandharvA na pizAcA na rAkSasAH . na sarpA yakSapatagA na manuSyAH kathaMcana .
utsahante ' nyathA kartumetadasraM mayeritam . tadidaM kevalaM hatvA zAntamakSauhiNI jvalat .
sarvaghAti mayA muktamatraM paramadAruNam . kenemau martyadharmANau nAvadhIt kezavArjunau .
etat prabrUhi bhagavan mayA pRSTo yathAtatham . zrotumicchAmi tattvena sarvametanmahAmune .
vyAsa uvAca mahAntamevamatha mAM yaM tvaM pRcchasi vismayAt . taM pravakSyAmi te sarvaM samAdhAya manaH zRNu .
yo ' sau nArAyaNo nAma pUrveSAmapi pUrvajaH . ajAyata ca kAryArthaM putro dharmasya vizvakRt .
sa tapastIvramAtasthe ziziraM girimAsthitaH . UrvabAhurmahAtejA jvalanAdityasaMnibhaH .
SaSTiM varSasahasrANi tAvantyeva zatAni ca . azoSayat tadA ' ' tmAnaM vAyubhakSo ' mbujekSaNaH .
athAparaM tapastaptvA dvistato ' nyat punarmahat . dyAvApRthivyorvivaraM tejasA samapUrayat .
sa tena tapasA tAta brahmabhUto yadAbhavat . tato vizvezvaraM yoni vizvasya jagataH patim . dadarza bhRzadurdharSaM sarvadevairabhiSTutam . aNIyAMsamaNubhyazca bRhadbhyazca bRhattamam .
rudramIzAnavRSabhaM haraM zambhuM kapardinam . cekitAnaM parAM yoni tiSThato gacchatazca ha .
durvAraNaM durdazaM tigmamanyu mahAtmAnaM sarvaharaM pracetasam . divyaM cApamiSudhI cAdadAnaM hiraNyavarmANamanantavIryam .
pinAkinaM vajriNaM dIptazUlaM parazvadhi gadinaM cAyatAsim . zubhaMjaTilaM musalinaM candramauliM vyAghrAjinaM parighiNaM daNDapANim .
zubhAGgadaM nAgayajJopavItaM vizvaigaNaiH zobhitaM bhUtasaMdhaiH . ekIbhUtaM tapasA saMnidhAnaM vayo ' tigaiH suSTutamiSTavAgbhiH .
jalaM dizaM khaM kSitiM candrasUryo tathA vAyvagnI pramimANaM jagaca . nAlaM draSTuM yaM janA bhinnavRttA brahmadviSaghnamamRtasya yonim .
yaM pazyanti brAhmaNAH sAdhuvRttAH kSINe pApe manasA vItazokAH . taM niSpatantaM tapasA dharmamIDyaM tadbhaktyA vai vizvarUpaM dadarza . dRSTvA cainaM vAmanobuddhidehai : saMhaSTAtmA mumude vAsudevaH . akSamAlAparikSiptaM jyotiSAM paramaM nidhim . tato nArAyaNo dRSTvA vavande vizvasambhavam .
varadaM pRthucAvaDyA pArvatyA sahitaM prabhum . krIDamAnaM mahAtmAnaM bhUtasaGghagaNairvRtam .
ajamIzAnamavyaktaM kAraNAtmAnamacyutam . abhivAdyAtha rudrAya sadyo ' ndhakanipAtine . padmAkSastaM virUpAkSamabhituSTAva bhaktimAn .
zrInArAyaNa uvAca tvatsambhUtA bhUtakRto vareNya goptAro ' sya bhuvanasyAdideva . AvizyemAM dharaNIM ye ' bhyarakSan . purA purANI tava devasRSTim .
surAsurAn nAgarakSaH pizAcAn narAn suparNAnatha gandharvayakSAn . pRthagvidhAn bhUtasaMghAMzca vizvAM stvatsambhUtAn vidma sarvAMstathaiva . aindraM yAmyaM vAruNaM vaittapAlyaM paitraM tvASTraM karma saumyaM ca tubhyam .
rUpaM jyotiH zabda AkAzavAyuH sparzaH svAdyaM salilaM gandha urvI . kAlo brahmA brahma ca brAhmaNAzca tvatsambhUtaM sthAsnu cariSNu cedam .
adbhyaH stokA yAnti yathA pRthaktvaM tAbhizcaikyaM saMkSaye yAnti bhUyaH . evaM vidvAn prabhavaM cApyayaM ca matvA bhUtAnAM tava sAyujyameti .
divyAmRtau mAnasau dvau suparNI vAcA zAkhAH pippalAH sapta gopAH . dazApyanye ye puraM dhArayanti tvayA sRSTAstvaM hi tebhyaH parohi .
bhUtaM bhavyaM bhavitA cApyadhRSyaM tvatsambhUtA bhuvanAnIha vizvA . bhaktaM ca mAM bhajamAnaM bhajasva mA rIriSo mAmahitAhitena .
AtmAnaM tvAmAtmano ' nanyabodhaM vidvAnevaM gacchati brahma zukram . astauSaM tvAM tava sammAnamicchan vicinvan vai sadRzaM devavarya . nabhiSTutaH pravikArSIzca mAyAm .
vyAsa uvAca tasmai varAnacintyAtmA nIlakaNThaH pinAkadhRt . arhate devamukhyAya prAyacchadRSisaMstutaH .
zrIbhagavAnuvAca matprasAdAnmanuSyeSu devagandharvayoniSu . aprameyabalAtmA tvaM nArAyaNa bhaviSyasi .
na ca tvAM prasahiSyanti devAsuramahoragAH . na pizAcA na gandharvA na yakSA na ca rAkSasAH .
na suparNAstathA nAgA na ca vizve viyonijAH . na kazcit tvAM ca devo ' pi samareSu vijeSyati .
na zastreNa na vajreNa nAgninA na ca vAyunA . na cATTaiNa na zuSkeNa brasena sthAvareNa ca . kazcit tava rujAM kartA matprasAdAt kathaMcanA avi vai samaraM gatvA bhaviSyasi mamAdhikaH .
evamete varA labdhAH purastAd viddhi zauriNA . sa eSa devazcarati mAyayA mohayaJjagat .
tasyaiva tapasA jAtaM naraM nAma mahAmunim . tulyametena devena taM jAnIhyarjunaM sadA .
tAvetau pUrvadevAnAM paramopacitAvRSI . lokayAtrAvidhAnArthaM saMjAyete yuge yuge .
tathaiva karmaNA kRtsnaM mahatastapaso ' pi ca . tejo manyuM ca vibhrattvaM jAto raudro mahAmate .
sa bhavAn devavat prAjJo jJAtvA bhavamayaM jagat . avAkarSastvamAtmAnaM niyamaistatpriyepsayA .
zubhramatra bhavAn kRtvA mahApuruSavigraham . IjivAMstvaM japaiomairupahAraizca mAnada .
janmakartatapoyogAstayostava ca puSkalAH . tAbhyAM liGge ' rcito devastvayArcAyAM yuge yuge . sarvarUpaM bhavaM jJAtvA liGge yo ' rcayati prabhum .
AtmayogAzca tasmin vai zAstrayogAzca zAzvatAH . evaM devA yajanto hi siddhAzca paramarSayaH .
prArthayante paraM loke sthANumekaM sa sarvakRt . sa eSa rudrabhaktazca kezavo rudrasambhavaH . kRSNa eva hi yaSTavyo yajJaizcaiva sanAtanaH .
sarvabhUtabhavaM jJAtvA liGgamarcati yaH prabhoH . tasminnabhyadhikAM prItiM karoti vRSabhadhvajaH .
saMjaya uvAca tasya tad vacanaM zrutvA droNaputro mahArathaH . namazcakAra rudrAya bahu mene ca kezavam .
hRSTaromA ca vazyAtmA so ' bhivAdya maharSaye . varUthinImabhiprekSya hyavahAramakArayat .
tataH pratyavahAro ' bhUt pANDavAnAM vizAmpate . kauravANAM ca dInAnAM droNe yudhi nipAtite .
yuddhaM kRtvA dinAn paJca droNo hatvA varUthinIm . brahmalokaM gato rAjan brAhmaNo vedapAragaH .
bhISma uvAca evamuktasya dUtena dupadasya tadA nRpa . corasyeva gRhItasya na prAvartata bhAratI .
sa yatnamakarot tIvra sambandhinyanumAnane . dUtairmadhurasambhASairna tadastIti saMdizan .
sa rAjA bhUya evAtha jJAtvA tattvamathAgamat . kanyeti pAJcAlasutAM tvaramANo viniryayau . .
tataH sampreSayAmAsa mitrANAmamitaujasAm . duhiturviprelambhaM taM dhAtrINAM vacanAt tadA .
tataH samudayaM kRtvA balAnAM rAjasattamaH . abhiyAne matiM cakre dupadaM prati bhArata .
tataH sammantrayAmAsa mantribhiH sa mahIpatiH . hiraNyavarmA rAjendra pAJcAlyaM pArthivaM prati .
tatra vai nizcitaM teSAmabhUd rAjJAM mahAtmanAm . tathyaM bhavati cedetat kanyA rAjan zikhaNDinI . baddhvA paJcAlarAjAnamAnayiSyAmahe gRham . anyaM rAjAnamAdhAya paJcAleSu narezvaram .
ghAtayiSyAma nRpatiM pAJcAlaM sazikhaNDinam . tat tadA ' nRtamAjJAya punarvRtAnnarAdhipaH . prAsthApayat pArSatAya nihanmIti sthiro bhava .
bhISma uvAca sa hi prakRtyA vai bhItaH kilbiSI ca narAdhipaH . bhayaM tIvramanuprApto dupadaH pRthivIpatiH .
visRjya dUtAn dAzArNe dupadaH zokamUrchitaH . sametya bhAryA rahite vAkyamAha narAdhipaH .
bhayena mahatA ' ' viSTo hRdi zokena cAhataH . pAJcAlarAjo dayitAM mAtaraM vai zikhaNDinaH .
abhiyAsyati mAM kopAt sambandhI sumahAbalaH . hiraNyavarmA nRpatiH karSamANo varUthinIm .
kimidAnIM kariSyAvo mUDhau kanyAmimAM prati . zikhaNDI kila putraste kanyeti parizaGkitaH .
iti saMcintya yatnena samitraH sabalAnugaH . vaJcito ' smIti manvAno mAM kiloddhartumicchati .
kimatra tathyaM suzroNi mithyA kiM brUhi zobhane . zrutvA tvattaH zubhaM vAkyaM saMvidhAsyAmyahaM tathA .
ahaM hi saMzayaM prApto bAlA ceyaM zikhaNDinI . tvaM ca rAjJi mahat kRcchre samprAptA varavarNini .
sA tvaM sarvavimokSAya tattvamAkhyAhi pRcchataH . tathA vidadhyAM suzroNi kRtyamAzu zucismite .
zikhaNDini ca mA bhaistvaM vidhAsye tatra tattvataH . kRpayA ' haM varArohe vaJcitaH putradharmataH .
mayA dAzArNako rAjA vaJcitaH sa mahIpatiH . tadAcakSva mahAbhAge vidhAsye tatra yaddhitam .
jAnatA hi narendreNa khyApanArthaM parasya vai . prakAzaM coditA devI pratyuvAca mahIpatim .
dupada uvAca bhUtAnAM prANinaH zreSThAH prANinAM buddhijIvinaH . buddhimatsu narAH zreSThA nareSvapi dvijAtayaH .
dvijeSu vaidyAH zreyAMso vaidyeSu kRtabuddhayaH . kRtabuddhiSu kartAraH kartRSu brahmavAdinaH .
sa bhavAn kRtabuddhInAM pradhAna iti me matiH . kulena ca viziSTo ' si vayasA ca zrutena ca .
prajJayA sadRzazcAsi zukreNAGgirasena ca . viditaM cApi te sarvaM yathAvRttaH sa kauravaH .
pANDavazca yathAvRttaH kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . dhRtarASTrasya vidite vaJcitAH pANDavAH paraiH .
vidureNAnunIto ' pi putramevAnuvartate . zakunirbuddhipUrvaM hi kuntIputraM samAhvayat .
anakSajJaM matAkSaH san kSatravRtte sthitaM zucim . te tathA vaJcayitvA tu dharmarAja yudhiSThiram .
na kasyAJcidavasthAyAM rAjyaM dAsyanti vai svayam . bhavAMstu dharmasaMyuktaM dhRtarASTra bruvan vacaH .
manAMsi tasya yodhAnAM dhruvamAvartayiSyati . vidurazcApi tad vAkyaM sAdhayiSyati tAvakam . bhISmadroNakRpAdInAM bhedaM saMjanayiSyati . amAtyeSu ca bhinneSu yodheSu vimukheSu ca .
punarekatrakaraNaM teSAM karma bhaviSyati . etasminnantare pArthAH sukhamekAgrabuddhayaH . senAkarma kariSyanti dravyANAM caiva saMcayam . vidyamAneSu ca sveSu lambamAne tathA tvayi .
na tathA te kariSyanti senAkarma na saMzayaH . etat prayojanaM cAtra prAdhAnyenopalabhyate .
saMgatyA dhRtarASTrazca kuryAd dharmyaM vacastava . sa bhavAn dharmayuktazca dhan/a teSu samAcaran .
kRpAluSu pariklezAn pANDavIyAn prakIrtayan . vRddheSu kuladharmaM ca bruvan pUrvairanuSThitam .
vibhetsyati manAMsyeSAmiti me nAtra saMzayaH . na ca tebhyo bhayaM te ' sti brAhmaNo hyasi vedavit .
dUtakarmaNi yuktazca sthavirazca vizeSataH . sa bhavAn puSyayogena muhUrtena jayena ca . kauraveyAn prayAtvAzu kaunteyasyArthasiddhaye .
vaizampAyana uvAca tathAnuziSTaH prayayau dupadena mahAtmanA . purodhA vRttasampanno nagaraM nAgasAhvayam .
ziSyaiH parivRto vidvAn nItizAstrArthakovidaH . pANDavAnAM hitArthAya kauravAn prati jagmivAn .
vaizampAyana uvAca cAturAzramyadharmAzca yatidharmAzca pANDava . lokavedottarAzcaiva kSAtradharme samAhitAH .
sarvANyetAni karmANi kSAtre bharatasattama . nirAziSo jIvalokAH kSatradharme ' vyavasthite .
apratyakSaM bahudvAraM dharmamAzramavAsinAm . prarUpayanti tadbhAvamAgamaireva zAzvatam .
apare vacanaiH puNyairvAdino lokanizcayam . anizcayajJA dharmANAmadRSTAnte pare hatAH .
pratyakSaM sukhabhUyiSThamAtmasAkSikamacchalam . sarvalokahitaM dharmaM kSatriyeSu pratiSThitam .
dharmAzrame ' dhyavasinAM brAhmaNAnAM yudhiSThira . yathA trayANAM varNAnAM saMkhyAtopazrutiH purAH .
rAjadharmeSvanumatA lokAH sucaritaiH saha . udAhRtaM te rAjendra yathA viSNuM mahaujasam .
sarvabhUtezvaraM devaM prabhuM nArAyaNaM purA . jagmuH subahuzaH zUrA rAjAno daNDanItaye . ekaikamAtmanaH karma tulayitvA ' ' zramaM purA . rAjAnaH paryupAsanta dRSTAntavacane sthitAH .
sAdhyA devA vasavazcAzvinau ca rudrAzca vizve marutAM gaNAzca . sRSTAH purA hyAdidevena devAH kSAtre dharme vartayante ca siddhAH .
atra te vartayiSyAmi dharmamarthavinizcayam . nirmaryAde vartamAne dAnavaikArNave purA . babhUva rAjA rAjendra mAndhAtA nAma vIryavAn . purA vasumatIpAlo yajJaM cakre didRkSayA . anAdimadhyanidhanaM devaM nArAyaNaM prabhum . sa rAjA rAjazArdUla mAndhAtA paramezvaram .
jagAma zirasA pAdau yajJe viSNormahAtmanaH . darzayAmAsa taM viSNU rUpamAsthAya vAsavam .
sa pArthivairvRtaH sadbhirarcayAmAsa taM prabhum . tasya pArthivasiMhasya tasya caiva mahAtmanaH . saMvAdo ' yaM mahAnAsId viSNuM prati mahAdyutim .
indra uvAca kimiSyate dharmabhRtAM variSTha yad draSTukAmo ' si tamaprameyam . anantamAyAmitamantravIrya nArAyaNaM hyAdidevaM purANam .
nAsau devo vizvarUpo mayApi zakyodraSTuM brahmaNA vApi sAkSAt . ye ' nye kAmAstava rAjan hRdisthA dAsye caitAMstvaM hi maryeSu rAjA .
satye sthito dharmaparo jitendriyaH zUro dRDhaprItirata : surANAm . buddhyA bhaktyA cottamazraddhayA ca tataste ' haM dadhi varAn yatheSTam .
mAndhAtovAca asaMzayaM bhagavannAdidevaM drakSyAmitvAhaM zirasA samprasAdya . tyaktvA kAmAn dharmakAmo hyarame micche gantuM satpathaM lokadRSTam .
kSAtrAd dharmAd vipulAdaprameya llokAH prAptAH sthApitaM svaM yazazca . dharmo yo ' sAvAdidevAt pravRtto lokazreSThaM taM na jAnAmi kartum .
indra uvAca asainikA dharmaparAzca dharma parAM gatiM na nayante hyayuktam . kSAtro dharmo hyAdidevAtpravRttaH pazcAdanye zeSabhUtAzca dharmAH .
zeSAH sRSTA hyantavanto hyanantAH saprasthAnAH kSAtradharmA viziSTAH . stasmAd dharmaM zreSThamimaM vadanti .
karmaNA vai purA devA RSayazcAmitaujasaH . trAtA : sarvaM prasahyArInkSatradharmeNa viSNunA .
yadi hyasau bhagavAnnAhaniSyad ripUn sarvAnasurAnaprameyaH . na brAhmaNA na ca lokAdikartA nAyaM dharmo nAdidharmo ' bhaviSyat .
imAmurvI nAjayadvikrameNa devazreSThaH sAsurAmAdidevaH . cAturvaNryaM cAturAzramyadharmAH sarve na syurbrAhmaNAnAM vinAzAt .
naSTA dharmAH zatadhA zAzvatAste kSAtreNa dharmeNa punaH pravRddhAH . yuge yuge hyAdidharmAH pravRttA lokajyeSThaM kSAtradharmaM vadanti .
AtmatyAgaH sarvabhUtAnukampA lokajJAnaM pAlanaM mokSaNaM ca . viSaNNAnAM mokSaNaM pIDitAnA kSAtre dharme vidyate pArthivAnAm . nirmaryAdA : kAmamanyupravRttA bhItA rAjJo nAdhigacchanti pApam . ziSTAzcAnye sarvadharmopapannAH sAdhvAcArAH sAdhu dharmaM vadanti .
putravat pAlyamAnAni rAjadharmeNa pArthivaiH . loke bhUtAni sarvANi carante nAtra saMzayaH .
sarvadharmaparaM kSAtraM lokazreSThaM sanAtanam . zazvadakSaraparyantamakSaraM sarvatomukham .
yudhiSThira uvAca kuta : sRSTamidaM vizvaM jagat sthAvarajaGgamam . pralaye ca kamabhyeti tanme brUhi pitAmaha .
sasAgaraH sagagana sazailaH sabalAhakaH . sabhUmiH sAgnipavano loko ' yaM kena nirmita : .
kathaM sRSTAni bhUtAni kathaM varNavibhaktayaH . zaucazaucaM kathaM teSAM dharmAdharmavidhiH katham .
kIdRzo jIvatAM jIvaH kva vA gacchanti ye mRtAH . asmAllokAdamuM lokaM sarvaM zaMsatu no bhavAn .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . bhRguNAbhihitaM zAstraM bharadvAjAya pRcchate .
bhRgu maharSimAsInaM bharadvAjo ' nvapRcchat .
sasAgara : sagaganaH sazaila : sabalAhakaH . sabhUmiH sAgnipavano loko ' yaM kena nirmitaH .
kathaM sRSTAni bhUtAni kathaM varNavibhaktayaH . zaucAzaucaM kathaM teSAM dharmAdharmavidhiH katham .
kIdRzo jIvatAM jIvaH kva vA gacchanti ye mRtAH . paralokamimaM cApi sarvaM zaMsitumarhasi .
evaM sa bhagavAn pRSTo bharadvAjena saMzayam . brahmarSirbrahmasaMkAzaH sarvaM tasmai tato ' bravIt .
bhRguruvAca mAnaso nAma vikhyAtaH zrutapUrvo maharSibhiH . anAdinidhano devastathAbhedyo ' jarAmaraH .
avyakta iti vikhyAtaH zAzvato ' thAkSayo ' vyayaH . yataH sRSTAni bhUtAni jAyante ca mriyanti ca .
so ' sRjat prathamaM devo mahAntaM nAma nAmataH . mahAn sasarjAhaMkAraM sa cApi bhagavAnatha . AkAzamiti vikhyAtaM sarvabhUtadharaH prabhuH .
AkAzAdabhavad vAri salilAdagnimArutau . agnimArutasaMyogAt tataH samabhavanmahI .
tatastejomayaM divyaM padmaM sRSTaM svayambhuvA . tasmAt padmAt samabhavad brahmA vedamayo nidhiH .
ahaMkAra iti khyAtaH sarvabhUtAtmabhUtakRt . brahmA vai sa mahAtejA ya ete paJca dhAtavaH .
zailAstasyAsthisaMjJAstu medo mAMsaM ca medinI . samudrAstasya rudhiramAkAzamudaraM tathA .
pavanazcaiva niHzvAsastejo ' gnirnimnagAH zirAH . agnISomau tu candrArko nayane tasya vizrute .
nabhazcordhvaM zirastasya kSitiH pAdau bhujau dizaH . durvijJeyo hyacintyAtmA siddhairapi na saMzayaH .
