ahaMkArasya yaH sraSTA sarvabhUtabhavAya vai . yataH samabhavad vizvaM pRSTo ' haM yadiha tvayA .
bharadvAja uvAca gaganasya dizAM caiva bhUtalasyAnilasya vA . kAnyatra parimANAni saMzayaM chindhi tattvataH .
