dvipAH sambhinnavarmANo vajrazAnisamaiH zaraiH . peturgiryapravezmAni vajravAtAgnibhiryathA .
sArohAsturagAH peturbahavo ' rjunatADitAH . nirjihvAtrAH kSitau kSINA rudhirAdrauH sudurdazaH .
