yathA nalavanaM kruddhaH prabhinnaH SaSTihAyanaH . mRdgIyAt tadvadAyastaH pArtho ' mRdgAccamU tava .
tasmin pramathite sainye bhagadatto narAdhipaH . tena nAgena sahasA dhanaMjayamupAdravat .
taM rathena naravyAghraH pratyagRhNAd dhanaMjayaH . sa saMnipAtastumulo babhUva sthanAgayoH .
kalpitAbhyAM yathAzAstraM rathena ca gajena ca . saMgrAme ceraturvIrau bhagadattadhanaJjayau .
