tatastu zarajAlena mahatA ' bhyavakIrya tau . codayAmAsa taM nAga vadhAyAcyutapArthayoH .
tamApatantaM dviradaM dRSTvA kuddhamivAntakam . cakre ' pasavyaM tvaritaH syandanena janArdanaH .
