karNaM drakSyati kuntI ca saubhadraM cApi yAdavI . draupadI paJca putrAMzca pitRRn bhrAtUMstathaiva ca .
pUrvamevaiSa hRdaye vyavasAyo ' bhavanmama . yadAsmi codito rAjJA bhavatyA pRthayaiva ca .
