gandharvApsarasazcaiva pizAcA guhmarAkSasAH . tathA puNyajanAzcaiva siddhA devarSayo ' pi ca . devAzca dAnavAzcaiva tathA devarSayo ' malAH . ta ete nidhanaM prAptAH kurukSetre raNAjire .
gandharvarAjo yo dhImAn dhRtarASTra iti zrutaH . sa eva mAnuSe loke dhRtarASTra : patistava .
pANDuM marudgaNAd viddhi viziSTatamamacyutam . dharmasyAMzo ' bhavat kSattA rAjA caiva yudhiSThiraH .
kaliM duryodhanaM viddhi zakuni dvAparaM tathA . duHzAsanAdIn viddhi tvaM rAkSasAzubhadarzane .
