nArAyaNaM hRSIkezamazvinau yamajau tathA . yaH sa vairArthamudbhUtaH saMgharSajananastathA . taM karNaM viddhi kalyANi bhAskaraM zubhadarzane . yazca pANDavadAyAdo hataH SaDbhirmahArathaiH . sa soma iha sobhadro yogAdevAbhavad dvidhA . dvidhA kRtvA ' ' tmano dehamAdityaM tapatAM varam . lokAMzca tApayAnaM vai viddhi karNaM ca zobhane .
draupadyA saha sambhUtaM dhRSTadyumnaM ca pAvakAt . agnerbhAgaM zubhaM viddhi rAkSasaM tu zikhaNDinam .
droNaM bRhaspaterbhAgaM viddhi drauNiM ca rudrajam . bhISmaM ca viddhi gAGgeyaM vasuM mAnuSatAM gatam .
