iti saMcitya manasA zraddadhAnaH striyA vacaH . balAkApratyayenAsau dhayazca vacanaiH zubhaiH . sampratasthe sa mithilAM kautUhalasamanvitaH .
atikrAmanaraNyAni grAmAMzca nagarANi cA . tato jagAma mithilAM janakena surakSitAm . dharmasetusamAkIrNAM yajJotsavavatI zubhAm .
gopurATTAlakavatI harmyaprAkArazobhanAm . pravizya nagarI ramyAM vimAnairbahubhiryutAm .
