mArgamAhiSamAMsAni vikrINantaM tapasvinam . AkulatvAcca kretRNAmekAnte saMsthito dvijaH .
sa tu jJAtvA dvijaM prAptaM sahasA sambhramotthitaH . AjagAma yato vipraH sthita ekAntadarzane .
vyAdha uvAca abhivAdaye tvAM bhagavan svAgataM te dvijottam . ahaM vyAdho hi bhadraM te kiM karomi prazAdhi mAm .
ekapalyA yadukto ' si gaccha tvaM mithilAmiti . jAnAmyetadahaM sarvaM yadarthaM tvamihAgataH .
zrutvA ca tasya tad vAkyaM sa vipro bhRzavismitaH dvitIyamidamAzcaryamityacintayata dvijaH .
adezasthaM hi te sthAnamiti vyAdho ' bravIdidam . gRhaM gacchAva bhagavan yadi te rocate ' nagha .
mArkaNDeya uvAca bADhamityeva taM vipro hRSTo vanacamabravIt . acatastu dvijaM kRtvA sa jagAma gRhaM prati .
pravizya ca gRhaM ramyamAsanenAbhipUjitaH . aryeNa ca sa vai tena vyAdhena dvijasattamaH .
tataH sukhopaviSTastaM vyAdhaM vacanamabravIt . karmaitad vai na sadRzaM bhavataH pratibhAti me . anutapye bhRzaM tAta tava ghoreNa karmaNA .
vyAdha uvAca kulocitamidaM karma pitRpaitAmahaM param . vartamAnasya me dharme sve manyuM mA kRthA dvija .
vidhAtrA vihita pUrvaM karma svamanupAlayan . prayatnAcca gurU vRddhau zuzrUSe ' haM dvijottama .
satyaM vade nAbhyasUye yathAzakti dadAmi ca . devatAtithibhRtyAnAmavaziSTena vartaye .
na kutsayAmyahaM kiMcinna garhe balavattaram . kRtamanveti kartAraM purA karma dvijottama .
kRSigorakSyavANijyamiha lokasya jIvanam . daNDanItistrayI vidyA tena loko bhavatyuta .
karma zUdre kRSirvaizye saMgrAmaH kSatriye smRtaH . brahmacaryaM tapo mantrAH satyaM ca brAhmaNe sadA .
rAjA prazAsti dharmeNa svakarmaniratAH prajAH . vikarmANazca ye kecit tAn yunakti svakarmasu .
