karma caitadasAdhUnAM vRjinAnAmasAdhuvat . na dharmo ' stIti manvAnAH zucInavahasanti ye . azraddadhAnA dharmasya te nazyanti na saMzayaH . mahAdRtirivAghmAtaH pApo bhavati nityadA .
