vedoktaH paramo dharmo dharmazAstreSu cAparaH . ziSTAcArazca ziSTAnAM trividhaM dharmalakSaNam .
dhAraNaM cApi vidyAnAM tIrthAnAmavagAhanam . kSamA satyArjavaM zaucaM satAmAcAradarzanam .
sarvabhUtadayAvanto ahiMsAniratAH sadA . paruSaM ca na bhASante sadA santo dvijapriyAH .
zubhAnAmazubhAnAM ca karmaNAM phalasaMcaye . vipAkamabhijAnanti te ziSTAH ziSTasammatAH . nyAyopetA guNopetAH sarvalokahitaiSiNaH . santaH svargajitaH zuklAH saMniviSTAzca satpathe .
dAtAraH saMvibhaktAro dInAnugrahakAriNaH . sarvapUjyAH zrutadhanAstathaiva ca tapasvinaH . sarvabhUtadayAvantaste ziSTAH ziSTasammatAH .
dAnaziSTAH sukhA~llokAnApnuvantIha ca zriyam . pIDayA ca kalatrasya bhRtyAnAM ca samAhitAH . atizaktyA prayacchanti santa : sadbhiH samAgatAH . lokayAtrAM ca pazyanto dharmamAtmahitAni ca .
evaM santo vartamAnAstvedhante zAzvatIH samAH . ahiMsA satyavacanamAnRzaMsyamathArjavam . adroho nAbhimAnazca hrIstitikSA damaH zamaH . dhImanto dhRtimantazca bhUtAnAmanukampakAH . akAmadveSasaMyuktAste santo lokasAkSiNaH .
trINyeva tu padAnyAhuH satAM vratamanuttamam . na caiva duhyed dadyAcca satyaM caiva sadA vadet .
sarvatra ca dayAvantaH santaH karuNavedinaH . gacchantIha susaMtuSTA dharmapanthAnamuttamam . ziSTAcArAH mahAtmAno yeSAM dharmaH sunizcitaH .
anasUyA kSamA zAntiH saMtoSa : priyavAditA . kAmakrodhaparityAga : ziSTAcAraniSevaNam . karma ca zrutasampannaM satAM mArgamanuttamam .
ziSTAcAra niSevante nityaM dharmamanuvratAH . prajJAprAsAdamAruhya mucyante mahato bhayAt . prekSanto lokavRttAni vividhAni dvijottama . atipuNyAni pApAni tAni dvijavarottama .
etat te sarvamAkhyAtaM yathAprajJaM yathAzrutam . ziSTAcAraguNaM brahman puraskRtya dvijarSabha .
yudhiSThira uvAca kanyAyAH prAptazulkAyAH patizcennAsti kazcana . tatra kA pratipattiH syAt tanme brUhi pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca yA ' putrakasya Rddhasya pratipAlyA tadA bhavet . atha cennAharecchulkaM krItA zulkapradasya sA .
tasyArthe ' patyamIheta yena nyAyena zaknuyAt . na tasmAnmantravatkAryaM kazcit kurvIta kiMcana .
svayaMvRtena sA ' ' jJaptA pitrA vai pratyapadyatA tat tasyAnye prazaMsanti dharmajJA netare janAH .
etat tu nApare cakrurapare jAtu sAdhavaH . sAdhUnAM punarAcAro garIyAn dharmalakSaNaH .
asminneva prakaraNe sukraturvAkyamabravIt . naptA videharAjasya janakasya mahAtmanaH .
asadAcarite mArge kathaM syAdanukIrtanam . atra praznaH saMzayo vA satAmevamupAlabhet .
asadeva hi dharmasya pradAnaM dharma AsuraH . nAnuzuzruma jAtvetAmimAM pUrveSu karmasu .
bhAryApatyorhi sambandhaH strIpuMsoH svalpa eva tu . ratiH sAdhAraNo dharma iti cAha sa pArthivaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca atha kena pramANena puMsAmAdIyate dhanam . putravaddhi pitustasya kanyA bhavitumarhati .
bhISma uvAca yathaivAtmA tathA putraH putreNa duhitA samA . tasyAmAtmani tiSThantyAM kathamanyo dhanaM haret .
mAtuzca yautakaM yat syAt kumArIbhAga eva saH . dauhitra eva tad rikthamaputrasya piturharet .
dadAti hi sa piNDAn vai piturmAtAmahasya ca . putradauhitrayoreva vizeSo nAsti dharmataH .
anyatra jAmayA sAdhu prajAnAM putra Ihate . duhitAnyatra jAtena putreNApi viziSyate .
dauhitrakeNa dharmeNa nAtra pazyAmi kAraNam . vikrItAsu hi ye putrA bhavanti pitureva te .
asUyavastvadharmiSThAH parasvAdAyinaH zaThAH . AsurAdadhisambhUtA dharmAd viSamavRttayaH .
atra gAthA yamodbhItAH kIrtayanti purAvidaH . dharmajJA dharmazAstreSu nibaddhA dharmasetuSu .
yo manuSyaH svakaM putraM vikrIya dhanamicchati . kanyAM vA jIvitArthAya yaH zulkena prayacchati . saptAvare mahAghore niraye kAlasAhvaye . svedaM mUtraM purISaM ca tasmin mUDhaH samaznute .
ArSe gomithunaM zulkaM kecidAhum\aSaiva tat . alpo vA bahu vA rAjan vikrayastAvadeva saH .
yadyapyAcarita : kaizcinnaiSa dharmaH sanAtanaH . anyeSAmapi dRzyante lokataH sampravRttayaH .
vazyAM kumArI balato ye tAM samupabhujate . ete pApasya kartArastamasyanthe ca zerate .
anyo ' pyatha na vikreyo manuSyaH kiM punaH prajAH . adharmamUlairhi dhanaistairna dharmo ' tha kazcana .
vaizampAyana uvAca samAgatAn vedavido rAjJazca pRthivIzvarAn . dRSTvA yudhiSThiro rAjA bhImasenamabhASata . upayAtA naravyAghrA ya ete pRthivIzvarAH eteSAM kriyatAM pUjA pUjArhA hi narAdhipAH .
ityuktaH sa tathA cakre narendreNa yazasvinA . bhImaseno mahAtejA yamAbhyAM saha pANDavaH .
athAbhyagacchadgovindo vRSNibhiH saha dharmajam . baladevaM puraskRtya sarvaprANabhRtAM varaH .
yuyudhAnena sahitaH pradyumnena gadena ca . nizaThenAtha sAmbena tathaiva kRtavarmaNA . .
teSAmapi parAM pUjAM cakre bhImo mahArathaH . vivizuste ca vezmAni ratnavanti ca sarvazaH .
yudhiSThirasamIpe tu kathAnte madhusUdanaH . arjunaM kathayAmAsa bahusaMgrAmakarSitam .
sa taM papraccha kaunteyaH punaH punarariMdamam . dharmajaH zakrajaM jiSNuM samAcaSTa jagatpatiH .
Agamad dvArakAvAsI mamAptaH puruSo nRpa . yo ' drAkSIt pANDavazreSTha bahusaMgrAmakarSitam .
samIpe ca mahAbAhupAcaSTa ca mama prabho . kuru kAryANi kaunteya hayamedhArthasiddhaye .
ityuktaH pratyuvAcainaM dharmarAjo yudhiSThiraH . diSTyA sa kuzalI jiSNurupAyAti ca mAdhava .
yadidaM saMdidezAsmin pANDavAnAM balAgraNI : tadA jJAtumihecchAmi bhavatA yadunandana .
ityukto dharmarAjena vRSNyandhakapatistadA . provAcedaM vaco vAgmI dharmAtmAnaM yudhiSThiram . idamAha mahArAja pArthavAkyaM smaran naraH . vAcyo yudhiSThiraH kRSNa kAle vAkyamidaM mama .
AgamiSyanti rAjAnaH sarve vai kauravarSabha . prAptAnAM mahatAM pUjA kAryA hyetat kSamaM hi naH .
ityetadvacanAd rAjA vijJApyo mama mAnada . yathA cAtyayikaM na syAd yadAharaNa ' bhavat . kartumarhati tada rAjA bhavAMzcApyanumanyatAm . rAjadvaSAnna nazyeyurimA rAjan punaH prajAH .
idamanyacca kaunteya vacaH sa puruSo ' bravIt . dhanaMjayasya nRpate tanme nigadataH zRNu .
upAyAsyati yajJaM no maNipUrapatirnRpaH . putro mama mahAtejA dayito babhruvAhanaH .
taM bhavAn madapezcArtha vidhivat pratipUjayet . sa tu bhakto ' nuraktazca mama nityamiti prabho .
ityetad vacanaM zrutvA dharmarAjo yudhiSThiraH . AbhanandyAsya tad vAkyamidaM vacanamabravIt .
parAzara uvAca kaH kasya copakurute kazca kasmai prayacchati . prANI karotyayaM karma sarvamAtmArthamAtmanA .
gauraveNa parityaktaM niHsnehaM parivarjayet . sodaryaM bhrAtaramapi kimutAnyaM pRthagjanam .
viziSTasya viziSTAcca tulyau dAnapratigrahau . tayoH puNyataraM dAnaM tad dvijasya prayacchataH .
nyAyAgataM dhanaM caiva nyAyenaiva vivardhitam . saMrakSyaM yatnamAsthAya dharmArthamiti nizcayaH .
na dharmArthI nRzaMsena karmaNA dhanamarjayet . zaktitaH sarvakAryANi kuryAnnarddhimanusmaret .
apo hi prayataH zItAstApitA jvalanena vA . zaktito ' tithaye dattvA kSudhArtAyAznute phalam .
rantidevena lokeSTA siddhiH prAptA mahAtmanA . phalapatrairatho mUlairmunInarcitavAMzca saH .
taireva phalapatraizca sa mATharamatoSayat . tasmAllebhe paraM sthAnaM zaibyo ' pi pRthivIpatiH .
devatAtithibhRtyebhyaH pitRbhyazcAtmanastathA . RNavAn jAyate martyastasmAdanRNatAM vrajet .
svAdhyAyena maharSibhyo devebhyo yajJakarmaNA . pitRbhyaH zrAddhadAnena nRNAmabhyarcanena ca .
vAcA zeSAvahAryeNa pAlanenAtmano ' pi ca . yathAvad bhRtyavargasya cikIt karma AditaH .
prayatnena ca saMsiddhA dhanairapi vivarjitAH . samyagghutvA hutavahaM munayaH siddhimAgatAH .
vizvAmitrasya putratvamRcIkatanayo ' gamat . RgbhiH stutvA mahAbAho devAn vai yajJabhAginaH .
gataH zukratvamuzanA devadevaprasAdanAt . devIM stutvA tu gagane modate yazasA vRtaH .
asito devalazcaiva tathA nAradaparvatau . kakSIvAn jAmadagnyazca rAmastANDyastathA ' ' tmavAn . . vasiSTho jamadagnizca vizvAmitro ' trireva ca . bharadvAjo harizmazruH kuNDadhAraH zrutazravAH . ete maharSayaH stutvA viSNumRgbhiH samAhitAH . lebhire tapasA siddhiM prasAdAt tasya dhImataH .
anazciAhatAM prAptAH santaH stutvA tameva ha . na tu vRddhimihAnvicchet karma kRtvA jugupsitam .
ye ' rthA dharmeNa te satyA ye ' dharmeNa dhigastu tAn . dharmaM vai zAzvataM loke na jahyAd dhanakAjhyA .
AhitAgnirhi dharmAtmA yaH sa puNyakRduttamaH . vedA hi sarve rAjendra sthitAstriSvagniSu prabho .
sa cApyagnyAhito vipraH kriyA yasya na hIyate . zreyo hyanAhitAgnitvamagnihotraM na niSkriyam .
agnirAtmA ca mAtA ca pitA janayitA tathA . guruzca narazArdUla paricaryA yathAtatham .
mAnaM tyaktvA yo naro vRddhasevI vidvAn klIbaH pazyati prItiyogAt . dAkSyeNa hIno dharmayukto nadAnto loke ' smin vai pUjyate sadbhirAryaH .
lomaharSaNaputra ugrazravAH paurANiko naimiSAraNye zaunakasya kulapateAdazavArSika satre RSInabhyAgatAnupatasthe .
paurANikaH purANe kRtazramaH sa kRtAJjalistAnuvAca . kiM bhavantaH zrotumicchanti kimahaM bravANIti .
tamRSayaH UcuH paramaM lomaharSaNe vakSyAmastvAM naH prativakSyasi vacaH zuzrUSatAM kathAyogaM na : kathAyoge .
tatra bhagavAn kulapatistu madhyAste .
yo ' sau divyA : kathA veda devatAsurasaMzritAH . manuSyoragagandharvakathA veda ca sarvazaH .
sa cApyasminmakhe saute vidvAn kulapatirdvijaH . dakSodhRtavrato dhImAn zAstre cAraNyake guruH .
satyavAdI zamaparastapasvI niyatavrataH . sarveSAmeva no mAnyaH sa tAvatpratipAlyatAm .
tasminnadhyAsati gurAvAsanaM paramArcitam . tato vakSyasi yattvAM sa prakSyati dvijasattamaH .
sautiruvAca evamastu gurau tasminnupaviSTe mahAtmani . tena pRSTaH kathA : puNyA vakSyAmi vividhAzrayAH .
so ' tha viprarSabhaH sarvaM kRtvA kAryaM yathAvidhi . devAnvAgbhiH pitRRnadbhistarpayitvAjagAma ha . yatra brahmarSayaH siddhAH sukhAsInA dhRtavratAH . yajJAyatanamAzritya sUtaputrapuraHsarAH .
RtvikSvatha sadasyeSu sa vai gRhapatistadA . upaviSTeSUpaviSTaH zaunako ' thAbravIdidam .
saMjaya uvAca AdadAnastu zUrANAmAyUMSyabhavadArjuniH . antakaH sarvabhUtAnAM prANAn kAla ivAgate .
sa zakra iva vikrAntaH zakrasUnoH suto balI . abhimanyustadAnIkaM loDayan samadRzyata .
pravizyaiva tu rAjendra kSatriyendrAntakopamaH . satyazravasamAdatta vyAghro mRgamivolvaNaH .
satyavasi cAkSise tvaramANA mahArathAH . pragRhya vipulaM zastramabhimanyumupAdravan .
ahaM pUrvamahaM pUrvamiti kSatriyapuGgavAH . svardhamAnAH samAjagmurjighAMsanto ' rjunAtmajam .
kSatriyANAmanIkAni pradutAnyabhidhAvatAm . jagrAsa timirAsAdya kSudramatsyAnivArNave .
ye kecana gatAstasya samIpamapalAyinaH . na te pratinyavartanta samudrAdiva sindhavaH .
mahAgrAhagRhIteva vAtavegabhayArditA . samakampata sA senA vibhraSTA naurivArNave .
atha rukmaratho nAma madrezvarasuto balI . trastAmAzvAsayan senAmatrasto vAkyamabravIt .
alaM trAsena vaH zUrA naiSa kazcinmayi sthite . mahamenaM grahISyAmi jIvagrAhaM na saMzayaH .
evamuktvA tu saubhadramabhidudrAva vIryavAn . sukalpitenohyamAnaH syandanena virAjatA .
sau ' bhimanyu tribhirbANairviddhvA vakSasyathAnadat . tribhizca dakSiNe bAhau savye ca nizitaistribhiH .
sa tasteSvasanaM chittvA phAlguniH savyadakSiNau . bhujau zirazca svakSibhU kSitau kSipramapAtayat .
dRSTvA rukmarathaM rugNaM putraM zalyasya mAninam . jIvagrAhaM jighRkSantaM saubhadreNa yazasvinA .
saMgrAmadurmadA rAjan rAjaputrAH prahAriNaH . vayasyAH zalyaputrasya suvarNavikRtadhvajAH .
tAlamAtrANi cApAni vikarSanto mahAbalAH . Arjuni zaravarSeNa samantAt paryavArayan .
zUraiH zikSAbalopetaistaruNairatyamarSaNaiH . dRSTikaM samare zUraM saubhadramaparAjitam . chAdyamAnaM zaravrAtaiiSTo duryodhano ' bhavat . vaivasvatasya bhavanaM gataM hyenamamanyata .
suvarNapuGariSubhirnAnAliGgaiH sutejanaiH . adRzyamArjuniM cakrurnimeSAt te nRpAtmajAH .
sUtAzvadhvajaM tasya syandanaM taM ca mAriSa . AcitaM samapazyAma zvAvidhaM zalalairiva .
sa gADhaviddhaH kruddhazca totrairgaja ivAditaH . gAndharvamastramAyacchad rathamAyAM ca bhArata .
arjunena tapastaptvA gandharvebhyo yadAhRtam . tumburupramukhebhyo vai tenAmohayatAhitAn .
ekadA zatadhA rAjan dRzyate sma sahasradhA . alAtacakravat saMkhye kSipramastrANi darzayan .
rathacaryAstramAyAbhirmohayitvA paraMtapaH . vibheda zatadhA rAjazarIrANi mahIkSitAm .
prANAH prANabhRtAM saMkhye preSitAni zitaiH zaraiH . rAjan prApuramuM lokaM zarIrANyavaniM yayuH .
dhanUMSyazvAn niyantuMzca dhvajAn bAhUMca sAGgadAn . zirAMsi ca zitairbANaisteSAM ciccheda phAlguniH .
cUtArAmo yathA bhagnaH paJcavarSaH phalopagaH . rAjaputrazataM tadvat saubhadreNa nipAtitam .
kruddhAzIviSasaMkAzAn sukumArAn sukhocitAn . ekena nihatAn dRSTvA bhIto duryodhano ' bhavat .
rathinaH kuJjarAnazvAn padAtIMzcApi majjataH . dRSTvA duryodhanaH kSipramupAyAt tamamarSitaH .
tayoH kSaNamivApUrNaH saMgrAmaH samapadyatA athAbhavat te vimukhaH putraH zarazatAhataH .
yudhiSThira uvAca yathA buddhyA mahIpAlo bhraSTazrIvicarenmahIm . kAladaNDaviniSpiSTastanme brUhi pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . vAsavasya ca saMvAdaM balevairocanasya ca .
pitAmahamupAgamya praNipatyakRtAJjaliH . sarvAnevAsurAn jitvA baliM papraccha vAsavaH .
yasya sma dadato vittaM na kadAcana hIyate . taM baliM nAdhigacchAmi brahmannAcakSva me balim .
sa vAyurvaruNazcaiva sa raviH sa ca candramAH . so ' gnistapati bhUtAni jalaM ca sa bhavatyuta .
taM baliM nAdhigacchAmi brahmannAcakSva me balim . sa eva hyastamayate sa sma vidyotate dizaH . sa varSati sma varSANi yathAkAlamatandritaH . taM baliM nAdhigacchAmi brahmannAcakSva me balim .
brahmovAca naitat te sAdhu maghavan yadenamanupRcchasi . pRSTastu nAnRtaM brUyAt tasmAd vakSyAmi te balim .
uSTeSu yadi vA goSu khareSvazveSu vA punaH . variSTho bhavitA jantuH zUnyAgAre zacIpate .
zakra uvAca yadi sma balinA brahmazUnyAgAre sameyivAn . hanyAmenaM na vA hanyAM tad brahmannanuzAdhi mAm .
brahmovAca mA sma zakra baliM hiMsIna balirvadhamarhati . nyAyastu zakra praSTavyastvayA vAsava kAmyayA .
evamukto bhagavatA mahendraH pRthivIM tadA . cacArairAvataskandhamadhiruhya zriyA vRtaH .
tato dadarza sa baliM kharaveSeNa saMvRtam . yathA ' ' khyAtaM bhagavatA zUnyAgArakRtAlayam .
zakra uvAca kharayonimanuprAptastuSabhakSo ' si dAnava . iyaM te yoniradhamA zocasyAho na zocasi .
adRSTaM bata pazyAmi dviSatAM vazAmAgatam . zriyA vihInaM mitraizca bhraSTavIryaparAkramam .
yat tad yAnasahaustvaM jJAtibhiH parivAritaH . lokAn pratApayan sarvAn yAsyasmAnavitarkayan .
tvanmukhAzcaiva daiteya vyatiSThaMstva zAsane . akRSTapacyA ca mahI tavaizvarye babhUva ha .
idaM ca te ' dya vyasanaM zocasyAho na zocasi . yadA ' ' tiSThaH samudrasya pUrvakUle vilelihan .
jJAtIn vibhajato vittaM tadA ' ' sIt te manaH katham . yat te sahasrasamitA nanRturdevayoSitaH .
kathamadya tadA caiva manaste dAnavezvara . chatraM tavAsIt sumahat sauvarNaM ratnabhUSitam .
bahUni varSapUgAni vihAre dIpyataH zriyA . sarvAH puSkaramAlinyaH sarvAH kAJcanasaprabhAH .
nanRtustatra gandharvAH SaT sahasrANi saptadhA . yUpastavAsIt sumahAn yajataH sarvakAzanaH .
yatrAdadaH sahasrANi ayutAnAM gavAM daza . anantaraM sahasreNa tadA ' ' sId dainya kA matiH .
yadA ca pRthivIM sarvAM yajamAno ' nuparyagAH . zamyAkSepeNa vidhinA tadA ' ' sIt kiM tu te hRdi . na te pazyAmi bhRGgAraM na cchatraM vyajane na ca . brahmadattAM ca te mAlAM na pazyAmyasurAdhipa .
baliruvAca na tvaM pazyasi bhRGgAraM na cchatraM vyajane na ca . brahmadattAM ca me mAlAM na tvaM drakSyasi vAsava .
guhAyAM nihitAni tvaM mama ratnAni pRcchasi . yadA me bhavitA kAlastadA tvaM yAni drakSyasi .
na tvetadanurUpaM te yazaso vA kulasya ca . samRddhArtho ' samRddhArthaM yanmAM kasthitumicchasi .
na hi duHkheSu zocante na prahRSyanti cardhiSu . kRtaprajJA jJAnatRptAH kSAntAH santo manISiNaH .
tvaM tu prAkRtayA buddhyA purandara vikatyase . yadAhamiva bhAvI syAstadA naivaM vadiSyasi .
tvaM tu prAkRtayA buddhyA purandara vikatyase . yadAhamiva bhAvI syAstadA naivaM vadiSyasi .
saMjaya uvAca tato yudhiSThiro rAjA pratinandya janArdanam . uvAca paramaprItaH kaunteyo devakIsutam .
kaccijjJAnAni sarvANi prasannAni tavAcyuta .
vAsudevo ' pi tadyuktaM paryapRcchad yudhiSThiram . tatazca prakRtIH kSattA nyavedayadupasthitAH .
anujJAtazca rAjJA sa prAvezayata taM janam . virATaM bhImasenaM ca dhRSTadyumnaM ca sAtyakim . cedipaM dhRSTaketuM ca drupadaM ca mahAratham . zikhaNDinaM yamo caiva cekitAnaM sakekayam . yuyutsuM caiva kauravyaM pAJcAlyaM cottamaujasam . yudhAmanyuM subAhuM ca draupadeyAMzca sarvazaH .
ete cAnye ca bahavaH kSatriyAH kSatriyarSabham . upatasthurmahAtmAnaM vivizuzcAsane zubhe .
ekasminnAsane vIrAvupaviSTau mahAbalau . kRSNazca yuyudhAnazca mahAtmAnau mahAdyutI .
tato yudhiSThirasteSAM zrRNvatAM madhusUdanam . abravIt puNDarIkAkSamAbhASya madhuraM vacaH .
ekaM tvAM vayamAzritya sahasrAkSamivAmarAH . prArthamAyo jayaM yuddhe zAzvatAni sukhAni ca .
tvaM hi rAjyavinAzaM na dviSadbhizcanirAkriyAm . klezAMzca vividhAn kRSNa sarvAMstAnapi veda naH .
tvayi sarveza sarveSAmasmAkaM bhaktavatsala . sukhamAyattamatyarthe yAtrA ca madhusUdana .
sa tathA kuru vArSNeya yathA tvayi mano mama . arjunasya yathA satyA pratijJA syAccikIrSitA .
sa bhavAMstArayatvasmAd duHkhAmarSamahArNavAt . pAraM titIrSatAmadya plavo no bhava mAdhava .
na hi tat kurute saMkhye rathI ripuvadhodyataH . yathA vai kurute kRSNa sArathiryalamAsthitaH .
yathaiva sarvAsvApatsu pAsi vRSNIJjanArdana . tathaivAsmAn mahAbAho vRjinAt trAtumarhasi .
tvamagAdhe ' plave magnAn pANDavAn kurusAgare . samuddhara plavo bhUtvA zaGkhacakragadAdhara .
namaste devadeveza sanAtana vizAtana . viSNo jiSNo hare kRSNa vaikuNTha puruSottama .
nAradastvAM samAcakhyau purANamRSisattamam . varadaM zAGgiNaM zreSThaM tat satyaM kuru mAdhava .
ityuktaH puNDarIkAkSo dharmarAjena saMsadi . toyameghasvano vAgmI pratyuvAca yudhiSThiram .
vAsudeva uvAca sAmareSvapi lokeSu sarveSu na tathAvidhaH . zarAsanadharaH kazcid yathA pArtho dhanajaMyaH .
vIryavAnastrasampannaH parAkrAnto mahAbalaH . yuddhazoNDaH sadAmarSI tejasA paramo nRNAm .
sa yuvA vRSabhaskandho dIrghabAhurmahAbalaH . siMharSabhagatiH zrImAn dviSataste haniSyati .
ahaM ca tat kariSyAmi yathA kuntIsuto ' rjunaH . dhArtarASTrasya sainyAni dhakSyatyagnirivendhanam .
adya taM pApakarmANaM kSudraM saubhadraghAtinam . apunardarzanaM mArgamiSubhiH kSepsyate ' rjunaH .
tasyAdya gRdhrAH zyenAzca caNDagomAyavastathA . bhakSayiSyanti mAMsAni ye cAnye puruSAdakAH .
yadyasya devA goptAraH sendrAH sarve tathApyasau . rAjadhAnI yamasyAdya hataH prApsyati saMkule .
nihatya saindhavaM jiSNuradya tvAmupayAsyati . vizoko vijvaro rAjan bhava bhUtipuraskRtaH .
dhRtarASTra uvAca yadidaM dharmagahanaM buddhyA samanugamyate . taddhi vistarataH sarvaM buddhimArga prazaMsa me .
vidura uvAca atra te vartayiSyAmi namaskRtvA svayaMbhuve . yathA saMsAragahanaM vadanti paramarSayaH .
kazcinmahati kAntAre vartamAno dvijaH kila . mahad durgamanuprApto vanaM kravyAdasaMkulam .
siMhavyAghragajaughairatighoraM mahAsyanaiH . pizitAdairatibhayairmahogrAkRtibhistathA . samantAt saMparikSiptaM yat sma dRSTvA trased yamaH .
tadasya dRSTvA hRdayamudvegamagamat param . abhyucchayazca romNAM vai vikriyAca paraMtapa .
sa tad vanaM vyanusaran sampradhAvannitastataH . vIkSamANo dizaH sarvAH zaraNaM va bhavediti .
sa teSAM chidramanvicchan pradruto bhayapIDitaH . na ca niryAti vai dUraM na vA tairvipramocyate .
athApazyad vanaM ghoraM samantAd vAgarAvRtam . bAhubhyAM samparikSipta striyA paramaghorayA .
paJcazIrSadharai gaiH zailairiva samunnataiH . nabhaHspRzairmahAvRkSaH parikSiptaM mahAvanam .
vanamadhye ca tatrAbhUdudapAnaH samAvRtaH . vallIbhistRNachannAbhirdUDhAbhirabhisaMvRtaH .
papAta sa dvijastatra nigUDhe salilAzaye . . vilagnazcAbhavat tasmin latAsaMtAnasaMkule . panasasya yathA jAtaM vRntavaddhaM mahAphalam . sa tathA lambate tatra rArdhvapAdo hyadhaHzirAH .
atha tatrApi cAnyo ' sya bhUyo jAta upadravaH . kUpamadhye mahAnAgamapazyata mahAbalam .
kUpavInAhavelAyAmapazyata mahAgajam . SaDvaktraM kRSNazuklaM ca dviSaTkapadacAriNam .
krameNa parisarpantaM vallIvRkSasamAvRtam . tasya cApi prazAkhAsu vRkSazAkhAvalambinaH . nAnArUpA madhukarA ghorarUpA bhayAvahAH . Asate madhu saMvRtya pUrvameva niketajAH .
bhUyo bhUyaH samIhante madhUni bharatarSabha . svAdanIyAni bhUtAnAM yairbAlo viprakRSyate .
tatraiva ca manuSyasya teSAM madhUnAM bahudhA dhArA prasravate tadA . AlambamAnaH sa pumAn dhArAM pibati sarvadA .
na cAsya tRSNA viratA pibamAnasya saMkaTe . abhIpsati tadA nityamatRptaH sa punaH punaH .
na cAsya jIvite rAjan nirvedaH samajAyata . jIvitAzA pratiSThitA . kRSNAH zvetAzca taM vRkSaM kuTTayanti ca mUSikAH .
vyAlaizca vanadurgAnte striyA ca paramograyA . kUpAdhastAca nAgena vInAhe kuJjareNa ca . vRkSaprapAtAca bhayaM mUSikebhyazca paJcamam . madhulobhAnmadhukaraiH SaSThamAhurmahad bhayam .
evaM sa vasate tatra kSiptaH saMsArasAgare . na caiva jIvitAzAyAM nirvedamupagacchati .
janamejaya uvAca prApya rAjyaM mahAbAhurdharmaputrau yudhiSThiraH . yadanyadakarod vipra tanme vaktumihArhasi .
bhagavAn vA hRSIkezastrailokyasya paro guruH . RSe yadakarodvIrastacca vyAkhyAtumarhasi .
vaizampAyana uvAca zRNu tattvena rAjendra kIrtyamAnaM mayAnagha . vAsudevaM puraskRtya yadakurvata pANDavAH .
prApya rAjyaM mahArAja kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . cAturvaNryaM yathAyogyaM sve sve sthAne nyavezayat .
brAhmaNAnAM sahasraM ca snAtakAnAM mahAtmanAm . sahasraM niSkamekaikaM dApayAmAsa pANDavaH .
tathA ' nujIvino bhRtyAn saMzritAnatithInapi . kAmaiH saMtarpayAmAsa kRpaNAMstarkakAnapi .
purohitAya dhaumyAya prAdAdayutazaH sa gA : . dhanaM suvarNa rajataM vAsAMsi vividhAnyapi .
kRpAya ca mahArAja guruvRttimavartata . vidurAya ca rAjAsau pUjAM cakre yatavrataH .
bhakSyAnapAnairvividhasairvAsobhiH zayanAsanaiH . sarvAn saMtoSayAmAsa saMzritAn dadatAM varaH .
labdhaprazamanaM kRtvA sa rAjA rAjasattama . yuyutsordhArtarASTrasya pUjAM cakre mahAyazAH .
dhRtarASTrAya tad rAjyaM gAndhArtha vidurAya ca . nivedya susthavad rAjA sukhamAste yudhiSThiraH .
tathA sarvaM sa nagaraM prasAdya bharatarSabha . vAsudevaM mahAtmAnamabhyagacchat kRtAJjaliH .
tato mahati paryaGke maNikAJcanabhUSite . dadarza kRSNamAsInaM nIlameghasamadyutim .
jAjvalyamAnaM vapuSA divyAbharaNabhUSitam . pItakauzeyavasanaM hemnevopagataM maNim .
kaustubhenorasisthena maNinAbhivirAjitam . udyatevodayaM zailaM sUryeNAbhivirAjitam .
naupamyaM vidyate tasya triSu lokeSu kiMcana . so ' bhigamya mahAtmAnaM viSNuM puruSavigraham . uvAdha madhuraM rAjA smitapUrvamidaM tadA . sukhena te nizA kaccid vyuSTA buddhimatAM vara .
kaccijjJAnAni sarvANi prasannAni tavAcyuta . tathaivopazritA devI buddhirbuddhimatAM vara .
vayaM rAjyamanuprAptAH pRthivI ca vaze sthitA . tava prasAdAd bhagavaMstrilokagativikrama . jayaM prAptA yazazcayaM na ca dharmacyutA vayam .
taM tathA bhASamANaM tu dharmarAjamariMdamam . novAca bhagavAn kiMcid dhyAnamevAnvapadyata .
utathya uvAca kAlavIM ca parjanyo dharmacArI ca pArthivaH . sampad yadeSA bhavati sA bibhati sukhaM prajAH .
yo na jAnAti hartuM vA vastrANAM rajako malam . raktAnAM vA zodhayituM yathA nAsti tathaiva saH .
evametad dvijendrANAM kSatriyANAM vizAM tathA . zUdrazcaturtho varNAnAM nAnAkarmasvavasthitaH .
karma zUdre kRSivaizye daNDanItizca rAjani . brahmacaryaM tapo mantrAH satyaM cApi dvijAtiSu .
teSAM yaH kSatriyo veda vastrANAmiva zodhanam . zIladoSAn vinirhartuM sa pitA sa prajApatiH .
kRtaM tretA dvAparaM ca kalizca bharatarSabha . rAjavRttAni sarvANi rAjaiva yugamucyate .
cAturvaNryaM tathA vedAzcAturAzramyameva ca . sarvaM pramuhyate hyetad yadA rAjA pramAdyati .
agnitretA trayI vidyA yajJAzca sahadakSiNAH . sarva eva pramAdyanti yadA rAjA pramAdyati .
rAjaiva kartA bhUtAnAM rAjaiva ca vinAzakaH . dharmAtmA yaH sa kartA syAdadharmAtmA vinAzakaH .
rAjJo bhAryAzca putrAzca bAndhavAH suhRdastathA . sametya sarve zocanti yadA rAjA pramAdyati .
hastino ' zvAzca gAvacApyuSTrAzvataragardabhAH . adharmabhUte nRpatau sarve sIdanti jantavaH .
durbalArthaM valaM sRSTaM dhAtrA mAndhAtarucyate . abalaM tu mahadbhUtaM yasmin sarvaM pratiSThitam .
yacca bhUtaM sambhajate ye ca bhUtAstadanvayAH . adharmasthe hi nRpatau sarve zocanti pArthiva .
durbalasya ca yaccakSurmunerAzIviSasya ca . aviSahyatamaM manye mA sma durbalamAsadaH .
durbalAMstAta budhyethA nityamevAvimAnitAn . mA tvAM durbalacaDhUMSi pradaheyuH sabAndhavam .
na hi durbaladagdhasya kule kiMcit prarohati . AmUlaM nirdahantyeva mA sma durbalamAsadaH .
abalaM vai balAcchreyo yaccAtibalavabalam . balasyAbaladagdhasya na kiMcidavaziSyate .
vimAnito hataH kruzstrAtAraM cena vindati . amAnuSakRtastatra daNDo hanti narAdhipam .
mA sma tAta raNe sthitvA bhuJjIthA durbalaM janam . mA tvAM durbalacakSUSi dahantvagnirivAzrayam .
yAni mithyAbhizastAnAM patantyazrUNi rodatAm . tAni putrAn pazUn nanti teSAM mithyAbhizaMsanAt .
yadi nAtmani putreSu na cet pautreSu naptRSu . na hi pApaM kRtaM karma sadyaH phalati gauriva .
yatrAbalo vadhyamAnastrAtAraM nAdhigacchati . mahAn daivakRtastatra daNDaH patati dAruNaH .
yuktA yadA jAnapadA bhikSante brAhmaNA iva . abhIkSNaM bhikSurUpeNa rAjAnaM manti tAdRzAH .
rAjJo yadA janapade bahavo rAjapUruSAH . anayenopavartante tad rAjJaH kilbiSaM mahat .
yadA yuktyA nayedarthAn kAmAdarthavazena vA . kRpaNaM yAcamAnAnAM tad rAjJo vaizasaM mahat .
mahAn vRkSo jAyate vardhate ca taM caiva bhUtAni samAzrayanti . yadA vRkSazchidyate dahyate ca tadAzrayA aniketA bhavanti .
yadA rASTre dharmamayaM caranti saMskAraM vA rAjaguNaM bruvANA : . tairevAdharmazcarito dharmamohAt tUrNaM jahyAt sukRtaM duSkRtaM ca .
yatra pApA jJAyamAnAzcaranti satAM kalivindate tatra rAjJaH . stadA rAjyaM vardhate bhUmipasya .
yazcAmAtyAn mAnayitvA yathArtha mantre ca yuddhe ca nRpo niyuGgyAt . vivardhate tasya rASTra nRpasya bhukke mahIM cApyakhilAM cirAya .
yaccApi sukRtaM karma vAcaM caiva subhASitAm . samIkSya pUjayan rAjA dharmaM prApnotyanuttamam .
saMvibhajya yadA bhukke nAmAtyAnavamanyate . nihanti balinaM dRptaM sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
trAyate hi yadA sarvaM vAcA kAyena karmaNA . putrasyApi na mRSyecca sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
saMvibhajya yadA bhukke nRpatirdurbalAn narAn . tadA bhavanti balinaH sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
yadA rakSati rASTrANi yadA dasyUnapohati . yadA jayati saMgrAme sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
pApamAcarato yatra karmaNA vyAhRtena vA . priyasyApi na mRSyeta sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
yadA zAraNikAn rAjA putravat parirakSati . bhinatti ca na maryAdAM sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
yadA ' ' ptadakSiNairyajJairyajate zraddhayAnvitaH . kAmadveSAvanAdRtya sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
kRpaNAnAthavRddhAnAM yadAzru parimArjati . harSa saMjanayan nRNAM sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
vivardhayati mitrANi tathArIzcApi karSati . sampUjayati sAdhUMzca sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
satyaM pAlayati prItyA nityaM bhUmiM prayacchati . pUjayedatithIn bhRtyAn sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
nigrahAnugrahau cobhau yatra syAtAM pratiSThitau . asmin loke pare caiva rAjA sa prApnute phalam .
yamo rAjA dhArmikANAM mAndhAtaH paramezvaraH . saMyacchan bhavati prANAnasaMyacchaMstu pAtukaH .
RtvikpurohitAcAryAn satkRtyAnavamanya ca . yadA samyak pragRhNAti sa rAjJo dharma ucyate .
yamo yacchati bhUtAni sarvANyevAvizeSataH . tathA rAjJAnukartavyaM yantavyA vidhivat prajAH .
sahasrAkSeNa rAjA hi sarvathaivopamIyate . sa pazyati ca yaM dharma sa dharmaH puruSarSabha .
apramAdena zikSethAH kSamAM buddhiM dhRti matim . bhUtAnAM caiva jijJAsA sAdhvasAdhu ca sarvadA .
saMgrahaH sarvabhUtAnAM dAnaM ca madhuraM vacaH . paurajAnapadAcaiva goptavyAste yathAsukham .
na jAtvadakSo nRpatiH prajAH zaknoti rakSitum . bhAro hi sumahAMstAta rAjyaM nAma suduSkaram .
taddaNDavinnRpaH prAjJaH zUraH zaknoti rakSitum . na hi zakyamadaNDena klIbenAbuddhinApi vA .
abhirUpaiH kule jAtairdakSairbhaktairbahuzrutaiH . sarvA buddhIH parIkSepAstApasAzramiNAmapi .
atastvaM sarvabhUtAnAM dharmaM vetsyasi vai param . svadeze paradeze vA na te dharmo vinakSayati .
tasmAdarthAcca kAmAcca dharma evottaro bhavet . asmilloke pare caiva dharmAtmA sukhamedhate .
tyajanti dArAn putrAMzca manuSyAH paripUjitAH . saMgrahazcaiva bhUtAnAM dAnaM ca madhurA ca vAk . apramAdazca zaucaM ca rAjJo bhUtikaraM mahat . etebhyazcaiva mAndhAtaH satataM mA pramAdithAH .
apramatto bhaved rAjA chidradarzI parAtmanoH . nAsyacchidraM paraH pazyecchidreSu paramanviyAt .
etad vRttaM vAsavasya yamasya varuNasya ca . rAjarSINAM ca sarveSAM tat tvamapyanupAlaya .
tat kuruSva mahArAja vRttaM rAjarSisevitam . AtiSTha divyaM panthAnamahnAya puruSarSabha .
dharmavRttaM hi rAjAnaM pretya ceha ca bhArata . devarSipitRgandharvAH kIrtayanti mahaujasaH .
bhISma uvAca sa evamukto mAndhAtA tenotathyena bhArata . kRtavAnavizaGkazca ekaH prApa ca medinIm .
bhavAnapi tathA samyaGmAndhAteva mahIpate . dharma kRtvA mahIM rakSa svarge sthAnamavApsyasi .
yudhiSThira uvAca evamagrAhyake tasmijJAtisambandhimaNDale . mitreSvamitreSvapi ca kathaM bhAvo vibhAvyate .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . saMvAdaM vAsudevasya surarSernAradasya ca .
vAsudeva uvAca nAsuhRt paramaM mantraM nAradArhati veditum . apaNDito vApi suhRt paNDito vApyanAtmavAn .
sa te sauhRdamAsthAya kiJcid vakSyAmi nArada . kRtsnaM buddhibalaM prekSya sampRcchestridivaMgama .
dAsyamaizvaryavAdena jJAtInAM na karomyaham . ardhaM bhoktAsmi vAgduruktAni ca kSame .
araNImagnikAmo vA manAti hRdayaM mama . vAcA duruktaM devarSe tanme dahati nityadA .
balaM saMkarSaNe nityaM saukumArya punargade . rUpeNa mattaH pradyumnaH so ' sahAyo ' smi nArada .
anye hi sumahAbhAgA balavanto durutsahAH . nityotthAnena sampannA nAradAndhakavRSNayaH .
yasya na syurna vai sa syAd yasya syuH kRtsnameva tat . dvAbhyAM nivArito nityaM vRNomyekataraM na ca .
syAtAM yasyAhukAkrUrau kiM nu duHkhataraM tataH . yasya cApi na tau syAtAM kiM nu duHkhataraM tataH .
so ' haM kitavamAteva dvayorapi mahAmate . ekasya jayamAzaMse dvitIyasyAparAjayam .
mamaivaM klizyamAnasya nAradobhayataH sadA . vaktumarhasi yacchreyo jJAtInAmAtmanastathA .
nArada uvAca Apado dvividhAH kRSNa bAhyAzcAbhyantarAzca ha . prAdurbhavanti vArSNeya svakRtA yadi vAnyataH .
seyamAbhyantarA tubhyamApat kRcchA svakarmajA . akrUrabhojaprabhavA sarve hyete tvadanvayAH .
arthahetohi kAmAd vA vAcA bIbhatsayApi vA . AtmanA prAptamaizvaryamanyatra pratipAditam . kRtamUlamidAnIM tajjJAtivRndaM sahAyavan . na zakyaM punarAdAtuM vAntamanamiva tvayA .
babhUgrasenayo rAjyaM nAptuM zakyaM kathaMcana . jJAtibhedabhayAt kRSNa tvayA cApi vizeSataH .
tacca sidhyet prayatlena kRtvA karma suduSkaram . mahAkSayaM vyayo vA syAd vinAzo vA punarbhavet .
anAyasena zastreNa mRdunA hRdayacchidA . jihvAmuddhara sarveSAM parimRjyAnumRjya ca .
vAsudeva uvAca anAyasaM mune zastraM mRdu vidyAmahaM katham . yenaiSAmuddhare jihvAM parimRjyAnumRjya ca . .
nArada uvAca zaktyAnnadAnaM satataM titikSArjavamArdavam . yathArhapratipUjA ca zastrametadanAyasam .
jJAtInAM vaktukAmAnAM kaTukAni laghUni ca . girA tvaM hRdayaM vAcaM zamayasva manAMsi ca .
nAmahApuruSaH kazcinnAnAtmA nAsahAyavAn . mahatIM dhuramAdhatte tAmudyamyorasA vaha .
sarva eva guruM bhAramanaDvAna vahate same . durge pratItaH sugavo bhAraM vahati durvaham .
bhedAd vinAzaH saMghAnAM saMghamukhyo ' si kezava . yathA tvAM prApya notsIdedayaM saMghastathA kuru .
nAnyatra buddhikSAntibhyAM nAnyatrendriyanigrahAt . nAnyatra dhanasaMtyAgAd gaNaH prAjJe ' vatiSThate .
dhanyaM yazasyamAyuSyaM svapakSodbhAvanaM sadA . jJAtInAmavinAzaH syAd yathA kRSNa tathA kuru .
AyatyAM ca tadAtve ca na te ' styaviditaM prabho . pADguNyasya vidhAnena yAtrAyAnavidhau tathA .
yAdavAH kukurA bhojAH sarve cAndhakavRSNayaH . tvayyAsaktA mahAbAho lokA lokezvarAzca ye . upAsate hi tvabuddhimRSayazcApi mAdhava .
tvaM guruH sarvabhUtAnAM jAnISe tvaM gatAgatam . tvAmAsAdya yaduzreSThamedhante yAdavAH sukham .
vaizampAyana uvAca evaM tadabhavad yuddhaM tumulaM janamejaya . yatra duHkhAnvito rAjA dhRtarASTro ' bravIdidam .
dhRtarASTra uvAca rAmaM saMnihitaM dRSTvA gadAyuddha upasthite . mama putraH kathaM bhIma pratyayudhyata saMjaya .
saMjaya uvAca rAmasAMnidhyamAsAdya putro duryodhanastava . yuddhakAmo mahAbAhuH samahaSyata vIryavAn .
dRSTavA lAgalinaM rAjA pratyutthAya ca bhArata . prItyA paramayA yuktaH samabhyarcya yathAvidhi . AsanaM ca dadau tasmai paryapRcchadanAmayam .
tato yudhiSTharaM rAmo vAkyametaduvAca ha . madhuraM dharmasaMyuktaM zUrANAM hitameva ca . mayA zrutaM kathayatAmRSINAM rAjasattama . kurukSetraM paraM puNyaM pAvanaM svargameva ca . daivataiRSibhirjuSTaM brAhmaNaizca mahAtmabhiH .
tatra vai yotsyamAnA ya dehaM tyakSyanti mAnavAH . teSAM svarge dhruvo vAsaH zakreNa saha mAriSa .
tasmAt samantapaJcakamito yAma drutaM nRpa . prathitottaravedI sA devaloke prajApateH .
tasmin mahApuNyatame trailokyasya sanAtane . saMgrAme nidhanaM prApya dhruvaM svarge bhaviSyati .
tathetyuktvA mahArAja kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . samantapaJcakaM vIraH prAyAdabhimukhaH prabhuH .
tato duryodhano rAjA pragRhya mahatIM gadAm . padbhyAmaparSI dyutimAnagacchat pANDavaiH saha .12 . .
tathA ' ' yAntaM gadAhastaM varmaNA cApi daMzitam . antarikSacarA devAH sAdhu sAdhvityapUjayan . vAtikAcAraNA ye tu dRSTvA te harSamAgatAH . sa pANDavaiH parivRtaH kururAjastavAtmajaH . mattasyeva gajendrasya gatimAsthAya so ' vrajat . tataH zaGkhaninAdena bherINAM ca mahAsvanaiH . siMhanAdaizca zUrANAM dizaH sarvAH prapUritAH .
tataste tu kurukSetraM prAptA naravarottamAH . pratIcyabhimukhaM dezaM yathoddiSTaM sutena te .
dakSiNena sarasvatyAH svayanaM tIrthamuttamam . tasmin deze tvaniriNe te tu yuddhamarocayan .
tato bhImo mahAkoTiM gadAM gRhyAtha varmabhRt . bibhradrUpaM mahArAja sadRzaM hi garutmataH .
avabaddhazirastrANaH saMkhye kAJcanavarmabhRt . rarAja rAjan putraste kAJcanaH zailarADiva .
varmabhyAM saMyatau vIrau bhImaduryodhanAvubhau . saMyuge ca prakAzete saMrabdhAviva kuJjarau .
raNamaNDalamadhyasthau bhrAtarau tau nararSabhau . azobhetAM mahArAja candrasUryAvivoditau .
tAvanyonyaM nirIkSetAM kruddhAviva mahAdvipau . dahantau locanau rAjan parasparavadhaiSiNau .
samprahRSTamanA rAjan gadAmAdAya kauravaH . sRkkiNI saMlihan rAjan krodharaktekSaNaH zvasan . tato duryodhano rAjan gadAmAdAya vIryavAn . bhImasenamabhiprekSya gajo gajamivAhvayat .
adrisAramayIM bhImastathaivAdAya vIryavAn . AhvayAmAsa nRpati siMha siMho yathA vane .
tAvudyatagadApANI duryodhanavRkodarau . saMyuge ca prakAzetAM girI sazikharAviva .
tAvubhau samatikruddhAvubhau bhImaparAkramau . ubhau ziSyau gadAyuddhe rauhiNeyasya dhImataH . ubhau sadRzakarmANau yamavAsavayoriva . tathA sadRzakarmANau varuNasya mahAbalau . vAsudevasya rAmasya tathA vaizravaNasya ca . sadRzau tau mahArAja madhukaiTabhayoryudhi .
ubhau sadRzakarmANau tathA sundopasundayoH . rAmarAvaNayozcaiva vAlisugrIvayostathA .
tathaiva kAlasya samau mRtyozcaiva paraMtapau . anyonyamabhidhAvantau mattAviva mahAdvipau . vAsitAsaMgame dRptau zaradIva madotkaTau . ubhau krodhaviSaM dIptaM vamantAvuragAviva .
anyonyamabhisaMrabdhau prekSamANAvariMdamau . ubhau bharatazArdUlau vikrameNa samanvitau .
siMhAviva durAdharSoM gadAyuddhavizAradau . nakhadaMSTrAyudhau vIrau vyAghrAviva durutsahau . prajAsaMharaNe kSubdhau samudrAviva dustarau . lohitAGgAviva kruddho pratapantau mahArathau . pUrvapazcimajau meghau prekSamANAvariMdamau . garjamAnau suviSamaM kSarantau prAdRSIva hi . razmiyuktau mahAtmAnau dIptimantau mahAbalau . dadRzAte kuruzreSThau kAlasUryAvivoditau .
vyAghrAviva susaMrabdhau garjantAviva toyadau . jahaSAte mahAbAhU siMhakesariNAvivA jagAviva susaMrabdhau jvalitAviva pAvakau . dadRzAte mahAtmAnau sazRGgAviva parvatau . roSAt prasphuramANoSThau nirIkSantau parasparam . tau sametau mahAtmAnau gadAhastau narottamau .
ubhau paramasaMhRSTAvubhau paramasammatau . sadazvAviva heSantau bRhantAviva kuJjarau .
vRSabhAviva garjantau duryodhanavRkodarau . daityAviva balonmattau rejatustau narottamau . tato duryodhano rAjannidamAha yudhiSThiram . bhrAtRbhiH saMhitaM caiva kRSNena ca mahAtmanA . rAmeNAmitavIryeNa vAkyaM zauTIryasammatam .
kekayaiH sRJjayairdRptaM paJcAlaizca mahAtmabhiH . idaM vyavasitaM yuddhaM mama bhImasya cobhayoH . upopaviSTAH pazyadhvaM sahitainUpapuGgavaiH . zrutvA duryodhanavacaH pratyapadyanta tattathA . tataH samupaviSTaM tat sumahadrajamaNDalam . virAjamAnaM dadRze divIvAdityamaNDalam .
teSAM madhye mahAbAhuH zrImAn kezavapUrvajaH . upaviSTo mahArAja pUjyamAnaH samantataH .
zuzubhe rAjamadhyastho nIlavAsAH sitaprabhaH . nakSatrairiva sampUrNo vRto nizi nizAkaraH .
tau tathA tu mahArAja gadAhastau suduHsahau . anyonyaM vAgbhirugrAbhistakSamANau vyavasthitau .
apriyANi tato ' nyonyamuktvA tau kurusattamau . udIkSantau sthitau tatra vRtrazakrau yathA ' ' have .
dhaumya uvAca AnarteSu pratIcyAM vai kIrtayiSyAmi te dizi . yAni tatra pavitrANi puNyAnyAyatanAni ca .
priyaGgvAmraNopetA vAnIraphalamAlinI . pratyaksrotA nadI puNyA narmadA tatra bhArata .
