mANDavyazApAddhi sa vai dharmo viduratAM gataH . mahAbuddhirmahAyogI mahAtmA sumahAmanAH .
bRhaspatirvA deveSu zukro vApyasureSu ca . na tathA buddhisampanno yathA sa puruSarSabhaH .
tapobalavyayaM kRtvA sucirAt sambhRtaM tadA . mANDavyenarSiNA dharmo hyabhibhUtaH sanAtanaH .
niyogAd brahmaNaH pUrve mayA svena balena ca . vaicitravIryake kSetre jAtaH sa sumahAmatiH .
bhrAtA tava mahArAja devadevaH sanAtanaH . dhAraNAnmanasA dhyAnAd yaM dharmaM kavayo viduH .
satyena saMvardhayati yo damena zamena ca . ahiMsayA ca dAnena tapyamAnaH sanAtanaH .
yena yogabalAjjAtaH kururAjo yudhiSThiraH . dharma ityeSa nRpate prAjJenAmitabuddhinA .
yathA vahniryathA vAyuryathA ' ' paH pRthivI yathA . yathA ' ' kAzaM tathA dharma iha cAmutra ca sthitaH .
sarvagazcaiva rAjendra sarvaM vyApya carAcaram . dRzyate devadevaiH sa siddhairnirmuktakalmaSaiH .
yo hi dharmaH sa viduro viduro yaH sa pANDavaH . sa eSa rAjan dRzyaste pANDavaH preSyavat sthitaH .21
praviSTaH sa mahAtmAnaM bhrAtA te buddhisattamaH . dRSTvA mahAtmA kaunteyaM mahAyogabalAnvitaH .
tvAM cApi zreyasA yokSye na cirAd bharatarSabha . saMzayacchedanArthAya prAptaM mAM viddhi putrakA .
na kRtaM yaiH purA kaizcit karma loke maharSibhiH . AzcaryabhUtaM tapasaH phalaM tad darzayAmi vaH .
kimicchasi mahIpAla mattaH prAptumabhIpsitam . draSTuM spraSTumatha zrotuM tatkartA ' smi tavAnagha . .
parAzara uvAca vRttiH sakAzAd varNebhyastribhyo hInasya zobhanA . prItyopanItA nirdiSTA dharmiSThAn kurute sadA .
vRttizcennAsti zUdrasya pitRpaitAmahI dhruvA . na vRttiM parato mArgecchuzrUSAM tu prayojayet .
sadbhistu saha saMsargaH zobhate dharmadarzibhiH . nityaM sarvAsvavasthAsu nAsadbhiriti me matiH .
yathodayagirau dravyaM saMnikarSeNa dIpyate . tathA satsaMnikarSeNa hInavarNo ' pi dIpyate .
yAdRzena hi varNena bhAvyate zuklamambaram . tAdRzaM kurute rupametadevamavehi me .
tasmAd guNeSu rajyethA mA doSeSu kadAcana . anityamiha mAnAM jIvitaM hi calAcalam .
sukhe vA yadi vA duHkhe vartamAno vicakSaNaH . yazcinoti zubhAnyeva sa tantrANIha pazyati .
dharmAdapetaM yat karma yadyapi syAnmahAphalam . na tat seveta medhAvI na taddhitamihocyate .
yo hatvA gosahasrANi nRpo dadyAdarakSitA . sa zabdamAtraphalabhAg rAjA bhavati taskaraH .
svayambhUrasRjaccAgre dhAtAraM lokasatkRtam . dhAtAsRjat putramekaM lokAnAM dhAraNe ratam .
tamarcayitvA vaizyastu kuryAdatyarthamRddhimat . rakSitavyaM tu rAjanyairupayojyaM dvijAtibhiH .
ajiaurazaThakrodhairhavyakavyaprayoktRbhiH . zUdranirmArjanaM kAryamevaM dharmo na nazyati .
apraNaSTe tato dharme bhavanti sukhitAH prajAH . sukhena tAsAM rAjendra modante divi devatAH .
tasmAd yo rakSati nRpaH sa dharmeNeti pUjyate . adhIte cApi yo vipro vaizyo yazcArjane rataH . yazca zuzrUSate zUdraH satataM niyatendriyaH . ato ' nyathA manuSyendra svadharmAt parihIyate .
prANasaMtApanirdiSTAH kAkiNyo ' pi mahAphalAH . nyAyenopArjitA dattA : kimutAnyAH sahasrazaH .
satkRtya hi dvijAtibhyo yo dadAti narAdhipaH . yAdRzaM tAdRzaM nityamaznAti phalamUrjitam .
abhigamya ca tat tuSTyA dattamAhurabhiSTutam . yAcitena tu tad dattaM tadAhurmadhyamaM budhAH .
avajJayA dIyate yat tathaivAzraddhayApi vA . tamAhuradhamaM dAnaM munayaH satyavAdinaH .
atikrAmenmajjamAno vividhena naraH sadA . tathA prayatnaM kurvIta yathA mucyeta saMzrayAt .
damena zobhate vipraH kSatriyo vijayena tu . dhanena vaizyaH zUdrastu nityaM dAkSyeNa zobhate .
vaizampAyana uvAca tato yudhiSThiro rAjA bhUyaH zAntanavaM nRpam . godAnavistaraM dharmAn papraccha vinayAnvitaH .
rAjovAca gopradAnaguNAn samyak punarme brUhi bhArata . na hi tRpyAmyahaM vIra zRNvAno ' mRtamIdRzam .
vaizampAyana uvAca ityukto dharmarAjena tadA zAntanavo nRpaH . samyagAha guNAMstasmai gopradAnasya kevalAn .
bhISma uvAca vatsalAM guNasampannAM taruNIM vastrasaMyutAm . dattvedRzIM gAM viprAya sarvapApaiH pramucyate .
asuryA nAma te lokA gAM dattvA tAn na gacchati . pItodakAM jagdhatRNAM naSTakSIrAM nirindriyAm .
jarArogopasampannAM jIrNAM vApImivAjalAm . dattvA tamaH pravizati dvijaM klezena yojayet .
ruSTA duSTA vyAdhitA durbalA vA no dAtavyA yAzca mUlyairadattaiH . klezairvipraM yo ' phalaiH saMyunakti tasyAvIryAzcAphalAzcaiva lokAH .
balAnvitAH zIlavayopapannAH sarve prazaMsanti sugandhavatyaH . yathA hi gaGgA saritAM variSThA tathArjunInAM kapilA variSThA .
yudhiSThira uvAca kasmAt samAne bahulApradAne saddhiH prazastaM kapilApradAnAm . vizeSamicchAmi mahAprabhAvaM zrotuM samartho ' smi bhavAn pravaktum .
bhISma uvAca vRddhAnAM bruvatAM tAta zrutaM me yat purAtanam . vakSyAmi tadazeSeNa rohiNyo nirmitA yathA . .
prajAH sRjeti cAdiSTaH pUrvaM dakSaH svayambhuvA . asRjad vRttimevAgre prajAnAM hitakAmyayA .
yathA hyamRtamAzritya vartayanti divaukasaH . tathA vRttiM samAzritya vartayanti prajA vibho .
acarebhyazca bhUtebhyazcarAH zreSThAH sadA narAH . brAhmaNAzca tataH zreSThAsteSu yajJAH pratiSThitAH .
yajJairavApyate somaH sa ca goSu pratiSThitaH . tato devAH pramodante pUrvaM vRttistataH prajAH .
prajAtAnyeva bhUtAni prAkrozan vRttikAjhayA . vRttidaM cAnvapadyanta tRSitAH pitRmAtRvat .
itIdaM manasA gatvA prajAsargArthamAtmanaH . prajApatistu bhagavAnamRtaM prApibat tadA .
sa gatastasya tRpti tu gandhaM surabhimudbhiran . dadarzodvArasaMvRttAM surabhiM mukhajAM sutAm .
sAsRjat saurabheyIstu surabhirlokamAtRkAH . suvarNavarNAH kapilAH prajAnAM vRttidhenavaH .
tAsAmamRtavarNAnAM kSarantInAM samantataH . babhUvAmRtajaH phenaH sravantInAmivormijaH .
sa vatsamukhavibhraSTo bhavasya bhuvi tiSThataH . zirasyavApa tat kruddhaH sa tadaikSata ca prabhuH .
lalATaprabhaveNAkSvA rohiNIM pradahanniva . tattejastu tato raudraM kapilAstA vizAmpate . nAnAvarNatvamanayanmeghAniva divAkaraH . yAstu tasmAdapakramya somameSAbhisaMzritAH . yathautpannAH svavarNAsthAstA hyetA nAnyavarNagAH . atha kruddhaM mahAdevaM prajApatirabhASata . amRtenAvasiktastavaM nocchiSTaM vidyate gavAm . yathA hyamRtamAdAya somo visyandate punaH .
tathA kSIraM kSarantyetA rohiNyo ' mRtasambhavam . na duSyatyanilo nAgnirna suvarNaM na codadhiH .
nAmRte nAmRtaM pItaM vatsapItA na vatsalA . imAllokAn bhariSyanti haviSA prasraveNa ca .
AsAmaizcaryamicchanti sarve ' mRtamayaM zubham . vRSabhaM ca dadau tasmai saha gobhiH prajApatiH .
prasAdayAmAsa manastena rudrasya bhArata . prItazcApi mahAdevazcakAra vRSabhaM tadA . dhvajaM ca vAhanaM caiva tasmAt sa vRSabhadhvajaH .
tato devairmahAdevastadA pazupatiH kRtaH . IzvaraH sa gavAM madhye vRSabhAGkaH prakIrtitaH .
evamavyagravarNAnAM kapilAnAM mahaujasAm . pradAne prathamaH kalpaH sarvAsAmeva kIrtitaH .
lokajyeSThA lokavRttipravRttA rudropetA : somaviSyandabhUtAH . saumyAH puNyAH kAmadAH prANadAzca gA vai dattvA sarvakAmapradaH syAt .
idaM gavAM prabhavavidhAnamuttamaM paThan sadAzucirapi maGgalapriyaH . vimucyate kalikaluSeNa mAnava : zriyaM sutAn dhanapazumApnuyAt sadA .
havyaM kavyaM tarpaNaM zAntikarma yAnaM vAso vRddhabAlasya tuSTiH . etAn sarvAn gopradAne guNAn vai dAtA rAjannApnuyAd vai sadaiva .
vaizampAyana uvAca pitAmahasyAtha nizamya vAkyaM rAjA saha bhrAtRbhirAjamIDhaH . suvarNavarNAnaDuhastathA gAH pArtho dadau brAhmaNasattamebhyaH .
tathaiva tebhyo ' pi dadau dvijebhyo gavAM sahasrANi zatAni caiva . yajJAn samuddizya ca dakSiNArthe lokAn vijetuM paramAM ca kIrtim .
jarAsaMdha uvAca na smarAmi kadA vairaM kRtaM yuSmAbhirityuta . cintayaMzca na pazyAmi bhavatAM prati vaikRtam .
vaikRte vAsati kathaM manyadhvaM mAmanAgasam . ariM vai brUta he viprAH satAM samaya eSa hi .
atha dharmopaghAtAddhi manaH samupatapyate . yo ' nAgasi prasajati kSatriyo hi na saMzayaH . ato ' nyathA cara~lloke dharmajJaH san mahArathaH . vRjinAM gatimApnoti zreyaso ' pyupahanti ca . .
trailokye kSatradharmo hi zreyAn vai sAdhucAriNAm . nAnyaM dharmaM prazaMsanti ye ca dharmavido janAH .
tasya me ' dya sthitasyeha svadharme niyatAtmanaH . anAgasaM prajAnAM ca pramAdAdiva jalpatha .
zrIkRSNa uvAca kulakAryaM mahAbAho kazcidekaH kulodvahaH . vahate yastanniyogAd vayamabhyudyatAstvayi .
tvayA copahRtA rAjan kSatriyA lokavAsinaH . tadAgaH krUramutpAdya manyase kimanAgasam .
rAjA rAjJaH kathaM sAdhUn hiMsyAnRpatisattama . tad rAjJaH saMnigRhya tvaM rudrAyopajihIrSasi .
asmAMstadeno gaccheddhi kRtaM vArhadratha tvayA . vayaM hi zaktA dharmasya rakSaNe dharmacAriNaH .
manuSyANAM samAlambho na ca dRSTaH kadAcana . sa kathaM mAnuSairdevaM yaSTumicchasi zaGkaram .
savarNo hi savarNAnAM pazusaMjJAM kariSyasi . ko ' nya eva yathA hi tvaM jarAsaMdha vRthAmatiH .
yasyAM yasyAmavasthAyAM yadyat karma karoti yaH . tasyAM tasyAmavasthAyAM tatphalaM samavApnuyAt .
te tvAM jJAtikSayakaraM vayamArtAnusAriNaH . jJAtivRddhinimittArthaM vinihantumihAgatAH .
nAsti loke pumAnanyaH kSatriyeSviti caiva tat . manyase sa ca te rAjan sumahAn buddhiviplavaH .
ko hi jAnannabhijanamAtmavAn kSatriyo nRpa . nAvizet svargamatulaM raNAnantaramavyayam .
svargaM hyeva samAsthAya raNayajJeSu dIkSitAH . jayanti kSatriyA lokAMstad viddhi manujarSabha .
svargayonirmahad brahma svargayonirmahad yazaH . svargayonistapo yuddhe mRtyuH so ' vyabhicAravAn .
eSa ndrio vaijayanto guNairnityaM samAhitaH . yenAsurAn parAjitya jagat pAti zatakratuH .
svargamArgAya kasya syAd vigraho vai yathA tava . mAgadhairvipulaiH sainyairbAhulyabaladarpitaH .
mAvamaMsthAH parAn rAjannasti vIryaM nare nare . samaM tejastvayA caiva viziSTaM vA narezvara .
yAvadetadasambuddhaM tAvadeva bhavet tava . viSahyametadasmAkamato rAjan bravImi te .
jahi tvaM sadRzeSveva mAnaM darpaM ca mAgadha . mA gamaH sasutAmAtya sabalazca yamakSayam .
dambhodbhavaH kArtavIrya uttarazca bRhadrathaH . zreyaso hyavamanyeha vinezuH sabalA nRpAH .
yuyukSamANAstvatto hi na vayaM brAhmaNA dhruvam . zaurirasmi hRSikezo nRvIrau pANDavAvimau . anayormAtuleyaM ca kRSNaM mAM viddhi te ripum .
tvAmAhvayAmahe rAjan sthiro yudhyasva mAgadha . muJca vA nRpatIn sarvAn gaccha vA tvaM yamakSayam .
jarAsaMdha uvAca nAjitAn vai narapatInahamAdadi kAMzcana . ajitaH paryavasthAtA ko ' tra yo na mayA jitaH .
kSatriyasyaitadevAhurdharmya kRSNopajIvanam . vikramya vazamAnIya kAmato yat samAcaret .
devatArthamupAhatya rAjJaH kRSNa kathaM bhayAt . ahamadya vimucyeyaM kSAtraM vratamanusmaran . .
sainyaM sainyena vyUDhena eka ekena vA punaH . dvAbhyAM tribhirvA yotsye ' haM yugapat pRthageva vA .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktvA jarAsaMdhaH sahadevAbhiSecanam . AjJApayat tadA rAjA yuyutsurbhImakarmabhiH .
sa tu senApati rAjA sasmAra bharatarSabha . kauzikaM citrasenaM ca tasmin yuddha upasthite .
yayoste nAmanI rAjan haMseti Dimbhaketi ca . pUrvaM saMkathitaM pumbhirnRloke lokasatkRte .
taM tu rAjan vibhuH zaurI rAjAnaM balinAM varam . smRtvA puruSazArdUla : zArdUlasamavikramam . satyasaMdho jarAsaMdhaM bhuvi bhImaparAkramam . bhAgamanyasya nirdiSTamavadhyaM madhubhirmadhe . nAtmanA ' ' tmavatAM mukhya iyeSa madhusUdanaH . brAhmImAjJAM puraskRtya hantuM haladharAnujAH .
yudhiSThira uvAca kimidaM paramAzcaryaM dhyAyasyamitavikrama . kaccillokatrayasyAsya svasti lokaparAyaNa . .zA
caturthaM dhyAnamArga tvamAlambya puruSarSabha . apakrAnto yato devastena me vismitaM manaH .
nigRhIto hi vAyuste paJcakarmA zarIragaH . indriyANi prasannAni manasi sthApitAni te .
vAk ca sattvaM ca govinda buddhau saMvezitAni te . sarve caiva guNA devAH kSetrajJe te nivezitAH .
neGganti tava romANi sthirA buddhistathA manaH . kASThakuDyazilAbhUto nirIhazcAsi mAdhavA .
yathA dIpo nivAtasthA niriGgo jvalate punaH . tathAsi bhagavan deva pASANa iva nizcalaH .
yadi zrotumihArhAmi na rahasyaM ca te yadi . chindhi me saMzayaM deva prapannAyAbhiyAcate .
tvaM hi kartA vikartA ca kSaraM caivAkSaraM ca hi . anAdinidhanazcAdyastvameva puruSottama .
tvatprapannAya bhaktAya zirasA praNatAya ca . dhyAnasyAsya yathA tattvaM brUhi dharmabhRtAM vara .
tataH sve gocare nyasya manobuddhindriyANi saH . smitapUrvamuvAcedaM bhagavAn vAsavAnujaH .
vAsudeva uvAca zaratalpagato bhISmaH zAmyanniva hutAzanaH mAM dhyAti puruSavyAghrastato me tadgataM manaH .
yasya jyAtalanirghoSaM visphUrjitamivAzaneH . na sehe devarAjo ' pi tamasmi manasA gataH .
yenAbhijitya tarasA samastaM rAjamaNDalam . UDhAstistrastu tAH kanyAstamasmi manasA gataH .
trayoviMzatirAtraM yo yodhayAmAsa bhArgavam . na ca rAmeNa nistIrNastamasmi manasA gataH .
ekIkRtyendriyagrAma manaH saMyamya medhayA . zaraNaM mAmupAgacchat tato me tadgataM manaH .
yaM gaGgA garbhavidhinA dhArayAmAsa pArthiva . vasiSThazikSitaM tAta tamasmi manasA gataH .
divyAstrANi mahAtejA yo dhArayati buddhimAn . sAGgAMzca caturo vedAMstamasmi manasA gataH .
rAmasya dayitaM ziSyaM jAmadagnyasya pANDava . AdhAraM sarvavidyAnAM tamasmi manasA gataH .
sa hi bhUtaM bhaviSyacca bhavacca bharatarSabha . vetti dharmavidAM zreSThaM tamasmi manasA gataH .
tasmin hi puruSavyAghne karmabhiH svairdivaM gate . bhaviSyati mahI pArtha naSTacandreva zarvarI .
tad yudhiSThira gAGgeyaM bhISmaM bhImaparAkramam . abhigamyopasaMgRhya pRccha yat te manogatam .
cAturvidyaM cAturhotraM cAturAzramyameva ca . rAjadharmAMzca nikhilAn pRcchainaM pRthivIpate .
tasminnastamite bhISme kauravANAM dhuraMdhare . jJAnAnyastaM gamiSyanti tasmAttvAM codayAmyaham .
tacchrutvA vAsudevasya tathyaM vacanamuttamam . sAzrukaNThaH sa dharmajJo janArdanamuvAca ha . yad bhavAnAha bhISmasya prabhAvaM prati mAdhava . tathA tannAtra saMdeho vidyate mama mAdhava . .
mahAbhAgyaM ca bhISmasya prabhAvazca mahAdyute . zrutaM mayA kathayatAM brAhmaNAnAM mahAtmanAm .
bhavAMzca kartA lokAnAM yad bravItyarisUdana . tathA tadanabhidhyeyaM vAkyaM yAdavanandana .
yadi tvanugrahavatI buddhiste mayi mAdhava . tvAmagrataH puraskRtya bhISmaM yAsyAmahe vayam .
AvRte bhagavatyarke sa hi lokAn gamiSyati . tvadarzanaM mahAbAho tasmAdarhati kauravaH .
tava cAdyasya devasya kSarasyaivAkSarasya ca . darzanaM tvasya lAbhaH syAt tvaM hi brahmamayo nidhiH . .
vaizampAyana uvAca zrutvaivaM dharmarAjasya vacanaM madhusUdanaH . pArzvasthaM sAtyakiM prAha ratho me yujyatAmiti .
sAtyakistvAzu niSkramya kezavasya samIpataH . dArukaM prAha kRSNasya yujyatAM ratha ityuta . .
sa sAtyakerAzu vaco nizamya rathottamaM kAJcanabhUSitAGgam . vibhUSitaM hemanibaddhacakram . divAkarAMzuprabhamAzugAmina vicitranAnAmaNibhUSitAntaram . navoditaM sUryamiva pratApinaM vicitratA _ dhvajinaM patAkinam . manojavaiH kAJcanabhUSitAGgaiH . saMyuktamAvedayadacyutAya kRtAJjalirdAruko rAjasiMha .
sUrya uvAca mAhitaM karNa kArSIstvamAtmanaH suhRdAM tathA . putrANAmatha bhAryANAmatho mAturatho pituH .
zarIrasyAvirodhena prANinAM prANabhRdvara . iSyate yazasaH prAptiH kIrtizca tridive sthirA .
yastvaM prANavirodhena kIrtimicchasi zAzvatIm . sA te prANAn gamiSyati na saMzayaH .
jIvatAM kurute kAryaM pitA mAtA sutAstathA . ye cAnye bAndhavAH kecilloke ' smin puruSarSabha . .
rAjAnazca naravyAghra pauruSeNa nibodha tat . kIrtizca jIvataH sAdhvI puruSasya mahAdyute .
mRtasya kIrtyA kiM kAryaM bhasmIbhUtasya dehinaH . mRtaH kIrti na jAnIte jIvana kIrtiM samaznute .
mRtasyA kIrtimartyasya yathA mAlA gatAyuSaH . ahaM tu tvAM bravImyetad bhakto ' sIti hitepsayA .
bhaktimanto hi me rakSyA ityetenApi hetunA . bhakto ' yaM parayA bhaktyA mAmityeva mahAbhujA mamApi bhaktirutpannA sa tvaM kuru vaco mama .
asti cAtra paraM kiJcidadhyAtmaM devanirmitam . atazca tvAM bravImyetat kriyatAmavizaGkayA .
devaguhyaM tvayA jJAtuM na zakyaM puruSarSabha . tasmAnnAkhyAmi te guhyaM kAle vetsyati tad bhavAn .
punaruktaM ca vakSyAmi tvaM rAdheya nibodha tat . mAsmai te kuNDale dadyA bhikSite valApANinA .
zobhase kuNDalAbhyAM ca rucirAbhyAM mahAdyute . vizAkhayormadhyagataH zazIva vimale divi .
kIrtizca jIvataH sAdhvI puruSasyeti viddhi tat . pratyAkhyeyastvayA tAta kuNDalArthe surezvaraH .
zakyA bahuvidhairvAkyaiH kuNDalepsA tvayAnagha . vihantuM devarAjasya hetuyuktaiH punaH punaH .
hetumadupapannArthairmAdhuryakRtabhUSaNaiH . purandarasya karNa tvaM buddhimetAmapAnuda .
tvaM hi nityaM naravyAghra spardhase savyasAcinA . savyasAcI tvayA ceha yudhi zUraH sameSyati .
na tu tvAmarjunaH zaktaH kuNDalAbhyAM samanvitam . vijetuM yudhi yadyasya svayamindraH sakhA bhavet .
tasmAnna deye zakrAya tvayaite kuNDale zubhe . saMgrAme yadi nirjetuM karNa kAmayase ' rjunam .
saMjaya uvAca dRSTvA tu saMnivRttAMstAn saMzaptakagaNAn punaH . vAsudevaM mahAtmAnamarjunaH samabhASata .
codayAzvAn hRSIkeza saMzaptakagaNAn prati . naitai hAsyanti saMgrAmaM jIvanta iti me matiH .
pazyame ' strabalaM ghoraM bAhoriSvasanasya ca . adyaitAn pAtayiSyAmi kruddho rudraH pazUniva .
tataH kRSNaH smitaM kRtvA pratinandya zivena tam . prAvezayata durdharSo yatra yatraicchadarjunaH .
sa ratho bhrAjate ' tyarthamuhyamAno raNe tadA . uhyamAnamivAkAze vimAnaM pANDurairhayaiH .
maNDalAni tatazcakre gatapratyAgatAni ca . yathA zakraratho rAjan yuddhe devAsure purA .
atha nArAyaNAH kuddhA vividhAyudhapANayaH . kSAdayantaH zaravrAtaiH parivavardhanaMjayam .
adRzyaM ca muhUrtena cakuste bharatarSabha . kRSNena sahitaM yuddhe kuntIputraM dhanaMjayam .
kruddhastu phAlgunaH saMkhye dviguNIkRtavikramaH . gANDIvaM dhanurAmRjya tUrNaM jagrAha saMyuge .
baddhvA ca bhrukuTi vaktre krodhasya pratilakSaNam . devadattaM mahAzaGkha pUrayAmAsa pANDavaH .
athAstramarisaMghaghnaM tvASTramabhyasyadarjunaH . tato rUpasahasrANi prAdurAsan pRthak pRthak .
AtmanaH pratirUpaistairnAnArUpairvimohitAH . anyonyenArjunaM matvA svamAtmAnaM ca jajire .
ayamarjuno ' yaM govinda imau pANDavayAdavau . iti bruvANAH sammUDhA jaghnuranyonyamAhave .
mohitAH paramAstreNa kSayaM jagmuH parasparam . azobhanta raNe yodhAH puSpitA iva kiMzukAH .
tataH zarasahasrANi tairvimuktAni bhasmasAt . kRtvA tadastraM tAn vIrAnanayad yamasAdanam .
atha prahasya bIbhatsurlalitthAn mAlavAnapi . mAvellakAstrigatazci yaudheyAMzcAdayaccharaiH .
te hanyamAnA vIreNa kSatriyAH kAlacoditAH . vyasRjaJcharajAlAni pArthe nAnAvidhAni ca .
na dhvajo nArjunastatra na ratho na ca kezavaH . pratyadRzyata ghoreNa zaravarSeNa saMvRtaH .
tataste labdhalakSatvAdanyonyamabhicukuzuH . hatau kRSNAviti prItyA vAsAMsyAdudhuvustadA .
bherImRdaGgazaGkhAMzca dadhmurvIrAH sahasrazaH . siMhanAdaravAMzcogrAMzcakrire tatra mAriSa .
tataH prasiSvide kRSNaH khinnazcArjunamabravIt . kvAsipArthana pazyetvAM kaccijjIvasizatruhan .
tasya tad bhASitaM zrutvA tvaramANo dhanaMjayaH . vAyavyAstreNa tairastAM zaravRSTimapAharat .
tataH saMzaptakavAtAn sAzvadviparathAyudhAn . uvAha bhagavAn vAyuH zuSkaparNacayAniva .
uhyamAnAstu te rAjan bahvazobhanta vAyunA . praDInAH pakSiNa : kAle vRkSebhya iva mAriSa .
tAMstathA vyAkulIkRtya tvaramANo dhanaMjayaH . jaghAna nizitairbANaiH sahasrANi zatAni ca . .
zirAMsi bhallairaharad bAhUnapi ca sAyudhAn . hastihastopamAMzcorUzarairukmapAtayat .
pRSThacchinnAn vicaraNAn bAhupArvekSaNAkulAn . nAnADAvayavaiInAMzcakArArIn dhanaMjayaH .
gandharvanagarAkArAn vidhivatkalpitAn rathAn . zarairvizakalIkurvezcakre vyazvarathadvipAn .
muNDatAlavanAnIva tatra tatra cakAzire . chinnA rathadhvajavAtAH kecittatra kvacit kvacit .
sottarAyudhino nAgAH sapatAkAMkuzadhvajAH . petuH zakrAzanihatA dumavanta ivAcalAH .
cAmarApIDakavacAH strastAntranayanAstathA . sArohAsturagAH petuH pArthavANahatAH kSitau .
vipraviddhAsinakharAzchinnavarmaTizaktayaH . pattayazchinnavarmANaH kRpaNAH zerate hatAH .
tairhatairhanyamAnaizca patadbhiH patitairapi . bhramadbhirniSTanadbhizca krUramAyodhanaM babhau .
rajazca sumahajjAtaM zAntaM rudhiravRSTibhiH mahI cApyabhavad durgA kabandhazatasaMkulA .
tada babhau raudrabIbhatsaM bIbhatsoryAnamAhave . AkrIDamiva rudrasya ghanataH kAlAtyaya pazUn .
te vadhyamAnAH pArthena vyAkulAzca rathadvipAH . tamevAbhimukhAH kSINAH zakrasyAtithitAM gatAH .
sA bhUmirbharatazreSTha nihataistairmahArathaiH . AstIrNA sambabhau sarvA pretIbhUtaiH samantataH .
esminnantare caiva pramatte savyasAcini . vyUDhAnIkastato droNo yudhiSThiramupAdravat .
taM pratyagRNaMstvaritA vyUDhAnIkA : prahAriNaH . yudhiSThiraM parIpsantastadAsIt tumulaM mahat .
